#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/02_Tenma_Versus_Aetheryon.cfg:320
msgid "Midori"
msgstr "Midori"

#. [unit], id=Akane, type=Yasai Peasant, gender=female
#. [unit], id=Akane, type=Sogen Huntress
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:204
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/02_Tenma_Versus_Aetheryon.cfg:334
msgid "Akane"
msgstr "Akane"

#. [unit], id=Koko, type=Yasai Peasant, gender=female
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:214
msgid "Koko"
msgstr "Koko"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:248
msgid ""
"Geez, that's so annoying... Kenshiro, you owe me <i>so much</i> for taking "
"care of your mom..."
msgstr ""
"Qué fastidio... Kenshiro, me debes <i>muchísimo</i> por cuidar de tu mamá..."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:264
msgid "Morning, Ms. Ohka!"
msgstr "¡Buenos días, señora Ohka!"

#. [message], speaker=Ohka
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:268
msgid ""
"Good morning, Tenma dear! My goodness, I never tire of getting amazed at how "
"much you've grown; it looked like it was yesterday that I saw you parents "
"returning from the Death Meadows with you on their arms... And to think that "
"your mother lived for nine months in that region, your birth was truly a "
"miracle..."
msgstr ""
"Buenos días, querida Tenma. ¡Dios mío, nunca me canso de maravillarme de lo "
"mucho que has crecido! Parece que fue ayer cuando vi a tus padres regresar "
"de las Praderas de la Muerte contigo en brazos... Y pensar que tu madre "
"vivió nueve meses en esa región, tu nacimiento fue realmente un milagro..."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:272
msgid ""
"But it's not like she and my dad lived in the open, right? You told me that "
"they lived inside that tall mountain to the south."
msgstr ""
"Pero no es como que vivieran a la intemperie, ¿verdad? Me contaste que "
"vivieron dentro de esa montaña alta al sur."

#. [message], speaker=Ohka
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:276
msgid ""
"Mount Kamishiro, yes, they did say they'd lived there, that no animal dared "
"enter that place... But I won't delay you anymore, dear, I see that you're "
"going fetch some water. Have a good day!"
msgstr ""
"Monte Kamishiro, sí, dijeron que habían vivido allí, que ningún animal se "
"atrevía a entrar en ese lugar... Pero no te voy a entretener más, querida, "
"veo que vas a buscar agua. ¡Que tengas un buen día!"

#. [message], speaker=Beoc
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:296
msgid "Out of my way, piglet!"
msgstr "¡Quítate del camino, lechoncita!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:300
msgid ""
"But if you were just standing there doing nothing, how could I have blocked "
"your way to begin with?"
msgstr ""
"Pero si estabas ahí parado sin hacer nada, ¿cómo podría haberte bloqueado el "
"paso desde el principio?"

#. [message], speaker=Beoc
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:304
msgid ""
"(angry) You impudent farmer girl, you should be thankful to Prince "
"Aeldhoryan and to Prince Aetheryon for being so kind on you Sogen! Would "
"that Prince Aelvar was the one ruling this province, then I'd crush your "
"head at your slightest squint!"
msgstr ""
"(enojado) Muchacha campesina insolente, deberías estar agradecida al "
"príncipe Aeldhoryan y al príncipe Aetheryon por ser tan benevolentes con "
"ustedes, los Sogen. ¡Ojalá fuera el príncipe Aelvar quien gobernara esta "
"provincia, entonces te aplastaría la cabeza al menor gesto!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:308
msgid ""
"Right, but the lord in this province is not him, it's your High Lord "
"Graceful Majestic or whatever Prince Aetheryon, and he won't like it if you "
"disobey him, so be a good obedient soldier and leave me be, I'm just a law-"
"abiding girl on the way to fetch water."
msgstr ""
"Claro, pero el señor de esta provincia no es él, es su Alteza el Gracioso "
"Majestuoso o como sea que se llame el príncipe Aetheryon, y no le va a "
"gustar que le desobedezcas, así que sé un buen soldado obediente y déjame en "
"paz, solo soy una chica respetuosa de la ley que va camino a buscar agua."

#. [message], speaker=Beoc
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:312
msgid ""
"(fuming) Just keep walking, you bloody farmer, or I'll get you arrested for "
"troubling my watch!"
msgstr ""
"(furioso) Sigue caminando, maldita campesina, ¡o haré que te arresten por "
"perturbar mi guardia!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#. [message], speaker=Leukothea
#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#. [unit_type], id=Mage_Dummy, race=human
#. [unit_type], id=MaatKarian Chariot, race=mechanical
#. [unit_type], id=Ashura_Dummy, race=undead
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:330
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:537
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:926
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:561
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1271
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/Olokun_Dummy.cfg:17
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/miscelanea/Caravan.cfg:19
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/undead/Shura_Dummy.cfg:22
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:334
msgid "Don't be afraid, girl, I'm not going to harm you."
msgstr "No tengas miedo, muchacha, no voy a hacerte daño."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:338
msgid ""
"Ah, no, that's not it, I was just wondering if you could understand any "
"language I speak. You sure don't look like any folk I know."
msgstr ""
"Ah, no, no es eso, solo me preguntaba si entenderías algún idioma que hable. "
"Realmente no te pareces a ninguna gente que conozca."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:342
msgid "I'd be surprised if you did; I come from a very distant land, you see."
msgstr ""
"Me sorprendería que lo hicieras; vengo de una tierra muy lejana, ¿sabes?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:346
msgid ""
"Oh, so cool! We don't usually receive people from other lands... except for "
"the Wesnothians, but they don't count, they're meanies... so it's always "
"interesting when a foreigner arrives. Feel welcome in our village; if you "
"need anything, just ask me!"
msgstr ""
"¡Qué genial! No solemos recibir gente de otras tierras... excepto a los "
"wesnothianos, pero ellos no cuentan, son unos crueles... así que siempre es "
"interesante cuando llega un extranjero. ¡Siéntete bienvenido en nuestra "
"aldea! Si necesitas algo, solo pídemelo."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:350
msgid "I really appreciate your hospitality, miss."
msgstr "Realmente aprecio tu hospitalidad, señorita."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:354
msgid ""
"*So mysterious... I wonder where he comes from... Ah, if I didn't have to go "
"fetch water for Natsu...*"
msgstr ""
"*Qué misterioso... Me pregunto de dónde vendrá... Ay, si no tuviera que ir a "
"buscar agua para Natsu...*"

#. [message], speaker=Shin
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:373
msgid ""
"And there goes our favourite little troublemaker! How many Wesnothians have "
"you pissed off already today?"
msgstr ""
"¡Y ahí va nuestra pequeña alborotadora favorita! ¿A cuántos wesnothianos ya "
"has hecho enojar hoy?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:377
msgid "None, but the day's still young."
msgstr "A ninguno, pero el día apenas comienza."

#. [message], speaker=Chuusuke
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:381
msgid ""
"You fool, what do you expect to accomplish by angering them? You'll only get "
"yourself killed for nothing! Poor Natsu has had the disgust of seeing her "
"son become a traitor, she doesn't need to lose you as well!"
msgstr ""
"Idiota, ¿qué esperas conseguir enfureciéndolos? ¡Solo vas a conseguir que te "
"maten por nada! La pobre Natsu ya tuvo que soportar ver a su hijo "
"convertirse en traidor, ¡no necesita perderte a ti también!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:385
msgid ""
"(annoyed) Kenshiro is a traitor as much as you, and the Ken-ningen, and the "
"Uma-ningen are, for letting the Wesnothians exploit us all as they wish! "
"Now, leave me alone, I have work to do!"
msgstr ""
"(molesta) Kenshiro es tan traidor como tú, y los ken-ningen, y los uma-"
"ningen, por permitir que los wesnothianos nos exploten a todos como quieren. "
"¡Ahora déjenme en paz, tengo trabajo que hacer!"

#. [message], speaker=Midori
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:403
msgid ""
"Oh, look who's finally come! We were wondering why Miss Natsu was taking so "
"long to kick you out of bed!"
msgstr ""
"¡Oh, mira quién por fin llegó! Nos preguntábamos por qué la señorita Natsu "
"tardaba tanto en sacarte de la cama."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:407
msgid ""
"Seriously, this is so unfair... Those useless Wesnothians could've at least "
"brought us some of their technology if they're going to rule us; I hear they "
"can even resurrect people, I refuse to believe they don't have some machine "
"that collects water for them."
msgstr ""
"En serio, esto es muy injusto... Esos wesnothianos inútiles al menos podrían "
"habernos traído algo de su tecnología si van a gobernarnos; he oído que "
"hasta pueden resucitar gente, me niego a creer que no tengan alguna máquina "
"que recolecte agua por ellos."

#. [message], speaker=Koko
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:411
msgid "Speaking of Wesnothians and dead people..."
msgstr "Hablando de wesnothianos y gente muerta..."

#. [message], speaker=Akane
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:415
msgid ""
"Stop it, Koko, don't tell her anything! You want to get Tenma killed or what?"
msgstr "Para, Koko, ¡no le digas nada! ¿Quieres que maten a Tenma o qué?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:419
msgid ""
"Wait, now I'm curious, what are you talking about? (rolls eyes) Don't worry, "
"I'm not doing anything irresponsible..."
msgstr ""
"Espera, ahora estoy curiosa, ¿de qué están hablando? (revolea los ojos) No "
"se preocupen, no voy a hacer nada irresponsable..."

#. [message], speaker=Midori
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:423
msgid ""
"It's nothing, it's just that... well, we think that we've seen a... Well, a "
"ghost on the other side of the river just now."
msgstr ""
"No es nada, es solo que... bueno, creemos que vimos un... Bueno, un fantasma "
"al otro lado del río hace un rato."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:427
msgid ""
"Wait, does that mean that there's some Wesnothian dark sorcerer doing "
"experiments on our dead...? (suddenly angry) Damn them, won't they even give "
"our dead the right to rest? Even if they're a bunch of arrogant cowards, the "
"Uma will surely not stay quiet if the Wesnothians desecrate Sogen corpses; "
"I'll go there and check this out myself..."
msgstr ""
"Espera, ¿eso significa que hay algún nigromante wesnothiano haciendo "
"experimentos con nuestros muertos...? (de repente enojada) Malditos, ¿ni "
"siquiera van a dejar descansar a nuestros muertos? Aunque sean un montón de "
"cobardes arrogantes, los uma seguro no se quedarán callados si los "
"wesnothianos profanan cadáveres sogen; voy a ir a verlo yo misma..."

#. [message], speaker=Akane
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:431
msgid "Tenma, you promised not to do anything irresponsible!"
msgstr "¡Tenma, prometiste no hacer nada irresponsable!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:435
msgid ""
"This isn't anything irresponsible! If it's true that there are dark "
"sorcerers playing with our dead, our people must know it! Now, be silent, "
"all of you, or else whoever is on the other side of the river will see me!"
msgstr ""
"¡Esto no es nada irresponsable! Si es cierto que hay nigromantes jugando con "
"nuestros muertos, ¡nuestra gente tiene que saberlo! Ahora, cállense todas, o "
"quien sea que esté al otro lado del río me va a ver."

#. [message], speaker=Midori
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:439
msgid ""
"(frightened) Please, be careful! If they catch you peeking on what you "
"shouldn't, they won't be merciful!"
msgstr ""
"(asustada) ¡Por favor, ten cuidado! ¡Si te descubren espiando lo que no "
"debes, no tendrán piedad!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:500
msgid ""
"*So far, so good; the only noises around are the forest's, so there must be "
"no one nearby. Who knows, maybe those silly girls were just seeing things, "
"but maybe I should search a bit further. Besides, the Forbidden Ruins must "
"be nearby... I've always wanted to see them, and, if there's nobody around, "
"why not give them a look...?*"
msgstr ""
"*Hasta ahora todo bien; los únicos ruidos son los del bosque, así que no "
"debe haber nadie cerca. Quién sabe, tal vez esas chicas tontas solo vieron "
"cosas raras, pero quizás debería buscar un poco más lejos. Además, las "
"Ruinas Prohibidas deben estar cerca... Siempre quise verlas, y si no hay "
"nadie alrededor, ¿por qué no echarles un vistazo...?*"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:506
msgid "Search for the Forbidden Ruins in the centre of the map"
msgstr "Busca las Ruinas Prohibidas en el centro del mapa"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:546
msgid ""
"*So these are the ruins the elders talk so much about; the ruins of a very "
"ancient civilization that our ancestors used to to fight all the time... "
"They must have been powerful indeed, for their ruins to have remained so "
"imposing even after all this time...*"
msgstr ""
"*Entonces estas son las ruinas de las que tanto hablan los mayores; las "
"ruinas de una civilización muy antigua con la que nuestros antepasados "
"peleaban todo el tiempo... Debían ser muy poderosos para que sus ruinas "
"sigan siendo tan imponentes después de tanto tiempo...*"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:555
msgid ""
"*Um, seems like there's someone inside these ruins... Well, I can't go back "
"after coming all the way here...*"
msgstr ""
"*Mmm, parece que hay alguien dentro de estas ruinas... Bueno, no puedo "
"volver después de haber venido hasta aquí...*"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:561
msgid "Investigate the Forbidden Ruins"
msgstr "Investiga las Ruinas Prohibidas"

#. [unit], id=Ghost, type=Wraith
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:608
msgid "Ancient Ghost"
msgstr "Fantasma antiguo"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:623
msgid ""
"*That's Prince Aetheryon, overseer of Kodakuni! Is he... talking to that "
"ghost?*"
msgstr ""
"*¡Ese es el príncipe Aetheryon, el supervisor de Kodakuni! ¿Está... hablando "
"con ese fantasma?*"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:627
msgid ""
"Come on, soldier, you can remember what happened next! The trolls, the "
"elves, the dwarves and the humans fled the city when the huge dragon "
"appeared, this High Ascendant Maat stepped forth to fight him, but what was "
"the outcome of their battle?"
msgstr ""
"Vamos, soldado, ¡puedes recordar qué pasó después! Los trolls, los elfos, "
"los enanos y los humanos huyeron de la ciudad cuando apareció el enorme "
"dragón, esta Alta Ascendente Maat avanzó para enfrentarlo, pero ¿cuál fue el "
"resultado de esa batalla?"

#. [message], speaker=Ghost
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:631
msgid ""
"I... She... The dragon... I remained on the battlefield, to fight off the "
"drakes as they duelled, but there was... there was a flash of light... and "
"it was like the world had exploded... Don't question me any longer, that's "
"all I can remember, now please, let me go..."
msgstr ""
"Yo... Ella... El dragón... Me quedé en el campo de batalla, para rechazar a "
"los dracos mientras ellos duelaban, pero hubo... hubo un destello de luz... "
"y fue como si el mundo hubiera explotado... No me preguntes más, eso es todo "
"lo que recuerdo, ahora por favor, déjame ir..."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:635
msgid "*What the...*"
msgstr "*¿Qué demonios...?*"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:657
msgid "(whisper) Damn you, Kenshiro, you frightened me!"
msgstr "(susurro) Maldito seas, Kenshiro, ¡me asustaste!"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:661
msgid ""
"(whisper) As did you! What on earth are you doing here? Don't you know that "
"these ruins are taboo?"
msgstr ""
"(susurro) ¡Tú también! ¿Qué demonios haces aquí? ¿No sabes que estas ruinas "
"son tabú?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:665
msgid ""
"(whisper) Of course I do, but I had to come and see what was going on; my "
"friends said they'd seen a ghost, so I thought that the Wesnothians were "
"desecrating our..."
msgstr ""
"(susurro) Claro que sí, pero tenía que venir a ver qué pasaba; mis amigas "
"dijeron que habían visto un fantasma, así que pensé que los wesnothianos "
"estaban profanando nuestros..."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:669
msgid ""
"(whisper) Yes, he's doing something with the dead, but with those of whoever "
"lived on these ruins, so don't worry. Now, go back to Kuroi at once, "
"before..."
msgstr ""
"(susurro) Sí, está haciendo algo con los muertos, pero con los de quienes "
"vivieron en estas ruinas, así que no te preocupes. Ahora, regresa a Kuroi de "
"inmediato, antes de que..."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:673
msgid ""
"(alarmed) Who's there? Answer immediately, if you don't want to get burned "
"to a cinder!"
msgstr ""
"(alarmado) ¿Quién está ahí? ¡Responde inmediatamente si no quieres quedar "
"reducido a cenizas!"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:677
msgid ""
"(whisper) ...before that happens. Hurry up now, Tenma, if he finds us we're "
"both dead!"
msgstr ""
"(susurro) ...antes de que ocurra eso. ¡Apúrate ya, Tenma, si nos encuentra "
"estamos muertos los dos!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:698
msgid "Return Tenma to whence she came"
msgstr "Regresa a Tenma a donde vino"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:728
msgid ""
"Now, back to the village, and don't you even think of coming back here, "
"understand?"
msgstr ""
"Ahora, de regreso a la aldea, y ni se te ocurra volver aquí, ¿entendido?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:732
msgid ""
"All right, Mr. Shadow Treader, I'm fine, by the way, thanks for asking, your "
"mother is doing great too..."
msgstr ""
"Está bien, señor Caminante de las Sombras, estoy bien, por cierto, gracias "
"por preguntar, tu madre también está muy bien..."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:736
msgid ""
"(sigh) I know I haven't visited you in a while, but I can't simply refuse to "
"accomplish the missions they give me. I'll try to visit you and mother "
"tonight, is that good for you?"
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) Sé que hace tiempo que no te visito, pero no puedo simplemente "
"negarme a cumplir las misiones que me dan. Intentaré visitarte a ti y a mamá "
"esta noche, ¿te parece bien?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:740
msgid ""
"Please, do that. Not for me, but for your mother; she misses you, you know."
msgstr ""
"Por favor, hazlo. No por mí, sino por tu madre; ella te extraña, lo sabes."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:744
msgid ""
"Of course I know, I miss her too. Now, run, and don't say a word about what "
"you did or heard here! If Lord Aetheryon has the slightest hunch that some "
"Yasai was peeking on him, he won't stop until he finds the culprit!"
msgstr ""
"Claro que lo sé, también la extraño. Ahora corre, ¡y ni una palabra de lo "
"que hiciste o escuchaste aquí! Si al señor Aetheryon le surge la menor "
"sospecha de que algún yasai lo estaba espiando, no parará hasta encontrar al "
"culpable."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:845
msgid "What is all this fuss about?"
msgstr "¿Qué es todo este alboroto?"

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:849
msgid ""
"(alarmed) It's the Wesnothians... It seems like they've caught someone... Oh "
"my, they've caught the girl of the Aiyama!"
msgstr ""
"(alarmada) Son los wesnothianos... Parece que atraparon a alguien... ¡Ay, "
"Dios mío, atraparon a la chica de los Aiyama!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:853
msgid "You mean Midori?! I must..."
msgstr "¿Te refieres a Midori? ¡Tengo que...!"

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:857
msgid ""
"Tenma, don't go! This time they're serious, they won't take kindly to your "
"meddling!"
msgstr ""
"¡Tenma, no vayas! Esta vez van en serio, ¡no van a tolerar que te metas!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:861
msgid "I can't let them hurt her! *Especially when it's for what I did...*"
msgstr ""
"¡No puedo dejar que le hagan daño! *¡Especialmente si es por lo que yo "
"hice...!*"

#. [message], speaker=Yuki
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:869
msgid "(desperate) Please, don't take my daughter, she's my only...!"
msgstr "(desesperada) ¡Por favor, no se lleven a mi hija, es mi única...!"

#. [message], speaker=Hwyn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:873
msgid ""
"This is an order by His Grace himself, old man, so stand aside, unless you "
"want to suffer the same fate!"
msgstr ""
"Esta es una orden directa de Su Gracia, anciano, así que apártese, ¡a menos "
"que quiera sufrir el mismo destino!"

#. [message], speaker=Midori
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:877
msgid "(scared) But I-I haven't done anyt-thing...!"
msgstr "(asustada) ¡P-pero yo n-no he hecho na-nada...!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:881
msgid ""
"She's right, you fools, she hasn't done anything! The one your precious "
"Aetheryon wants is me, I was the one who saw him in the Forbidden Ruins!"
msgstr ""
"Ella tiene razón, idiotas, ¡no ha hecho nada! Al que su preciado Aetheryon "
"quiere es a mí, ¡yo fui quien lo vio en las Ruinas Prohibidas!"

#. [message], speaker=Beoc
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:885
msgid ""
"Oh, is that true? My, my, my, the Gods of Light have finally answered my "
"prayers! Finally I'll have permission to give you what you deserve, you "
"brat..."
msgstr ""
"¿Ah, de verdad? Vaya, vaya, vaya, ¡los Dioses de la Luz por fin respondieron "
"mis plegarias! Por fin tendré permiso para darte lo que mereces, pequeña "
"mocosa..."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:889
msgid ""
"Come on then, brave soldier of Wesnoth, come and slay this so very dangerous "
"farmer girl! I bet your name will be engraved on the memory of your people "
"for such deed, right, you coward?"
msgstr ""
"¡Vamos entonces, valiente soldado de Wesnoth, ven y acaba con esta tan "
"peligrosa muchacha campesina! Apuesto a que tu nombre quedará grabado en la "
"memoria de tu pueblo por tal hazaña, ¿verdad, cobarde?"

#. [message], speaker=Beoc
#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:893
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:416
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1508
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:191
msgid "You...!"
msgstr "¡Tú…!"

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:897
msgid "Tenma, stop this folly at once!"
msgstr "¡Tenma, detén esta locura ahora mismo!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:901
msgid ""
"The hell I will! Maybe you can accept them exploiting and humiliating us on "
"our own land without even putting up a fight, but I can't! I will rather die "
"standing than live on my knees!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ni de broma! Tal vez tú puedas aceptar que nos exploten y humillen en "
"nuestra propia tierra sin siquiera plantar cara, ¡pero yo no! ¡Prefiero "
"morir de pie que vivir de rodillas!"

#. [message], speaker=Beoc
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:905
msgid "(enraged) As you wish..."
msgstr "(enfurecido) Como quieras..."

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:914
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1482
msgid "TENMA!!!"
msgstr "¡¡¡TENMA!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:918
msgid "(choking) Now... you may... let her go..."
msgstr "(ahogándose) Ahora... pueden... dejarla ir..."

#. [message], speaker=Beoc
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:922
msgid ""
"Pfff, yeah, right... Rean, take the girl to Lord Aetheryon's tower, she'll "
"tell him everything she knows, even if we have to force her to spit it out."
msgstr ""
"Pff, claro... Rean, lleva a la chica a la torre del señor Aetheryon, le "
"contará todo lo que sabe, aunque tengamos que obligarla a escupirlo."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:926
msgid "N-no...!"
msgstr "¡N-no...!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:943
msgid ""
"*So, is that it? Is this how I'm going to die? Maybe everyone was right; "
"dying for nothing will do no good...*"
msgstr ""
"*Entonces, ¿esto es todo? ¿Así es como voy a morir? Tal vez todos tenían "
"razón; morir por nada no sirve de mucho...*"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:947
msgid ""
"<i>We are the ones who should ask those questions, girl. Is this really how "
"you're going to die, smitten by a soldier's steel without even putting up a "
"good fight?</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Nosotros somos quienes deberíamos hacer esas preguntas, muchacha. "
"¿Realmente vas a morir así, abatida por el acero de un soldado sin siquiera "
"presentar una buena pelea?</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:951
msgid "*What... Who are...*"
msgstr "*¿Qué...? ¿Quiénes son...?*"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:955
msgid ""
"<i>You must remember who you truly are, and what you have once done, and let "
"your power flow out at last. Come, we shall help you...</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Debes recordar quién eres realmente, y lo que una vez hiciste, y dejar "
"que tu poder fluya por fin. Ven, te ayudaremos...</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:959
msgid "*But...*"
msgstr "*Pero...*"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:966
msgid "*Argh...! My head...!*"
msgstr "*¡Argh...! ¡Mi cabeza...!*"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:970
msgid ""
"<span size='large'><i>...You will know it when the time comes. I'm sure you "
"will...</i>*</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span size='large'><i>...Lo sabrás cuando llegue el momento. Estoy seguro de "
"que lo harás...</i>*</span>"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:974
msgid ""
"<span size='large'><i>...W-what on the wide green world is this massive "
"power...?!</i>*</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span size='large'><i>...¿Q-qué es este poder inmenso en el vasto mundo "
"verde...?!</i>*</span>"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:978
msgid ""
"<i>*...Just as a father lives on long after his own death in the blood of "
"his children, Nitiballi still lives in his legacy: all the life that dwells "
"on Irdya...*</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>*...Así como un padre vive mucho después de su propia muerte en la sangre "
"de sus hijos, Nitiballi aún vive en su legado: toda la vida que habita en "
"Irdya...*</i>"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:982
msgid "<i>*...please, allow me to die like this, nestled in your arms...*</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>*...por favor, permíteme morir así, acurrucado en tus brazos...*</i>"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:986
msgid ""
"<span size='large'><i>...I knew I was right in choosing you, my child. I am "
"so proud of you...*</i></span>"
msgstr ""
"<span size='large'><i>...Sabía que había elegido bien al escogerte, mi niña. "
"Estoy tan orgulloso de ti...*</i></span>"

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:1013
msgid "(crying) T-Tenma, w-why did you d-do that...?!"
msgstr "(llorando) ¡T-Tenma, p-por qué h-hiciste eso...?!"

#. [message], speaker=Shin
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:1017
msgid "You didn't have to do that, Wesnothian!!! She was just a girl!!!"
msgstr "¡No tenías que hacer eso, wesnothiano! ¡Solo era una chica!"

#. [message], speaker=Beoc
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:1021
msgid ""
"Keep your distance, you dirty peasants, or I swear that I will crush this "
"puny village of yours!"
msgstr ""
"¡Mantengan distancia, sucios campesinos, o juro que aplastaré esta miserable "
"aldea suya!"

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:1037
msgid "(sobbing) T-Tenma...?"
msgstr "(sollozando) ¿T-Tenma...?"

#. [message], speaker=Hwyn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:1041
msgid "Wait... Captain, you sure you hit her right?"
msgstr "Espera... Capitán, ¿está seguro de que le dio bien?"

#. [message], speaker=Beoc
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:1045
msgid "(shocked) That girl, she should be dead by now...!"
msgstr "(impactado) ¡Esa chica debería estar muerta ya...!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:1049
msgid ""
"It is <i>I</i> who shall crush <i>you</i> if you don't leave us in peace, "
"soldier. This is my first and last warning; you better take it, or I shall "
"obliterate you."
msgstr ""
"Soy <i>yo</i> quien te aplastará a <i>ti</i> si no nos dejan en paz, "
"soldado. Esta es mi primera y última advertencia; más te vale tomarla en "
"serio, o te haré desaparecer."

#. [message], speaker=Beoc
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:1053
msgid ""
"(scared) You puny farmer, I don’t know how you’re doing this, but you must "
"strive harder to impress a Wesnothian! Men, seize her!"
msgstr ""
"(asustado) Campesina insignificante, no sé cómo estás haciendo esto, ¡pero "
"tendrás que esforzarte más para impresionar a un wesnothiano! ¡Hombres, "
"captúrenla!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:1057
msgid "Well, I did warn you..."
msgstr "Bueno, te lo advertí..."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:1061
msgid "'Warden, who gave up your life for the sake of the earth, awake...'"
msgstr ""
"«Guardián, que entregaste tu vida por el bien de la tierra, despierta...»"

#. [message], speaker=Beoc
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:1065
msgid "What are you afraid of, you fools? GET HER!!!"
msgstr "¿De qué tienen miedo, idiotas? ¡¡ATRÁPENLA!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:1069
msgid ""
"'Dragon God from the ancient days, rise! Roar once more, and split the skies "
"in your wake!'"
msgstr ""
"«¡Dios Dragón de los tiempos antiguos, levántate! ¡Ruge una vez más y parte "
"los cielos a tu paso!»"

#. [message], speaker=Chuusuke
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:1073
msgid "(alarmed) Take cover everyone!"
msgstr "(alarmado) ¡Todos a cubierto!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:1077
msgid "RYUUJIN TENSHOU!!!"
msgstr "¡¡¡RYUUJIN TENSHOU!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Beoc
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:1092
msgid "W-w-w-what t-t-t-the h-h-hell...?!"
msgstr "¡¿Q-q-qué d-d-demonios...?!"

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:1096
msgid "(shocked) Tenma, what..."
msgstr "(impactada) Tenma, qué..."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:1100
msgid "(astonished) *This power... Could she possibly be...?*"
msgstr "(asombrado) *Este poder... ¿Será posible que ella sea...?*"

#. [message], speaker=Beoc
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:1104
msgid ""
"(furious) I think I've underestimated you, girl, but even this trick of "
"yours won't be enough to defeat an entire troop!"
msgstr ""
"(furioso) Creo que te subestimé, muchacha, ¡pero ni siquiera este truco tuyo "
"será suficiente para derrotar a toda una tropa!"

#. [message], speaker=Chuusuke
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:1121
msgid "Oh, no, he's going to send the entire sentry corps to kill us!"
msgstr "¡Oh, no, va a enviar todo el cuerpo de centinelas a matarnos!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:1125
msgid ""
"Fear not, villagers; just stand aside, that I shall defeat them, it will "
"only take a while."
msgstr ""
"No teman, aldeanos; solo apártense, yo los derrotaré, solo tomará un rato."

#. [message], speaker=Shin
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:1129
msgid ""
"I-if you say so, then we won't hinder you. Come on, Natsu, everyone, let's "
"not stay on her way, Tenma will protect us from the Wesnothians!"
msgstr ""
"S-si tú lo dices, entonces no te estorbaremos. Vamos, Natsu, todos, no nos "
"quedemos en su camino, ¡Tenma nos protegerá de los wesnothianos!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:1173
msgid "Defeat Captain Beoc"
msgstr "Derrota al capitán Beoc"

