msgid "NOTE: Tenma may recruit from 26,22"
msgstr "NOTA: Tenma puede reclutar desde 26,22"

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:1204
msgid "Captain Beoc has been killed! We must flee!"
msgstr "¡El capitán Beoc ha sido asesinado! ¡Tenemos que huir!"

#. [message], speaker=Beoc
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:1214
msgid "No way... I was defeated... by a farmer girl...?!"
msgstr "¿No puede ser... fui derrotado... por una muchacha campesina...?!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:1218
msgid "I'm not just a farmer girl, soldier; I am..."
msgstr "No soy solo una muchacha campesina, soldado; yo soy..."

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:1295
msgid "Tenma!"
msgstr "¡Tenma!"

#. [message], speaker=Midori
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:1299
msgid "By the Great Kami, what has just happened here?"
msgstr "¡Por el Gran Kami, qué acaba de pasar aquí?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/01_Dawn_Of_A_New_Day.cfg:1303
msgid ""
"Excuse me, villagers, I think I can answer that question. But first, we must "
"tend to Miss Tenma; after such a vast unleashing of magical power, her body "
"must be exhausted and wounded. *Even if she's truly that mage from our "
"legends...*"
msgstr ""
"Disculpen, aldeanos, creo que puedo responder esa pregunta. Pero primero "
"debemos atender a la señorita Tenma; después de liberar tanto poder mágico, "
"su cuerpo debe estar exhausto y herido. *Aunque realmente sea esa maga de "
"nuestras leyendas...*"

