#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:59
msgid "Travellers"
msgstr "Viajeros"

#. [side], type=Saurian Ancient Lich
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/03_Haunted_By_The_Past.cfg:67
msgid "Apepis"
msgstr "Apepis"

#. [side], type=Saurian Ancient Lich
#. [side]
#. [side], type=Lich
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/03_Haunted_By_The_Past.cfg:72
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Black_Elf.cfg:92
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Dwarf.cfg:92
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Troll.cfg:93
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:160
msgid "Undead"
msgstr "No muertos"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/03_Haunted_By_The_Past.cfg:109
msgid ""
"Wait, so we're probably distant cousins! According to our legends, our "
"ancestors too came from the steppes... before they became the Doom "
"Wasteland, of course."
msgstr ""
"Espera, ¡entonces probablemente somos primos lejanos! Según nuestras "
"leyendas, nuestros antepasados también vinieron de las estepas... antes de "
"que se convirtieran en el Yermo de la Perdición, claro."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/03_Haunted_By_The_Past.cfg:113
msgid ""
"There's a lot I could tell you, but our time is short. These caves were once "
"the cradle of a thriving kingdom of dwarves, and a stalwart nation of "
"trolls, until they were invaded by the saurians, allies of the drakes. My "
"people's scrolls tell that those saurians used dark magic in that war, "
"raising what was one of the first large-scale undead armies in recorded "
"history. It's not unlikely that those undead still roam these caves."
msgstr ""
"Hay mucho que podría contarte, pero nuestro tiempo es corto. Estas cuevas "
"fueron alguna vez la cuna de un próspero reino de enanos y una nación "
"robusta de trolls, hasta que fueron invadidas por los saurios, aliados de "
"los dracos. Los pergaminos de mi pueblo cuentan que esos saurios usaron "
"magia oscura en esa guerra, levantando lo que fue uno de los primeros "
"ejércitos no muertos a gran escala en la historia registrada. No es "
"improbable que esos no muertos todavía vaguen por estas cuevas."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/03_Haunted_By_The_Past.cfg:117
msgid ""
"But even if they can't die like we do, after so much time, they're probably "
"quite worn out, right?"
msgstr ""
"Pero aunque no puedan morir como nosotros, después de tanto tiempo, "
"probablemente ya están bastante desgastados, ¿no?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/03_Haunted_By_The_Past.cfg:121
msgid ""
"Actually, no: the oldest the undead, the most dangerous it becomes. Our "
"elementals are strong, but we must still proceed carefully."
msgstr ""
"En realidad, no: cuanto más antiguos son los no muertos, más peligrosos se "
"vuelven. Nuestros elementales son fuertes, pero aun así debemos proceder con "
"cuidado."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/03_Haunted_By_The_Past.cfg:125
msgid "And so you've brought us to a hole full with ancient monsters..."
msgstr "Y entonces nos trajiste a un agujero lleno de monstruos antiguos..."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/03_Haunted_By_The_Past.cfg:129
msgid "Would you rather have fought endless hordes of Wesnothians?"
msgstr ""
"¿Preferirías haber luchado contra hordas interminables de wesnothianos?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/03_Haunted_By_The_Past.cfg:133
msgid "Don't fight, boys..."
msgstr "No peleen, chicos..."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/03_Haunted_By_The_Past.cfg:148
msgid ""
"There! I was right after all; the saurian liches have remained here, in the "
"dark caves where they feel more at home, even after the war's end: the last "
"battalion of the once-dreaded Dragon Army..."
msgstr ""
"¡Ahí están! Al final tenía razón; los liches saurios se han quedado aquí, en "
"las cuevas oscuras donde se sienten más en casa, incluso después del fin de "
"la guerra: el último batallón del otrora temido Ejército del Dragón..."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/03_Haunted_By_The_Past.cfg:152
msgid ""
"They don't look all the same... Was that army composed of that many "
"different factions?"
msgstr ""
"No se ven todos iguales... ¿Acaso ese ejército estaba compuesto por tantas "
"facciones diferentes?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/03_Haunted_By_The_Past.cfg:156
msgid ""
"No; the slender undead are saurian, but the taller ones are trolls, and the "
"short ones, dwarvish. They were clearly killed in the invasion of these "
"caves."
msgstr ""
"No; los no muertos delgados son saurios, pero los más altos son trolls, y "
"los bajos, enanos. Claramente fueron asesinados durante la invasión de estas "
"cuevas."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/03_Haunted_By_The_Past.cfg:160
msgid ""
"Then we must put these brave warriors who died in defence of their home to "
"their deserved rest..."
msgstr ""
"Entonces debemos darles a estos valientes guerreros que murieron defendiendo "
"su hogar el descanso que merecen..."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/03_Haunted_By_The_Past.cfg:166
msgid "Destroy the undead"
msgstr "Destruye a los no muertos"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/03_Haunted_By_The_Past.cfg:182
msgid ""
"Both Tenma and Olokun can recruit from the hexes they're standing at the "
"start of the battle."
msgstr ""
"Tanto Tenma como Olokun pueden reclutar desde los hexágonos en los que están "
"parados al inicio de la batalla."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/03_Haunted_By_The_Past.cfg:203
msgid ""
"Beware now; that's an ancient lich, an undead mage whose powers have grown "
"vaster with the ages; let the elementals attack first and wear him out, then "
"we strike the fatal blow, he's too powerful for us to take of him by "
"ourselves!"
msgstr ""
"¡Cuidado ahora! Ese es un liche antiguo, un mago no muerto cuyos poderes han "
"crecido enormemente con los siglos; dejen que los elementales ataquen "
"primero y lo desgasten, luego daremos el golpe fatal, ¡es demasiado poderoso "
"para que lo enfrentemos solos!"

#. [message], speaker=Apepis
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/03_Haunted_By_The_Past.cfg:215
msgid "Cursssed apes, why don't you DIE...!!!"
msgstr "¡Malditas simias, por qué no mueren...!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/03_Haunted_By_The_Past.cfg:227
msgid ""
"Geez, he spent so much time hating everyone that he's gone nuts; how can "
"anyone choose such existence...?"
msgstr ""
"Qué horror, pasó tanto tiempo odiando a todos que se volvió loco; ¿cómo "
"puede alguien elegir esa existencia...?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/03_Haunted_By_The_Past.cfg:231
msgid ""
"The lure of power and the fear of death, which some find worthwhile to "
"exchange their souls for. That's a common fate for those who immerse "
"themselves in dark magic: unable to die, and shunned by their fellows, "
"they're consumed by hatred for everyone and everything, a hatred that only "
"grows as time goes by."
msgstr ""
"El atractivo del poder y el miedo a la muerte, que algunos consideran digno "
"de intercambiar sus almas. Ese es un destino común para quienes se sumergen "
"en la magia oscura: incapaces de morir y rechazados por sus semejantes, son "
"consumidos por un odio hacia todos y todo, un odio que solo crece con el "
"paso del tiempo."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/03_Haunted_By_The_Past.cfg:235
msgid ""
"Very philosophical indeed, but I hope we don't find many more of these, or "
"we won't even live long enough to see the suns' light again."
msgstr ""
"Muy filosófico, sin duda, pero espero que no encontremos muchos más de "
"estos, o ni siquiera viviremos lo suficiente para volver a ver la luz de los "
"soles."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/03_Haunted_By_The_Past.cfg:239
msgid "Well, in any case just hide behind me, I'll protect you."
msgstr "Bueno, en cualquier caso solo escóndete detrás de mí, yo te protegeré."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/03_Haunted_By_The_Past.cfg:243
msgid "(annoyed) As if I'd ever need your protection..."
msgstr "(molesto) Como si alguna vez necesitara tu protección..."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/03_Haunted_By_The_Past.cfg:247
msgid "Boys, stop, I told you already..."
msgstr "Chicos, paren, ya se los dije..."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/03_Haunted_By_The_Past.cfg:263
msgid ""
"We shouldn't have wasted so much time in these caves! Our presence here will "
"only attract more and more undead, until we're completely overwhelmed!"
msgstr ""
"¡No deberíamos haber perdido tanto tiempo en estas cuevas! ¡Nuestra "
"presencia aquí solo atraerá cada vez más no muertos, hasta que nos superen "
"por completo!"

#. [scenario], id=04_Vengeful_Pursuit
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/04_Vengeful_Pursuit.cfg:4
msgid "Vengeful Pursuit"
msgstr "Persecución vengativa"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/04_Vengeful_Pursuit.cfg:23
msgid "Defeat Prince Aetheryon once again"
msgstr "Derrota al príncipe Aetheryon una vez más"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/04_Vengeful_Pursuit.cfg:39
msgid "NOTE: Both Tenma and Olokun can recruit from 13,4 and 14,4"
msgstr "NOTA: Tanto Tenma como Olokun pueden reclutar desde 13,4 y 14,4"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/04_Vengeful_Pursuit.cfg:101
msgid ""
"You certainly are clever, to have managed to leave Kodakuni unseen, but "
"you'll only advance so far. I told you that I wouldn't give up on you, Tenma "
"Yozora."
msgstr ""
"Ciertamente eres astuta, al haber logrado salir de Kodakuni sin ser vista, "
"pero solo avanzarás hasta cierto punto. Te dije que no me rendiría contigo, "
"Tenma Yozora."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/04_Vengeful_Pursuit.cfg:105
msgid ""
"(affecting abashment) Oh, please, Your High Graceful Lord, you're making me "
"blush!"
msgstr ""
"(fingiendo vergüenza) Ay, por favor, Su Alteza el Gracioso Señor, ¡me está "
"haciendo sonrojar!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/04_Vengeful_Pursuit.cfg:109
msgid "(puzzled) What do you...?"
msgstr "(confundido) ¿Qué estás...?"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/04_Vengeful_Pursuit.cfg:113
msgid "(snorting) Tenma, get serious, he's come to arrest you!"
msgstr "(bufando) Tenma, ponte seria, ¡vino a arrestarte!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/04_Vengeful_Pursuit.cfg:117
msgid "I've come for much more than that, Kenshiro, I..."
msgstr "He venido por mucho más que eso, Kenshiro, yo..."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/04_Vengeful_Pursuit.cfg:121
msgid "(giggling) See, he liiiikes me!"
msgstr "(riendo) ¡Miren, le gustoooo!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/04_Vengeful_Pursuit.cfg:125
msgid ""
"(annoyed) Will you stop this?! (recomposing) As I was saying, I've come for "
"more than just arresting a pair of rebels. I want to know more about this "
"strange magic of yours, which allows you to summon those element-like "
"creatures."
msgstr ""
"(molesto) ¿Vas a parar con eso? (recomponiéndose) Como decía, he venido por "
"más que solo arrestar a un par de rebeldes. Quiero saber más sobre esa "
"extraña magia tuya, la que te permite invocar esas criaturas parecidas a "
"elementales."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/04_Vengeful_Pursuit.cfg:129
msgid ""
"I would gladly teach you about Elemental magic, Prince of Wesnoth, if only I "
"didn't know you'd use it to further strengthen your country's tyranny over "
"this continent's peoples."
msgstr ""
"Con gusto te enseñaría sobre la magia elemental, príncipe de Wesnoth, si no "
"supiera que la usarías para fortalecer aún más la tiranía de tu país sobre "
"los pueblos de este continente."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/04_Vengeful_Pursuit.cfg:133
msgid ""
"You speak from such a lofty moral pedestal, stranger; do your people use it "
"only for altruistic means? Allow me to answer: I doubt that. Everyone, from "
"this Great Continent to Arajunna, always use whatever means they have "
"available to fight against neighbouring peoples, be it for defence or for "
"conquest."
msgstr ""
"Hablas desde un pedestal moral tan elevado, extranjero; ¿acaso tu pueblo la "
"usa solo con fines altruistas? Permíteme responder: lo dudo. Todos, desde "
"este Gran Continente hasta Arajunna, siempre usan los medios que tienen "
"disponibles para luchar contra los pueblos vecinos, ya sea por defensa o por "
"conquista."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/04_Vengeful_Pursuit.cfg:137
msgid ""
"(smirks) Very clever of you, Prince Aetheryon, but I will not fall for such "
"tricks."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo con ironía) Muy astuto de tu parte, príncipe Aetheryon, pero no "
"caeré en esos trucos."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/04_Vengeful_Pursuit.cfg:141
msgid ""
"Then you will fall by my power, and will tell me what I want to know by "
"force. Come, summon your element creatures, let us measure their power "
"against my undead!"
msgstr ""
"Entonces caerás por mi poder, y me dirás lo que quiero saber por la fuerza. "
"Vamos, invoca a tus criaturas elementales, ¡midamos su poder contra mis no "
"muertos!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/04_Vengeful_Pursuit.cfg:160
msgid "I don't understand, what did you mean by 'falling for his trick'?"
msgstr "No entiendo, ¿qué quisiste decir con «caer en su truco»?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/04_Vengeful_Pursuit.cfg:164
msgid ""
"He told me, 'everyone, from the Great Continent to Arajunna', clearly trying "
"to lure me into giving hints that I'm from neither continent; the sort of "
"subtle trick a cocky individual might fall for. Regardless, he must be "
"highly interested, if he's risked venturing outside of his empire's "
"frontiers on his own only to get that information."
msgstr ""
"Me dijo «todos, desde el Gran Continente hasta Arajunna», claramente "
"intentando inducirme a dar pistas de que no soy de ninguno de esos "
"continentes; el tipo de truco sutil en el que podría caer alguien engreído. "
"De todas formas, debe estar muy interesado, si ha arriesgado aventurarse "
"fuera de las fronteras de su imperio solo para obtener esa información."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/04_Vengeful_Pursuit.cfg:168
msgid ""
"If he's so bent on getting this information, then that means we must protect "
"it even harder."
msgstr ""
"Si está tan empeñado en obtener esta información, entonces significa que "
"debemos protegerla aún más."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/04_Vengeful_Pursuit.cfg:180
msgid "Well, there you have it: your undead are no match for our elementals."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, ahí lo tienes: tus no muertos no son rival para nuestros elementales."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/04_Vengeful_Pursuit.cfg:184
msgid ""
"(annoyed) Seems like I have underestimated you again, Tenma Yozora... I will "
"withdraw now, but do not think that I'll give up on you so easily; Wesnoth's "
"sight is far-reaching, and its arm never fails to crush an enemy!"
msgstr ""
"(molesto) Parece que te he subestimado otra vez, Tenma Yozora... Me retiraré "
"ahora, pero no pienses que me rendiré contigo tan fácilmente; la vista de "
"Wesnoth llega muy lejos, ¡y su brazo nunca falla al aplastar a un enemigo!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/04_Vengeful_Pursuit.cfg:188
msgid ""
"(merrily) I'll be waiting for you, dear! Hope you bring me a gift worthy of "
"me next time, for these skeletons were not!"
msgstr ""
"(alegre) ¡Te estaré esperando, querido! Espero que la próxima vez me traigas "
"un regalo digno de mí, ¡porque estos esqueletos no lo fueron!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/04_Vengeful_Pursuit.cfg:195
msgid "(chuckles)"
msgstr "(ríe)"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/04_Vengeful_Pursuit.cfg:199
msgid "Aha! Finally I managed to squeeze a smile out of this stern face!"
msgstr "¡Ajá! ¡Por fin logré sacarle una sonrisa a esa cara tan seria!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/04_Vengeful_Pursuit.cfg:203
msgid "(blushing slightly) Well..."
msgstr "(sonrojándose ligeramente) Bueno..."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/04_Vengeful_Pursuit.cfg:207
msgid "And, as a bonus, a cute blushing!"
msgstr "¡Y de regalo, un sonrojo adorable!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/04_Vengeful_Pursuit.cfg:211
msgid ""
"(smiling) Teasings aside, do you really want to continue on the surface, "
"Tenma? You heard Aetheryon, he won't give up on us anytime soon, and he "
"found us here quite easily. In the undergrounds, not only will we be harder "
"to find, but we'll also be able to better defend against forces larger than "
"our own."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Dejando las bromas de lado, ¿realmente quieres seguir en la "
"superficie, Tenma? Escuchaste a Aetheryon, no se rendirá con nosotros en "
"mucho tiempo, y nos encontró aquí con bastante facilidad. En el subsuelo no "
"solo será más difícil encontrarnos, sino que también podremos defendernos "
"mejor contra fuerzas más grandes que las nuestras."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/04_Vengeful_Pursuit.cfg:215
msgid ""
"Well, you've got a point there... Let's return to those caves then, if it's "
"for the best."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, tienes razón en eso... Regresemos a esas cuevas entonces, si es lo "
"mejor."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/04_Vengeful_Pursuit.cfg:219
msgid ""
"Fine then, there's another of those entrances to the underground on the way "
"to this field..."
msgstr ""
"Está bien entonces, hay otra de esas entradas al subsuelo en el camino hacia "
"este campo..."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/04_Vengeful_Pursuit.cfg:235
msgid ""
"We should have been done with Aetheryon sooner, at this pace we'll be caught "
"by Wesnothian reinforcements!"
msgstr ""
"¡Deberíamos haber acabado con Aetheryon antes! ¡A este ritmo nos alcanzarán "
"los refuerzos wesnothianos!"

#. [scenario], id=05_Inner_World
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:4
msgid "Inner World"
msgstr "Mundo interior"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:20
msgid "Explore the caves after Olokun and Kenshiro"
msgstr "Explora las cuevas después de Olokun y Kenshiro"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:24
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:148
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:192
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:397
msgid "Tenma can't recruit in this scenario"
msgstr "Tenma no puede reclutar en este escenario"

#. [side]
#. [side], type=Ashura_Dummy
#. [side], type=Eternal Night
#. [unit_type], id=Shadow Avatar, race=elemental
#. [unit_type], id=Ashura_Dummy, race=undead
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:50
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:129
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:128
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:128
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:183
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:70
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:190
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:285
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/miscelanea/Shadow_Avatar.cfg:6
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/undead/Shura_Dummy.cfg:4
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/characters.cfg:650
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/characters.cfg:760
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/characters.cfg:880
msgid "???"
msgstr "???"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:72
msgid ""
"*Ouch... Where am I... Oh, yes, we're back to the caves... But where is "
"everyone? I can't believe they left me alone to go scouting... Well, in that "
"case they can't get mad at me if I decide to do the same; perhaps I should "
"summon some of my elementals to guard me, who knows what may lurk in these "
"tunnels...*"
msgstr ""
"*Ay... ¿Dónde estoy...? Ah, sí, volvimos a las cuevas... Pero ¿dónde está "
"todo el mundo? No puedo creer que me hayan dejado sola para ir a explorar... "
"Bueno, en ese caso no pueden enojarse conmigo si decido hacer lo mismo; tal "
"vez debería invocar algunos de mis elementales para que me protejan, quién "
"sabe qué puede acechar en estos túneles...*"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:76
msgid ""
"*Wait a minute, they're not appearing... Have I lost my summoning ability...?"
"*"
msgstr ""
"*Espera un momento, no están apareciendo... ¿Acaso perdí mi habilidad de "
"invocación...?*"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:80
msgid "<i>Tenma...</i>"
msgstr "<i>Tenma...</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:84
msgid "Who's there?"
msgstr "¿Quién está ahí?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:91
msgid ""
"*Silence... Right, now I'm starting to get freaked out; maybe someone or "
"something has captured Kenshiro and Olokun. Let's see, that whisper came "
"from the north...*"
msgstr ""
"*Silencio... Bien, ahora sí que estoy empezando a asustarme; tal vez alguien "
"o algo capturó a Kenshiro y a Olokun. Veamos, ese susurro vino del norte...*"

#. [unit], id=Niti, type=Niti
#. [unit_type], id=Niti, race=trueelemental
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:114
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/true-elementals/Niti.cfg:4
msgid "Niti"
msgstr "Niti"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:134
msgid "You...! Are you... one of my elementals?"
msgstr "¡Tú...! ¿Eres... uno de mis elementales?"

#. [message], speaker=Niti
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:138
msgid ""
"We are no mere elementals, child, we are something far greater. We thought "
"you worthy of materializing us into this world and leading us to battle, but "
"you are unable to even recognize us... Maybe we should bring you back to our "
"own dimension, you're not prepared yet to fulfil your destiny!"
msgstr ""
"No somos simples elementales, niña, somos algo mucho mayor. Pensamos que "
"eras digna de materializarnos en este mundo y liderarnos en batalla, pero ni "
"siquiera eres capaz de reconocernos... Tal vez deberíamos llevarte de vuelta "
"a nuestra propia dimensión, ¡aún no estás preparada para cumplir tu destino!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:144
msgid "Defeat the Niti"
msgstr "Derrota a Niti"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:166
msgid ""
"Wait a minute now, I recognize you; you are the spirits of nature Olokun was "
"talking about, the ones with whom Myra could communicate."
msgstr ""
"Espera un momento, te reconozco; ustedes son los espíritus de la naturaleza "
"de los que hablaba Olokun, los que Myra podía comunicarse."

#. [message], speaker=Niti
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:170
msgid ""
"(pleased) It is so, girl. You have proved me wrong, and proved yourself "
"worthy; the spirits of water shall follow you till the oceans and rivers dry "
"out, and nothing is left but for an arid wasteland."
msgstr ""
"(satisfecho) Así es, muchacha. Me has demostrado que estaba equivocado y has "
"demostrado ser digna; los espíritus del agua te seguirán hasta que los "
"océanos y ríos se sequen y no quede más que un árido desierto."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:182
msgid ""
"*I've defeated him, but I sense more spirits ahead. Maybe if I defeat them "
"all I'll find Kenshiro and Olokun...*"
msgstr ""
"*Lo derroté, pero siento más espíritus adelante. Tal vez si los derroto a "
"todos encuentre a Kenshiro y a Olokun...*"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:188
msgid "Fight the remaining Spirits of Nature to rescue Olokun and Kenshiro"
msgstr ""
"Lucha contra los espíritus de la naturaleza restantes para rescatar a Olokun "
"y Kenshiro"

#. [unit], id=Galli, type=Gali
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:221
msgid "Galli"
msgstr "Galli"

#. [message], speaker=Galli
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:241
msgid ""
"We see that you have overcome the Niti, and recognized us as we are, but "
"that is far from being enough for us. You ignore what we exist for, and thus "
"you cannot possibly fulfil the mission you designed yourself. Maybe we "
"should bring you back to our own dimension, you're not prepared yet to "
"fulfil your destiny!"
msgstr ""
"Vemos que superaste a Niti y nos reconociste como somos, pero eso está muy "
"lejos de ser suficiente para nosotros. Ignoras para qué existimos y, por lo "
"tanto, no puedes cumplir la misión que te propusiste. Tal vez deberíamos "
"llevarte de vuelta a nuestra dimensión, ¡aún no estás preparada para cumplir "
"tu destino!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:253
msgid ""
"I know the reason of your existence, spirits. You are sparks from the "
"essence of Demere herself, the Avatar who gave birth to all life in this "
"universe; you exist to protect this planet and make sure that it's always "
"hospitable for life."
msgstr ""
"Conozco la razón de su existencia, espíritus. Son chispas de la esencia de "
"la propia Demere, la Avatar que dio origen a toda la vida en este universo; "
"existen para proteger este planeta y asegurarse de que siempre sea habitable "
"para la vida."

#. [message], speaker=Galli
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:257
msgid ""
"(pleased) So you have not forgotten everything... You have convinced us to "
"stay by your side; the spirits of air shall follow you until all the "
"atmosphere is burned out and disintegrated."
msgstr ""
"(satisfecho) Así que no lo has olvidado todo... Nos has convencido de "
"quedarnos a tu lado; los espíritus del aire te seguirán hasta que toda la "
"atmósfera se queme y se desintegre."

#. [unit], id=Agni, type=Agni
#. [unit_type], id=Agni, race=trueelemental
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:280
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/true-elementals/Agni.cfg:4
msgid "Agni"
msgstr "Agni"

#. [message], speaker=Agni
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:300
msgid ""
"So you have bested the Niti and the Galli... They wanted you to understand "
"things, but what angers us about you is your sheer weakness. We are the "
"flames that consume everything on our path; why should we serve you in your "
"quest to save all life? Show us that you are worth fighting for, or vanish "
"from this world in ash!"
msgstr ""
"Así que venciste a Niti y a Galli... Ellos querían que entendieras las "
"cosas, pero lo que nos enfurece de ti es tu pura debilidad. Somos las llamas "
"que consumen todo a su paso; ¿por qué deberíamos servirte en tu búsqueda por "
"salvar toda la vida? ¡Muéstranos que vales la pena luchar por ti, o "
"desaparece de este mundo convertida en cenizas!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:312
msgid ""
"It's true that fire can destroy everything, but it's also invaluable for "
"those who know how to wield it. A flame's heat can protect against the cold, "
"and also purify both the waters and the food from diseases, and a flame's "
"light can chase away the darkness. Agni, you are as much necessary for life "
"as all others, that's why I need you."
msgstr ""
"Es cierto que el fuego puede destruir todo, pero también es invaluable para "
"quienes saben manejarlo. El calor de una llama puede proteger del frío, y "
"también purificar tanto el agua como los alimentos de enfermedades, y la luz "
"de una llama puede ahuyentar la oscuridad. Agni, eres tan necesario para la "
"vida como todos los demás, por eso te necesito."

#. [message], speaker=Agni
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:316
msgid ""
"(pleased) You have seen through my destructive façade, and proved that you "
"can use a power of chaos for good. The spirits of fire shall follow you "
"until the last light fades, and all the universe is plunged into frozen "
"darkness."
msgstr ""
"(satisfecho) Has visto más allá de mi fachada destructiva y has demostrado "
"que puedes usar un poder del caos para el bien. Los espíritus del fuego te "
"seguirán hasta que se apague la última luz y todo el universo se sumerja en "
"una oscuridad helada."

#. [unit], id=Bhumi, type=Bhumi
#. [unit_type], id=Bhumi, race=trueelemental
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:339
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/true-elementals/Bhumi.cfg:4
msgid "Bhumi"
msgstr "Bhumi"

#. [message], speaker=Bhumi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:359
msgid ""
"We are satisfied to see that you have proved yourself both worthy and "
"strong, but we deem you to be lacking still. It does not matter how strong "
"you are, you must be willing to use this strength for the sake of others, no "
"matter what happens to you. Show us that you are willing to sacrifice "
"yourself for those you love, or they shall die."
msgstr ""
"Estamos satisfechos de ver que has demostrado ser digna y fuerte, pero aún "
"consideramos que te falta algo. No importa cuán fuerte seas, debes estar "
"dispuesta a usar esa fuerza por el bien de los demás, sin importar lo que te "
"pase a ti. Muéstranos que estás dispuesta a sacrificarte por quienes amas, o "
"ellos morirán."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:387
msgid "Olokun, Kenshiro! Don't you dare do anything to them, you bastard!"
msgstr "¡Olokun, Kenshiro! ¡No te atrevas a hacerles nada, maldito!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:393
msgid "Destroy the Bhumi, even if it costs you your life"
msgstr "Destruye a Bhumi, aunque te cueste la vida"

#. [message], speaker=Bhumi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:415
msgid "Good fight, child, but this is not enough to destroy the earth..."
msgstr ""
"Buena pelea, niña, pero esto no es suficiente para destruir la tierra..."

#. [message], speaker=Bhumi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:422
msgid ""
"Now, you should stop this folly, girl; I am as strong as ever, whilst you "
"are weakened after fighting the other spirits. If you continue straining "
"yourself so much, you will die.!"
msgstr ""
"Ahora deberías detener esta locura, muchacha; sigo tan fuerte como siempre, "
"mientras que tú estás debilitada después de luchar contra los otros "
"espíritus. ¡Si sigues forzándote tanto, morirás!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:426
msgid "(panting) I don't care... just release my... friends...!"
msgstr "(jadeando) No me importa... ¡solo libera a mis... amigos...!"

#. [message], speaker=Bhumi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:430
msgid ""
"(pleased) Enough, girl, you may stop now; we would never truly hurt your "
"friends. You have once again proved that you are capable of sacrificing "
"yourself for those you love, but this determination alone shall be of no use "
"if you do not have the strength to defeat those who threaten your friends. "
"The spirits of earth shall lend you their strength, and follow you until the "
"very earth becomes nothing but dust floating adrift in the depths of space."
msgstr ""
"(satisfecho) Basta, muchacha, puedes detenerte ahora; nunca lastimaríamos "
"realmente a tus amigos. Has demostrado una vez más que eres capaz de "
"sacrificarte por quienes amas, pero esa determinación sola no servirá de "
"nada si no tienes la fuerza para derrotar a quienes amenazan a tus amigos. "
"Los espíritus de la tierra te prestarán su fuerza y te seguirán hasta que la "
"tierra misma no sea más que polvo flotando a la deriva en las profundidades "
"del espacio."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:451
msgid ""
"*I've done it... But I must make sure that Kenshiro and Olokun are both "
"unharmed...*"
msgstr ""
"*Lo logré... Pero debo asegurarme de que tanto Kenshiro como Olokun estén "
"ilesos...*"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:504
msgid "(worried) At last she woke up!"
msgstr "(preocupado) ¡Por fin despertó!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:508
msgid "What... why are you..."
msgstr "¿Qué...? ¿Por qué están...?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:512
msgid ""
"You looked like you were suffering terribly, but you wouldn't wake up no "
"matter what we did! What was happening?"
msgstr ""
"¡Parecías estar sufriendo terriblemente, pero no despertabas por más que "
"hiciéramos! ¿Qué estaba pasando?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:516
msgid ""
"I had a dream... No, it wasn't a dream, I was... communicating with the "
"spirits of nature... I remember it all now, Olokun; who I once was, what I "
"once did, and why I am on this world: I must destroy the Sky Dragon "
"Svarballi once and for all."
msgstr ""
"Tuve un sueño... No, no fue un sueño, estaba... comunicándome con los "
"espíritus de la naturaleza... Ahora lo recuerdo todo, Olokun; quién fui "
"alguna vez, qué hice alguna vez y por qué estoy en este mundo: debo destruir "
"al Dragón del Cielo Svarballi de una vez por todas."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:520
msgid "(smiling) I'm glad that you've finally realised that, Tenma."
msgstr "(sonriendo) Me alegra que finalmente lo hayas comprendido, Tenma."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:524
msgid ""
"Still, I want you to understand one thing: I may have been Myra in a past "
"life, but now I'm Tenma Yozora, and I still have Tenma Yozora's worries and "
"feelings, which means that saving Kodakuni is still an important mission for "
"me."
msgstr ""
"Aun así, quiero que entiendas una cosa: puede que haya sido Myra en una vida "
"pasada, pero ahora soy Tenma Yozora, y todavía tengo las preocupaciones y "
"sentimientos de Tenma Yozora, lo que significa que salvar Kodakuni sigue "
"siendo una misión importante para mí."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:528
msgid ""
"Fair enough. Come, then, these tunnels should lead us to Knalga, the "
"greatest kingdom of the dwarves; all that separates us from them is distance!"
msgstr ""
"Muy bien. Ven entonces, estos túneles deberían llevarnos a Knalga, el mayor "
"reino de los enanos; ¡todo lo que nos separa de ellos es la distancia!"

#. [message], speaker=Niti
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:550
msgid "Perhaps you truly are not ready yet..."
msgstr "Tal vez realmente aún no estás lista..."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:554
msgid "Ugh... I'm not... going down... yet!"
msgstr "Ugh... ¡Aún... no... voy a caer...!"

#. [message], speaker=Galli
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:581
msgid "I expected more..."
msgstr "Esperaba más..."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:585
msgid "Oh, you <i>are</i> getting more...!"
msgstr "¡Oh, <i>sí</i> que vas a tener más...!"

#. [message], speaker=Agni
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:612
msgid "Is that all you have?"
msgstr "¿Eso es todo lo que tienes?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:616
msgid "Oh, I've got much more...!"
msgstr "¡Oh, tengo mucho más...!"

#. [message], speaker=Bhumi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:643
msgid "Are you truly going down with only this...?"
msgstr "¿Realmente vas a caer con solo esto...?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/05_Inner_World.cfg:647
msgid "Takes a lot more... to bring me down...!"
msgstr "¡Se necesita mucho más... para derribarme...!"

#. [scenario], id=06_Underground_War
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:4
msgid "Underground War"
msgstr "Guerra subterránea"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:23
msgid "Explore the caves after any sign of civilization"
msgstr "Explora las cuevas en busca de cualquier señal de civilización"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:39
msgid "NOTE: Both Tenma and Olokun can recruit from 23,44 and 24,44"
msgstr "NOTA: Tanto Tenma como Olokun pueden reclutar desde 23,44 y 24,44"

#. [side]
#. [side], type=Dwarvish Dragonguard
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:73
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Dwarf.cfg:73
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:106
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:105
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:100
msgid "Aurvang Dwarves"
msgstr "Enanos Aurvang"

#. [side]
#. [side], type=Black Elf Barbarian
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:93
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Black_Elf.cfg:73
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:82
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:82
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:122
msgid "Black Elves"
msgstr "Elfos negros"

#. [side]
#. [side], type=Great Troll
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:113
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Troll.cfg:74
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:82
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:105
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:145
msgid "Drokkor Trolls"
msgstr "Trolls Drokkor"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:165
msgid "Beware now, these noises don't seem to come from any peaceful activity."
msgstr ""
"Cuidado ahora, estos ruidos no parecen venir de ninguna actividad pacífica."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:169
msgid ""
"It's possible that there are dwarves fighting Wesnothians ahead; Knalga is "
"an extremely rich realm, I wouldn't be surprised if the empire sought to "
"conquer it as well."
msgstr ""
"Es posible que haya enanos luchando contra wesnothianos más adelante; Knalga "
"es un reino extremadamente rico, no me sorprendería que el imperio también "
"buscara conquistarlo."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:173
msgid ""
"I don't care who we find, as long as they give us something to do; I'm bored "
"to death walking in these empty caves..."
msgstr ""
"No me importa a quién encontremos, mientras nos den algo que hacer; estoy "
"aburrida hasta la muerte caminando por estas cuevas vacías..."

#. [message], speaker=Thrur
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:193
msgid "You tiny vermin, when will you learn to leave us in PEACE?!"
msgstr "¡Pequeñas alimañas, cuándo aprenderán a dejarnos en PAZ?!"

#. [message], speaker=Augdras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:197
msgid "Only when ye learn to get yer stinkin' arses outta our caves!"
msgstr ""
"¡Solo cuando aprendan a sacar sus apestosos traseros de nuestras cuevas!"

#. [message], speaker=Thrur
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:201
msgid ""
"<i>Your</i> caves? The Drokkor Trolls have been living here since before "
"Griknagh merged with the Abyss, and especially since before you snivelling "
"dwarves arrived here!"
msgstr ""
"¿<i>Sus</i> cuevas? ¡Los trolls Drokkor hemos vivido aquí desde antes de que "
"Griknagh se fusionara con el Abismo, y especialmente desde antes de que "
"llegaran ustedes, enanos llorones!"

#. [message], speaker=Shwarzel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:205
msgid ""
"Please, boys, we all know that a land belongs to whoever manages to conquer "
"it, so let us end this useless chatter and decide whoever shall reign in "
"these mountains by our blades!"
msgstr ""
"Por favor, muchachos, todos sabemos que una tierra pertenece a quien logre "
"conquistarla, así que terminemos con esta charla inútil y decidamos quién "
"reinará en estas montañas con nuestras espadas."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:209
msgid ""
"So these are trolls and dwarves? I kind of expected them to be more... "
"civilized."
msgstr ""
"¿Entonces estos son trolls y enanos? Pensé que serían un poco más... "
"civilizados."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:213
msgid ""
"Not all of them are trolls or dwarves; the pointy-eared ones look like "
"elves, but I've never heard of them seeking to live in the underground..."
msgstr ""
"No todos son trolls ni enanos; los de orejas puntiagudas parecen elfos, pero "
"nunca he oído que busquen vivir en el subsuelo..."

#. [message], speaker=Shwarzel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:217
msgid ""
"And look, seems like we've got another contender for supremacy in the "
"Hammermounts! You've come just in time, foreigners, we haven't started the "
"fight yet!"
msgstr ""
"¡Y miren, parece que tenemos otro contendiente por la supremacía en los "
"Montes Martillo! Llegaron justo a tiempo, extranjeros, ¡aún no hemos "
"empezado la pelea!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:221
msgid ""
"Hold on, we haven't come to take this realm! We're just travellers seeking "
"Knalga, we have no intention of fighting any of you!"
msgstr ""
"¡Esperen, no hemos venido a tomar este reino! Solo somos viajeros buscando "
"Knalga, ¡no tenemos intención de pelear con ninguno de ustedes!"

#. [message], speaker=Augdras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:225
msgid ""
"Knalga? Och, human, ye've gone a good deal astray, haven't ye. These are the "
"caves of the Hammermounts, Knalga is far away to the west. But, if ye help "
"us, the Aurvang Dwarves, we'll gladly take ye to our distant cousins."
msgstr ""
"¿Knalga? Vaya, humano, se han desviado bastante, ¿no? Estas son las cuevas "
"de los Montes Martillo, Knalga está muy lejos al oeste. Pero si nos ayudan a "
"nosotros, los enanos Aurvang, con gusto los llevaremos con nuestros primos "
"lejanos."

#. [message], speaker=Thrur
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:229
msgid ""
"Humans, do not hear these treacherous vermin! Our tribe also descends of "
"Groth the Great's tribe, which once fought alongside your folk against the "
"dragons; let us fight alongside each other once more, and we shall help you "
"reach Knalga, where trolls dwell too."
msgstr ""
"¡Humanos, no escuchen a estas alimañas traicioneras! Nuestra tribu también "
"desciende de la tribu de Groth el Grande, que alguna vez luchó junto a su "
"pueblo contra los dragones; ¡luchen junto a nosotros una vez más y los "
"ayudaremos a llegar a Knalga, donde también habitan trolls!"

#. [message], speaker=Shwarzel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:233
msgid ""
"Well, black elves do not need humans to help them solve their problems, but "
"I confess it would please me, to have such good-looking human specimens next "
"to me, so, if you side with Svaryarna, she will commend you to her kin in "
"Lins-Elens, the greatest forest of the elves."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, los elfos negros no necesitamos humanos para resolver nuestros "
"problemas, pero confieso que me agradaría tener especímenes humanos tan "
"atractivos a mi lado, así que, si se ponen del lado de Svaryarna, ella los "
"recomendará ante su familia en Lins-Elens, el mayor bosque de los elfos."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:237
msgid ""
"Seems like we have no way of avoiding this battle... Each one of these "
"factions could be very useful allies, who should we aid...?"
msgstr ""
"Parece que no hay forma de evitar esta batalla... Cada una de estas "
"facciones podría ser una aliada muy útil, ¿a quién deberíamos ayudar...?"

#. [option]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:239
msgid "Let's side with the dwarves"
msgstr "Apoyemos a los enanos"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#. [message], speaker=Thrur
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:253
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:315
msgid ""
"Hrumph! Seems like your people have forgotten our ancient friendship! In "
"that case, we shall crush humans, dwarves and elves alike!"
msgstr ""
"¡Hrumph! ¡Parece que su pueblo ha olvidado nuestra antigua amistad! ¡En ese "
"caso, aplastaremos a humanos, enanos y elfos por igual!"

#. [message], speaker=Shwarzel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:257
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:377
msgid ""
"(sigh) It'll be a pity to slash such gorgeous faces, but you give me no "
"choice..."
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) Será una lástima tener que cortar caras tan hermosas, pero no me "
"dejan opción..."

#. [message], speaker=Augdras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:261
msgid ""
"Wise choice, lads. Now come, let us be done with it as soon as possible, so "
"that we may better know each other in a feast!"
msgstr ""
"Elección sabia, muchachos. Ahora vengan, terminemos con esto lo antes "
"posible para que podamos conocernos mejor en un banquete."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:267
msgid "Defeat the trolls and the black elves"
msgstr "Derrota a los trolls y a los elfos negros"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:283
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Dwarf.cfg:39
msgid "Death of Augdras"
msgstr "Muerte de Augdras"

#. [option]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:297
msgid "Let's side with the black elves"
msgstr "Apoyemos a los elfos negros"

#. [message], speaker=Augdras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:311
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:373
msgid "Pah! I knew humans couldn't be trusted! Strike at them, boys!"
msgstr ""
"¡Pah! ¡Sabía que no se podía confiar en los humanos! ¡Ataquen, muchachos!"

#. [message], speaker=Shwarzel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:319
msgid ""
"That is excellent, humans! Come, let us clean these caves off these filthy "
"brutes, and I shall please you as you wish! I'll really enjoy pleasing such "
"cute humans!..."
msgstr ""
"¡Eso es excelente, humanos! Vengan, limpiemos estas cuevas de estas bestias "
"inmundas, ¡y los complaceré como deseen! ¡Realmente disfrutaré complaciendo "
"a humanos tan adorables!..."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:323
msgid "(whisper) You know, she kind of freaks me out..."
msgstr "(susurro) Sabes, ella me da un poco de miedo..."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:329
msgid "Defeat the trolls and the dwarves"
msgstr "Derrota a los trolls y a los enanos"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:345
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Black_Elf.cfg:39
msgid "Death of Shwarzel"
msgstr "Muerte de Shwarzel"

#. [option]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:359
msgid "Let's side with the trolls"
msgstr "Apoyemos a los trolls"

#. [message], speaker=Thrur
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:381
msgid ""
"I knew I could trust you, humans. In the name of Griknagh, I promise I will "
"repay your aid in full."
msgstr ""
"Sabía que podía confiar en ustedes, humanos. En nombre de Griknagh, prometo "
"que pagaré su ayuda con creces."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:387
msgid "Defeat the dwarves and the black elves"
msgstr "Derrota a los enanos y a los elfos negros"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:403
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Troll.cfg:39
msgid "Death of Thrur"
msgstr "Muerte de Thrur"

#. [message], speaker=Shwarzel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:432
msgid ""
"Agh! How dare you hurt me...! I can't go on fighting like this, I must "
"retreat..."
msgstr ""
"¡Agh! ¡Cómo se atreven a herirme...! No puedo seguir luchando así, debo "
"retirarme..."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:441
msgid "Oh, no, we've let Shwarzel die! Now, we'll be helpless in these caves!"
msgstr ""
"¡Oh, no, dejamos que muriera Shwarzel! ¡Ahora quedaremos indefensos en estas "
"cuevas!"

#. [message], speaker=Thrur
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:463
msgid ""
"May you perish in the utmost darkness of the deepest pity for this, "
"humans... We'll leave now, but this won't be the last you hear of us..."
msgstr ""
"Que perezcan en la más absoluta oscuridad de la más profunda lástima por "
"esto, humanos... Nos vamos ahora, pero esta no será la última vez que oigan "
"de nosotros..."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:472
msgid "Oh, no, we've let Thrur die! Now, we'll be helpless in these caves!"
msgstr ""
"¡Oh, no, dejamos que muriera Thrur! ¡Ahora quedaremos indefensos en estas "
"cuevas!"

#. [message], speaker=Augdras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:494
msgid ""
"Ack! Ye treacherous little humans, hope ye get crushed beneath a "
"landslide...! I have to withdraw now, but I promise ye all ye'll pay for "
"that!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ack! Pequeños humanos traicioneros, ¡espero que los aplaste un derrumbe...! "
"Tengo que retirarme ahora, ¡pero les prometo que pagarán por esto!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:503
msgid "Oh, no, we've let Augdras die! Now, we'll be helpless in these caves!"
msgstr ""
"¡Oh, no, dejamos que muriera Augdras! ¡Ahora quedaremos indefensos en estas "
"cuevas!"

#. [message], speaker=Augdras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:522
msgid ""
"Aha, ye sure fight much better than I expected, humans! Come, I'll give ye a "
"feast, as promised, and then we'll talk business!"
msgstr ""
"¡Aha, seguro que pelean mucho mejor de lo que esperaba, humanos! Vengan, les "
"daré un banquete como prometí, ¡y luego hablaremos de negocios!"

#. [message], speaker=Thrur
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:540
msgid ""
"The Drokkor tribe is indebted to you, tiny humans. Come, our shamans shall "
"tend to your wounds and feed you, and then we'll discuss how we may repay "
"you."
msgstr ""
"La tribu Drokkor está en deuda con ustedes, pequeños humanos. Vengan, "
"nuestros chamanes atenderán sus heridas y les darán de comer, y luego "
"discutiremos cómo pagarles."

#. [message], speaker=Shwarzel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:559
msgid ""
"So, my gorgeous humans, follow me to my palace. I shall put my fairest maids "
"to attend to your every need, and then you shall ask me whatever you want in "
"return."
msgstr ""
"Entonces, mis hermosos humanos, síganme a mi palacio. Pondré a mis doncellas "
"más bellas para atender todas sus necesidades, y luego me pedirán lo que "
"quieran a cambio."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:563
msgid ""
"I won't complain if you send me your finest warriors too; I welcome all "
"kinds."
msgstr ""
"No me quejaré si también me envías a tus mejores guerreros; acepto todo tipo."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:567
msgid "(chuckles) Tenma, Tenma..."
msgstr "(riendo) Tenma, Tenma..."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:571
msgid ""
"Come on, don't tell me you're not going to enjoy having so many pretty girls "
"serving you. I'm sure even Kenshiro will have thoughts of abandoning his "
"warrior's celibate vow..."
msgstr ""
"Vamos, no me digan que no van a disfrutar teniendo tantas chicas bonitas "
"sirviéndoles. Estoy segura de que hasta Kenshiro pensará en abandonar su "
"voto de celibato de guerrero..."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:575
msgid "(blushing) Shut up..."
msgstr "(sonrojado) Cállate..."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/06_Underground_War.cfg:594
msgid ""
"Damn it, we should really be careful with our pace! We'll never reach "
"Knalga, much less, Maat'Kare, if we keep going so slowly!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldición, realmente deberíamos ser más cuidadosos con nuestro ritmo! "
"¡Nunca llegaremos a Knalga, mucho menos a Maat'Kare, si seguimos avanzando "
"tan lento!"

#. [scenario], id=07_Dead_Caves_Black_Elf
#. [scenario], id=07_Dead_Caves_Dwarf
#. [scenario], id=07_Dead_Caves_Troll
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Black_Elf.cfg:4
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Dwarf.cfg:4
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Troll.cfg:4
msgid "Dead Caves"
msgstr "Cuevas muertas"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Black_Elf.cfg:23
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Dwarf.cfg:23
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Troll.cfg:23
msgid "Destroy all undead in the cave"
msgstr "Destruye a todos los no muertos en la cueva"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Black_Elf.cfg:43
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Dwarf.cfg:43
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Troll.cfg:43
msgid "NOTE: Both Tenma and Olokun can recruit from their initial hexes"
msgstr ""
"NOTA: Tanto Tenma como Olokun pueden reclutar desde sus hexágonos iniciales"

#. [message], speaker=Shwarzel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Black_Elf.cfg:220
msgid ""
"I wish those aberrations would stop spilling their filthy arcane dejects on "
"my halls. I should have known that they hadn't disappeared forever..."
msgstr ""
"Ojalá esas aberraciones dejaran de derramar sus inmundos desechos arcanos en "
"mis salones. Debí saber que no habían desaparecido para siempre..."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Black_Elf.cfg:224
msgid ""
"Do you know the source of these undead? If it's a lich or a necromancer, we "
"could help you; it'd be one less threat to worry about when we leave these "
"mountains anyway."
msgstr ""
"¿Conoces el origen de estos no muertos? Si es un liche o un nigromante, "
"podríamos ayudarte; sería una amenaza menos de la que preocuparse cuando "
"dejemos estas montañas de todos modos."

#. [message], speaker=Shwarzel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Black_Elf.cfg:228
msgid ""
"It's so kind of you to help me, but alas, even though I have sent druids to "
"detect their origin, I have no idea where the lair of those undead is."
msgstr ""
"Es muy amable de tu parte ayudarme, pero ay, aunque envié druidas a detectar "
"su origen, no tengo idea de dónde está la guarida de esos no muertos."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Black_Elf.cfg:232
msgid ""
"Well, they couldn't have come from the southern caves, or we'd have faced "
"them before; and, considering that we're far into the Hammermounts, they "
"must come from somewhere in their middle. I think I know a way of locating "
"them, but first we must deal with the ones attacking us right now."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, no pudieron venir de las cuevas del sur, o los habríamos enfrentado "
"antes; y considerando que estamos bastante adentro de los Montes Martillo, "
"deben venir de algún lugar en el medio. Creo que sé una forma de "
"localizarlos, pero primero debemos encargarnos de los que nos están atacando "
"ahora."

#. [message], speaker=Shwarzel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Black_Elf.cfg:236
msgid ""
"I beg you, beware! I would hate to see such lovely creatures hacked by "
"unworthy undead blades!"
msgstr ""
"¡Les ruego, tengan cuidado! ¡Odiaría ver a criaturas tan adorables "
"destrozadas por espadas indignas de no muertos!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Black_Elf.cfg:240
msgid "Right back at you, lady..."
msgstr "Lo mismo para ti, señora..."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Black_Elf.cfg:244
msgid "(rolls eyes)"
msgstr "(pone los ojos en blanco)"

#. [message], speaker=Shwarzel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Black_Elf.cfg:287
msgid ""
"Enough! I am weary of dealing with these disgusting aberrations, I shall "
"wipe them out even if that is my last deed on Irdya!"
msgstr ""
"¡Basta! Estoy cansada de lidiar con estas aberraciones repugnantes, ¡las "
"eliminaré aunque sea mi última acción en Irdya!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Black_Elf.cfg:291
msgid ""
"Calm down, miss, look on the bright side: more enemies mean more experience "
"for your warriors and our elementals."
msgstr ""
"Cálmate, señorita, mira el lado bueno: más enemigos significa más "
"experiencia para tus guerreros y para nuestros elementales."

#. [message], speaker=Shwarzel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Black_Elf.cfg:361
msgid "Tsc, tsc, and I'd just had my halls cleaned..."
msgstr "Tsc, tsc, y justo había limpiado mis salones..."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Black_Elf.cfg:365
msgid ""
"Don't worry, they're nothing that we can't deal with, though we shouldn't "
"underestimate the necromancer summoning them. Lady Svaryarna, I advise you "
"to make a truce with the dwarves and the trolls; fighting too many foes at "
"once will be too much even for your people. The ideal would be to ally with "
"them against the undead..."
msgstr ""
"No te preocupes, no son nada que no podamos manejar, aunque no deberíamos "
"subestimar al nigromante que los está invocando. Señora Svaryarna, te "
"aconsejo hacer una tregua con los enanos y los trolls; pelear contra "
"demasiados enemigos a la vez será demasiado incluso para tu pueblo. Lo ideal "
"sería aliarse con ellos contra los no muertos..."

#. [message], speaker=Shwarzel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Black_Elf.cfg:369
msgid ""
"I know you mean the best for me, human, but never, I say again, <i>never</i> "
"even suggest me to walk alongside those stinking barbarians again. We are "
"black elves; we have conquered the nether-world which everyone thought "
"forbidden to us, and we have become a match for those who have lived here "
"for ages, and so we shall prevail against these undead on our own."
msgstr ""
"Sé que quieres lo mejor para mí, humano, pero nunca, repito, <i>nunca</i> me "
"sugieras volver a caminar junto a esos bárbaros apestosos. Somos elfos "
"negros; hemos conquistado el inframundo que todos pensaban prohibido para "
"nosotros, y nos hemos convertido en rivales de aquellos que han vivido aquí "
"por edades, así que prevaleceremos contra estos no muertos por nuestra "
"cuenta."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Black_Elf.cfg:373
msgid ""
"Well, do as you wish... As for locating the source of the undead, I believe "
"I can do that: whoever is summoning them must be powerful, specially if he's "
"an ancient lich, so I should be able to sense his power if I get near it. "
"However, I'll need your warriors to guide me, for I don't know the "
"Hammermounts."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, haz como quieras... En cuanto a localizar la fuente de los no "
"muertos, creo que puedo hacerlo: quien sea que los esté invocando debe ser "
"poderoso, especialmente si es un liche antiguo, así que debería poder sentir "
"su poder si me acerco lo suficiente. Sin embargo, necesitaré que tus "
"guerreros me guíen, porque no conozco los Montes Martillo."

#. [message], speaker=Shwarzel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Black_Elf.cfg:377
msgid ""
"Then I shall put some of my finest warriors and most skilled druids at your "
"service. Go, locate the disgusting necromancer and return swiftly, or else I "
"will become worried!"
msgstr ""
"Entonces pondré a algunos de mis mejores guerreros y druidas más hábiles a "
"tu servicio. Vayan, localicen al repugnante nigromante y regresen pronto, ¡o "
"me pondré preocupada!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Black_Elf.cfg:381
msgid "Don't worry, miss, I promise I'll bring Kenshiro in one piece."
msgstr "No te preocupes, señorita, prometo que traeré a Kenshiro entero."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Black_Elf.cfg:385
msgid "(rolls eyes) Tsc..."
msgstr "(revolea los ojos) Tsc..."

#. [message], speaker=Shwarzel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Black_Elf.cfg:413
msgid ""
"Curses upon curses on these undead! At this pace, we have no hope of "
"surviving this attack!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldiciones sobre maldiciones a estos no muertos! ¡A este ritmo no tenemos "
"esperanza de sobrevivir este ataque!"

#. [message], speaker=Augdras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Dwarf.cfg:221
msgid ""
"It's been a while since those wispy fellows last appeared... Heh, get yer "
"axes n' hammers ready, boys, it's exercise time!"
msgstr ""
"Ha pasado un tiempo desde que aparecieron esos tipos etéreos... Je, preparen "
"sus hachas y martillos, muchachos, ¡es hora de hacer ejercicio!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Dwarf.cfg:225
msgid ""
"These undead couldn't have come from the southern caves, or we'd have faced "
"them before. Is there any lich or necromancer living in these mountains?"
msgstr ""
"Estos no muertos no pudieron venir de las cuevas del sur, o los habríamos "
"enfrentado antes. ¿Hay algún liche o nigromante viviendo en estas montañas?"

#. [message], speaker=Augdras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Dwarf.cfg:229
msgid ""
"Probably there is, but we've never got to locate it. It's never been much of "
"a problem, though; since my clan first arrived in these mountains, these "
"ghosts have been appearing from time to time, always in small, scattered "
"bunches."
msgstr ""
"Probablemente sí, pero nunca hemos logrado localizarlo. Aunque nunca ha sido "
"gran problema; desde que mi clan llegó por primera vez a estas montañas, "
"estos fantasmas han aparecido de vez en cuando, siempre en grupos pequeños y "
"dispersos."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Dwarf.cfg:233
msgid ""
"(grunts) Do we really need 'exercise time' now? I feel like I got a thousand "
"hammer-mounts to my skull already..."
msgstr ""
"(gruñe) ¿Realmente necesitamos «hora de ejercicio» ahora? Siento como si ya "
"tuviera mil montes-martillo en mi cráneo..."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Dwarf.cfg:237
msgid ""
"You were warned not to commit excesses, now haul your butt off that chair "
"and join the fray."
msgstr ""
"Te advirtieron que no te excedieras, ahora saca tu trasero de esa silla y "
"únete a la pelea."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Dwarf.cfg:241
msgid "Hrumph!"
msgstr "¡Hrumph!"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Dwarf.cfg:284
msgid ""
"More of them are coming... Not that I'm getting tired of anything, but is "
"such a large number of undead normal?"
msgstr ""
"Vienen más... No es que me esté cansando de nada, pero ¿es normal una "
"cantidad tan grande de no muertos?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Dwarf.cfg:288
msgid "Admit it, Kenshiro, you're starting to get freaked out..."
msgstr "Admítelo, Kenshiro, estás empezando a asustarte..."

#. [message], speaker=Augdras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Dwarf.cfg:292
msgid ""
"Och, I've never seen so many of them showing up at once, to be honest... Who "
"knows, maybe they're multiplyin' amongst themselves."
msgstr ""
"Vaya, honestamente nunca he visto tantos aparecer a la vez... Quién sabe, "
"tal vez se estén multiplicando entre ellos."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Dwarf.cfg:296
msgid ""
"Undead do not grow in numbers unless there's someone summoning them. Lord "
"Augdras, when this battle's over I'd like to talk to you about investigating "
"the source of these undead; it's likely that there's a lich living in these "
"mountains since before your people came in."
msgstr ""
"Los no muertos no aumentan en número a menos que alguien los esté invocando. "
"Señor Augdras, cuando termine esta batalla me gustaría hablar contigo sobre "
"investigar la fuente de estos no muertos; es probable que haya un liche "
"viviendo en estas montañas desde antes de que llegara tu pueblo."

#. [message], speaker=Augdras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Dwarf.cfg:366
msgid ""
"I confess that this attack was much harder to repel than I expected... You "
"said that there might be a summoner o' undead in the Hammermounts; do ye "
"think ye can locate 'im?"
msgstr ""
"Confieso que este ataque fue mucho más difícil de repeler de lo que "
"esperaba... Dijiste que podría haber un invocador de no muertos en los "
"Montes Martillo; ¿crees que puedes localizarlo?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Dwarf.cfg:370
msgid ""
"Yes; I can sense any source of magic activity if it's powerful enough, and "
"whoever did summon these undead must be really strong. Furthermore, you "
"should consider the possibility of making truce with the trolls and the "
"black elves, for you'll probably need many fighters to eradicate this "
"necromancer. The ideal would be to form an alliance, even if a brief one, "
"with your neighbours..."
msgstr ""
"Sí; puedo sentir cualquier fuente de actividad mágica si es lo "
"suficientemente poderosa, y quien haya invocado a estos no muertos debe ser "
"realmente fuerte. Además, deberías considerar la posibilidad de hacer una "
"tregua con los trolls y los elfos negros, porque probablemente necesitarás "
"muchos combatientes para erradicar a este nigromante. Lo ideal sería formar "
"una alianza, aunque sea breve, con tus vecinos..."

#. [message], speaker=Augdras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Dwarf.cfg:374
msgid ""
"The truce is a wise idea, but fighting alongside trolls and elves?! Now "
"that's asking too much, boy; besides, we dinna need 'em to fight our "
"enemies, we can do it ourselves!"
msgstr ""
"La tregua es una idea sabia, ¡pero pelear junto a trolls y elfos! ¡Eso ya es "
"pedir demasiado, muchacho! Además, ¡no los necesitamos para luchar contra "
"nuestros enemigos, podemos hacerlo solos!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Dwarf.cfg:378
msgid "If that's your choice... Come on, Tenma, Kenshiro, we have work to do."
msgstr ""
"Si esa es tu elección... Vamos, Tenma, Kenshiro, tenemos trabajo que hacer."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Dwarf.cfg:382
msgid "Aye sir!"
msgstr "¡Sí señor!"

#. [message], speaker=Augdras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Dwarf.cfg:410
msgid ""
"By all Nine Hells, these smoky bastards don't stop coming! We'll end up "
"overwhelm'd here!"
msgstr ""
"¡Por los Nueve Infiernos, estos bastardos humeantes no dejan de venir! "
"¡Terminaremos abrumados aquí!"

#. [message], speaker=Thrur
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Troll.cfg:217
msgid ""
"It's been so long since these smoky creatures last appeared that I had "
"forgotten about them... Stay inside your houses, little friends, you don't "
"need to risk yourself fighting them."
msgstr ""
"Ha pasado tanto tiempo desde que aparecieron estas criaturas humeantes que "
"casi las había olvidado... Quédense dentro de sus casas, pequeños amigos, no "
"necesitan arriesgarse luchando contra ellos."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Troll.cfg:221
msgid ""
"Ah, don't worry about us, we really want to fight these undead too, we're "
"good at destroying them."
msgstr ""
"Ah, no te preocupes por nosotros, también queremos luchar contra estos no "
"muertos, somos buenos destruyéndolos."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Troll.cfg:225
msgid ""
"They couldn't have come from the southern caves, or we'd have faced them "
"before. Is there any mage summoner of the dead living in these mountains?"
msgstr ""
"No pudieron haber venido de las cuevas del sur, o los habríamos enfrentado "
"antes. ¿Hay algún mago invocador de muertos viviendo en estas montañas?"

#. [message], speaker=Thrur
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Troll.cfg:229
msgid ""
"Those monsters have pestered our tribe for ages, but we've never found where "
"they come from. But you seem to know more about them than we do, so, after "
"we get ridden of them, we shall talk about it."
msgstr ""
"Esos monstruos han molestado a nuestra tribu durante generaciones, pero "
"nunca hemos encontrado de dónde vienen. Pero parece que ustedes saben más de "
"ellos que nosotros, así que, después de deshacernos de ellos, hablaremos del "
"tema."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Troll.cfg:272
msgid ""
"And yet more of them are appearing... Is it normal, to have so many of them "
"attacking at once?"
msgstr ""
"Y sin embargo siguen apareciendo más… ¿Es normal que ataquen tantos a la vez?"

#. [message], speaker=Thrur
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Troll.cfg:276
msgid ""
"No, it is not; I've never seen them attacking so strongly in my life, even "
"when I still wasn't chief."
msgstr ""
"No, no lo es; nunca en mi vida los he visto atacar con tanta fuerza, ni "
"siquiera cuando aún no era jefe."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Troll.cfg:280
msgid ""
"This means, almost certainly, that there's a lich or a necromancer living in "
"these mountains – but let's talk about it later, now we have to worry about "
"this battle."
msgstr ""
"Esto significa, casi con seguridad, que hay un liche o un nigromante "
"viviendo en estas montañas… pero hablemos de eso después, ahora tenemos que "
"preocuparnos por esta batalla."

#. [message], speaker=Thrur
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Troll.cfg:349
msgid ""
"That was a difficult fight; our hammers and fists have little effect on "
"those smoky creatures, we wouldn't have done it with our shamans' fires "
"alone. We are even more indebted to you now, little friends."
msgstr ""
"Fue una pelea difícil; nuestros martillos y puños tienen poco efecto sobre "
"esas criaturas humeantes, no lo habríamos logrado solo con los fuegos de "
"nuestros chamanes. Ahora les debemos aún más, pequeños amigos."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Troll.cfg:353
msgid "Don't sweat it, we were defending ourselves as well."
msgstr "No te preocupes, también nos estábamos defendiendo."

#. [message], speaker=Thrur
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Troll.cfg:357
msgid ""
"So, little Olokun, do you think that there is someone creating those... "
"undead?"
msgstr ""
"Entonces, pequeño Olokun, ¿crees que hay alguien creando a esos… no-muertos?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Troll.cfg:361
msgid ""
"I'm almost certain that there is. If I search throughout the Hammermounts, I "
"could locate this necromancer by sensing his power, but I'd need the aid of "
"you trolls to find him."
msgstr ""
"Estoy casi seguro de que sí. Si buscara por todo los Hammermounts, podría "
"localizar a ese nigromante sintiendo su poder, pero necesitaría la ayuda de "
"ustedes, los trolls, para encontrarlo."

#. [message], speaker=Thrur
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Troll.cfg:365
msgid ""
"Then I shall put some of my best warriors and shamans to escort and guide "
"you. Be warned that the Hammermounts are a vast place; you may not easily "
"find this summoner."
msgstr ""
"Entonces pondré a algunos de mis mejores guerreros y chamanes para "
"escoltarlos y guiarlos. Les advierto que los Hammermounts son un lugar "
"vasto; no será fácil encontrar a ese invocador."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Troll.cfg:369
msgid ""
"Necromancers never send their minions too far from where they are "
"themselves, so whoever is summoning these ghosts is seated not far from "
"here. While I'm searching for him, I advise you to form a truce with the "
"dwarves and the black elves; it wouldn't be wise to have so many enemies "
"attacking you at once. The ideal would be to form an alliance with them, so "
"that you could fight these undead together..."
msgstr ""
"Los nigromantes nunca envían a sus sirvientes demasiado lejos de donde ellos "
"mismos están, así que quien sea que esté invocando a estos fantasmas no está "
"lejos de aquí. Mientras busco, les aconsejo formar una tregua con los enanos "
"y los elfos negros; no sería sabio tener tantos enemigos atacándolos a la "
"vez. Lo ideal sería formar una alianza con ellos, para que pudieran luchar "
"juntos contra estos no-muertos…"

#. [message], speaker=Thrur
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Troll.cfg:373
msgid ""
"Hrumph! Your idea is right, little human, but I doubt those arrogant elves "
"or those greedy midgets would ever accept allying with us! But don't worry, "
"trolls are strong and live in great numbers, we'll surely be able to defend "
"ourselves from them while we fight those undead."
msgstr ""
"¡Hrumph! Tu idea es correcta, pequeño humano, pero dudo que esos elfos "
"arrogantes o esos enanos codiciosos acepten alguna vez aliarse con nosotros. "
"Pero no te preocupes, los trolls somos fuertes y vivimos en gran número, "
"seguramente podremos defendernos de ellos mientras luchamos contra esos no-"
"muertos."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Troll.cfg:377
msgid "If you say so... Come on, friends, we have work to do."
msgstr "Si tú lo dices… Vamos, amigos, tenemos trabajo que hacer."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Troll.cfg:381
msgid ""
"(in low voice) Thank the Kami we have, I was getting bored to death here..."
msgstr ""
"(en voz baja) Gracias a los Kami que tenemos, me estaba aburriendo hasta la "
"muerte aquí…"

#. [message], speaker=Thrur
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/07_Dead_Caves_Troll.cfg:409
msgid ""
"Those creatures don't stop coming! At this rate, we're going to be crushed "
"soon!"
msgstr ""
"¡Esas criaturas no dejan de venir! ¡A este ritmo nos aplastarán pronto!"

#. [scenario], id=08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf
#. [scenario], id=08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf
#. [scenario], id=08_Cold_Mountains_Troll
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:4
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:4
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:4
msgid "Cold Mountains"
msgstr "Montañas Frías"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:30
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:30
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:30
msgid "Locate the source of the undead"
msgstr "Localizar la fuente de los no-muertos"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:46
msgid ""
"NOTE: If possible, refrain yourself from killing either the troll or the "
"dwarvish leader; they may be of aid later."
msgstr ""
"NOTA: Si es posible, abstente de matar al líder troll o al líder enano; "
"podrían ser de ayuda más adelante."

#. [side], type=Great Troll
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:76
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:99
msgid "Zurg"
msgstr "Zurg"

#. [side], type=Dwarvish Dragonguard
#. [side], type=Dwarvish Explorer
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:100
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:99
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:74
msgid "Pelaitsil"
msgstr "Pelaitsil"

#. [message], speaker=Thranyel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:173
msgid ""
"This is the Deep Valley, the very heart of the Hammermounts. If you say that "
"the source of the undead is here, I believe you, but I must tell you that "
"we'll come across trolls and dwarves; there are entrances to their caves in "
"this valley."
msgstr ""
"Este es el Valle Profundo, el mismísimo corazón de los Hammermounts. Si "
"dices que la fuente de los no-muertos está aquí, te creo, pero debo decirte "
"que nos toparemos con trolls y enanos; hay entradas a sus cuevas en este "
"valle."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:177
msgid ""
"Good; this way, dwarves and trolls may see for themselves the danger lying "
"at the heart of their lands. Lady Svaryarna may be disgusted at the idea of "
"fighting alongside them, but the truth is that these undead are everyone's "
"enemies, and you could only benefit from fighting together."
msgstr ""
"Bien; de esta forma, enanos y trolls podrán ver por sí mismos el peligro que "
"acecha en el corazón de sus tierras. A la señora Svaryarna podría "
"disgustarle la idea de luchar junto a ellos, pero la verdad es que estos no-"
"muertos son enemigos de todos, y solo podrían beneficiarse luchando juntos."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:181
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:180
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:180
msgid ""
"What a misty region... Where do we search exactly? Is the summoner hidden "
"amidst the forest or inside the surrounding mountains?"
msgstr ""
"Qué región tan brumosa… ¿Dónde buscamos exactamente? ¿Está el invocador "
"escondido en medio del bosque o dentro de las montañas circundantes?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:185
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:184
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:184
msgid ""
"At the centre of this valley. I can sense it... Though I've never sensed "
"such energy before... An energy so oppressive and full of hatred..."
msgstr ""
"En el centro de este valle. Puedo sentirlo… Aunque nunca había sentido una "
"energía así antes… Una energía tan opresiva y llena de odio…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:189
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:188
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:188
msgid ""
"Precisely. Prepare yourselves; if there's really a lich here, he's probably "
"older and mightier than the one we found in the Kodakuni Mountains."
msgstr ""
"Exacto. Prepárense; si realmente hay un liche aquí, probablemente sea más "
"antiguo y poderoso que el que encontramos en las montañas de Kodakuni."

#. [message], speaker=Thranyel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:210
msgid ""
"Finally the stinking brute has revealed himself! Get ready to meet you "
"ancestors, you unworthy animal!"
msgstr ""
"¡Por fin el bruto apestoso se ha revelado! ¡Prepárate para conocer a tus "
"ancestros, animal indigno!"

#. [message], speaker=Zurg
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:214
msgid ""
"Damn these puny vermin, as if we didn't have our hands full with these wispy "
"monsters and the annoying midgets already!"
msgstr ""
"¡Malditas alimañas insignificantes, como si no tuviéramos las manos llenas "
"con estos monstruos humeantes y los molestos enanos ya!"

#. [message], speaker=Pelaitsil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:218
msgid ""
"The troll spoke my thoughts; you, puny weaklings! If you want to die so "
"hard, wait in line, that right now we're busy with other idiots with death "
"wishes!"
msgstr ""
"El troll dijo lo que pienso; ¡ustedes, débiles insignificantes! Si tanto "
"quieren morir, esperen su turno, ¡que ahora estamos ocupados con otros "
"idiotas con deseos de muerte!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:222
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:221
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:221
msgid ""
"Wait a minute, all of you! I know that you hate each other, but can't you "
"see that these undead are enemy to all of you? Please, stop behaving as if "
"you didn't need anyone else's aid; if you don't fight side by side, you may "
"as well be killed side by side!"
msgstr ""
"¡Esperen un momento, todos ustedes! Sé que se odian entre sí, pero ¿no ven "
"que estos no-muertos son enemigos de todos? Por favor, dejen de comportarse "
"como si no necesitaran la ayuda de nadie; ¡si no luchan hombro con hombro, "
"bien podrían morir hombro con hombro!"

#. [message], speaker=Pelaitsil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:226
msgid ""
"Now that was too much! It does not matter how many foes come at once, human, "
"I shall blow them all away with my dragonstaff – and when I'm done with "
"them, I shall blow you away for your impertinence!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ahora sí fue demasiado! No importa cuántos enemigos vengan de una vez, "
"humana, ¡los haré volar a todos con mi bastón de dragón… y cuando termine "
"con ellos, te haré volar a ti por tu impertinencia!"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:230
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:229
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:229
msgid ""
"Give up, Tenma, they'll just ignore you regardless of how many arguments you "
"have. But we can still use them to defeat this summoner: let them take the "
"brunt of the undead assault, then we finish the rest."
msgstr ""
"Ríndete, Tenma, solo te ignorarán sin importar cuántos argumentos tengas. "
"Pero aún podemos usarlos para derrotar a este invocador: dejémoslos recibir "
"el grueso del asalto de los no-muertos, y luego terminamos con el resto."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:234
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:233
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:233
msgid ""
"I didn't say that only to win this battle, I really wanted them to ally with "
"each other; unless they start trying to understand each other, their "
"senseless war will rage on forever, and that's so... insane..."
msgstr ""
"No lo dije solo para ganar esta batalla, realmente quería que se aliaran "
"entre sí; a menos que empiecen a intentar entenderse mutuamente, su guerra "
"sin sentido continuará para siempre, y eso es tan… insensato…"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:240
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:328
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:239
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:331
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:239
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:331
msgid "Find a way to stop the undead wave"
msgstr "Encontrar una forma de detener la oleada de no-muertos"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:256
msgid ""
"Tenma doesn't want to kill the trolls and the dwarves; maybe you should "
"follow her heart..."
msgstr ""
"Tenma no quiere matar a los trolls ni a los enanos; tal vez deberías seguir "
"su corazón…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:284
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:283
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:283
msgid "(alarmed) Watch out, there is a huge wave of undead coming!"
msgstr "(alarmado) ¡Cuidado, viene una enorme oleada de no-muertos!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:288
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:287
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:287
msgid ""
"<i>You fight well, mortals, but you cannot hope to defeat me. I was but "
"dormant, restrained by ancient elven glyphs, but now they're gone, and I "
"shall rise unimpeded!</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Luchan bien, mortales, pero no pueden esperar derrotarme. Solo estaba "
"dormido, retenido por antiguos glifos élficos, pero ahora se han ido, ¡y me "
"elevaré sin obstáculos!</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Zurg
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:292
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:291
msgid "Curses, so many smoky blades...!"
msgstr "¡Maldición, tantas hojas humeantes…!"

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:301
msgid "Damn it, their arcane blades can seriously wound us...!"
msgstr "¡Maldición, sus hojas arcanas pueden herirnos gravemente…!"

#. [message], speaker=Pelaitsil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:305
msgid ""
"Even our hardest steel plate is useless against those bastard's cursed "
"blades... Argh... Though I don't to admit that, ye are all right... Be it "
"then, let's avoid hitting each other for a while, and hit the smoky "
"creatures instead!"
msgstr ""
"Incluso nuestras placas de acero más duras son inútiles contra las hojas "
"malditas de esos bastardos… Argh… Aunque no quiera admitirlo, todos tienen "
"razón… Que así sea, evitemos golpearnos entre nosotros por un rato y "
"golpeemos a las criaturas humeantes en su lugar."

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:309
msgid ""
"Fighting alongside those brutes? I doubt Lady Svaryarna will be please for "
"that..."
msgstr ""
"¿Luchar junto a esos brutos? Dudo que a la señora Svaryarna le agrade eso…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:313
msgid ""
"I'm sure she'll be even less pleased to hear that her precious kin were all "
"butchered by them. Now, let's destroy the undead once and for all!"
msgstr ""
"Estoy segura de que le agradará aún menos oír que a su precioso pueblo lo "
"masacraron todos ellos. ¡Ahora, destruyamos a los no-muertos de una vez por "
"todas!"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:344
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:347
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:347
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:49
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:49
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:62
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:605
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:765
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:633
msgid "Death of any allied leader"
msgstr "Muerte de cualquier líder aliado"

#. [message], speaker=Shadow
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:365
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:368
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:368
msgid ""
"So this age has bred worthy foes after all... Yet no worthier than those I "
"once fought. Greater beings than you sacrificed much to seal me, but now "
"they are gone - whilst I have an army built over the course of five thousand "
"years. When it rises, the world shall finally be mine!"
msgstr ""
"Entonces esta era ha engendrado enemigos dignos después de todo… Aunque "
"ninguno más digno que aquellos contra los que luché una vez. Seres mayores "
"que ustedes sacrificaron mucho para sellarme, pero ahora se han ido —"
"mientras yo tengo un ejército construido a lo largo de cinco mil años. "
"¡Cuando se levante, el mundo finalmente será mío!"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:383
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:386
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:386
msgid ""
"Seems like we'll have to search for him further underground... Damn, we've "
"just fought so hard, and it was all for nothing..."
msgstr ""
"Parece que tendremos que buscarlo más abajo en la tierra… Maldición, "
"acabamos de luchar tan duro y todo fue para nada…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:387
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:390
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:390
msgid ""
"It wasn't for nothing, it allowed us to better assess the enemy's forces, "
"and also who it may actually be. It's just a guess, of course, but what the "
"voice spoke, about how it was sealed once, how its army has been built for "
"five thousand years, and these being the Hammermounts... then our enemy must "
"be the fallen Ascendant of the Order of the Windsong: the Demon of "
"Hiera'Duath, Ashura."
msgstr ""
"No fue para nada, nos permitió evaluar mejor las fuerzas del enemigo y "
"también quién podría ser en realidad. Es solo una suposición, por supuesto, "
"pero lo que dijo la voz, sobre cómo fue sellada una vez, cómo su ejército ha "
"sido construido durante cinco mil años, y que estos son los Hammermounts… "
"entonces nuestro enemigo debe ser la Ascendente caída de la Orden de las "
"Hijas del Viento: el Demonio de Hiera'Duath, Ashura."

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:397
msgid "(frightened) Do you mean Ashura the Demon?!"
msgstr "(asustado) ¿Te refieres a Ashura la Demonio?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:401
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:394
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:394
msgid ""
"All right, now, if you don't mind it, translate all these strange words to "
"me, please."
msgstr ""
"Está bien, ahora, si no te molesta, traduce todas esas palabras extrañas "
"para mí, por favor."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:405
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:398
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:398
msgid ""
"The Windsong are a hidden order of mages and historians, founded more than "
"five millennia ago; they were once powerful, but they disappeared from this "
"continent after the Dragon War. My people's scrolls tell that Ashura was an "
"infamous Ascendant, or leader, of that order: she experimented on living "
"beings, and went as far as to create new species; but when she found a way "
"to the Land of the Dead and started bringing them to this world, elves, "
"humans and even other Windsong united to stop her."
msgstr ""
"Las Hijas del Viento son una orden oculta de magos e historiadores, fundada "
"hace más de cinco milenios; alguna vez fueron poderosas, pero desaparecieron "
"de este continente tras la Guerra de los Dragones. Los pergaminos de mi "
"pueblo cuentan que Ashura fue una infame Ascendente, o líder, de esa orden: "
"experimentó con seres vivos y llegó tan lejos como para crear nuevas "
"especies; pero cuando encontró un camino hacia la Tierra de los Muertos y "
"comenzó a traerlos a este mundo, elfos, humanos e incluso otras Hijas del "
"Viento se unieron para detenerla."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:409
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:402
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:402
msgid ""
"Does this mean that this Ashura was the one who <i>created</i> the dark arts?"
msgstr ""
"¿Esto significa que esta Ashura fue quien <i>creó</i> las artes oscuras?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:413
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:406
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:406
msgid ""
"Precisely. She was the first necromancer, and she wrote down her spells in "
"the Book of the Dead, which is currently kept by my people. The dragons "
"managed to learned its secrets once; they legated that knowledge to an "
"ancient people known as Skironians, whom Wesnothian lore knows as the "
"Wesfolk. Through them, and through the ships of Haldric I of Wesnoth, "
"Ashura's arts made their way back to this continent."
msgstr ""
"Exactamente. Ella fue la primera nigromante y escribió sus hechizos en el "
"Libro de los Muertos, que actualmente guarda mi pueblo. Los dragones "
"lograron aprender sus secretos una vez; legaron ese conocimiento a un pueblo "
"antiguo conocido como los skironianos, a quienes la tradición wesnothiana "
"conoce como los wesfolk. A través de ellos, y a través de los barcos de "
"Haldric I de Wesnoth, las artes de Ashura regresaron a este continente."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:417
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:410
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:410
msgid ""
"As for Ashura herself, after her defeat, her fate was given to the elven "
"King-in-the-Woods to decide. It's said, however, that no art of his could "
"truly destroy Ashura. He then opted to seal her in her own lair of "
"Hiera'Duath with elven magic. Evidently, time has overcome the King-in-the-"
"Woods' magic, while Ashura has used her imprisonment to mass her forces once "
"more."
msgstr ""
"En cuanto a la propia Ashura, tras su derrota, su destino fue entregado al "
"Rey-en-el-Bosque para que decidiera. Sin embargo, se dice que ningún arte "
"suyo pudo destruir verdaderamente a Ashura. Entonces optó por sellarla en su "
"propia guarida de Hiera'Duath con magia élfica. Evidentemente, el tiempo ha "
"superado la magia del Rey-en-el-Bosque, mientras que Ashura ha usado su "
"encarcelamiento para reunir sus fuerzas una vez más."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:421
msgid ""
"So, we're going to face the Mother of all the Undead? Sounds pretty cool to "
"me, but I don't think we'll be able to fight an army that was built for five "
"thousand years – don't you agree, dwarves, trolls, black elves?"
msgstr ""
"Entonces, ¿vamos a enfrentarnos a la Madre de todos los No-muertos? Suena "
"bastante genial para mí, pero no creo que podamos luchar contra un ejército "
"que fue construido durante cinco mil años… ¿no están de acuerdo, enanos, "
"trolls, elfos negros?"

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:425
msgid ""
"(begrudgingly) Well, in this you're right... We, the black elves, remember "
"the history of our kin in the distant forests, and so we know the story of "
"that war, and of the heavy sacrifices demanded in order to achieve victory "
"against Ashura the Demon. You're right, we can't fight her alone."
msgstr ""
"(de mala gana) Bueno, en esto tienes razón… Nosotros, los elfos negros, "
"recordamos la historia de nuestro pueblo en los bosques lejanos, y por eso "
"conocemos la historia de esa guerra y de los grandes sacrificios exigidos "
"para lograr la victoria contra Ashura la Demonio. Tienes razón, no podemos "
"luchar contra ella solos."

#. [message], speaker=Zurg
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:429
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:427
msgid ""
"Trolls are strong and tough, but those smoky blades are really dangerous. I "
"think we have no choice but to fight them alongside the puny... I mean, the "
"dwarves and the black elves."
msgstr ""
"Los trolls somos fuertes y resistentes, pero esas hojas humeantes son "
"realmente peligrosas. Creo que no tenemos opción más que luchar junto a los "
"insignificantes… quiero decir, los enanos y los elfos negros."

#. [message], speaker=Pelaitsil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:433
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:427
msgid ""
"The whole world knows how dwarves are tough, but our hardest steel is "
"useless against the cursed blades of the cursed undead. As much as it "
"displeases me, I say... let us fight together, by all Nine Hells!"
msgstr ""
"Todo el mundo sabe lo resistentes que son los enanos, pero nuestro acero más "
"duro es inútil contra las hojas malditas de los no-muertos malditos. Por más "
"que me disguste, digo… ¡luchemos juntos, por todos los Nueve Infiernos!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:437
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:435
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:435
msgid ""
"Excellent! In this case, your leaders must gather, on neutral ground of "
"course, and plan our invasion of the ruins of Hiera'Duath. I will remain "
"here to guard this valley against more undead, but Tenma and Kenshiro can be "
"at the gathering, to mediate it. Tenma, do you think you can do it?"
msgstr ""
"¡Excelente! En ese caso, sus líderes deben reunirse, en terreno neutral por "
"supuesto, y planear nuestra invasión de las ruinas de Hiera'Duath. Yo "
"permaneceré aquí para proteger este valle contra más no-muertos, pero Tenma "
"y Kenshiro pueden estar en la reunión para mediarla. Tenma, ¿crees que "
"puedes hacerlo?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:441
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:439
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:439
msgid ""
"Of course I do, what I want to know is whether you'll be able to stop a "
"horde of ghosts on your own, should it appear."
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto que sí, lo que quiero saber es si podrás detener una horda de "
"fantasmas tú solo, en caso de que aparezca."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:445
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:443
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:443
msgid ""
"(smiling) Don't worry, I'll just block this passage with my power, not fight "
"the undead. But you must hurry, for I won't be able to block it forever "
"against their attack!"
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) No te preocupes, solo bloquearé este pasaje con mi poder, no "
"lucharé contra los no-muertos. ¡Pero deben apresurarse, pues no podré "
"bloquearlo para siempre contra su ataque!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:449
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:447
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:447
msgid "Stand strong, then, that I promise I'll be back in a blink..."
msgstr ""
"Resiste fuerte entonces, te prometo que volveré en un abrir y cerrar de ojos…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:478
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:476
msgid "No! Without him, we won't be able to get the trolls on our side!"
msgstr ""
"¡No! ¡Sin él no podremos conseguir que los trolls estén de nuestro lado!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:493
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:476
msgid "No! Without him, we won't be able to get the dwarves on our side!"
msgstr ""
"¡No! ¡Sin él no podremos conseguir que los enanos estén de nuestro lado!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Black_Elf.cfg:505
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:503
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:503
msgid ""
"Darn it! We've taken too much time to block that tunnel, now the undead are "
"pouring out of it in too great numbers!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldición! ¡Hemos tardado demasiado en bloquear ese túnel, ahora los no-"
"muertos están saliendo de él en demasiados números!"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:46
msgid ""
"NOTE: If possible, refrain yourself from killing either the black-elvish or "
"the troll leader; they may be of aid later."
msgstr ""
"NOTA: Si es posible, abstente de matar al líder elfo negro o al líder troll; "
"podrían ser de ayuda más adelante."

#. [side], type=Black Elf Barbarian
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:76
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:76
msgid "Thranyel"
msgstr "Thranyel"

#. [message], speaker=Pelaitsil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:172
msgid ""
"'Tis the Deep Valley, friends; right now we're in the middle of the "
"Hammermounts. If ye say that the source of those bastards is here, then I "
"believe ye, but know that we'll come across trolls and black elves; there "
"are entrances to their caves in this valley."
msgstr ""
"Este es el Valle Profundo, amigos; ahora estamos en medio de los "
"Hammermounts. Si dicen que la fuente de esos bastardos está aquí, entonces "
"les creo, pero sepan que nos toparemos con trolls y elfos negros; hay "
"entradas a sus cuevas en este valle."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:176
msgid ""
"Good; this way, trolls and black elves may see for themselves the danger "
"lying at the heart of their lands. Your Lord Augdras may dislike the idea of "
"fighting alongside them, but the truth is that these undead are everyone's "
"enemies, and you could only benefit from fighting together."
msgstr ""
"Bien; de esta forma, trolls y elfos negros podrán ver por sí mismos el "
"peligro que acecha en el corazón de sus tierras. A su señor Augdras podría "
"disgustarle la idea de luchar junto a ellos, pero la verdad es que estos no-"
"muertos son enemigos de todos, y solo podrían beneficiarse luchando juntos."

#. [message], speaker=Pelaitsil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:209
msgid ""
"Aha, there ye are! Prepare to meet yer ancestors, you worthless invader!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ajá, ahí están! ¡Prepárense para conocer a sus ancestros, invasores "
"indignos!"

#. [message], speaker=Zurg
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:213
msgid ""
"Damn these puny vermin, as if we didn't have our hands full with these wispy "
"monsters and the annoying elves already!"
msgstr ""
"¡Malditas alimañas insignificantes, como si no tuviéramos las manos llenas "
"con estos monstruos humeantes y los molestos elfos ya!"

#. [message], speaker=Thranyel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:217
msgid ""
"I find it weird to say that, but I agree with the troll. You, midgets! "
"Wouldn't you wait patiently for your time to be killed? We're already busy "
"with our share of creatures with death wishes!"
msgstr ""
"Me resulta extraño decirlo, pero estoy de acuerdo con el trol. ¡Ustedes, "
"enanos! ¿No podrían esperar pacientemente su turno para morir? ¡Ya estamos "
"ocupados con nuestra propia cuota de criaturas con ansias de muerte!"

#. [message], speaker=Thranyel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:225
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:225
msgid ""
"I've had it with you, human! It does not matter how many foes come at once, "
"I shall crush them all – and when I'm done with them, I shall crush you for "
"your impertinence!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ya tuve suficiente contigo, humana! No importa cuántos enemigos vengan de "
"una vez, ¡los aplastaré a todos… y cuando termine con ellos, te aplastaré a "
"ti por tu impertinencia!"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:255
msgid ""
"Tenma doesn't want to kill the black elves and the trolls; maybe you should "
"follow her heart..."
msgstr ""
"Tenma no quiere matar a los elfos negros ni a los trolls; tal vez deberías "
"seguir su corazón…"

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:300
msgid ""
"By all Nine Hells, our armour is of little use against their strange "
"weapons..."
msgstr ""
"¡Por los Nueve Infiernos! Nuestra armadura casi no sirve contra sus armas "
"extrañas..."

#. [message], speaker=Thranyel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:304
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:304
msgid ""
"Yes, they can cause us some damage, can't they... and our forces are "
"depleted already... (sigh) Well, maybe the human girl was right after all; "
"if we fight together, we have a chance of defeating the undead."
msgstr ""
"Sí, pueden hacernos algún daño, ¿verdad?... y nuestras fuerzas ya están muy "
"mermadas... (suspiro) Bueno, tal vez la chica humana tenía razón después de "
"todo; si luchamos juntos, tenemos una posibilidad de derrotar a los no "
"muertos."

#. [message], speaker=Zurg
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:308
msgid ""
"Hrumph! Though I don't to admit that, you're all right... Be it then, let's "
"avoid hitting each other for a while, and hit the smoky creatures instead!"
msgstr ""
"¡Hrumph! Aunque no quiera admitirlo, todos tienen razón... Que así sea, "
"dejemos de golpearnos entre nosotros por un rato y golpeemos mejor a esas "
"criaturas humeantes!"

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:312
msgid ""
"Och, I ain't sure Lord Augdras will like to hear that we sided with them "
"because we couldn't defeat an enemy on our own..."
msgstr ""
"Och, no estoy seguro de que al señor Augdras le guste oír que nos aliaron "
"con ellos porque no pudimos derrotar solos a un enemigo..."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:316
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:316
msgid ""
"I'm sure he'll be even less pleased to hear that his soldiers were all "
"butchered by them. Now, let's destroy the undead once and for all!"
msgstr ""
"Estoy segura de que le disgustará aún más enterarse de que sus soldados "
"fueron masacrados por ellos. ¡Ahora, destruyamos a los no muertos de una vez "
"por todas!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:414
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:414
msgid ""
"So, we're going to face the Mother of all the Undead? Sounds pretty cool to "
"me, but I don't think we'll be able to fight an army that was built for five "
"thousand years on our own – don't you agree, dwarves, trolls, black elves?"
msgstr ""
"Entonces, ¿vamos a enfrentarnos a la Madre de todos los No Muertos? Suena "
"bastante genial para mí, pero no creo que podamos luchar solos contra un "
"ejército que lleva cinco mil años formándose, ¿no están de acuerdo, enanos, "
"troles, elfos negros?"

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:423
msgid "(mumbling) Och, you have a point there..."
msgstr "(murmurando) Och, tienes razón en eso..."

#. [message], speaker=Thranyel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:431
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:431
msgid ""
"We, the black elves, remember the history of our kin in the distant forests, "
"and so we know the story of that war, and of the heavy sacrifices demanded "
"in order to achieve victory against Ashura the Demon. No, we can't fight her "
"alone; we should ally with you."
msgstr ""
"Nosotros, los elfos negros, recordamos la historia de nuestro pueblo en los "
"bosques lejanos, y por eso conocemos la historia de aquella guerra y de los "
"enormes sacrificios que se exigieron para lograr la victoria contra Ashura "
"la Demonio. No, no podemos luchar contra ella solos; debemos aliarnos con "
"ustedes."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Dwarf.cfg:491
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:491
msgid "No! Without him, we won't be able to get the black elves on our side!"
msgstr ""
"¡No! ¡Sin él no podremos conseguir que los elfos negros estén de nuestro "
"lado!"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:46
msgid ""
"NOTE: If possible, refrain yourself from killing either the black-elvish or "
"the dwarvish leader; they may be of aid later."
msgstr ""
"NOTA: Si es posible, evita matar al líder elfo negro o al líder enano; "
"podrían ser de ayuda más adelante."

#. [message], speaker=Zurg
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:172
msgid ""
"This is the Deep Valley, little friends; right now we're in the middle of "
"the Hammermounts. If you say the smoky creatures are coming from here, fine, "
"but you must know that there are entrances to the caves of dwarves and black "
"elves in this valley, so we'll probably stumble on them too."
msgstr ""
"Esta es el Valle Profundo, pequeños amigos; ahora mismo estamos en medio de "
"las Montañas Martillo. Si dicen que las criaturas humeantes vienen de aquí, "
"está bien, pero deben saber que hay entradas a las cuevas de enanos y elfos "
"negros en este valle, así que probablemente también nos toparemos con ellos."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:176
msgid ""
"Good; this way, dwarves and black elves may see for themselves the danger "
"lying at the heart of their lands. Chief Thrur may dislike the idea of "
"fighting alongside them, but the truth is that these undead are everyone's "
"enemies, and you would only benefit from fighting together."
msgstr ""
"Bien; de esta forma, los enanos y los elfos negros podrán ver por sí mismos "
"el peligro que acecha en el corazón de sus tierras. Al jefe Thrur tal vez no "
"le guste la idea de luchar junto a ellos, pero la verdad es que estos no "
"muertos son enemigos de todos, y solo saldrían beneficiados al luchar juntos."

#. [message], speaker=Zurg
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:209
msgid "Aha! Found those tiny pests! Zurg smash!"
msgstr "¡Aja! ¡Encontré a esas pequeñas plagas! ¡Zurg aplasta!"

#. [message], speaker=Pelaitsil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:213
msgid ""
"By all Nine Hells, as if we didn't have our hands full with these wispy "
"monsters and the annoying elves already, there come more cursed trolls!"
msgstr ""
"¡Por los Nueve Infiernos! Como si no tuviéramos bastante con estos monstruos "
"etéreos y los elfos molestos, ¡ahora vienen más troles malditos!"

#. [message], speaker=Thranyel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:217
msgid ""
"I find it weird to say that, but I agree with the dwarf. You, troglodites! "
"Wouldn't you wait patiently for your time to be killed? We're already busy "
"with our share of creatures with death wishes!"
msgstr ""
"Me resulta extraño decirlo, pero estoy de acuerdo con el enano. ¡Ustedes, "
"trogloditas! ¿No podrían esperar pacientemente su turno para morir? ¡Ya "
"estamos ocupados con nuestra propia cuota de criaturas con ansias de muerte!"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:255
msgid ""
"Tenma doesn't want to kill the black elves and the dwarves; maybe you should "
"follow her heart..."
msgstr ""
"Tenma no quiere matar a los elfos negros ni a los enanos; tal vez deberían "
"seguir su corazón..."

#. [message], speaker=Pelaitsil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:291
msgid ""
"Damn these filthy ghosts! Even our armour has little use against their "
"blades!"
msgstr ""
"¡Malditos fantasmas sucios! ¡Incluso nuestra armadura tiene poco uso contra "
"sus hojas!"

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:300
msgid ""
"Their smoky blades can also cut through our rock-hard skin without problems, "
"we'll be in trouble if they catch any of us..."
msgstr ""
"Sus hojas humeantes también pueden cortar nuestra piel dura como roca sin "
"problemas, estaremos en apuros si atrapan a alguno de nosotros…"

#. [message], speaker=Pelaitsil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:308
msgid ""
"Argh... Though I don't to admit that, ye are all right... Be it then, let's "
"avoid hitting each other for a while, and hit the smoky creatures instead!"
msgstr ""
"Argh… Aunque no quiera admitirlo, todos tienen razón… Que así sea, evitemos "
"golpearnos entre nosotros por un rato y golpeemos a las criaturas humeantes "
"en su lugar."

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:312
msgid ""
"Are you sure that it's better to fight with them instead of against them? I "
"don't think Chief Thrur will like knowing that we helped those tiny vermin..."
msgstr ""
"¿Estás seguro de que es mejor luchar con ellos en vez de contra ellos? No "
"creo que al jefe Thrur le guste saber que ayudamos a esas alimañas diminutas…"

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/08_Cold_Mountains_Troll.cfg:423
msgid "(grumbling) Well, maybe you're right..."
msgstr "(refunfuñando) Bueno, tal vez tengas razón…"

#. [scenario], id=09_Mother_Of_Death
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:4
msgid "Mother of Death"
msgstr "Madre de la Muerte"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:23
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1625
msgid "Destroy Ashura of Hiera'Duath"
msgstr "Destruir a Ashura de Hiera'Duath"

#. [side], type=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:69
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/characters.cfg:813
msgid "Ashura of Hiera'Duath"
msgstr "Ashura de Hiera'Duath"

#. [side], type=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:75
msgid "Hiera'Duath"
msgstr "Hiera'Duath"

#. [message], speaker=Shwarzel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:185
msgid ""
"I don't believe I actually let you make me descend into these stinking "
"tunnels... I'll have to bath in nether-water for three days in a row in "
"order to cleanse my skin."
msgstr ""
"No puedo creer que realmente te dejé hacerme descender a estos túneles "
"apestosos… Tendré que bañarme en agua del inframundo durante tres días "
"seguidos para limpiar mi piel."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:189
msgid ""
"I have to agree with her, the air here is just gross; not only does it "
"stink, but it feels somehow sticky..."
msgstr ""
"Tengo que estar de acuerdo con ella, el aire aquí es simplemente asqueroso; "
"no solo apesta, sino que se siente de alguna manera pegajoso…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:193
msgid ""
"It smells to corpses, and corpses that have rotten here for five thousand "
"years. We have entered the tunnels of Hiera'Duath, the cursed underground "
"Foundation of the Windsong."
msgstr ""
"Huele a cadáveres, y cadáveres que han podrido aquí durante cinco mil años. "
"Hemos entrado en los túneles de Hiera'Duath, la maldita Fundación "
"Subterránea de las Hijas del Viento."

#. [message], speaker=Augdras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:197
msgid ""
"Well, I don't know who exactly lives in these sorry caves, but it doesn't "
"matter, we shall crush them all the same. C'mon fighters, we can't let our "
"'friends' have the highest body count!"
msgstr ""
"Bueno, no sé exactamente quién vive en estas cuevas lamentables, pero no "
"importa, los aplastaremos igual. ¡Vamos, luchadores, no podemos dejar que "
"nuestros «amigos» tengan el mayor conteo de cuerpos!"

#. [message], speaker=Thrur
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:201
msgid ""
"This darkness is where we like fighting, warriors! Attack and leave no enemy "
"standing!"
msgstr ""
"¡Esta oscuridad es donde nos gusta luchar, guerreros! ¡Ataquen y no dejen a "
"ningún enemigo de pie!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:205
msgid ""
"<i>Ah... After so long, someone has come to make me company... Make "
"yourselves comfortable; you have an eternity ahead of you down here...</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Ah… Después de tanto tiempo, alguien ha venido a hacerme compañía… "
"Pónganse cómodos; tienen una eternidad por delante aquí abajo…</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:209
msgid "We'll see about that."
msgstr "Ya veremos eso."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:213
msgid ""
"Olokun... Leave her to me. A being that powerful, I don't think usual means "
"or even your magic will be a match for her..."
msgstr ""
"Olokun… Déjamela a mí. Un ser tan poderoso, no creo que los medios "
"habituales ni siquiera tu magia sean rival para ella…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:217
msgid "I see... *Could this be another memory from her life as a Windsong...?*"
msgstr ""
"Entiendo… *¿Podría ser este otro recuerdo de su vida como una Hija del "
"Viento…?*"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:240
msgid "And so you reveal yourself, Demon of Hiera'Duath."
msgstr "Y así te revelas, Demonio de Hiera'Duath."

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:245
msgid ""
"Demon? Yes, that was what they once called me, when I dared expand the "
"horizons of our knowledge in ways no one else had: Ashura the Demon, Ashura "
"the Dark Ascendant, Ashura the "
msgstr ""
"¿Demonio? Sí, así me llamaban una vez, cuando me atreví a expandir los "
"horizontes de nuestro conocimiento de formas que nadie más había hecho: "
"Ashura la Demonio, Ashura la Ascendente Oscura, Ashura la "

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:250
msgid ""
"But tell me, young one... The surface world has been closed to me for a long "
"time, yet I have witnessed the stirrings in the Land of the Dead as those "
"who wield my arts breach into it, aspiring to harness its power. Once, I "
"witnessed one who very nearly brought down the gates of Death itself; more "
"than once, I witnessed <i>elves</i> attempt to master Death. Once, I "
"witnessed an empire rise through the path I carved, and even now another "
"follows in its ancestors' steps. A <i>demon's</i> legacy would never have "
"been embraced by so many, young one. The truth you refuse to see, like my "
"sisters of old, like those foolish elves, is that what I achieved was "
"<i>greatness</i>."
msgstr ""
"Pero dime, joven… El mundo de la superficie me ha estado cerrado por mucho "
"tiempo, sin embargo he presenciado los movimientos en la Tierra de los "
"Muertos mientras aquellos que manejan mis artes irrumpen en ella, aspirando "
"a aprovechar su poder. Una vez presencié a uno que casi derribó las puertas "
"de la Muerte misma; más de una vez presencié a <i>elfos</i> intentar dominar "
"la Muerte. Una vez presencié un imperio alzarse a través del camino que yo "
"tracé, y ahora otro sigue los pasos de sus ancestros. El legado de un "
"<i>demonio</i> nunca habría sido abrazado por tantos, joven. La verdad que "
"te niegas a ver, como mis antiguas hermanas, como esos elfos necios, es que "
"lo que logré fue <i>grandeza</i>."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:254
msgid ""
"All you have achieved is the corruption of life, Ashura, and the only ones "
"who embrace your legacy are those as twisted as you."
msgstr ""
"Todo lo que has logrado es la corrupción de la vida, Ashura, y los únicos "
"que abrazan tu legado son aquellos tan retorcidos como tú."

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:259
msgid ""
"Corruption? No... <i>Improvement</i>. Life is frail and weak; to try and "
"transcend it is in the nature of all sentient races - and my arts have "
"allowed me, and all those who embrace them, to achieve the oldest dream of "
"all, the prerogative of the gods themselves: <i>immortality</i>. Everyone "
"who once opposed and condemned me has long turned to dust... Yet I still "
"stand on this world, and once I escape this tomb I shall raise the bones of "
"my old foes to fight for me at last!"
msgstr ""
"¿Corrupción? No… <i>Mejora</i>. La vida es frágil y débil; intentar "
"trascenderla está en la naturaleza de todas las razas conscientes —y mis "
"artes me han permitido a mí, y a todos los que las abrazan, lograr el sueño "
"más antiguo de todos, el privilegio de los dioses mismos: <i>inmortalidad</"
"i>. Todos los que alguna vez se opusieron y me condenaron hace mucho se "
"convirtieron en polvo… Sin embargo yo aún permanezco en este mundo, y una "
"vez que escape de esta tumba levantaré los huesos de mis viejos enemigos "
"para que luchen por mí al fin."

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:278
msgid ""
"(laughing) Poor idiots, do you think that will be enough to destroy me? I "
"have lived for five thousand years, I have walked on realms no one else has "
"and my name made even the greatest lords of elves and dwarves tremble; such "
"base weapons and creatures shall never be able to destroy me!"
msgstr ""
"(riendo) Pobres idiotas, ¿creen que eso será suficiente para destruirme? He "
"vivido durante cinco mil años, he caminado por reinos que nadie más ha "
"pisado y mi nombre hizo temblar incluso a los mayores señores de elfos y "
"enanos; ¡armas y criaturas tan bajas nunca podrán destruirme!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:285
msgid ""
"Blast it, if we can't defeat her by destroying her body, how will we prevail?"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldición, si no podemos derrotarla destruyendo su cuerpo, cómo vamos a "
"prevalecer?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:289
msgid ""
"If neither physical weapons nor my magic has any effect on her, maybe a "
"different power will... Tenma, use your strongest attack on her; I doubt "
"even Ashura will be able to withstand the power of Irdya itself."
msgstr ""
"Si ni las armas físicas ni mi magia tienen efecto sobre ella, tal vez un "
"poder diferente sí… Tenma, usa tu ataque más fuerte contra ella; dudo que "
"incluso Ashura pueda resistir el poder de Irdya mismo."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:293
msgid ""
"Still, if you face her alone you'll be at danger; let us wear her out first, "
"then you strike her the final blow."
msgstr ""
"Aun así, si la enfrentas sola estarás en peligro; dejémosla agotada primero, "
"luego tú le das el golpe final."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:297
msgid "Got it..."
msgstr "Entendido…"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:303
msgid "Destroy Ashura with Tenma's Ryujin Tenshou attack"
msgstr "Destruir a Ashura con el ataque Ryujin Tenshou de Tenma"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:340
msgid "ARGHHH!!! What... What is this power... Who on Irdya are you...?!"
msgstr "¡ARGHHH! ¿Qué… qué es este poder… quién en Irdya eres tú…?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:344
msgid ""
"I'm Tenma Yozora, the one the spirits of nature have seen fit to wield their "
"power; and in their name, I will stop your corruption of life and death!"
msgstr ""
"Soy Tenma Yozora, aquella a quien los espíritus de la naturaleza han "
"considerado digna de empuñar su poder; ¡y en su nombre detendré tu "
"corrupción de la vida y la muerte!"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:349
msgid "I haven't endured all this time... to fall this easily...!!!"
msgstr "¡No he soportado todo este tiempo… para caer tan fácilmente…!"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:363
msgid "Damn it all, what did she do now?"
msgstr "¡Maldición, qué hizo ahora!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:367
msgid "I believe... no, she definitely plunged into the Land of the Dead..."
msgstr "Creo… no, definitivamente se sumergió en la Tierra de los Muertos…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:371
msgid "So she's not really gone?"
msgstr "¿Entonces no se fue realmente?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:375
msgid ""
"Actually, to all effects she is. She's powerful and knowledgeable enough to "
"preserve her mind and soul while in the realm, but her physical form will be "
"destroyed, barring her from returning to this plane... so long as nobody "
"brings her back, that is."
msgstr ""
"En realidad, a todos los efectos sí se fue. Es lo suficientemente poderosa y "
"conocedora para preservar su mente y alma mientras está en ese reino, pero "
"su forma física será destruida, impidiéndole regresar a este plano… siempre "
"y cuando nadie la traiga de vuelta, claro."

#. [message], speaker=Shwarzel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:379
msgid ""
"Let that be a concern for another time, however. For now, victory is "
"achieved - and no small share of the glory lies on the human girl's "
"shoulders."
msgstr ""
"Que eso sea una preocupación para otro momento. Por ahora, la victoria está "
"lograda… y no poca parte de la gloria recae sobre los hombros de la chica "
"humana."

#. [message], speaker=Thrur
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:383
msgid ""
"Argh, can't believe I'm saying this but I make the elf's words mine. There "
"was no way we would have won this battle without you, human; for this we are "
"grateful."
msgstr ""
"Argh, no puedo creer que esté diciendo esto, pero comparto las palabras de "
"la elfa. No había forma de que ganáramos esta batalla sin ustedes, humanos; "
"por eso les estamos agradecidos."

#. [message], speaker=Augdras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:387
msgid ""
"Aye, we probably wouldn't even have survived that damn witch's attack "
"without these humans' strength and knowledge."
msgstr ""
"Sí, probablemente ni siquiera habríamos sobrevivido al ataque de esa maldita "
"bruja sin la fuerza y el conocimiento de estos humanos."

#. [message], speaker=Augdras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:397
msgid ""
"Still, ye have done us a great service, friends. As a token of gratitude, I "
"shall let you choose whichever of me fighters you want, to follow and aid "
"you in your quests henceforth. Those who have already fought for you pledge "
"the same; they've taken a shine to you, and want to make sure you reach the "
"end of your journey safe and sound."
msgstr ""
"Aun así, nos han prestado un gran servicio, amigos. Como muestra de "
"gratitud, les permitiré elegir a cualquiera de mis luchadores que deseen, "
"para que los sigan y ayuden en sus misiones de ahora en adelante. Los que ya "
"han luchado por ustedes juran lo mismo; les han tomado cariño y quieren "
"asegurarse de que lleguen al final de su viaje sanos y salvos."

#. [message], speaker=Shwarzel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:401
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:458
msgid ""
"I can't spare any warrior, but I shall give you a map on the regions between "
"the Hammermounts and Knalga, so you won't get lost."
msgstr ""
"No puedo prescindir de ningún guerrero, pero les daré un mapa de las "
"regiones entre los Hammermounts y Knalga, para que no se pierdan."

#. [message], speaker=Thrur
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:405
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:510
msgid "And I shall give you provisions for your journey!"
msgstr "¡Y yo les daré provisiones para su viaje!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:409
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:466
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:514
msgid "Thank you very much, friends, we could really use the help..."
msgstr "Muchas gracias, amigos, realmente podríamos usar la ayuda…"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:414
msgid "What dwarvish unit do you want in your army?"
msgstr "¿Qué unidad enana quieres en tu ejército?"

#. [option]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:416
msgid "Dwarvish Fighter"
msgstr "Luchador enano"

#. [option]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:425
msgid "Dwarvish Guardsman"
msgstr "Guardia enano"

#. [option]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:434
msgid "Dwarvish Thunderer"
msgstr "Atronador enano"

#. [message], speaker=Thrur
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:454
msgid ""
"But you have still done us a great service, little friends. To show you my "
"people's gratitude, I shall put some of my younger fighters at your service. "
"They may not be strong now, but under your leadership they'll become "
"powerful and loyal warriors. And those who have already fought for you shall "
"stay with you."
msgstr ""
"Pero aún así nos han prestado un gran servicio, pequeños amigos. Para "
"mostrarles la gratitud de mi pueblo, pondré a algunos de mis luchadores más "
"jóvenes a su servicio. Puede que ahora no sean fuertes, pero bajo su "
"liderazgo se convertirán en guerreros poderosos y leales. Y los que ya han "
"luchado por ustedes se quedarán con ustedes."

#. [message], speaker=Augdras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:462
msgid "And I shall give ye provisions and gold for your journey!"
msgstr "¡Y yo les daré provisiones y oro para su viaje!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:471
msgid "What troll unit do you want in your army?"
msgstr "¿Qué unidad troll quieres en tu ejército?"

#. [option]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:473
msgid "Troll Whelp"
msgstr "Cría de trol"

#. [option]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:482
msgid "Troll Hero"
msgstr "Héroe trol"

#. [message], speaker=Shwarzel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:502
msgid ""
"But a mere 'thank you' is not enough to show you our gratitude; in addition "
"to the ones who have already fought for you, I shall order some of my "
"warriors or shamans to follow you as if following me. Choose whoever you "
"want, and they shall fight for you to death or until you free them from "
"their duties."
msgstr ""
"Pero un simple «gracias» no es suficiente para mostrarles nuestra gratitud; "
"además de los que ya han luchado por ustedes, ordenaré que algunos de mis "
"guerreros o chamanes los sigan como si me siguieran a mí. Elijan a quien "
"quieran, y lucharán por ustedes hasta la muerte o hasta que los liberen de "
"sus deberes."

#. [message], speaker=Augdras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:506
msgid ""
"I can't spare any warrior, but I shall give you a map on the regions between "
"the Hammermounts and Knalga and an amount of gold."
msgstr ""
"No puedo prescindir de ningún guerrero, pero les daré un mapa de las "
"regiones entre los Hammermounts y Knalga y una cantidad de oro."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:519
msgid "What black-elvish unit do you want in your army?"
msgstr "¿Qué unidad elfo negro quieres en tu ejército?"

#. [option]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:521
msgid "Black Elf Fighter"
msgstr "Luchador Elfo Negro"

#. [option]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:530
msgid "Black Elf Crossbowman"
msgstr "Ballestero Elfo Negro"

#. [option]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:539
msgid "Black Elf Shaman"
msgstr "Chamán Elfo Negro"

#. [option]
#. [unit_type], id=Cave Rider, race=blackelf
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:548
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/black-elves/Cave_Rider.cfg:5
msgid "Cave Rider"
msgstr "Jinete de Cuevas"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:636
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:667
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:698
msgid ""
"After so many aeons, the Hammermounts are free from Ashura's haunting... "
"There's nothing else we can do here, so we must hurry to Knalga."
msgstr ""
"Tras tantos eones, los Hammermounts están libres del tormento de Ashura… No "
"hay nada más que podamos hacer aquí, así que debemos apresurarnos a Knalga."

#. [message], speaker=Augdras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:640
msgid ""
"Aye, friends, go and triumph in whatever you do; I hope that we're able to "
"meet again in the future."
msgstr ""
"Sí, amigos, vayan y triunfen en lo que hagan; espero que podamos volver a "
"encontrarnos en el futuro."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:644
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:675
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:706
msgid ""
"Let's hurry indeed, we've lost too much time already in these caves... I "
"wonder whether the dwarves, the trolls and the black elves will keep on "
"fighting each other, now that they've seen how strong they can get if "
"united..."
msgstr ""
"Apresurémonos de verdad, ya hemos perdido demasiado tiempo en estas cuevas… "
"Me pregunto si los enanos, los trolls y los elfos negros seguirán luchando "
"entre sí, ahora que han visto lo fuertes que pueden ser si se unen…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:648
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:679
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:710
msgid ""
"Without a common foe, they'll probably return to their old squabbling, but "
"you have showed them that coexistence is possible, so who knows..."
msgstr ""
"Sin un enemigo común, probablemente volverán a sus antiguas peleas, pero les "
"has mostrado que la coexistencia es posible, así que quién sabe…"

#. [message], speaker=Thrur
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:671
msgid ""
"Farewell, little friends; may you be victorious in your enterprises as you "
"were here in the Hammermounts."
msgstr ""
"Adiós, pequeños amigos; que sean victoriosos en sus empresas como lo fueron "
"aquí en los Hammermounts."

#. [message], speaker=Shwarzel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:702
msgid ""
"I'm saddened for losing such gorgeous friends, but I have no right to delay "
"you. I wish you luck, and also that we meet again in the future!"
msgstr ""
"Me entristece perder a amigos tan maravillosos, pero no tengo derecho a "
"retrasarlos. Les deseo suerte, ¡y también que nos volvamos a encontrar en el "
"futuro!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/09_Mother_Of_Death.cfg:729
msgid ""
"We should have been done sooner, I don't think any of our allies, much less "
"us, will resist staying in these rotten caves any longer...!"
msgstr ""
"¡Deberíamos haber terminado antes, no creo que ninguno de nuestros aliados, "
"y mucho menos nosotros, resista quedarse más tiempo en estas cuevas "
"podridas…!"

#. [scenario], id=10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:4
msgid "Swamp of Ten Thousand Spears"
msgstr "Pantano de las Diez Mil Lanzas"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:23
msgid "Kill all enemy leaders to safely cross the swamp"
msgstr ""
"Matar a todos los líderes enemigos para cruzar el pantano con seguridad"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:39
msgid "Death of Prince Aetheryon"
msgstr "Muerte del Príncipe Aetheryon"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:43
msgid "NOTE: Both Tenma and Olokun can recruit from 22,19 and 23,19"
msgstr "NOTA: Tanto Tenma como Olokun pueden reclutar desde 22,19 y 23,19"

#. [side], type=Saurian Flanker
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:97
msgid "Krilix"
msgstr "Krilix"

#. [side], type=Saurian Flanker
#. [side], type=Saurian Prophet
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:103
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:127
msgid "Saurians"
msgstr "Saurios"

#. [side], type=Saurian Prophet
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:121
msgid "Ssirax"
msgstr "Ssirax"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:149
msgid "Ebonwood Elves"
msgstr "Elfos de Ebonwood"

#. [side]
#. [side], type=Inferno Drake
#. [side], type=Drake Enforcer
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:170
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:77
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/13_Elven_Path.cfg:75
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:88
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:90
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:133
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:77
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:167
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:173
msgid "Kehshakaar Drakes"
msgstr "Dracos Kehshakaar"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:206
msgid ""
"Look who comes from the south, our old friend Prince Aetheryon. I told you "
"there was someone stalking us..."
msgstr ""
"Mira quién viene del sur, nuestro viejo amigo el Príncipe Aetheryon. Te dije "
"que alguien nos estaba siguiendo…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:210
msgid ""
"I hope you didn't assume I'd give up after our last confrontation. The "
"Silent Lands may not be under Wesnothian jurisdiction, but we have charted "
"the realm quite extensively, and so I knew you had entered the Hammermounts."
msgstr ""
"Espero que no hayan asumido que me rendiría tras nuestro último "
"enfrentamiento. Las Tierras Silenciosas pueden no estar bajo jurisdicción "
"wesnothiana, pero hemos cartografiado el reino bastante extensamente, y por "
"eso sabía que habían entrado en los Hammermounts."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:214
msgid ""
"Fine, you found us again. What are you going to do now? Because finding us "
"will be of no use if you can't actually seize us."
msgstr ""
"Bien, nos encontraste de nuevo. ¿Qué vas a hacer ahora? Porque encontrarnos "
"no servirá de nada si no puedes capturarnos realmente."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:218
msgid ""
"I told you I would better prepare for our next encounter; allow me to show "
"that I spoke the tr..."
msgstr ""
"Les dije que me prepararía mejor para nuestro próximo encuentro; permítanme "
"demostrar que hablé con ver…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:230
msgid "(alert) What was that?"
msgstr "(alerta) ¿Qué fue eso?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:234
msgid ""
"That sounded like a saurian hissing... I think we've walked right into their "
"domain..."
msgstr ""
"Eso sonó como el siseo de un saurio… Creo que hemos entrado directamente en "
"su dominio…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:238
msgid ""
"Of course we have, this is the Swamp of Ten Thousand Frogs. Look, there they "
"come."
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto que sí, este es el Pantano de las Diez Mil Ranas. Miren, ahí "
"vienen."

#. [message], speaker=Krilix
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:242
msgid ""
"Hissss! Curssed humanss never give uss any resst, always trying to take our "
"landss – but they sshal ssuffer the ssame fate of those who came before! "
"Sskirmissherss, I want their headss on a sspear by the end of the day!"
msgstr ""
"¡Hissss! ¡Malditos humanos nunca nos dan resssst, siempre intentando tomar "
"nuessstrass tierrass… pero ssufrirán la misma suerte que los que vinieron "
"antes! ¡Escaramuzadores, quiero sus cabezas en una lanza antes del anochecer!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:246
msgid ""
"Geez, so many of them... Maybe this place should be called Swamp of Ten "
"Thousand Spears instead."
msgstr ""
"Cielos, cuántos son… Tal vez este lugar debería llamarse Pantano de las Diez "
"Mil Lanzas en su lugar."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:250
msgid ""
"You should be afraid of them, I suppose; my undead, on the other hand, shall "
"hack them to pieces with..."
msgstr ""
"Supongo que deberían temerles; mis no-muertos, en cambio, los harán pedazos "
"con…"

#. [unit], id=Kohn, type=Drake Enforcer
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:261
msgid "Gar Kohn"
msgstr "Gar Kohn"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:271
msgid "...ease..."
msgstr "…facilidad…"

#. [message], speaker=Kohn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:275
msgid ""
"My gliders have spotted two human bands coming here, and so I thought you "
"could use our help, underling."
msgstr ""
"Mis planeadores han avistado dos bandas humanas viniendo hacia aquí, y pensé "
"que podrían usar nuestra ayuda, subordinado."

#. [message], speaker=Ssirax
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:279
msgid "And we thank you for your aid, Lord Gar Kohn."
msgstr "Y te agradecemos por tu ayuda, Lord Gar Kohn."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:283
msgid ""
"(sigh) I guess now's the time I practice what I preach... Say, Your Graceful "
"Highness, shall we make peace for the next few hours? There's no way any of "
"us can win against each other <i>and</i> all these natives."
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) Supongo que ahora es el momento de practicar lo que predico… Dime, "
"Su Grácil Alteza, ¿hacemos la paz por las próximas horas? No hay forma de "
"que ninguno de nosotros gane contra el otro <i>y</i> contra todos estos "
"nativos."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:287
msgid ""
"You have a point there... Besides, I won't risk having you captured by those "
"lizards."
msgstr ""
"Tienes razón ahí… Además, no voy a arriesgar que te capturen esos lagartos."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:291
msgid "Of course you won't. I'm yours only, am I not?"
msgstr "Por supuesto que no. Soy solo tuya, ¿no es así?"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:295
msgid "Smart girl. I need-"
msgstr "Chica lista. Necesito—"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:299
msgid ""
"Weird way of showing you're interested, but whatever. Wesnothian boys are "
"creepy."
msgstr ""
"Manera rara de mostrar que estás interesado, pero como sea. Los chicos "
"wesnothianos dan miedo."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:303
msgid "(embarrassed) Tsc, as if..."
msgstr "(avergonzado) Tch, como si…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:307
msgid ""
"We should be careful with him, though; we can't take too many losses, or "
"else we won't be able to defend ourselves when we defeat the saurians and "
"the drakes."
msgstr ""
"Aun así deberíamos tener cuidado con él; no podemos sufrir demasiadas bajas, "
"o no podremos defendernos cuando derrotemos a los saurios y a los dracos."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:311
msgid ""
"Let us make another pact, then: after defeating our enemies, we'll go our "
"separate ways without assaulting each other – a truce valid for this battle "
"only; next time I find you, we shall fight to the death."
msgstr ""
"Hagamos otro pacto entonces: después de derrotar a nuestros enemigos, "
"seguiremos caminos separados sin atacarnos —una tregua válida solo para esta "
"batalla; la próxima vez que te encuentre, lucharemos a muerte."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:315
msgid "So be it."
msgstr "Que así sea."

#. [unit], id=Elvor, type=Elvish Marshal
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:330
msgid "General Elvor"
msgstr "General Elvor"

#. [message], speaker=Elvor
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:345
msgid ""
"These saurians sure are noisy; let's see what they're up too now... (looks "
"at the battlefield) Oh, look, they're fighting humans; maybe I should take "
"this chance to get ridden of the saurians who keep threatening my forest..."
msgstr ""
"Estos saurios sí que son ruidosos; veamos qué están tramando ahora… (mira el "
"campo de batalla) Oh, mira, están luchando contra humanos; tal vez debería "
"aprovechar esta oportunidad para deshacerme de los saurios que siguen "
"amenazando mi bosque…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:349
msgid "Damn it, as if we didn't have our hands full already!"
msgstr "¡Maldición, como si no tuviéramos las manos llenas ya!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:364
msgid ""
"Wait a minute, elves! I'm a friend of your people, I'm even going to your "
"great forest, Lins-Elens! Here, I have the Fey Laurel of Svaryarna, leader "
"of your kin in the Hammermounts!"
msgstr ""
"¡Esperen un momento, elfos! Soy amiga de su pueblo, ¡incluso voy hacia su "
"gran bosque, Lins-Elens! Aquí tengo el Laurel Feérico de Svaryarna, líder de "
"su pueblo en los Hammermounts."

#. [message], speaker=Elvor
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:368
msgid ""
"(surprised) Well, the black elves have long ceased contact with us, and "
"personally, I'm not very fond of them and their dwarf-like tendencies, but "
"they're still our kin, and if you have earned their trust and respect, then "
"you've earned mine as well. Come, let us defeat these lizards together."
msgstr ""
"(sorprendido) Bueno, los elfos negros han dejado de tener contacto con "
"nosotros hace mucho, y personalmente no les tengo mucho aprecio a ellos ni a "
"sus tendencias enanas, pero siguen siendo nuestros parientes, y si has "
"ganado su confianza y respeto, entonces también has ganado el mío. Ven, "
"derrotemos juntos a estos lagartos."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:372
msgid "Not that it pleases me to admit it, but well done, Tenma..."
msgstr "No es que me agrade admitirlo, pero bien hecho, Tenma…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:376
msgid "(winks)"
msgstr "(guiña un ojo)"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:382
msgid ""
"A pity we didn't help the black elves back when we arrived in the "
"Hammermounts; with Shwarzel's seal, we could have won the elves' friendship. "
"They're a people who never ignores neither aid nor harm done to their kin."
msgstr ""
"Lástima que no ayudamos a los elfos negros cuando llegamos a los "
"Hammermounts; con el sello de Shwarzel, podríamos haber ganado la amistad de "
"los elfos. Son un pueblo que nunca ignora ni la ayuda ni el daño hecho a sus "
"parientes."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:393
msgid ""
"That was a good fight, but I hope we don't come across these saurians very "
"often, they sure are an annoying foe to fight against..."
msgstr ""
"Fue una buena pelea, pero espero que no nos topemos con estos saurios muy a "
"menudo, seguro que son un enemigo molesto contra el que luchar…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:397
msgid "You're telling me..."
msgstr "A mí me lo dices…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:408
msgid ""
"By the way, we could enjoy the fact that we have the elves as allies and get "
"ridden of this Wesnothian nuisance once and for all..."
msgstr ""
"Por cierto, podríamos aprovechar que tenemos a los elfos como aliados y "
"deshacernos de esta molestia wesnothiana de una vez por todas…"

#. [message], speaker=Elvor
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:412
msgid ""
"If that man is your foe, just say it, that we shall help you as you've "
"helped us free our forest from saurian threat!"
msgstr ""
"Si ese hombre es tu enemigo, solo dilo, ¡que te ayudaremos como tú nos "
"ayudaste a liberar nuestro bosque de la amenaza sauria!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:420
msgid ""
"Don't worry, elf friends, we've just had a few quarrels, but nothing that he "
"must die for."
msgstr ""
"No se preocupen, amigos elfos, solo hemos tenido algunos roces, pero nada "
"por lo que él deba morir."

#. [message], speaker=Elvor
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:424
msgid ""
"In this case, I shall return to my capital and tend my warriors. Farewell, "
"friends-of-elves; may you reach Lins-Elens safe and sound."
msgstr ""
"En ese caso, regresaré a mi capital y cuidaré de mis guerreros. Adiós, "
"amigos de los elfos; que lleguen sanos y salvos a Lins-Elens."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:431
msgid ""
"You don't need to insult me with your pity, Yasai girl, I could have taken "
"on you all..."
msgstr ""
"No necesitas insultarme con tu lástima, chica Yasai, podría haber enfrentado "
"a todos ustedes…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:435
msgid ""
"No you couldn't, and I didn't do that out of pity. We promised not to attack "
"each other at the end of the battle, remember?"
msgstr ""
"No, no podrías, y no lo hice por lástima. Prometimos no atacarnos al final "
"de la batalla, ¿recuerdas?"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:439
msgid ""
"I see... Well, I compliment you for your honour, Tenma Yozora. When I "
"capture you, I promise I shall remember this, and give you and your friends "
"a worthy treatment, unlike those usually received by prisoners and rebels."
msgstr ""
"Entiendo… Bueno, te felicito por tu honor, Tenma Yozora. Cuando te capture, "
"prometo que recordaré esto y les daré a ti y a tus amigos un trato digno, a "
"diferencia del que suelen recibir los prisioneros y rebeldes."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:443
msgid "<i>If</i> you capture me, which you won't."
msgstr "<i>Si</i> me capturas, cosa que no harás."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:449
msgid ""
"You've proved yourself a worthy ally, Tenma Yozora. Now, as promised, let us "
"part in peace. However, next time I find you, not even a horde of dwarves "
"and elves shall make me change my plans of capturing you."
msgstr ""
"Te has probado como una aliada digna, Tenma Yozora. Ahora, como prometí, "
"partamos en paz. Sin embargo, la próxima vez que te encuentre, ni siquiera "
"una horda de enanos y elfos me hará cambiar mis planes de capturarte."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:453
msgid ""
"Damn are you clingy... Well then, till next time, Your High Graceful Lord..."
msgstr ""
"Qué pegajoso eres… Bueno entonces, hasta la próxima, Su Alta Grácil Señor…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:457
msgid "(angry) And stop calling me that, if you will!"
msgstr "(enojado) ¡Y deja de llamarme así, por favor!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:461
msgid "(chuckling) Tenma, Tenma..."
msgstr "(riendo) Tenma, Tenma…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:483
msgid "I can't... die...!"
msgstr "¡No puedo… morir…!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:487
msgid "Damn it, we needed him to defend against the lizards!"
msgstr "¡Maldición, lo necesitábamos para defendernos de los lagartos!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/10_Swamp_Of_Ten_Thousand_Spears.cfg:500
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/11_Emerald_Warriors.cfg:192
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:354
msgid ""
"More lizard troops are coming! We can't vanquish so many foes at once, this "
"is our end!"
msgstr ""
"¡Vienen más tropas lagarto! ¡No podemos vencer a tantos enemigos a la vez, "
"este es nuestro fin!"

#. [scenario], id=11_Emerald_Warriors
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/11_Emerald_Warriors.cfg:5
msgid "Emerald Warriors"
msgstr "Guerreros Esmeralda"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/11_Emerald_Warriors.cfg:24
msgid "Defeat Raskol (reduce his HP to 0 or below)"
msgstr "Derrotar a Raskol (reducir sus PV a 0 o menos)"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/11_Emerald_Warriors.cfg:40
msgid "NOTE: Both Tenma and Olokun can recruit from 24,6 and 25,6"
msgstr "NOTA: Tanto Tenma como Olokun pueden reclutar desde 24,6 y 25,6"

#. [side], type=Baryag Warfather
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/11_Emerald_Warriors.cfg:68
msgid "Raskol"
msgstr "Raskol"

#. [side], type=Baryag Warfather
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/11_Emerald_Warriors.cfg:73
msgid "Yevan"
msgstr "Yevan"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/11_Emerald_Warriors.cfg:108
msgid ""
"Baryags of the Emerald Plains, greetings! I am Olokun Maahes, and my friends "
"and I are travelling to the mountains of..."
msgstr ""
"¡Baryags de las Llanuras Esmeralda, saludos! Soy Olokun Maahes, y mis amigos "
"y yo viajamos hacia las montañas de…"

#. [message], speaker=Raskol
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/11_Emerald_Warriors.cfg:112
msgid ""
"You sure are daring to invade the lands of Yevan announcing yourself like "
"that! You seem to come from the east; I suppose the people there don't know "
"the folk of the west very well, you must live far away for us to have never "
"even heard of you, so I shall give you a few lessons on how things work "
"here: first of all, you never trespass the Baryags' lands without paying the "
"death price!"
msgstr ""
"¡Seguro que son muy valientes al invadir las tierras de Yevan anunciándose "
"así! Parecen venir del este; supongo que la gente de allá no conoce muy bien "
"al pueblo del oeste, deben vivir muy lejos para que nunca hayamos oído de "
"ustedes, así que les daré unas lecciones sobre cómo funcionan las cosas "
"aquí: primero que nada, ¡nunca invaden las tierras baryag sin pagar el "
"precio de la muerte!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/11_Emerald_Warriors.cfg:116
msgid ""
"Wait, wait, calm down for a second! We meant no offence, there was just no "
"way we could have known that you don't like travellers in your lands, but if "
"that's the case we're going back from whence we came and..."
msgstr ""
"¡Espera, espera, cálmate un segundo! No quisimos ofender, simplemente no "
"había forma de saber que no les gustan los viajeros en sus tierras, pero si "
"es así volvemos por donde vinimos y…"

#. [message], speaker=Raskol
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/11_Emerald_Warriors.cfg:120
msgid ""
"Too late, strangers! Baryags, pick up your weapons! I want their heads "
"before next sunset!"
msgstr ""
"¡Demasiado tarde, extraños! ¡Baryags, tomen sus armas! ¡Quiero sus cabezas "
"antes del próximo atardecer!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/11_Emerald_Warriors.cfg:124
msgid ""
"(offended) What the hell was that?! Why are they attacking us without even "
"letting us explain ourselves?"
msgstr ""
"(ofendida) ¿¡Qué demonios fue eso!? ¿Por qué nos atacan sin siquiera "
"dejarnos explicarnos?"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/11_Emerald_Warriors.cfg:128
msgid ""
"That's just as I heard: they're a very aggressive people who's never "
"bothered very much about making friends out of other nations. Well, if "
"fighting is what they want, then fight shall they have..."
msgstr ""
"Eso es justo lo que había oído: son un pueblo muy agresivo que nunca se ha "
"molestado mucho en hacer amigos de otras naciones. Bueno, si lo que quieren "
"es pelear, entonces pelear tendrán…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/11_Emerald_Warriors.cfg:132
msgid ""
"Still, we must not kill their leader unless he doesn't give us any other "
"choice. If we're going to cross the Emerald Plains – and going around them "
"now will cost us too much time – it won't be wise to earn the natives' anger."
msgstr ""
"Aun así, no debemos matar a su líder a menos que no nos dé otra opción. Si "
"vamos a cruzar las Llanuras Esmeralda —y rodearlas ahora nos costará "
"demasiado tiempo— no sería sabio ganarnos la ira de los nativos."

#. [message], speaker=Raskol
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/11_Emerald_Warriors.cfg:143
msgid ""
"Damn you, strangers...! Don't be fooled, though, Yevan is but one of our "
"many towns! The deeper you go into our realm, the worst your situation will "
"become!"
msgstr ""
"¡Malditos sean, extraños…! Pero no se engañen, Yevan es solo una de nuestras "
"muchas ciudades. Cuanto más profundo entren en nuestro reino, peor será su "
"situación."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/11_Emerald_Warriors.cfg:147
msgid ""
"We've been trying to tell you that we DON'T want to fight, we're just "
"travellers seeking the mountains of Knalga!"
msgstr ""
"¡Hemos estado intentando decirte que NO queremos pelear, solo somos viajeros "
"buscando las montañas de Knalga!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/11_Emerald_Warriors.cfg:151
msgid ""
"I'm rather disappointed, to be honest; of the many people I have visited in "
"my travels, none of them failed to show the value of hospitality – that is, "
"until now."
msgstr ""
"La verdad es que estoy bastante decepcionado; de las muchas personas que he "
"visitado en mis viajes, ninguna dejó de mostrar el valor de la hospitalidad… "
"hasta ahora."

#. [message], speaker=Raskol
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/11_Emerald_Warriors.cfg:155
msgid ""
"(stung) Wait a minute, it's not like Baryags are uncivilized barbarians! If "
"you wanted to be welcomed in our lands, all you had to do was to invoke the "
"sacred laws of hospitality!"
msgstr ""
"(herido) Espera un momento, ¡no es que los baryags seamos bárbaros "
"incivilizados! Si querían ser bienvenidos en nuestras tierras, ¡todo lo que "
"tenían que hacer era invocar las sagradas leyes de hospitalidad!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/11_Emerald_Warriors.cfg:159
msgid ""
"Which we tried to do, but you didn't even let us finish introducing "
"ourselves!"
msgstr ""
"¡Que intentamos hacer, pero ni siquiera nos dejaron terminar de presentarnos!"

#. [message], speaker=Raskol
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/11_Emerald_Warriors.cfg:163
msgid ""
"Well, maybe I was too rash... But let's leave it in the past, and let me "
"make amends: come into Yevan and enjoy our hospitality, that when you "
"depart, I'll give you a blue laurel, with which you may cross the Emerald "
"Plains safely and even be allowed in our great city of Mhreghost!"
msgstr ""
"Bueno, tal vez fui demasiado impulsivo… Pero dejémoslo en el pasado y "
"permítanme enmendarlo: vengan a Yevan y disfruten de nuestra hospitalidad, y "
"cuando partan les daré un laurel azul, con el cual podrán cruzar las "
"Llanuras Esmeralda con seguridad e incluso serán permitidos en nuestra gran "
"ciudad de Mhreghost."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/11_Emerald_Warriors.cfg:167
msgid "Seems fair enough, I think."
msgstr "Parece bastante justo, creo."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/11_Emerald_Warriors.cfg:171
msgid ""
"Let's accept it, please, I'm tired of sleeping on cold grass; it's been so "
"long since I last slept on a normal, human bed, I barely remember how it "
"feels like..."
msgstr ""
"Aceptémoslo, por favor, estoy cansada de dormir en hierba fría; ha pasado "
"tanto tiempo desde la última vez que dormí en una cama humana normal que "
"apenas recuerdo cómo se siente…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/11_Emerald_Warriors.cfg:175
msgid "Well, if you so insist..."
msgstr "Bueno, si tanto insisten…"

#. [scenario], id=12_Fire_Storm_Rising
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:5
msgid "Fire Storm Rising"
msgstr "Tormenta de Fuego Ascendente"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:23
msgid "Defeat the Drake Army"
msgstr "Derrotar al Ejército Draco"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:39
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1434
msgid "Death of Dragana Vasilya"
msgstr "Muerte de Dragana Vasilya"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:43
msgid "NOTE: Both Tenma and Olokun can recruit from 26,14 and 27,14"
msgstr "NOTA: Tanto Tenma como Olokun pueden reclutar desde 26,14 y 27,14"

#. [side], type=Inferno Drake
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:72
msgid "Mar'Ildian"
msgstr "Mar’Ildian"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:95
msgid "Mhreghost"
msgstr "Mhreghost"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:144
msgid "What's all this sudden fuss about...?"
msgstr "¿Qué es todo este alboroto repentino…?"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:148
msgid ""
"Considering that there are soldiers running all around the city, I'd say the "
"city's going to be attacked..."
msgstr ""
"Considerando que hay soldados corriendo por toda la ciudad, diría que la "
"ciudad va a ser atacada…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:152
msgid "Damn it...! Look to the east, there's a drake army arriving!"
msgstr "¡Maldición…! ¡Miren al este, llega un ejército draco!"

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:156
msgid ""
"*Damn them and their wings, they made all our defences useless...!* Drake "
"Lord, listen to me! I demand you to explain the reason of this sudden "
"attack; we have a peace treaty, in case you have forgotten!"
msgstr ""
"*¡Malditos sean ellos y sus alas, hicieron inútiles todas nuestras defensas…!"
"* ¡Señor draco, escúchame! ¡Exijo que expliques la razón de este ataque "
"repentino; tenemos un tratado de paz, por si lo has olvidado!"

#. [message], speaker=Marildian
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:160
msgid ""
"Ha, now you speak of treaties, don't you, treacherous human? But where were "
"those treaties when your people invaded the Swamp of Ten Thousand Frogs and "
"destroyed a saurian and a drake clans without provocation?"
msgstr ""
"Ja, ahora hablas de tratados, ¿verdad, humana traicionera? Pero ¿dónde "
"estaban esos tratados cuando tu gente invadió el Pantano de las Diez Mil "
"Ranas y destruyó clanes saurios y dracos sin provocación?"

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:164
msgid ""
"I know nothing of what you talk about, drake, but if any of my vassals has "
"harassed your people, it was not under my command. If it was really a Baryag "
"who did that, I shall give him to your justice, as dictated by our treaty, "
"so take your army and leave this city, or I'll be forced to eliminate you!"
msgstr ""
"No sé de qué hablas, draco, pero si alguno de mis vasallos ha hostigado a tu "
"pueblo, no fue bajo mi mando. Si realmente fue un baryag quien hizo eso, lo "
"entregaré a tu justicia, como dicta nuestro tratado, ¡así que toma tu "
"ejército y deja esta ciudad, o me veré obligada a eliminarte!"

#. [message], speaker=Marildian
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:168
msgid ""
"To the Frozen Hells with your treaties! The drakes have hindered themselves "
"for far too long, only for the benefit of lesser races – but now Lord "
"Vladnir Ohn has decided that it is time for the Children of Morogor to rule "
"once more, and your puny city shall be the first brazier to lit the "
"conflagration we're going to unleash upon this world!"
msgstr ""
"¡Al Infierno Helado con tus tratados! Los dracos se han contenido demasiado "
"tiempo, solo para beneficio de razas menores… ¡pero ahora el Señor Vladnir "
"Ohn ha decidido que es hora de que los Hijos de Morogor gobiernen una vez "
"más, y tu insignificante ciudad será el primer brasero que encienda la "
"conflagración que desatremos sobre este mundo!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:173
msgid ""
"What madness is this? Could it be that they're seeking to start a new Dragon "
"War, like those of the ancient days?"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué locura es esta? ¿Será que buscan iniciar una nueva Guerra de los "
"Dragones, como las de los días antiguos?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:177
msgid ""
"This I can't say, but to me it's pretty clear that this attack has been "
"motivated by our carelessness when entering that swamp. I hope you agree "
"that we can't let the Baryags die because of our mistakes?"
msgstr ""
"No puedo decirlo, pero para mí está bastante claro que este ataque ha sido "
"motivado por nuestra imprudencia al entrar en ese pantano. Espero que estén "
"de acuerdo en que no podemos dejar que los baryags mueran por nuestros "
"errores."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:181
msgid ""
"Of course we can't. More than that, I really want to fight these drakes; "
"it's always good to test my skills on new opponents..."
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto que no podemos. Más que eso, realmente quiero luchar contra "
"estos dracos; siempre es bueno probar mis habilidades contra nuevos "
"oponentes…"

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:192
msgid ""
"What is that, summoners in my city...? You, foreigners! Are you friend or "
"foe?"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué es eso, invocadores en mi ciudad…? ¡Ustedes, extranjeros! ¿Son amigos o "
"enemigos?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:196
msgid ""
"Don't worry, queen, we just want to help defending your city – after all, if "
"it gets captured it'll be our end too!"
msgstr ""
"No se preocupe, reina, solo queremos ayudar a defender su ciudad… ¡después "
"de todo, si la capturan también será nuestro fin!"

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:200
msgid ""
"Fair enough then, help me repel the drakes and I shall personally reward you "
"for that."
msgstr ""
"Bastante justo entonces, ayúdenme a repeler a los dracos y yo personalmente "
"les recompensaré por ello."

#. [message], speaker=Marildian
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:212
msgid ""
"Argh...! Enjoy well this petty victory, humans, for your end is at hand...!"
msgstr ""
"¡Argh…! Disfruten bien esta pequeña victoria, humanos, ¡porque su fin está "
"cerca…!"

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:224
msgid ""
"(sigh) Just when I thought we'd have times of peace... Anyway, I thank your "
"aid, foreigners; as you must know, I am Dragana Vasilya, Queen of Mhreghost "
"and of all the Emerald Plains."
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) Justo cuando pensé que tendríamos tiempos de paz… De todos modos, "
"agradezco su ayuda, extranjeros; como deben saber, soy Dragana Vasilya, "
"Reina de Mhreghost y de todas las Llanuras Esmeralda."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:228
msgid ""
"I am Olokun Maahes, and these are Tenma and Kenshiro; we come from beyond "
"the Silent Lands, and seek to reach the western shores of the continent "
"through Knalga."
msgstr ""
"Soy Olokun Maahes, y ellos son Tenma y Kenshiro; venimos de más allá de las "
"Tierras Silenciosas y buscamos llegar a las costas occidentales del "
"continente a través de Knalga."

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:232
msgid ""
"So there are people living beyond those lands! Perhaps I should send a "
"herald there... Only to talk, not to attack your people. I'm always willing "
"to establish cordial, mutually profitable ties with other nations. Who "
"knows, when you return from the west, should you pass through Mhreghost, you "
"could guide my herald to your land."
msgstr ""
"¡Entonces hay gente viviendo más allá de esas tierras! Tal vez debería "
"enviar un heraldo allí… Solo para hablar, no para atacar a su pueblo. "
"Siempre estoy dispuesta a establecer lazos cordiales y mutuamente "
"provechosos con otras naciones. Quién sabe, cuando regresen del oeste, si "
"pasan por Mhreghost, podrían guiar a mi heraldo hacia su tierra."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:236
msgid "That would be good, majesty, but..."
msgstr "Eso sería bueno, majestad, pero…"

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:240
msgid ""
"(laughs) No, no, call me just Vasilya, that's how we call a woman who leads "
"in our land. Leave these pompous addresses to Wesnothians!"
msgstr ""
"(ríe) No, no, llámame solo Vasilya, así llamamos a una mujer que lidera en "
"nuestra tierra. ¡Deja esas direcciones pomposas a los wesnothianos!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:244
msgid "(whisper) I like her already."
msgstr "(susurra) Ya me cae bien."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:248
msgid ""
"As you wish, Vasilya... As I was saying, we could do what you suggested, but "
"right now we're worried about your people and this drake attack. Am I right "
"to assume that this was but a vanguard?"
msgstr ""
"Como desees, Vasilya… Como decía, podríamos hacer lo que sugeriste, pero "
"ahora estamos preocupados por tu pueblo y este ataque de dracos. ¿Tengo "
"razón al asumir que esto fue solo una vanguardia?"

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:252
msgid ""
"Yes; the drakes would never attack Mhreghost itself unless they were really "
"bent on destroying our nation. I fail to see why that damn Vladnir Ohn is "
"attacking us so out of a sudden, though... But I won't admit that you worry "
"about that, friends. You have already risked yourselves defending our city, "
"you owe us nothing."
msgstr ""
"Sí; los dracos nunca atacarían Mhreghost en sí a menos que realmente "
"estuvieran decididos a destruir nuestra nación. Sin embargo, no entiendo por "
"qué ese maldito Vladnir Ohn nos ataca tan de repente… Pero no admitiré que "
"se preocupen por eso, amigos. Ya se arriesgaron defendiendo nuestra ciudad, "
"no nos deben nada."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:256
msgid ""
"I'm afraid we do, Vasilya. Remember what that drake said about humans "
"attacking saurians and drakes in that swamp? Well, we were those humans. We "
"had no idea that the swamp had such an inhospitable owner already. So we "
"can't just go away and leave you to deal with a problem we've caused."
msgstr ""
"Me temo que sí te debemos, Vasilya. ¿Recuerdas lo que dijo ese draco sobre "
"humanos atacando saurios y dracos en ese pantano? Bueno, nosotros fuimos "
"esos humanos. No teníamos idea de que el pantano ya tuviera un dueño tan "
"inhóspito. Así que no podemos simplemente irnos y dejarte lidiar con un "
"problema que causamos nosotros."

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:260
msgid ""
"If you didn't trespass into their domain on purpose, then I maintain that "
"you can't be held accountable, but I appreciate your sense of honour "
"nonetheless. I will prepare my people for war; perhaps I should send the "
"elves and the Aragwaithi a warning so that they may do the same..."
msgstr ""
"Si no invadieron su dominio a propósito, entonces mantengo que no pueden ser "
"considerados responsables, pero aun así aprecio su sentido del honor. "
"Prepararé a mi pueblo para la guerra; tal vez debería enviar una advertencia "
"a los elfos y a los aragwaithi para que hagan lo mismo…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:264
msgid "So there are elves living nearby?"
msgstr "¿Entonces hay elfos viviendo cerca?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:268
msgid "And Aragwaithi too? I wasn't aware their civilisation still endured!"
msgstr "¿Y aragwaithi también? ¡No sabía que su civilización aún perduraba!"

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:272
msgid ""
"Aye, the Emerald Plains share borders with the vast forests of the Lins-"
"Elens to the south, and with the Aragwaithi cities of the Frozen Shores to "
"the north."
msgstr ""
"Sí, las Llanuras Esmeralda comparten fronteras con los vastos bosques de los "
"Lins-Elens al sur, y con las ciudades aragwaithi de las Costas Heladas al "
"norte."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:283
msgid ""
"I don't know about these Aragwaithi, but with Svaryarna's laurel, the elves "
"will surely let us enter their kingdom, maybe even talk to their rulers!"
msgstr ""
"No sé nada de esos aragwaithi, pero con el laurel de Svaryarna, los elfos "
"seguramente nos dejarán entrar en su reino, ¡tal vez incluso hablar con sus "
"gobernantes!"

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:287
msgid ""
"Could it be? Do you think that you can get the elves to join us? That would "
"practically decide victory for us!"
msgstr ""
"¿Será posible? ¿Creen que puedan conseguir que los elfos se unan a nosotros? "
"¡Eso prácticamente decidiría la victoria para nosotros!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:291
msgid ""
"Well, we did find elves on our way here who helped us simply because we'd "
"helped their distant cousins before, so I suppose the elves from this Lins-"
"Elens kingdom will be the same."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, encontramos elfos en nuestro camino que nos ayudaron simplemente "
"porque habíamos ayudado a sus primos lejanos antes, así que supongo que los "
"elfos de este reino Lins-Elens serán iguales."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:295
msgid ""
"Besides, the elves will not be left in peace even if they decide to remain "
"neutral. Remember what that drake commander said: his lord has decided to "
"start a war like the one their ancestors started ages ago, a war of global "
"domination and of extermination of other races. The elves surely remember "
"that war, they'll understand what I'm talking about."
msgstr ""
"Además, los elfos no quedarán en paz ni siquiera si deciden permanecer "
"neutrales. Recuerda lo que dijo ese comandante draco: su señor ha decidido "
"iniciar una guerra como la que sus ancestros empezaron hace edades, una "
"guerra de dominación global y exterminio de otras razas. Los elfos "
"seguramente recuerdan esa guerra, entenderán de qué hablo."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:301
msgid ""
"I see... Perhaps there is a way to get them both to join us against the "
"drakes."
msgstr ""
"Entiendo… Tal vez haya una forma de conseguir que ambos se unan a nosotros "
"contra los dracos."

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:305
msgid ""
"I wouldn't count on the Aragwaithi; they're isolationist enough as it is, "
"and the drake threat is too far from their homeland still. But the elves are "
"a different matter... Do you think that you can get the elves to join us? "
"That would practically decide victory for us!"
msgstr ""
"No contaría con los aragwaithi; ya son bastante aislacionistas, y la amenaza "
"draco aún está demasiado lejos de su patria. Pero los elfos son otro asunto… "
"¿Creen que puedan conseguir que los elfos se unan a nosotros? ¡Eso "
"prácticamente decidiría la victoria para nosotros!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:309
msgid ""
"Remember what that drake commander said: his lord has decided to start a "
"war, and not any war. Your people may not know that, but the drakes have "
"once tried to rule the entire world, and they attacked everyone they found "
"on their way. That was a catastrophic war, one the elves certainly remember; "
"if I tell them that the drakes are going to repeat the attempt, they'll "
"surely take the threat seriously."
msgstr ""
"Recuerda lo que dijo ese comandante draco: su señor ha decidido iniciar una "
"guerra, y no cualquier guerra. Tu pueblo puede no saberlo, pero los dracos "
"una vez intentaron gobernar el mundo entero y atacaron a todos los que "
"encontraron en su camino. Fue una guerra catastrófica, una que los elfos "
"seguramente recuerdan; si les digo que los dracos van a repetir el intento, "
"sin duda tomarán la amenaza en serio."

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:315
msgid ""
"Then you must hurry to Metheldur and talk to the elf king Gil-Thelyon! I'll "
"give you resources and our finest horses, even some soldiers if you so wish; "
"there's always a possibility that you may encounter a xenophobic elvish "
"captain when trying to enter their kingdom."
msgstr ""
"¡Entonces deben apresurarse a Metheldur y hablar con el rey elfo Gil-"
"Thelyon! Les daré recursos y nuestros mejores caballos, incluso algunos "
"soldados si lo desean; siempre existe la posibilidad de que encuentren un "
"capitán elfo xenófobo al intentar entrar en su reino."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:319
msgid ""
"We accept the horses and the provisions, but please, keep your soldiers near "
"you; our power will be enough to defend against enemies."
msgstr ""
"Aceptamos los caballos y las provisiones, pero por favor, mantengan a sus "
"soldados cerca de ustedes; nuestro poder será suficiente para defendernos de "
"los enemigos."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:323
msgid "Let's go, then! As Vasilya said, we have no second to waste!"
msgstr ""
"¡Vamos entonces! Como dijo Vasilya, ¡no tenemos ni un segundo que perder!"

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/12_Fire_Storm_Rising.cfg:342
msgid "I failed to protect my people...!"
msgstr "¡Fallé en proteger a mi pueblo…!"

#. [scenario], id=13_Elven_Path
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/13_Elven_Path.cfg:5
msgid "Elven Path"
msgstr "Sendero Élfico"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/13_Elven_Path.cfg:23
msgid "Help the elves defeat the drake attack"
msgstr "Ayudar a los elfos a derrotar el ataque draco"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/13_Elven_Path.cfg:39
msgid "Death of Aniwen"
msgstr "Muerte de Aniwen"

#. [side], type=Drake Enforcer
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/13_Elven_Path.cfg:70
msgid "Karrash"
msgstr "Karrash"

#. [side], type=Elvish Avenger
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/13_Elven_Path.cfg:90
msgid "Commander Aniwen"
msgstr "Comandante Aniwen"

#. [side], type=Elvish Avenger
#. [side]
#. [side], type=Elvish Sharpshooter
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/13_Elven_Path.cfg:97
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/14_The_King_In_The_Woods.cfg:35
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:131
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:173
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:121
msgid "Lins-Elens Elves"
msgstr "Elfos Lins-Elens"

#. [message], speaker=Aniwen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/13_Elven_Path.cfg:134
msgid ""
"I confess I never thought Queen Dragana would be so kind as to send anyone "
"to our aid! You've come right in the nick of time, friends; with their "
"wings, the drakes have managed to strike deep into our forests!"
msgstr ""
"Confieso que nunca pensé que la reina Dragana sería tan amable de enviar a "
"alguien en nuestra ayuda. ¡Han llegado justo a tiempo, amigos; con sus alas, "
"los dracos han logrado golpear profundo en nuestros bosques!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/13_Elven_Path.cfg:138
msgid ""
"We shall help you defeat this offensive, elf commander, but know that we "
"were sent by Queen Dragana to ask for elvish aid, as the Baryags too are "
"under heavy attack by the drakes."
msgstr ""
"Te ayudaremos a derrotar esta ofensiva, comandante elfa, pero sabe que "
"fuimos enviados por la reina Dragana para pedir ayuda élfica, ya que los "
"baryags también están bajo fuerte ataque de los dracos."

#. [message], speaker=Aniwen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/13_Elven_Path.cfg:142
msgid ""
"Then help us now, that I'll give you my personal seal for you to speak to "
"Lord Gil-Thelyon himself! If the drakes have opted on all-out war on us, "
"maybe it will be best to unite in an alliance."
msgstr ""
"Entonces ayúdennos ahora, ¡y les daré mi sello personal para que hablen "
"directamente con el señor Gil-Thelyon! Si los dracos han optado por una "
"guerra total contra nosotros, tal vez lo mejor sea unirnos en una alianza."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/13_Elven_Path.cfg:146
msgid ""
"'Maybe' it will be best? Of course it will be best, what is she thinking?"
msgstr ""
"¿«Tal vez» lo mejor? ¡Por supuesto que será lo mejor, en qué está pensando!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/13_Elven_Path.cfg:150
msgid ""
"Well, elves are known for being a very aloof people; some call it arrogance, "
"others just plain xenophobia, but one thing is certain: even the haughtiest "
"elves know when to join forces with other peoples to defend against a common "
"and powerful enemy."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, los elfos son conocidos por ser un pueblo muy distante; algunos lo "
"llaman arrogancia, otros simple xenofobia, pero una cosa es segura: incluso "
"los elfos más altivos saben cuándo unirse a otros pueblos para defenderse "
"contra un enemigo común y poderoso."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/13_Elven_Path.cfg:159
msgid ""
"So, Kenshiro, I bet you've never fought alongside such fine allies, have you?"
msgstr ""
"Entonces, Kenshiro, apuesto a que nunca has luchado junto a aliados tan "
"finos, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/13_Elven_Path.cfg:163
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1038
msgid "What do you mean?"
msgstr "¿Qué quieres decir?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/13_Elven_Path.cfg:167
msgid "Come on, don't tell you haven't even squinted at all those elf ladies!"
msgstr ""
"Vamos, no me digas que ni siquiera has mirado de reojo a todas esas damas "
"elfas."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/13_Elven_Path.cfg:171
msgid ""
"I would be a failure as a warrior if I allowed such things to distract me in "
"the midst of battle."
msgstr ""
"Sería un fracaso como guerrero si permitiera que tales cosas me distrajeran "
"en medio de la batalla."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/13_Elven_Path.cfg:175
msgid "Well, I for one am getting distracted all the time..."
msgstr "Bueno, yo por mi parte me distraigo todo el tiempo…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/13_Elven_Path.cfg:182
msgid ""
"Geesh, Kenshiro, speak something for a change! You're always so silent and "
"gloomy, you weren't like this before..."
msgstr ""
"Cielos, Kenshiro, ¡di algo por variar! Siempre estás tan callado y sombrío, "
"no eras así antes…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/13_Elven_Path.cfg:186
msgid ""
"I wasn't an adult before either. Maybe you should grow up too; one could "
"think that being through two violent wars would have matured you, but you "
"keep behaving like we're off on a merry quest."
msgstr ""
"Tampoco era adulto antes. Tal vez tú también deberías madurar; uno podría "
"pensar que haber pasado por dos guerras violentas te habría hecho madurar, "
"pero sigues comportándote como si estuviéramos en una alegre búsqueda."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/13_Elven_Path.cfg:190
msgid ""
"(serious) Don't misunderstand me, Kenshiro. When we fought Ashura, I knew "
"very well what failing to destroy her would mean for this world – and I also "
"know what may happen if the drakes are not stopped. It's just... I refuse to "
"let fear and violence change who I am; I feel like I'd be repeating a grave "
"mistake if I did..."
msgstr ""
"(seria) No me malinterpretes, Kenshiro. Cuando luchamos contra Ashura, sabía "
"muy bien qué significaría fallar en destruirla para este mundo… y también sé "
"qué podría pasar si no detenemos a los dracos. Es solo que… me niego a dejar "
"que el miedo y la violencia cambien quién soy; siento que estaría repitiendo "
"un grave error si lo hiciera…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/13_Elven_Path.cfg:194
msgid ""
"*Amazing; she must be referring to the Ughure Incident, when Myra nearly "
"died using the Sky Soul... She seems to be remembering more and more of her "
"past life...*"
msgstr ""
"*Asombroso; debe estar refiriéndose al Incidente de Ughure, cuando Myra casi "
"murió usando el Alma del Cielo… Parece que está recordando cada vez más de "
"su vida pasada…*"

#. [message], speaker=Aniwen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/13_Elven_Path.cfg:203
msgid ""
"Friends, I am deeply grateful for your aid; I'm not certain I'd have been "
"able to defend the Northern Arch on my own. As promised, I'll give you my "
"personal seal, with which you may not only cross the Lins-Elens freely, but "
"also enter Metheldur, where Lord Gil-Thelyon resides. Once there, ask for an "
"audience with him; but know that, even with my seal, you may not be allowed "
"that. Even elves can't always speak with him."
msgstr ""
"Amigos, estoy profundamente agradecida por su ayuda; no estoy segura de "
"haber podido defender el Arco Norte por mi cuenta. Como prometí, les daré mi "
"sello personal, con el cual no solo podrán cruzar los Lins-Elens libremente, "
"sino también entrar en Metheldur, donde reside el señor Gil-Thelyon. Una vez "
"allí, pidan audiencia con él; pero sepan que, incluso con mi sello, podrían "
"no ser admitidos. Ni siquiera los elfos siempre pueden hablar con él."

#. [message], speaker=Aniwen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/13_Elven_Path.cfg:207
msgid ""
"And good luck, humans; in this increasingly strange world, where two suns "
"shine in the sky and trust between peoples is growing rarer, it heartens me "
"to see that there are still worthy friends beyond Lins-Elens."
msgstr ""
"Y buena suerte, humanos; en este mundo cada vez más extraño, donde dos soles "
"brillan en el cielo y la confianza entre pueblos se hace más rara, me alegra "
"ver que aún hay amigos dignos más allá de Lins-Elens."

#. [message], speaker=Aniwen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/13_Elven_Path.cfg:226
msgid ""
"I couldn't protect this frontier, now the drakes may invade the Lins-"
"Elens...!"
msgstr ""
"¡No pude proteger esta frontera, ahora los dracos podrían invadir los Lins-"
"Elens…!"

#. [message], speaker=Aniwen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/13_Elven_Path.cfg:238
msgid "Oh, no, more drake troops are coming! We're overwhelmed!"
msgstr "¡Oh, no, vienen más tropas draco! ¡Estamos abrumados!"

#. [scenario], id=14_The_King_In_The_Woods
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/14_The_King_In_The_Woods.cfg:5
msgid "The King-in-the-Woods"
msgstr "El Rey-en-el-Bosque"

#. [unit], id=Kaldan, type=Elvish High Lord
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/14_The_King_In_The_Woods.cfg:58
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:171
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:193
msgid "Sage Kaldan"
msgstr "Sabio Kaldan"

#. [message], speaker=Kaldan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/14_The_King_In_The_Woods.cfg:80
msgid ""
"The King-in-the-Woods! What are you waiting for, humans? Bow down and show "
"him your respect and gratitude for being the first humans allowed in this "
"palace in thousands of years!"
msgstr ""
"¡El Rey-en-el-Bosque! ¿Qué esperan, humanos? ¡Inclínense y muéstrenle su "
"respeto y gratitud por ser los primeros humanos permitidos en este palacio "
"en miles de años!"

#. [message], speaker=Thelyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/14_The_King_In_The_Woods.cfg:84
msgid ""
"Kaldan, please, let us be kind to our guests; they come from another "
"culture, and so they are not obliged to know, or even follow, our customs. "
"But I deem it fair that I ask you to introduce yourselves, for I still "
"ignore who you may be."
msgstr ""
"Kaldan, por favor, seamos amables con nuestros invitados; vienen de otra "
"cultura, y por eso no están obligados a conocer ni seguir nuestras "
"costumbres. Pero considero justo pedirles que se presenten, pues aún ignoro "
"quiénes podrían ser."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/14_The_King_In_The_Woods.cfg:88
msgid ""
"Lord Gil-Thelyon, I am Olokun Maahes, and these are Tenma and Kenshiro; we "
"are travellers from a distant land, but we have befriended Queen Dragana "
"Vasilya as we crossed the Emerald Plains, and so we accepted bringing you a "
"request on her behalf..."
msgstr ""
"Señor Gil-Thelyon, soy Olokun Maahes, y estos son Tenma y Kenshiro; somos "
"viajeros de una tierra lejana, pero nos hemos hecho amigos de la reina "
"Dragana Vasilya al cruzar las Llanuras Esmeralda, y por eso aceptamos "
"traerle una petición en su nombre…"

#. [message], speaker=Thelyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/14_The_King_In_The_Woods.cfg:92
msgid ""
"And I presume it is something related to this sudden attack by the drakes, "
"am I correct? Go on, young man, I am really interested in learning more "
"about that."
msgstr ""
"Y supongo que tiene que ver con este ataque repentino de los dracos, ¿estoy "
"en lo cierto? Continúa, joven, estoy realmente interesado en saber más al "
"respecto."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/14_The_King_In_The_Woods.cfg:96
msgid ""
"This drake attack seems to have been triggered by our... careless "
"trespassing of drake and saurian territory. What is worse, according to the "
"drake commander who attacked Mhreghost a few days ago, Lord Vladnir Ohn "
"actually seeks to start a new Dragon War, like the one from ages ago, to "
"bring all of this continent under his people's control."
msgstr ""
"Este ataque draco parece haber sido desencadenado por nuestra… imprudente "
"invasión del territorio draco y saurio. Peor aún, según el comandante draco "
"que atacó Mhreghost hace unos días, el señor Vladnir Ohn en realidad busca "
"iniciar una nueva Guerra de los Dragones, como la de hace edades, para poner "
"todo este continente bajo el control de su pueblo."

#. [message], speaker=Thelyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/14_The_King_In_The_Woods.cfg:100
msgid ""
"A new Dragon War...? I have consulted with my wisest advisors, and none of "
"them even considered that as the reason behind this attack – and yet it "
"makes perfect sense... I am also surprised that you actually know about that "
"war; I did not know that humans remembered it still."
msgstr ""
"¿Una nueva Guerra de los Dragones…? He consultado con mis consejeros más "
"sabios, y ninguno consideró siquiera eso como la razón detrás de este "
"ataque… y sin embargo tiene perfecto sentido… También me sorprende que "
"realmente sepan de esa guerra; no sabía que los humanos aún la recordaran."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/14_The_King_In_The_Woods.cfg:104
msgid ""
"Most humans don't; but my people descend from refugees of that war, amongst "
"them Aragwaithi and Windsong survivors, all led by Myra of Hiera'Shirsha and "
"by other heroes, such as Princess Alenya of Lintanir."
msgstr ""
"La mayoría de los humanos no; pero mi pueblo desciende de refugiados de esa "
"guerra, entre ellos sobrevivientes aragwaithi y de las Hijas del Viento, "
"todos liderados por Myra de Hiera'Shirsha y por otros héroes, como la "
"princesa Alenya de Lintanir."

#. [message], speaker=Thelyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/14_The_King_In_The_Woods.cfg:108
msgid ""
"(surprised) I am frankly impressed, young man; your knowledge on that war "
"must be indeed vast, for you to know about even the Lost Princess of "
"Lintanir... But we digress. You claim that the drakes want a new Dragon War; "
"indeed, the drakes of Vladnir Ohn have spent enough time in the Kehshakaar "
"Mountains to have multiplied into hundreds of thousands – not to mention the "
"clan of the Shakaar Mountains, led by Vladnir's sister. This seems enough "
"reason for us to formally build an alliance with the Baryags and whoever "
"else may be willing to aid us."
msgstr ""
"(sorprendido) Estoy francamente impresionado, joven; tu conocimiento sobre "
"esa guerra debe ser realmente vasto, para que sepas incluso de la Princesa "
"Perdida de Lintanir… Pero nos desviamos. Afirman que los dracos quieren una "
"nueva Guerra de los Dragones; en efecto, los dracos de Vladnir Ohn han "
"pasado suficiente tiempo en las Montañas Kehshakaar para haberse "
"multiplicado en cientos de miles… sin mencionar el clan de las Montañas "
"Shakaar, liderado por la hermana de Vladnir. Esto parece razón suficiente "
"para que construyamos formalmente una alianza con los baryags y con quien "
"más esté dispuesto a ayudarnos."

#. [message], speaker=Kaldan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/14_The_King_In_The_Woods.cfg:112
msgid ""
"It certainly seems so, Lord King, but I question whether allying ourselves "
"with weaker nations will be profitable for us. Being the strongest member of "
"an alliance means that the burden of supporting it would fall on our "
"shoulders; in other words, many elves would have to die to protect allies "
"that, not long after this war ends, may even attack us themselves!"
msgstr ""
"Ciertamente parece así, señor Rey, pero cuestiono si aliarse con naciones "
"más débiles será provechoso para nosotros. Ser el miembro más fuerte de una "
"alianza significa que la carga de sostenerla recaería sobre nuestros "
"hombros; en otras palabras, ¡muchos elfos tendrían que morir para proteger a "
"aliados que, poco después de que termine esta guerra, podrían incluso "
"atacarnos a nosotros mismos!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/14_The_King_In_The_Woods.cfg:116
msgid "Wait a minute, you..."
msgstr "Espera un minuto, tú…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/14_The_King_In_The_Woods.cfg:120
msgid "Tenma, wait!"
msgstr "¡Tenma, espera!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/14_The_King_In_The_Woods.cfg:124
msgid ""
"...you will pardon my lack of ceremony and all, but I won't let that slide. "
"You elves may know lots of things, and your country is wonderful, powerful "
"and advanced, but you're not too high that you can disregard your neighbours "
"like that. There are thousands of people out there, and this is their planet "
"as much as it is yours, so maybe you should try and work together to the "
"extent you can!"
msgstr ""
"…perdona mi falta de ceremonia y todo, pero no dejaré pasar eso. Ustedes los "
"elfos pueden saber muchas cosas, y su país es maravilloso, poderoso y "
"avanzado, pero no están tan por encima como para despreciar a sus vecinos de "
"esa manera. Hay miles de personas allá afuera, y este es su planeta tanto "
"como es el de ustedes, ¡así que tal vez deberían intentar trabajar juntos en "
"la medida de lo posible!"

#. [message], speaker=Thelyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/14_The_King_In_The_Woods.cfg:128
msgid ""
"(smiling) There you have it, more bluntly expressed, but still my thoughts "
"precisely! My people, there have been two instances in the past when the "
"Lins-Elens marched alongside other nations: first in the War of Irdya's "
"Kings, and second in the Dragon War. Our ancestors were not troubled by "
"cultural differences when it came to fighting a threat to all, so why should "
"we? I say let us fight along with Queen Dragana of the Baryags and whoever "
"else accepts to join us to once more stop the drakes' rampage!"
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) ¡Ahí lo tienen, expresado de forma más directa, pero aún así "
"exactamente mis pensamientos! Mi pueblo, ha habido dos ocasiones en el "
"pasado en que los Lins-Elens marcharon junto a otras naciones: primero en la "
"Guerra de los Reyes de Irdya, y segundo en la Guerra de los Dragones. "
"Nuestros ancestros no se dejaron perturbar por diferencias culturales cuando "
"se trataba de luchar contra una amenaza para todos, ¿por qué deberíamos "
"hacerlo nosotros? ¡Digo que luchemos junto a la reina Dragana de los Baryags "
"y con quien más acepte unirse a nosotros para detener una vez más la furia "
"de los dracos!"

#. [message], speaker=Gelendras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/14_The_King_In_The_Woods.cfg:132
msgid ""
"Well, father, if that is your choice, I shall respect it, for you're much "
"wiser than I am."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, padre, si esa es tu decisión, la respetaré, pues eres mucho más sabio "
"que yo."

#. [message], speaker=Kaldan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/14_The_King_In_The_Woods.cfg:136
msgid ""
"I make Prince Gelendras' words mine. I shall send the message throughout the "
"Lins-Elens, informing all cities that they must prepare their soldiers for "
"battle."
msgstr ""
"Comparto las palabras del príncipe Gelendras. Enviaré el mensaje por todo "
"Lins-Elens, informando a todas las ciudades que deben preparar a sus "
"soldados para la batalla."

#. [message], speaker=Thelyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/14_The_King_In_The_Woods.cfg:140
msgid ""
"The Lins-Elens Elves shall march alongside the Baryags of Dragana Vasilya; "
"we shall send messengers to all neighbouring nations, even the Wesnothians, "
"warning them of this threat; the drakes are foes to everyone, after all."
msgstr ""
"Los elfos Lins-Elens marcharán junto a los baryags de Dragana Vasilya; "
"enviaremos mensajeros a todas las naciones vecinas, incluso a los "
"wesnothianos, advirtiéndoles de esta amenaza; después de todo, los dracos "
"son enemigos de todos."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/14_The_King_In_The_Woods.cfg:144
msgid ""
"Though I have no such authority, I'd like to thank you on behalf of all "
"Baryags, Lord Gil-Thelyon. We shall return as soon as we can, and transmit "
"Queen Dragana this news!"
msgstr ""
"Aunque no tengo tal autoridad, me gustaría agradecerte en nombre de todos "
"los baryags, señor Gil-Thelyon. ¡Regresaremos tan pronto como podamos y "
"transmitiremos esta noticia a la reina Dragana!"

#. [message], speaker=Thelyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/14_The_King_In_The_Woods.cfg:148
msgid ""
"I suggest you take a different path: you could earn us another powerful ally "
"if you go south, to Firecloud Peak. There lives a mighty human sorceress "
"called Valerya: she is known as the slayer of the last dragon on this "
"continent, and her knowledge on how to kill the fire lizards would be "
"invaluable to us. She's also known for her neutrality, but she may be "
"convinced to follow you if she meets this smart girl next to you – after "
"all, one seldom has the opportunity to meet someone whose powers defy all "
"established lore on magic..."
msgstr ""
"Les sugiero tomar un camino diferente: podrían ganarnos otro poderoso aliado "
"si van al sur, al Pico Nube de Fuego. Allí vive una poderosa hechicera "
"humana llamada Valerya: es conocida como la matadragones del último dragón "
"en este continente, y su conocimiento sobre cómo matar a los lagartos de "
"fuego sería invaluable para nosotros. También es conocida por su "
"neutralidad, pero podría ser convencida de seguirlos si conoce a esta chica "
"inteligente a tu lado… después de todo, rara vez se tiene la oportunidad de "
"conocer a alguien cuyos poderes desafían todo el saber establecido sobre "
"magia…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/14_The_King_In_The_Woods.cfg:152
msgid "(blushes)"
msgstr "(se sonroja)"

#. [message], speaker=Thelyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/14_The_King_In_The_Woods.cfg:156
msgid ""
"Be warned though: on the path to that volcano, you may come across "
"Wesnothians and minotaurs, neither of whom can be expected to greet you as "
"friends."
msgstr ""
"Aun así, estén advertidos: en el camino hacia ese volcán, podrían "
"encontrarse con wesnothianos y minotauros, ninguno de los cuales se espera "
"que los reciba como amigos."

#. [message], speaker=Gelendras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/14_The_King_In_The_Woods.cfg:160
msgid ""
"But the most dangerous threat for you probably lies within this forest: "
"Cornelya. If she finds you wandering amidst our trees, not even my father's "
"seal and escorts will save you from her fury. I would go along with you, and "
"thus she might refrain herself, but, as the High Marshal of the Lins-Elens "
"Elves, I have other duties."
msgstr ""
"Pero la amenaza más peligrosa para ustedes probablemente está dentro de este "
"bosque: Cornelya. Si los encuentra vagando entre nuestros árboles, ni "
"siquiera el sello de mi padre y las escoltas los salvarán de su furia. Iría "
"con ustedes, y así podría contenerse, pero como Alto Mariscal de los Elfos "
"Lins-Elens tengo otros deberes."

#. [message], speaker=Thelyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/14_The_King_In_The_Woods.cfg:164
msgid ""
"(sigh) Unfortunately, what my son says is true. Cornelya is my foster-"
"daughter; since tragedy struck her as a child, she has felt a deep distrust "
"of all non-elves. If you come across her, you have my permission to stop and "
"capture her; I had to do something about that bloodthirsty war band of hers "
"anyway..."
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) Desafortunadamente, lo que dice mi hijo es cierto. Cornelya es mi "
"hija adoptiva; desde que la tragedia la golpeó de niña, ha sentido una "
"profunda desconfianza hacia todos los no-elfos. Si se topan con ella, tienen "
"mi permiso para detenerla y capturarla; de todos modos tenía que hacer algo "
"con esa banda guerrera sedienta de sangre suya…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/14_The_King_In_The_Woods.cfg:168
msgid ""
"Well, if that is all, then we shall head to Firecloud Peak as soon as "
"possible. But, before we leave, if I may ask... What was the War of Irdya's "
"Kings?"
msgstr ""
"Bueno, si eso es todo, entonces nos dirigiremos al Pico Nube de Fuego lo "
"antes posible. Pero, antes de irnos, si me permites preguntar… ¿Qué fue la "
"Guerra de los Reyes de Irdya?"

#. [message], speaker=Thelyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/14_The_King_In_The_Woods.cfg:172
msgid ""
"A war so ancient that it was considered legend even in the age of the Dragon "
"War – but this is a long story, which I am certain you would rather hear "
"another day, am I correct?"
msgstr ""
"Una guerra tan antigua que era considerada leyenda incluso en la era de la "
"Guerra de los Dragones… pero es una larga historia, de la que estoy seguro "
"preferirían oír otro día, ¿estoy en lo cierto?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/14_The_King_In_The_Woods.cfg:176
msgid "Indeed, Lord Gil-Thelyon. With your permission, we shall depart now."
msgstr "En efecto, señor Gil-Thelyon. Con su permiso, partiremos ahora."

#. [scenario], id=15_Princess_Of_Blood
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/15_Princess_Of_Blood.cfg:5
msgid "Princess of Blood"
msgstr "Princesa de Sangre"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/15_Princess_Of_Blood.cfg:34
msgid "Defeat Princess Cornelya"
msgstr "Derrotar a la Princesa Cornelya"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/15_Princess_Of_Blood.cfg:50
msgid "Killing more than $units_slayed elvish units"
msgstr "Matar más de $units_slayed unidades élficas"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/15_Princess_Of_Blood.cfg:84
msgid "Red Leaves Ranger Battalion"
msgstr "Batallón de Exploradores de Hojas Rojas"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/15_Princess_Of_Blood.cfg:125
msgid ""
"Well, we're about to leave this forest, and nobody's trying to stop us; I "
"told you we didn't have to worry so much..."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, estamos a punto de dejar este bosque, y nadie intenta detenernos; te "
"dije que no teníamos que preocuparnos tanto…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/15_Princess_Of_Blood.cfg:129
msgid "(alert) Watch out, there's someone in the woods...!"
msgstr "(alerta) ¡Cuidado, hay alguien en el bosque…!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/15_Princess_Of_Blood.cfg:138
msgid ""
"I've always known humans to be foolish creatures, but you've exceeded your "
"right to be stupid, girl. Did you really think that any creature would "
"manage to spread their filth over our forest and leave unscathed?"
msgstr ""
"Siempre he sabido que los humanos son criaturas necias, pero has excedido tu "
"derecho a ser estúpida, chica. ¿Realmente pensaste que cualquier criatura "
"lograría esparcir su suciedad por nuestro bosque y salir ilesa?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/15_Princess_Of_Blood.cfg:142
msgid ""
"Princess Cornelya, please do not engage us in battle; we're on a mission "
"given us by your father, the King-in-the-Woods himself, we're not your foes. "
"Look, we have his seal to prove what..."
msgstr ""
"Princesa Cornelya, por favor no nos involucres en batalla; estamos en una "
"misión encomendada por tu padre, el propio Rey-en-el-Bosque, no somos tus "
"enemigos. Mira, tenemos su sello para probar que…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/15_Princess_Of_Blood.cfg:149
msgid ""
"This is what I think of your seals and excuses, human. Now, get a hold of "
"your weapons; I'll be merciful enough to at least give you a chance to fight "
"for your lives!"
msgstr ""
"Esto es lo que pienso de tus sellos y excusas, humana. Ahora, tomen sus "
"armas; seré lo suficientemente misericordiosa como para al menos darles una "
"oportunidad de luchar por sus vidas."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/15_Princess_Of_Blood.cfg:153
msgid "Damn, I really wish we didn't have to fight elves in their own turf..."
msgstr ""
"Maldición, realmente desearía que no tuviéramos que luchar contra elfos en "
"su propio terreno…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/15_Princess_Of_Blood.cfg:157
msgid ""
"Come on, we've fought and defeated the Mother of Death, this stupid little "
"princess is small fry next to her!"
msgstr ""
"Vamos, hemos luchado y derrotado a la Madre de la Muerte, ¡esta estúpida "
"princesita es un pez chico comparada con ella!"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/15_Princess_Of_Blood.cfg:161
msgid ""
"Agreed; and besides, I've had it with these elves' high-and-mighty attitude. "
"It's about time we give them a lesson on respect!"
msgstr ""
"De acuerdo; y además, ya estoy harto de la actitud altanera de estos elfos. "
"¡Ya es hora de darles una lección de respeto!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/15_Princess_Of_Blood.cfg:165
msgid ""
"Don't forget that the elves are our allies! Let's defend ourselves however "
"we can, but we must not kill too many of them, or they might change their "
"minds about helping the Baryags!"
msgstr ""
"¡No olviden que los elfos son nuestros aliados! Defendámonos como podamos, "
"pero no debemos matar a demasiados de ellos, ¡o podrían cambiar de opinión "
"sobre ayudar a los baryags!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/15_Princess_Of_Blood.cfg:189
msgid ""
"You cursed humans, how dare you kill so many elves inside the holy Lins-"
"Elens?! I <i>will</i> have your heads, and not even my father's words shall "
"save you from the wrath of elvenkind!"
msgstr ""
"¡Malditos humanos, cómo se atreven a matar a tantos elfos dentro del sagrado "
"Lins-Elens! ¡Tendré sus cabezas, y ni siquiera las palabras de mi padre los "
"salvarán de la ira de los elfos!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/15_Princess_Of_Blood.cfg:193
msgid "This is no good, we shouldn't have killed so many of them!"
msgstr "¡Esto no está bien, no deberíamos haber matado a tantos de ellos!"

#. [print]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/15_Princess_Of_Blood.cfg:202
msgid "You may still defeat $units_slayed elves!"
msgstr "¡Aún puedes derrotar a $units_slayed elfos!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/15_Princess_Of_Blood.cfg:218
msgid "Argh! How could I have been... bested by humans...?!"
msgstr "¡Argh! ¿Cómo pude ser… vencida por humanos…?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/15_Princess_Of_Blood.cfg:222
msgid ""
"Listen, what the hell is wrong with you? Haven't we told you that we're "
"friends? Instead of fighting us, you should be fighting the drakes, who are "
"trying to kill everyone in this side of the world – including you elves!"
msgstr ""
"Escucha, ¿qué demonios te pasa? ¿No te hemos dicho que somos amigos? En "
"lugar de luchar contra nosotros, deberías estar luchando contra los dracos, "
"¡que están intentando matar a todos en este lado del mundo… incluidos "
"ustedes los elfos!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/15_Princess_Of_Blood.cfg:226
msgid ""
"(furious) Don't you dare tell me what I have to do, you disgusting vermin! "
"You know nothing about anything, much less about me...!"
msgstr ""
"(furiosa) ¡No te atrevas a decirme qué tengo que hacer, repugnante alimaña! "
"¡No sabes nada de nada, y mucho menos de mí…!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/15_Princess_Of_Blood.cfg:230
msgid ""
"You could try and enlighten us, then – but not now; we're really in a hurry, "
"and you've delayed us far too much already. We shall bring you along with us "
"as a captive, and when we return, we'll return you to your father."
msgstr ""
"Podrías intentar iluminarnos, entonces… pero no ahora; realmente tenemos "
"prisa, y ya nos has retrasado demasiado. Te llevaremos con nosotros como "
"cautiva, y cuando regresemos, te devolveremos a tu padre."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/15_Princess_Of_Blood.cfg:234
msgid ""
"You defeat me in my own land and then you humiliate me further by making me "
"your pet?! Why don't you just behead me and feed my corpse to your dogs and "
"be done with..."
msgstr ""
"¿Me derrotas en mi propia tierra y luego me humillas aún más haciéndome tu "
"mascota? ¿Por qué no me cortan la cabeza y alimentan mi cadáver a sus perros "
"y terminan con…?"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/15_Princess_Of_Blood.cfg:259
msgid ""
"We'll have to tie her tightly, she won't waste a single opportunity to flee "
"and kill us in our sleep."
msgstr ""
"Tendremos que atarla fuerte, no desaprovechará ni una sola oportunidad de "
"escapar y matarnos mientras dormimos."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/15_Princess_Of_Blood.cfg:263
msgid ""
"(sigh) Indeed we'll have. I just wonder what must have happened to make her "
"so bitter; elves are not known for being so violent for nothing..."
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) En efecto tendremos que hacerlo. Solo me pregunto qué habrá pasado "
"para hacerla tan amargada; los elfos no son conocidos por ser tan violentos "
"sin razón…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/15_Princess_Of_Blood.cfg:282
msgid ""
"You have proved your mettle, humans, but this is end game for you. Kill them "
"all, elves!"
msgstr ""
"Han probado su valía, humanos, pero este es el fin para ustedes. ¡Mátenlos a "
"todos, elfos!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/15_Princess_Of_Blood.cfg:286
msgid ""
"Damn it, elvish reinforcements have arrived! Even if we show them Gil-"
"Thelyon's seal, I doubt they'll listen to us, covered in elvish blood as we "
"are!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldición, han llegado refuerzos élficos! ¡Aunque les mostremos el sello de "
"Gil-Thelyon, dudo que nos escuchen, cubiertos de sangre élfica como estamos!"

