#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:98
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:120
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:159
msgid "Minotaurs"
msgstr "Minotauros"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/16_Firecloud_Peak.cfg:181
msgid ""
"Olokun, do you know anything about this sorceress Gil-Thelyon was talking "
"about?"
msgstr ""
"Olokun, ¿sabes algo sobre esta hechicera de la que hablaba Gil-Thelyon?"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/16_Firecloud_Peak.cfg:185
msgid ""
"Don't abuse his knowledge, Tenma, he doesn't know everything; how can he "
"know some random sorceress in this vast continent when he comes from another?"
msgstr ""
"No abuses de su conocimiento, Tenma, no lo sabe todo; ¿cómo podría conocer a "
"una hechicera cualquiera en este vasto continente cuando viene de otro?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/16_Firecloud_Peak.cfg:189
msgid ""
"Actually, I do know who she is be, because she's known in Maat'Kare too. "
"Valerya is an ancient mage, a master of fire magic who's visited my people a "
"few times over the centuries. She's even learned some of our lore, elemental "
"summoning included."
msgstr ""
"En realidad, sí sé quién es, porque también es conocida en Maat'Kare. "
"Valerya es una maga antigua, maestra de la magia de fuego que ha visitado a "
"mi pueblo varias veces a lo largo de los siglos. Incluso ha aprendido algo "
"de nuestro saber, incluida la invocación elemental."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/16_Firecloud_Peak.cfg:193
msgid "See? He does know everything."
msgstr "¿Ves? Sí sabe todo."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/16_Firecloud_Peak.cfg:197
msgid ""
"(snorting) Anyway, we must leave someone at our camp as we search for that "
"mage; if our princess is left alone, she'll surely find a way to escape."
msgstr ""
"(bufando) De todos modos, debemos dejar a alguien en nuestro campamento "
"mientras buscamos a esa maga; si dejamos sola a nuestra princesa, "
"seguramente encontrará una forma de escapar."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/16_Firecloud_Peak.cfg:201
msgid ""
"Well thought. Also, we must be careful as we search for her; not only does "
"this volcano constantly erupt, but Valerya herself may think we're enemies "
"and rain fire upon us."
msgstr ""
"Bien pensado. Además, debemos tener cuidado al buscarla; no solo este volcán "
"erupciona constantemente, sino que la propia Valerya podría pensar que somos "
"enemigos y hacernos llover fuego encima."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/16_Firecloud_Peak.cfg:218
msgid ""
"<i>You certainly are bold, travellers, to walk so willingly into a living "
"volcano...</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Ciertamente son valientes, viajeros, al entrar tan dispuestos en un "
"volcán vivo…</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/16_Firecloud_Peak.cfg:222
msgid "Lady Valerya, is that you?"
msgstr "Señora Valerya, ¿es usted?"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/16_Firecloud_Peak.cfg:226
msgid ""
"<i>...and well-informed too, to know my name... Usually I just chase "
"unwanted trespassers away, but I sense a strange power coming from one of "
"you, and that's making me curious... Come, travellers, meet me at my "
"Academy, I'll hear whatever you have to say...</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>…y también bien informados, al conocer mi nombre… Normalmente solo "
"ahuyento a los intrusos no deseados, pero siento un poder extraño viniendo "
"de uno de ustedes, y eso me está haciendo curiosa… Vengan, viajeros, "
"encuéntrenme en mi Academia, escucharé lo que tengan que decir…</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/16_Firecloud_Peak.cfg:249
msgid ""
"So you are the lassie who wields such strange elemental powers... I am "
"Valerya of the Northlands, headmistress of this independent magic academy; I "
"have gathered a vast knowledge within these walls, and have learned "
"different kinds of magic, but I don't recognize the energy emanating from "
"you. Would you please tell me what they are?"
msgstr ""
"Así que tú eres la muchacha que empuña poderes elementales tan extraños… Soy "
"Valerya de las Tierras del Norte, directora de esta academia de magia "
"independiente; he reunido un vasto conocimiento dentro de estas paredes y he "
"aprendido diferentes tipos de magia, pero no reconozco la energía que emana "
"de ti. ¿Podrías decirme qué son, por favor?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/16_Firecloud_Peak.cfg:253
msgid ""
"Er, well, sure, but you seem to be in trouble right now, attacked by so many "
"people at once; don't you think we should deal with them first?"
msgstr ""
"Eh, bueno, claro, pero parece que estás en problemas ahora mismo, atacada "
"por tanta gente a la vez; ¿no crees que deberíamos lidiar con ellos primero?"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/16_Firecloud_Peak.cfg:257
msgid ""
"Yeah, maybe you're right; though we're always repelling stray bands of "
"Eventide and Wesnothians, it's not like we truly need to totally focus on "
"them..."
msgstr ""
"Sí, tal vez tengas razón; aunque siempre estamos repeliendo bandas perdidas "
"de Eventide y wesnothianos, no es como si realmente necesitáramos enfocarnos "
"totalmente en ellos…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/16_Firecloud_Peak.cfg:261
msgid ""
"By the way, my name is Tenma Yozora, and these are my friends, Olokun from "
"New Maat'Kare and Kenshiro from Kodakuni."
msgstr ""
"Por cierto, mi nombre es Tenma Yozora, y estos son mis amigos, Olokun de "
"Nueva Maat'Kare y Kenshiro de Kodakuni."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/16_Firecloud_Peak.cfg:265
msgid ""
"Oh, so you're Maat'Karian? How's the city these days? It's been ages since "
"I've last been there – though I don't think it's changed that much, right? "
"Come, I'll serve you some beer while we..."
msgstr ""
"Oh, ¿entonces eres maat'kariana? ¿Cómo está la ciudad estos días? Hace "
"siglos que no he estado allí… aunque no creo que haya cambiado tanto, "
"¿verdad? Vengan, les serviré algo de cerveza mientras…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/16_Firecloud_Peak.cfg:269
msgid "Ahem! Lady Valerya, we have to fight, remember?"
msgstr "¡Ejem! Señora Valerya, tenemos que pelear, ¿recuerda?"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/16_Firecloud_Peak.cfg:273
msgid "(sigh) Ah, yeah, right. These folks are so troublesome..."
msgstr "(suspiro) Ah, sí, cierto. Esta gente es tan problemática…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/16_Firecloud_Peak.cfg:277
msgid "(whisper) You didn't tell me she was so air-headed."
msgstr "(susurra) No me dijiste que era tan despistada."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/16_Firecloud_Peak.cfg:281
msgid ""
"(whisper) Well, I'd only heard stories about her; judging from them, I'd "
"really thought she'd be more solemn and all..."
msgstr ""
"(susurra) Bueno, solo había oído historias sobre ella; a juzgar por ellas, "
"realmente pensé que sería más solemne y todo eso…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/16_Firecloud_Peak.cfg:335
msgid "Wait, are those... oxen or men?"
msgstr "Espera, ¿esos son… bueyes o hombres?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/16_Firecloud_Peak.cfg:339
msgid ""
"Those are minotaurs; they may look bestial, but they're actually very "
"intelligent. There are many of them in Netjer-Ta, but I had no idea that "
"they lived on this continent too. Who knows, maybe they were taken there "
"from this continent by the Windsong in ancient times..."
msgstr ""
"Esos son minotauros; pueden parecer bestiales, pero en realidad son muy "
"inteligentes. Hay muchos en Netjer-Ta, pero no tenía idea de que también "
"vivieran en este continente. Quién sabe, tal vez fueron llevados allí desde "
"este continente por las Hijas del Viento en tiempos antiguos…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/16_Firecloud_Peak.cfg:348
msgid ""
"(smiling) Well, so now we can talk! Come in, please, my cook Hanya was "
"preparing venison before those amateurs arrived, she must be done already, "
"so let's eat while we talk!"
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) ¡Bueno, ahora sí podemos hablar! Pasen, por favor, mi cocinera "
"Hanya estaba preparando venado antes de que llegaran esos aficionados, ya "
"debe estar listo, ¡así que comamos mientras hablamos!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/16_Firecloud_Peak.cfg:352
msgid ""
"(happy) You read my thoughts, Lady Valerya, I was starving after travelling "
"so long!"
msgstr ""
"(feliz) ¡Me leyó el pensamiento, señora Valerya, me moría de hambre después "
"de viajar tanto tiempo!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/16_Firecloud_Peak.cfg:356
msgid ""
"Nay, call me Valerya, please, I'm a Northerner, not a frivolous Wesnothian "
"noblewoman to be addressed as 'Lady'! Now, please do tell me how you manage "
"to summon those elemental-like creatures; it's been a really long time since "
"I last saw such interesting novelty!"
msgstr ""
"No, llámame Valerya, por favor, soy norteña, ¡no una frívola noble "
"wesnothiana a la que hay que llamar «señora»! Ahora, por favor cuéntenme "
"cómo logran invocar a esas criaturas parecidas a elementales; ¡hace "
"muchísimo tiempo que no veía una novedad tan interesante!"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/16_Firecloud_Peak.cfg:360
msgid ""
"It may be only my impression, but these two will get along quite well..."
msgstr "Puede ser solo mi impresión, pero estas dos se llevarán muy bien…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/16_Firecloud_Peak.cfg:364
msgid ""
"(chuckles) That doesn't surprise me, though; Tenma is the kind of person "
"around whom other people gather with ease. Now, let's follow them; if we "
"don't intervene, they'll spend months talking about every possible subject "
"but for the one we came to discuss."
msgstr ""
"(ríe) Eso no me sorprende, sin embargo; Tenma es el tipo de persona "
"alrededor de la cual la gente se reúne con facilidad. Ahora, sigámoslas; si "
"no intervenimos, pasarán meses hablando de cualquier tema posible excepto "
"del que vinimos a discutir."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/16_Firecloud_Peak.cfg:368
msgid ""
"You go there, I'm returning to our camp; someone has to keep an eye on our "
"princess, after all..."
msgstr ""
"Ustedes vayan allá, yo regreso a nuestro campamento; después de todo, "
"alguien tiene que vigilar a nuestra princesa…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/16_Firecloud_Peak.cfg:403
msgid ""
"And, as expected, I manage to escape. I will be merciful to you, humans: go "
"as far away from the Lins-Elens as you can, and I will not come for you with "
"an entire elvish army. Get within our earshots, though, and not even all the "
"hordes of Wesnoth shall save you from my wrath!"
msgstr ""
"Y, como era de esperar, logré escapar. Seré misericordiosa con ustedes, "
"humanos: aléjense lo más posible de los Lins-Elens y no iré tras ustedes con "
"todo un ejército élfico. Pero si se acercan lo suficiente como para que los "
"escuchemos, ni siquiera todas las hordas de Wesnoth los salvarán de mi ira."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/16_Firecloud_Peak.cfg:407
msgid ""
"Damn it! She will surely slander us to the entire kingdom, and we won't even "
"be able to defend ourselves! I fear we've just ruined the alliance between "
"the elves and the Baryags..."
msgstr ""
"¡Maldición! Seguramente nos calumniará ante todo el reino y ni siquiera "
"podremos defendernos. ¡Temo que acabamos de arruinar la alianza entre los "
"elfos y los baryags!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/16_Firecloud_Peak.cfg:423
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:144
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:259
msgid ""
"So, after living for so long and travelling so much, this is how I'm gonna "
"die...?"
msgstr ""
"Entonces, después de vivir tanto tiempo y viajar tanto, ¿así es como voy a "
"morir…?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/16_Firecloud_Peak.cfg:435
msgid ""
"We're too slow, at this rate we'll return to the Emerald Plains only to see "
"it burning!"
msgstr ""
"Somos demasiado lentos, ¡a este ritmo regresaremos a las Llanuras Esmeralda "
"solo para verlas ardiendo!"

