#. [side]
#. [side], type=Drake Flameheart
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:80
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:151
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:189
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:81
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:155
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:164
msgid "Shakaar Drakes"
msgstr "Dracos Shakaar"

#. [message], speaker=Kaldan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:200
msgid ""
"How dare you bring the daughter of the King-in-the-Woods in chains to this "
"palace?! I'll have you executed for this-"
msgstr ""
"¡Cómo se atreven a traer a la hija del Rey-en-el-Bosque encadenada a este "
"palacio! ¡Los haré ejecutar por esto—"

#. [message], speaker=Thelyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:204
msgid ""
"Kaldan, that is enough! And you, Cornelya, should I understand this as "
"meaning that you disrespected the safe-conduct I gave these humans?"
msgstr ""
"¡Kaldan, basta! Y tú, Cornelya, ¿debo entender esto como que desrespetaste "
"el salvoconducto que les di a estos humanos?"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:208
msgid ""
"(annoyed) I saw these humans wandering about our forests on their own, how "
"could I have guessed that they were here with your permission?"
msgstr ""
"(molesta) Vi a estos humanos vagando solos por nuestros bosques, ¿cómo iba a "
"adivinar que estaban aquí con tu permiso?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:212
msgid ""
"Well, we actually told you that, and even showed you Lord Gil-Thelyon's "
"seal, which you pierced with an arrow..."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, en realidad te lo dijimos y hasta te mostramos el sello del señor Gil-"
"Thelyon, que atravesaste con una flecha…"

#. [message], speaker=Thelyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:216
msgid ""
"(sigh) I apologise for my daughter's misdeeds, friends. I shall compensate "
"you for that later, but now I want to say that I'm both impressed and "
"satisfied that you managed to bring the feared Crimson Sorceress out of her "
"abode."
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) Me disculpo por las fechorías de mi hija, amigos. Los compensaré "
"por eso más tarde, pero ahora quiero decir que estoy tanto impresionado como "
"satisfecho de que hayan logrado sacar a la temida Hechicera Carmesí de su "
"morada."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:220
msgid ""
"What can I say? Even I will be troubled if the drakes become too powerful; "
"of all beings on this planet, they're the ones against whom my flames are "
"least effective."
msgstr ""
"¿Qué puedo decir? Hasta yo tendré problemas si los dracos se vuelven "
"demasiado poderosos; de todos los seres en este planeta, son aquellos contra "
"quienes mis llamas son menos efectivas."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:224
msgid ""
"Lord Gil-Thelyon, if I may ask, how's the war going on in this forest and in "
"the Emerald Plains?"
msgstr ""
"Señor Gil-Thelyon, si me permite preguntar, ¿cómo va la guerra en este "
"bosque y en las Llanuras Esmeralda?"

#. [message], speaker=Thelyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:228
msgid ""
"Not as well as I would have wished, unfortunately; the north-eastern "
"outskirts of our forest have been burned to a cinder, and yesterday one of "
"my messengers returned from the Baryag lands with news that the eastern half "
"of the Emerald Plains had been almost completely taken – though that is "
"mostly because Queen Dragana evacuated the cities there."
msgstr ""
"No tan bien como hubiera deseado, lamentablemente; las afueras nororientales "
"de nuestro bosque han sido reducidas a cenizas, y ayer uno de mis mensajeros "
"regresó de las tierras baryag con la noticia de que la mitad oriental de las "
"Llanuras Esmeralda había sido casi completamente tomada… aunque eso es "
"principalmente porque la reina Dragana evacuó las ciudades allí."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:232
msgid ""
"Scorched earth strategy, I see... It usually works on humans, elves and "
"dwarves, but it won't work on drakes. Olokun tells me you asked for the aid "
"of other nations, Wesnoth included, is that true?"
msgstr ""
"Estrategia de tierra arrasada, ya veo… Suele funcionar con humanos, elfos y "
"enanos, pero no funcionará con dracos. Olokun me dice que pidieron ayuda a "
"otras naciones, incluido Wesnoth, ¿es cierto?"

#. [message], speaker=Thelyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:236
msgid ""
"Yes, but alas, none of them has your sense, and have opted to stay out of "
"our alliance – though the Northern Alliance claimed that, as soon as they "
"are done with a threat of their own, they shall send an army to our aid."
msgstr ""
"Sí, pero lamentablemente ninguno de ellos tiene tu sentido común y ha optado "
"por quedarse fuera de nuestra alianza… aunque la Alianza del Norte afirmó "
"que, tan pronto como terminen con una amenaza propia, enviarán un ejército "
"para ayudarnos."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:240
msgid ""
"Northerners are tough, but they won't be of much aid against drakes; if you "
"want my opinion, I say that we need to fight fire with fire: we must get "
"drakes to help us fight drakes."
msgstr ""
"Los norteños son duros, pero no serán de mucha ayuda contra dracos; si "
"quieres mi opinión, digo que debemos luchar contra el fuego con fuego: "
"debemos conseguir que dracos nos ayuden a luchar contra dracos."

#. [message], speaker=Thelyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:244
msgid ""
"Would that even possible? I thought every drake on this side of the "
"continent was united under Vladnir Ohn's campaign."
msgstr ""
"¿Sería siquiera posible? Pensé que todos los dracos de este lado del "
"continente estaban unidos bajo la campaña de Vladnir Ohn."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:248
msgid ""
"Not the clan of Veshtar Joohn, who lives in the Shakaar Mountains. She's "
"Vladnir Ohn's sister, but I know that they're fierce rivals, so maybe she "
"considers him as much of a threat as we do. If anything, she'll listen to "
"what I have to say; we know each other, after all."
msgstr ""
"No el clan de Veshtar Joohn, que vive en las Montañas Shakaar. Ella es "
"hermana de Vladnir Ohn, pero sé que son rivales feroces, así que tal vez lo "
"considere una amenaza tanto como nosotros. Si algo, escuchará lo que tengo "
"que decir; nos conocemos, después de todo."

#. [message], speaker=Thelyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:252
msgid ""
"Then you must hurry again, this time to the Shakaar Mountains. I shall "
"provide you with more provisions for this journey, and I shall also provide "
"you with reinforcements: Cornelya, I want you to follow these humans, and "
"fight alongside them until they decide your service is enough."
msgstr ""
"Entonces deben apresurarse de nuevo, esta vez a las Montañas Shakaar. Les "
"proporcionaré más provisiones para este viaje y también refuerzos: Cornelya, "
"quiero que sigas a estos humanos y luches junto a ellos hasta que decidan "
"que tu servicio es suficiente."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:256
msgid ""
"WHAT?! No, you better choose another punishment for me, father, for there's "
"absolutely no way I will-"
msgstr ""
"¿¡QUÉ!? No, mejor elige otro castigo para mí, padre, porque de ninguna "
"manera voy a—"

#. [message], speaker=Thelyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:260
msgid ""
"(angry) I speak not as your father now, but as your king! If you wish to "
"disobey it, you are free to do so, but then you must accept the consequences "
"of that and leave the Lins-Elens forever!"
msgstr ""
"(enojado) ¡Ahora hablo no como tu padre, sino como tu rey! Si deseas "
"desobedecer, eres libre de hacerlo, ¡pero entonces debes aceptar las "
"consecuencias y dejar los Lins-Elens para siempre!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:264
msgid ""
"Lord King, with all due respect, if she has no wish to fight for us, then we "
"shall not demand that of her."
msgstr ""
"Señor Rey, con todo respeto, si no tiene deseo de luchar por nosotros, "
"entonces no se lo exigiremos."

#. [message], speaker=Thelyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:268
msgid ""
"You are too kind, Olokun, but this is about much more than her attack on "
"you. She has often exceeded her duties of protecting our forest, going as "
"far as to prey on those beyond our trees. Since she refuses to stop fighting "
"outsiders, then it seems fitting that she fights <i>for</i> them. Let the "
"battlefield teach her to rely on those standing by her side, no matter their "
"background; for if they fall, so does she."
msgstr ""
"Eres demasiado amable, Olokun, pero esto va mucho más allá de su ataque "
"contra ustedes. A menudo ha excedido sus deberes de proteger nuestro bosque, "
"llegando incluso a cazar a quienes están más allá de nuestros árboles. Ya "
"que se niega a dejar de luchar contra forasteros, entonces parece apropiado "
"que luche <i>por</i> ellos. Que el campo de batalla le enseñe a confiar en "
"quienes están a su lado, sin importar su origen; porque si ellos caen, ella "
"también cae."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:275
msgid ""
"(furious) If that is your wish, King-in-the-Woods, then I shall comply. Now, "
"if I may, I shall leave and suit myself for the tort... I mean, the journey "
"ahead."
msgstr ""
"(furiosa) Si ese es tu deseo, Rey-en-el-Bosque, entonces cumpliré. Ahora, si "
"me permites, me iré a preparar para la tortu… quiero decir, el viaje que "
"tengo por delante."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:291
msgid "Lord Gil-Thelyon, may I ask you why she hates humans so much?"
msgstr ""
"Señor Gil-Thelyon, ¿puedo preguntarle por qué odia tanto a los humanos?"

#. [message], speaker=Thelyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:295
msgid ""
"(sigh) She was not always this ruthless warrior. As a child, she used to "
"visit Baryag towns near our north-eastern frontiers, to tend to their ill. "
"Her blood father had been a frontier captain who died defending those same "
"Baryags from Wesnothians; I believe she wanted to honour his sacrifice by "
"helping those he gave his life defending. Tending to those humans did her "
"well: it was then that she developed her connection to the faerie plane, and "
"she held the promise of becoming a powerful healer, perhaps even a Sylph."
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) No siempre fue esta guerrera despiadada. De niña solía visitar "
"pueblos baryag cerca de nuestras fronteras nororientales para cuidar a sus "
"enfermos. Su padre de sangre había sido un capitán fronterizo que murió "
"defendiendo a esos mismos baryags de los wesnothianos; creo que quería "
"honrar su sacrificio ayudando a quienes él dio su vida defendiendo. Cuidar a "
"esos humanos le hizo bien: fue entonces cuando desarrolló su conexión con el "
"plano feérico y tenía el potencial de convertirse en una poderosa sanadora, "
"tal vez incluso en una Sílfide."

#. [message], speaker=Thelyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:299
msgid ""
"But one day, as she visited one of those towns alongside her mother - "
"herself a warrior -, the two found themselves involved in one of the endless "
"clan wars of the Baryags. Cornelya and her mother both stayed to help their "
"friends; but that very town's inhabitants betrayed their own chief as the "
"tides of battle turned against them, and opened their own gates to the "
"enemy. I will not paint with words the brutalities visited upon the two as "
"they became prisoners; it suffices to say that Cornelya alone managed to "
"escape."
msgstr ""
"Pero un día, mientras visitaba uno de esos pueblos junto a su madre —ella "
"misma una guerrera—, ambas se vieron involucradas en una de las "
"interminables guerras de clanes de los baryags. Cornelya y su madre se "
"quedaron para ayudar a sus amigos; pero los habitantes de ese mismo pueblo "
"traicionaron a su propio jefe cuando las tornas de la batalla se volvieron "
"contra ellos y abrieron sus propias puertas al enemigo. No describiré con "
"palabras las brutalidades cometidas contra las dos al convertirse en "
"prisioneras; basta decir que Cornelya logró escapar sola."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:303
msgid "That's... horrible..."
msgstr "Eso es… horrible…"

#. [message], speaker=Thelyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:307
msgid ""
"I adopted her into my household, hoping to provide her with a place of love "
"and kindness in which she could heal... but to little avail. Cornelya's hurt "
"has turned to rage, a rage so great it has grown to encompass anyone and "
"everyone beyond our forests. In her heart, all she understands is that her "
"father, her mother and herself sought to help humans and suffered greatly "
"for that; suffered because the very people they sought to help betrayed them."
msgstr ""
"La adopté en mi hogar, esperando proporcionarle un lugar de amor y bondad en "
"el que pudiera sanar… pero de poco sirvió. El dolor de Cornelya se convirtió "
"en rabia, una rabia tan grande que ha crecido para abarcar a cualquiera y "
"todos más allá de nuestros bosques. En su corazón, todo lo que entiende es "
"que su padre, su madre y ella misma buscaron ayudar a humanos y sufrieron "
"enormemente por ello; sufrieron porque las mismas personas a las que "
"intentaron ayudar los traicionaron."

#. [message], speaker=Thelyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:311
msgid ""
"But I believe the little girl who loved saving lives instead of taking them "
"has not died completely. Notice how her weapons are crafted out of ironwood "
"rather than iron or steel, metals that dampen elvenkind's deeper bonds to "
"the faerie. Had she truly embraced the path of the warrior, she would not "
"have bothered to do that. I want to believe that, deep down, she wants to be "
"freed of all this hatred, but is unable to do that alone - and unable to do "
"that by living among elves only."
msgstr ""
"Pero creo que la niña pequeña que amaba salvar vidas en lugar de quitarlas "
"no ha muerto por completo. Fíjense en que sus armas están hechas de madera "
"de hierro en lugar de hierro o acero, metales que amortiguan los lazos más "
"profundos de los elfos con lo feérico. Si realmente hubiera abrazado el "
"camino del guerrero, no se habría molestado en hacer eso. Quiero creer que, "
"en el fondo, quiere liberarse de todo este odio, pero es incapaz de hacerlo "
"sola… y es incapaz de hacerlo viviendo solo entre elfos."

#. [message], speaker=Thelyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:315
msgid ""
"She feels my 'sentence' is a punishment, but I made this decision with the "
"hope that I have set her on the path to returning to the person she once "
"was. I can feel you are good people; can I trust that you will keep my "
"daughter safe - from both the world and from herself?"
msgstr ""
"Ella siente que mi «sentencia» es un castigo, pero tomé esta decisión con la "
"esperanza de haberla puesto en el camino de volver a ser la persona que "
"alguna vez fue. Siento que son buena gente; ¿puedo confiar en que mantendrán "
"a mi hija a salvo… tanto del mundo como de sí misma?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:319
msgid ""
"Lord Gil-Thelyon, I may not know what she's experienced, but I know I can be "
"there for her whenever she needs. You can rest assured that we'll bring her "
"back home safe and sound."
msgstr ""
"Señor Gil-Thelyon, puede que no sepa lo que ella ha vivido, pero sé que "
"puedo estar ahí para ella cuando lo necesite. Puede estar tranquilo de que "
"la traeremos de vuelta a casa sana y salva."

#. [message], speaker=Thelyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:323
msgid ""
"I thank you from the bottom of my heart, Tenma Yozora. Now, you must go and "
"convince Veshtar Joohn to help us; the outcome of this war depends on your "
"success!"
msgstr ""
"Les agradezco desde el fondo de mi corazón, Tenma Yozora. Ahora deben ir y "
"convencer a Veshtar Joohn de que nos ayude; ¡el resultado de esta guerra "
"depende de su éxito!"

#. [unit], id=Kohn, type=Drake Flameheart
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:381
msgid "Grenn Kohn"
msgstr "Grenn Kohn"

#. [unit], id=Viryos, type=Minotaur Elder
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:390
msgid "Viryos"
msgstr "Viryos"

#. [unit], id=Kaicos, type=Minotaur Executioner
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:399
msgid "Kaicos"
msgstr "Kaicos"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:421
msgid ""
"Well, we're now on the southern border of Veshtar's lands; those mountains "
"to the north are the Shakaar, and the river plains before you are minotaur "
"land. Just a little more walking and we'll reach Inferno's Mouth, the valley "
"which leads to Veshtar's citadel, but let's proceed carefully; the minotaurs "
"are even less kind and hospitable than the Baryags."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, ahora estamos en la frontera sur de las tierras de Veshtar; esas "
"montañas al norte son las Shakaar, y las llanuras fluviales delante de "
"ustedes son territorio minotauro. Solo un poco más de caminata y llegaremos "
"a la Boca del Infierno, el valle que lleva a la ciudadela de Veshtar, pero "
"avancemos con cuidado; los minotauros son aún menos amables y hospitalarios "
"que los baryags."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:425
msgid ""
"(whisper) Tenma, I know you want to help her, but beware that elf; someone "
"who tries to kill you once may as well give it another try..."
msgstr ""
"(susurra) Tenma, sé que quieres ayudarla, pero ten cuidado con esa elfa; "
"alguien que intenta matarte una vez bien podría intentarlo de nuevo…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:429
msgid ""
"Does that mean that I should be wary of you humans too? And before you ask, "
"yes, I heard you; my hearing is elven, after all."
msgstr ""
"¿Eso significa que también debo desconfiar de ustedes los humanos? Y antes "
"de que preguntes, sí, los oí; mi oído es élfico, después de todo."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:433
msgid ""
"You ignored your father's orders to attack us once, so it's only natural "
"that I distrust you."
msgstr ""
"Ignoraste las órdenes de tu padre de atacarnos una vez, así que es natural "
"que desconfíe de ti."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:437
msgid ""
"It's different now; he'll actually expel me from the Lins-Elens if I don't "
"guard your sorry backs, and I don't want to be forced out of my home, at "
"least not because of some unworthy humans."
msgstr ""
"Ahora es diferente; realmente me expulsará de los Lins-Elens si no protejo "
"sus miserables espaldas, y no quiero ser forzada a salir de mi hogar, al "
"menos no por culpa de unos humanos indignos."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:441
msgid "Don't worry, Cornelya, he's just too paranoid."
msgstr "No te preocupes, Cornelya, solo es demasiado paranoico."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:445
msgid "(annoyed) Tsc..."
msgstr "(molesto) Tch…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:480
msgid ""
"For once I'd have liked to simply cross a stretch of land without a battle "
"to delay and wear us out..."
msgstr ""
"Por una vez me hubiera gustado simplemente cruzar un tramo de tierra sin una "
"batalla que nos retrase y nos desgaste…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:484
msgid ""
"But that may be used in our favour; help the drakes repel minotaurs, and our "
"audience with Veshtar herself is be all but guaranteed. I may be her friend, "
"but that isn't enough to convince other drakes to let me inside their land."
msgstr ""
"Pero eso puede usarse a nuestro favor; ayudemos a los dracos a repeler a los "
"minotauros y nuestra audiencia con la propia Veshtar estará prácticamente "
"garantizada. Puede que sea su amiga, pero eso no es suficiente para "
"convencer a otros dracos de dejarme entrar en su tierra."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:506
msgid ""
"I'm certain I've already told you to stop staring at me like I'm some sort "
"of deity, Olokun Maahes."
msgstr ""
"Estoy segura de que ya te dije que dejes de mirarme como si fuera algún tipo "
"de deidad, Olokun Maahes."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:510
msgid ""
"I know, right? Took him two months to stop giving me offerings and prayers."
msgstr ""
"Lo sé, ¿verdad? Le tomó dos meses dejar de hacerme ofrendas y oraciones."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:514
msgid ""
"(blushing) I didn't...! Well, I'm simply curious to see you in action, La- I "
"mean, Valerya. In the circles of our Crimson scholars, one of the most "
"popular debates is the one regarding who the most powerful Crimson master in "
"history was. Many consider Sadjet, the Fire Empress, the obvious choice; but "
"there are some who argue - quite passionately, I must say - that you reached "
"an even higher level than she did. Sadjet never single-handedly slayed "
"dragons or destroyed the Wall of Heaven and Earth... (to the others) That's "
"one of our cities defences, mind you."
msgstr ""
"(sonrojado) ¡No lo hice…! Bueno, simplemente tengo curiosidad por verte en "
"acción, Se— quiero decir, Valerya. En los círculos de nuestros eruditos "
"Carmesí, uno de los debates más populares es el de quién fue el maestro "
"Carmesí más poderoso de la historia. Muchos consideran a Sadjet, la "
"Emperatriz del Fuego, la elección obvia; pero hay algunos que argumentan —"
"bastante apasionadamente, debo decir— que tú alcanzaste un nivel aún más "
"alto que ella. Sadjet nunca mató dragones sola ni destruyó la Muralla del "
"Cielo y la Tierra… (a los demás) Eso es una de las defensas de nuestras "
"ciudades, por cierto."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:518
msgid ""
"You're totally one of those who 'passionately' defend Valerya's the "
"strongest, aren't you?"
msgstr ""
"Eres totalmente uno de esos que «apasionadamente» defienden que Valerya es "
"la más fuerte, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:522
msgid "Well..."
msgstr "Bueno..."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:526
msgid ""
"Kenshiro's eyes have been fixed on you with the same intensity, sorceress; "
"he's just better at disguising it."
msgstr ""
"Los ojos de Kenshiro han estado fijos en ti con la misma intensidad, "
"hechicera; solo es mejor disimulándolo."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:530
msgid "(flustered) Keep <i>your</i> eyes on the battle ahead, <i>princess</i>."
msgstr ""
"(aturrullado) Mantén <i>tus</i> ojos en la batalla que viene, <i>princesa</"
"i>."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:534
msgid "Oh, now I'm curious. What has earned your special attention, warrior?"
msgstr ""
"Oh, ahora estoy curiosa. ¿Qué ha ganado tu atención especial, guerrero?"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:538
msgid ""
"It's just... I'm told you've been alive for seven centuries, so you must've "
"lived through the Silver Age of Wesnoth."
msgstr ""
"Es solo que… me han dicho que has estado viva durante siete siglos, así que "
"debiste haber vivido la Edad de Plata de Wesnoth."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:542
msgid ""
"I spent most of those years abroad, but yes, I knew the Wesnoth of those "
"days."
msgstr ""
"Pasé la mayor parte de esos años en el extranjero, pero sí, conocí el "
"Wesnoth de aquellos días."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:546
msgid ""
"I've also read the genealogies of Wesnoth's kings, and I recall that Queen "
"Alaevyanne, whose marriage to King Elemyrion sealed the Silver Peace, was "
"the niece of Addraryn, the Wyvern of Wesnoth, who had a single child: a girl "
"called Valerya. So I was wondering..."
msgstr ""
"También he leído las genealogías de los reyes de Wesnoth, y recuerdo que la "
"reina Alaevyanne, cuyo matrimonio con el rey Elemyrion selló la Paz de "
"Plata, era sobrina de Addraryn, el Guiverno de Wesnoth, quien tuvo una sola "
"hija: una chica llamada Valerya. Así que me preguntaba…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:550
msgid ""
"(sighs) Yes, I'm that Valerya. My father was Addraryn, who saved Wesnoth "
"from a Dunefolk invasion and helped pave the way to the Silver Peace..."
msgstr ""
"(suspira) Sí, soy esa Valerya. Mi padre fue Addraryn, quien salvó a Wesnoth "
"de una invasión barjana y ayudó a allanar el camino hacia la Paz de Plata…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:554
msgid ""
"Really?! I-it's an honour...! I mean, well... Addraryn is my favourite "
"Wesnothian historical figure: a peasant who became a hero and saved his "
"country from an invasion that would otherwise have destroyed everything..."
msgstr ""
"¿En serio? ¡E-es un honor…! Quiero decir, bueno… Addraryn es mi figura "
"histórica wesnothiana favorita: un campesino que se convirtió en héroe y "
"salvó a su país de una invasión que de otra forma habría destruido todo…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:558
msgid "I'm never hearing the end of it, am I?"
msgstr "Nunca voy a dejar de oírlo, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:562
msgid "Welcome to the club, sis."
msgstr "Bienvenida al club, hermana."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:576
msgid "So, Olokun, is she as cool as you've always thought her to be?"
msgstr "Entonces, Olokun, ¿es tan genial como siempre pensaste que sería?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:580
msgid ""
"(smirks) I'd say yes, but she'd dislike the flattery, and I'd rather not be "
"on the receiving end of her fireballs..."
msgstr ""
"(sonríe) Diría que sí, pero le disgustaría la adulación, y preferiría no "
"estar en el extremo receptor de sus bolas de fuego…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:584
msgid "(chuckles) Smart man."
msgstr "(ríe) Hombre listo."

#. [message], speaker=Viryos
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:598
msgid "By the Cursed Horns, Where did these people come from?!"
msgstr "¡Por los Cuernos Malditos, de dónde salieron estas personas!"

#. [message], speaker=Kohn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:602
msgid ""
"You, strangers! I don't know who you are, but if you help me repel these "
"pesky bull men, I shall aid you however I can. My post was caught completely "
"off guard..."
msgstr ""
"¡Ustedes, extraños! No sé quiénes son, pero si me ayudan a repeler a estos "
"molestos hombres toro, los ayudaré como pueda. Mi puesto fue tomado "
"completamente por sorpresa…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:606
msgid "Deal! (whisper) See, I told you it'd work..."
msgstr "¡Trato hecho! (susurra) ¿Ves? Te dije que funcionaría…"

#. [message], speaker=Kohn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:615
msgid ""
"Your aid came just in time, friends; my post never gets attacked, and so I "
"didn't think it'd be troublesome to send half of my warriors to Veshtar "
"Joohn's citadel, but then the river people chose precisely this time to "
"attack. Now, ask me whatever you want in return, that I shall give it to "
"you, as long as it's within my power, of course."
msgstr ""
"Su ayuda llegó justo a tiempo, amigos; mi puesto nunca es atacado, así que "
"no pensé que sería problemático enviar a la mitad de mis guerreros a la "
"ciudadela de Veshtar Joohn, pero entonces la gente del río eligió "
"precisamente este momento para atacar. Ahora, pídanme lo que quieran a "
"cambio, se los daré siempre y cuando esté en mi poder, por supuesto."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:619
msgid ""
"Drake, probably you've never heard of me, but I'm Valerya, more known as the "
"Crimson Sorceress, and I'm a friend of your Mother Queen, whom I've saved as "
"a small hatchling from Rohas, the Last Dragon. I came here wishing to see my "
"old friend again after so long, do you think it's within your power to get "
"me an audience with her?"
msgstr ""
"Draco, probablemente nunca has oído hablar de mí, pero soy Valerya, más "
"conocida como la Hechicera Carmesí, y soy amiga de tu Reina Madre, a quien "
"salvé cuando era una pequeña cría de Rohas, el Último Dragón. Vine aquí "
"deseando volver a ver a mi vieja amiga después de tanto tiempo, ¿crees que "
"está en tu poder conseguirme una audiencia con ella?"

#. [message], speaker=Kohn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:623
msgid ""
"I have heard of the Crimson Sorceress, but I didn't know she was friends "
"with Veshtar Joohn. If what you say is true, you'll surely be welcome in her "
"citadel, but I must first send our Mother Queen a request for an audience. "
"In the meanwhile, you may rest in my fortress."
msgstr ""
"He oído hablar de la Hechicera Carmesí, pero no sabía que era amiga de "
"Veshtar Joohn. Si lo que dices es cierto, seguramente serás bienvenida en su "
"ciudadela, pero primero debo enviar a nuestra Reina Madre una solicitud de "
"audiencia. Mientras tanto, pueden descansar en mi fortaleza."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:627
msgid ""
"I know I shouldn't think like this, but it will be kind of weird to have "
"drakes as friends after fighting against them for such a long time..."
msgstr ""
"Sé que no debería pensar así, pero será un poco raro tener dracos como "
"amigos después de luchar contra ellos tanto tiempo…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:631
msgid ""
"(smirking) You said you didn't want to be treated as Myra, but you don't "
"help us very much on that, do you?"
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Dijiste que no querías ser tratada como Myra, pero no nos ayudas "
"mucho en eso, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:635
msgid "(blushing) Well..."
msgstr "(sonrojada) Bueno…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/17_Friendly_Fire.cfg:652
msgid ""
"You know, I like doing things at my own pace, but maybe we should really "
"have hurried a bit now..."
msgstr ""
"Sabes, me gusta hacer las cosas a mi propio ritmo, pero tal vez realmente "
"deberíamos habernos apresurado un poco ahora…"

#. [scenario], id=18_Dead_Flames
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:5
msgid "Dead Flames"
msgstr "Llamas Muertas"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:25
msgid "Defeat Kon Garashé"
msgstr "Derrotar a Kon Garashé"

#. [side], type=Inferno Drake
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:82
msgid "Kon Garashé"
msgstr "Kon Garashé"

#. [side], type=Baryag Warfather
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:103
msgid "General Razhikin"
msgstr "General Razhikin"

#. [side], type=Baryag Warfather
#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:109
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:112
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:146
msgid "Baryags"
msgstr "Baryags"

#. [side], type=Elvish Sharpshooter
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:124
msgid "Commander Tindë"
msgstr "Comandante Tindë"

#. [side], type=Drake Flameheart
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:145
msgid "Kashiere"
msgstr "Kashiere"

#. [unit]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:208
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:247
msgid "Reanimated Drake"
msgstr "Draco Reanimado"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:231
msgid ""
"Everyone else caught the irony of this place's naming, right? I don't think "
"I've seen a worse battlefield before..."
msgstr ""
"Todos los demás captaron la ironía del nombre de este lugar, ¿verdad? No "
"creo haber visto un campo de batalla peor antes…"

#. [message], speaker=Tinde
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:235
msgid ""
"Lo, there comes Princess Cornelya and the human wanderers! They've truly "
"managed to bring the Shakaar Drakes to our side!"
msgstr ""
"¡Miren, ahí vienen la princesa Cornelya y los humanos errantes! ¡Realmente "
"lograron traer a los dracos Shakaar a nuestro lado!"

#. [message], speaker=Kashiere
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:239
msgid ""
"Hold on, elves, we're not your friends, but we're not your enemies either. "
"Attack our common enemies instead of us, and we shall do the same."
msgstr ""
"Esperen, elfos, no somos sus amigos, pero tampoco sus enemigos. Ataquen a "
"nuestros enemigos comunes en lugar de a nosotros y haremos lo mismo."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:243
msgid ""
"Veshtar Joohn didn't accept joining our alliance, friends, but her warriors "
"shall fight Vladnir Ohn's armies as well."
msgstr ""
"Veshtar Joohn no aceptó unirse a nuestra alianza, amigos, pero sus guerreros "
"lucharán contra los ejércitos de Vladnir Ohn también."

#. [message], speaker=Razhikin
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:247
msgid ""
"Eh, s'ppose that's better than nothing... Warriors, watch out which drake "
"you strike down, that not all of them are enemies!"
msgstr ""
"Eh, supongo que es mejor que nada… ¡Guerreros, tengan cuidado a qué draco "
"derriban, que no todos son enemigos!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:251
msgid ""
"So, Shadow Dancer, do you really want to compete against me on number of "
"kills?"
msgstr ""
"Entonces, Bailarín de las Sombras, ¿realmente quieres competir conmigo en "
"número de muertes?"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:255
msgid ""
"I should be the one asking that. You're a warrior amongst peaceful, sensible "
"elves, while I'm a warrior amongst warriors; there's no way I'll lose to you."
msgstr ""
"Debería ser yo quien preguntara eso. Tú eres una guerrera entre elfos "
"pacíficos y sensatos, mientras que yo soy un guerrero entre guerreros; no "
"hay forma de que te pierda."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:259
msgid ""
"We'll see about that... To make things more interesting, let us make a "
"wager: whoever wins shall hunt and cook for the other for a whole week, is "
"that good for you?"
msgstr ""
"Ya veremos… Para hacerlo más interesante, hagamos una apuesta: quien gane "
"cazarán y cocinarán para el otro durante toda una semana, ¿te parece bien?"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:263
msgid "Deal..."
msgstr "Trato hecho…"

#. [message], speaker=Kashiere
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:303
msgid ""
"By the Eternal Flame, what is happening to those drakes? Has that idiot "
"Vladnir thrown some curse on his own warriors?!"
msgstr ""
"¡Por la Llama Eterna, qué les está pasando a esos dracos! ¿Acaso ese idiota "
"de Vladnir lanzó alguna maldición sobre sus propios guerreros?"

#. [message], speaker=Garashe
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:307
msgid ""
"It pains me to defile our brother's corpses with such vile human magic, but "
"Lord Vladnir Ohn says it's necessary for our victory... Fight on, brothers, "
"don't let death itself stop our dream from coming true!"
msgstr ""
"Me duele profanar los cadáveres de nuestros hermanos con esa vil magia "
"humana, pero el señor Vladnir Ohn dice que es necesario para nuestra "
"victoria… ¡Luchen, hermanos, no dejen que la muerte misma detenga nuestro "
"sueño de hacerse realidad!"

#. [message], speaker=Razhikin
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:311
msgid ""
"What the hell, even when we strike them down they rise again! They look like "
"those monsters summoned by the Wesnothians!"
msgstr ""
"¡Qué demonios, incluso cuando los derribamos se levantan otra vez! ¡Parecen "
"esos monstruos invocados por los wesnothianos!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:315
msgid ""
"(serious) Indeed, and this is something to be worried about. If they're "
"using Necromancy to increase their armies, just as they did in the first "
"Dragon War, we'll have even more trouble than we're having already..."
msgstr ""
"(seria) En efecto, y esto es algo por lo que preocuparse. Si están usando "
"nigromancia para aumentar sus ejércitos, tal como hicieron en la primera "
"Guerra de los Dragones, tendremos aún más problemas de los que ya tenemos…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:327
msgid ""
"Now, drake, tell us: where did you learn this dark magic? Was it from the "
"saurians?"
msgstr ""
"Ahora, draco, dinos: ¿dónde aprendiste esta magia oscura? ¿Fue de los "
"saurios?"

#. [message], speaker=Garashe
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:331
msgid ""
"(roaring) As if those good-for-nothing saurians could ever be capable of "
"such deed! No, puny apes, we learned it from someone else, but don't be "
"fools and expect me to tell... Just know that your days are counted..."
msgstr ""
"(rugiendo) ¡Como si esos saurios inútiles pudieran ser capaces de tal "
"hazaña! No, simios insignificantes, lo aprendimos de alguien más, pero no "
"sean tontos y esperen que se los diga… Solo sepan que sus días están "
"contados…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:335
msgid "Tindë, didn't you know that the drakes were using Necromancy?"
msgstr "Tindë, ¿no sabías que los dracos estaban usando nigromancia?"

#. [message], speaker=Tinde
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:339
msgid ""
"Of course not! This is probably the first time they use it, otherwise, it "
"would have been reported from other battles!"
msgstr ""
"¡Por supuesto que no! ¡Probablemente sea la primera vez que lo usan, de lo "
"contrario habría sido reportado desde otras batallas!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:343
msgid ""
"Still, their undead weren't like those of Aetheryon, Ashura or that saurian "
"lich in Kodakuni, they were just reanimated corpses. If they're really using "
"dark magic, they're still not very good at it."
msgstr ""
"Aun así, sus no-muertos no eran como los de Aetheryon, Ashura o ese liche "
"saurio en Kodakuni, solo eran cadáveres reanimados. Si realmente están "
"usando magia oscura, aún no son muy buenos en ello."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:347
msgid ""
"However, that doesn't mean that we can wave it aside as a minor problem; the "
"fact that their dead can be reanimated like this means that we'll have to "
"fight twice as many foes as we'd normally have. They must have suffered some "
"losses recently, to be resorting to such vile means to achieve victory."
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, eso no significa que podamos descartarlo como un problema "
"menor; el hecho de que sus muertos puedan ser reanimados así significa que "
"tendremos que luchar contra el doble de enemigos de lo que normalmente "
"tendríamos. Deben haber sufrido algunas pérdidas recientemente para recurrir "
"a medios tan viles para lograr la victoria."

#. [message], speaker=Tinde
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:351
msgid ""
"Indeed, we've managed to expel them from our forests, and Queen Dragana has "
"launched a counter-offensive which has managed to reconquer half of the lost "
"lands."
msgstr ""
"En efecto, hemos logrado expulsarlos de nuestros bosques, y la reina Dragana "
"ha lanzado una contraofensiva que ha logrado reconquistar la mitad de las "
"tierras perdidas."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:355
msgid ""
"Let's go to her aid, then; the elves and the drakes can invade the southern "
"Kehshakaar, but the Baryags will have trouble entering those mountains on "
"their own."
msgstr ""
"Vayamos en su ayuda entonces; los elfos y los dracos pueden invadir el sur "
"de Kehshakaar, pero los baryags tendrán problemas para entrar en esas "
"montañas por su cuenta."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:373
msgid "Well, congratulations on defeating more opponents... this time."
msgstr "Bueno, felicitaciones por derrotar a más oponentes... esta vez."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:377
msgid ""
"You are a graceful loser. For that, I offer you this piece of knowledge "
"about my people: we're peaceful because we <i>choose</i> to be, not because "
"that is all we're capable of. Also, I expect my food to be well seasoned - "
"and I won't take anything less than pheasant and snow hare."
msgstr ""
"Eres un perdedor elegante. Por eso te ofrezco este dato sobre mi pueblo: "
"somos pacíficos porque <i>elegimos</i> serlo, no porque sea lo único que "
"podemos hacer. Además, espero que mi comida esté bien sazonada, y no acepto "
"nada menos que faisán y liebre de nieve."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:381
msgid "Don't worry Kenshiro, you'll get her next time."
msgstr "No te preocupes, Kenshiro, la próxima vez la vencerás."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:394
msgid ""
"What do you know, you actually managed to keep up with me. Not bad... for a "
"warrior from a backwater nation."
msgstr ""
"Mira qué sorpresa, realmente lograste seguirme el paso. No está mal… para un "
"guerrero de una nación atrasada."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:398
msgid ""
"And that's because you fight from a distance, while I fight in the heat of "
"battle."
msgstr ""
"Y eso es porque tú peleas a distancia, mientras que yo lucho en el calor de "
"la batalla."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:402
msgid ""
"Oh, you think I've ignored how you kept throwing those impractical star-"
"shapped blades all throughout the battle?"
msgstr ""
"¿Oh, crees que no me di cuenta de cómo estuviste lanzando esas cuchillas en "
"forma de estrella poco prácticas durante toda la batalla?"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:406
msgid ""
"Those are 'shuriken', and I don't use them nearly as much as you use your "
"bow."
msgstr ""
"Esas son «shuriken», y no las uso ni de cerca tanto como tú usas tu arco."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:410
msgid ""
"Excuses, excuses. See? I failed to beat you as well, yet you don't see "
"<i>me</i> whining. As tiebreaker, I suggest the ability to honour your "
"opponents' skill - and in this, Kenshiro of Kodakuni, you just failed "
"soundly. I win."
msgstr ""
"Excusas, excusas. ¿Ves? Yo también fallé en vencerte, y sin embargo no me "
"ves <i>a mí</i> quejándome. Como desempate, propongo la capacidad de honrar "
"la habilidad del oponente, y en eso, Kenshiro de Kodakuni, acabas de fallar "
"estrepitosamente. Gano yo."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:414
msgid "Hold on, don't I get to suggest a-"
msgstr "Espera, ¿no me toca sugerir a mí un—"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:418
msgid ""
"Too late. I expect my food to be well seasoned - and I won't take anything "
"less than pheasant and snow hare."
msgstr ""
"Demasiado tarde. Espero que mi comida esté bien sazonada, y no acepto nada "
"menos que faisán y liebre de nieve."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:422
msgid "*rolls eyes*"
msgstr "*pone los ojos en blanco*"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:435
msgid "And I believe I've won our dispute, princess."
msgstr "Y creo que he ganado nuestra disputa, princesa."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:439
msgid ""
"What do you know, you actually did. Of course, it is difficult to get a high "
"kill count when you're constantly sent away from the centre of the battle, "
"but that is no excuse. Your victory will be bitter, however; for once you "
"have tasted the delicacies of elven cuisine, every food your tongue touches "
"shall taste like ash."
msgstr ""
"Vaya sorpresa, realmente lo hiciste. Claro, es difícil conseguir un alto "
"conteo de bajas cuando te mantienen constantemente lejos del centro de la "
"batalla, pero eso no es excusa. Tu victoria será amarga, sin embargo; una "
"vez que pruebes las delicias de la cocina élfica, todo lo que toque tu "
"lengua sabrá a ceniza."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:443
msgid ""
"You're making excuses, but I look forward to seeing if elven stuff really is "
"that good."
msgstr ""
"Estás poniendo excusas, pero tengo ganas de ver si la comida élfica "
"realmente es tan buena."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:447
msgid ""
"(whisper) Just so you know, I actually did keep her away from wherever the "
"fighting was hardest. I really want to know what it tastes like, to have an "
"elven princess cook food for you. 'Cause you <i>are</i> sharing it with me, "
"right? Otherwise I'll tell everyone I helped you, and your warrior's honour "
"will be tarnished and all that."
msgstr ""
"(susurro) Para que lo sepas, sí la mantuve alejada de donde la pelea estaba "
"más dura. Realmente quiero saber qué sabor tiene que una princesa élfica te "
"cocine. Porque <i>sí</i> vas a compartir conmigo, ¿verdad? Si no, le voy a "
"contar a todos que te ayudé, y tu honor de guerrero quedará manchado y todo "
"eso."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:451
msgid "(Exasperated snort)"
msgstr "(Resoplido exasperado)"

#. [message], speaker=Kashiere
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/18_Dead_Flames.cfg:472
msgid ""
"(roaring) Curse them, they've received reinforcements! We're too outnumbered "
"now!"
msgstr ""
"(rugiendo) ¡Malditos sean, han recibido refuerzos! ¡Ahora estamos demasiado "
"en desventaja numérica!"

#. [scenario], id=19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:5
msgid "The Siege of Shek'harya"
msgstr "El asedio de Shek'harya"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:25
msgid "Defeat Vladnir Ohn"
msgstr "Derrota a Vladnir Ohn"

#. [side], type=Drake Enforcer
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:127
msgid "Korrash"
msgstr "Korrash"

#. [side], type=Saurian Flanker
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:148
msgid "Ssiliz"
msgstr "Ssiliz"

#. [side], type=Saurian Flanker
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:154
msgid "Swamp Saurians"
msgstr "Saurios del pantano"

#. [unit]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:277
msgid "Reanimated Saurian"
msgstr "Saurio reanimado"

#. [message], speaker=Vladnir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:300
msgid ""
"I must admit that you have been fighting well, apes, but attacking us at our "
"own home was a great mistake... We shall drown your forces in the lava, and "
"then we shall attack again – and this time, you won't be there to defend "
"your lands!"
msgstr ""
"Debo admitir que han peleado bien, simios, pero atacar en nuestra propia "
"casa fue un gran error… Vamos a ahogar sus fuerzas en lava, y luego "
"atacaremos de nuevo… ¡y esta vez no estarán ahí para defender sus tierras!"

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:304
msgid ""
"A fine plan, if only you didn't find yourself cornered, besieged, and "
"outnumbered. As it stands, the only thing that will drown today is your "
"stupid ambition of conquering the whole world!"
msgstr ""
"Bonito plan, si tan solo no te encontraras acorralado, sitiado y en "
"desventaja numérica. Tal como están las cosas, lo único que se va a ahogar "
"hoy es tu estúpida ambición de conquistar el mundo entero."

#. [message], speaker=Vladnir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:308
msgid ""
"You sure speak mightily, human queen; one could even think that your people "
"would still be alive and winning if they hadn't been aided by every "
"charitable soul they could find..."
msgstr ""
"Hablas con mucha fuerza, reina humana; hasta podría pensarse que tu pueblo "
"seguiría vivo y ganando si no hubiera sido ayudado por todas las almas "
"caritativas que pudo encontrar…"

#. [message], speaker=Gelendras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:312
msgid ""
"There's nothing wrong with counting on others, drake lord; all living beings "
"are weak on their own, but when they help each other they can face even the "
"most devastating of storms – and so there's no way we will lose to you, "
"who's too arrogant to even consider non-drakes as worthy living beings!"
msgstr ""
"No hay nada malo en contar con otros, señor draco; todos los seres vivos son "
"débiles por sí solos, pero cuando se ayudan mutuamente pueden enfrentar "
"incluso las tormentas más devastadoras… ¡y por eso no hay forma de que "
"perdamos contra ti, que eres demasiado arrogante como para considerar a los "
"no dracos seres vivos dignos!"

#. [message], speaker=Vladnir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:316
msgid ""
"You say that non-drakes are worthy too, and yet you needed the aid of my "
"sister's drakes to fight me... And you, sister, I knew you were a failure as "
"a drake, but never would I have suspected that you'd fall so low as to help "
"these disgusting apes..."
msgstr ""
"Dices que los no dracos también son dignos, y aun así necesitaste la ayuda "
"de los dracos de mi hermana para enfrentarme… Y tú, hermana, sabía que eras "
"un fracaso como draco, pero jamás habría imaginado que caerías tan bajo como "
"para ayudar a estos simios asquerosos…"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:320
msgid ""
"I'm a failure? I have populated this world with drakes, while you have only "
"sent them to their deaths! If any drake here is a failure, that is you, "
"Vladnir!"
msgstr ""
"¿Yo soy un fracaso? ¡Yo he poblado este mundo con dracos, mientras que tú "
"solo los has enviado a la muerte! Si hay algún draco aquí que es un fracaso, "
"ese eres tú, ¡Vladnir!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:324
msgid ""
"And I say the same of you, Aetheryon. Why are you helping those drakes? "
"Aren't you aware that they'd destroy even your precious Wesnoth if they won?"
msgstr ""
"Y yo digo lo mismo de ti, Aetheryon. ¿Por qué estás ayudando a esos dracos? "
"¿No te das cuenta de que destruirían incluso tu preciado Wesnoth si ganaran?"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:328
msgid ""
"'My precious Wesnoth'? Do not associate me to that country just because I "
"was born there; although it was once bright, it's now plagued with "
"corruption, and so it has been for centuries now. Such a nation, in my view, "
"deserves to be purged from this world by fire!"
msgstr ""
"¿«Mi preciado Wesnoth»? No me asocies con ese país solo porque nací allí; "
"aunque alguna vez fue brillante, ahora está plagado de corrupción, y así ha "
"sido por siglos. ¡Una nación así, en mi opinión, merece ser purgada de este "
"mundo por el fuego!"

#. [message], speaker=Vladnir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:332
msgid ""
"Well said, my human friend. Now, you must return to the safety of the "
"dungeons, and keep working on our secret weapon; leave the brunt of the "
"fighting for us, drakes."
msgstr ""
"Bien dicho, amigo humano. Ahora debes volver a la seguridad de las mazmorras "
"y seguir trabajando en nuestra arma secreta; deja lo más duro de la pelea "
"para nosotros, los dracos."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:339
msgid ""
"What the hell was that? Has he decided to turn on his own country out of a "
"sudden?"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué demonios fue eso? ¿Ha decidido de repente traicionar a su propio país?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:343
msgid ""
"Of course not, that's just pretense. I have a guess on why he's doing that, "
"but we'll have time for that later; now, let's put an end to Vladnir Ohn's "
"insanity and capture the prince..."
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto que no, eso es solo una farsa. Tengo una idea de por qué lo "
"hace, pero ya habrá tiempo para eso después; ahora, pongamos fin a la locura "
"de Vladnir Ohn y capturemos al príncipe…"

#. [message], speaker=Gelendras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:365
msgid "Sister, I'm glad to see you safe and sound!"
msgstr "¡Hermana, me alegra verte sana y salva!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:369
msgid ""
"Yes, these humans aren't as bad as I expected; like well-trained hounds, "
"they know how to protect their betters."
msgstr ""
"Sí, estos humanos no son tan malos como esperaba; como sabuesos bien "
"entrenados, saben cómo proteger a sus superiores."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:373
msgid "(annoyed) I'll show you 'betters', you..."
msgstr "(molesta) Ya te voy a mostrar quiénes son los «superiores», tú…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:377
msgid ""
"Hold on, Tenma, you don't want to waste time and energy fighting her, as "
"much as she deserves a good smacking. Look, imagine that drake there is "
"Cornelya, and vent all your anger on him!"
msgstr ""
"Espera, Tenma, no querrás gastar tiempo y energía peleando con ella, por más "
"que se merezca unos buenos golpes. Mira, imagina que ese draco de allá es "
"Cornelya, ¡y desahoga toda tu rabia en él!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:381
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:202
msgid "Tsc..."
msgstr "Tsc…"

#. [unit], id=Krathon, type=Skeletal Dragon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:394
msgid "Krathon"
msgstr "Krathon"

#. [message], speaker=Vladnir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:405
msgid ""
"(roaring) At long last it is completed! I praise your skill and "
"intelligence, little Aetheryon; now, let our foes see the glory and power of "
"the ancient days for themselves!"
msgstr ""
"(rugiendo) ¡Por fin está terminado! Alabo tu habilidad e inteligencia, "
"pequeño Aetheryon; ahora, que nuestros enemigos vean por sí mismos la gloria "
"y el poder de los días antiguos."

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:409
msgid "What the hell is that thing...?!"
msgstr "¿Qué demonios es esa cosa…?"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:413
msgid ""
"It's an undead dragon; I knew such kind of monster was possible, but I never "
"thought there would actually still exist dragon remains in a state good "
"enough to be turned into an undead..."
msgstr ""
"Es un dragón no muerto; sabía que ese tipo de monstruo era posible, pero "
"nunca pensé que todavía existirían restos de dragón en un estado lo "
"suficientemente bueno como para convertirlos en un no muerto…"

#. [message], speaker=Vladnir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:417
msgid ""
"This dragon, apes, is the reborn form of the mighty Krathon, killed "
"treacherously by humans, and whose death Shek'har the Great avenged by "
"wiping their entire culture in fire and ash!"
msgstr ""
"Este dragón, simios, es la forma renacida del poderoso Krathon, asesinado "
"traicioneramente por humanos, ¡y cuya muerte Shek'har el Grande vengó "
"borrando toda su cultura en fuego y ceniza!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:421
msgid ""
"'Reborn form'? That is just an undead imitation of what Krathon once was, "
"stupid drake! A mere pile of bones which once belonged to him and which can "
"now move again on their own!"
msgstr ""
"¿«Forma renacida»? ¡Eso es solo una imitación no muerta de lo que alguna vez "
"fue Krathon, estúpido draco! ¡Una simple pila de huesos que alguna vez le "
"pertenecieron y que ahora pueden moverse solos!"

#. [message], speaker=Vladnir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:425
msgid ""
"Let us see whether you'll still think so lowly of this 'mere pile of bones' "
"after it rips you in two..."
msgstr ""
"Veamos si sigues pensando tan poco de esta «simple pila de huesos» después "
"de que te parta en dos…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:440
msgid ""
"Well, my friend, even you must now admit that monster isn't just a 'mere "
"pile of bones'..."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, amigo mío, hasta tú debes admitir ahora que ese monstruo no es solo "
"una «simple pila de huesos»…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:444
msgid ""
"I never said he was weak, but he shall fall just like any other skeleton if "
"he's hit with arcane or fire magic!"
msgstr ""
"Nunca dije que fuera débil, ¡pero caerá igual que cualquier otro esqueleto "
"si lo golpean con magia arcana o de fuego!"

#. [message], speaker=Vladnir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:456
msgid ""
"You have fallen again, mighty Krathon, but your destruction shall be avenged "
"just like it was the last time: with rivers of human and elvish blood!"
msgstr ""
"Has caído de nuevo, poderoso Krathon, pero tu destrucción será vengada igual "
"que la última vez: ¡con ríos de sangre humana y élfica!"

#. [message], speaker=Vladnir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:468
msgid ""
"Curses upon curses upon curses on you disgusting apes...! Shek'har, my "
"forefather, I have failed you and our people...!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldiciones sobre maldiciones sobre maldiciones sobre ustedes, simios "
"asquerosos…! ¡Shek'har, mi antepasado, he fallado contigo y con nuestro "
"pueblo…!"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:472
msgid ""
"We don't even descend of him, you idiot. Now die, and take all your folly "
"with you to the Frozen Hells!"
msgstr ""
"Ni siquiera descendemos de él, idiota. ¡Ahora muere y llévate toda tu locura "
"contigo a los Infiernos Helados!"

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:485
msgid ""
"Lord Vladnir Ohn has fallen! There is no hope to win now, run for your lives!"
msgstr ""
"¡El señor Vladnir Ohn ha caído! ¡Ya no hay esperanza de ganar, huyan por sus "
"vidas!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:505
msgid ""
"I know they disliked each other, but shouldn't she be a little sadder that "
"her brother has died?"
msgstr ""
"Sé que no se soportaban, pero ¿no debería estar un poco más triste porque su "
"hermano murió?"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:509
msgid ""
"I don't think so. The only thing connecting them was blood; there was no "
"actual feeling of love to bond them as brother and sister. Cornelya and "
"Gelendras, who were not born by the same parents but were raised together "
"and love each other, are much truer siblings."
msgstr ""
"No lo creo. Lo único que los unía era la sangre; no había un verdadero "
"sentimiento de amor que los uniera como hermanos. Cornelya y Gelendras, que "
"no nacieron de los mismos padres pero se criaron juntos y se quieren, son "
"hermanos mucho más verdaderos."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:516
msgid "And now, Prince Aetheryon, you have nowhere to run..."
msgstr "Y ahora, príncipe Aetheryon, no tienes adónde huir…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:525
msgid ""
"(angry) Release me at once, you Arajunnan peasant! How dare you lay a finger "
"on a Prince of Wesnoth?!"
msgstr ""
"(enojado) ¡Suéltenme de inmediato, campesino arajunnano! ¿Cómo te atreves a "
"ponerle un dedo encima a un príncipe de Wesnoth?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:529
msgid ""
"I've never thought highly of you, and still you managed to disappoint me, "
"Aetheryon. How could you side with creatures who thought you inferior, who "
"would have killed your people and your family without a care?"
msgstr ""
"Nunca pensé muy bien de ti, y aun así lograste decepcionarme, Aetheryon. "
"¿Cómo pudiste ponerte del lado de criaturas que te consideraban inferior, "
"que habrían matado a tu pueblo y a tu familia sin pestañear?"

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:533
msgid ""
"So this is the Wesnothian princeling who was chasing you, I see... Well, let "
"us bring him to my castle; I too have a few words to exchange with him..."
msgstr ""
"Así que este es el principito wesnothiano que te perseguía, ya veo… Bueno, "
"llevémoslo a mi castillo; yo también tengo unas palabras que intercambiar "
"con él…"

#. [message], speaker=Gelendras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:537
msgid ""
"And thus the Second Dragon War ends, fortunately with victory for our "
"side... Mother Queen Veshtar Joohn, as the highest drake authority in these "
"mountains, what will you do with your deceased brother's clan? Will it "
"follow you now?"
msgstr ""
"Y así termina la Segunda Guerra de los Dracos, afortunadamente con victoria "
"para nuestro lado… Reina Madre Veshtar Joohn, como la máxima autoridad draco "
"en estas montañas, ¿qué harás con el clan de tu hermano fallecido? ¿Te "
"seguirá ahora?"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:541
msgid ""
"They will, and those who don't want to shall be sent out of these mountains "
"into the Silent Lands; the same is valid for the saurians."
msgstr ""
"Lo harán, y los que no quieran serán enviados fuera de estas montañas a las "
"Tierras Silenciosas; lo mismo aplica para los saurios."

#. [message], speaker=Gelendras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:545
msgid ""
"In that case, would you like to become a steadfast ally of the Lins-Elens "
"elves and the Baryags of the Plains? Vladnir Ohn wasn't the last threat "
"we'll be seeing on our frontiers, but together we could defend against any "
"foe."
msgstr ""
"En ese caso, ¿te gustaría convertirte en una aliada firme de los elfos Lins-"
"Elens y los baryags de las Llanuras? Vladnir Ohn no fue la última amenaza "
"que veremos en nuestras fronteras, pero juntos podríamos defendernos de "
"cualquier enemigo."

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:549
msgid ""
"There's too much bad blood between our peoples right now, elf; I can't force "
"my new sons to accept those who wounded and killed them as friends, not so "
"soon. But one thing I can guarantee you is that the drakes shall no longer "
"attack you, not unless you attack us first."
msgstr ""
"Hay demasiada sangre mala entre nuestros pueblos ahora mismo, elfo; no puedo "
"obligar a mis nuevos hijos a aceptar como amigos a quienes los hirieron y "
"mataron, no tan pronto. Pero una cosa te puedo garantizar: los dracos ya no "
"los atacarán, a menos que ustedes nos ataquen primero."

#. [message], speaker=Gelendras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:553
msgid ""
"If that's your wish, Mother Queen, then be it, though I find it unfortunate "
"that we remain separate."
msgstr ""
"Si ese es tu deseo, Reina Madre, que así sea, aunque me parece lamentable "
"que sigamos separados."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:557
msgid ""
"*(sigh) And once again people refuse to unite even after cooperating against "
"a common threat... Is there really no other way for this world to exist...?*"
msgstr ""
"*(suspiro) Y una vez más la gente se niega a unirse incluso después de "
"cooperar contra una amenaza común… ¿De verdad no hay otra forma de que este "
"mundo exista…?*"

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:678
msgid ""
"So, after being captured by the drakes, you decided to pretend to be another "
"person and use the drakes to weaken or eliminate some of Wesnoth's strongest "
"foes; capturing Tenma and her friends was to be just a bonus... As much as I "
"despise such sneaky tactics, I have to admit that you were very clever "
"indeed. You sure have a dedicated man after you, Tenma..."
msgstr ""
"Entonces, después de ser capturado por los dracos, decidiste fingir ser otra "
"persona y usar a los dracos para debilitar o eliminar a algunos de los "
"enemigos más fuertes de Wesnoth; capturar a Tenma y sus amigos iba a ser "
"solo un extra… Por más que desprecio esas tácticas taimadas, debo admitir "
"que fuiste muy astuto. Seguro tienes a un hombre muy dedicado "
"persiguiéndote, Tenma…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:682
msgid ""
"A wraith, more like. You stupid prince, how could you start a war for a "
"reason so petty, so greedy?! Thousands of people and drakes died because of "
"you, don't you realise that?!"
msgstr ""
"Un espectro, más bien. ¡Príncipe estúpido, cómo pudiste empezar una guerra "
"por una razón tan mezquina, tan codiciosa! ¡Miles de personas y dracos "
"murieron por tu culpa, no te das cuenta!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:686
msgid ""
"What did I start?! Vladnir Ohn already hated everyone for that ancient war "
"long before I met him, the elves already made everyone hate them long before "
"I set foot in this region, and the Baryags were already belligerent before I "
"even thought of walking into that saurian swamp! All I did was to give it a "
"push, and the tower crumbled on its own!"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué empecé yo? ¡Vladnir Ohn ya odiaba a todos por esa guerra antigua mucho "
"antes de conocerme, los elfos ya hicieron que todos los odiaran mucho antes "
"de que yo pusiera un pie en esta región, y los baryags ya eran beligerantes "
"antes de que siquiera pensara en entrar en ese pantano saurio! ¡Todo lo que "
"hice fue darle un empujón, y la torre se derrumbó sola!"

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:690
msgid ""
"You blame others for your own misdeeds, a behaviour befitting a sneaky "
"coward like you; my wish is to have you beheaded and your corpse fed to our "
"pigs, but you're worth much more alive. I will..."
msgstr ""
"Les echas la culpa a otros de tus propias fechorías, comportamiento propio "
"de un cobarde taimado como tú; mi deseo sería hacerte cortar la cabeza y dar "
"tu cadáver a nuestros cerdos, pero vales mucho más vivo. Yo…"

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:708
msgid "Wait there, you can't enter now...!"
msgstr "¡Espera ahí, no puedes entrar ahora…!"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:712
msgid ""
"Oh, c'mon, I've been waiting for days already, and besides, I doubt your "
"queen will mind it if I storm into her hall, actually she'll probably be "
"pleased for seeing me..."
msgstr ""
"Oh, vamos, ya llevo días esperando, y además dudo que a tu reina le moleste "
"si irrumpo en su salón; de hecho, probablemente se alegre de verme…"

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:716
msgid ""
"(smiling) And why would anyone, let alone me, be pleased at the sight of "
"such an ugly mug? My friends, this is Donar of the Dwarven Doors, a captain "
"of the Northern Alliance and an old friend of mine."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) ¿Y por qué alguien, y menos yo, se alegraría de ver una cara tan "
"fea? Amigos míos, este es Donar de las Puertas Enanas, capitán de la Alianza "
"del Norte y viejo amigo mío."

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:720
msgid ""
"Aye, that's me, and I must apologize for interrupting your stuff and all, "
"but the matter that brings me here is very urgent and demands no delays."
msgstr ""
"Sí, soy yo, y debo disculparme por interrumpir todo esto, pero el asunto que "
"me trae aquí es muy urgente y no admite demoras."

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:724
msgid ""
"In this case, I shall leave this prince's fate for later. Say, Donar, what "
"has brought you here in such a hurry? Do you come on behalf of the Northern "
"Alliance?"
msgstr ""
"En ese caso, dejaré el destino de este príncipe para después. Dime, Donar, "
"¿qué te trae con tanta prisa? ¿Vienes en nombre de la Alianza del Norte?"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:728
msgid ""
"Aye. The thing is, the Iron Giant of Wesnoth has decided to invade Knalga, "
"and he's even managed to bring some orcish clans to his side for that."
msgstr ""
"Sí. El asunto es que el Gigante de Hierro de Wesnoth ha decidido invadir "
"Knalga, e incluso ha logrado llevar a algunos clanes orcos a su bando para "
"eso."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:732
msgid "(shocked) My brother has decided what?!"
msgstr "(atónito) ¿¡Mi hermano ha decidido qué!?"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:736
msgid "Your... (astonished) Wait a minute, is that lad a Wesnothian prince?!"
msgstr ""
"Tu… (asombrado) ¡Espera un momento, ese muchacho es un príncipe wesnothiano!"

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:740
msgid ""
"Aye, Aetheryon, the emperor's youngest son, who's just given us no short "
"amount of headache himself. Back to the matter at hand, if Aelvar has "
"decided to attack Knalga, too bad for him, right? It's common sense that "
"there are few surer ways to die than defying the dwarves in their own domain."
msgstr ""
"Sí, Aetheryon, el hijo menor del emperador, que él mismo nos ha dado no "
"pocos dolores de cabeza. Volviendo al tema, si Aelvar ha decidido atacar "
"Knalga, peor para él, ¿no? Es sentido común que hay pocas formas más seguras "
"de morir que desafiar a los enanos en su propio dominio."

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:744
msgid ""
"I fear this just isn't the case now. Aelvar's amassed a powerful army in his "
"provinces of the Far North; for a while now, there's even been rumours that "
"he wishes to carve a kingdom of his own out of those provinces. Now if he "
"does conquer Knalga and uses its wealth to bolster his own cause, we might "
"have an empire even worse than Wesnoth itself. That's why the Lord Protector "
"thought this matter should concern you."
msgstr ""
"Me temo que ahora no es así. Aelvar ha reunido un ejército poderoso en sus "
"provincias del Lejano Norte; desde hace un tiempo incluso corren rumores de "
"que desea tallar un reino propio con esas provincias. Si conquista Knalga y "
"usa su riqueza para fortalecer su causa, podríamos tener un imperio incluso "
"peor que el mismo Wesnoth. Por eso el Señor Protector pensó que este asunto "
"debería preocuparte."

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:748
msgid ""
"And he is right. Though I don't personally know this Aelvar, I've heard many "
"stories about his ruthlessness; any nation ruled by one such as him is a "
"threat to anyone living nearby. However, I think you're unaware of the "
"violent war we've just fought, one that left half of my cities as scorched "
"ruins. As much as I wish to send armies to reinforce the Northern Alliance, "
"I don't think I have any to spare..."
msgstr ""
"Y tiene razón. Aunque no conozco personalmente a este Aelvar, he oído muchas "
"historias sobre su crueldad; cualquier nación gobernada por alguien así es "
"una amenaza para cualquiera que viva cerca. Sin embargo, creo que no te das "
"cuenta de la violenta guerra que acabamos de librar, una que dejó la mitad "
"de mis ciudades como ruinas quemadas. Por más que desee enviar ejércitos "
"para reforzar la Alianza del Norte, no creo que me sobre ninguno…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:752
msgid "Then we shall go to their aid in your name, Vasilya!"
msgstr "¡Entonces iremos en su ayuda en tu nombre, Vasilya!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:756
msgid ""
"Tenma, wait a minute! I know you wish to help people defend against tyrants, "
"but if we keep getting involved in every war we come cross we'll never reach "
"Maat'Kare, nor be able to save your country!"
msgstr ""
"¡Tenma, espera un momento! Sé que quieres ayudar a la gente a defenderse de "
"tiranos, pero si nos seguimos involucrando en cada guerra que encontramos "
"nunca llegaremos a Maat'Kare, ¡ni podremos salvar tu país!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:760
msgid ""
"If this prince Aelvar is as ruthless as they're saying, then he's a threat "
"to Kodakuni too – especially now that everyone standing between my home and "
"Wesnoth is weakened by this Second Dragon War! Besides, by defeating Aelvar "
"and his armies we'll be weakening Wesnoth, which will come in hand later, "
"when we fight to break Kodakuni free of Wesnothian rule!"
msgstr ""
"Si este príncipe Aelvar es tan cruel como dicen, entonces también es una "
"amenaza para Kodakuni, ¡especialmente ahora que todos los que están entre mi "
"hogar y Wesnoth están debilitados por esta Segunda Guerra de los Dracos! "
"Además, al derrotar a Aelvar y sus ejércitos estaremos debilitando a "
"Wesnoth, lo que nos vendrá muy bien después, ¡cuando luchemos para liberar a "
"Kodakuni del dominio wesnothiano!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:764
msgid ""
"She's right, Olokun. If we leave this matter to be dealt with later, it "
"might become just too difficult for us to handle. Now, on the other hand, we "
"have the chance to face it with the aid of the Northern Alliance and all of "
"Knalga; there are few better allies we could have on this world."
msgstr ""
"Tiene razón, Olokun. Si dejamos este asunto para después, podría volverse "
"demasiado difícil de manejar. Ahora, en cambio, tenemos la oportunidad de "
"enfrentarlo con la ayuda de la Alianza del Norte y todo Knalga; hay pocos "
"aliados mejores que podríamos tener en este mundo."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:768
msgid ""
"(sigh) Well, it's not like I can decide what you want to do. If you've "
"decided to march into yet another war, all that is left for me is follow you."
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) Bueno, no es como si pudiera decidir qué quieres hacer. Si has "
"decidido marchar a otra guerra más, lo único que me queda es seguirte."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:772
msgid "Hey, Olokun, don't be like that! I-"
msgstr "¡Oye, Olokun, no seas así! Yo—"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:776
msgid ""
"(impatient) I'm not angry, see? Now, if we're leaving as soon as possible, I "
"must go prepare everything for the travel. Vasilya, if I may leave now..."
msgstr ""
"(impaciente) No estoy enojado, ¿ves? Ahora, si nos vamos lo antes posible, "
"debo ir a preparar todo para el viaje. Vasilya, si me permites irme ahora…"

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:780
msgid ""
"Go in peace, friend, and know that you'll always find a haven in my castle."
msgstr ""
"Ve en paz, amigo, y sabe que siempre encontrarás refugio en mi castillo."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:790
msgid "Don't worry, Tenma, he's just worried about you."
msgstr "No te preocupes, Tenma, solo está preocupado por ti."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:794
msgid "(upset) I see..."
msgstr "(molesta) Ya veo…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:798
msgid ""
"Ahem! Excuse me, but if you're going to fight Aelvar, then you'll need me. "
"As you said, there have been rumours that he has been planning a rebellion; "
"but those rumours were born in my father's own throne room. He's always "
"known that Aelvar would try something like this, but my brother was just too "
"powerful and influential in the Northlands to be simply removed from there. "
"If he's decided to attack Knalga on his own accord, then he's acting without "
"my father's consent, which means that he has become Wesnoth's enemy as well."
msgstr ""
"¡Ejem! Disculpen, pero si van a luchar contra Aelvar, entonces me "
"necesitarán. Como dijeron, han corrido rumores de que estaba planeando una "
"rebelión; pero esos rumores nacieron en la propia sala del trono de mi "
"padre. Siempre supo que Aelvar intentaría algo así, pero mi hermano era "
"demasiado poderoso e influyente en las Tierras del Norte como para "
"simplemente apartarlo de allí. Si ha decidido atacar Knalga por su cuenta, "
"entonces está actuando sin el consentimiento de mi padre, lo que significa "
"que también se ha convertido en enemigo de Wesnoth."

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:802
msgid ""
"So you're suggesting what, that the Northern Alliance should ally with "
"Wesnoth, centuries of bad blood and distrust be damned?"
msgstr ""
"¿Entonces estás sugiriendo qué, que la Alianza del Norte se alíe con "
"Wesnoth, malditos sean siglos de sangre mala y desconfianza?"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:806
msgid ""
"I know we're not on friendly terms, but you can't deny that, while the "
"Northern Alliance's forces have waned fighting my country and the orcs, "
"Aelvar's armies have grown and developed – and that's not counting the "
"dwarvish Foreign Legions he's managed to sway to his side..."
msgstr ""
"Sé que no estamos en términos amistosos, pero no puedes negar que, mientras "
"las fuerzas de la Alianza del Norte se han debilitado luchando contra mi "
"país y los orcos, los ejércitos de Aelvar han crecido y se han desarrollado… "
"y eso sin contar las Legiones Extranjeras enanas que ha logrado convencer de "
"su lado…"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:810
msgid "(suddenly uncomfortable)"
msgstr "(de repente incómodo)"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:814
msgid ""
"...and the Baryags are weakened, and I doubt the Lins-Elens elves will get "
"involved in another war so soon, not one that does not offer immediate "
"threat to themselves. So the only possible friend the Alliance has left, as "
"ironic as it may be, is Wesnoth."
msgstr ""
"…y los baryags están debilitados, y dudo que los elfos Lins-Elens se "
"involucren en otra guerra tan pronto, no una que no represente una amenaza "
"inmediata para ellos mismos. Así que el único amigo posible que le queda a "
"la Alianza, por irónico que sea, es Wesnoth."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:818
msgid ""
"Few things are more mortifying than a bastard making good points... He's "
"right, Vasilya; I know this man has done your people a great harm, but if "
"you let him come with us, he will earn the Alliance a much needed ally."
msgstr ""
"Pocas cosas son más mortificantes que un bastardo teniendo razón… Tiene "
"razón, Vasilya; sé que este hombre ha hecho mucho daño a tu pueblo, pero si "
"lo dejas venir con nosotros, conseguirá para la Alianza un aliado muy "
"necesario."

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:822
msgid ""
"Argh, you're right... Well, then, for the sake of the Northern Alliance, I "
"will let this weasel go away..."
msgstr ""
"Argh, tienen razón… Bueno, entonces, por el bien de la Alianza del Norte, "
"dejaré que esta comadreja se vaya…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:826
msgid ""
"Then I pledge myself to do everything in my power to seal this alliance, "
"temporary as it may be. You may think me cunning, but once I give my word I "
"always keep it - as Tenma herself can attest."
msgstr ""
"Entonces me comprometo a hacer todo lo que esté en mi poder para sellar esta "
"alianza, por temporal que sea. Pueden pensar que soy astuto, pero una vez "
"que doy mi palabra siempre la cumplo, como la misma Tenma puede atestiguar."

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:830
msgid ""
"Well then, folks, let's get prepared for leaving as soon as we can – which "
"means, after we eat Vasilya's food. It's inadmissible that I come all the "
"way to Mhreghost and leave without enjoying the widely famous feasts of the "
"Warrior Queen of the Emerald Plains."
msgstr ""
"Bueno entonces, gente, preparémonos para partir lo antes posible… lo que "
"significa, después de comer la comida de Vasilya. Es inadmisible que venga "
"hasta Mhreghost y me vaya sin disfrutar de los famosos banquetes de la Reina "
"Guerrera de las Llanuras Esmeralda."

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:834
msgid ""
"(smirking) And you keep flattering me like this, do you want to unite our "
"peoples by marriage or what?"
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo con picardía) ¿Y sigues halagándome así? ¿Quieres unir a nuestros "
"pueblos por matrimonio o qué?"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:838
msgid ""
"(mutters) Fighting amongst humans, and now fighting amongst dwarves... Damn "
"you, father..."
msgstr ""
"(murmura) Peleando entre humanos, y ahora peleando entre enanos… Maldito "
"seas, padre…"

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:857
msgid "I have... failed my people..."
msgstr "He… fallado a mi pueblo…"

#. [message], speaker=Gelendras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:871
msgid ""
"I return to the earth from which I came... fight on without me, my "
"warriors..."
msgstr ""
"Vuelvo a la tierra de donde vine… sigan luchando sin mí, mis guerreros…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:875
msgid ""
"BROTHER, NO!!! You useless humans, how could you have let him die?! Follow "
"me, elves, we must leave this battlefield before we're left to die as well!"
msgstr ""
"¡HERMANO, NO! ¡Humanos inútiles, cómo pudieron dejarlo morir! ¡Síganme, "
"elfos, debemos abandonar este campo de batalla antes de que nos dejen morir "
"también!"

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:879
msgid "The elves are withdrawing! This is a disaster!"
msgstr "¡Los elfos se están retirando! ¡Esto es un desastre!"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:894
msgid "I'm dying... Who will watch over my children now...?"
msgstr "Me estoy muriendo… ¿Quién cuidará ahora de mis hijos…?"

#. [message], speaker=Vladnir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:907
msgid ""
"(roaring) For a moment, I confess, I feared we might lose - but no more, not "
"now that the rest of our drakes and saurians have arrived!"
msgstr ""
"(rugiendo) Por un momento, lo confieso, temí que pudiéramos perder… ¡pero ya "
"no, no ahora que el resto de nuestros dracos y saurios han llegado!"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/19_The_Siege_Of_Shekharya.cfg:911
msgid ""
"Damn you, brother! Their numbers are too great now, and to make it worse, "
"we're surrounded! This is the end of us!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldito seas, hermano! ¡Ahora son demasiados, y para empeorar las cosas, "
"estamos rodeados! ¡Este es nuestro fin!"

