#. [side], type=General
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:107
msgid "General Guldoc"
msgstr "General Guldoc"

#. [side], type=General
#. [side], type=Iron Mauler
#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:113
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:94
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:99
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:98
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:90
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:119
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:193
msgid "Aelvar's Rebels"
msgstr "Rebeldes de Aelvar"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:178
msgid ""
"Ah, the sounds of the north: the cry of the eagles, the howl of the winds, "
"the flow of the rivers and the clashing of steel against steel, how I missed "
"them all..."
msgstr ""
"Ah, los sonidos del norte: el grito de las águilas, el aullido de los "
"vientos, el fluir de los ríos y el choque del acero contra el acero, cuánto "
"los extrañaba…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:182
msgid ""
"Dorest is under siege, and the attackers wear Wesnothian armour... You "
"didn't tell me that my brother's armies were so deep south already, Donar!"
msgstr ""
"¡Dorest está bajo asedio, y los atacantes llevan armadura wesnothiana…! ¡No "
"me dijiste que los ejércitos de mi hermano ya estaban tan al sur, Donar!"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:186
msgid ""
"Because he hadn't when I departed for Mhreghost! Back then, his armies "
"hadn't even been sighted south of the Mountains of Haag yet!"
msgstr ""
"¡Porque no lo habían hecho cuando partí hacia Mhreghost! ¡En ese entonces ni "
"siquiera habían sido avistados al sur de las Montañas de Haag!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:190
msgid ""
"And yet here they are. Let's go to that city's help; even if it's doomed to "
"fall, we can at least help the citizens evacuate back into Wesnoth."
msgstr ""
"Y sin embargo aquí están. Vamos a ayudar a esa ciudad; aunque esté condenada "
"a caer, al menos podemos ayudar a los ciudadanos a evacuar de regreso a "
"Wesnoth."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:194
msgid ""
"You seem to care so much for the citizens of the empire that oppresses your "
"country..."
msgstr ""
"Parece que te preocupas mucho por los ciudadanos del imperio que oprime tu "
"país…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:198
msgid ""
"They may be Wesnothians, but they're human just like my countrymen, neither "
"better nor worse. It's a little thing called 'empathy', you see."
msgstr ""
"Pueden ser wesnothianos, pero son humanos igual que mis compatriotas, ni "
"mejores ni peores. Es una pequeña cosa llamada «empatía», ¿sabes?"

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:225
msgid ""
"Lady Aethra, look! A new battalion comes from the south; they don't carry "
"Wesnothian banners, but, if I'm not mistaken, they're led by Prince "
"Aetheryon!"
msgstr ""
"¡Señora Aethra, mire! Un nuevo batallón viene del sur; no llevan estandartes "
"wesnothianos, pero, si no me equivoco, ¡están liderados por el príncipe "
"Aetheryon!"

#. [message], speaker=Aethra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:229
msgid ""
"Brother! The Gods of Light have answered my prayers after all, they knew how "
"much I needed you right now!"
msgstr ""
"¡Hermano! Al final los Dioses de la Luz han respondido a mis oraciones, "
"¡sabían cuánto te necesitaba en este momento!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:233
msgid ""
"Aethra, why are you leading the city's defence on your own? Hasn't father "
"left any general protecting it?"
msgstr ""
"Aethra, ¿por qué estás liderando la defensa de la ciudad tú sola? ¿Padre no "
"dejó a ningún general protegiéndola?"

#. [message], speaker=Aethra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:237
msgid ""
"Lord Garren was the one in charge of Dorest, but alas, he perished just "
"yesterday, when brother Aelvar's soldiers launched the first and most "
"vicious assault on this city. I have sent a messenger southwards, to "
"Soradoc, where brother Aeldhoryan should be stationed, but it must take a "
"few more days until he arrives."
msgstr ""
"El señor Garren estaba a cargo de Dorest, pero ay, pereció ayer mismo, "
"cuando los soldados de nuestro hermano Aelvar lanzaron el primer y más feroz "
"asalto sobre esta ciudad. He enviado un mensajero hacia el sur, a Soradoc, "
"donde debería estar estacionado nuestro hermano Aeldhoryan, pero deben pasar "
"unos días más hasta que llegue"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:241
msgid ""
"So we must hold Dorest until then. I have no soldiers with me, but my "
"companions wield powers unknown even to Alduin's mages; with their aid, we "
"may prevail."
msgstr ""
"Entonces debemos mantener Dorest hasta ese momento. No traigo soldados "
"conmigo, pero mis compañeros manejan poderes desconocidos incluso para los "
"magos de Alduin; con su ayuda, podríamos prevalecer."

#. [message], speaker=Aethra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:260
msgid ""
"Impressive! My brother made no overstatement when commenting on your power, "
"foreigners, the creatures you've summoned are truly fearsome!"
msgstr ""
"¡Impresionante! Mi hermano no exageró al hablar de su poder, extranjeros; "
"las criaturas que han invocado son realmente temibles"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:282
msgid "Still mad at me, big brother?"
msgstr "¿Todavía estás enojado conmigo, hermano mayor?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:286
msgid ""
"I was never mad at you to begin with – and please, stop leaning on me like "
"that, I must focus on the battle..."
msgstr ""
"Nunca estuve enojado contigo desde el principio… y por favor, deja de "
"apoyarte en mí así, tengo que concentrarme en la batalla…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:290
msgid ""
"You haven't laughed at my silly jokes, you haven't prepared me breakfast, "
"you haven't stared at me full of questions about that Myra... Come on, I'll "
"let you ask me anything about her, I'll even let you call me Myra if you "
"want, but I want to see a smile on this stern face again!"
msgstr ""
"No te has reído de mis chistes tontos, no me has preparado el desayuno, no "
"me has mirado lleno de preguntas sobre esa Myra… Vamos, te dejo preguntarme "
"lo que quieras sobre ella, hasta te dejo llamarme Myra si quieres, ¡pero "
"quiero volver a ver una sonrisa en esa cara seria"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:294
msgid ""
"(smiling slightly) I just can't stay angry at you, can I? But, seriously: I "
"just don't want to see you rushing to a danger you can't deal with."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo ligeramente) Simplemente no puedo enojarme contigo, ¿verdad? "
"Pero, en serio: solo no quiero verte lanzarte a un peligro con el que no "
"puedas lidiar."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:298
msgid ""
"And I've told you not to worry, that I know very well the importance of my "
"mission on this planet..."
msgstr ""
"Y te he dicho que no te preocupes, que sé muy bien la importancia de mi "
"misión en este planeta…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:302
msgid "That's not what I'm thinking about; I just don't want you to die..."
msgstr "No es eso en lo que estoy pensando; solo no quiero que mueras…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:306
msgid ""
"(smiling) Aaaahhh, so even you can be cute sometimes, can't you? (kissing "
"him on his bald head) I won't die before finishing what my past self started "
"ages ago, and this is a promise. So, if we're all good, next morning I want "
"to wake up with breakfast next to me, or else I'll be the one glowering all "
"the time!"
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Aaaahhh, ¿así que hasta tú puedes ser tierno a veces, verdad? "
"(besándolo en la cabeza calva) No voy a morir antes de terminar lo que mi yo "
"del pasado empezó hace eras, y esa es una promesa. Así que, si todo está "
"bien, mañana por la mañana quiero despertar con el desayuno al lado, ¡o seré "
"yo la que esté frunciendo el ceño todo el tiempo"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:328
msgid ""
"You've been staring at me for quite a while, Crimson Sorceress. I hear "
"you're Northerner; if you have any grievance to settle with Wesnoth, know "
"that I-"
msgstr ""
"Llevas un buen rato mirándome, Hechicera Carmesí. He oído que eres del "
"Norte; si tienes alguna cuenta pendiente con Wesnoth, quiero que sepas que yo"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:332
msgid ""
"Ah, don't you worry, prince; I'm not exactly fond of Wesnoth, but I wish it "
"no great ill. My father fought too hard for it, I wouldn't wish to see his "
"beloved homeland crumble."
msgstr ""
"Ah, no te preocupes, príncipe; no soy precisamente fan de Wesnoth, pero "
"tampoco le deseo un gran mal. Mi padre luchó demasiado por él, no querría "
"ver desmoronarse su amada patria."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:336
msgid ""
"So your father was Wesnothian, interesting... Where in Wesnoth did he hail "
"from?"
msgstr ""
"Entonces tu padre era wesnothiano, interesante… ¿De qué parte de Wesnoth era "
"originario?"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:340
msgid ""
"Kerlath, and it wasn't just him who was Wesnothian. My mother was a former "
"noblewoman of the Horse Clans of the east; it wasn't from her that I "
"inherited any love for Wesnoth, though."
msgstr ""
"Kerlath, y no solo él era wesnothiano. Mi madre era una antigua noble de los "
"Clanes de los Caballos del este; aunque no fue de ella de quien heredé "
"ningún amor por Wesnoth."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:344
msgid ""
"The Horse Clans? Interesting, I thought they were mostly of Akladian blood, "
"yet you look nothing like them..."
msgstr ""
"¿Los Clanes de los Caballos? Interesante, pensaba que eran mayormente de "
"sangre akladiana, y sin embargo no te pareces en nada a ellos…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:348
msgid ""
"And you look nothing like your great-great-great-grandparents... But then "
"again, after a few centuries and some dynasties, I shouldn't have expected "
"you to be anything like Elemyrion or Alaevyanne."
msgstr ""
"Y tú no te pareces en nada a tus tatarabuelos… Pero claro, después de unos "
"siglos y algunas dinastías, no debería haber esperado que te parecieras en "
"algo a Elemyrion o Alaevyanne."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:352
msgid ""
"Certainly you shouldn't, as both Elemyrion and Alaevyanne lived long before "
"you were even born."
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto que no deberías, ya que tanto Elemyrion como Alaevyanne "
"vivieron mucho antes de que tú nacieras."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:356
msgid ""
"Not at all. I'm older than the both of them, actually. I've walked this "
"earth for centuries, lad... And don't even start asking me how I did that; "
"Tenma warned me of how impertinent you can be."
msgstr ""
"En absoluto. En realidad soy mayor que ambos. He caminado por esta tierra "
"durante siglos, muchacho… Y ni siquiera empieces a preguntarme cómo lo hice; "
"Tenma ya me advirtió lo impertinente que puedes llegar a ser."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:360
msgid ""
"I've seen enough of your magic to know the wisdom of Alduin's masters is "
"sorely lacking still. Might I simply ask you how well you knew King "
"Elemyrion and Queen Alaevyanne? I've always thirsted for my country's "
"history from before the Akladian invasion; much was burned by those "
"barbarians."
msgstr ""
"He visto suficiente de tu magia como para saber que la sabiduría de los "
"maestros de Alduin aún está muy lejos. ¿Podría simplemente preguntarte qué "
"tan bien conociste al rey Elemyrion y a la reina Alaevyanne? Siempre he "
"tenido sed de la historia de mi país antes de la invasión akladiana; mucho "
"fue quemado por esos bárbaros."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:364
msgid ""
"Why, I knew them quite well. Elemyrion's parents always adored receiving me "
"as guest in their palace, and Alaevyanne was my actual cousin, daughter of "
"my father's sister, aunt Reana."
msgstr ""
"Pues los conocí bastante bien. Los padres de Elemyrion siempre adoraban "
"recibirme como invitada en su palacio, y Alaevyanne era mi prima real, hija "
"de la hermana de mi padre, la tía Reana."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:368
msgid "Wait... You... Your father was Addraryn, the Wyvern of Wesnoth?!"
msgstr "Espera… ¿Tú… tu padre era Addraryn, el Guiverno de Wesnoth?"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:372
msgid ""
"And my mother Elyniver Bayar of the original Horse Clans; she never wanted "
"to be remembered as heroine, but she fought for Wesnoth almost as much as my "
"father did. So, there you have it: I've known Elemyrion and Alaevyanne, and "
"King Vortern and Queen Malene and Eäreldor, and oh how ashamed they'd be if "
"they saw the brutes and knaves who now rule Wesnoth..."
msgstr ""
"Y mi madre Elyniver Bayar de los Clanes de los Caballos originales; ella "
"nunca quiso ser recordada como heroína, pero luchó por Wesnoth casi tanto "
"como mi padre. Así que ahí lo tienes: conocí a Elemyrion y Alaevyanne, al "
"rey Vortern y la reina Malene y a Eäreldor, y ay, qué avergonzados estarían "
"si vieran a los brutos y villanos que ahora gobiernan Wesnoth"

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:414
msgid "The Gods be blessed, Lord Aeldhoryan, the Wyvern of Wesnoth, has come!"
msgstr ""
"¡Que los Dioses sean benditos, el señor Aeldhoryan, el Guiverno de Wesnoth, "
"ha llegado!"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:418
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:581
msgid "Aeldhoryan...!"
msgstr "¡Aeldhoryan…!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:422
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:585
msgid ""
"So this is the man who killed Mad Dog Kyouken and conquered our country..."
msgstr ""
"Entonces este es el hombre que mató al Perro Loco Kyouken y conquistó "
"nuestro país…"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:426
msgid ""
"Defenders of Dorest, Aetheryon, Aethra, you've done well holding off the "
"rebel army; now, please stand back while I deal with the enemy!"
msgstr ""
"Defensores de Dorest, Aetheryon, Aethra, han hecho un gran trabajo "
"conteniendo al ejército rebelde; ahora, por favor retrocedan mientras me "
"encargo del enemigo."

#. [message], speaker=Guldoc
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:430
msgid ""
"Curses, I stand no chance against him with my forces so worn out! Lord "
"Aelvar will kill me for failing to take Dorest..."
msgstr ""
"¡Maldición, no tengo ninguna posibilidad contra él con mis fuerzas tan "
"desgastadas! ¡El señor Aelvar me matará por no haber tomado Dorest…!"

#. [message], speaker=Aethra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:445
msgid ""
"Brother, I'm so relieved you've come! I don't think I would have been able "
"to lead our men for much longer!"
msgstr ""
"¡Hermano, estoy tan aliviada de que hayas llegado! ¡No creo que hubiera "
"podido liderar a nuestros hombres mucho más tiempo!"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:449
msgid ""
"You've done excellently, sister, specially for someone with no military "
"experience; I'm really proud of you."
msgstr ""
"Lo has hecho excelentemente, hermana, especialmente para alguien sin "
"experiencia militar; estoy realmente orgulloso de ti."

#. [message], speaker=Aethra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:453
msgid ""
"Thank you, brother, but most of the credit should go to Aetheryon and his "
"companions; without them, we wouldn't have withstood the siege for so long."
msgstr ""
"Gracias, hermano, pero la mayor parte del crédito debería ir para Aetheryon "
"y sus compañeros; sin ellos no habríamos resistido el asedio tanto tiempo."

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:457
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:605
msgid ""
"And you, Aetheryon... These last weeks, I've often thought about you, and "
"the reasons which led you to abandon your post as the governor of Kodakuni "
"in my stead, and disappear in the world without leaving a trace..."
msgstr ""
"Y tú, Aetheryon… Estas últimas semanas he pensado mucho en ti, y en las "
"razones que te llevaron a abandonar tu puesto como gobernador de Kodakuni en "
"mi lugar, y desaparecer del mundo sin dejar rastro…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:461
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:609
msgid "Erm, well..."
msgstr "Ejem, bueno…"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:465
msgid ""
"...but now I see, once again, proof that some ills come for better, as your "
"intervention seems to have been crucial for the survival of Dorest. Now, I "
"must say that you have gathered quite an interesting group... (smirking) As "
"for this brave Sogen young lady, should I understand that she's the reason "
"you vanished from Kodakuni? I understand; never would father have accepted "
"such union..."
msgstr ""
"…pero ahora veo, una vez más, prueba de que algunos males vienen para bien, "
"ya que tu intervención parece haber sido crucial para la supervivencia de "
"Dorest. Ahora, debo decir que has reunido un grupo bastante interesante… "
"(sonriendo con picardía) En cuanto a esta valiente joven sogen, ¿debo "
"entender que ella es la razón por la que desapareciste de Kodakuni? Lo "
"entiendo; jamás habría aceptado padre una unión así"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:469
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:617
msgid "(blushing) What?! Ew, no!"
msgstr "(sonrojada) ¿¡Qué!? ¡Ew, no!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:473
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:621
msgid ""
"(blushing slightly) In fact, brother, I'm the one who joined them, after... "
"Well, it's a long story, I promise I'll tell it all, but first I have "
"something to discuss with you regarding this war started by our older "
"brother."
msgstr ""
"(sonrojado ligeramente) En realidad, hermano, fui yo quien se unió a ellos, "
"después de… Bueno, es una larga historia, te prometo que te lo contaré todo, "
"pero primero tengo algo que discutir contigo respecto a esta guerra iniciada "
"por nuestro hermano mayor."

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:477
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:625
msgid ""
"I see... Well, my White Mages shall tend to the wounded; while they're at "
"it, we shall discuss whatever you have to say in the City Hall."
msgstr ""
"Ya veo… Bueno, mis Magos Blancos atenderán a los heridos; mientras lo hacen, "
"discutiremos lo que tengas que decir en el Ayuntamiento."

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:493
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:641
msgid ""
"So it's true that you have deserted the Ken-Ningen to flee with the rebel "
"Tenma Yozora, Kenshiro."
msgstr ""
"Entonces es cierto que desertaste de los Ken-Ningen para huir con la rebelde "
"Tenma Yozora, Kenshiro."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:497
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:645
msgid ""
"You knew who she was, and yet you did nothing to arrest her? She... I mean, "
"we killed Wesnothian soldiers, after all."
msgstr ""
"¿Sabías quién era ella y aun así no hiciste nada por arrestarla? Ella… "
"quiero decir, nosotros matamos soldados wesnothianos, después de todo."

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:501
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:649
msgid ""
"Of course I do know her, I'm always aware of what happens in my dear "
"Kodakuni. As for arresting her... Well, let's say that I forgive her crimes "
"for saving my little sister and Dorest."
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto que la conozco, siempre estoy al tanto de lo que pasa en mi "
"querido Kodakuni. En cuanto a arrestarla… digamos que perdono sus crímenes "
"por haber salvado a mi hermanita y a Dorest."

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:508
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:656
msgid "By the way, Kenshiro... how fares your mother?"
msgstr "Por cierto, Kenshiro… ¿cómo está tu madre?"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:512
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:660
msgid ""
"She was crying the last time I saw her, but she was healthy anyway. Maybe "
"you should pay her a visit, though, if you're so interested in her welfare."
msgstr ""
"Estaba llorando la última vez que la vi, pero estaba sana de todos modos. "
"Tal vez deberías visitarla, si estás tan interesado en su bienestar."

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:516
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:664
msgid ""
"Maybe you are right, after all... Now, let's follow the others into the "
"hall, there is much to be discussed..."
msgstr ""
"Tal vez tengas razón, después de todo… Ahora, sigamos a los demás al salón, "
"hay mucho que discutir…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:539
msgid "Excellent! We've managed to break the siege on our own!"
msgstr "¡Excelente! ¡Hemos logrado romper el asedio por nuestra cuenta!"

#. [message], speaker=Aethra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:577
msgid "Oh, look, it's brother Aeldhoryan!"
msgstr "¡Oh, mira, es el hermano Aeldhoryan!"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:597
msgid ""
"Defenders of Dorest, Aetheryon, Aethra, I apologize for not being able to "
"arrive sooner; it seems that you had to deal with the enemy on your own, and "
"for this I am sorry."
msgstr ""
"Defensores de Dorest, Aetheryon, Aethra, les pido disculpas por no haber "
"podido llegar antes; parece que tuvieron que enfrentarse al enemigo solos, y "
"por eso lo lamento."

#. [message], speaker=Aethra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:601
msgid ""
"It is well, brother, Aetheryon's friends were too powerful for our "
"attackers, that was why none of them managed to last until your arrival!"
msgstr ""
"Está bien, hermano, los amigos de Aetheryon eran demasiado poderosos para "
"nuestros atacantes, ¡por eso ninguno logró resistir hasta tu llegada"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:613
msgid ""
"...but now I see, once again, proof that some ills come for better, as your "
"intervention seems to have been crucial for the survival of Dorest. Now, I "
"must say that you have gathered quite an interesting group... (smirking) As "
"for this gorgeous Sogen young lady, should I understand that she's the "
"reason you vanished from Kodakuni? I understand; never would father have "
"accepted such union..."
msgstr ""
"…pero ahora veo, una vez más, prueba de que algunos males vienen para bien, "
"ya que tu intervención parece haber sido crucial para la supervivencia de "
"Dorest. Ahora, debo decir que has reunido un grupo bastante interesante… "
"(sonriendo con picardía) En cuanto a esta hermosa joven sogen, ¿debo "
"entender que ella es la razón por la que desapareciste de Kodakuni? Lo "
"entiendo; jamás habría aceptado padre una unión así"

#. [message], speaker=Aethra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:683
msgid "Brother...!"
msgstr "¡Hermano…!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:687
msgid "SISTER, NO!!!"
msgstr "¡HERMANA, NO!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/20_Into_The_Northlands.cfg:691
msgid "Damn it, how could we have let her die like this?!"
msgstr "¡Maldición, cómo pudimos dejarla morir así!"

#. [scenario], id=21_Northern_Alliances
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:5
msgid "Northern Alliances"
msgstr "Alianzas del Norte"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:26
msgid "Defeat the Rebels"
msgstr "Derrota a los rebeldes"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:58
msgid ""
"In order to get either the dwarves or the trolls to aid you, recruit/recall "
"either a dwarvish or a troll unit.\n"
"From now on, Donar can recruit Dokkor soldiers, and Aetheryon can recruit "
"spearmen, bowmen, horsemen and mages. Aetheryon's mages seem to take a "
"liking for Valerya; it wouldn't be surprising if some of them choose to "
"follow her in later travels..."
msgstr ""
"Para conseguir que ya sea los enanos o los trolls te ayuden, recluta/"
"reincorpora ya sea una unidad enana o trol.\n"
"A partir de ahora, Donar puede reclutar soldados Dokkor, y Aetheryon puede "
"reclutar lanceros, arqueros, jinetes y magos. Los magos de Aetheryon parecen "
"haberle tomado cariño a Valerya; no sería sorprendente que algunos decidan "
"seguirla en viajes posteriores…"

#. [side], type=Iron Mauler
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:88
msgid "General Rhaent"
msgstr "General Rhaent"

#. [side], type=Troll Warrior
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:109
msgid "Chief Grokk"
msgstr "Jefe Grokk"

#. [side], type=Troll Warrior
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:115
msgid "Haag Trolls"
msgstr "Trolls de Haag"

#. [side], type=Dwarvish Dragonguard
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:132
msgid "Lord Dulcatul"
msgstr "Señor Dulcatul"

#. [side], type=Dwarvish Dragonguard
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:138
msgid "Haag Dwarves"
msgstr "Enanos de Haag"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:156
msgid "Orcs"
msgstr "Orcos"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:226
msgid ""
"Ha! I told you that the rebels would have to pay a heavy price for venturing "
"into these mountains, the trolls and dwarves living here would never let "
"them come in and do as they wish!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ja! Te dije que los rebeldes tendrían que pagar un precio muy alto por "
"aventurarse en estas montañas, ¡los trolls y enanos que viven aquí jamás les "
"permitirían entrar y hacer lo que quisieran!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:230
msgid ""
"Nevertheless, that won't do us any good either. Haven't you said that the "
"dwarvish and troll clans living are not under the Northern Alliance?"
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, eso tampoco nos beneficia a nosotros. ¿No dijiste que los "
"clanes enanos y trolls que viven aquí no están bajo la Alianza del Norte?"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:240
msgid ""
"Donar has dwarves in his army; can't we use that to get those dwarves to "
"side with us?"
msgstr ""
"Donar tiene enanos en su ejército; ¿no podemos usar eso para que esos enanos "
"se pongan de nuestro lado?"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:244
msgid ""
"Och, unfortunately that won't do. The dwarves of the Haag Mountains are "
"hostile to the Northern Alliance, and even more to the dwarves allied to it. "
"You see, the Alliance has once sided with an orcish sovereign, Kapou'e, "
"against an alliance of some human, elvish and dwarvish nations – and these "
"latter were the ancestors of the Haag Dwarves."
msgstr ""
"Och, lamentablemente eso no sirve. Los enanos de las Montañas Haag son "
"hostiles a la Alianza del Norte, y más aún a los enanos aliados a ella. "
"Verás, la Alianza alguna vez se puso del lado de un soberano orco, Kapou'e, "
"contra una alianza de algunas naciones humanas, élficas y enanas… y estos "
"últimos fueron los antepasados de los Enanos de Haag."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:248
msgid ""
"I see... Still, we did fight alongside the dwarves of the Aurvang Clan back "
"in the Hammermounts, and there are still some of them in our group; maybe "
"the Haag Dwarves will be friendlier towards them, and be neutral towards us."
msgstr ""
"Ya veo… Aun así, luchamos junto a los enanos del Clan Aurvang allá en los "
"Hammermounts, y todavía hay algunos de ellos en nuestro grupo; tal vez los "
"Enanos de Haag sean más amigables con ellos y neutrales con nosotros."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:261
msgid ""
"Well, we did fight alongside trolls back in the Hammermounts, and there are "
"still some of them in our group; maybe if these trolls see some of their kin "
"amongst us, they may choose to help us fight the rebels."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, luchamos junto a trolls allá en los Hammermounts, y todavía hay "
"algunos de ellos en nuestro grupo; tal vez si estos trolls ven a algunos de "
"sus parientes entre nosotros, decidan ayudarnos a luchar contra los rebeldes."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:274
msgid ""
"Had we befriended either trolls or dwarves back in the Hammermounts, we "
"might have been able to get some new friends here..."
msgstr ""
"Si hubiéramos hecho amistad con trolls o enanos allá en los Hammermounts, "
"tal vez podríamos haber conseguido algunos amigos nuevos aquí"

#. [message], speaker=Dulcatul
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:289
msgid ""
"Och, I see more dwarves coming from the south; they must be from the "
"Northern Alliance, though, judging by their companions..."
msgstr ""
"Och, veo más enanos viniendo del sur; deben ser de la Alianza del Norte, a "
"juzgar por sus compañeros…"

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:300
msgid ""
"We do have companions from this Northern Alliance, but we're Aurvang Dwarves "
"from the Hammermounts. We're told that ye have a grudge against Knalgan "
"dwarves, but, in the name of our ancestor Aurvang, son of Motsoghnir, we ask "
"ye to ignore us on the battlefield; we don't want to attack ye, and those "
"humans are our enemies just as they are yours."
msgstr ""
"Sí tenemos compañeros de esta Alianza del Norte, pero nosotros somos Enanos "
"Aurvang de los Hammermounts. Nos han dicho que guardan rencor contra los "
"enanos knalganos, pero, en nombre de nuestro ancestro Aurvang, hijo de "
"Motsoghnir, les pedimos que nos ignoren en el campo de batalla; no queremos "
"atacarlos, y esos humanos son nuestros enemigos igual que son los suyos."

#. [message], speaker=Dulcatul
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:304
msgid ""
"Hrumph! I'd be troubled to attack dwarves who have never done anything "
"against us... Very well then, we won't drive our axes against ye if that "
"means fighting our kin from the Far Realms; feel yourselves lucky, folk o' "
"the Alliance..."
msgstr ""
"¡Hrumph! Me costaría atacar a enanos que nunca nos han hecho nada… Muy bien "
"entonces, no blandiremos nuestras hachas contra ustedes si eso significa "
"luchar contra nuestros parientes de los Reinos Lejanos; siéntanse "
"afortunados, gente de la Alianza…"

#. [message], speaker=Grokk
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:322
msgid ""
"What is that? Are there trolls fighting alongside those humans and those "
"dwarves? Could you possibly be from the Northern Alliance?"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué es eso? ¿Hay trolls luchando junto a esos humanos y esos enanos? ¿Acaso "
"podrían ser de la Alianza del Norte?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:326
msgid ""
"Our friend here is, but we're travellers from the Far East; the trolls "
"following us are friends we've made in the distant Hammermounts, where we "
"helped their tribe, the Drokkor, fight against a great menace."
msgstr ""
"Nuestro amigo aquí sí lo es, pero nosotros somos viajeros del Lejano "
"Oriente; los trolls que nos siguen son amigos que hicimos en los lejanos "
"Hammermounts, donde ayudamos a su tribu, los Drokkor, a luchar contra una "
"gran amenaza."

#. [message], speaker=Grokk
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:330
msgid ""
"Humans who befriend trolls, that's something I've never heard of before... "
"But I won't ignore it either: if you're friend-of-trolls, you won't attack "
"my people, and in return we won't attack you."
msgstr ""
"Humanos que hacen amistad con trolls, eso es algo que nunca había oído "
"antes… Pero tampoco lo ignoraré: si son amigos de los trolls, no atacarán a "
"mi pueblo, y a cambio nosotros no los atacaremos."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:334
msgid "Fair enough."
msgstr "Me parece justo."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:361
msgid ""
"You seem to have befriended my sister quite quickly, Tenma; that was quite a "
"surprise to me, as Aethra doesn't easily trust strangers."
msgstr ""
"Parece que te has hecho amiga de mi hermana muy rápido, Tenma; eso me "
"sorprendió bastante, ya que Aethra no confía fácilmente en extraños."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:365
msgid ""
"Yeah, I was very surprised too, but by how lovely she is, even though she's "
"your sister. Not even Cornelya could help being nice to her."
msgstr ""
"Sí, yo también me sorprendí mucho, pero por lo encantadora que es, aunque "
"sea tu hermana. Ni siquiera Cornelya pudo evitar ser amable con ella."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:369
msgid ""
"Flowers bloom even among the thorniest weed. I'm not so cold-hearted as to "
"trample them as I would the rest."
msgstr ""
"Las flores florecen incluso entre la maleza más espinosa. No soy tan de "
"corazón frío como para pisotearlas como haría con el resto."

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:373
msgid "Leave it to elves to wax poetic even when being prejudiced."
msgstr ""
"Déjenle a los elfos ponerse poéticos incluso cuando están siendo "
"prejuiciosos."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:377
msgid ""
"Is it prejudice, to say humans are brutish and bellicose? Look no further "
"than the battlefield ahead: I spot humans, dwarves and trolls, but no elf "
"raising their blade in unnecessary hostility against us."
msgstr ""
"¿Es prejuicio decir que los humanos son brutales y belicosos? No hay que "
"buscar más lejos que el campo de batalla de adelante: veo humanos, enanos y "
"trolls, pero ningún elfo alzando su espada en una hostilidad innecesaria "
"contra nosotros."

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:381
msgid ""
"We're not deep enough into the Northlands, princess. Ye're not from around "
"here, are ye? Only reason ye don't see elves waging war as often is because "
"they content themselves with the forests they're born into; but try even "
"squinting at their damn woods and see how 'graceful' and 'civilised' they "
"get."
msgstr ""
"No estamos lo suficientemente adentro de las Tierras del Norte, princesa. No "
"eres de por aquí, ¿verdad? La única razón por la que no ves a los elfos "
"hacer la guerra tan a menudo es porque se contentan con los bosques en los "
"que nacen; pero intenta siquiera entrecerrar los ojos hacia sus malditos "
"bosques y verás qué tan «graciosos» y «civilizados» se ponen."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:385
msgid ""
"Sodding suns, can we go <i>five minutes<i/> without bashing each other's "
"culture? I swear it, seven centuries and people don't change..."
msgstr ""
"Malditos soles, ¿podemos pasar <i>cinco minutos</i> sin atacar la cultura "
"del otro? Lo juro, siete siglos y la gente no cambia…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:404
msgid ""
"I've been thinking, Valerya... distant as we may be, we're actual cousins."
msgstr ""
"He estado pensando, Valerya… por distantes que estemos, somos primos de "
"verdad."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:408
msgid "Ugh, don't even start it, lad..."
msgstr "Ugh, ni siquiera empieces, muchacho…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:412
msgid ""
"In fact, you're related to the entire Iron Dynasty, and with your Bayar "
"blood, you could inherit their castle. It still stands, ruined and weakened "
"as it may be."
msgstr ""
"De hecho, estás emparentada con toda la Dinastía de Hierro, y con tu sangre "
"Bayar podrías heredar su castillo. Todavía está en pie, aunque arruinado y "
"debilitado como esté."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:416
msgid ""
"I much prefer my little academy at the Firecloud Peak, thanks very much. I "
"would be grateful if someone stopped sending foolish Wesnothian generals to "
"harass us, however."
msgstr ""
"Prefiero mucho más mi pequeña academia en la Cumbre de la Nube de Fuego, "
"muchas gracias. Sin embargo, estaría agradecida si alguien dejara de enviar "
"generales wesnothianos estúpidos a acosarnos."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:420
msgid ""
"My point is, you may disapprove of Wesnoth's current dynasty... and I agree "
"with you. The Iron emperors are every bit the brutes and knaves you deem "
"them to be. But my brother Aeldhoryan is different; it's not without reason "
"he's been the first Iron prince to wield both Elemyrion's bow and your "
"father's sword-"
msgstr ""
"Mi punto es que puedes desaprobar a la dinastía actual de Wesnoth… y estoy "
"de acuerdo contigo. Los emperadores de Hierro son en todo sentido los brutos "
"y villanos que consideras. Pero mi hermano Aeldhoryan es diferente; no es "
"sin razón que ha sido el primer príncipe de Hierro en empuñar tanto el arco "
"de Elemyrion como la espada de tu padre"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:424
msgid ""
"-Which I <i>might</i> be wanting back, if only to make sure it's never used "
"for unworthy goals again. I still can't believe it was wielded in the "
"conquest of Kodakuni."
msgstr ""
"—que <i>quizá</i> quiera recuperar, aunque sea solo para asegurarme de que "
"nunca más se use para fines indignos. Todavía no puedo creer que se haya "
"usado en la conquista de Kodakuni."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:428
msgid "Damn right!"
msgstr "¡Maldita sea, claro que sí!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:432
msgid ""
"Elven sages have done that for you centuries ago; only honourable hearts may "
"wield the Oreyand blade, and never against defenceless foes. I guess Tenma "
"failed to tell you, or perhaps she simply ignores that the conquest of "
"Kodakuni was inevitable from the moment our charters found that country. My "
"brother led the charge to make sure that Kodakuni was <i>spared</i> the "
"worse brutalities of our empire's expansion.  As I was saying, I've always "
"thought Aeldhoryan was the best successor to my father Wesnoth could hope "
"for - and now, with Aelvar disowned, Aeldhoryan is sure to become the next "
"Emperor. He could turn Wesnoth into a much fairer nation... But he would "
"need strong people, reliable people, by his side."
msgstr ""
"Los sabios elfos hicieron eso por ti hace siglos; solo corazones honorables "
"pueden empuñar la hoja Oreyand, y nunca contra enemigos indefensos. Supongo "
"que Tenma no te lo dijo, o tal vez simplemente ignora que la conquista de "
"Kodakuni era inevitable desde el momento en que nuestras cartas encontraron "
"ese país. Mi hermano lideró la carga para asegurarse de que Kodakuni <i>se "
"librara</i> de las peores brutalidades de la expansión de nuestro imperio. "
"Como decía, siempre he pensado que Aeldhoryan era el mejor sucesor que "
"Wesnoth podía esperar de mi padre… y ahora, con Aelvar desheredado, "
"Aeldhoryan seguramente será el próximo Emperador. Podría convertir a Wesnoth "
"en una nación mucho más justa… Pero necesitaría gente fuerte, gente "
"confiable, a su lado."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:436
msgid "Pfff..."
msgstr "Pfff…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:440
msgid ""
"In any case, as I was saying, I've always deemed Aeldhoryan the best emperor "
"Wesnoth could hope for - and now, with Aelvar disowned, he is sure to "
"succeed our father. He could turn Wesnoth into a much fairer nation... But "
"he would need strong people, reliable people, by his side."
msgstr ""
"En cualquier caso, como decía, siempre he considerado a Aeldhoryan el mejor "
"emperador que Wesnoth podía esperar… y ahora, con Aelvar desheredado, "
"seguramente sucederá a nuestro padre. Podría convertir a Wesnoth en una "
"nación mucho más justa… Pero necesitaría gente fuerte, gente confiable, a su "
"lado."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:444
msgid ""
"And you think that I, the mighty Crimson Sorceress, blood of one of "
"Wesnoth's most celebrated heroes, one who came to symbolise the purest, most "
"honest aspects of Wesnoth's soul, would be the perfect ally for your "
"brother. You're not wrong, I <i>could</i> help him greatly."
msgstr ""
"Y tú piensas que yo, la poderosa Hechicera Carmesí, sangre de uno de los "
"héroes más celebrados de Wesnoth, quien llegó a simbolizar los aspectos más "
"puros y honestos del alma de Wesnoth, sería la aliada perfecta para tu "
"hermano. No estás equivocado, <i>podría</i> ayudarlo enormemente."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:448
msgid "By your tone, I foresee you'll nevertheless refuse..."
msgstr "Por tu tono, preveo que aun así te negarás…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:452
msgid ""
"(smirks) Clever boy... If also naive. Aeldhoryan may be honourable, but a "
"single individual, not even an emperor, can shape an entire nation in his "
"own image. A nation is its people, and Wesnoth didn't become a warmongering "
"empire without the enthusiastic support of its people, who are all too proud "
"to brag about their country's so-called 'glory'."
msgstr ""
"(sonríe con ironía) Chico listo… aunque también ingenuo. Aeldhoryan puede "
"ser honorable, pero un solo individuo, ni siquiera un emperador, puede "
"moldear a toda una nación a su imagen. Una nación es su pueblo, y Wesnoth no "
"se convirtió en un imperio belicista sin el apoyo entusiasta de su gente, "
"que está demasiado orgullosa como para jactarse de la supuesta «gloria» de "
"su país."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:456
msgid ""
"So, what? Are we destined to be a corrupt nation, without a chance at "
"redemption? Are we to be ruled by greedy tyrants and sycophants our entire "
"existence?"
msgstr ""
"¿Entonces qué? ¿Estamos destinados a ser una nación corrupta, sin "
"posibilidad de redención? ¿Vamos a ser gobernados por tiranos codiciosos y "
"aduladores toda nuestra existencia?"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:460
msgid ""
"Not if they were all removed, forcefully if needed, but by the people of "
"Wesnoth themselves."
msgstr ""
"No si todos fueran removidos, por la fuerza si fuera necesario, pero por el "
"propio pueblo de Wesnoth."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:464
msgid ""
"(chuckles) So you disapprove of nobles fearing a tyrant, but not their own "
"people..."
msgstr ""
"(ríe entre dientes) Entonces desapruebas que los nobles teman a un tirano, "
"pero no a su propio pueblo…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:468
msgid ""
"If there's anyone the rulers of a country should fear, it's their people. In "
"fact, in a truly fairer society, the rulers do fear their people - and are "
"all the better as rulers for that."
msgstr ""
"Si hay alguien a quien los gobernantes de un país deberían temer, es a su "
"pueblo. De hecho, en una sociedad verdaderamente más justa, los gobernantes "
"sí temen a su pueblo… y son mucho mejores gobernantes por eso."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:472
msgid ""
"You speak of dreamlands and impossibilities... But I take your point. A "
"shame, though; it would have been an honour, to have one such as you by our "
"side."
msgstr ""
"Hablas de tierras de sueños e imposibilidades… Pero entiendo tu punto. Es "
"una lástima, sin embargo; habría sido un honor tener a alguien como tú a "
"nuestro lado."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:476
msgid ""
"Ah, of course it would. But my mother surely would come back from the dead "
"to kill me if I ever sat beside a Wesnothian ruler's throne..."
msgstr ""
"Ah, por supuesto que lo sería. Pero mi madre seguramente volvería de entre "
"los muertos para matarme si alguna vez me sentara junto al trono de un "
"gobernante wesnothiano…"

#. [message], speaker=Rhaent
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:492
msgid ""
"And so our 'friends' from the south attack, as expected... Damn their "
"timing, I can't fight them, the dwarves and the trolls at the same time; "
"someone go call the reinforcements, quickly – and they better come in time, "
"or I'll come back as a wraith and gut them like pigs!"
msgstr ""
"Y así nuestros «amigos» del sur atacan, como era de esperarse… Maldita sea "
"su timing, no puedo luchar contra ellos, los enanos y los trolls al mismo "
"tiempo; ¡que alguien vaya a llamar a los refuerzos, rápido… y más les vale "
"llegar a tiempo, o volveré como un espectro y los destriparé como cerdos!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:511
msgid ""
"A rider has just left their fortress... We should defeat them soon, or else "
"this battle will drag on and we will lose even more soldiers."
msgstr ""
"Un jinete acaba de salir de su fortaleza… Deberíamos derrotarlos pronto, o "
"esta batalla se prolongará y perderemos aún más soldados."

#. [unit], id=Borg, type=Orcish Warlord
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:564
msgid "Borg"
msgstr "Borg"

#. [message], speaker=Rhaent
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:590
msgid "You stupid beasts, you came late on purpose, didn't you?!"
msgstr "¡Bestias estúpidas, vinieron tarde a propósito, ¿verdad?!"

#. [message], speaker=Borg
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:594
msgid ""
"Shut the hell up, weakling! We stopped our feast only to save your sorry "
"ass, so stop whining at once!"
msgstr ""
"¡Cállate de una vez, débil! ¡Detuvimos nuestro banquete solo para salvar tu "
"miserable pellejo, así que deja de lloriquear de inmediato!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:598
msgid ""
" Curses, don't tell me Aelvar's managed to bring even the orcs to his side!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldición, no me digas que Aelvar ha logrado llevar incluso a los orcos a "
"su bando!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:602
msgid ""
"We don't need to worry right now; orcs usually act as independent warbands, "
"that doesn't mean all of the orcish clanates have joined your brother."
msgstr ""
"No necesitamos preocuparnos ahora; los orcos suelen actuar como bandas de "
"guerra independientes, eso no significa que todos los conglomerados de "
"clanes orcos se hayan unido a tu hermano."

#. [message], speaker=Borg
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:627
msgid ""
"That stupid weakling just got himself killed... Grunts, we have nothing to "
"do here any more, let the humans, the dwarves and the trolls butcher each "
"other!"
msgstr ""
"Ese estúpido débil acaba de hacerse matar… Gruñones, ya no tenemos nada que "
"hacer aquí, ¡dejen que los humanos, los enanos y los trolls se despedacen "
"entre sí!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:638
msgid ""
"We've managed to destroy the rebel fortress, but I'm afraid that they might "
"try and rebuild it... Trolls, dwarves, I know I have no right to meddle in "
"your business, but I advise you to stay united, at least for now, or you may "
"not be able to resist another rebel assault."
msgstr ""
"Hemos logrado destruir la fortaleza rebelde, pero me temo que podrían "
"intentar reconstruirla… Trolls, enanos, sé que no tengo derecho a meterme en "
"sus asuntos, pero les aconsejo que permanezcan unidos, al menos por ahora, o "
"podrían no resistir otro asalto rebelde."

#. [message], speaker=Grokk
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:642
msgid ""
"Grumph! As if anyone could live with these disgusting dwarves who only care "
"about gold and precious ores!"
msgstr ""
"¡Grumph! ¡Como si alguien pudiera vivir con estos enanos asquerosos que solo "
"se preocupan por el oro y los minerales preciosos!"

#. [message], speaker=Dulcatul
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:646
msgid ""
"And I, by my turn, would rather die than bleed for the sake of these stupid "
"brutes! And ye better stay outta our way, humans, or ye'll be next to die!"
msgstr ""
"¡Y yo, por mi parte, preferiría morir antes que sangrar por el bien de estos "
"brutos estúpidos! ¡Y mejor manténganse fuera de nuestro camino, humanos, o "
"serán los próximos en morir!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:650
msgid ""
"I appreciate your good intentions, Tenma, but you're only wasting your time. "
"Trolls and dwarves have been battling each other for ages to count, and the "
"Northlands, along with Knalga, are the birthplace of this enmity."
msgstr ""
"Aprecio tus buenas intenciones, Tenma, pero solo estás perdiendo el tiempo. "
"Los trolls y los enanos han estado luchando entre sí durante eras "
"incontables, y las Tierras del Norte, junto con Knalga, son el lugar de "
"nacimiento de esta enemistad."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:654
msgid ""
"But what could have been so terrible that makes them kill each other century "
"after century?!"
msgstr ""
"¡Pero qué pudo haber sido tan terrible como para que se maten entre sí siglo "
"tras siglo!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:658
msgid ""
"I don't know many details, but it has something to do with an ancient "
"dwarvish lord betraying and killing the leader of the trolls. The latter "
"have never forgiven the dwarves, who, by their turn, are too proud to accept "
"that they were on the wrong side."
msgstr ""
"No conozco muchos detalles, pero tiene que ver con un antiguo señor enano "
"que traicionó y mató al líder de los trolls. Estos últimos nunca han "
"perdonado a los enanos, quienes, a su vez, son demasiado orgullosos como "
"para aceptar que estaban del lado equivocado."

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:662
msgid ""
"Nice story, but we should get moving already, or we're actually going to get "
"smashed and chopped before we can even say 'not fair'."
msgstr ""
"Buena historia, pero ya deberíamos movernos, o nos van a aplastar y cortar "
"en pedazos antes de que podamos decir «no es justo»."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:666
msgid ""
"Yes, let's move already, I have no interest in learning about the petty "
"grudges of petty people."
msgstr ""
"Sí, vámonos de una vez, no tengo ningún interés en enterarme de los rencores "
"insignificantes de gente insignificante."

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:670
msgid ""
"You sure talk a lot for someone who does nothing for the group, don't you?"
msgstr ""
"Seguro que hablas mucho para alguien que no hace nada por el grupo, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:674
msgid ""
"Don't misunderstand me, I'm not following these people on my own accord, so "
"I have no reason to be a dedicated companion, let alone to you, human "
"dwarf..."
msgstr ""
"No me malinterpretes, no estoy siguiendo a esta gente por decisión propia, "
"así que no tengo ninguna razón para ser una compañera dedicada, y mucho "
"menos para ti, enano humano"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:678
msgid "(livid) You darn...!"
msgstr "(furioso) ¡Maldita…!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:682
msgid ""
"Donar, do not let her get under your skin. You say she's useless, which is "
"mostly true, but I think I have just found a usefulness for her. We've "
"completed our original mission, but we could go even beyond and storm "
"Aelvar's fortress by surprise, while most of his armies are away. To "
"accomplish that, though, we must first cross the Forest of Thelien."
msgstr ""
"Donar, no dejes que te saque de quicio. Dices que es inútil, y en gran parte "
"es cierto, pero creo que acabo de encontrarle una utilidad. Ya completamos "
"nuestra misión original, pero podríamos ir más allá y asaltar la fortaleza "
"de Aelvar por sorpresa mientras la mayoría de sus ejércitos están lejos. "
"Para lograrlo, sin embargo, primero debemos cruzar el Bosque de Thelien."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:686
msgid ""
"(suddenly troubled) Hell no...! I mean, I'd rather not go through that "
"forest. The Thelien Elves are almost as hostile to outsiders as those from "
"the Silent Forest; I doubt even Cornelya's presence will guarantee us safety."
msgstr ""
"(de repente inquieta) ¡De ninguna manera…! Quiero decir, preferiría no pasar "
"por ese bosque. Los elfos de Thelien son casi tan hostiles con los "
"forasteros como los del Bosque Silencioso; dudo que ni siquiera la presencia "
"de Cornelya nos garantice seguridad."

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:690
msgid ""
"It won't be only the princess requesting passage, but a commander of the "
"Northern Alliance too. Besides, as much as it annoys me to admit, I like the "
"Wesnothian's plan. Aelvar is a powerful lord, but he's very arrogant too; I "
"bet the last thing he expects is to be attacked at his own turf right now, "
"so he must be unguarded. And, if we manage to strike him down quickly, we'll "
"still be able to escape through the same way we arrived there, as the rebels "
"won't dare follow us into the Forest of Thelien."
msgstr ""
"No será solo la princesa pidiendo paso, sino también un comandante de la "
"Alianza del Norte. Además, aunque me moleste admitirlo, me gusta el plan del "
"wesnothiano. Aelvar es un señor poderoso, pero también muy arrogante; "
"apuesto a que lo último que espera es ser atacado en su propio terreno justo "
"ahora, así que debe estar poco protegido. Y si logramos derribarlo rápido, "
"todavía podremos escapar por el mismo camino por el que llegamos, ya que los "
"rebeldes no se atreverán a seguirnos hasta el Bosque de Thelien."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:694
msgid ""
"I too agree with this plan; do you have any problem with that forest in "
"special, Valerya?"
msgstr ""
"Yo también estoy de acuerdo con este plan; ¿tienes algún problema en "
"especial con ese bosque, Valerya?"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:698
msgid "Of course not, I was just worried about the elves' hostility."
msgstr "Claro que no, solo estaba preocupada por la hostilidad de los elfos."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:702
msgid ""
"I am a princess of Metheldur, not even Landar the Ruthless would have dared "
"to hurt me, as that means suffering retaliation from the Sylvan Host itself."
msgstr ""
"Soy una princesa de Metheldur, ni siquiera Landar el Implacable se habría "
"atrevido a hacerme daño, porque eso significaría sufrir la represalia de la "
"Hueste Silvana misma."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:706
msgid ""
"I have no idea who Landar is, nor do I care to know. Now, we really need to "
"go, the trolls and the dwarves are about to get us already!"
msgstr ""
"No tengo idea de quién es Landar, ni me interesa saberlo. Ahora, de verdad "
"necesitamos irnos, ¡los trolls y los enanos ya casi nos alcanzan!"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:710
msgid "Agreed... *I wonder what she meant by 'human dwarf', though...*"
msgstr ""
"De acuerdo… *Me pregunto qué quiso decir con «enano humano», de todos modos…*"

#. [message], speaker=Rhaent
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:729
msgid ""
"Those useless orcs weren't enough to repel the southerners... Someone go and "
"ask Lord Aelvar for reinforcements!"
msgstr ""
"¡Esos orcos inútiles no fueron suficientes para repeler a los sureños…! ¡Que "
"alguien vaya a pedirle refuerzos al señor Aelvar!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/21_Northern_Alliances.cfg:733
msgid ""
"No! We won't be able to prevail if we're attacked by Aelvar's own forces!"
msgstr ""
"¡No! ¡No podremos prevalecer si nos atacan las propias fuerzas de Aelvar!"

#. [scenario], id=22_Memories
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:5
msgid "Memories"
msgstr "Recuerdos"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:25
msgid "Cross the Forest of Thelien"
msgstr "Cruzar el Bosque de Thelien"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:57
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:402
msgid "Death of General Varyon"
msgstr "Muerte del General Varyon"

#. [side], type=Elvish High Lord
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:89
msgid "Lord Thalmen"
msgstr "Señor Thalmen"

#. [side], type=Elvish High Lord
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:95
msgid "Thelien Elves"
msgstr "Elfos de Thelien"

#. [side], type=Orcish Sovereign
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:110
msgid "Chief Rurk"
msgstr "Jefe Rurk"

#. [side], type=Orcish Sovereign
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:116
msgid "Orcish Clanates"
msgstr "Conglomerados de clanes orcos"

#. [side], type=Aragwaith Captain
#. [unit], id=Varyon, type=Aragwaith Captain
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:132
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/scenario-utils.cfg:61
msgid "General Varyon"
msgstr "General Varyon"

#. [side], type=Aragwaith Captain
#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:138
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:177
msgid "Aragwaithi"
msgstr "Aragwaithi"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:199
msgid ""
"Beware now, everyone: we're deep into the Forest of Thelien, and so we're "
"going to stumble on its inhabitants soon enough. We may have the little "
"princess with us, but until they recognize her we might be struck by a few "
"dozen arrows if we're not careful enough."
msgstr ""
"Precaución ahora, todos: estamos muy adentro del Bosque de Thelien, y pronto "
"tropezaremos con sus habitantes. Puede que tengamos a la pequeña princesa "
"con nosotros, pero hasta que la reconozcan podríamos recibir varias docenas "
"de flechas si no tenemos suficiente cuidado."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:203
msgid ""
"Valerya, is everything all right? You've been... distracted since we decided "
"to cross this forest..."
msgstr ""
"Valerya, ¿está todo bien? Has estado… distraída desde que decidimos cruzar "
"este bosque…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:207
msgid ""
"I... (sigh) Well, it's just that I don't have good memories from this "
"forest. I lost a friend here, long ago; the Thelien Elves weren't known for "
"their hostility yet, so we thought we'd have a safe journey through this "
"region..."
msgstr ""
"Yo… (suspiro) Bueno, es solo que no tengo buenos recuerdos de este bosque. "
"Perdí a un amigo aquí, hace mucho tiempo; los elfos de Thelien todavía no "
"eran conocidos por su hostilidad, así que pensamos que tendríamos un viaje "
"seguro por esta región…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:211
msgid ""
"The Thelien Elves cannot be blamed for mistrusting outsiders, though, not "
"after all they've suffered at the hands of the Orcish Empire and the "
"Aragwaithi."
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, no se puede culpar a los elfos de Thelien por desconfiar de los "
"forasteros, no después de todo lo que han sufrido a manos del Imperio Orco y "
"los aragwaithi."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:215
msgid "Are there Aragwaithi living in these Northlands?"
msgstr "¿Hay aragwaithi viviendo en estas Tierras del Norte?"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:219
msgid ""
"Yes, there's a people under that name living in the Frosty Wastes; they "
"arrived there a few centuries ago, but, except for trading, they maintain "
"very little contact with their neighbours. Do you know of them?"
msgstr ""
"Sí, hay un pueblo con ese nombre viviendo en las Tierras Heladas; llegaron "
"allí hace unos siglos, pero, salvo por el comercio, mantienen muy poco "
"contacto con sus vecinos. ¿Los conoces?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:223
msgid ""
"Only from scrolls. They're a very ancient people, possibly the first great "
"human nation, but they were dispersed after the First Dragon War; some went "
"northwards, to the frosty northern shores of this continent, and lived there "
"in such isolation that they shouldn't have changed much since those times."
msgstr ""
"Solo por pergaminos. Son un pueblo muy antiguo, posiblemente la primera gran "
"nación humana, pero se dispersaron después de la Primera Guerra de los "
"Dragones; algunos fueron hacia el norte, a las costas heladas del norte de "
"este continente, y vivieron allí en un aislamiento tan grande que no "
"deberían haber cambiado mucho desde entonces."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:227
msgid "Interesting... But how do you know so much about them?"
msgstr "Interesante… Pero ¿cómo sabes tanto de ellos?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:231
msgid "I... So you still haven't given up on learning my origins, have you?"
msgstr ""
"Yo… Así que todavía no has desistido de averiguar mis orígenes, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:235
msgid ""
"True, but this time I merely thought that your knowledge might earn us safe "
"passage through their lands towards Castelfrost."
msgstr ""
"Es cierto, pero esta vez solo pensé que tu conocimiento podría garantizarnos "
"un paso seguro por sus tierras hacia Castelfrost."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:239
msgid ""
"Leave that for later, now we must pay attention to our surroundings; I've "
"sensed movement amidst these trees already..."
msgstr ""
"Dejen eso para después, ahora debemos prestar atención a los alrededores; ya "
"he sentido movimiento entre estos árboles"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:258
msgid "Uh-oh, seems like we have more company than we expected..."
msgstr "Uy, parece que tenemos más compañía de la que esperábamos…"

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:268
msgid ""
"General, there's an unknown army coming from the south, led by humans! "
"Should I strike them as well?"
msgstr ""
"General, ¡hay un ejército desconocido viniendo desde el sur, liderado por "
"humanos! ¿También debo atacarlos?"

#. [message], speaker=Varyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:272
msgid ""
"If it's human-led, then it must be either from Wesnoth or from the Northern "
"Alliance, neither of which is our foe. Unless they strike you, leave them "
"be; we could benefit from their aid in this wretched battle..."
msgstr ""
"Si está liderado por humanos, entonces debe ser de Wesnoth o de la Alianza "
"del Norte, ninguno de los cuales es nuestro enemigo. A menos que os ataquen, "
"déjenlos en paz; podríamos beneficiarnos de su ayuda en esta miserable "
"batalla…"

#. [message], speaker=Thalmen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:276
msgid ""
"With a thousand nightmares, you vermin never learn, regardless of how many "
"arrows we plant into your bodies! Attack, warriors, and make sure to take no "
"survivors!"
msgstr ""
"¡Con mil pesadillas, alimañas nunca aprenden, sin importar cuántas flechas "
"les clavemos en el cuerpo! ¡Ataquen, guerreros, y asegúrense de no dejar "
"supervivientes!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:280
msgid ""
"Hold on, noble lord, I'm not your foe! I am Princess Cornelya of Metheldur, "
"daughter of Gil-Thelyon, the King-in-the-Woods, and I ask your warriors to "
"lower your bows for a moment!"
msgstr ""
"¡Esperen, noble señor, no soy su enemiga! Soy la princesa Cornelya de "
"Metheldur, hija de Gil-Thelyon, el Rey-en-el-Bosque, ¡y pido a sus guerreros "
"que bajen los arcos por un momento!"

#. [message], speaker=Thalmen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:284
msgid ""
"Are you Cornelya?! I know you from when I visited your noble father years "
"ago; I'm pleased to see that you've grown into a healthy and fair young elf, "
"but, if I may ask, why are you in the company of humans?"
msgstr ""
"¿Eres Cornelya? ¡Te conozco de cuando visité a tu noble padre hace años! Me "
"alegra ver que has crecido convertida en una joven elfa sana y hermosa, "
"pero, si me permites preguntar, ¿por qué estás en compañía de humanos?"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:288
msgid ""
"An unfortunate chain of events has forced me to follow these travellers. "
"However..."
msgstr ""
"Una desafortunada cadena de eventos me ha obligado a seguir a estos "
"viajeros. Sin embargo…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:295
msgid ""
"...now that I'm finally amidst my own again, I need not remain with them any "
"longer. I ask you to grant me asylum, Lord Thalmen, and in exchange I'll ask "
"my father to duly reward you."
msgstr ""
"…ahora que por fin estoy de nuevo entre los míos, no necesito permanecer con "
"ellos por más tiempo. Te pido que me concedas asilo, señor Thalmen, y a "
"cambio le pediré a mi padre que te recompense debidamente."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:299
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1511
msgid "What..."
msgstr "Qué…"

#. [message], speaker=Thalmen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:303
msgid ""
"You need not ask me to do that, princess; I would cease being an elf if I "
"had allowed you to remain in such unworthy company. Please, come into my "
"keep, and my shamans shall attend your every need. I promise I'll be done "
"with these invaders shortly enough."
msgstr ""
"No necesitas pedírmelo, princesa; dejaría de ser un elfo si te permitiera "
"permanecer en una compañía tan indigna. Por favor, entra en mi torreón, y "
"mis chamanes atenderán todas tus necesidades. Te prometo que acabaré con "
"estos invasores en poco tiempo."

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:307
msgid ""
"(furious) I should have known that an elf like her shouldn't be trusted...!"
msgstr ""
"(furioso) ¡Debí imaginar que no se podía confiar en una elfa como ella…!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:311
msgid ""
"(enraged) Have you forgotten your father's orders, princess? Have you "
"forgotten your oath to him?"
msgstr ""
"(furiosa) ¿Has olvidado las órdenes de tu padre, princesa? ¿Has olvidado tu "
"juramento hacia él?"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:315
msgid ""
"I forget nothing, Crimson Sorceress; not my oath to my father, nor the "
"suffering I have endured at the hands of humans."
msgstr ""
"No olvido nada, Hechicera Carmesí; ni mi juramento a mi padre, ni el "
"sufrimiento que he soportado a manos de los humanos."

#. [message], speaker=Thalmen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:319
msgid ""
"(appalled) Did you say... Is that woman in red robes the Crimson Sorceress?! "
"But she couldn't be alive, not after so many years..."
msgstr ""
"(horrorizado) ¿Has dicho…? ¿Esa mujer de túnicas rojas es la Hechicera "
"Carmesí? ¡Pero no puede estar viva, no después de tantos años…!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:323
msgid ""
"I have powers of which you can only dream of, elf. Now, you shall let me and "
"my friends pass through your forest in peace, or else I shall unleash an "
"inferno that will make the last one look like a festival bonfire!"
msgstr ""
"Tengo poderes de los que solo puedes soñar, elfo. Ahora, me dejarás a mí y a "
"mis amigos pasar por tu bosque en paz, ¡o desataré un infierno que hará que "
"el anterior parezca una hoguera de festival!"

#. [message], speaker=Thalmen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:327
msgid ""
"As if I'd let this opportunity to punish the one who nearly destroyed our "
"forest slip by! Warriors, our priorities have changed: send in every single "
"elf to battle!"
msgstr ""
"¡Como si fuera a dejar pasar esta oportunidad de castigar a la que casi "
"destruyó nuestro bosque! ¡Guerreros, nuestras prioridades han cambiado: "
"envíen a todos los elfos al combate!"

#. [message], speaker=Rurk
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:331
msgid ""
"Damn those elves, they've started getting serious! Very well, so shall we: "
"call in the reserves!"
msgstr ""
"¡Malditos elfos, han empezado a ponerse serios! Muy bien, nosotros también: "
"¡llamen a las reservas!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:335
msgid "Valerya, what is going on here...?"
msgstr "Valerya, ¿qué está pasando aquí…?"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:339
msgid ""
"I've just told you that I've once lost a dear friend here; this friend was "
"actually my husband..."
msgstr ""
"Acabo de decirte que perdí a un querido amigo aquí; ese amigo era en "
"realidad mi esposo…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:343
msgid ""
"I don't want to go into details and relive those moments, but know one "
"thing: I did not let his death go unavenged. Now, let's open our way through "
"this forest by force!"
msgstr ""
"No quiero entrar en detalles ni revivir esos momentos, pero que sepan una "
"cosa: no dejé su muerte sin venganza. ¡Ahora, abramos paso a través de este "
"bosque por la fuerza!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:347
msgid ""
"We must kill the elf lord first, he won't stop harassing us until we're "
"dead. Also, by killing him we may earn favour from the Aragwaithi."
msgstr ""
"Debemos matar primero al señor elfo, no dejará de acosarnos hasta que "
"estemos muertos. Además, al matarlo podríamos ganarnos el favor de los "
"aragwaithi."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:351
msgid "By the Gods of Light, this will be a slaughter..."
msgstr "Por los Dioses de la Luz, esto va a ser una masacre…"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:374
msgid "Defeat Lord Thalmen"
msgstr "Derrotar al señor Thalmen"

#. [message], speaker=Thalmen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:423
msgid "Argh...! Someone... warn... our... kin..."
msgstr "¡Argh…! ¡Que alguien… avise… a nuestros… parientes…!"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:435
msgid "Now, we only have to kill the orc chief..."
msgstr "Ahora solo tenemos que matar al jefe orco…"

#. [message], speaker=Rurk
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:439
msgid ""
"Ha! The humans have spared us some effort by killing the tree-hugging chief, "
"but we still have to wipe them all out before..."
msgstr ""
"¡Ja! Los humanos nos han ahorrado algo de esfuerzo al matar al jefe abraza-"
"árboles, pero todavía tenemos que acabar con todos ellos antes de…"

#. [message], speaker=Rurk
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:453
msgid "Gaahhh!!!"
msgstr "¡Gaaahhh!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:457
msgid ""
"And thus dies another would-be orcish sovereign. (to friends) Let the "
"remaining orcs and elves fight each other and take this chance to flee!"
msgstr ""
"Y así muere otro aspirante a soberano orco. (a los amigos) Dejen que los "
"orcos y elfos restantes se enfrenten entre sí y aprovechen esta oportunidad "
"para huir."

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:461
msgid "Wait, but hadn't you..."
msgstr "Espera, pero no habías…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:465
msgid ""
"I told you already, I won't be banished from my home because of stupid "
"humans! I wanted to sneak into the orcish camp and slay their chief, but I "
"wouldn't be able to move freely through the woods with other elves targeting "
"me! And besides, my stomach aches at the very idea of killing elves on the "
"behalf of humans."
msgstr ""
"Ya te lo dije, ¡no voy a ser desterrada de mi hogar por culpa de estúpidos "
"humanos! Quería infiltrarme en el campamento orco y matar a su jefe, ¡pero "
"no podría moverme libremente por el bosque si otros elfos me tuvieran como "
"blanco! Además, me revuelve el estómago la sola idea de matar elfos en "
"nombre de humanos."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:469
msgid "Well, we'll talk later... Valerya, hurry, we have to leave!"
msgstr "Bueno, hablaremos después… Valerya, date prisa, ¡tenemos que irnos!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:473
msgid "I-I...! All right, I'm going..."
msgstr "Yo-yo… ¡De acuerdo, voy…!"

#. [message], speaker=Varyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:590
msgid ""
"It's curious how a common threat paves the way for the unlikeliest of "
"alliances; to think that Wesnoth and the Northern Alliance would unite... I "
"understand you, though; we Aragwaithi are keenly aware of Aelvar's threat. "
"Now that we know the Northlands are uniting against him, and that the elves "
"who kept attacking our farms are broken, we wish to join your alliance "
"against the Iron Giant."
msgstr ""
"Es curioso cómo una amenaza común allana el camino para las alianzas más "
"improbables; pensar que Wesnoth y la Alianza del Norte se unirían… Sin "
"embargo, los entiendo; nosotros los aragwaithi somos muy conscientes de la "
"amenaza de Aelvar. Ahora que sabemos que las Tierras del Norte se están "
"uniendo contra él, y que los elfos que seguían atacando nuestras granjas "
"están quebrados, deseamos unirnos a su alianza contra el Gigante de Hierro."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:594
msgid ""
"And I, as the Prince of Wesnoth, declare that our banners shall march "
"together from now on. However, we're on a mission that might bring an early "
"end to this war; we're going for Aelvar's own fortress, Castelfrost. We "
"could reach it even sooner than expected if you allow us to cross the Frosty "
"Wastes..."
msgstr ""
"Y yo, como Príncipe de Wesnoth, declaro que nuestros estandartes marcharán "
"juntos desde ahora. Sin embargo, estamos en una misión que podría poner fin "
"prematuro a esta guerra; vamos por la propia fortaleza de Aelvar, "
"Castelfrost. Podríamos llegar incluso antes de lo esperado si nos permiten "
"cruzar las Tierras Heladas"

#. [message], speaker=Varyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:598
msgid ""
"And you shall not only have my permission for that, but also my aid: if you "
"need any reinforcement to destroy Castelfrost, just send a sign, like a "
"fireball from your fire mage, and my army shall come to your aid."
msgstr ""
"Y no solo tendrán mi permiso para eso, sino también mi ayuda: si necesitan "
"refuerzos para destruir Castelfrost, solo envíen una señal, como una bola de "
"fuego de su mago de fuego, y mi ejército acudirá en su ayuda."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:602
msgid "Speaking of which, where is Valerya?"
msgstr "A propósito, ¿dónde está Valerya?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:606
msgid "I saw her going into the trees, I'll check up on her..."
msgstr "La vi meterse entre los árboles, voy a ver cómo está…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:613
msgid ""
"(smiling faintly) So now you can understand why Gil-Thelyon referred to me "
"as the 'feared Crimson Sorceress'... (sigh) I've never liked fighting, but "
"travelling throughout this world will inevitably force you to it; I used to "
"cheat myself, saying that I was only defending myself, when, in fact, most "
"of the time I was actually the one getting in others' way... And when "
"Hadryan died, I couldn't control myself, I... I became like those drakes we "
"saw in the Kehshakaar, burning and tearing everyone, reducing everything to "
"ashes..."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo débilmente) Así que ahora entienden por qué Gil-Thelyon se "
"refería a mí como la «temida Hechicera Carmesí»… (suspiro) Nunca me ha "
"gustado luchar, pero viajar por este mundo inevitablemente te obliga a "
"hacerlo; solía engañarme diciendo que solo me defendía, cuando en realidad "
"la mayoría de las veces era yo quien se metía en el camino de los demás… Y "
"cuando Hadryan murió, no pude controlarme, yo… me convertí en como esos "
"dracos que vimos en Kehshakaar, quemando y desgarrando a todos, reduciendo "
"todo a cenizas…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:617
msgid ""
"Shhh, Valerya, don't be so hard on yourself. As you've just said yourself, "
"this isn't a kind world that we live in; so long as you're not the one "
"attacking others without provocation, you're not wrong to defend yourself. "
"I'm young, but I've come across some really nasty people, so I can tell "
"you're as far from being a monster as it gets. That you grieve so much for "
"hurting even your enemies should prove that. Now, vaporise these tears off "
"your face and come back to us, I won't be left dealing with those bores and "
"that annoying princess by myself!"
msgstr ""
"Shhh, Valerya, no seas tan dura contigo misma. Como tú misma acabas de "
"decir, este no es un mundo amable en el que vivimos; mientras no seas tú "
"quien ataque a los demás sin provocación, no está mal que te defiendas. Soy "
"joven, pero me he topado con gente realmente despreciable, así que puedo "
"decir que estás lo más lejos posible de ser un monstruo. Que sientas tanto "
"dolor incluso por haber herido a tus enemigos debería demostrarlo. Ahora, "
"evapora esas lágrimas de tu cara y vuelve con nosotros, ¡no voy a quedarme "
"lidiando sola con esos aburridos y esa princesa molesta!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:621
msgid ""
"So... You're not afraid of me? I could seriously burn you and the others if "
"I go out of control like I almost did back there!"
msgstr ""
"Entonces… ¿no me tienes miedo? ¡Podría quemarte seriamente a ti y a los "
"demás si pierdo el control como casi lo hice allá atrás!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:625
msgid ""
"You ever go off spewing fire like mad, I'm throwing all my water elementals "
"on you until you calm yourself."
msgstr ""
"Si alguna vez empiezas a escupir fuego como loca, voy a lanzarte todos mis "
"elementales de agua hasta que te calmes."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:629
msgid ""
"(smiling) You darling lassie... Fine, then, I'm not leaving you to those "
"boring guys – and besides, someone has to keep our princess in line, right?"
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Pequeña encantadora… Está bien entonces, no voy a dejarte con "
"esos tipos aburridos… y además, alguien tiene que mantener a nuestra "
"princesa a raya, ¿no?"

#. [message], speaker=Thalmen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:646
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:1014
msgid ""
"At last the reinforcements from our kin have arrived! Unleash an arrow-storm "
"upon these unworthy invaders, and leave none alive!"
msgstr ""
"¡Por fin han llegado los refuerzos de nuestros parientes! ¡Desaten una "
"tormenta de flechas sobre estos invasores indignos y no dejen a ninguno con "
"vida!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/22_Memories.cfg:650
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:1018
msgid ""
"Damn, we can't fight so many enemies at once! We're in serious trouble "
"now...!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldición, no podemos pelear contra tantos enemigos a la vez! ¡Ahora "
"estamos en serios problemas…!"

#. [scenario], id=23_Frosty_Shores
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:5
msgid "Frosty Shores"
msgstr "Costas Heladas"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:26
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:573
msgid "Storm Castelfrost and capture Aelvar"
msgstr "Asaltar Castelfrost y capturar a Aelvar"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:30
msgid "Lead Olokun to the sea (35,14) and keep him there for 5 turns"
msgstr ""
"Llevar a Olokun hasta el mar (35,14) y mantenerlo allí durante 5 turnos"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:66
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:609
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:769
msgid ""
"You may summon Aragwaithi reinforcements by right-click on Valerya. Know the "
"right time to summon them, though, as the enemy's outposts will send out "
"soldiers whenever it sights a foe!"
msgstr ""
"Puedes invocar refuerzos aragwaithi haciendo clic derecho en Valerya. Sin "
"embargo, escoge bien el momento de invocarlos, ¡porque los puestos avanzados "
"del enemigo enviarán soldados cada vez que detecten a un enemigo!"

#. [side], type=General
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:93
msgid "General Doneryl"
msgstr "General Doneryl"

#. [side]
#. [side], type=Master at Arms
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:120
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:142
msgid "Castelfrost's Outposts"
msgstr "Puestos avanzados de Castelfrost"

#. [side], type=Master at Arms
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:137
msgid "Admiral Raylyn"
msgstr "Almirante Raylyn"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:159
msgid "Merfolk"
msgstr "Sirénidos"

#. [unit], id=Vaenvan, type=General
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:260
msgid "General Vaenvan"
msgstr "General Vaenvan"

#. [unit], id=Blurryn, type=Iron Mauler
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:270
msgid "Captain Blurryn"
msgstr "Capitán Blurryn"

#. [unit], id=Rhaddan, type=Cavalier
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:280
msgid "Lord Rhaddan"
msgstr "Señor Rhaddan"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:295
msgid ""
"Brrrrrrr... What the hell is wrong with this Far North, how can a place be "
"so freezing cold?! Even my fire spirits are trembling!"
msgstr ""
"¡Brrrrrrr…! ¿Qué demonios le pasa a este Lejano Norte, cómo puede un lugar "
"estar tan helado?! ¡Hasta mis espíritus de fuego están temblando!"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:299
msgid ""
"Shhh, Tenma, don't speak so loud! In this open plain, even the slightest "
"noise echoes like crazy!"
msgstr ""
"¡Shhh, Tenma, no hables tan alto! ¡En esta llanura abierta, hasta el ruido "
"más leve retumba como loco!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:303
msgid ""
"Everyone, please listen: Castelfrost lies to the southwest, in a small inlet "
"which is heavily guarded by land, and even more by sea, which is rife with "
"warships; furthermore, there are smaller outposts all over the region. If "
"we're caught by those before getting near the fortress, even if we do manage "
"to take it Aelvar will have had enough time to escape."
msgstr ""
"Todos, por favor escuchen: Castelfrost está al suroeste, en una pequeña "
"ensenada que está fuertemente vigilada por tierra, y aún más por mar, "
"plagado de buques de guerra; además, hay puestos avanzados más pequeños por "
"toda la región. Si nos atrapan esos puestos antes de acercarnos a la "
"fortaleza, aunque lográramos tomarla, Aelvar habría tenido tiempo suficiente "
"para escapar."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:307
msgid "What do you propose, then?"
msgstr "¿Qué propones entonces?"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:311
msgid ""
"A lightning attack by land, sea and air with all we've got; thus we should "
"be able to catch them off guard and capture or kill Aelvar before he can "
"escape."
msgstr ""
"Un ataque relámpago por tierra, mar y aire con todo lo que tenemos; así "
"deberíamos poder tomarlos por sorpresa y capturar o matar a Aelvar antes de "
"que pueda escapar."

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:315
msgid ""
"Never thought I'd say that, but I like your plan – even if I still can't "
"brush off the feeling that you're jus' trying to get us all killed..."
msgstr ""
"Nunca pensé que diría esto, pero me gusta tu plan… aunque todavía no puedo "
"quitarme la sensación de que solo estás intentando matarnos a todos"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:319
msgid ""
"Attacking from the sea... It's been so long since I've last been near the "
"sea that I almost forgot about that... Folks, I'll go to the beach for a "
"while, I'll catch up with you later..."
msgstr ""
"Atacar desde el mar… Ha pasado tanto tiempo desde la última vez que estuve "
"cerca del mar que casi lo había olvidado… Gente, voy a la playa un rato, los "
"alcanzo después…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:323
msgid ""
"Erm, I know you love the sea and all, but don't you think this is a rather "
"inappropriate time for sightseeing?"
msgstr ""
"Ejem, sé que te encanta el mar y todo eso, pero ¿no crees que este es un "
"momento bastante inapropiado para hacer turismo?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:327
msgid ""
"Evidently I'm not going for sightseeing; I just have a plan that may make it "
"easier for us to take Castelfrost..."
msgstr ""
"Evidentemente no voy a hacer turismo; solo tengo un plan que podría "
"facilitarnos tomar Castelfrost…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:331
msgid "Got it. Come on, everyone, we have no time to waste."
msgstr "Entendido. Vamos, todos, no tenemos tiempo que perder."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:353
msgid ""
"(seizes Valerya) And don't you dare get away from me, I'll freeze to death "
"if you leave me alone..."
msgstr ""
"(agarra a Valerya) Y ni se te ocurra alejarte de mí, ¡me voy a congelar "
"hasta la muerte si me dejas sola…!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:357
msgid ""
"(smiling) Aawww, come to me, child, I'll keep you warm – and you too, "
"blondie, we can't let even you suffer in this cold."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Awww, ven aquí, pequeña, te mantendré calentita… y a ti también, "
"rubiecito, no podemos dejar que ni siquiera tú sufras con este frío."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:361
msgid "No, thanks, this weather does not faze me in the slightest."
msgstr "No, gracias, este clima no me afecta en lo más mínimo."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:365
msgid "Fine, but I was talking to Kenshiro, not you."
msgstr "Está bien, pero le hablaba a Kenshiro, no a ti."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:369
msgid "(laughing) Ha! Take that, little princess!"
msgstr "(riendo) ¡Ja! ¡Toma eso, pequeña princesa!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:373
msgid "(stung) Tsc!"
msgstr "(picada) ¡Tsc!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:398
msgid ""
"Well then, Oceanstar, let us see whether your amulet actually works... "
"(throws a jewel into the sea)"
msgstr ""
"Bien entonces, Estrella del Océano, veamos si tu amuleto realmente funciona… "
"(lanza una joya al mar)"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:402
msgid "Will you bother explaining what that was for?"
msgstr "¿Te molestarías en explicar para qué fue eso?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:409
msgid ""
"Just wait and see; if that amulet really works, we'll have a new ally soon "
"enough..."
msgstr ""
"Solo espera y verás; si ese amuleto realmente funciona, tendremos un nuevo "
"aliado muy pronto…"

#. [unit], id=Leukothea, type=Mermaid Diviner
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:481
msgid "Leukothea"
msgstr "Leucotea"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:505
msgid "Olokun, watch out!"
msgstr "¡Olokun, cuidado!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:509
msgid ""
"Don't worry, I expected her to appear... I'm relieved that your master's "
"amulet truly works, Leukothea."
msgstr ""
"No te preocupes, esperaba que apareciera… Me alivia que el amuleto de tu ama "
"realmente funcione, Leucotea."

#. [message], speaker=Leukothea
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:513
msgid ""
"And you, of all people, should have doubted neither her power nor her words. "
"That's why I keep telling her not to trust or dedicate herself so much to a "
"human, but unfortunately she'll give me no heed..."
msgstr ""
"Y tú, precisamente tú, no deberías haber dudado ni de su poder ni de sus "
"palabras. Por eso sigo diciéndole que no confíe ni se dedique tanto a un "
"humano, pero desgraciadamente no me hace caso…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:517
msgid ""
"I didn't doubt her, I just thought that amulet might have lost power after "
"all this time... But I digress. Has she come alone with you?"
msgstr ""
"No dudé de ella, solo pensé que el amuleto podría haber perdido poder "
"después de tanto tiempo… Pero me desvío. ¿Vino ella sola contigo?"

#. [message], speaker=Leukothea
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:521
msgid ""
"(tiredly) She's brought the finest Thunder Warriors from the Ocean's Heart, "
"fearing that you might be in grave danger..."
msgstr ""
"(cansada) Trajo a los mejores Guerreros del Trueno del Corazón del Océano, "
"temiendo que pudieras estar en grave peligro"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:525
msgid ""
"Then tell her this: my friends and I are attempting to conquer the fortress "
"of Aelvar, a Wesnothian prince who seeks to carve out a new expansionistic "
"empire for himself. He has many warships in the sea nearby; I ask her to "
"deal with them while we storm the fortress from land."
msgstr ""
"Entonces dile esto: mis amigos y yo estamos intentando conquistar la "
"fortaleza de Aelvar, un príncipe wesnothiano que busca forjarse un nuevo "
"imperio expansionista para sí mismo. Tiene muchos buques de guerra en el mar "
"cercano; le pido que se ocupe de ellos mientras nosotros asaltamos la "
"fortaleza desde tierra."

#. [message], speaker=Leukothea
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:529
msgid "And? What do you have to offer in exchange?"
msgstr "¿Y? ¿Qué ofreces a cambio?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:533
msgid ""
"(sigh) I'll go meet her, and spend as much time with her as she wants, would "
"that be enough?"
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) Iré a verla y pasaré con ella todo el tiempo que ella quiera, "
"¿sería suficiente?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:541
msgid ""
"(annoyed) Have it your way then, I will... (whispers something at the "
"mermaid's ear)"
msgstr ""
"(molesto) Hazlo a tu manera entonces, lo haré… (susurra algo al oído de la "
"sirena)"

#. [message], speaker=Leukothea
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:545
msgid ""
"(blushing) ...! I, er, I'm going, then... Go on and attack that fortress, "
"that your enemy's ships won't be able to go to its aid."
msgstr ""
"(sonrojada) …¡! Yo, eh, me voy entonces… Adelante, ataquen esa fortaleza, "
"para que los barcos de su enemigo no puedan ir en su ayuda."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:552
msgid ""
"So you have merfolk friends? That's quite impressive, they don't easily "
"befriend humans..."
msgstr ""
"¿Entonces tienes amigas sirénidas? Eso es bastante impresionante, no se "
"hacen amigas de humanos fácilmente…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:556
msgid ""
"More importantly, what did you offer that fish-girl's master that made her "
"scales go purple?"
msgstr ""
"Más importante aún, ¿qué le ofreciste a la ama de esa chica-pez que le hizo "
"ponerse las escamas moradas?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:560
msgid "Never mind, you'll probably understand everything soon enough anyway..."
msgstr "No importa, probablemente entenderás todo pronto de todos modos…"

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:659
msgid "Grim Gods, what the hell is going on here?!"
msgstr "¡Dioses sombríos, ¿qué demonios está pasando aquí?!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:663
msgid ""
"I am Prince Aetheryon of Wesnoth, and in the name of Emperor Taryen the "
"First I have come to deliver Imperial justice upon the Betrayer! And you, "
"Aelvar, why don't you show up? I have new 'magic tricks' for you, let us "
"measure them against your so-called invincible armour!"
msgstr ""
"¡Soy el príncipe Aetheryon de Wesnoth, y en nombre del emperador Taryen "
"Primero he venido a impartir justicia imperial sobre el Traidor! ¡Y tú, "
"Aelvar, por qué no apareces! Tengo nuevos «trucos mágicos» para ti, ¡veamos "
"cómo se miden contra tu supuesta armadura invencible!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:667
msgid ""
"And so it all comes down to a rivalry between eldest and youngest brothers..."
msgstr ""
"Y así todo se reduce a una rivalidad entre el hermano mayor y el menor…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:671
msgid ""
"Yeah, I bet Aetheryon suffered quite a bully at the hands of this Aelvar..."
msgstr ""
"Sí, apuesto a que Aetheryon sufrió bastante acoso por parte de este Aelvar…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:675
msgid "(annoyed) Shut up, you...!"
msgstr "(molesto) ¡Cállate, tú…!"

#. [message], speaker=Doneryl
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:679
msgid ""
"We must not let this fortress fall, soldiers, not when Lord Aelvar has "
"entrusted it to our care! Send word to the outer sentries not to spare any "
"troop, I want every single soldier fighting the invaders!"
msgstr ""
"¡No debemos permitir que esta fortaleza caiga, soldados, no cuando el señor "
"Aelvar la ha confiado a nuestro cuidado! ¡Envíen palabra a los centinelas "
"exteriores de que no perdonen a ninguna tropa, quiero a cada soldado "
"luchando contra los invasores!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:690
msgid ""
"Maybe this would be a good time to call for the Aragwaithi reinforcements..."
msgstr ""
"Tal vez este sería un buen momento para pedir refuerzos a los aragwaithi..."

#. [message], speaker=Raylyn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:707
msgid ""
"With a thousand curses, where did so many fish-people appear?! And why do "
"they all have magic tridents?!"
msgstr ""
"¡Con mil maldiciones, de dónde salieron tantos hombres-pez?! ¡¿Y por qué "
"todos tienen tridentes mágicos?!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:719
msgid ""
"Is that the one northerners call the 'Iron Giant'? He looks quite puny to "
"me..."
msgstr ""
"¿Ese es el que los norteños llaman el «Gigante de Hierro»? A mí me parece "
"bastante enclenque..."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:723
msgid ""
"That's not Aelvar! What must have happened to him? He never lets a general "
"fight in his stead, not unless he..."
msgstr ""
"¡Ese no es Aelvar! ¿Qué le habrá pasado? Nunca deja que un general luche en "
"su lugar, a menos que él..."

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:727
msgid ""
"...is not there to fight in person, right? I got a bad feeling about that... "
"But let's not worry about that now; what matters is that he left his "
"fortress weakened. Let's raze it to the ground and end his control of the "
"Utmost North!"
msgstr ""
"…no está ahí para luchar en persona, ¿verdad? Tengo un mal presentimiento "
"con eso… Pero no nos preocupemos por eso ahora; lo importante es que dejó su "
"fortaleza debilitada. ¡Arrasémosla hasta los cimientos y acabemos con su "
"control del Extremo Norte!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:733
msgid "Kill General Doneryl and the Outpost Commanders"
msgstr "Matar al general Doneryl y a los comandantes de los puestos avanzados"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:789
msgid ""
"Hey, Olokun, Valerya... Are you sensing the same thing as me...? An insanely "
"intense power drawing nearer and nearer..."
msgstr ""
"Oye, Olokun, Valerya… ¿Están sintiendo lo mismo que yo…? Un poder "
"insanamente intenso que se acerca cada vez más…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:793
msgid "(sigh) Calm down, that's nothing dangerous, it's just <i>her</i>..."
msgstr "(suspiro) Tranquila, no es nada peligroso, es solo <i>ella</i>…"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:811
msgid ""
"(hugging Olokun) Olokunnnn my dearest!!! So glad you're in one piece after "
"crossing this brutal continent... and so glad that you really called me, I "
"knew you would miss me almost as much as I missed you!"
msgstr ""
"(abrazando a Olokun) ¡¡Olokunnnn mi querido!!! ¡Qué alegría verte entero "
"después de cruzar este continente brutal… y qué alegría que realmente me "
"llamaste, sabía que me extrañarías casi tanto como yo a ti!"

#. [message], speaker=Leukothea
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:815
msgid "Actually he only called you when he needed your aid..."
msgstr "En realidad solo te llamó cuando necesitaba tu ayuda…"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:819
msgid ""
"Silence, o killjoy priestess! That he hurled himself against such a danger "
"knowing that I would come for him means that he trusts me with his life!"
msgstr ""
"¡Silencio, sacerdotisa aguafiestas! Que se lanzara contra semejante peligro "
"sabiendo que yo vendría por él significa que confía en mí con su vida!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:823
msgid "Whoa..."
msgstr "Vaya…"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:827
msgid ""
"Um, so you are the companions Olokun found in his travels, I see... I am "
"Derceto Stella Maris, Guardian of the Ocean's Heart and of the Merfolk's "
"Lore, called Oceanstar by my people; allow me to thank you for keeping my "
"dearest safe, we merfolk know, from the seafarers' tales, how terrible the "
"Great Continent is..."
msgstr ""
"Emm, entonces ustedes son los compañeros que Olokun encontró en sus viajes, "
"ya veo… Soy Derceto Stella Maris, Guardiana del Corazón del Océano y del "
"Saber de los Sirenidos, llamada Estrella Marina por mi pueblo; permítanme "
"agradecerles por mantener a salvo a mi querido, nosotros los sirenidos "
"sabemos, por los relatos de los marineros, lo terrible que es el Gran "
"Continente…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:831
msgid "Ah, er, well..."
msgstr "Ah, eh, bueno…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:835
msgid "Feeling overwhelmed by her... exuberance, aren't you, shrimp?"
msgstr "¿Te sientes abrumada por su… exuberancia, verdad, camarón?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:839
msgid "(blushing) You prissy elf, I'll make you-!"
msgstr "(sonrojada) ¡Elfa presumida, te voy a…!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:843
msgid ""
"Girls, behave yourselves! It's an honour to meet you, Oceanstar; I've heard "
"tales about your lineage from the people of Myra of Hiera'Shirsha, who was "
"once a friend of the naiad Atargatis."
msgstr ""
"¡Chicas, compórtense! Es un honor conocerla, Estrella Marina; he escuchado "
"historias sobre su linaje de parte de la gente de Myra de Hiera’Shirsha, "
"quien alguna vez fue amiga de la náyade Atargatis."

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:847
msgid ""
"Interesting, never would I have thought that a dweller of this continent "
"would know all these things... Nor that one such dweller would have such an "
"interesting power within herself – a power that is akin to the one that can "
"still be felt in the Underwater Temple..."
msgstr ""
"Interesante, nunca habría pensado que una habitante de este continente "
"sabría todas estas cosas… Ni que una habitante así tuviera un poder tan "
"interesante dentro de sí, un poder parecido al que todavía se puede sentir "
"en el Templo Submarino…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:851
msgid ""
"You know, according to your beloved, she's the reincarnation of some human "
"heroine called Myra of Hiera'Shirsha..."
msgstr ""
"Sabes, según tu querido, ella es la reencarnación de cierta heroína humana "
"llamada Myra de Hiera’Shirsha…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:855
msgid ""
"(annoyed) Cornelya, you sure have no restraint about being an ultimate jerk, "
"don't you? You know I hate it when people talk about that..."
msgstr ""
"(molesta) Cornelya, realmente no tienes ningún freno para ser una completa "
"idiota, ¿verdad? Sabes que odio cuando la gente habla de eso…"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:859
msgid ""
"(smiling) Yes, elven princess, I have noticed that. It's a long story, one "
"that deserves to be told in a calmer moment – though I could tell it to you "
"at any time, dearest... Let me ask you, I heard something from Leukothea a "
"while ago, was that true...?"
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Sí, princesa élfica, me he dado cuenta. Es una historia larga, "
"una que merece ser contada en un momento más tranquilo… aunque podría "
"contártela en cualquier momento, querida… Déjame preguntarte, escuché algo "
"de Leukothea hace un rato, ¿era cierto…?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:863
msgid "(blushing) Well, I did promise that, did I not?"
msgstr "(sonrojado) Bueno, sí lo prometí, ¿no es así?"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:872
msgid ""
"(panting) Friends, I... (looks at Derceto and Olokun) Well, leaving that "
"aside... I have found the reason Aelvar has left Castelfrost – and also his "
"true plans: he's going to invade Knalga..."
msgstr ""
"(jadeando) Amigos, yo… (mira a Derceto y Olokun) Bueno, dejando eso de lado… "
"He descubierto la razón por la que Aelvar dejó Castelfrost… y también sus "
"verdaderos planes: va a invadir Knalga…"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:876
msgid "And you needed run across his fortress to discover..."
msgstr "¿Y tuviste que correr por toda su fortaleza para descubrirlo…?"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:880
msgid ""
"That's not all! The true reason he wants to conquer Knalga is not for its "
"wealth, he seeks the Hammer of Thursagan itself!"
msgstr ""
"¡Eso no es todo! La verdadera razón por la que quiere conquistar Knalga no "
"es por su riqueza, ¡busca el Martillo de Thursagan en sí mismo!"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:884
msgid ""
"(shocked) What? That damn warmonger, how dare he even dream of laying his "
"filthy hands on that relic?!"
msgstr ""
"(impactado) ¿Qué? ¡Ese maldito belicista, cómo se atreve siquiera a soñar "
"con poner sus sucias manos en esa reliquia?!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:888
msgid "But why exactly does he seek it? Does he want to craft runes or what?"
msgstr "Pero ¿por qué exactamente la busca? ¿Quiere fabricar runas o qué?"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:892
msgid ""
"I have found some journals written by him; it seems that he was researching "
"about some relics of great power, which he referred to as 'the Kings' "
"Regalia'..."
msgstr ""
"He encontrado algunos diarios escritos por él; parece que estaba "
"investigando sobre ciertas reliquias de gran poder, a las que se refería "
"como «el Regalia de los Reyes»…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:896
msgid ""
"(looking distraught) He's searching for the Regalia...? (recomposing) Well, "
"I must confess that the prospect of a human collecting those items sours my "
"wine, unthinkable as it is that he could ever seize them all..."
msgstr ""
"(con aspecto perturbado) ¿Está buscando el Regalia…? (reponiéndose) Bueno, "
"debo confesar que la idea de que un humano recolecte esos objetos me agria "
"el vino, por impensable que sea que alguna vez pueda hacerse con todos…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:900
msgid "Do you know what they are, Cornelya?"
msgstr "¿Sabes qué son, Cornelya?"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:904
msgid ""
"Yes, it's a well-known tale amongst Metheldur's wisest, and my father's "
"favourite story; don't ask me about it any further, I don't feel like "
"telling such a long legend..."
msgstr ""
"Sí, es un cuento muy conocido entre los más sabios de Metheldur, y la "
"historia favorita de mi padre; no me preguntes más al respecto, no tengo "
"ganas de contar una leyenda tan larga…"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:908
msgid ""
"I, for one, enjoy telling stories, and I know that one in particular... But, "
"first, time for my reward, dearest..."
msgstr ""
"Yo, por mi parte, disfruto contando historias, y conozco esa en particular… "
"Pero primero, hora de mi recompensa, querido…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:912
msgid ""
"Fine... Now that we've secured this whole region, we should be able to rest "
"for a day at this fortress; the depths of Knalga will surely present many "
"more challenges than the Hammermounts, so we must be ready for them..."
msgstr ""
"Está bien… Ahora que hemos asegurado toda esta región, deberíamos poder "
"descansar un día en esta fortaleza; las profundidades de Knalga seguro que "
"presentarán muchos más desafíos que las Montañas del Martillo, así que "
"debemos estar preparados para ellos…"

#. [message], speaker=Doneryl
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:950
msgid "Lord Aelvar... forgive..."
msgstr "Señor Aelvar… perdone…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:968
msgid ""
"Damn it, he had to stay alive long enough for us to interrogate him... But "
"it might be possible that we can find hints to Aelvar's plans in his "
"fortress. I'll go into Castelfrost to search for them, but first we must "
"deal with the sentry guards; with the Aragwaithi and the merfolk on our "
"side, we're capable of cleaning this whole region."
msgstr ""
"Maldición, tenía que seguir vivo lo suficiente para interrogarlo… Pero tal "
"vez sea posible encontrar pistas de los planes de Aelvar en su fortaleza. "
"Iré a Castelfrost a buscarlas, pero primero debemos encargarnos de los "
"guardias centinelas; con los aragwaithi y los sirenidos de nuestro lado, "
"somos capaces de limpiar toda esta región."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:974
msgid ""
"Damn it, he had to stay alive long enough for us to interrogate him... But "
"it might be possible that we can find hints to Aelvar's plans in his "
"fortress. I'll go into Castelfrost to search for them; please, wait for me..."
msgstr ""
"Maldición, tenía que seguir vivo lo suficiente para interrogarlo… Pero tal "
"vez sea posible encontrar pistas de los planes de Aelvar en su fortaleza. "
"Iré a Castelfrost a buscarlas; por favor, espérenme…"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:997
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:532
msgid "I... have fallen...?!"
msgstr "Yo… ¿he caído…?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/23_Frosty_Shores.cfg:1001
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:536
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1676
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:665
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:449
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:617
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:762
msgid "DERCETO, NO!!!"
msgstr "¡DERCETO, NO!"

#. [scenario], id=24_The_Earths_Mouth
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:5
msgid "The Earth's Mouth"
msgstr "La Boca de la Tierra"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:26
msgid "Defeat Lord Aigcathil in order to enter Knalga"
msgstr "Derrotar al señor Aigcathil para poder entrar en Knalga"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:58
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:53
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:599
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:484
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:692
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:936
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1255
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:48
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:652
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:49
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:961
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1446
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:38
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:727
msgid "Death of Derceto"
msgstr "Muerte de Derceto"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:62
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:779
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1099
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1177
msgid "Death of Tallin IV"
msgstr "Muerte de Tallin IV"

#. [side], type=Grand Marshal
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:117
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:110
msgid "Tallin IV"
msgstr "Tallin IV"

#. [side], type=Grand Marshal
#. [side]
#. [side], type=Dwarvish Arcanister
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:122
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27A_Spark_Of_Hope.cfg:49
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:115
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:144
msgid "Northern Alliance"
msgstr "Alianza del Norte"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:141
msgid "Stella Maris' Retinue"
msgstr "Séquito de Stella Maris"

#. [side], type=Orcish Sovereign
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:151
msgid "Chief Bragor"
msgstr "Jefe Bragor"

#. [side], type=Orcish Sovereign
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:156
msgid "Army of Prestim"
msgstr "Ejército de Prestim"

#. [unit], id=Vendryn, type=Necromancer
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:226
msgid "Master Vendryn"
msgstr "Maestro Vendryn"

#. [unit], id=Menvan, type=Silver Mage
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:234
msgid "Master Menvan"
msgstr "Maestro Menvan"

#. [unit], id=Tenvan, type=Silver Mage
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:242
msgid "Master Tenvan"
msgstr "Maestro Tenvan"

#. [message], speaker=Aelvar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:259
msgid ""
"Ha! Once again the Northern Alliance's best is not enough to stop us! Leave "
"our dead behind, they were weaklings weeded out of our forces; now, prepare "
"to march into the caves!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ja! ¡Una vez más lo mejor de la Alianza del Norte no es suficiente para "
"detenernos! Dejen atrás a nuestros muertos, eran débiles que hemos eliminado "
"de nuestras fuerzas; ¡ahora, prepárense para marchar a las cuevas!"

#. [message], speaker=Bragor
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:263
msgid ""
"You're late, humans! That bloody bastard and his mercenaries have smashed "
"through the beardy ones' fortifications, and now nothing stands between then "
"and Knalga!"
msgstr ""
"¡Llegan tarde, humanos! Ese maldito bastardo y sus mercenarios han "
"destrozado las fortificaciones de los barbudos, ¡y ahora nada se interpone "
"entre ellos y Knalga!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:267
msgid ""
"Not so late, though; if we defeat them quickly, we may yet be able to catch "
"up with Aelvar before he goes too deep into the mountains!"
msgstr ""
"No tan tarde, sin embargo; si los derrotamos rápido, aún podríamos alcanzar "
"a Aelvar antes de que se adentre demasiado en las montañas."

#. [message], speaker=Tallin
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:271
msgid ""
"Easier said than done, prince. See, we would have captured him already, if "
"Aigcathil wasn't protecting his rear; we've been storming his Sentinel lines "
"since this battle started, to no avail."
msgstr ""
"Más fácil decirlo que hacerlo, príncipe. Mira, ya lo habríamos capturado si "
"Aigcathil no estuviera protegiendo su retaguardia; hemos estado asaltando "
"sus líneas de centinelas desde que empezó esta batalla, sin resultado."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:275
msgid ""
"But you didn't have fire mages with you before; even the mighty dwarvish "
"sentinels can't stand against a few fireballs."
msgstr ""
"Pero antes no tenían magos de fuego con ustedes; incluso los poderosos "
"centinelas enanos no resisten unos cuantos bolas de fuego."

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:279
msgid ""
"Nor can they stand against storm tridents; though we'll be of little aid in "
"the hills, we are deadly even on flat ground."
msgstr ""
"Tampoco resisten los tridentes de tormenta; aunque seremos de poca ayuda en "
"las colinas, somos mortales incluso en terreno plano."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:283
msgid ""
"Why are there dwarves fighting for that Aelvar, though? I thought he was "
"trying to conquer their kingdom."
msgstr ""
"¿Por qué hay enanos luchando por ese Aelvar? Pensé que intentaba conquistar "
"su reino."

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:287
msgid ""
"The clan of the dwarvish lord Aigcathil is one of Wesnoth's many Foreign "
"Legions: they help the empire enforce its power on lands, terrains and "
"climates its people are not familiar with. Aigcathil was sworn to Aelvar, "
"who ruled the northern provinces, and so he's chosen to follow him in his "
"rebellion; Aigcathil has always been fond of humans, you see..."
msgstr ""
"El clan del señor enano Aigcathil es una de las muchas Legiones Extranjeras "
"de Wesnoth: ayudan al imperio a imponer su poder en tierras, terrenos y "
"climas con los que su pueblo no está familiarizado. Aigcathil juró lealtad a "
"Aelvar, quien gobernaba las provincias del norte, y por eso ha elegido "
"seguirlo en su rebelión; a Aigcathil siempre le han gustado los humanos, ya "
"ves…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:291
msgid ""
"You seem to know him very well; are you acquainted with him? You could give "
"us hints on his fighting tactics and..."
msgstr ""
"Parece que lo conoces muy bien; ¿estás relacionado con él? Podrías darnos "
"pistas sobre sus tácticas de combate y…"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:295
msgid "It's a little bit more than just acquaintance; he's my father."
msgstr "Es un poco más que solo conocido; es mi padre."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:299
msgid ""
"(surprised) But... I mean no offence, but you don't look quite dwarvish to "
"me..."
msgstr "(sorprendida) Pero… sin ofender, no te ves muy enano que digamos…"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:303
msgid ""
"He's my father, but my mother was a human from the Dwarven Doors. No time to "
"tell my life's story now, we must break through Aigcathil's defence and "
"capture Aelvar once and for all!"
msgstr ""
"Es mi padre, pero mi madre era humana de las Puertas Enanas. No hay tiempo "
"para contar la historia de mi vida ahora, ¡debemos atravesar la defensa de "
"Aigcathil y capturar a Aelvar de una vez por todas!"

#. [message], speaker=Aigcathil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:307
msgid ""
"Lord Aelvar, I'll stay here and delay them as much as I can; please, hurry "
"into Knalga before more battalions come from the caves!"
msgstr ""
"Señor Aelvar, me quedaré aquí y los retrasaré todo lo que pueda; por favor, "
"apresúrese a entrar en Knalga antes de que lleguen más batallones desde las "
"cuevas."

#. [message], speaker=Aelvar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:311
msgid ""
"Don't get yourself killed, my loyal Aigcathil; I'll need you more than ever "
"in these caves, so I allow you to flee if the enemy is too strong for you."
msgstr ""
"No te dejes matar, mi leal Aigcathil; te necesitaré más que nunca en estas "
"cuevas, así que te permito huir si el enemigo es demasiado fuerte para ti."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:345
msgid ""
"Cornelya, I remember you calling Donar a 'human dwarf'. Did you know about "
"this true identity already?"
msgstr ""
"Cornelya, recuerdo que llamaste a Donar «enano humano». ¿Ya sabías de esta "
"identidad real?"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:349
msgid ""
"Not completely; I did notice his skin looked as rough as a dwarf's, and that "
"his build is too sturdy for a human's, but I didn't think it was even "
"possible for humans and dwarves to interbreed..."
msgstr ""
"No del todo; sí noté que su piel parecía tan áspera como la de un enano y "
"que su constitución es demasiado robusta para un humano, pero no pensé que "
"fuera siquiera posible que humanos y enanos se cruzaran…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:353
msgid ""
"Not just humans and dwarves, by the way. Princess Alenya of Lintanir, who "
"followed Myra to Netjer-Ta, bore children to a dwarf."
msgstr ""
"No solo humanos y enanos, por cierto. La princesa Alenya de Lintanir, que "
"siguió a Myra hasta Netjer-Ta, tuvo hijos con un enano."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:357
msgid ""
"An elf and a dwarf...? Surely you jest; there's no way children from such "
"differing lineages could survive, or even be born."
msgstr ""
"¿Una elfa y un enano…? Seguro estás bromeando; no hay forma de que niños de "
"linajes tan diferentes puedan sobrevivir, ni siquiera nacer."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:361
msgid ""
"They were said to be as healthy and strong as any child, and their eldest, "
"Belendra, wedded Aldrik, son of Myra and a human. Their children too grew up "
"to be healthy and long-lived."
msgstr ""
"Se decía que eran tan sanos y fuertes como cualquier niño, y su hija mayor, "
"Belendra, se casó con Aldrik, hijo de Myra y un humano. Sus hijos también "
"crecieron sanos y de larga vida."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:365
msgid ""
"And I myself met a man who was the son of an elf and a human: Elemyrion, "
"once King of Wesnoth. But, of course, you can always stick to your rather "
"limited world view..."
msgstr ""
"Y yo misma conocí a un hombre que era hijo de una elfa y un humano: "
"Elemyrion, alguna vez rey de Wesnoth. Pero, claro, siempre puedes aferrarte "
"a tu visión del mundo bastante limitada…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:369
msgid ""
"Do not patronise me, Sorceress. I simply had never heard of such unions... "
"Or even cared to imagine one."
msgstr ""
"No me trates con condescendencia, hechicera. Simplemente nunca había oído "
"hablar de tales uniones… ni siquiera me había molestado en imaginar una."

#. [message], speaker=Aigcathil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:384
msgid ""
"I expected to find ye in Bitok's defence, son, as did so many other Allied "
"captains; how is yer mother faring?"
msgstr ""
"Esperaba encontrarte defendiendo Bitok, hijo, como tantos otros capitanes "
"aliados; ¿cómo está tu madre?"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:388
msgid ""
"Just like ye last saw her: gloomy, silent and sickly. My turn to ask "
"questions: how does it feel like, to be a traitor of yer own people?"
msgstr ""
" Igual que la última vez que la viste: sombría, callada y enferma. Ahora me "
"toca preguntar a mí: ¿cómo se siente ser un traidor de tu propio pueblo?"

#. [message], speaker=Aigcathil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:392
msgid ""
"My people? (chuckling) C'mon, son, ye, of all people, taking the Knalgans' "
"side? Have ye forgotten everything they've put ye through?"
msgstr ""
"¿Mi pueblo? (riendo) Vamos, hijo, ¿tú, precisamente tú, tomando partido por "
"los knalganos? ¿Has olvidado todo lo que te hicieron pasar?"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:396
msgid ""
"I haven't, I just didn't expect to see a proud dwarf lord bow and obey a "
"scoundrel like Aelvar like a lap dog."
msgstr ""
"No lo he olvidado, solo que no esperaba ver a un orgulloso señor enano "
"inclinarse y obedecer a un canalla como Aelvar como si fuera un perro "
"faldero."

#. [message], speaker=Aigcathil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:400
msgid ""
"(menacing) Mind yer words, boy! Ye have no idea of what goes in the caves "
"behind me; if ye knew, ye might as well be fighting along with me!"
msgstr ""
"(amenazante) ¡Cuida tus palabras, muchacho! No tienes idea de lo que pasa en "
"las cuevas detrás de mí; si lo supieras, ¡bien podrías estar luchando a mi "
"lado!"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:404
msgid ""
"I would never bow to one such as Aelvar, nor fight alongside a traitor such "
"as ye! Even so, though it disgusts me, I bear yer blood, so know that I'll "
"at the very least give ye a warrior's death."
msgstr ""
"¡Nunca me inclinaría ante alguien como Aelvar, ni lucharía junto a un "
"traidor como tú! Aun así, aunque me repugna, llevo tu sangre, así que sabe "
"que al menos te daré una muerte de guerrero."

#. [message], speaker=Aigcathil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:408
msgid "Ye will <i>try</i>, son..."
msgstr "Lo <i>intentarás</i>, hijo…"

#. [message], speaker=Aigcathil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:420
msgid ""
"Ugh! I wanted to stay and fight to death, but Lord Aelvar wants me by his "
"side... I will withdraw now, son, but I'll be waiting for you in the depths "
"of Knalga..."
msgstr ""
"¡Ugh! Quería quedarme y luchar hasta la muerte, pero el señor Aelvar me "
"quiere a su lado… Me retiraré ahora, hijo, pero te estaré esperando en las "
"profundidades de Knalga…"

#. [message], speaker=Tallin
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:435
msgid ""
"A shame we haven't had time to warn the Knalgans of Aelvar's invasion; "
"gryphons are hindered inside caves, and the nearest surface Knalgan outpost "
"is far from here..."
msgstr ""
"Qué lástima que no hayamos tenido tiempo de advertir a los knalganos de la "
"invasión de Aelvar; los grifos están limitados dentro de las cuevas, y el "
"puesto avanzado knalgano en superficie más cercano está muy lejos de aquí…"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:439
msgid ""
"No problem, we shall pursue them into the deepest caves if needed be, so "
"that, when they next find resistance, they'll be surrounded!"
msgstr ""
"No hay problema, los perseguiremos hasta las cuevas más profundas si es "
"necesario, ¡así que cuando encuentren resistencia la próxima vez, estarán "
"rodeados!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:443
msgid ""
"We'll follow you, then; we've fought underground before, and most "
"importantly, we can't allow Aelvar to seize a Regalia. Besides, if he was "
"able to find out about such ancient lore, it wouldn't surprise me if he knew "
"about other powers..."
msgstr ""
"Te seguiremos, entonces; ya hemos luchado bajo tierra antes, y lo más "
"importante, no podemos permitir que Aelvar se apodere de un Regalia. Además, "
"si fue capaz de enterarse de un saber tan antiguo, no me sorprendería que "
"conociera otros poderes…"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:447
msgid ""
"How cruel of you, Olokun! Forcing me to dive into caves, you know how "
"mermaids hate that environment!"
msgstr ""
"¡Qué cruel eres, Olokun! Obligarme a meterme en cuevas, ¡sabes cuánto odian "
"las sirenas ese ambiente!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:451
msgid ""
"Don't follow me, then; you can just wait for me outside, we won't be "
"underground for too long."
msgstr ""
"Entonces no me sigas; puedes esperarme afuera, no estaremos bajo tierra "
"demasiado tiempo."

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:455
msgid ""
"That is even worse! I thought you were glad that we were finally reunited, "
"but there you are, leaving me behind once again!"
msgstr ""
"¡Eso es aún peor! Pensé que estabas contento de que por fin nos reuniéramos, "
"¡pero ahí estás, dejándome atrás otra vez!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:459
msgid "I'll be back... (blushes slightly) I always am."
msgstr "Volveré… (se sonroja ligeramente) Siempre lo hago."

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:463
msgid ""
" (smiling) That much is true. Go swiftly then, dearest, or I'll flood Knalga "
"only so that I may search for you there!"
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Eso es cierto. Ve rápido entonces, querido, ¡o inundaré Knalga "
"solo para poder buscarte ahí!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:467
msgid "If you're ready, let us go into Knalga at once."
msgstr "Si están listos, entremos en Knalga de inmediato."

#. [message], speaker=Tallin
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:471
msgid ""
"I can't send soldiers with you right now, but I can help you with gold. Good "
"luck, friends; do not allow Aelvar to succeed..."
msgstr ""
"No puedo enviar soldados con ustedes ahora, pero sí puedo ayudarlos con oro. "
"Buena suerte, amigos; no permitan que Aelvar tenga éxito…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:475
msgid ""
"(in private) You complain that she's clingy and everything, but you actually "
"like that about her, don't you?"
msgstr ""
"(en privado) Te quejas de que es pegajosa y todo eso, pero en realidad te "
"gusta eso de ella, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:479
msgid "(blushing) Be silent, you..."
msgstr "(sonrojado) Cállate, tú…"

#. [message], speaker=Tallin
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:551
msgid "Ugh!..."
msgstr "¡Ugh!…"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:555
msgid ""
"No! How could we have let the Lord Protector of the Northern Alliance die?!"
msgstr ""
"¡No! ¿Cómo pudimos dejar que muriera el Señor Protector de la Alianza del "
"Norte?!"

#. [message], speaker=Bragor
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:570
msgid "Bloody hell! I died to these midgets...!"
msgstr "¡Maldita sea! ¡Morí a manos de estos enanos…!"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/24_The_Earths_Mouth.cfg:579
msgid ""
"By all Nine Hells, we're taking so long to enter Knalga that we'll enter it "
"only to see Aelvar seizing the Hammer!"
msgstr ""
"¡Por todos los Nueve Infiernos, estamos tardando tanto en entrar a Knalga "
"que entraremos solo para ver a Aelvar apoderándose del Martillo!"

#. [scenario], id=25_Common_Enemies
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:5
msgid "Common Enemies"
msgstr "Enemigos Comunes"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:25
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:339
msgid "Advance further into Knalga"
msgstr "Avanzar más adentro en Knalga"

#. [side], type=Washraja
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:87
msgid "Accalu"
msgstr "Accalu"

#. [side], type=Washraja
#. [side], type=Washraha Lightning Striker
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:92
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:173
msgid "Washrahan Mercenaries"
msgstr "Mercenarios de Washrahan"

#. [side], type=Dwarvish Arcanister
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:111
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:139
msgid "Master Thriththil"
msgstr "Maestro Thriththil"

#. [side], type=Dwarvish Arcanister
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:116
msgid "Thursaz Clan"
msgstr "Clan Thursaz"

#. [side], type=Great Troll
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:134
msgid "Ög"
msgstr "Ög"

#. [side], type=Great Troll
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:139
msgid "Knalgan Trolls"
msgstr "Trolls knalganos"

#. [side], type=Lich
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:155
msgid "Mal-Zuryn"
msgstr "Mal-Zuryn"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:219
msgid ""
"We haven't even sighted Aelvar's army yet, but his trail grows more and more "
"evident; don't lose heart, friends, we're almost reaching him!"
msgstr ""
"Aún no hemos avistado el ejército de Aelvar, pero su rastro se hace cada vez "
"más evidente; no pierdan el ánimo, amigos, ¡casi lo alcanzamos!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:223
msgid ""
"I can hear faint sounds of battle in the distance; he's probably met some "
"sturdy dwarven opposition already."
msgstr ""
"Puedo oír débiles sonidos de batalla a lo lejos; probablemente ya se topó "
"con alguna oposición enana resistente."

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:227
msgid ""
"Aye, we're entering the domains of the Thursaz, a runecrafter clan of which "
"my half-brother is a member; Aelvar surely will try to steal some knowledge "
"on Thursagan's Hammer from them."
msgstr ""
"Sí, estamos entrando en los dominios de los Thursaz, un clan de forjadores "
"de runas del que mi medio hermano es miembro; seguro que Aelvar intentará "
"robarles algún conocimiento sobre el Martillo de Thursagan."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:231
msgid ""
"And so we've got no second to waste – but we must be careful too. It's been "
"a while, but these northern caves used to be plagued with undead."
msgstr ""
"Y por eso no tenemos ni un segundo que perder… pero también debemos ser "
"cuidadosos. Ha pasado un tiempo, pero estas cuevas del norte solían estar "
"plagadas de no-muertos."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:249
msgid ""
"Watch out, everyone; from here onwards, I see signs of very violent "
"fighting..."
msgstr "Cuidado todos; a partir de aquí veo señales de combates muy violentos…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:253
msgid ""
"Search for survivors, please. I sense something here, a faint presence of "
"life..."
msgstr ""
"Busquen sobrevivientes, por favor. Siento algo aquí, una tenue presencia de "
"vida…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:278
msgid "There!"
msgstr "¡Allí!"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:282
msgid "Wait... Algil, is that you?!"
msgstr "Espera… ¿Algil, eres tú?!"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:286
msgid "(grumbles something unintelligible)"
msgstr "(refunfuña algo ininteligible)"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:290
msgid "Stand aside, I will tend him..."
msgstr "Apártense, yo lo atenderé…"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:305
msgid ""
"(coughing) Donar... Ye damn mongrel, ye late again... That cursed Wesnothian "
"has broken through my defences... And entered the main caves... What a fool, "
"he wants to take all of Knalga by himself..."
msgstr ""
"(tos) Donar… maldito mestizo, llegas tarde otra vez… Ese maldito wesnothiano "
"ha atravesado mis defensas… y ha entrado en las cuevas principales… Qué "
"idiota, quiere tomar todo Knalga él solo…"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:309
msgid ""
"Except that Knalga isn't his primary target, you idiot, he seeks the Hammer "
"of Thursagan!"
msgstr ""
"Excepto que Knalga no es su objetivo principal, idiota, ¡busca el Martillo "
"de Thursagan!"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:313
msgid ""
"(suddenly enraged) That puny unworthy human weasel, how dare...!!! But this "
"is bad, this is very bad..."
msgstr ""
"(de repente furioso) ¡Ese miserable humano insignificante, cómo se atreve…! "
"¡¡¡Pero esto es malo, esto es muy malo…!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:317
msgid "Don't tell me the Hammer is being kept by your clan!"
msgstr "¡No me digas que el Martillo lo tiene tu clan!"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:321
msgid ""
"No, but... Och, if he seizes the Arcanister's runic hammer he'll be able to "
"find Thursagan's Hammer... See, all runic hammers are connected to each "
"other through magic; this means, amongst other things, that one can detect "
"the presence of another. And, because Arcanisters' hammers have been crafted "
"from Thursagan's Hammer itself..."
msgstr ""
"No, pero… Och, si se apodera del martillo rúnico del Arcanista, podrá "
"encontrar el Martillo de Thursagan… Mira, todos los martillos rúnicos están "
"conectados entre sí por magia; esto significa, entre otras cosas, que uno "
"puede detectar la presencia de otro. Y como los martillos de los arcanistas "
"fueron forjados a partir del propio Martillo de Thursagan…"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:325
msgid ""
"...they can sense Thursagan's more easily than any other... In the end, it "
"all comes down to finding and striking Aelvar down all the same. You sit "
"here smoking your bagpipe while I chase him down."
msgstr ""
"…pueden sentir el de Thursagan más fácilmente que cualquier otro… Al final, "
"todo se reduce a encontrar y acabar con Aelvar de todos modos. Tú quédate "
"aquí fumando tu gaita mientras yo lo persigo."

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:329
msgid ""
"By the Nine Hells I will! I was just a tad too badly wounded to move by "
"myself, but thanks to this human's magic I now feel well again. It's you who "
"should stand aside drinking that tint water you humans call wine while we "
"deal with that Wesnothian fool!"
msgstr ""
"¡Por los Nueve Infiernos que sí lo haré! Estaba demasiado malherido para "
"moverme solo, pero gracias a la magia de este humano ahora me siento bien de "
"nuevo. ¡Eres tú quien debería quedarse a un lado bebiendo esa agua teñida "
"que los humanos llaman vino mientras nosotros nos encargamos de ese idiota "
"wesnothiano!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:333
msgid "What a loving brotherly relationship they have..."
msgstr "Qué relación fraternal tan cariñosa tienen…"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:371
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:629
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:53
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:510
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:57
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:603
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:538
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:52
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:656
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:53
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:965
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1450
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:40
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1083
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:42
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:731
msgid "Death of Algil"
msgstr "Muerte de Algil"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:402
msgid ""
"Listen, friend, I may have sounded harsh back there, but actually I like ye "
"humans – not all of ye, of course, only the nice ones. Sorry if I hurt ye "
"feelings."
msgstr ""
"Escucha, amigo, puede que haya sonado duro antes, pero en realidad me gustan "
"los humanos… no todos, claro, solo los buenos. Perdona si herí tus "
"sentimientos."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:406
msgid "(smirking) In that case, you're forgiven."
msgstr "(sonriendo con ironía) En ese caso, estás perdonado."

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:428
msgid "You see, elf, I..."
msgstr "Mira, elfa, yo…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:432
msgid "Algil, watch out!"
msgstr "¡Algil, cuidado!"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:436
msgid "(startled) Oi! Why the hell did you scream so out of a sudden?!"
msgstr "(sobresaltado) ¡Oye! ¿Por qué demonios gritaste así de repente?!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:440
msgid ""
"Don't let her speak to you, or you'll be sprayed by the world's worst poison!"
msgstr "¡No dejes que te hable, o te rociará con el peor veneno del mundo!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:444
msgid "Shut the hell up, shrimp!"
msgstr "¡Cállate de una vez, camarón!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:448
msgid "(sigh) Children..."
msgstr "(suspiro) Niños…"

#. [message], speaker=Accalu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:490
msgid ""
"So that 'Northern Alliance' has sent reinforcements? Let them come, I'm "
"really enjoying killing the denizens of this hole!"
msgstr ""
"¿Entonces esa «Alianza del Norte» ha enviado refuerzos? Que vengan, ¡estoy "
"disfrutando mucho matando a los habitantes de este agujero!"

#. [message], speaker=Zuryn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:494
msgid "Yes, yes, let them come, let them die and let them join my hordes!"
msgstr "¡Sí, sí, que vengan, que mueran y que se unan a mis hordas!"

#. [message], speaker=Og
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:498
msgid ""
"Is there no end to these pesky surface insects?! Smash them quickly, "
"warriors, I want to return to my feast as soon as I can!"
msgstr ""
"¿No hay fin para estos molestos insectos de la superficie?! ¡Aplástenlos "
"rápido, guerreros, quiero volver a mi banquete cuanto antes!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:502
msgid "Wait, what on Irdya are Washraha doing here?!"
msgstr "¡Espera, qué demonios hacen los washraha aquí en Irdya?!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:506
msgid ""
"Those are probably mercenaries hired by Aelvar; as you know, Wesnoth has "
"some colonies on Arajunna, and we employ natives of that continent as "
"mercenaries and even as Foreign Legions."
msgstr ""
"Probablemente son mercenarios contratados por Aelvar; como saben, Wesnoth "
"tiene algunas colonias en Arajunna, y empleamos a nativos de ese continente "
"como mercenarios e incluso como Legiones Extranjeras."

#. [message], speaker=Thrith
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:510
msgid ""
"At last the Alliance has come to our aid! We didn't expect Aelvar's army to "
"be so huge, they crushed our outer defences as if they were nothing!"
msgstr ""
"¡Por fin llegó la Alianza a ayudarnos! No esperábamos que el ejército de "
"Aelvar fuera tan enorme, ¡aplastaron nuestras defensas exteriores como si no "
"fueran nada!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:514
msgid "But where is he right now? Have you managed to capture him?"
msgstr "¿Pero dónde está él ahora mismo? ¿Lograron capturarlo?"

#. [message], speaker=Thrith
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:518
msgid ""
"Alas, we haven't. He left this troop to deal with us, and then he took the "
"Crimson Path, led by that traitor Aigcathil."
msgstr ""
"Lamentablemente, no. Dejó esta tropa para enfrentarnos y luego tomó el "
"Camino Carmesí, guiado por ese traidor Aigcathil."

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:522
msgid ""
"The Crimson Path? But it only leads to the volcanic chambers beneath "
"Knalga... Is father trying to lure Aelvar to his doom...?"
msgstr ""
"¿El Camino Carmesí? Pero ese solo lleva a las cámaras volcánicas bajo "
"Knalga… ¿Acaso padre está intentando atraer a Aelvar a su perdición…?"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:526
msgid ""
"That's something to think about later, now we must go to the runecrafters' "
"aid and..."
msgstr ""
"Eso lo pensaremos después, ahora debemos ir a ayudar a los forjadores de "
"runas y…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:530
msgid ""
"Hold on! If you want to help those dwarves, I'm fine with that, but I refuse "
"to do so."
msgstr ""
"¡Un momento! Si quieren ayudar a esos enanos, por mí está bien, pero yo me "
"niego a hacerlo."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:534
msgid ""
"Never thought I'd say that, but I'm with the shrimp. Let's return to "
"surface, this infected cave atmosphere is making me sick..."
msgstr ""
"Nunca pensé que diría esto, pero estoy con el camarón. Volvamos a la "
"superficie, esta atmósfera infectada de las cuevas me está enfermando…"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:538
msgid ""
"But... why are you doing that now, girl? Did you decide to let Aelvar do as "
"he wishes?!"
msgstr ""
"Pero… ¿por qué hacen eso ahora, chicas? ¿Decidieron dejar que Aelvar haga lo "
"que quiera?!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:542
msgid ""
"We could just go around this battlefield and find another way to him. All "
"I'm saying is that I won't help these dwarves, nor those trolls, not while "
"they refuse to unite even to face a common threat. If we do that, we still "
"won't be able to defeat trolls, undead and Washraha, and we'll all die."
msgstr ""
"Podríamos simplemente rodear este campo de batalla y encontrar otra forma de "
"llegar a él. Lo único que digo es que no voy a ayudar a estos enanos, ni a "
"esos trolls, mientras se nieguen a unirse incluso frente a una amenaza "
"común. Si hacemos eso, igual no podremos derrotar a trolls, no-muertos y "
"washraha, y todos moriremos."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:546
msgid ""
"Damn right. The mercenaries and the undead alone are dangerous enough; with "
"the trolls also against us, any win here will be pyrrhic at best, and then "
"we'll be in no shape to fight Aelvar."
msgstr ""
"Muy cierto. Los mercenarios y los no-muertos solos ya son bastante "
"peligrosos; con los trolls también en nuestra contra, cualquier victoria "
"aquí será pírica en el mejor de los casos, y luego no estaremos en "
"condiciones de enfrentar a Aelvar."

#. [message], speaker=Thrith
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:550
msgid ""
"Argh... I admit you've a point there... You see, troll, would you... (looks "
"hesitant) Darn it to all Nine Hells, would you fight these invaders along "
"with me?!"
msgstr ""
"Argh… Admito que tienen razón… Mira, troll, ¿tú… (mira dubitativo) Maldición "
"a los Nueve Infiernos, ¿lucharías contra estos invasores junto a mí?!"

#. [message], speaker=Og
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:554
msgid ""
"Joining you dwarves?! Dunno... Who can say you won't try something "
"treacherous on us? But that tiny girl spoke truth, you need us to win..."
msgstr ""
"¿Unirme a ustedes, enanos?! No sé… ¿Quién dice que no intentarán algo "
"traicionero contra nosotros? Pero la chica pequeña dijo la verdad, nos "
"necesitan para ganar…"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:558
msgid ""
"Troll chief, I am Donar, Captain of the Northern Alliance, and I assure you "
"that, if these dwarves try to betray you, I will personally lead Allied "
"armies to completely destroy their clan."
msgstr ""
"Jefe troll, soy Donar, Capitán de la Alianza del Norte, y te aseguro que si "
"estos enanos intentan traicionarte, personalmente lideraré ejércitos aliados "
"para destruir completamente su clan."

#. [message], speaker=Og
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:562
msgid ""
"Ah, that makes me more confident. Let's smash these invaders together, "
"little ones! Whoever gets more kills will get to suck their bone marrows!"
msgstr ""
"Ah, eso me da más confianza. ¡Aplastemos juntos a estos invasores, pequeños! "
"¡El que consiga más muertes se queda con la médula de sus huesos!"

#. [message], speaker=Thrith
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:566
msgid ""
"Who the hell would want that as prize?! Come on, dwarves, we can't let them "
"stand out on the battlefield more than ourselves!"
msgstr ""
"¡¿Quién demonios querría eso como premio?! ¡Vamos, enanos, no podemos dejar "
"que nos superen en el campo de batalla!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:570
msgid "Eh, in the end they still found a way to compete with each other..."
msgstr "Eh, al final igual encontraron una forma de competir entre ellos…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:574
msgid ""
"The Northern Alliance must be a truly renowned organisation, for that troll "
"to have trusted it so quickly..."
msgstr ""
"La Alianza del Norte debe ser una organización realmente reconocida, para "
"que ese troll confiara tan rápido en ella…"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:578
msgid ""
"There's a reason for that. A few years ago, a troll called Udhark became the "
"first of his people to join the Council of Warders, which rules of the "
"Northern Alliance. He's also a hero amongst the trolls, as he saved their "
"caves and all of Knalga from a massive Wesnothian invasion once."
msgstr ""
"Hay una razón para eso. Hace unos años, un troll llamado Udhark se convirtió "
"en el primero de su pueblo en unirse al Consejo de Guardianes, que gobierna "
"la Alianza del Norte. También es un héroe entre los trolls, ya que una vez "
"salvó sus cuevas y todo Knalga de una invasión masiva wesnothiana."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:582
msgid ""
"(sigh) And I was so hoping that we were going to leave this wretched realm..."
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) Y yo tenía tantas esperanzas de que íbamos a dejar este maldito "
"reino…"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:597
msgid "Defeat the Washraha and the undead"
msgstr "Derrotar a los washraha y a los no-muertos"

#. [message], speaker=Thrith
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:651
msgid ""
"Eh, it was rather fun, to fight along with trolls rather than against "
"them... But don't get the wrong idea, troll! That doesn't mean I want to be "
"friends with you or anything!"
msgstr ""
"Eh, fue bastante divertido luchar junto a trolls en vez de contra ellos… "
"¡Pero no te hagas ideas equivocadas, troll! ¡Eso no significa que quiera ser "
"tu amigo ni nada por el estilo!"

#. [message], speaker=Og
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:655
msgid "Good, it saves me time to remind you that we're enemies!"
msgstr "Bien, así me ahorras tiempo recordándote que somos enemigos."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:659
msgid "Ugh, they really are hopeless, aren't they..."
msgstr "Ugh, realmente son un caso perdido, ¿verdad…?"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:663
msgid ""
"Cheer up, at least they've learned the value of fighting together, even if "
"they won't admit that. You can't expect to end a millenarian rivalry in a "
"single day, you know."
msgstr ""
"Ánimo, al menos han aprendido el valor de luchar juntos, aunque no lo "
"admitan. No se puede esperar terminar una rivalidad milenaria en un solo "
"día, ¿sabes?"

#. [message], speaker=Thrith
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:667
msgid ""
"Now, friends, there's something I want to ask you. You seemed surprised when "
"you heard Aelvar had taken the Crimson Path; do you know anything about his "
"schemes?"
msgstr ""
"Ahora, amigos, hay algo que quiero preguntarles. Parecían sorprendidos "
"cuando escucharon que Aelvar tomó el Camino Carmesí; ¿saben algo de sus "
"planes?"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:671
msgid ""
"We do. He seeks the Hammer of Thursagan for himself; we thought he'd come "
"this way to steal the Thursaz Clan's knowledge on it, but it he's gone down "
"the Crimson Path..."
msgstr ""
"Lo sabemos. Busca el Martillo de Thursagan para sí mismo; pensamos que "
"vendría por aquí para robar el conocimiento del clan Thursaz sobre él, pero "
"si tomó el Camino Carmesí…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:675
msgid "...Then he must be pursuing an even more urgent objective."
msgstr "…entonces debe estar persiguiendo un objetivo aún más urgente."

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:679
msgid ""
"But there's nothing down the Crimson Path other than lava chambers, and "
"surely nothing more important than the Hammer of Thursagan!"
msgstr ""
"¡Pero no hay nada en el Camino Carmesí aparte de cámaras de lava, y seguro "
"nada más importante que el Martillo de Thursagan!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:683
msgid ""
"Nothing that we know of... But recall that Aelvar knew about the Kings' "
"Regalia, something few being on this world still remember."
msgstr ""
"Nada que nosotros sepamos… Pero recuerden que Aelvar conocía el Regalia de "
"los Reyes, algo que pocos seres en este mundo todavía recuerdan."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:687
msgid ""
"I have a bad feeling... Come, everyone, we have to hurry - before Aelvar "
"finds whatever he seeks!"
msgstr ""
"Tengo un mal presentimiento… Vamos, todos, tenemos que apresurarnos… ¡antes "
"de que Aelvar encuentre lo que sea que busca!"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:706
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:856
msgid "Gaaahhrrghhh!!! Curse them all..."
msgstr "¡Gaaahhrrghhh!!! Malditos sean todos…"

#. [message], speaker=Thrith
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:721
msgid "Och... I have..."
msgstr "Och… yo tengo…"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:725
msgid ""
"Master Thriththil couldn't have died! Now, the clan will be unprotected "
"against Aelvar' forces!"
msgstr ""
"¡El maestro Thriththil no puede haber muerto! ¡Ahora el clan quedará "
"desprotegido contra las fuerzas de Aelvar!"

#. [message], speaker=Og
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:740
msgid "Ugh! Sorry, my people, I can't go on like this...!"
msgstr "¡Ugh! Lo siento, mi gente, ¡no puedo seguir así…!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:744
msgid "No! Without the trolls, we're too outnumbered to win!"
msgstr "¡No! ¡Sin los trolls somos demasiado pocos para ganar!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/25_Common_Enemies.cfg:757
msgid ""
"I'm afraid we should have been quicker, folks; at this pace, we won't be "
"able to catch up with Aelvar's army any more!"
msgstr ""
"Me temo que deberíamos haber sido más rápidos, amigos; a este ritmo, ¡ya no "
"podremos alcanzar al ejército de Aelvar!"

#. [scenario], id=26_The_Earths_Core
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:5
msgid "The Earth's Core"
msgstr "El Núcleo de la Tierra"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:21
msgid "Find Aelvar and stop his mad schemes"
msgstr "Encontrar a Aelvar y detener sus locos planes"

#. [side], type=General
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:115
msgid "Commander Thorden"
msgstr "Comandante Thorden"

#. [side], type=Orcish Warlord
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:137
msgid "Red-Hand Bagrat"
msgstr "Bagrat Mano Roja"

#. [side], type=Orcish Warlord
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:141
msgid "Orcish Mercenaries"
msgstr "Mercenarios orcos"

#. [side], type=Troll Warrior
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:159
msgid "Chief Grukk"
msgstr "Jefe Grukk"

#. [side], type=Troll Warrior
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:163
msgid "Troll Mercenaries"
msgstr "Mercenarios trolls"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:330
msgid ""
"There he is...! (shouting) It's over, Aelvar! Your forces are weary, the "
"Northern Alliance sends forces down the Crimson Path even as we speak, and "
"all that awaits you in the path ahead is fire and darkness!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ahí está…! (gritando) ¡Se acabó, Aelvar! Tus fuerzas están agotadas, la "
"Alianza del Norte envía tropas por el Camino Carmesí mientras hablamos, ¡y "
"todo lo que te espera adelante es fuego y oscuridad!"

#. [message], speaker=Aelvar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:334
msgid ""
"Now that's rich: the bookworm princeling, who always prided himself in his "
"erudition, is more ignorant that the 'brutish' Aelvar... But I have to give "
"it to you, little brother: there <i>is</i> power to be obtained from scrolls "
"and learning. Though I bet even you would never have considered how much "
"knowledge can be had by simply talking to people, and to people who pass "
"their knowledge on through words instead of stinking parchment!"
msgstr ""
"Esto sí que es bueno: el principito ratón de biblioteca, que siempre se "
"enorgullecía de su erudición, resulta más ignorante que el «bruto» de "
"Aelvar… Pero debo reconocértelo, hermanito: <i>sí</i> hay poder que se puede "
"obtener de pergaminos y del estudio. Aunque apuesto que ni siquiera tú "
"habrías considerado cuánto conocimiento se puede obtener simplemente "
"hablando con la gente, y con gente que transmite su saber mediante palabras "
"en vez de apestosos pergaminos."

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:338
msgid ""
"You mean... the trolls? You fool, what knowledge could they offer you on the "
"Hammer of Thursagan?"
msgstr ""
"¿Te refieres… a los trolls? Necio, ¿qué conocimiento podrían ofrecerte ellos "
"sobre el Martillo de Thursagan?"

#. [message], speaker=Aelvar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:342
msgid ""
"Ha! Give it to a dwarf to think everything is about him. No, Algil son of "
"Aigcathil, I'll come for the Hammer eventually, but that wasn't what I "
"sought the trolls for. They know nothing about runecrafting, but they know "
"much, much more than anyone gives them credit for, and their memory is as "
"deep as the abysses they came from."
msgstr ""
"¡Ja! Típico de un enano pensar que todo gira en torno a él. No, Algil hijo "
"de Aigcathil, eventualmente vendré por el Martillo, pero no era eso lo que "
"buscaba de los trolls. No saben nada de forja rúnica, pero saben mucho, "
"muchísimo más de lo que cualquiera les reconoce, y su memoria es tan "
"profunda como los abismos de donde vinieron."

#. [message], speaker=Aelvar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:346
msgid ""
"Has any of your scrolls ever told you, little brother, of the world before "
"the first scrolls were written? Of when great beings walked this earth, and "
"the very shape of the land was different? Algil, does any of you lorekeepers "
"know the very Heart Mountains used to spew fire and brimstone all over? I "
"don't think they do, because it was thanks to the <i>trolls</i> that these "
"mountains were calmed and their caves made livable!"
msgstr ""
"¿Alguno de tus pergaminos te ha contado alguna vez, hermanito, del mundo "
"antes de que se escribieran los primeros pergaminos? ¿De cuando grandes "
"seres caminaban por esta tierra y la forma misma del terreno era diferente? "
"Algil, ¿alguno de sus guardianes del saber sabe que las mismísimas Montañas "
"del Corazón solían escupir fuego y azufre por todas partes? No creo que lo "
"sepan, porque fue gracias a los <i>trolls</i> que estas montañas se calmaron "
"y sus cuevas se volvieron habitables."

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:350
msgid "What?!"
msgstr "¡¿Qué?!"

#. [message], speaker=Aelvar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:354
msgid ""
"The trolls themselves only remember it as legend, an ancestor myth: long "
"ago, a great troll chief and shaman called Griknagh led his people out of "
"the fiery womb of the earth, but the earth's fires gave pursuit. With his "
"magic, Griknagh bound the anger of the earth to a single stone, causing the "
"rock to grow still and the fires to be quenched. This stone is called the "
"Earthenheart, and the trolls' tale end with a grim warning: should that "
"stone be destroyed, the anger of the earth shall be unleashed once more, and "
"the mountains will be engulfed in flames."
msgstr ""
"Los propios trolls solo lo recuerdan como leyenda, un mito ancestral: hace "
"mucho tiempo, un gran jefe y chamán troll llamado Griknagh sacó a su pueblo "
"del vientre ardiente de la tierra, pero los fuegos de la tierra los "
"persiguieron. Con su magia, Griknagh ató la ira de la tierra a una sola "
"piedra, haciendo que la roca se calmara y los fuegos se apagaran. Esa piedra "
"se llama el Corazón de Tierra, y el cuento de los trolls termina con una "
"sombría advertencia: si esa piedra es destruida, la ira de la tierra se "
"desatará de nuevo y las montañas serán consumidas por las llamas."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:358
msgid "You... don't tell me..."
msgstr "Tú… no me digas…"

#. [message], speaker=Aelvar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:362
msgid ""
"Yes, little brother, the Earthenheart is no mere myth... though it will "
"presently become mere history."
msgstr ""
"Sí, hermanito, el Corazón de Tierra no es un mero mito… aunque pronto se "
"convertirá en mera historia."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:366
msgid ""
"He can't defeat all of Knalga by himself, so he'll let nature do his dirty "
"work...!"
msgstr ""
"¡No puede derrotar a todo Knalga él solo, así que dejará que la naturaleza "
"haga el trabajo sucio por él…!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:370
msgid ""
"Over our dead bodies! Come, everyone, if this Earthenheart is as he "
"described, its destruction will ruin all of the Northlands!"
msgstr ""
"¡Sobre nuestros cadáveres! ¡Vamos, todos, si este Corazón de Tierra es como "
"él lo describió, su destrucción arruinará todas las Tierras del Norte!"

#. [message], speaker=Aelvar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:374
msgid ""
"Do you think I'd have revealed my plan if there was any chance you could "
"interfere? You're even bigger fools than I thought, but if you want to doom "
"yourselves by daring to attack me, be my guests!"
msgstr ""
"¿Creen que habría revelado mi plan si hubiera alguna posibilidad de que "
"interfirieran? Son aún más idiotas de lo que pensaba, ¡pero si quieren "
"condenarse atacándome, adelante!"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:419
msgid "Oh, no, no, NO!!!"
msgstr "¡Oh, no, no, NO!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:423
msgid "(in despair) Damn it, how could we let him destroy the Earthenheart?!"
msgstr ""
"(desesperada) ¡Maldición, cómo pudimos dejar que destruyera el Corazón de "
"Tierra?!"

#. [message], speaker=Aelvar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:427
msgid ""
"Ha ha!!! The hardest part is done, now all I have to do is find the best "
"view to enjoy Knalga's destruction! Silver Masters, you know what to do! "
"Aigcathil, Vendryn, cover them!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ja ja! ¡La parte más difícil está hecha, ahora solo tengo que encontrar el "
"mejor lugar para disfrutar de la destrucción de Knalga! ¡Maestros de Plata, "
"saben qué hacer! ¡Aigcathil, Vendryn, cúbranlos!"

#. [message], speaker=Aigcathil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:431
msgid "As you command, Lord Aelvar!"
msgstr "¡Como ordene, señor Aelvar!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:452
msgid ""
"Silver Masters...? Damn it, of course! I wondered how Aelvar planned on "
"escaping these caves alive after destroying the Earthenheart; <i>silver "
"mages</i> is how he's escaping, they'll open a teleport link for him!"
msgstr ""
"¿Maestros de Plata…? ¡Maldición, claro! Me preguntaba cómo planeaba Aelvar "
"escapar vivo de estas cuevas después de destruir el Corazón de Tierra; con "
"<i>magos de plata</i> es como escapará, ¡ellos abrirán un enlace de "
"teleportación para él!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:456
msgid "So if we get rid of those two, Aelvar will be trapped?"
msgstr "¿Entonces si nos deshacemos de esos dos, Aelvar quedará atrapado?"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:460
msgid ""
"What's even the point now? The Earthenheart was shattered and these caves "
"are about to crumble!"
msgstr ""
"¿Cuál es siquiera el punto ahora? ¡El Corazón de Tierra fue destrozado y "
"estas cuevas están a punto de derrumbarse!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:464
msgid ""
"He will be trapped, but we don't have to. I know a thing or two about "
"teleportation; Aelvar's silver mages must be activating the teleport link by "
"now, so if we get rid of them, and with Valerya and Olokun supporting me, I "
"can maintain the link long enough for us to escape."
msgstr ""
"Él quedará atrapado, pero nosotros no tenemos por qué. Sé un par de cosas "
"sobre teleportación; los magos de plata de Aelvar deben estar activando el "
"enlace de teleportación ahora mismo, así que si nos deshacemos de ellos, y "
"con Valerya y Olokun apoyándome, puedo mantener el enlace lo suficiente para "
"que escapemos."

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:468
msgid ""
"Consider it done. If Knalga falls, at least it falls on that bastard's head!"
msgstr ""
"Considérenlo hecho. Si Knalga cae, ¡al menos caerá sobre la cabeza de ese "
"bastardo!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:474
msgid "Kill Aelvar's Silver Mages"
msgstr "Matar a los Magos de Plata de Aelvar"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:478
msgid "Capture Aigcathil (reduce his HP to 0 or below)"
msgstr "Capturar a Aigcathil (reducir su PV a 0 o menos)"

#. [message], speaker=Vendryn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:532
msgid "Ack! Forgive me, Lord Aelvar, I've failed you..."
msgstr "¡Ack! Perdóneme, señor Aelvar, le he fallado…"

#. [message], speaker=Aigcathil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:545
msgid "You... have no idea... what you're doing..."
msgstr "Ustedes… no tienen idea… de lo que están haciendo…"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:549
msgid ""
"Then tell us, father! Why did you side with that tyrant against the dwarves "
"and the humans you've once fought for?!"
msgstr ""
"¡Entonces díganos, padre! ¿Por qué te pusiste del lado de ese tirano contra "
"los enanos y los humanos por los que alguna vez luchaste?!"

#. [message], speaker=Aigcathil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:553
msgid ""
"It is I who should be asking why you want to save dwarves from whom you've "
"only known hatred, who forced me to live apart from the only woman I ever "
"loved! I'm a dwarf, yes, but I despise this race whose greed nearly ruined "
"this world once, and who is too arrogant to even acknowledge their own wrong-"
"doings!"
msgstr ""
"¡Soy yo quien debería preguntar por qué quieres salvar a enanos de los que "
"solo has conocido odio, que me obligaron a vivir separado de la única mujer "
"que amé! Sí, soy enano, ¡pero desprecio a esta raza cuya codicia casi "
"arruinó este mundo alguna vez, y que es demasiado arrogante para siquiera "
"reconocer sus propios errores!"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:557
msgid ""
"I wish to know what you're talking about, father, but we've got no time for "
"that right now. Someone knock him unconscious; as a representative of the "
"Thursaz clan, I will take him as prisoner."
msgstr ""
"Quisiera saber de qué hablas, padre, pero ahora no tenemos tiempo para eso. "
"Alguien déjelo inconsciente; como representante del clan Thursaz, lo tomaré "
"prisionero."

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:589
msgid "Curses, I can't finish the portal with only my power!"
msgstr "¡Maldición, no puedo terminar el portal solo con mi poder!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:593
msgid ""
"Allow me to aid you, 'master'! Tell your henchmen to cover me, will you? At "
"least until <i>my</i> companions can take your place maintaining this portal!"
msgstr ""
"Permíteme ayudarte, «maestro». Dile a tus secuaces que me cubran, ¿quieres? "
"¡Al menos hasta que <i>mis</i> compañeros puedan tomar tu lugar manteniendo "
"este portal!"

#. [message], speaker=Aelvar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:597
msgid "You petulant worm, don't you know when to DIE?!"
msgstr "¡Gusano insolente, no sabes cuándo MORIR?!"

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:616
msgid "(coughing blood) Lord A-Aelvar...!"
msgstr "(tosiendo sangre) ¡Señor A-Aelvar…!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:620
msgid "His strikes' shockwaves are causing the roof to collapse!"
msgstr "¡Las ondas de choque de sus golpes están haciendo colapsar el techo!"

#. [message], speaker=Aelvar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:624
msgid "Let us all fall together then!"
msgstr "¡Entonces caigamos todos juntos!"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:628
msgid "Damn it...!"
msgstr "¡Maldición…!"

#. [message], speaker=Aelvar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:635
msgid "You... <i>puny</i> Sogen scum... But, hold on, your face..."
msgstr "Tú… escoria <i>insignificante</i> sogen… Pero espera, tu cara…"

#. [message], speaker=Aelvar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:644
msgid ""
"Ha! So <i>you</i> are that bastard... The Gods couldn't have been more "
"generous; even if I die, I'll be glad if I just manage to take your bastard, "
"mongrel life...!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ja! Así que <i>tú</i> eres ese bastardo… Los dioses no podrían haber sido "
"más generosos; aunque muera, me alegraré si al menos logro llevarme la vida "
"de bastardo mestizo tuyo…!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:651
msgid ""
"Cursed Aelvar...! Everyone, get as are from him as you can, or else you'll "
"be within the reach of his mace's shockwaves!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldito Aelvar…! ¡Todos, aléjense lo más posible de él, o quedarán al "
"alcance de las ondas de choque de su maza!"

#. [message], speaker=Aelvar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:655
msgid "As if I'd let you escape!"
msgstr "¡Como si los fuera a dejar escapar!"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:662
msgid "Ugh...! I can't... move...!"
msgstr "¡Ugh…! ¡No puedo… moverme…!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:666
msgid "(frightened) Damn that Aelvar...!"
msgstr "(asustada) ¡Maldito Aelvar…!"

#. [message], speaker=Aelvar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:673
msgid ""
"Your feeble elvish arrows have no effect on my armour, girl! Now, boy, I "
"shall honour you by killing you with my very own-"
msgstr ""
"¡Tus débiles flechas élficas no tienen efecto en mi armadura, niña! Ahora, "
"muchacho, te honraré matándote con mi propia-"

#. [message], speaker=Aelvar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:697
msgid "...What...! This arrow...!!!"
msgstr "…¿Qué…! ¡¡Esta flecha…!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:701
msgid "I-it's..."
msgstr "E-es…"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:705
msgid "Don't..."
msgstr "No…"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:712
msgid "...you dare..."
msgstr "…te atrevas…"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:719
msgid "...hit..."
msgstr "…a golpear…"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:725
msgid "...my son!"
msgstr "…¡a mi hijo!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:729
msgid "Wait, did he just..."
msgstr "Espera, ¿acaba de…?"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:733
msgid "(appalled) Brother, he's... He's your <i>son</i>?!"
msgstr "(horrorizado) ¡Hermano, él… es tu <i>hijo</i>?!"

#. [message], speaker=Aelvar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:737
msgid ""
"(coughing blood) I knew it... so this is the bastard... you sired by a Sogen "
"whore... How shameful... that I couldn't kill him sooner..."
msgstr ""
"(tosiendo sangre) Lo sabía… así que este es el bastardo… que engendraste con "
"una puta sogen… Qué vergüenza… que no pude matarlo antes…"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:741
msgid ""
"Everyone, fall back! I have silver mages of my own, they have a teleport "
"link at the ready to take us to the upper caves!"
msgstr ""
"¡Todos, retrocedan! Tengo mis propios magos de plata, ¡tienen un enlace de "
"teleportación listo para llevarnos a las cuevas superiores!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:745
msgid "Cornelya, wait, I'll help you carry him!"
msgstr "Cornelya, espera, ¡te ayudo a cargarlo!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:749
msgid ""
"There's no need for that, I can carry Kenshiro alone, just get moving "
"already before we're caught in the eruption!"
msgstr ""
"No hace falta, puedo llevar a Kenshiro sola, ¡muévanse ya antes de que nos "
"atrape la erupción!"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:753
msgid ""
"And you, brother, help me carry our father; we have to warn everyone... "
"This... This is the end of Knalga..."
msgstr ""
"Y tú, hermano, ayúdame a cargar a nuestro padre; tenemos que advertir a "
"todos… Esto… Esto es el fin de Knalga…"

#. [message], speaker=Aelvar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:869
msgid ""
"It's time! Come, my soldiers, we must leave this cave before it explodes!"
msgstr ""
"¡Es hora! ¡Vengan, mis soldados, debemos abandonar esta cueva antes de que "
"exploten!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/26_The_Earths_Core.cfg:873
msgid "NO! We haven't made it in time, this... this is our end...?!"
msgstr "¡NO! No llegamos a tiempo, esto… ¿esto es nuestro fin…?"

#. [scenario], id=27A_Spark_Of_Hope
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27A_Spark_Of_Hope.cfg:5
msgid "The Legend's Cradle: Spark of Hope"
msgstr "La Cuna de la Leyenda: Chispa de Esperanza"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27A_Spark_Of_Hope.cfg:151
msgid ""
"Tenma Yozora, I want you and your friends to know that I, Prince Aeldhoryan, "
"in the name of my people, thank you for your aid in this war, even though "
"you had no such duty."
msgstr ""
"Tenma Yozora, quiero que tú y tus amigos sepan que yo, el príncipe "
"Aeldhoryan, en nombre de mi pueblo, les agradezco su ayuda en esta guerra, "
"aunque no tenían ninguna obligación de hacerlo."

#. [message], speaker=Udhark
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27A_Spark_Of_Hope.cfg:155
msgid ""
"And I, Chief Udhark, in the name of the Northern Alliance, wish to thank you "
"as well. Though tragedy could not be averted in the end, without your "
"intervention an even greater tragedy would have taken place, as Aelvar would "
"still be alive and unimpeded to continue his schemes."
msgstr ""
"Y yo, jefe Udhark, en nombre de la Alianza del Norte, también quiero "
"agradecerles. Aunque al final no pudimos evitar la tragedia, sin su "
"intervención habría ocurrido una tragedia aún mayor, pues Aelvar seguiría "
"vivo y sin obstáculos para continuar con sus planes."

#. [message], speaker=Aethra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27A_Spark_Of_Hope.cfg:159
msgid ""
"Do not lose heart, my friend. Defeats too are part of life; what truly makes "
"us winners is the ability to turn pain into strength, and to use this "
"strength to carry on bravely."
msgstr ""
"No pierdas el ánimo, amigo. Las derrotas también forman parte de la vida; lo "
"que realmente nos hace ganadores es la capacidad de convertir el dolor en "
"fuerza, y usar esa fuerza para seguir adelante con valentía."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27A_Spark_Of_Hope.cfg:163
msgid "Thank you all for your kindness, Chief Udhark, prince, princess..."
msgstr "Gracias a todos por su amabilidad, jefe Udhark, príncipe, princesa…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27A_Spark_Of_Hope.cfg:167
msgid ""
"Tenma, I... I don't expect you to have forgiven me for what I've done to "
"you, but... I want you to know... It was an honour, to fight alongside you."
msgstr ""
"Tenma, yo… no espero que me hayas perdonado por lo que te hice, pero… quiero "
"que sepas… Fue un honor luchar a tu lado."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27A_Spark_Of_Hope.cfg:171
msgid ""
"You're right, Aetheryon, I can't say I have forgiven you... but know that, "
"if I once wanted you dead, now... Now I hope that, next time we meet, you'll "
"have become someone I may forgive."
msgstr ""
"Tienes razón, Aetheryon, no puedo decir que te haya perdonado… pero sabe "
"que, si alguna vez quise verte muerto, ahora… ahora espero que, la próxima "
"vez que nos encontremos, te hayas convertido en alguien a quien pueda "
"perdonar."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27A_Spark_Of_Hope.cfg:175
msgid "(smirk) I'll do my best."
msgstr "(sonrisa) Haré lo mejor que pueda."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27A_Spark_Of_Hope.cfg:179
msgid ""
"And brother, there's something I must tell you. Some of the mages who fought "
"alongside us have asked for permission to follow Lady Valerya."
msgstr ""
"Y hermano, hay algo que debo decirte. Algunos de los magos que lucharon "
"junto a nosotros han pedido permiso para seguir a la dama Valerya."

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27A_Spark_Of_Hope.cfg:183
msgid ""
"And they shall have it; we can't afford to repay your aid with gold or "
"soldiers, so please, accept this as a token of gratitude."
msgstr ""
"Y lo tendrán; no podemos permitirnos pagar su ayuda con oro ni soldados, así "
"que por favor, acepten esto como muestra de gratitud."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27A_Spark_Of_Hope.cfg:187
msgid ""
"Thank you, Prince Aeldhoryan; I promise I shall guide and return them to "
"their homeland in safety."
msgstr ""
"Gracias, príncipe Aeldhoryan; prometo guiarlos y devolverlos sanos y salvos "
"a su tierra natal."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27A_Spark_Of_Hope.cfg:191
msgid "So, if we're d-"
msgstr "Entonces, si ya estamos—"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27A_Spark_Of_Hope.cfg:202
msgid ""
"(panting) Wait! Wait... Friends, I have a request to ye: I wish to accompany "
"ye in yer travel across the ocean."
msgstr ""
"(jadeando) ¡Esperen! Esperen… Amigos, tengo una petición para ustedes: deseo "
"acompañarlos en su viaje a través del océano."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27A_Spark_Of_Hope.cfg:206
msgid ""
"Well, we see no problem in you coming along, but, if I may ask... are you "
"coming because of that hammer I told you about...?"
msgstr ""
"Bueno, no vemos problema en que vengas, pero, si puedo preguntar… ¿vienes "
"por ese martillo del que te hablé…?"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27A_Spark_Of_Hope.cfg:210
msgid ""
"Aye. I haven't told others about what my father told my brother and I... He "
"told me, friends, about Aelvar's research on the so-called King's Regalia; "
"according to him, in that research it was discovered the true origins of "
"Thursagan's Hammer, once known as Hammer of Buri – but Aelvar's researchers "
"had also discovered about another artefact, known as the Hammer of Ymer, "
"wielded by the troll king Griknagh..."
msgstr ""
"Sí. No le he contado a los demás lo que mi padre le dijo a mi hermano y a "
"mí… Me contó, amigos, sobre la investigación de Aelvar acerca del llamado "
"Regalia de los Reyes; según él, en esa investigación se descubrieron los "
"verdaderos orígenes del Martillo de Thursagan, antes conocido como Martillo "
"de Buri… pero los investigadores de Aelvar también descubrieron otro "
"artefacto, conocido como el Martillo de Ymer, empuñado por el rey troll "
"Griknagh…"

#. [message], speaker=Udhark
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27A_Spark_Of_Hope.cfg:214
msgid ""
"(surprised) But... I thought only our wisest shamans knew this story! To "
"think that Aelvar delved so deep into ancient lore..."
msgstr ""
"(sorprendido) Pero… ¡pensé que solo nuestros chamanes más sabios conocían "
"esta historia! Pensar que Aelvar se adentró tanto en el saber antiguo…"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27A_Spark_Of_Hope.cfg:218
msgid ""
"It was then that Aelvar's researchers discovered the greatest shame of the "
"dwarves, which we forgot – by accident or by purpose, it doesn't matter; "
"what matters is that Moradin, our forefather, stole Griknagh's hammer for "
"himself. Such was the spark of this endless war between my people and the "
"trolls..."
msgstr ""
"Fue entonces cuando los investigadores de Aelvar descubrieron la mayor "
"vergüenza de los enanos, que olvidamos —por accidente o a propósito, no "
"importa; lo que importa es que Moradin, nuestro antepasado, robó el martillo "
"de Griknagh para sí mismo. Esa fue la chispa de esta guerra interminable "
"entre mi pueblo y los trolls…"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27A_Spark_Of_Hope.cfg:222
msgid ""
"So I want to go to this Netjer-Ta and find the Hammer of Ymer, and then, "
"Chief Udhark, I will return it to its rightful owners. Olokun and his "
"mermaid companion have confirmed what I have witnessed all my life: this "
"world – our world – is fast walking down a path of decadence and ruin, and "
"so we must, more than ever before, lay aside senseless rivalries and unite "
"in order to survive."
msgstr ""
"Por eso quiero ir a este Netjer-Ta y encontrar el Martillo de Ymer, y luego, "
"jefe Udhark, lo devolveré a sus legítimos dueños. Olokun y su compañera "
"sirena han confirmado lo que he visto toda mi vida: este mundo —nuestro mundo"
"— está avanzando rápidamente por un camino de decadencia y ruina, y por eso "
"debemos, más que nunca, dejar de lado rivalidades sin sentido y unirnos para "
"sobrevivir."

#. [message], speaker=Udhark
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27A_Spark_Of_Hope.cfg:226
msgid ""
"Hearing such words proves that nothing I have strived for in my life was in "
"vain. Good luck, worthy Algil; I shall be waiting for you here, so that, at "
"long last, the Twin Hammers may stand side by side in the hands of friends."
msgstr ""
"Oír tales palabras demuestra que nada de lo que he luchado en mi vida fue en "
"vano. Buena suerte, digno Algil; te esperaré aquí, para que al fin los "
"Mellizos Martillos puedan estar lado a lado en manos de amigos."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27A_Spark_Of_Hope.cfg:230
msgid ""
"(beaming) Well, about damn time someone learned that! Now, everyone, we have "
"another mission, and so we can't waste any more second here; Derceto, show "
"us the way, and we'll follow you!"
msgstr ""
"(radiante) ¡Bueno, ya era hora de que alguien aprendiera eso! Ahora, todos, "
"tenemos otra misión, así que no podemos perder ni un segundo más aquí; "
"Derceto, muéstranos el camino, ¡y te seguiremos!"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27A_Spark_Of_Hope.cfg:234
msgid ""
"Right! (hugging Olokun) Did you hear what that lovely dwarf said? 'Olokun "
"and his mermaid companion'... See, everyone looks at us as a couple already!"
msgstr ""
"¡Claro! (abrazando a Olokun) ¿Escuchaste lo que dijo ese encantador enano? "
"«Olokun y su compañera sirena»… ¡Miren, todos ya nos ven como pareja!"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27A_Spark_Of_Hope.cfg:238
msgid ""
"Good luck, so... Kenshiro. When you see your mother again, please send her "
"my regards, and tell her... What I told her under that cherry tree remains "
"true."
msgstr ""
"Buena suerte, entonces… Kenshiro. Cuando vuelvas a ver a tu madre, por favor "
"dale mis saludos, y dile… que lo que le dije bajo aquel cerezo sigue siendo "
"verdad."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27A_Spark_Of_Hope.cfg:242
msgid ""
"I told you already, why don't you do that yourself? You're the governor of "
"Kodakuni, after all."
msgstr ""
"Ya te lo dije, ¿por qué no lo haces tú mismo? Al fin y al cabo eres el "
"gobernador de Kodakuni."

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27A_Spark_Of_Hope.cfg:246
msgid ""
"It seems I wasn't supposed to sign treaties with the Northern Alliance, and "
"so the Emperor has deemed it fitting to send me to our southern provinces "
"instead."
msgstr ""
"Parece que no debía firmar tratados con la Alianza del Norte, y por eso el "
"Emperador ha considerado apropiado enviarme a nuestras provincias del sur en "
"su lugar."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27A_Spark_Of_Hope.cfg:250
msgid "Well, then, in that case I shall give her your message..."
msgstr "Bueno, entonces, en ese caso le daré tu mensaje…"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27A_Spark_Of_Hope.cfg:254
msgid "Good journey, friends; please, take care of my brother for me..."
msgstr "Buen viaje, amigos; por favor, cuiden a mi hermano por mí…"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27A_Spark_Of_Hope.cfg:258
msgid ""
"You puny brat, you should worry about your own helpless arse before worrying "
"about mine!"
msgstr ""
"¡Pequeño mocoso, deberías preocuparte por tu propio trasero indefenso antes "
"de preocuparte por el mío!"

#. [message], speaker=Aethra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27A_Spark_Of_Hope.cfg:262
msgid "Good luck, friends! I hope we meet again in the future!"
msgstr ""
"¡Buena suerte, amigos! ¡Espero que nos volvamos a encontrar en el futuro!"

#. [scenario], id=27B_The_Legends_Cradle
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:5
msgid "The Legend's Cradle"
msgstr "La Cuna de la Leyenda"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:25
msgid "Find the city of New Maat'Kare"
msgstr "Encontrar la ciudad de Nueva Maat'Kare"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:29
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:30
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:29
msgid ""
"NOTE: During daytime in this scenario, living units will suffer the effects "
"of the land's heat, suffering dehydration and losing 1 HP per turn unless "
"treated by healers. Staying inside a castle, village, keep or in water will "
"nullify the dehydration's effects."
msgstr ""
"NOTA: Durante el día en este escenario, las unidades vivas sufrirán los "
"efectos del calor de la tierra, padeciendo deshidratación y perdiendo 1 PV "
"por turno a menos que sean tratadas por sanadores. Permanecer dentro de un "
"castillo, aldea, torreón o en el agua anulará los efectos de la "
"deshidratación."

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:61
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:607
msgid "Death of Master Ankhmare"
msgstr "Muerte del maestro Ankhmare"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:96
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:35
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:77
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:107
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_I.cfg:35
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:201
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:241
msgid "New Maat'Kare"
msgstr "Nueva Maat'Kare"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:126
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:223
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:214
msgid "Red Moon Clan"
msgstr "Clan Luna Roja"

#. [side], type=Minotaur Overlord
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:148
msgid "Gnathos"
msgstr "Gnathos"

#. [side], type=Minotaur Overlord
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:153
msgid "Minotaur Mercenaries"
msgstr "Mercenarios minotauros"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:178
msgid "Fauns"
msgstr "Faunos"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:273
msgid ""
"At long last! Stand strong, friends, we have just a couple of miles until we "
"sight New Maat'Kare!"
msgstr ""
"¡Por fin! ¡Resistan, amigos, solo nos faltan un par de millas para avistar "
"Nueva Maat'Kare!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:277
msgid "(panting) You're really eager to get back home, aren't you..."
msgstr "(jadeando) Realmente estás ansioso por volver a casa, ¿verdad…?"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:281
msgid ""
"(panting) Be sympathetic, he's been away from it for years. And do not "
"complain; for those who have crossed both the Great Continent and the Vast "
"Sea, this little stretch of sand should be no trouble..."
msgstr ""
"(jadeando) Ten compasión, ha estado lejos de aquí durante años. Y no te "
"quejes; para quienes han cruzado tanto el Gran Continente como el Vasto Mar, "
"este pequeño tramo de arena no debería ser problema…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:285
msgid "You're one to talk, you're the most exhausted of all!"
msgstr "¡Tú eres la que menos debería hablar, eres la más agotada de todos!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:289
msgid ""
"(sighing amusedly) You really should have waited at the beach... But I "
"should have been more sensitive too; I'll invoke some water elementals to "
"shelter you from the heat and the dryness. They should also make it easier "
"for you to move on solid ground."
msgstr ""
"(suspirando divertido) Realmente deberían haber esperado en la playa… Pero "
"yo también debí ser más considerado; invocaré algunos elementales de agua "
"para protegerlos del calor y la sequedad. También deberían facilitarles "
"moverse en terreno sólido."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:293
msgid ""
"The Undines wrap themselves around Derceto, shielding her from the desert's "
"heat and facilitating both her movement and her defence when fighting on dry "
"land."
msgstr ""
"Las ondinas se envuelven alrededor de Derceto, protegiéndola del calor del "
"desierto y facilitando tanto su movimiento como su defensa al luchar en "
"tierra firme."

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:323
msgid "Thank you, dearest! I shall think of your Undines' embrace as your own."
msgstr ""
"¡Gracias, querido! Pensaré en el abrazo de tus ondinas como si fuera el tuyo."

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:327
msgid ""
"The queen is right, this little stretch of sand is nothing, but these "
"burning suns are boiling my brains! I hope your city has plenty of shade and "
"drinks, Olokun, or else I'll have to go straight to the caves of the "
"Aigathol!"
msgstr ""
"La reina tiene razón, este pequeño tramo de arena no es nada, ¡pero estos "
"soles ardientes me están hirviendo el cerebro! Espero que tu ciudad tenga "
"mucha sombra y bebidas, Olokun, ¡o tendré que ir directo a las cuevas de los "
"Aigathol"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:331
msgid ""
"Such a lively conversation of which Tenma doesn't participate... Are you "
"feeling all right?"
msgstr ""
"Qué conversación tan animada en la que Tenma no participa… ¿Te sientes bien?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:335
msgid "I am, it's just... These sands make me feel weird..."
msgstr "Sí, es solo que… estas arenas me hacen sentir rara…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:339
msgid ""
"Fitting, I imagine, given how you're about to visit the place where you died "
"fighting that Sky Dragon?"
msgstr ""
"Apropiado, imagino, considerando que estás a punto de visitar el lugar donde "
"moriste luchando contra ese Dragón del Cielo."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:343
msgid ""
"(angry) The 'other woman' did, don't kill me off like that! Now, onwards to "
"New Maat'Kare, that I can't wait to see a shadow again!"
msgstr ""
"(enojada) ¡La «otra mujer» lo hizo, no me mates así! Ahora, ¡en marcha hacia "
"Nueva Maat'Kare, que no puedo esperar a ver una sombra otra vez!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:365
msgid "Hey shrimp, there's something I want to ask you..."
msgstr "Oye camarón, hay algo que quiero preguntarte…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:369
msgid ""
"And what makes you think I'll tell you anything with such attitude? Call me "
"'princess', and I might tell you what you want."
msgstr ""
"¿Y qué te hace pensar que te voy a contar algo con esa actitud? Llámame "
"«princesa» y tal vez te diga lo que quieres."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:373
msgid ""
"Dream on... Seriously now: did Derceto tell you anything about how she met "
"Olokun? I'm not one to pry, but I confess that made me very curious. She's a "
"powerful sea queen and he's a human... A talented and worthy one, I'll give "
"him that."
msgstr ""
"Sigue soñando… En serio ahora: ¿Derceto te contó algo sobre cómo conoció a "
"Olokun? No soy de meterme donde no me llaman, pero confieso que eso me dio "
"mucha curiosidad. Ella es una poderosa reina del mar y él es un humano… Uno "
"talentoso y valioso, le doy eso."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:377
msgid "All this time and you still look down on us, uh?"
msgstr "¿Todo este tiempo y todavía nos miras por encima del hombro, eh?"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:381
msgid ""
"I didn't mean it like that, I swear. Besides, he's as talented and worthy as "
"any sage of Metheldur. Still, none of that changes the fact that she's a "
"mermaid and he's a human."
msgstr ""
"No lo dije en ese sentido, lo juro. Además, es tan talentoso y valioso como "
"cualquier sabio de Metheldur. Aun así, nada de eso cambia el hecho de que "
"ella es una sirena y él es un humano."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:385
msgid ""
"You know what? I'll tell you, if only to further shatter your narrow-minded "
"world view. Derceto loves Olokun, simple as that."
msgstr ""
"¿Sabes qué? Te lo voy a contar, solo para terminar de romper tu visión "
"estrecha del mundo. Derceto ama a Olokun, así de simple."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:389
msgid ""
"But <i>how</i> did they meet? Surely they've been through intense "
"experiences, for them to be brought together across so many barriers!"
msgstr ""
"Pero <i>cómo</i> se conocieron. ¡Seguro pasaron por experiencias intensas "
"para que los uniera a pesar de tantas barreras!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:393
msgid ""
"This is what I heard from them: Derceto once led an attack on an Arajunnan "
"sea city to punish them for preying on mermen living in the Vast Sea; that "
"the same day, Olokun's mother was in labour, but she was on a ship and she "
"couldn't go to a healing centre because of the merfolk's attack. Derceto "
"said that she heard the poor woman's scream just as the battle started; "
"realising that she was going to punish an innocent, she called off the "
"charge and went to her aid, healing the woman and delivering the baby in "
"safety."
msgstr ""
"Esto es lo que escuché de ellos: Derceto alguna vez lideró un ataque contra "
"una ciudad marítima arajunna para castigarlos por cazar sirenidos que vivían "
"en el Vasto Mar; ese mismo día, la madre de Olokun estaba de parto, pero "
"estaba en un barco y no pudo ir a un centro de sanación por el ataque de los "
"sirenidos. Derceto dijo que oyó el grito de la pobre mujer justo cuando "
"empezó la batalla; al darse cuenta de que iba a castigar a una inocente, "
"canceló el ataque y fue en su ayuda, sanándola y ayudando a dar a luz al "
"bebé a salvo."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:397
msgid ""
"Olokun, by his turn, told me that, when he was a child, he was very curious "
"about the 'sea-queen' who had saved both himself and his mother, and that he "
"used to spend hours every day walking or playing by the sea."
msgstr ""
"Por su parte, Olokun me contó que, cuando era niño, sentía mucha curiosidad "
"por la «reina del mar» que había salvado tanto a él como a su madre, y que "
"pasaba horas todos los días caminando o jugando junto al mar."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:401
msgid ""
"During one of those walks, Olokun found Leukothea - that mermaid we saw "
"approach him near Castelfrost - stranded on the beach, about to be killed by "
"some sailors, and he protected her. He thought that she was the 'sea-queen' "
"from his mother's stories, but then Leukothea took him to the real one. "
"Derceto told me she felt attracted to how peaceful and kind he was, even "
"though he was an aristocrat from a kingdom known for its military "
"traditions. She started to invite him to her court, and he, curious about "
"the merfolk, always accepted. Eventually they got... well, let's say more "
"intimate."
msgstr ""
"Durante una de esas caminatas, Olokun encontró a Leukothea —esa sirena que "
"vimos acercarse a él cerca de Castelfrost— varada en la playa, a punto de "
"ser asesinada por unos marineros, y la protegió. Pensó que ella era la "
"«reina del mar» de las historias de su madre, pero entonces Leukothea lo "
"llevó con la verdadera. Derceto me dijo que se sintió atraída por lo "
"pacífico y amable que era, aunque fuera un aristócrata de un reino conocido "
"por sus tradiciones militares. Empezó a invitarlo a su corte, y él, curioso "
"por los sirenidos, siempre aceptaba. Eventualmente se volvieron… bueno, "
"digamos más íntimos."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:405
msgid "Go on, continue the tale! Don't tell me that's all they told you!"
msgstr ""
"¡Sigue, continúa el cuento! ¡No me digas que eso es todo lo que te contaron!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:409
msgid ""
"I... (squinting at Cornelya) You seem to have gotten very interested out a "
"sudden... You naughty princess, you want to hear the spicy details, don't "
"you?"
msgstr ""
"Yo… (entrecerrando los ojos a Cornelya) De repente te has interesado mucho… "
"Princesa traviesa, quieres oír los detalles picantes, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:413
msgid ""
"(blushing) I-I... Well, I'm simply a demanding listener, I like stories rich "
"in details..."
msgstr ""
"(sonrojada) Yo-yo… Bueno, simplemente soy una oyente exigente, me gustan las "
"historias ricas en detalles…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:417
msgid "Yeah, right..."
msgstr "Sí, claro…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:439
msgid ""
"(sigh) I've told you already, Valerya, I've been doing very well so far "
"without you playing guardian Kami with me..."
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) Ya te lo dije, Valerya, he estado muy bien hasta ahora sin que "
"juegues a ser la kami guardiana conmigo…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:443
msgid ""
"Aw, of course I know that, dear. It's just that I'm happy to be travelling "
"alongside a cousin once again, after all this time... As distant as said "
"cousin may be."
msgstr ""
"Ay, claro que lo sé, querido. Solo estoy feliz de volver a viajar junto a un "
"primo después de tanto tiempo… por distante que sea dicho primo."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:447
msgid "Aetheryon did travel with us for a few weeks, though..."
msgstr "Aetheryon sí viajó con nosotros unas semanas, eso sí…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:451
msgid ""
"Oh, please, you're not really saying that snob is better company than you?"
msgstr ""
"Oh, por favor, ¿no estarás diciendo en serio que ese presumido es mejor "
"compañía que tú?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:455
msgid ""
"He's like that with everyone, Valerya. I've been trying to get a smile out "
"of him for years, but that's been my greatest failure."
msgstr ""
"Es así con todos, Valerya. Llevo años intentando sacarle una sonrisa, pero "
"esa ha sido mi mayor fracaso."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:459
msgid "Where you failed, Cornelya apparently succeeded, though..."
msgstr "Donde tú fallaste, al parecer Cornelya tuvo éxito…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:463
msgid "Don't...!"
msgstr "¡No…!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:467
msgid ""
"Wait, what?! You're telling me that prissy princess made him smile? "
"Kenshiro, you traitor!"
msgstr ""
"¡Espera, qué?! ¿Me estás diciendo que esa princesa presumida lo hizo "
"sonreír? ¡Kenshiro, traidor!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:471
msgid "(presumptuous smirk)"
msgstr "(sonrisa presumida)"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:486
msgid "Hey, we saw guys like those when we met Valerya in the Firecloud Peak!"
msgstr ""
"¡Oye, vimos tipos como esos cuando conocimos a Valerya en la Cumbre de la "
"Nube de Fuego!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:490
msgid ""
"Indeed, those are minotaurs. At the time, I was surprised to find them so "
"far from Netjer-Ta, as I thought this was their original homeland, but..."
msgstr ""
"En efecto, son minotauros. En ese momento me sorprendió encontrarlos tan "
"lejos de Netjer-Ta, ya que pensaba que era su patria original, pero…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:494
msgid ""
"...They've actually came from the Great Continent into Netjer-Ta, brought "
"here aeons ago by the ancient order of mages and historians, the Windsong."
msgstr ""
"…en realidad vinieron del Gran Continente a Netjer-Ta, traídos aquí hace "
"eones por la antigua orden de magos e historiadores, las Hijas del Viento."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:498
msgid "Have you ever met them? The Windsong, I mean."
msgstr "¿Alguna vez las has conocido? Me refiero a las Hijas del Viento."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:502
msgid ""
"I haven't, and going by the witness tales I have come across, I don't think "
"I want to."
msgstr ""
"No, y a juzgar por los relatos de testigos que he encontrado, no creo que "
"quiera."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:506
msgid ""
"Really? From the stories Olokun told me of them, they seem a pretty cool "
"order..."
msgstr ""
"¿En serio? Por las historias que Olokun me contó de ellas, parecen una orden "
"bastante genial…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:510
msgid ""
"A very long time ago, maybe. Nowadays, the few stories involving the "
"Windsong paint them as self-centred, ruthless even. True, these stories "
"could be biased; plenty of cultures out there are suspicious of women, let "
"alone a whole order of them. But the Windsong themselves haven't had a "
"worthy deed to their name in a very long time... not like they once did, in "
"any case."
msgstr ""
"Hace muchísimo tiempo, tal vez. Hoy en día, las pocas historias que "
"involucran a las Hijas del Viento las pintan como egocéntricas, incluso "
"despiadadas. Es cierto, esas historias podrían estar sesgadas; muchas "
"culturas desconfían de las mujeres, y mucho más de toda una orden de ellas. "
"Pero las propias Hijas del Viento no han tenido una hazaña digna de mención "
"en mucho tiempo… no como solían tener, en todo caso."

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:553
msgid "Och, friend, your city sure is coveted by many, innit?"
msgstr "Och, amigo, tu ciudad seguro es codiciada por muchos, ¿no es así?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:557
msgid ""
"It's true we're often attacked by orcish, minotaur, even vampire bands, but "
"this attack is a bit too massive to be considered normal... Sorry, friends, "
"I was hoping we would have a warmer welcome, but we won't have any rest "
"until we completely defeat these armies."
msgstr ""
"Es cierto que a menudo nos atacan bandas orcas, minotauros, incluso "
"vampiros, pero este ataque es demasiado masivo para considerarlo normal… Lo "
"siento, amigos, esperaba que tuviéramos una bienvenida más cálida, pero no "
"tendremos descanso hasta derrotar completamente a estos ejércitos."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:561
msgid ""
"No need to apologise for sending us to battle; I wanted to see how the "
"people of this continent fight anyway..."
msgstr ""
"No hace falta que te disculpes por enviarnos a la batalla; de todos modos "
"quería ver cómo luchan las gentes de este continente…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:565
msgid ""
"Geesh, I can barely look at that city... Why is it so shining? Are its walls "
"made of gold?"
msgstr ""
"Cielos, apenas puedo mirar esa ciudad… ¿Por qué brilla tanto? ¿Sus murallas "
"están hechas de oro?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:569
msgid ""
"That's a magical dome which maintains the weather inside New Maat'Kare "
"always cool and humid; this serves not only for comfort, but, also, to keep "
"our farms always fertile. That was how we've managed to survive in this "
"desert for so long."
msgstr ""
"Es una cúpula mágica que mantiene el clima dentro de Nueva Maat'Kare siempre "
"fresco y húmedo; esto no solo sirve para la comodidad, sino también para "
"mantener nuestras granjas siempre fértiles. Así hemos logrado sobrevivir en "
"este desierto tanto tiempo."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:575
msgid "Defeat the besiegers of New Maat'Kare"
msgstr "Derrotar a los asediadores de Nueva Maat'Kare"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:633
msgid ""
"Who else comes to our city's walls now...? Wait, that's... It's Olokun! At "
"long last you returned, my boy, I feared I had sent you to your doom!"
msgstr ""
"¿Quién más se acerca ahora a las murallas de nuestra ciudad…? Espera, ese "
"es… ¡Es Olokun! ¡Por fin regresaste, muchacho, temía haberte enviado a tu "
"perdición!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:637
msgid ""
"(chuckling) Did you really have so little faith in one trained by you, "
"Master Ankhmare? Though I must say that I owe much of my success to my "
"friends."
msgstr ""
"(riendo) ¿De verdad tenías tan poca fe en alguien entrenado por ti, maestro "
"Ankhmare? Aunque debo decir que debo gran parte de mi éxito a mis amigos."

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:641
msgid "Success? Could you possibly mean...?"
msgstr "¿Éxito? ¿Acaso quieres decir…?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:645
msgid ""
"Yes, Master, I've found the One From the Prophecy: this girl, Tenma Yozora, "
"is the person in whose form Myra has been reborn."
msgstr ""
"Sí, maestro, he encontrado a la Elegida de la Profecía: esta chica, Tenma "
"Yozora, es la persona en cuya forma Myra ha renacido."

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:649
msgid ""
"This girl...! (to his soldiers) Soldiers and mages of New Maat'Kare, "
"rejoice! Our brother Olokun Maahes has succeeded in his mission, and has "
"guided our ancient heroine back to her people! Akhen's Prophecy was true, "
"Myra of Hiera'Shirsha has returned!"
msgstr ""
"¡Esta chica…! (a sus soldados) ¡Soldados y magos de Nueva Maat'Kare, "
"regocíjense! ¡Nuestro hermano Olokun Maahes ha tenido éxito en su misión y "
"ha guiado a nuestra antigua heroína de vuelta a su pueblo! ¡La Profecía de "
"Akhen era cierta, Myra de Hiera’Shirsha ha regresado!"

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:657
msgid ""
"Could it be...?! If that is true, then the orcs and the minotaurs stand no "
"chance!"
msgstr ""
"¿Será posible…?! ¡Si eso es cierto, entonces los orcos y los minotauros no "
"tienen ninguna oportunidad!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:661
msgid "Geez, Olokun, couldn't you have been a little more discreet?"
msgstr "Cielos, Olokun, ¿no podías haber sido un poco más discreto?"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:665
msgid "(chuckling) He was just eager to boast his success to everyone..."
msgstr "(riendo) Solo estaba ansioso por presumir su éxito ante todos…"

#. [message], speaker=Bogor
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:669
msgid ""
"Those stinking Maat'Karian vermin have become noisy so out of a sudden, but "
"let them enjoy themselves while they still can; soon this Silent Desert will "
"really deserve its name! Orcs, attack with everything you've got!"
msgstr ""
"¡Esos apestosos vermin de Maat'Kare se han puesto ruidosos de repente, pero "
"que se diviertan mientras puedan; pronto este Desierto Silencioso merecerá "
"realmente su nombre! ¡Orcos, ataquen con todo lo que tienen!"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:687
msgid ""
"Impressive... Such unusual power, such connection to nature's energy... You "
"can't be anyone other than..."
msgstr ""
"Impresionante… Un poder tan inusual, una conexión tan fuerte con la energía "
"de la naturaleza… No puedes ser otra que…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:691
msgid ""
"(impatient) You will pardon me, old man, but I'm having a really bad day, "
"this place gives me horrible memories already, so I don't want to hear any "
"more of this 'Myra' crap for the next few hours, all right?"
msgstr ""
"(impaciente) Perdóneme, anciano, pero estoy teniendo un día realmente malo, "
"este lugar ya me trae horribles recuerdos, así que no quiero oír más "
"tonterías sobre «Myra» en las próximas horas, ¿de acuerdo?"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:695
msgid "I bet she doesn't see the irony in her own words..."
msgstr "Apuesto a que no ve la ironía en sus propias palabras…"

#. [message], speaker=Umbrius
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:713
msgid ""
"You, lady! Apologies for bothering you in the midst of battle, but I "
"couldn't ignore your presence, or your faerie aura; are you an elven sylph "
"from beyond the blue seas?"
msgstr ""
"¡Usted, señora! Perdón por molestarla en medio de la batalla, pero no pude "
"ignorar su presencia ni su aura feérica; ¿es usted una sílfide élfica de más "
"allá de los mares azules?"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:717
msgid ""
"(suddenly uneasy) You've made a mistake, faun; sylphs don't wield weapons, "
"nor do they devote themselves to shedding the blood of others."
msgstr ""
"(de repente incómoda) Te has equivocado, fauno; las sílfides no empuñan "
"armas, ni se dedican a derramar la sangre de otros."

#. [message], speaker=Umbrius
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:721
msgid ""
"Still, I have no doubt that the blood of the First flows in your veins; even "
"if you walk the warrior's path, the faerie path is definitely open to-"
msgstr ""
"Aun así, no tengo duda de que la sangre de los Primeros corre por tus venas; "
"aunque sigas el camino del guerrero, el camino feérico definitivamente está "
"abierto para—"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:725
msgid ""
"You bother me, faun! As skilled as I am, I will end up dead if you keep "
"distracting me like this!"
msgstr ""
"¡Me molestas, fauno! Por hábil que sea, terminaré muerta si sigues "
"distrayéndome así!"

#. [message], speaker=Umbrius
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:729
msgid ""
"In this case, I beg your pardon, lady – but I humbly ask you to hear me when "
"this battle's over; while you may not know it right now, there's an entire "
"nation in need of words from one such as you."
msgstr ""
"En ese caso, le pido perdón, señora —pero humildemente le pido que me "
"escuche cuando termine esta batalla; aunque ahora no lo sepa, hay toda una "
"nación que necesita palabras de alguien como usted."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:733
msgid ""
"Fine then, have it your way... By the Seven Arrows, the people of this "
"continent sure love their 'Chosen Ones'..."
msgstr ""
"Está bien, como quieras… Por las Siete Flechas, la gente de este continente "
"realmente ama a sus «Elegidos»…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:737
msgid "You called him 'faun'; do you know his people? "
msgstr "Lo llamaste «fauno»; ¿conoces a su pueblo?"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:741
msgid ""
"I've read about them in Metheldur's Library, but this is the first time I "
"see one with my own eyes. In ages long past, elves, fauns and faeries were "
"close friends, in spite of living so far apart, but those ties were severed "
"by time and catastrophe."
msgstr ""
"He leído sobre ellos en la Biblioteca de Metheldur, pero es la primera vez "
"que veo uno con mis propios ojos. En edades muy lejanas, elfos, faunos y "
"feéricos eran amigos cercanos, a pesar de vivir tan lejos unos de otros, "
"pero esos lazos fueron rotos por el tiempo y la catástrofe."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:759
msgid ""
"It doesn't matter how many centuries pass, this city remains the same... but "
"I prefer it that way. It's comforting to find a place that remains familiar "
"as the centuries go by."
msgstr ""
"No importa cuántos siglos pasen, esta ciudad sigue siendo la misma… pero lo "
"prefiero así. Es reconfortante encontrar un lugar que permanece familiar a "
"medida que pasan los siglos."

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:763
msgid ""
"You, who wield fire like an extension of yourself, and who casts the Sedjet "
"Netjer with such potency, could you be the famous Crimson Sorceress who's "
"visited our city in the past?"
msgstr ""
"Usted, que maneja el fuego como una extensión de sí misma y que lanza el "
"Sedjet Netjer con tanta potencia, ¿podría ser la famosa Hechicera Carmesí "
"que visitó nuestra ciudad en el pasado?"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:767
msgid "The one and only, pleased to meet you!"
msgstr "¡La única e inigualable, un placer conocerlo!"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:771
msgid ""
"I've read, like every other student of the Academy, about the legendary "
"fight you had with Star Master Rahothep; it's an honour to meet you. When "
"this battle ends, I'd like to invite you to drink tea with me; one doesn't "
"always have the chance to meet such a legend in flesh and blood."
msgstr ""
"He leído, como todos los estudiantes de la Academia, sobre la legendaria "
"lucha que tuvo con el Maestro Estelar Rahothep; es un honor conocerla. "
"Cuando termine esta batalla, me gustaría invitarla a tomar té conmigo; no "
"siempre se tiene la oportunidad de conocer a una leyenda en carne y hueso."

#. [message], speaker=Bogor
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:784
msgid ""
"A thousand bloody curses on you, Maat'Karians! You look down on us, but "
"you're the worst of all!"
msgstr ""
"¡Mil maldiciones sangrientas sobre ustedes, maatkarianos! ¡Nos miran por "
"encima del hombro, pero son los peores de todos!"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:788
msgid ""
"You've been attacking, wounding and insulting us from the moment you sighted "
"this city, Chief Bogor, but you haven't told us why. Has New Maat'Kare ever "
"broken the treaty with the Red Moon Clan? Have we ever left you helpless "
"against a threat you couldn't defeat on your own?"
msgstr ""
"Ha estado atacándonos, hiriéndonos e insultándonos desde el momento en que "
"avistó esta ciudad, jefe Bogor, pero no nos ha dicho por qué. ¿Ha roto Nueva "
"Maat'Kare alguna vez el tratado con el Clan Luna Roja? ¿Alguna vez los hemos "
"dejado desamparados ante una amenaza que no pudieran derrotar solos?"

#. [message], speaker=Bogor
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:792
msgid "(fuming) And you still have the audacity to say that...!"
msgstr "(furioso) ¡Y todavía tiene la audacia de decir eso…!"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:796
msgid ""
"I suspect there's more to his words than it may initially seem... Please, "
"knock him unconscious and bring him to our city; there are a few questions I "
"want to ask him..."
msgstr ""
"Sospecho que hay más en sus palabras de lo que parece a simple vista… Por "
"favor, déjenlo inconsciente y tráiganlo a nuestra ciudad; hay unas preguntas "
"que quiero hacerle…"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:809
msgid "Agh! Apologies, fellow masters, but I have to retire now..."
msgstr "¡Agh! Perdón, compañeros maestros, pero debo retirarme ahora…"

#. [message], speaker=Akhetamun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:826
msgid ""
"Argh! Would that I could fight longer, friends, but I'm forced to withdraw "
"now..."
msgstr ""
"¡Argh! Ojalá pudiera luchar más tiempo, amigos, pero me veo forzado a "
"retirarme ahora…"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:830
msgid ""
"Please do it, my friend; we cannot afford to lose our greatest Crimson "
"Master now!"
msgstr ""
"Por favor hazlo, amigo; ¡no podemos permitirnos perder a nuestro mayor "
"Maestro Carmesí ahora!"

#. [message], speaker=Shirahel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:847
msgid "Ouch! You brute, do you really think I'll go down that eas-"
msgstr "¡Ouch! Bruto, ¿de verdad crees que voy a caer tan fáci—"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:851
msgid ""
"Shirahel, please don't! You're too wounded to continue, and we cannot afford "
"to lose you now!"
msgstr ""
"¡Shirahel, por favor no! Estás demasiado herido para continuar, ¡y no "
"podemos permitirnos perderte ahora!"

#. [message], speaker=Ramoses
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:868
msgid ""
"Arrgghh! You damn barbarian, do you think that's enough to take me down...?!"
msgstr ""
"¡Arrgghh! Maldito bárbaro, ¿crees que eso es suficiente para derribarme…?"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:872
msgid ""
"Lord Ramoses, please withdraw from battle; you clearly cannot continue any "
"longer, and New Maat'Kare cannot afford to lose its best general now."
msgstr ""
"Señor Ramoses, por favor retírese de la batalla; claramente no puede "
"continuar más, y Nueva Maat'Kare no puede permitirse perder a su mejor "
"general ahora."

#. [message], speaker=Shirahel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:876
msgid ""
"He's right, Lord Ramoses; please, spare yourself this time, withdrawing from "
"this battle shall not be seen as an act of cowardice."
msgstr ""
"Tiene razón, señor Ramoses; por favor, perdónese esta vez, retirarse de esta "
"batalla no será visto como un acto de cobardía."

#. [message], speaker=Ramoses
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:880
msgid ""
"Argh... If you so insist, then I shall leave the rest to the summoning "
"masters..."
msgstr ""
"Argh… Si tanto insisten, entonces dejaré el resto a los maestros invocadores…"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:893
msgid ""
"Finally, this battle is over; it's been a while since we last had such a "
"vicious fight at our own gates... Let the wounded be healed; Olokun, please "
"come in with your friends, I'll order food and drink for all of you. When "
"you've restored your energies, I shall call on a gathering at the Wadjet "
"Hall with the Lords and the Sages; there's much to be discussed, and much to "
"be decided..."
msgstr ""
"Por fin, esta batalla terminó; ha pasado un tiempo desde que tuvimos un "
"combate tan feroz en nuestras propias puertas… Que curen a los heridos; "
"Olokun, por favor entra con tus amigos, ordenaré comida y bebida para todos. "
"Cuando hayan recuperado sus energías, convocaré una reunión en el Salón "
"Wadjet con los Señores y los Sabios; hay mucho que discutir y mucho que "
"decidir…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:897
msgid "Don't whine now, Tenma, you came here on your own accord..."
msgstr "No te quejes ahora, Tenma, viniste aquí por tu propia voluntad…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:901
msgid "(sigh) I know, I know..."
msgstr "(suspiro) Lo sé, lo sé…"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:922
msgid "How could I fail... to protect New Maat'Kare...?"
msgstr "¿Cómo pude fallar… en proteger Nueva Maat'Kare…?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:926
msgid ""
"Master, no!!! How could we let him die?! Without his guidance, we'll never "
"fulfil the Seer's Prophecy!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maestro, no! ¿Cómo pudimos dejarlo morir?! ¡Sin su guía, nunca cumpliremos "
"la Profecía del Vidente!"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/27B_The_Legends_Cradle.cfg:939
msgid ""
"More enemies coming from the north and the west! It's no good, even if we "
"prevail against so many foes, our human numbers will be too depleted!"
msgstr ""
"¡Más enemigos viniendo del norte y del oeste! No sirve de nada, aunque "
"prevalecamos contra tantos enemigos, ¡nuestros números humanos quedarán "
"demasiado diezmados!"

#. [scenario], id=28_Chosen_Paths
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:5
msgid "Chosen Paths"
msgstr "Caminos Elegidos"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:125
msgid ""
"My fellow Maat'Karians, you must have heard already, from the rumours "
"running the city, the reason I have called on this meeting. I wish to start "
"by reading Akhen's Prophecy:"
msgstr ""
"Compañeros maatkarianos, ya deben haber oído, por los rumores que corren por "
"la ciudad, la razón por la que convoqué esta reunión. Quiero empezar leyendo "
"la Profecía de Akhen:"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:129
msgid ""
"'Our history has been threatened since before its very founding by a being "
"of immense power: the High Dragon of the Sky, Svarballi. Four times has he "
"attempted to destroy the world, four times has he been thwarted: first by "
"the High Dragons of Fire and Water; second, by Maat of Hiera'Shirsha, who "
"sealed him within the Sky Soul; third, by our great heroine, Myra; and "
"fourth, by Menon Hekare and myself, Akhen Wadjet.'"
msgstr ""
"«Nuestra historia ha estado amenazada desde antes de su fundación por un ser "
"de inmenso poder: el Alto Dragón del Cielo, Svarballi. Cuatro veces ha "
"intentado destruir el mundo, cuatro veces ha sido frustrado: primero por los "
"Grandes Dragones de Fuego y Agua; segundo, por Maat de Hiera’Shirsha, quien "
"lo selló dentro del Alma del Cielo; tercero, por nuestra gran heroína, Myra; "
"y cuarto, por Menon Hekare y yo mismo, Akhen Wadjet.»"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:133
msgid ""
"'Why wasn't he ever decisively destroyed, you may ask? None of us could "
"accomplish the feat, not even the Fire and Water Dragons, for Svarballi can "
"only be destroyed by a power similar to the one that created him: the power "
"of the Ancient Ones, creators of this universe. Locked inside its cell, the "
"Sky Dragon awaits patiently for the next chance of destroying this world...'"
msgstr ""
"«¿Por qué nunca fue destruido de forma decisiva, podrían preguntar? Ninguno "
"de nosotros pudo lograrlo, ni siquiera los Dragones de Fuego y Agua, pues "
"Svarballi solo puede ser destruido por un poder similar al que lo creó: el "
"poder de los Antiguos, creadores de este universo. Encerrado en su celda, el "
"Dragón del Cielo espera pacientemente la próxima oportunidad de destruir "
"este mundo…»"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:137
msgid ""
"'But he shall not threaten our world forever. For every battle against "
"Svarballi, a new light was shed on how he may be destroyed for good. We must "
"look at the past and preserve its wisdom, for one day, a person will be born "
"who will need it. She will be our heroine reborn, and she will be the vessel "
"of Nature's wrath once more; when that happens, she will have the power and "
"the means to finally slay the dragon.''"
msgstr ""
"«Pero no amenazará nuestro mundo para siempre. Por cada batalla contra "
"Svarballi, una nueva luz se arrojó sobre cómo podría ser destruido para "
"siempre. Debemos mirar al pasado y preservar su sabiduría, pues un día "
"nacerá una persona que la necesitará. Ella será nuestra heroína renacida, y "
"volverá a ser el recipiente de la ira de la Naturaleza; cuando eso ocurra, "
"tendrá el poder y los medios para finalmente matar al dragón.»"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:141
msgid ""
"Now, you may be asking yourselves what this prophecy has to do with this "
"meeting. I believe, my friends, that the person whose coming Akhen Wadjet "
"has foreseen, the Dragon-Slayer who will be Myra reborn, is this young girl, "
"whom Olokun Maahes has brought from the Great Continent."
msgstr ""
"Ahora, tal vez se pregunten qué tiene que ver esta profecía con esta "
"reunión. Creo, amigos míos, que la persona cuya llegada predijo Akhen "
"Wadjet, la Matadragones que será Myra renacida, es esta joven chica que "
"Olokun Maahes ha traído del Gran Continente."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:145
msgid "<i>(surprised murmurs amongst Sages and Lords)</i>"
msgstr "<i>(murmullos de sorpresa entre Sabios y Señores)</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:149
msgid ""
"Master Ankhmare, we all know of your research on Akhen Wadjet's writings, "
"and of your belief in the absolute truth of his words. But I hope you "
"understand that not all of us may share your faith in a 'prophecy' made "
"without any basis in established lore. Souls can be summoned in ethereal "
"form, bodies can be reanimated, even a corpse's memories can be brought to "
"surface; but no mortal can be truly reborn, not in a living body, let alone "
"with memories and skills of their past lives. As a master of the Umbra Arts, "
"I should know that well."
msgstr ""
"Maestro Ankhmare, todos conocemos su investigación sobre los escritos de "
"Akhen Wadjet y su creencia en la verdad absoluta de sus palabras. Pero "
"espero que entienda que no todos compartimos su fe en una «profecía» hecha "
"sin base en el saber establecido. Las almas pueden invocarse en forma "
"etérea, los cuerpos pueden reanimarse, incluso los recuerdos de un cadáver "
"pueden traerse a la superficie; pero ningún mortal puede renacer "
"verdaderamente, no en un cuerpo vivo, y mucho menos con recuerdos y "
"habilidades de vidas pasadas. Como maestro de las Artes Umbra, debería "
"saberlo bien."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:153
msgid ""
"Master Wesir, Tenma is a seventeen-years-old girl raised in a farm village "
"from a culture that has little familiarity with magic; I've seen this girl "
"summon elementals far stronger than our own almost at the same time she "
"awoke her powers; not only that, but she's shown signs that she has memories "
"from her past life..."
msgstr ""
"Maestro Wesir, Tenma es una chica de diecisiete años criada en un pueblo "
"agrícola de una cultura con poca familiaridad con la magia; he visto a esta "
"chica invocar elementales mucho más fuertes que los nuestros casi al mismo "
"tiempo que despertó sus poderes; no solo eso, sino que ha mostrado señales "
"de que tiene recuerdos de su vida pasada…"

#. [message], speaker=Ramoses
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:157
msgid ""
"(chuckling) I see... Then allow me to ask her, why didn't you return before? "
"Why didn't you destroy the Sky Soul before it forced us to move into this "
"desert?"
msgstr ""
"(riendo) Ya veo… Entonces permítame preguntarle, ¿por qué no regresó antes? "
"¿Por qué no destruyó el Alma del Cielo antes de que nos obligara a mudarnos "
"a este desierto?"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:161
msgid ""
"If I may have the word, I can answer your question, lord. I've had the "
"chance to meet Myra's spirit in the Ocean's Heart, the very same temple "
"where she obtained the Trident of the Seas. According to herself, she "
"couldn't physically manifest onto this plane without aid; after Akhen's "
"death, there wasn't anyone left on this world who could even hear her beyond "
"certain places that bore a special connection to the natural place - such as "
"the Ocean's Heart itself."
msgstr ""
"Si me permiten la palabra, puedo responder su pregunta, señor. He tenido la "
"oportunidad de encontrarme con el espíritu de Myra en el Corazón del Océano, "
"el mismo templo donde obtuvo el Tridente de los Mares. Según ella misma, no "
"podía manifestarse físicamente en este plano sin ayuda; después de la muerte "
"de Akhen, no quedaba nadie en este mundo que pudiera siquiera oírla más allá "
"de ciertos lugares que tenían una conexión especial con el lugar natural —"
"como el propio Corazón del Océano."

#. [message], speaker=Shirahel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:165
msgid ""
"Fine, let us work with the premise that this girl is truly Myra reborn. What "
"does she have that made her, and no one else in all the millennia passed "
"since her death, a vessel for Myra's soul?"
msgstr ""
"Bien, trabajemos con la premisa de que esta chica es verdaderamente Myra "
"renacida. ¿Qué tiene ella que la hizo, y no a nadie más en todos los "
"milenios transcurridos desde su muerte, un recipiente para el alma de Myra?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:169
msgid ""
"I admit, Master Shirahel, that I still haven't found the answer to that "
"question, but-"
msgstr ""
"Admito, maestro Shirahel, que todavía no he encontrado la respuesta a esa "
"pregunta, pero—"

#. [message], speaker=Ramoses
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:173
msgid ""
"(chuckling) You expect us to believe your theory when not even you can "
"properly explain it? Frankly, you really <i>are</i> Master Ankhmare's "
"disciple, aren't you..."
msgstr ""
"(riendo) ¿Esperas que creamos en tu teoría cuando ni siquiera tú puedes "
"explicarla adecuadamente? Francamente, realmente <i>eres</i> discípulo del "
"maestro Ankhmare, ¿verdad…?"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:177
msgid ""
"(angry) You may choose not to believe us, Lord Ramoses, but I will not "
"tolerate insults, especially when they're motivated by sheer spite and "
"ignorance!"
msgstr ""
"(enojado) Puede elegir no creernos, señor Ramoses, ¡pero no toleraré "
"insultos, especialmente cuando están motivados por puro rencor e ignorancia!"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:181
msgid ""
"Apologies, Master Ankhmare, but you can't blame us for not always following "
"your ideas and projects – especially after the disaster of that expedition "
"to the Caves of Light!"
msgstr ""
"Perdón, maestro Ankhmare, pero no puede culparnos por no seguir siempre sus "
"ideas y proyectos —¡especialmente después del desastre de esa expedición a "
"las Cuevas de la Luz!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:185
msgid ""
"Excuse me, everyone... but should <i>I</i> have a word to say about myself "
"too?"
msgstr ""
"¿Perdón, todos…? ¿acaso <i>yo</i> no debería tener derecho a decir algo "
"sobre mí misma también?"

#. [message], speaker=Shirahel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:189
msgid "Fair enough. Explain, then, why do you think that you are Myra?"
msgstr "Está bien. Explícame entonces, ¿por qué crees que eres Myra?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:193
msgid ""
"First of all, I'm not Myra; I'm Tenma Yozora of Kodakuni, daughter of Yusuke "
"and Motoko, and I'm just a Yasai girl. I just happen to have the soul of "
"your heroine within myself, and from her I've got my powers and my ability "
"to speak with the spirits of nature."
msgstr ""
"Primero que nada, no soy Myra; soy Tenma Yozora de Kodakuni, hija de Yusuke "
"y Motoko, y solo soy una chica yasai. Solo resulta que tengo el alma de su "
"heroína dentro de mí, y de ella obtuve mis poderes y mi capacidad para "
"hablar con los espíritus de la naturaleza."

#. [message], speaker=Akhetamun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:197
msgid ""
"You still haven't answered Lady Shirahel's question, young lady; what makes "
"you believe that you're Myra's reincarnation, and not just a mage prodigy?"
msgstr ""
"Aún no has respondido la pregunta de la dama Shirahel, jovencita; ¿qué te "
"hace creer que eres la reencarnación de Myra, y no solo una maga prodigio?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:201
msgid ""
"Could you explain why do you think that you are yourself, mister? I simply "
"know who I am. As on why Myra's soul has chosen this body in particular to "
"return to this world... Maybe there was something about my birth which my "
"parents haven't told anyone."
msgstr ""
"¿Podría explicarme por qué cree que es usted mismo, señor? Simplemente sé "
"quién soy. En cuanto a por qué el alma de Myra eligió este cuerpo en "
"particular para regresar a este mundo… tal vez haya algo sobre mi nacimiento "
"que mis padres no le han contado a nadie."

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:205
msgid ""
"(sigh) In the spirit of fairness, I shall lend my own knowledge on souls to "
"try and explain Master Ankhmare's theory. A child can be influenced by magic "
"currents even in their mother's belly, should the mother be exposed to "
"unique arcane anomalies. I hear your people, these 'Yasai', are not familiar "
"with magic, so I assume there are no such anomalies in their homeland..."
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) En aras de la equidad, prestaré mi propio conocimiento sobre almas "
"para intentar explicar la teoría del maestro Ankhmare. Un niño puede ser "
"influido por corrientes mágicas incluso en el vientre de su madre, si ella "
"estuvo expuesta a anomalías arcanas únicas. Tengo entendido que su pueblo, "
"estos «yasai», no está familiarizado con la magia, así que supongo que no "
"hay tales anomalías en su tierra natal…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:209
msgid ""
"Er, sorry to interrupt, but perhaps I should tell you that I wasn't born "
"<i>in</i> my country. My parents had been on a hunting expedition when they "
"got lost in the wilderness; in fact, they remained lost during my mother's "
"whole pregnancy, and I was born in the place where they stayed: a mountain "
"called Kamishiro, which-"
msgstr ""
"Eh, perdón por interrumpir, pero tal vez debería decirles que no nací <i>en</"
"i> mi país. Mis padres estaban en una expedición de caza cuando se perdieron "
"en la naturaleza; de hecho, permanecieron perdidos durante todo el embarazo "
"de mi madre, y yo nací en el lugar donde se quedaron: una montaña llamada "
"Kamishiro, que—"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:213
msgid ""
"(surprised) Hold on, Mount Kamishiro?! Tenma, why didn't you tell me that "
"before?!"
msgstr ""
"(sorprendido) ¡Espera, Monte Kamishiro?! ¡Tenma, por qué no me dijiste eso "
"antes?!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:217
msgid "Probably because you've never asked? Besides, why does it even matter?"
msgstr ""
"¿Probablemente porque nunca lo preguntaste? Además, ¿por qué importa "
"siquiera?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:221
msgid ""
"I visited that mountain before reaching Kodakuni; Kamishiro is how your "
"people call it, but I knew it by another name, the one recorded in our "
"scrolls: Mount Hursag, the mountain where the crystallised body of the Water "
"Dragon Nitiballi, which became the Fountain of Life, lies."
msgstr ""
"Visité esa montaña antes de llegar a Kodakuni; Kamishiro es como la llaman "
"tu gente, pero yo la conocía por otro nombre, el que está registrado en "
"nuestros pergaminos: Monte Hursag, la montaña donde yace el cuerpo "
"cristalizado del Dragón de Agua Nitiballi, que se convirtió en la Fuente de "
"la Vida."

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:225
msgid ""
"Then...! My girl, it was by drinking from the Fountain of Life in Mount "
"Hursag that Myra gained her connection to the spirits of nature; but if your "
"mother drank from those same waters during her pregnancy, then your very "
"body must've become infused with the purest natural currents. This is far "
"deeper than a mere connection... and certainly it would explain why your "
"body was able to shelter Myra's soul - which, as we have always believed, "
"was merged with the natural plane after her death - when none other could!"
msgstr ""
"¡Entonces…! Mi niña, fue al beber de la Fuente de la Vida en el Monte Hursag "
"que Myra obtuvo su conexión con los espíritus de la naturaleza; pero si tu "
"madre bebió de esas mismas aguas durante su embarazo, entonces tu propio "
"cuerpo debió impregnarse de las corrientes naturales más puras. Esto es "
"mucho más profundo que una mera conexión… ¡y sin duda explicaría por qué tu "
"cuerpo pudo albergar el alma de Myra —que, como siempre hemos creído, se "
"fusionó con el plano natural tras su muerte— cuando ningún otro pudo!"

#. [message], speaker=Ramoses
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:229
msgid ""
"Still, according to the old scrolls, the Fountain of Life had already lost "
"much of its power even when Myra drank from it, and more than forty "
"centuries have passed since then!"
msgstr ""
"Aun así, según los pergaminos antiguos, la Fuente de la Vida ya había "
"perdido gran parte de su poder incluso cuando Myra bebió de ella, ¡y han "
"pasado más de cuarenta siglos desde entonces!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:233
msgid ""
"Notwithstanding, a mere six centuries ago the Fountain's waters were still "
"strong enough to slow my aging when I drank from them."
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, hace apenas seis siglos las aguas de la Fuente todavía eran lo "
"suficientemente fuertes como para ralentizar mi envejecimiento cuando bebí "
"de ellas."

#. [message], speaker=Ramoses
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:237
msgid ""
"And what about Tenma Yozora's mother, then? Does she exhibit similar powers?"
msgstr ""
"¿Y qué hay de la madre de Tenma Yozora, entonces? ¿Ella muestra poderes "
"similares?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:241
msgid "I have no idea, she died when I was a baby."
msgstr "No tengo idea, murió cuando yo era bebé."

#. [message], speaker=Ramoses
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:245
msgid ""
"Too early an end for someone who should've survived the centuries, wouldn't "
"you say?"
msgstr ""
"Un final demasiado temprano para alguien que debería haber sobrevivido "
"siglos, ¿no crees?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:249
msgid "She died by a Wesnothian sword, you <i>asshole</i>."
msgstr "Murió por una espada wesnothiana, <i>imbécil</i>."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:253
msgid ""
"(holding her laughter) I can attest, Lord Ramoses, that the Fountain's "
"powers only shield you from the ravages of time, not the aggression of "
"swords or the like."
msgstr ""
"(conteniendo la risa) Puedo atestiguar, señor Ramoses, que los poderes de la "
"Fuente solo te protegen de los estragos del tiempo, no de la agresión de "
"espadas ni cosas por el estilo."

#. [message], speaker=Shirahel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:257
msgid ""
"Peace, friends, peace! Tell us, Master Wesir, does that information shed any "
"light on your doubts?"
msgstr ""
"¡Paz, amigos, paz! Díganos, maestro Wesir, ¿esa información arroja alguna "
"luz sobre sus dudas?"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:261
msgid ""
"It does, I'll admit that much. So let us move on to the next logical "
"conclusion: according to the prophecy, this young lady should be able to "
"destroy the Sky Soul; we could take her to the jewel's chambers right now, "
"so that she may destroy it once and for all and at last free our city from "
"this burden. What do you say about that?"
msgstr ""
"Así es, lo admito. Entonces pasemos a la siguiente conclusión lógica: según "
"la profecía, esta joven debería ser capaz de destruir el Alma del Cielo; "
"podríamos llevarla ahora mismo a las cámaras de la joya, para que la "
"destruya de una vez por todas y por fin libere a nuestra ciudad de esta "
"carga. ¿Qué opinan de eso?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:265
msgid "Sure, show me the way and I'll hit it until it's dust."
msgstr "Claro, muéstrame el camino y le daré hasta que quede polvo."

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:269
msgid ""
"Wait, wait! The Sky Soul is a delicate prison created by High Ascendant Maat "
"with long-lost arts, surely it can't be destroyed with a method as mundane "
"as bashing it until it breaks! We have to ascertain that her powers can "
"disrupt it, or else we may release the Sky Dragon by accident!"
msgstr ""
"¡Espera, espera! El Alma del Cielo es una prisión delicada creada por la "
"Alta Ascendente Maat con artes perdidas hace mucho; ¡seguramente no puede "
"destruirse con un método tan mundano como golpearla hasta romperla! Tenemos "
"que comprobar que sus poderes pueden perturbarla, ¡o podríamos liberar al "
"Dragón del Cielo por accidente!"

#. [message], speaker=Ramoses
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:273
msgid ""
"'We have to ascertain'? Does that mean that even you are uncertain of her "
"capacity, Master Ankhmare?"
msgstr ""
"¿«Tenemos que comprobar»? ¿Eso significa que ni siquiera usted está seguro "
"de su capacidad, maestro Ankhmare?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhetamun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:277
msgid ""
"Fellow Lords and Sages, at this rate we're not getting anywhere. The "
"arguments in favour of Tenma Yozora being the fabled Dragon-Slayer are good, "
"though even Master Ankhmare is uncertain of whether her current technique is "
"enough to destroy the Sky Soul. Notwithstanding, I see no reason not to let "
"her try and prove herself and Master Ankhmare right; let her stay here and "
"train with him and, when they're done, we shall test her power."
msgstr ""
"Estimados Señores y Sabios, a este ritmo no llegaremos a ninguna parte. Los "
"argumentos a favor de que Tenma Yozora sea la legendaria Matadragones son "
"buenos, aunque incluso el maestro Ankhmare no está seguro de si su técnica "
"actual es suficiente para destruir el Alma Celestial. Sin embargo, no veo "
"razón para no dejarla intentar y demostrar que ella y el maestro Ankhmare "
"tienen razón; permitan que se quede aquí y entrene con él y, cuando "
"terminen, pondremos a prueba su poder."

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:281
msgid "This satisfies me – though Lord Ramoses seems to have a say on that?"
msgstr ""
"Esto me satisface —aunque parece que el señor Ramoses tiene algo que decir "
"al respecto, ¿no?"

#. [message], speaker=Ramoses
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:285
msgid ""
"(annoyed) I shall not oppose Lord Akhetamun in this. Let this young lady "
"stay and enjoy our hospitality; after all, she was the one who founded our "
"civilisation, wasn't she..."
msgstr ""
"(molesto) No me opondré al señor Akhetamun en esto. Que esta joven se quede "
"y disfrute de nuestra hospitalidad; después de todo, fue ella quien fundó "
"nuestra civilización, ¿no es así…?"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:289
msgid "<i>(chuckles from some Lords and civilians)</i>"
msgstr "<i>(risitas de algunos señores y civiles)</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:293
msgid "(whisper) I don't know who he is, but I really don't like him..."
msgstr "(susurro) No sé quién es, pero realmente no me cae bien…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:297
msgid ""
"He's our greatest living general, and an old oppositionist to Master "
"Ankhmare. You don't need to worry about him, though; he may not believe in "
"you being Myra, but he's not an evil man either."
msgstr ""
"Es nuestro mayor general vivo, y un viejo opositor del maestro Ankhmare. No "
"necesitas preocuparte por él, sin embargo; puede que no crea que eres Myra, "
"pero tampoco es un hombre malvado."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:301
msgid ""
"Well, he isn't wrong on that, I'm not Myra... Oh, damn, we've got another "
"audience to bear with?!"
msgstr ""
"Bueno, en eso no se equivoca, no soy Myra… Oh, maldición, ¿tenemos otra "
"audiencia que soportar?!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:305
msgid ""
"The audience dealing with your arrival is over, now the Lords and the Sages "
"will deal with the orc Bogor. You may leave, if you want; I wish to know "
"what Bogor has to say..."
msgstr ""
"La audiencia sobre tu llegada terminó, ahora los Señores y los Sabios se "
"ocuparán del orco Bogor. Puedes irte si quieres; yo deseo saber qué tiene "
"que decir Bogor…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:392
msgid ""
"...and so we're staying here until I'm capable of destroying this Sky Soul. "
"Cheer up, though, that this city has plenty of things to do: Valerya can "
"play with the local mages, Kenshiro can spar with the local soldiers, and "
"Cornelya can read as many books as she wants, that the local library is "
"larger even than Metheldur's."
msgstr ""
"…y así nos quedaremos aquí hasta que sea capaz de destruir este Alma del "
"Cielo. Ánimo, sin embargo, que esta ciudad tiene muchas cosas que hacer: "
"Valerya puede jugar con los magos locales, Kenshiro puede entrenar con los "
"soldados locales, y Cornelya puede leer todos los libros que quiera, que la "
"biblioteca local es incluso más grande que la de Metheldur."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:396
msgid "As if... Anyway, don't worry about me, I'll be going my own way too."
msgstr ""
"Como si… De todos modos, no te preocupes por mí, yo también iré por mi "
"propio camino."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:400
msgid ""
"What, are you taking a ship back to the Lins-Elens? You're pretty, but "
"Derceto won't be your escort if Olokun isn't with you."
msgstr ""
"¿Qué, vas a tomar un barco de regreso a los Lins-Elens? Eres bonita, pero "
"Derceto no será tu escolta si Olokun no está contigo."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:404
msgid "Of course I'm not going home, I... (snorts) Kenshiro, tell her, please."
msgstr "Claro que no voy a casa, yo… (resopla) Kenshiro, dile tú, por favor."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:408
msgid ""
"That faun, Umbrius, has offered to take her to a continent to the south, "
"Argea, where fauns and faeries live. He says they wish to meet her, since "
"she's one of their long lost elvish kin, and also because they can help "
"Cornelya improve her powers."
msgstr ""
"Ese fauno, Umbrius, le ofreció llevarla a un continente al sur, Argea, donde "
"viven faunos y feéricos. Dice que desean conocerla, ya que es una de sus "
"parientes élficas perdidas hace mucho, y también porque pueden ayudar a "
"Cornelya a mejorar sus poderes."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:412
msgid ""
"Thank you, mister stooge. (to Cornelya) And I was thinking that you'd sit "
"idly while I increased the difference in our powers... Kenshiro will go "
"along with you, I assume?"
msgstr ""
"Gracias, señor títere. (a Cornelya) Y yo pensando que te ibas a quedar de "
"brazos cruzados mientras yo aumentaba la diferencia en nuestros poderes… "
"Kenshiro irá contigo, supongo."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:416
msgid ""
"I... Well, I heard that Argea is the homeland of the Wesfolk, one of the "
"people from whom the Wesnothians descend, and so I'm curious about that land."
msgstr ""
"Yo… Bueno, escuché que Argea es la patria de los wesfolk, uno de los pueblos "
"de los que descienden los wesnothianos, y por eso me da curiosidad esa "
"tierra."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:420
msgid ""
"Oh? And here I thought you were just a musclehead... Nice to see you got "
"interests beyond just fighting."
msgstr ""
"¿Oh? Y yo que pensaba que solo eras un cabeza de músculo… Qué bueno ver que "
"tienes intereses más allá de solo pelear."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:424
msgid ""
"I've always been interested in the study of history; it's you who always "
"preferred to gossip about the other villagers, and the only gossip among the "
"Ken-Ningen are about who's fought who, who has the best technique..."
msgstr ""
"Siempre me ha interesado el estudio de la historia; eres tú la que siempre "
"prefería chismear sobre los otros aldeanos, y el único chisme entre los ken-"
"ningen es sobre quién peleó con quién, quién tiene la mejor técnica…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:428
msgid ""
"Come on, I'm not <i>that</i> shallow... Anyway, seems like everyone'll be "
"going on their own personal quests for a while; Algil is going to meet the "
"Aigathol, right?"
msgstr ""
"Vamos, no soy <i>tan</i> superficial… De todos modos, parece que todos irán "
"en sus propias misiones personales por un tiempo; Algil va a reunirse con "
"los Aigathol, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:432
msgid ""
"Aye. I found a merchant in this city who pledged to take me to their lady; "
"I'll try and convince her to let me take the Hammer of Ymer back to its true "
"owners. According to what I've learned, the Aigathol guard the Hammer rather "
"than use it for their own goals, so I think I have a chance to succeed."
msgstr ""
"Sí. Encontré un mercader en esta ciudad que se comprometió a llevarme con su "
"señora; intentaré convencerla de dejarme llevar el Martillo de Ymer de "
"vuelta a sus verdaderos dueños. Según lo que he aprendido, los Aigathol "
"custodian el Martillo en vez de usarlo para sus propios fines, así que creo "
"que tengo una oportunidad de tener éxito."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:436
msgid ""
"Well, I have nothing to do, so I think I'll just stay here and help Derceto "
"with Olokun and vice-versa..."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, no tengo nada que hacer, así que creo que me quedaré aquí y ayudaré a "
"Derceto con Olokun y viceversa…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:440
msgid ""
"You know, I think you should go and find a relationship of your own, rather "
"than meddle in other people's relationships..."
msgstr ""
"Sabes, creo que deberías ir a buscar una relación propia, en vez de meterte "
"en las relaciones de los demás…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:444
msgid ""
"And you should first know what if feels like to have a relationship, and "
"then you can begin to think of lecturing me on what I should do with my own "
"love life."
msgstr ""
"Y tú primero deberías saber qué se siente tener una relación, y luego puedes "
"empezar a pensar en darme lecciones sobre qué debería hacer con mi vida "
"amorosa."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:448
msgid "As you humans say, 'ouch'..."
msgstr "Como dicen ustedes los humanos, «ouch»…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:452
msgid ""
"(stung) Tsc, fine, I'll take the loss... Anyway, don't you get yourselves "
"lost or killed while I'm not around, understand? I still want to take "
"everyone to Kodakuni and eat Natsu's food..."
msgstr ""
"(picada) Tsc, está bien, acepto la derrota… De todos modos, no se pierdan ni "
"se dejen matar mientras no estoy, ¿entendido? Todavía quiero llevar a todos "
"a Kodakuni y comer la comida de Natsu…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:456
msgid ""
"We're the ones who should be telling you that, shrimp. Next time you fight, "
"we won't be there to shield your petite frame from enemy blows. Also, I "
"promise I'll bring your friend back in one piece; he's a good stooge, after "
"all."
msgstr ""
"Somos nosotros los que deberíamos decirte eso, camarón. La próxima vez que "
"luches, no estaremos ahí para proteger tu pequeño cuerpo de los golpes "
"enemigos. Además, prometo que traeré a tu amigo de una pieza; después de "
"todo, es un buen títere."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:460
msgid "Shut up you too..."
msgstr "Cállate tú también…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/28_Chosen_Paths.cfg:464
msgid "Good luck, friends! See you in a few weeks!"
msgstr "¡Buena suerte, amigos! ¡Nos vemos en unas semanas!"

#. [scenario], id=29_Legacy_Of_The_First
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:5
msgid "Legacy of the First"
msgstr "Legado de los Primeros"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:26
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:505
msgid "Find the Green Path to the south-west"
msgstr "Encontrar el Camino Verde al suroeste"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:38
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:517
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:675
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:712
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:956
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1275
msgid "Death of Umbrius"
msgstr "Muerte de Umbrius"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:42
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:521
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:679
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:708
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:952
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1271
msgid "Death of Bogor"
msgstr "Muerte de Bogor"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:48
msgid ""
"In this scenario, you may recruit Umbrius' fauns; Tenma's non-elemental "
"veterans and recruits are also available, such as the mages. Furthermore, if "
"you kill the enemy goblin/orcish leaders with Bogor, whatever unit they may "
"have left will join you. No gold will be carried over to next scenario."
msgstr ""
"En este escenario puedes reclutar faunos de Umbrius; también están "
"disponibles los veteranos y reclutas no elementales de Tenma, como los "
"magos. Además, si matas a los líderes goblin/orcos enemigos con Bogor, "
"cualquier unidad que les quede se unirá a ti. No se llevará oro al siguiente "
"escenario."

#. [side], type=Death Knight
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:74
msgid "Lord Eoros"
msgstr "Señor Eoros"

#. [side], type=Death Knight
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:79
msgid "Revenants"
msgstr "Resucitados"

#. [side], type=Orcish Warlord
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:99
msgid "Chief Praduk"
msgstr "Jefe Praduk"

#. [side], type=Orcish Warlord
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:104
msgid "Skull Banner Clan"
msgstr "Clan Estandarte de Calavera"

#. [side], type=Direwolf Rider
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:125
msgid "Chief Padrash"
msgstr "Jefe Padrash"

#. [side], type=Direwolf Rider
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:130
msgid "Gory Fang Clan"
msgstr "Clan Colmillo Sangriento"

#. [side], type=Minotaur Elder
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:154
msgid "Elder Rynthos"
msgstr "Anciano Rynthos"

#. [side], type=Gryphon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:180
msgid "Kreyyah"
msgstr "Kreyyah"

#. [side], type=Gryphon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:185
msgid "Gryphons"
msgstr "Grifos"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:200
msgid "Heartwood Valley"
msgstr "Valle del Corazón de Madera"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:306
msgid ""
"Blessed be the rain and the greenery, that dry desert was making me "
"seriously ill... So, folks, are you exhausted already? I told you that "
"following me through such thick woodlands would not be easy..."
msgstr ""
"Bendita sea la lluvia y el verdor, ese desierto seco me estaba poniendo "
"realmente enferma… Entonces, gente, ¿ya están agotados? Les dije que "
"seguirme por unos bosques tan espesos no sería fácil…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:310
msgid ""
"(panting) Well, we couldn't have let you follow a stranger to an unknown "
"continent on your own...!"
msgstr ""
"(jadeando) Bueno, ¡no podíamos dejarte seguir a un extraño a un continente "
"desconocido tú sola…!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:314
msgid ""
"(smiling) It's adorable that you think I need your protection... But I won't "
"say it displeases me either. Now, Umbrius, we've been travelling for a while "
"already; how far are we from your people's valley?"
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Es adorable que pienses que necesito tu protección… Pero no diré "
"que me desagrada tampoco. Ahora, Umbrius, ya llevamos un rato viajando; ¿qué "
"tan lejos estamos del valle de tu pueblo?"

#. [message], speaker=Umbrius
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:318
msgid ""
"The Green Pass, which is the only way into Heartwood Valley, is a few miles "
"to the southwest, but the path leading to it is very sinuous, and goes "
"through the ruins of the ancient empire of Skiron – ruins haunted not only "
"by its ghosts but, also, by orcish and minotaur warbands."
msgstr ""
"El Paso Verde, que es la única forma de entrar al Valle del Corazón de "
"Madera, está a unas pocas millas al suroeste, pero el camino que lleva a él "
"es muy sinuoso y atraviesa las ruinas del antiguo imperio de Skiron —ruinas "
"embrujadas no solo por sus fantasmas, sino también por bandas de guerra "
"orcas y minotauros."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:322
msgid ""
"I see... Maybe it was a good idea, after all, to bring our non-elemental "
"forces along."
msgstr ""
"Ya veo… Tal vez después de todo fue buena idea traer nuestras fuerzas no "
"elementales."

#. [message], speaker=Bogor
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:326
msgid ""
"Was than an innuendo, tree-hugger? You can rest your pretty, fearful head; I "
"gave the humans my word I'd take you back in one piece, and they gave me "
"theirs that they'll help me crush those stinking midgets. Should they no "
"fulfil their end of the deal, well, having you within arm's length will be "
"very useful..."
msgstr ""
"¿Eso fue una indirecta, abrazárboles? Puedes descansar tu linda cabecita "
"miedosa; les di mi palabra a los humanos de que te devolvería entera, y "
"ellos me dieron la suya de que me ayudarían a aplastar a esos apestosos "
"enanos. Si no cumplen su parte del trato, bueno, tenerte al alcance de la "
"mano será muy útil…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:330
msgid ""
"Let's hope they don't try and double-cross you... for <i>your</i> own sake, "
"of course."
msgstr ""
"Esperemos que no intenten traicionarte… por <i>tu</i> propio bien, claro."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:334
msgid ""
"I still don't get it, though. I thought the dwarves were Maat'Kare's allies? "
"Why would they side with the orcs against them?"
msgstr ""
"Aun así sigo sin entenderlo. Pensé que los enanos eran aliados de Maat'Kare. "
"¿Por qué se pondrían del lado de los orcos contra ellos?"

#. [message], speaker=Umbrius
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:338
msgid ""
"Allies they may be, but there's been a growing suspicion that a faction of "
"the Aigathol Dwarves has been preying on the orcish clans under the Golden "
"Union. This alliance was founded aeons ago to destroy Skiron... or the "
"Wesfolk, as you seem to call them. The alliance remained beyond Skiron's "
"fall, though to the orcs it's mostly a pact of non-aggression. Bogor's clan "
"is part of it, so any dwarven attack on his people is a violation of the "
"alliance."
msgstr ""
"Aliados pueden ser, pero ha crecido la sospecha de que una facción de los "
"enanos Aigathol ha estado cazando a los clanes orcos bajo la Unión Dorada. "
"Esta alianza fue fundada hace eones para destruir Skiron… o los wesfolk, "
"como parecen llamarlos ustedes. La alianza perduró más allá de la caída de "
"Skiron, aunque para los orcos es principalmente un pacto de no agresión. El "
"clan de Bogor forma parte de ella, así que cualquier ataque enano contra su "
"pueblo es una violación de la alianza."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:342
msgid ""
"Well, enough with the political talks. If you lazy men are done resting, let "
"us press on."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, basta de charlas políticas. Si ya terminaron de descansar, vagos, "
"sigamos adelante."

#. [message], speaker=Bogor
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:346
msgid ""
"Pfff, I was never tired, the whingeing came from your mate - and you were "
"the one who chose to stop so he could rest his pretty face."
msgstr ""
"Pfff, nunca estuve cansado, el quejido vino de tu compañero —y fuiste tú "
"quien decidió parar para que pudiera descansar su lindo rostro."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:350
msgid "(blushes) Shut-"
msgstr "(sonrojado) Calla—"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:354
msgid "(blushes harder) -up, orc! 'Mate'... as if!"
msgstr "(se sonroja más) —¡cállate, orco! «Compañero»… ¡como si!"

#. [message], speaker=Umbrius
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:358
msgid "(smirks)"
msgstr "(sonríe con ironía)"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:380
msgid "Hey, I was wondering-"
msgstr "Oye, estaba preguntándome—"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:384
msgid ""
"Ignore that orc's comment, he's an idiot and what he said means nothing to "
"me."
msgstr ""
"Ignora el comentario de ese orco, es un idiota y lo que dijo no significa "
"nada para mí."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:388
msgid "I... was going to ask about the history of the Isles of Tears..."
msgstr "Yo… iba a preguntar por la historia de las Islas de las Lágrimas…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:392
msgid ""
"Oh... (blushes slightly) Fine, I did promise I'd tell you... (clears throat) "
"Long before Haldric of Wesnoth arrived there, those islands were the home of "
"a unique clan of elves: the Solariel, or the sun elves. They wielded arts "
"unlike any known to our people, and were masterful sailors, the likes of "
"which were not to be seen for millennia."
msgstr ""
"Oh… (sonroja ligeramente) Está bien, prometí contarte… (aclara la garganta) "
"Mucho antes de que Haldric de Wesnoth llegara allí, esas islas fueron el "
"hogar de un clan élfico único: los solariel, o elfos del sol. Dominaban "
"artes distintas a cualquier otra conocida por nuestro pueblo, y eran "
"marineros magistrales, como no se han visto en milenios."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:396
msgid ""
"But shadows creeped into their abode during the war against Ashura the "
"Demon, the first Necromancer..."
msgstr ""
"Pero sombras se infiltraron en su morada durante la guerra contra Ashura el "
"Demonio, el primer nigromante…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:400
msgid "Whom Tenma, Olokun and I fought and defeated."
msgstr "A quien Tenma, Olokun y yo combatimos y derrotamos."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:404
msgid ""
"Yes, yes, you've mentioned that enough times that I could never forget. "
"Ashura captured the high priestess of the Solariel; she was much beloved by "
"her people, and so they eagerly rallied to their King's call as he joined "
"the hosts of the Lins-Elens and of the Aragwaithi in the final charge "
"against Ashura. They were victorious, Ashura was sealed, and the high "
"priestess was rescued. She returned home to a welcome as warm as the islands."
msgstr ""
"Sí, sí, lo has mencionado suficientes veces como para que nunca lo olvide. "
"Ashura capturó a la alta sacerdotisa de los solariel; era muy amada por su "
"pueblo, y así se apresuraron a responder al llamado de su rey cuando este se "
"unió a las huestes de los Lins-Elens y de los aragwaithi en la carga final "
"contra Ashura. Fueron victoriosos, Ashura fue sellado y la alta sacerdotisa "
"fue rescatada. Regresó a casa con una bienvenida tan cálida como las islas."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:408
msgid ""
"However, Ashura had done worse than capture the high priestess. The Demon's "
"evil, insidious as it was, seeped into her soul, twisting it; and so beloved "
"was the high priestess, and so gleeful her people for having her back, that "
"none noticed the shadows within her. She seduced the King, took the Queen's "
"place and even her name, and slowly cast a spell over all the Solariel, so "
"that not a one of them realised what she had done to the original Queen."
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, Ashura había hecho algo peor que capturar a la alta "
"sacerdotisa. El mal del Demonio, tan insidioso como era, se filtró en su "
"alma, torciéndola; y tan amada era la alta sacerdotisa, y tan alegre su "
"pueblo por tenerla de vuelta, que nadie notó las sombras dentro de ella. "
"Sedujo al rey, tomó el lugar de la reina y hasta su nombre, y lentamente "
"lanzó un hechizo sobre todos los solariel, de modo que ninguno se dio cuenta "
"de lo que había hecho con la reina original."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:412
msgid ""
"One day, a group of witches arrived to the Islands in friendship, seeking "
"aid in a quest of their own. It was then that the high priestess revealed "
"that she had learned Ashura's arts: she plotted to use the witches' powers "
"to open a gate to the Land of the Dead, drawing its power to rule "
"unchallenged even by Time itself."
msgstr ""
"Un día, un grupo de brujas llegó a las islas en son de amistad, buscando "
"ayuda en su propia misión. Fue entonces cuando la alta sacerdotisa reveló "
"que había aprendido las artes de Ashura: planeaba usar los poderes de las "
"brujas para abrir una puerta a la Tierra de los Muertos, extrayendo su poder "
"para gobernar sin desafío incluso por el Tiempo mismo."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:416
msgid ""
"The witches saw through her deception and fought the high priestess in a "
"terrible battle that littered the islands with corpses. The high priestess "
"was destroyed, but not before she cast a curse of undeath upon the home that "
"had loved her so: those felled in battle rose again to fell those who had "
"survived, until no living soul was left on the Islands."
msgstr ""
"Las brujas vieron a través de su engaño y lucharon contra la alta "
"sacerdotisa en una terrible batalla que dejó las islas cubiertas de "
"cadáveres. La alta sacerdotisa fue destruida, pero no antes de lanzar una "
"maldición de no-muerte sobre el hogar que tanto la había amado: los caídos "
"en batalla se levantaron de nuevo para derribar a los que habían "
"sobrevivido, hasta que no quedó ninguna alma viva en las islas."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:420
msgid ""
"And though the high priestess was gone, her daughter, the Solariel princess, "
"rose again in undeath too, taking her rightful place as the ruler of a dead "
"kingdom. For the tragedy that the loss of the Solariel meant for all "
"elvenkind, their abode was renamed 'Isles of Tears'."
msgstr ""
"Y aunque la alta sacerdotisa ya no estaba, su hija, la princesa solariel, "
"también se levantó en no-muerte, tomando su lugar legítimo como gobernante "
"de un reino muerto. Por la tragedia que significó la pérdida de los solariel "
"para toda la raza élfica, su morada fue renombrada «Islas de las Lágrimas»."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:424
msgid ""
"That's a grim tale indeed... I wonder if the 'midnight queen' Haldric was "
"said to fight there was the Solariel Princess?"
msgstr ""
"Es un cuento realmente sombrío… Me pregunto si la «reina de medianoche» con "
"la que se dice que Haldric luchó allí era la princesa solariel."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:428
msgid ""
"That is very likely... (chuckles) Ironic, isn't it? I rail against humans "
"and their irresponsibility, and yet the curse of the sun elves needed a "
"human to be corrected..."
msgstr ""
"Es muy probable… (ríe) Irónico, ¿no? Me quejo de los humanos y su "
"irresponsabilidad, y sin embargo la maldición de los elfos del sol necesitó "
"a un humano para ser corregida…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:432
msgid ""
"It's only ironic if you think of people as 'monoliths'. Look at a forest and "
"you'll find everything from weeds to flowers; would you burn away the "
"flowers just to get rid of the weeds?"
msgstr ""
"Solo es irónico si piensas en las personas como «monolitos». Mira un bosque "
"y encontrarás desde maleza hasta flores; ¿quemarías las flores solo para "
"deshacerte de la maleza?"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:436
msgid "I... (sigh) You're right, I suppose..."
msgstr "Yo… (suspiro) Tienes razón, supongo…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:440
msgid ""
"Besides, anyone who pays attention to history knows elves mess up a lot too. "
"Just look at Landar, the Ka'lian taking advantage of Haldric, Mal M'brin of "
"the Aethenwood, the Thelien Elves..."
msgstr ""
"Además, cualquiera que preste atención a la historia sabe que los elfos "
"también la cagan mucho. Solo mira a Landar, al Ka’lian aprovechándose de "
"Haldric, a Mal M’brin del Bosque de Edén, a los elfos thelien…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:444
msgid "Don't push your luck, human..."
msgstr "No tientes tu suerte, humano…"

#. [message], speaker=Umbrius
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:459
msgid ""
"Beware now! The presence of that orc here means we're about to enter orcish "
"domain; they never stray far from the rest of their brethren."
msgstr ""
"¡Cuidado ahora! La presencia de ese orco aquí significa que estamos a punto "
"de entrar en territorio orco; nunca se alejan mucho del resto de sus "
"hermanos."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:463
msgid ""
"Let's just keep going through the woods, they won't be able to see us amidst "
"them..."
msgstr "Sigamos avanzando por el bosque, no podrán vernos entre los árboles…"

#. [message], speaker=Bogor
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:467
msgid ""
"To hell with sneaking around like puny cowards! (shouting) Hey you grunt..."
msgstr ""
"¡Al diablo con andar a hurtadillas como cobardes insignificantes! (gritando) "
"¡Oye, tú, bruto…!"

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:475
msgid "(startled) Uh... what the...?!"
msgstr "(sobresaltado) ¿Eh… qué demonios…?!"

#. [message], speaker=Bogor
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:479
msgid ""
"...I am Bogor of the Red Moon Clan from the northern continent; I'm "
"travelling to some valley in the south with a few servants of mine, so you "
"have two choices: do us all a favour and peacefully give way to us, or be a "
"stubborn jerk and force me to violently push you aside all the same!"
msgstr ""
"…Soy Bogor del Clan Luna Roja del continente norte; estoy viajando a un "
"valle al sur con unos pocos sirvientes míos, así que tienes dos opciones: "
"haznos un favor a todos y déjanos pasar en paz, ¡o sé un terco idiota y "
"oblígame a empujarte violentamente de todos modos!"

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:483
msgid ""
"I don't know who the hell you think you are, but you've become a dead orc "
"the moment you stepped into Skull Banner's lands! (shouting) Invaders from "
"the north! Sharpen your blades, everyone!"
msgstr ""
"¡No sé quién demonios crees que eres, pero te convertiste en un orco muerto "
"en el momento en que pusiste un pie en las tierras del Estandarte de "
"Calavera! (gritando) ¡Invasores del norte! ¡Afilen sus cuchillas, todos!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:487
msgid "Ugh, you'd have been more help if you'd just stayed in Maat'Kare..."
msgstr "Ugh, habrías sido de más ayuda si te hubieras quedado en Maat'Kare…"

#. [message], speaker=Bogor
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:491
msgid "Be patient, tree-hugger..."
msgstr "Ten paciencia, abrazárboles…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:495
msgid "<i>You</i> telling anyone to be <i>patient</i>?"
msgstr "¿<i>Tú</i> diciéndole a alguien que sea <i>paciente</i>?"

#. [message], speaker=Bogor
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:499
msgid ""
"...I will bring those clans to our side, I just need to fell their leaders "
"with my blade. Your horned friend's people may be strong in their forests, "
"but we could use allies in the open plains and meadows."
msgstr ""
"…Traeré a esos clanes a nuestro lado, solo necesito derribar a sus líderes "
"con mi espada. La gente de tu amigo con cuernos puede ser fuerte en sus "
"bosques, pero nos vendrían bien aliados en las llanuras y praderas abiertas."

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:527
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:685
msgid ""
"In this scenario, you may recruit Umbrius' fauns; Tenma's non-elemental "
"veterans and recruits are also available, such as the mages. Furthermore, if "
"you kill the enemy goblin/orcish leaders with Bogor, whatever unit they may "
"have left will join you."
msgstr ""
"En este escenario puedes reclutar faunos de Umbrius; también están "
"disponibles los veteranos y reclutas no elementales de Tenma, como los "
"magos. Además, si matas a los líderes goblin/orcos enemigos con Bogor, "
"cualquier unidad que les quede se unirá a ti."

#. [message], speaker=Bogor
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:547
msgid ""
"See just how weak your chief was, grunts? If you want a true leader, who "
"will lead you to glory and not to a miserable death, then join me!"
msgstr ""
"¿Ven lo débil que era su jefe, brutos? Si quieren un líder de verdad, que "
"los lleve a la gloria y no a una muerte miserable, ¡únanse a mí!"

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:556
msgid "If you lead us to victory, then we follow you to the ends of the world!"
msgstr ""
"¡Si nos llevas a la victoria, te seguimos hasta los confines del mundo!"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:564
msgid "What a strange sense of loyalty they have..."
msgstr "Qué sentido de lealtad tan extraño tienen…"

#. [message], speaker=Bogor
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:584
msgid ""
"Your chief was weak and would lead you to doom, but I would make you gorge "
"in victory and spoils. Join me, wolf riders, and together we shall have the "
"world!"
msgstr ""
"Su jefe era débil y los habría llevado a la perdición, pero yo los haré "
"saciarse de victoria y botín. ¡Únanse a mí, jinetes de lobo, y juntos "
"tendremos el mundo!"

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:593
msgid ""
"If you promise to lead us better than our old chief, then our wolves and "
"spears are yours to command!"
msgstr ""
"¡Si prometes liderarnos mejor que nuestro viejo jefe, entonces nuestros "
"lobos y lanzas están a tu mando!"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:619
msgid ""
"So these are the ruins of the Wesfolk Empire... They must have been a great "
"empire, just as the stories tell..."
msgstr ""
"Entonces estas son las ruinas del Imperio Wesfolk… Deben haber sido un gran "
"imperio, tal como cuentan las historias…"

#. [message], speaker=Umbrius
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:623
msgid ""
"They were powerful indeed, a great human nation who delved into the secrets "
"of magic and nature; but their might came at a terrible price, as it was "
"built on dark magic. This green scenery so close to their buildings would "
"have been unthinkable during their time, as their lands were covered and "
"surrounded by death and decay."
msgstr ""
"Fueron poderosos en efecto, una gran nación humana que se adentró en los "
"secretos de la magia y la naturaleza; pero su poder tuvo un precio terrible, "
"pues se construyó sobre magia oscura. Este paisaje verde tan cerca de sus "
"edificios habría sido impensable en su tiempo, ya que sus tierras estaban "
"cubiertas y rodeadas de muerte y decadencia."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:638
msgid ""
"Umbrius, sorry to say this, but your people and the Maat'Karians have done a "
"lame job getting rid of the Wesfolk. Just look at those ruins, they're "
"crawling with their undead!"
msgstr ""
"Umbrius, lamento decirlo, pero tu pueblo y los maatkarianos hicieron un "
"trabajo lamentable deshaciéndose de los wesfolk. Solo mira esas ruinas, "
"¡están plagadas de sus no-muertos!"

#. [message], speaker=Umbrius
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:642
msgid ""
"I said the Golden Union had expelled the Lich-Lords from this continent, not "
"that we destroyed every single one of their creations. Over the centuries, "
"our scouts have sighted some forgotten Skironian battalions which, free from "
"the Lich-Lords' commands but still filled with dark energy, roam Argea "
"preying on weak opponents, unable to find any rest."
msgstr ""
"Dije que la Unión Dorada expulsó a los Señores Liche de este continente, no "
"que destruimos cada una de sus creaciones. A lo largo de los siglos, "
"nuestros exploradores han avistado algunos batallones skironianos olvidados "
"que, libres de las órdenes de los Señores Liche pero aún llenos de energía "
"oscura, vagan por Argea cazando oponentes débiles, incapaces de encontrar "
"descanso."

#. [message], speaker=Umbrius
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:657
msgid ""
"This is the entrance to the Green Path, Lady Cornelya! Once inside it, we "
"shall be safe, no other other denizen of Argea dares to get near Heartwood "
"Valley."
msgstr ""
"¡Esta es la entrada al Camino Verde, dama Cornelya! Una vez dentro, "
"estaremos a salvo, ningún otro habitante de Argea se atreve a acercarse al "
"Valle del Corazón de Madera."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:663
msgid "Move Cornelya to the end of the Green Path"
msgstr "Llevar a Cornelya al final del Camino Verde"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:700
msgid "So, let us meet the fauns and the faeries..."
msgstr "Entonces, vamos a conocer a los faunos y a los feéricos…"

#. [unit], id=Oberone, type=Faun Lord
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:756
msgid "Lord Oberone"
msgstr "Señor Oberone"

#. [unit], id=Idunn, type=Faerie Spirit
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:769
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1250
msgid "Lady Idunn"
msgstr "Dama Idunn"

#. [message], speaker=Umbrius
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:813
msgid ""
"Princess Cornelya, Kenshiro, Chief Bogor, welcome to the ancestral home of "
"fauns, and the new home of the faeries: the Heartwood Valley!"
msgstr ""
"Princesa Cornelya, Kenshiro, jefe Bogor, ¡bienvenidos al hogar ancestral de "
"los faunos y el nuevo hogar de los feéricos: el Valle del Corazón de Madera!"

#. [message], speaker=Umbrius
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:817
msgid ""
"Please, follow me to Dryas Island; Lord Oberone and Lady Idunn must meet "
"you... Kenshiro, Bogor, you may come as well, but I must ask you to wait at "
"the island's entrance..."
msgstr ""
"Por favor, síganme hasta la Isla Dryas; el señor Oberone y la dama Idunn "
"deben conocerlos… Kenshiro, Bogor, pueden venir también, pero les pido que "
"esperen en la entrada de la isla…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:821
msgid "Are you fine with that, Cornelya? If you wish, I could stay with you..."
msgstr ""
"¿Estás de acuerdo con eso, Cornelya? Si quieres, podría quedarme contigo…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:825
msgid ""
"Thank you, Kenshiro, but that won't be necessary; amid these mountains, I "
"feel safe like I haven't since..."
msgstr ""
"Gracias, Kenshiro, pero no será necesario; entre estas montañas me siento "
"segura como no lo he estado desde…"

#. [message], speaker=Bogor
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:829
msgid ""
"Pah, I won't bother going any further. No offence horned friend, but these "
"airy-fairy places make me wanna puke. I think I'll just wait at these "
"gates..."
msgstr ""
"Pah, no me molestaré en seguir más lejos. Sin ofender, amigo con cuernos, "
"pero estos lugares de airecitos feéricos me dan ganas de vomitar. Creo que "
"esperaré en estas puertas…"

#. [message], speaker=Umbrius
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:850
msgid ""
"Lord Oberone, Lady Idunn, forgive my intrusion, but I wish you to meet..."
msgstr ""
"Señor Oberone, dama Idunn, perdonen mi intrusión, pero deseo que conozcan…"

#. [message], speaker=Oberone
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:854
msgid ""
"...the Heiress of the Tithanya, who, at long last, comes to us! Apologies "
"for the interruption, good Umbrius, but I'm already aware of who she is. "
"I've been sensing her proximity to our valley for days."
msgstr ""
"…a la Heredera de Tithanya, ¡que por fin ha venido a nosotros! Perdón por la "
"interrupción, buen Umbrius, pero ya sé quién es. Llevo días sintiendo su "
"cercanía al valle."

#. [message], speaker=Idunn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:858
msgid ""
"My fair princess, it's an honour to meet one of our long-lost siblings from "
"the Great Continent, and an even greater honour to meet one who has the "
"blood of the First in her veins. It's been aeons since one such as you has "
"graced us faeries with her presence; more than forty-eight centuries, to be "
"more precise, since the time Alenya of Lintanir sang in the woods of Netjer-"
"Ta."
msgstr ""
"Mi bella princesa, es un honor conocer a una de nuestras hermanas perdidas "
"hace mucho del Gran Continente, y un honor aún mayor conocer a una que lleva "
"la sangre de los Primeros en sus venas. Han pasado eones desde que alguien "
"como usted ha honrado con su presencia a nosotras las feéricas; más de "
"cuarenta y ocho siglos, para ser más precisos, desde que Alenya de Lintanir "
"cantó en los bosques de Netjer-Ta."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:862
msgid ""
"As it's an honour to meet the forest folk which the elves of the Lins-Elens "
"have thought lost long ago. However, I must ask you to explain why, like "
"Umbrius, you refer to me as having 'the blood of the First'."
msgstr ""
"Al igual que es un honor conocer al pueblo del bosque que los elfos de los "
"Lins-Elens creyeron perdido hace mucho. Sin embargo, debo pedirles que me "
"expliquen por qué, al igual que Umbrius, se refieren a mí como alguien que "
"tiene «la sangre de los Primeros»."

#. [message], speaker=Oberone
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:866
msgid ""
"Why, don't the elves remember the tale of Tithanya, the First of the "
"Faeries, and El-Teleryon, the King-in-the-Woods?"
msgstr ""
"¿Cómo? ¿Acaso los elfos no recuerdan el cuento de Tithanya, la Primera de "
"las Feéricas, y El-Teleryon, el Rey-en-el-Bosque?"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:870
msgid ""
"Er, I'm afraid such tale concerns the higher mysteries of Sylphs and Shydes; "
"I'm but a warrior, so it's only natural that I'm not aware of it..."
msgstr ""
"Eh, me temo que ese cuento concierne a los misterios superiores de las "
"sílfides y shydes; yo solo soy una guerrera, así que es natural que no lo "
"conozca…"

#. [message], speaker=Idunn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:874
msgid ""
"(unsettled) A warrior? But... With such strong affinity to your faerie "
"nature, why do you walk the path of steel?"
msgstr ""
"(inquieta) ¿Una guerrera? Pero… con una afinidad tan fuerte con tu "
"naturaleza feérica, ¿por qué sigues el camino del acero?"

#. [message], speaker=Oberone
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:878
msgid ""
"I too wish to know more about her, my dear, but you must answer her question "
"first."
msgstr ""
"Yo también deseo saber más de ella, querida, pero primero debes responder su "
"pregunta."

#. [message], speaker=Idunn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:882
msgid ""
"Indeed... My princess, I cannot affirm that this is what the elven Sylphs "
"tell, but this is the story that we, faeries, have carried from generation "
"to generation since the Ancient Days."
msgstr ""
"En efecto… Mi princesa, no puedo afirmar que esto sea lo que cuentan las "
"sílfides élficas, pero esta es la historia que nosotras, las feéricas, hemos "
"transmitido de generación en generación desde los Días Antiguos."

#. [message], speaker=Idunn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:886
msgid ""
"Those were the days when even the elves still learned to survive against the "
"elements. Though dragons existed, the reign of the High Dragons was yet to "
"begin, for those were still the days when Demere, the Mother of All Life, "
"walked on Irdya."
msgstr ""
"Esos eran los días en que incluso los elfos aún aprendían a sobrevivir "
"contra los elementos. Aunque los dragones existían, el reinado de los "
"Grandes Dragones aún no había comenzado, pues eran todavía los días en que "
"Demere, la Madre de Toda Vida, caminaba por Irdya."

#. [message], speaker=Idunn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:890
msgid ""
"For many eras, she watched over the life on this planet, a life she had "
"created and filled with her ever-burning spark; and she loved them all, from "
"the smallest disease-bringer to the greatest dragon. But, for some reason, "
"she never managed to live happily amongst them. In her loneliness, she "
"birthed a new child; unlike the others, that one was created from the "
"Mother's own mystical body. This last of the Mother's children was Tithanya, "
"a being who dwelled in the twilight between the material and the arcane "
"worlds: the First of the Faeries."
msgstr ""
"Durante muchas eras, ella veló por la vida en este planeta, una vida que "
"ella misma había creado y llenado con su chispa siempre ardiente; y amaba a "
"todos, desde el más pequeño portador de enfermedades hasta el mayor dragón. "
"Pero, por alguna razón, nunca logró vivir feliz entre ellos. En su soledad, "
"dio a luz a un nuevo hijo; a diferencia de los demás, este fue creado del "
"propio cuerpo místico de la Madre. Este último de los hijos de la Madre fue "
"Tithanya, un ser que habitaba el crepúsculo entre los mundos material y "
"arcano: la Primera de las Feéricas."

#. [message], speaker=Idunn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:894
msgid ""
"She accompanied her Mother for a long time, even though they were so unlike "
"one another. The Mother, albeit loving of her children, had the strong-"
"willed spirit of a fighter – a trait she legated to most of her offspring – "
"whilst the demure First abhorred violence."
msgstr ""
"Ella acompañó a su Madre durante mucho tiempo, aunque eran tan distintas "
"entre sí. La Madre, aunque amaba a sus hijos, tenía el espíritu fuerte y "
"combativo de una luchadora —un rasgo que legó a la mayoría de su descendencia"
"—, mientras que la recatada Primera aborrecía la violencia."

#. [message], speaker=Idunn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:898
msgid ""
"This led her to love all forests, as the plants are amongst the few beings "
"that do not fight. From her own spark, she created a new race in her own "
"image; thus the lesser faeries, such as myself, were born. Like our mother, "
"we chose the deepest forests of Irdya as our dwelling, protecting them from "
"any foe. Not content, the First gave certain trees around the world a little "
"of her own spark as well; this was how the woses appeared, and also the "
"reason we're so closely related."
msgstr ""
"Esto la llevó a amar todos los bosques, ya que las plantas están entre los "
"pocos seres que no luchan. De su propia chispa creó una nueva raza a su "
"imagen; así nacieron las feéricas menores, como yo. Al igual que nuestra "
"madre, elegimos los bosques más profundos de Irdya como morada, "
"protegiéndolos de cualquier enemigo. No conforme con eso, la Primera también "
"dio una pequeña parte de su chispa a ciertos árboles alrededor del mundo; "
"así aparecieron los woses, y también la razón por la que estamos tan "
"estrechamente relacionados."

#. [message], speaker=Idunn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:902
msgid ""
"As the many intelligent races of Irdya thrived, they started chopping down "
"vast extensions of woodland to build their own nations. Tithanya watched "
"this 'progress' with contempt, but she couldn't stop them, as she had been "
"forbidden by the Mother from directly intervening in the affairs of other "
"peoples."
msgstr ""
"A medida que las muchas razas inteligentes de Irdya prosperaban, comenzaron "
"a talar vastas extensiones de bosque para construir sus propias naciones. "
"Tithanya observaba este «progreso» con desprecio, pero no podía detenerlos, "
"pues la Madre le había prohibido intervenir directamente en los asuntos de "
"otros pueblos."

#. [message], speaker=Idunn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:906
msgid ""
"It was then that she met the elves, whose fondness for the forests gained "
"them the First's attention – and she saw in them a way of countering the "
"woodlands' destruction: she married El-Teleryon, the King-in-the-Woods, and "
"bore children who, elves as they may have been, had some of the First's own "
"power within themselves. As those children mingled with other elves, the "
"power of the First spread across elven-kind, empowering it greatly."
msgstr ""
"Fue entonces cuando conoció a los elfos, cuyo cariño por los bosques captó "
"la atención de la Primera —y vio en ellos una forma de contrarrestar la "
"destrucción de los bosques: se casó con El-Teleryon, el Rey-en-el-Bosque, y "
"dio a luz a hijos que, aunque elfos, llevaban dentro parte del propio poder "
"de la Primera. A medida que esos hijos se mezclaron con otros elfos, el "
"poder de la Primera se extendió por toda la raza élfica, fortaleciéndola "
"enormemente."

#. [message], speaker=Idunn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:910
msgid ""
"It's true that many elves nowadays may trace their lineage to the First, but "
"it's only in a few that her power does awaken, either in the form of unusual "
"healing skills, or as the mastery over the ties to the faerie plane."
msgstr ""
"Es cierto que muchos elfos hoy en día pueden rastrear su linaje hasta la "
"Primera, pero solo en unos pocos despierta su poder, ya sea en forma de "
"habilidades curativas inusuales o como dominio sobre los lazos con el plano "
"feérico."

#. [message], speaker=Idunn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:914
msgid ""
"This, my princess, is what I meant when I said that you had 'the blood of "
"the First'. And not only that; I do not know other elven Sylphs to make a "
"comparison, but I can say that your affinity with your own faerie side is "
"extremely strong. I can feel it: a latent power, eager to burst with all its "
"intensity..."
msgstr ""
"Esto, mi princesa, es lo que quise decir cuando dije que tenías «la sangre "
"de los Primeros». Y no solo eso; no conozco otras sílfides élficas para "
"comparar, pero puedo decir que tu afinidad con tu lado feérico es "
"extremadamente fuerte. Lo siento: un poder latente, ansioso por estallar con "
"toda su intensidad…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:918
msgid ""
"(uneasy) I acknowledge that I have this faerie side; I did train as a shaman "
"when I was a little girl. However, having an innate talent for something "
"doesn't mean one must become that, and so I have chosen the path of the "
"warrior – and methinks that suits me and my needs much better than the path "
"I originally followed."
msgstr ""
"(incómoda) Reconozco que tengo este lado feérico; entrené como chamana "
"cuando era niña. Sin embargo, tener un talento innato para algo no significa "
"que uno deba convertirse en eso, y por eso he elegido el camino de la "
"guerrera —y creo que me conviene mucho más a mí y a mis necesidades que el "
"camino que seguí originalmente."

#. [message], speaker=Idunn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:922
msgid "And yet your weapons are all but made of iron?"
msgstr "¿Y sin embargo tus armas están hechas casi todas de hierro?"

#. [message], speaker=Idunn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:930
msgid ""
"Iron is a bane to us, as it corrupts our inner energy flow, and so it must "
"be the same for elves with a connection to their faerie side. A prolonged "
"contact with this metal can forever cripple a faerie's power; you certainly "
"knew that, so, if you were so adamant on walking the warrior's path, why did "
"you reject its use?"
msgstr ""
"El hierro es una plaga para nosotras, pues corrompe nuestro flujo interno de "
"energía, y debe ser lo mismo para los elfos con conexión a su lado feérico. "
"Un contacto prolongado con este metal puede inutilizar para siempre el poder "
"de una feérica; seguro lo sabías, entonces, si estabas tan decidida a seguir "
"el camino de la guerrera, ¿por qué rechazaste su uso?"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:934
msgid "I... I simply thought some healing power would be handy, that's all."
msgstr ""
"Yo… simplemente pensé que algo de poder curativo sería útil, eso es todo."

#. [message], speaker=Idunn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:938
msgid ""
"We both know that's not true, princess. I don't know what made you become a "
"warrior, but I can tell that, deep within, you don't sincerely wish to "
"forfeit your true nature..."
msgstr ""
"Ambas sabemos que eso no es cierto, princesa. No sé qué te hizo convertirte "
"en guerrera, pero puedo decir que, en el fondo, no deseas sinceramente "
"renunciar a tu verdadera naturaleza…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:942
msgid ""
"(angry) Fine, I don't want to completely lose this power, so what? Faeries "
"are peaceful, right? The thing, Faerie Lady, is: I cannot be at peace, not "
"in my heart, not now. I've endured too much pain to simply forget it, "
"understand?"
msgstr ""
"(enojada) Está bien, no quiero perder completamente este poder, ¿y qué? Las "
"feéricas son pacíficas, ¿verdad? Lo que pasa, dama feérica, es que no puedo "
"estar en paz, no en mi corazón, no ahora. He soportado demasiado dolor como "
"para simplemente olvidarlo, ¿entiendes?"

#. [message], speaker=Idunn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:946
msgid ""
"(smiling) If that's the case, then you have come to the right place. Faeries "
"and fauns excel in the healing arts, after all. Besides, you and your friend "
"may learn very useful skills here."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Si ese es el caso, entonces has venido al lugar correcto. "
"Después de todo, las feéricas y los faunos destacan en las artes curativas. "
"Además, tú y tu amigo podrían aprender habilidades muy útiles aquí."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:950
msgid ""
"Well... In that case, maybe... It would be better to stay here anyway. I "
"could really use some new skills, now that the shrimp is improving herself "
"too..."
msgstr ""
"Bueno… En ese caso, tal vez… De todos modos sería mejor quedarse aquí. "
"Realmente podría usar algunas habilidades nuevas, ahora que el camarón "
"también se está mejorando…"

#. [message], speaker=Oberone
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:954
msgid ""
"I know not who this 'shrimp' is, but I assure you that your stay here won't "
"go to waste. Be welcome, and feel at ease: Heartwood Valley is your home as "
"much as ours!"
msgstr ""
"No sé quién es esa «camarón», pero te aseguro que tu estancia aquí no será "
"en vano. Sé bienvenida y siéntete en casa: el Valle del Corazón de Madera es "
"tu hogar tanto como el nuestro."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:958
msgid ""
"Thank you, Lord Oberone, Lady Idunn... *maybe she was right, after all... "
"Have I become so used to hating that I'm just afraid of feeling anything "
"else...?*"
msgstr ""
"Gracias, señor Oberone, dama Idunn… *tal vez tenía razón después de todo… "
"¿Me habré acostumbrado tanto a odiar que solo tengo miedo de sentir "
"cualquier otra cosa…?*"

#. [message], speaker=Umbrius
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:1041
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1525
msgid "Apologies, Lady Cornelya, I've failed you..."
msgstr "Perdón, dama Cornelya, le he fallado…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:1045
msgid ""
"Damn it! Without him, we'll never find Heartwood Valley! We've come to this "
"continent for nothing!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldición! ¡Sin él nunca encontraremos el Valle del Corazón de Madera! "
"¡Hemos venido a este continente para nada!"

#. [message], speaker=Bogor
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:1062
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1542
msgid ""
"Ack! You let me die, unreliable bastards... Tell those stinking humans that "
"I'll be waiting for them in the Dead's Land..."
msgstr ""
"¡Ack! Me dejaron morir, bastardos poco confiables… Díganle a esos humanos "
"apestosos que los estaré esperando en la Tierra de los Muertos…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:1066
msgid ""
"As unpleasant as he may have been, we really shouldn't have let him die; "
"because of us, New Maat'Kare will be in huge trouble..."
msgstr ""
"Por desagradable que fuera, realmente no debimos dejarlo morir; por nuestra "
"culpa, Nueva Maat'Kare estará en graves problemas…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/29_Legacy_Of_The_First.cfg:1079
msgid ""
"Orcs, goblins and undead may be weak, but if we keep fighting so many of "
"them, we might actually get ourselves killed before even finding Heartwood "
"Valley!"
msgstr ""
"Los orcos, goblins y no-muertos pueden ser débiles, ¡pero si seguimos "
"luchando contra tantos de ellos, podríamos terminar muertos antes de "
"siquiera encontrar el Valle del Corazón de Madera!"

#. [scenario], id=30_The_Key_To_The_Past
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:5
msgid "The Key to the Past"
msgstr "La Llave del Pasado"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:23
msgid "Investigate the Caves of Light after the ancient graveyard"
msgstr "Investigar las Cuevas de la Luz después del antiguo cementerio"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:31
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:295
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:381
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:436
msgid "Death of Alafin"
msgstr "Muerte de Alafin"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:37
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:301
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:387
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:442
msgid ""
"In this scenario, you may recall the Wesnothian and undead veterans who "
"fought alongide Tenma in the Far North"
msgstr ""
"En este escenario puedes reincorporar a los veteranos wesnothianos y no-"
"muertos que lucharon junto a Tenma en el Lejano Norte"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:57
msgid "Aetheryon's Expedition"
msgstr "Expedición de Aetheryon"

#. [unit], id=Rhaent, type=Royal Guard
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:128
msgid "Rhaent"
msgstr "Rhaent"

#. [message], speaker=Rhaent
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:191
msgid ""
"Your Highness, erm... Are you sure that you want to go even further inside "
"these caves? There's... something about this place that gives me the "
"creeps..."
msgstr ""
"Su Alteza, emm… ¿está seguro de que quiere adentrarse aún más en estas "
"cuevas? Hay… algo en este lugar que me da escalofríos…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:195
msgid ""
"I feel the same way, but I won't go back a single step, specially not after "
"crossing the ocean and half of Arajunna to get here. Aelvar's journals had "
"too many gaps; he was seemingly content with learning about the Regalia, but "
"I refuse to believe that this place doesn't hold far more lost knowledge. If "
"that serves as comfort to you, know that we must be very close to the "
"graveyard where his mages found the ancient writings."
msgstr ""
"Siento lo mismo, pero no daré ni un paso atrás, especialmente después de "
"cruzar el océano y la mitad de Arajunna para llegar aquí. Los diarios de "
"Aelvar tenían demasiadas lagunas; parecía conforme con aprender sobre el "
"Regalia, pero me niego a creer que este lugar no oculte mucho más "
"conocimiento perdido. Si eso te consuela, sabed que debemos estar muy cerca "
"del cementerio donde sus magos encontraron los escritos antiguos."

#. [message], speaker=Rhaent
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:199
msgid ""
"A graveyard built by an ancient and mysterious civilisation? That sounds "
"like a nest of undead..."
msgstr ""
"¿Un cementerio construido por una civilización antigua y misteriosa? Eso "
"suena a nido de no-muertos…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:203
msgid ""
"Would that it was just a nest of undead; Aelvar's journals described "
"creatures far stranger and more dangerous ahead in these caves... "
"Notwithstanding, if he was able to make his way through them, then I see no "
"reason for us not to succeed as well. What worries me most is deciphering "
"whatever writing we find; I do hope they're in a language akin to that of "
"the Chomi or the Washrahan like you said, Alafin."
msgstr ""
"Ojalá fuera solo un nido de no-muertos; los diarios de Aelvar describían "
"criaturas mucho más extrañas y peligrosas más adelante en estas cuevas… No "
"obstante, si él pudo abrirse paso entre ellas, no veo razón para que "
"nosotros no lo logremos también. Lo que más me preocupa es descifrar "
"cualquier escritura que encontremos; espero que estén en un idioma parecido "
"al de los chomi o los washrahan, como dijiste, Alafin."

#. [message], speaker=Alafin
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:207
msgid ""
"Worry not, Prince Aetheryon; in all of our ancient history, the only peoples "
"registered to have lived in Arajunna, other than the dim Deshra, were the "
"Washraha and us, and our languages do share a common root. The only thing "
"that worries me, in the end, is the threat lurking in these tunnels. I'm "
"sure I've already told you about the legends regarding these caves..."
msgstr ""
"No se preocupe, príncipe Aetheryon; en toda nuestra historia antigua, los "
"únicos pueblos registrados que vivieron en Arajunna, aparte de los oscuros "
"deshra, fueron los washraha y nosotros, y nuestros idiomas comparten una "
"raíz común. Lo único que me preocupa al final es la amenaza que acecha en "
"estos túneles. Estoy seguro de que ya le conté sobre las leyendas respecto a "
"estas cuevas…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:211
msgid ""
"...that they're a sacred shrine built by a legendary tribe called the "
"Asherah, and that not even your Babalawos dare enter this place, yes, I "
"know. That only makes me more eager to find out the truth about these caves, "
"though; they may as well hide the key to deciphering the past of our world..."
msgstr ""
"…que son un santuario sagrado construido por una tribu legendaria llamada "
"los Asherah, y que ni siquiera sus Babalawos se atreven a entrar en este "
"lugar, sí, lo sé. Eso solo me hace más ansioso por descubrir la verdad sobre "
"estas cuevas; bien podrían ocultar la llave para descifrar el pasado de "
"nuestro mundo…"

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:231
msgid "Holy Gods of Light, what are those... things?!"
msgstr "¡Dioses Santos de la Luz, qué son esas… cosas?!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:235
msgid ""
"They can only be the creatures mentioned by Aelvar's journals and by Chomi "
"legends. It relieves me to see that they're physical, though; if they have a "
"body, that means they can be destroyed by earthly weapons."
msgstr ""
"Solo pueden ser las criaturas mencionadas en los diarios de Aelvar y en las "
"leyendas chomi. Me alivia ver que son físicas, sin embargo; si tienen un "
"cuerpo, significa que pueden ser destruidas por armas terrenales."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:250
msgid ""
"Impressive... There are beams of light sprouting from the ground... No, "
"they're not simple beams of light, they're... streams of pure magical "
"energy..."
msgstr ""
"Impresionante… Hay rayos de luz brotando del suelo… No, no son simples rayos "
"de luz, son… corrientes de pura energía mágica…"

#. [message], speaker=Alafin
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:254
msgid ""
"They must be 'magical discharges' caused by the intense magical energy "
"impregnating the rock; the points where these beams are must be the places "
"where the magic energy is the strongest."
msgstr ""
"Deben ser «descargas mágicas» causadas por la intensa energía mágica que "
"impregna la roca; los puntos donde están estos rayos deben ser los lugares "
"donde la energía mágica es más fuerte."

#. [message], speaker=Alafin
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:275
msgid ""
"Those tombs...! Prince Aetheryon, this has to be the graveyard found by "
"Aelvar's mages!"
msgstr ""
"¡Esas tumbas…! Príncipe Aetheryon, ¡este tiene que ser el cementerio "
"encontrado por los magos de Aelvar!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:279
msgid ""
"Indeed it has... Alafin, focus on deciphering whatever piece of text you "
"find here, that the soldiers and I shall cover you!"
msgstr ""
"En efecto lo es… Alafin, concéntrate en descifrar cualquier texto que "
"encuentres aquí, ¡que los soldados y yo te cubriremos!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:287
msgid ""
"Move Alafin to the tall rock in the middle of the graveyard (12,29) and let "
"him examine it for 3 turns"
msgstr ""
"Llevar a Alafin a la roca alta en el centro del cementerio (12,29) y dejar "
"que la examine durante 3 turnos"

#. [message], speaker=Alafin
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:352
msgid ""
"Prince Aetheryon, I'm sorry to report that the inscriptions in this "
"graveyard yielded no further information on the Regalia or the Asherah. All "
"they talk about is that the people buried here were called Keepers, and that "
"they had a leader called An-Usrukhar, but there's no further information on "
"him or her. This monolith must have once had many inscriptions on it, but it "
"seems that they were all erased by physical blows; considering how sharp "
"these cracks are, it must have been damaged recently."
msgstr ""
"Príncipe Aetheryon, lamento informar que las inscripciones en este "
"cementerio no arrojaron más información sobre el Regalia ni los Asherah. "
"Todo lo que hablan es que las personas enterradas aquí eran llamadas "
"Guardianes, y que tenían un líder llamado An-Usrukhar, pero no hay más "
"información sobre él o ella. Este monolito debió tener muchas inscripciones "
"alguna vez, pero parece que todas fueron borradas a golpes físicos; "
"considerando lo afiladas que están estas grietas, debió ser dañado "
"recientemente."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:356
msgid ""
"So that damn Aelvar wanted no one else to learn what he did... (smirking) "
"Well, all that means is that we'll have to investigate these caves even "
"further. The title of the men buried here has got my attention, as it does "
"the mention of An-Usrukhar; only the most avid readers of Wesnoth's History "
"scrolls know that the staff of Delfador the Great was called the Staff of An-"
"Usrukhar. And yet there is no register of Delfador having ever been to "
"Arajunna..."
msgstr ""
"Así que ese maldito Aelvar no quería que nadie más aprendiera lo que él "
"descubrió… (sonriendo) Bueno, todo eso significa que tendremos que "
"investigar estas cuevas aún más a fondo. El título de los hombres enterrados "
"aquí ha captado mi atención, al igual que la mención de An-Usrukhar; solo "
"los lectores más ávidos de los pergaminos de Historia de Wesnoth saben que "
"el bastón de Delfador el Grande se llamaba el Bastón de An-Usrukhar. Y sin "
"embargo no hay registro de que Delfador haya estado alguna vez en Arajunna…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:360
msgid ""
"Men, I can sense a great power source to the north; that must be where all "
"these creatures are coming from. Hearten yourselves, that we're growing "
"closer to making a discover that is likely to forever engrave our names in "
"the scrolls of History!"
msgstr ""
"Hombres, puedo sentir una gran fuente de poder al norte; ahí debe ser de "
"donde vienen todas estas criaturas. Ánimo, ¡nos estamos acercando a hacer un "
"descubrimiento que probablemente grabará nuestros nombres para siempre en "
"los pergaminos de la Historia!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:373
msgid "Go forward to whence the monsters are coming"
msgstr "Avanzar hacia donde vienen los monstruos"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:414
msgid ""
"Just as I have foreseen, this is where the monsters are coming from... and "
"also where the power source is."
msgstr ""
"Tal como lo había previsto, este es el lugar de donde vienen los monstruos… "
"y también donde está la fuente de poder."

#. [message], speaker=Alafin
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:418
msgid ""
"It seems that the origin of both the energy and the monsters is that statue "
"at the centre of this hall. What kind of magic would imbue it with such "
"power...?"
msgstr ""
"Parece que el origen tanto de la energía como de los monstruos es esa "
"estatua en el centro de esta sala. ¿Qué clase de magia la imbuye con tanto "
"poder…?"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:422
msgid "We shall soon discover the reason – but first we must clean the area..."
msgstr "Pronto descubriremos la razón —pero primero debemos limpiar la zona…"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:428
msgid "Destroy the dark clouds summoning the monsters"
msgstr "Destruir las nubes oscuras que invocan a los monstruos"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:460
msgid ""
"These creatures were quite strong, I acknowledge that; no wonder Aelvar "
"didn't risk going further in these caves... Too bad for him, though; now, "
"let us see what kind of lore this statue may hold..."
msgstr ""
"Estas criaturas eran bastante fuertes, lo reconozco; no es de extrañar que "
"Aelvar no se arriesgara a avanzar más en estas cuevas… Lástima para él, sin "
"embargo; ahora, veamos qué clase de saber puede contener esta estatua…"

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:472
msgid "Your Highness, watch out! There's something moving there!"
msgstr "¡Su Alteza, cuidado! ¡Hay algo moviéndose ahí!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:476
msgid "Don't attack! I see it now; it's not a monster, it's..."
msgstr "¡No ataquen! Ya lo veo; no es un monstruo, es…"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:489
msgid "(sleepy) Uwaaaahhhh...! What... Who are you...?"
msgstr "(somnolienta) ¡Uwaaaahhhh…! ¿Qué… quiénes son…?"

#. [message], speaker=Alafin
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:493
msgid ""
"It's a young maid! How did she get so far into these caves – and how did she "
"manage to sleep here, amidst all those monsters?!"
msgstr ""
"¡Es una joven doncella! ¿Cómo llegó tan lejos en estas cuevas —y cómo logró "
"dormir aquí, en medio de todos esos monstruos?!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:497
msgid ""
"(whisper) I shall find out soon... (to the girl) Pardon my intrusion, lady. "
"I am Aetheryon, a prince of Wesnoth; may I ask you who you are, and how you "
"found your way to this place so full of monsters?"
msgstr ""
"(susurro) Pronto lo averiguaré… (a la chica) Perdón por la intrusión, "
"señora. Soy Aetheryon, un príncipe de Wesnoth; ¿puedo preguntarle quién es "
"usted y cómo llegó a este lugar tan lleno de monstruos?"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:501
msgid ""
"Wesnoth, I've heard this name before; some men who looked like you came here "
"some time ago, claiming to come from this Wesnoth, but they attacked me, and "
"so I had to summon all those protectors..."
msgstr ""
"Wesnoth, he oído ese nombre antes; hace algún tiempo vinieron aquí unos "
"hombres que se parecían a usted, diciendo que venían de este Wesnoth, pero "
"me atacaron, y por eso tuve que invocar a todos esos protectores…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:505
msgid "You mean the... beings we've just fought? Were they summoned by you?"
msgstr ""
"¿Se refiere a los… seres con los que acabamos de luchar? ¿Los invocó usted?"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:509
msgid ""
"Yes... I've never needed to summon so many, but I had to, in order to sleep "
"in peace..."
msgstr ""
"Sí… Nunca había necesitado invocar tantos, pero tuve que hacerlo para poder "
"dormir en paz…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:513
msgid ""
"Then I offer you my sincere apologies for waking you up; we had no idea that "
"there would be a young lady living here. And don't worry, unlike those men "
"who came before, we're not hostile, we just seek knowledge. But, if that's "
"not too bold on my part, I ask you again: who are you, and where did you "
"come from?"
msgstr ""
"Entonces le ofrezco mis más sinceras disculpas por despertarla; no teníamos "
"idea de que habría una joven viviendo aquí. Y no se preocupe, a diferencia "
"de esos hombres que vinieron antes, nosotros no somos hostiles, solo "
"buscamos conocimiento. Pero, si no es demasiado atrevido por mi parte, le "
"pregunto de nuevo: ¿quién es usted y de dónde viene?"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:517
msgid ""
"I... I don't remember anything beyond these caves... I think I was born and "
"abandoned here; I've met some people who looked like me before, but they "
"always stared at me with suspicion and fear; the only beings I've had as "
"company were my protectors..."
msgstr ""
"Yo… no recuerdo nada más allá de estas cuevas… Creo que nací y fui "
"abandonada aquí; he conocido a algunas personas que se parecían a mí antes, "
"pero siempre me miraban con sospecha y miedo; los únicos seres que he tenido "
"como compañía fueron mis protectores…"

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:521
msgid ""
"(whispering) And who wouldn't be afraid of a girl who can summon such insane "
"monsters? Really, somehow she gives me the creeps, even more than those "
"monsters..."
msgstr ""
"(susurrando) ¿Y quién no tendría miedo de una chica que puede invocar "
"monstruos tan dementes? Realmente, de alguna forma me da más escalofríos que "
"esos monstruos…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:525
msgid ""
"So you have no name, nor any knowledge on your own origins... Still, you "
"speak our language very well; are you sure that you have absolutely no "
"memory of being among other people?"
msgstr ""
"Entonces no tiene nombre, ni conocimiento de sus propios orígenes… Aun así, "
"habla nuestro idioma muy bien; ¿está segura de que no tiene absolutamente "
"ningún recuerdo de haber estado entre otras personas?"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:529
msgid ""
"(distressed) I don't know how I can speak like you, but I told you already, "
"all I can remember is being in this cave!"
msgstr ""
"(angustiada) No sé cómo puedo hablar como ustedes, ¡pero ya se lo dije, todo "
"lo que recuerdo es estar en esta cueva!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:533
msgid ""
"I see, I believe your words; I shouldn't have been so rude. Please, let me "
"compensate that... I know! How about I give you a name with which you may "
"call yourself?"
msgstr ""
"Entiendo, creo en sus palabras; no debí ser tan grosero. Por favor, "
"permítame compensarlo… ¡Ya sé! ¿Qué tal si le doy un nombre con el que pueda "
"llamarse a sí misma?"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:537
msgid ""
"A name? But... Why would I need it? My protectors never talk to me, so they "
"don't need to call me by any name..."
msgstr ""
"¿Un nombre? Pero… ¿para qué lo necesitaría? Mis protectores nunca hablan "
"conmigo, así que no necesitan llamarme por ningún nombre…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:541
msgid ""
"Still, a name is a very important part of one's self, almost as much as "
"one's own soul; if you don't have a name, it's as if you didn't exist. Most "
"importantly... in the place where I'd like to take you, a name is of great "
"importance."
msgstr ""
"Aun así, un nombre es una parte muy importante de uno mismo, casi tanto como "
"el alma propia; si no tienes nombre, es como si no existieras. Más "
"importante aún… en el lugar al que me gustaría llevarla, un nombre tiene "
"gran importancia."

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:545
msgid "A place you want to...?"
msgstr "¿Un lugar al que quiere…?"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:549
msgid ""
"Not all people are bad, milady; if you would just give them a chance, they "
"can be kind – especially to a girl as gifted as you. Besides, I simply can't "
"leave a girl alone in such a damp cave; even if she can defend herself well, "
"she's not meant to be a lonely person."
msgstr ""
"No toda la gente es mala, milady; si solo les diera una oportunidad, pueden "
"ser amables —especialmente con una chica tan dotada como usted. Además, "
"simplemente no puedo dejar a una chica sola en una cueva tan húmeda; aunque "
"pueda defenderse bien, no está hecha para ser una persona solitaria."

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:553
msgid "I... Will you stay with me in this place you want to take me to?"
msgstr "Yo… ¿Se quedará conmigo en ese lugar al que quiere llevarme?"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:557
msgid "As long as you want me to stay with you, I will."
msgstr "Mientras usted quiera que me quede con usted, lo haré."

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:561
msgid ""
"(blushing) Then... Then I want to go with you; I've always wanted to see the "
"world from whence those other people came."
msgstr ""
"(sonrojada) Entonces… entonces quiero ir con usted; siempre he querido ver "
"el mundo de donde vinieron esas otras personas."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:565
msgid ""
"Good! Now, for your name: what about... Galdra? In the old tongue of my "
"people, it means 'magic'; I think it fits you, as you do possess great magic "
"power within yourself."
msgstr ""
"¡Bien! Ahora, para su nombre: ¿qué tal… Galdra? En la lengua antigua de mi "
"pueblo significa «magia»; creo que le queda bien, ya que usted posee un gran "
"poder mágico dentro de sí."

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:569
msgid "Galdra... (smiling) I love it! Thank you, Aetheryon..."
msgstr "Galdra… (sonriendo) ¡Me encanta! Gracias, Aetheryon…"

#. [message], speaker=Alafin
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:573
msgid ""
"(whispering) Prince Aetheryon, are you sure you want to bring this girl "
"along? If she actually can summon those creatures, she could be a great "
"threat to all of us!"
msgstr ""
"(susurrando) Príncipe Aetheryon, ¿está seguro de querer traer a esta chica "
"con nosotros? ¡Si realmente puede invocar esas criaturas, podría ser una "
"gran amenaza para todos!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:577
msgid ""
"(whispering) I don't think she'll do that, not to those who treat her well; "
"and she does have excellent control over both her own powers and her "
"monsters, as she's managed to live peacefully amongst them for so long. "
"Besides, and most importantly, I think there's much more to her than it may "
"appear; who knows, she may even be the very key to the past that I've sought "
"for all these years..."
msgstr ""
"(susurrando) No creo que lo haga, no contra quienes la traten bien; y tiene "
"un excelente control tanto sobre sus propios poderes como sobre sus "
"monstruos, ya que ha logrado vivir en paz entre ellos durante tanto tiempo. "
"Además, y lo más importante, creo que hay mucho más en ella de lo que "
"parece; quién sabe, tal vez sea precisamente la llave del pasado que he "
"buscado todos estos años…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:620
msgid "So close... Argh!"
msgstr "¡Tan cerca… Argh!"

#. [message], speaker=Alafin
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:637
msgid "I shouldn't... have accepted this job..."
msgstr "No debí… aceptar este trabajo…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:641
msgid ""
"No! Without him, I won't be able to decipher whatever text I find in these "
"caves!"
msgstr ""
"¡No! ¡Sin él no podré descifrar cualquier texto que encuentre en estas "
"cuevas!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/30_The_Key_To_The_Past.cfg:654
msgid ""
"We shouldn't have taken so long in these caves, at this rate we'll be "
"asphyxiated by lack of oxygen and overwhelmed by the creatures dwelling here!"
msgstr ""
"No debimos tardar tanto en estas cuevas, ¡a este ritmo nos asfixiaremos por "
"falta de oxígeno y seremos abrumados por las criaturas que habitan aquí!"

#. [scenario], id=31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:5
msgid "Rekindling of a Flame"
msgstr "Reavivando una Llama"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:26
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:227
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:334
msgid "Reach the Foundation of Hiera'Laksha"
msgstr "Llegar a la Fundación de Hiera'Laksha"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:38
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:239
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:342
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:582
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:31
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:37
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:534
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:37
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:476
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:684
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:928
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1247
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1753
msgid "Death of Ankhmare"
msgstr "Muerte de Ankhmare"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:44
msgid ""
"You may recruit/recall true elementals once again, and also recruit new "
"elementals through Ankhmare, but the veteran elementals belong to Olokun.\n"
"Also, you may recruit from all hexes adjacent to Tenma's starting point."
msgstr ""
"Puedes reclutar/reincorporar elementales verdaderos una vez más, y también "
"reclutar nuevos elementales a través de Ankhmare, pero los elementales "
"veteranos pertenecen a Olokun.\n"
"Además, puedes reclutar desde todos los hexágonos adyacentes al punto de "
"inicio de Tenma."

#. [side], type=Dwarvish Explorer
#. [side]
#. [side], type=Dwarvish Dragonguard
#. [side], type=Dwarvish Sentinel
#. [side], type=Dwarvish Runemaster
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:79
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:99
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:99
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:122
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:142
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:88
msgid "Rebels"
msgstr "Rebeldes"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:168
msgid ""
"(panting) Damn, the way you talked about going to Hiera'Laksha sounded like "
"it was much closer than this... Why the hell is this whole continent covered "
"in sand anyway?!"
msgstr ""
"(jadeando) Maldición, la forma en que hablabas de ir a Hiera'Laksha sonaba "
"como si estuviera mucho más cerca que esto… ¿Por qué demonios todo este "
"continente está cubierto de arena de todos modos?!"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:172
msgid ""
"Netjer-Ta used to be a much greener continent, but that was before the "
"Second Sun was raised in the skies. Remember that deep valley we saw on the "
"way here? That was once the greatest river on this continent, the Ruthen. "
"Sometimes I think we should reveal our existence and that of Netjer-Ta to "
"the rest of the civilised world, then everyone would see what is likely to "
"befall the whole of Irdya unless we work against it... But I digress. We "
"shouldn't be much far from Hiera'Laksha now, so cheer up!"
msgstr ""
"Netjer-Ta solía ser un continente mucho más verde, pero eso fue antes de que "
"se elevara el Segundo Sol en los cielos. ¿Recuerdas ese valle profundo que "
"vimos en el camino? Ese fue alguna vez el mayor río de este continente, el "
"Ruthen. A veces pienso que deberíamos revelar nuestra existencia y la de "
"Netjer-Ta al resto del mundo civilizado, entonces todos verían lo que "
"probablemente le ocurrirá a todo Irdya a menos que trabajemos en contra… "
"Pero me desvío. No debemos estar muy lejos de Hiera'Laksha ahora, ¡así que "
"ánimo!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:176
msgid ""
"Cheer up, yeah, easier said than done... I really hope your plan works, I'll "
"hate it so much if this journey ends up being in vain."
msgstr ""
"Ánimo, sí, más fácil decirlo que hacerlo… Realmente espero que tu plan "
"funcione, me odiaría muchísimo si este viaje termina siendo en vano."

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:180
msgid ""
"As I said, it's only a hunch, but there's a reasonable possibility that the "
"last Head of the Windsong in this continent, Hashira, discovered something "
"about how Myra and Maat managed to channel the full power of nature's "
"spirits; she made extensive researches on the Battles of Garet-Desh and of "
"the Crystal Tower, after all."
msgstr ""
"Como dije, es solo una corazonada, pero hay una posibilidad razonable de que "
"la última Cabeza de las Hijas del Viento en este continente, Hashira, "
"descubriera algo sobre cómo Myra y Maat lograron canalizar todo el poder de "
"los espíritus de la naturaleza; después de todo, hizo extensas "
"investigaciones sobre las Batallas de Garet-Desh y de la Torre de Cristal."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:195
msgid ""
"Oh, good, there are dwarves here! We could stop by their outpost to rest for "
"a while and drink something..."
msgstr ""
"Oh, qué bien, ¡hay enanos aquí! Podríamos parar en su puesto avanzado a "
"descansar un rato y tomar algo…"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:199
msgid ""
"(alarmed) Tenma, wait! There's something odd about them... (shouting) You, "
"dwarves! I am Ankhmare, Grand Master of Maat'Kare's Academy, and I'd like to "
"ask you..."
msgstr ""
"(alarmado) ¡Tenma, espera! Hay algo extraño en ellos… (gritando) ¡Ustedes, "
"enanos! Soy Ankhmare, Gran Maestro de la Academia de Maat'Kare, y me "
"gustaría preguntarles…"

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:209
msgid ""
"We know who ye are, old man, ye were exactly the one we were lookin' for – "
"as well as this little thief girl ye brought from beyond the sea! Now, be "
"good humans and die!"
msgstr ""
"Sabemos quién eres, viejo, eras exactamente a quien buscábamos —¡al igual "
"que a esta pequeña ladrona que trajiste de más allá del mar! ¡Ahora, sean "
"buenos humanos y mueran!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:213
msgid "What the...?! Why are they trying to murder us?"
msgstr "¿Qué demonios…?! ¿Por qué intentan asesinarnos?"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:217
msgid ""
"It seems that my suspicions were right, unfortunately: there is a faction of "
"the Aigathol acting behind Ansaxa' back. What I'm yet to figure out is why "
"they're after us..."
msgstr ""
"Parece que mis sospechas eran correctas, lamentablemente: hay una facción de "
"los Aigathol actuando a espaldas de Ansaxa. Lo que aún no logro entender es "
"por qué van tras nosotros…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:221
msgid ""
"And also why they've called me 'thief girl'. Frankly, that was so uncalled "
"for..."
msgstr ""
"Y también por qué me llamaron «niña ladrona». Francamente, eso fue "
"totalmente innecesario…"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:231
msgid "Defeat the dwarf leader"
msgstr "Derrotar al líder enano"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:245
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:348
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:592
msgid ""
"You may recruit/recall true elementals once again, and also recruit new "
"elementals through Ankhmare, but the veteran elementals belong to Olokun"
msgstr ""
"Puedes reclutar/reincorporar elementales verdaderos una vez más, y también "
"reclutar nuevos elementales a través de Ankhmare, pero los elementales "
"veteranos pertenecen a Olokun"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:264
msgid ""
"Ankhmare, not that I'm afraid of them or anything, but you never said "
"anything about this place being full of undead."
msgstr ""
"Ankhmare, no es que les tenga miedo ni nada, pero nunca dijiste nada sobre "
"que este lugar estuviera lleno de no-muertos."

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:268
msgid ""
"It shouldn't be... Considering that they're coming from Hiera'Laksha, I dare "
"say there's someone who doesn't want us to reach our goal."
msgstr ""
"No debería estarlo… Considerando que vienen de Hiera'Laksha, me atrevo a "
"decir que hay alguien que no quiere que lleguemos a nuestro objetivo."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:272
msgid "Could it be some dark mage sent by Ramoses?"
msgstr "¿Podría ser algún mago oscuro enviado por Ramoses?"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:276
msgid "I wouldn't rule out this theory, not now..."
msgstr "No descartaría esa teoría, no ahora…"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:288
msgid ""
"Now, dwarf commander, tell me, since you have nothing else to lose: why were "
"you sent after us, and why do you accuse Tenma of being a thief?"
msgstr ""
"Ahora, comandante enano, dime, ya que no tienes nada más que perder: ¿por "
"qué te enviaron tras nosotros y por qué acusas a Tenma de ser una ladrona?"

#. [message], speaker=Pelaitsil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:292
msgid ""
"(coughing) Ye think ye can always have it yer way, old man, but I won't do "
"whatever the hell ye want... Though I can tell ye, little girl, that we've "
"already dealt with that sneaky traitor ye sent to rob us..."
msgstr ""
"(tos) Piensas que siempre puedes salirte con la tuya, viejo, pero no haré lo "
"que demonios quieras… Aunque te puedo decir, pequeña, que ya nos encargamos "
"de ese traidor sigiloso que enviaste a robarnos…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:296
msgid ""
"What the hell are you... Wait, do you mean... (angry) You bastards, what did "
"you do to Algil?!"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué demonios estás…? Espera, ¿te refieres a…? (enojada) ¡Malditos "
"bastardos, ¿qué le hicieron a Algil?!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:312
msgid "It's no good, he's dead..."
msgstr "No sirve de nada, está muerto…"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:316
msgid ""
"Why did he have to do this...? (sigh) I suppose we can't study calmly at "
"Hiera'Laksha anymore, Tenma; if they knew we were coming here, they'll "
"certainly come in greater numbers when they receive no notice from the "
"rebels we've just fought. Let us discuss our next course of action later, "
"now we must rest - and to inform Lady Akashia on everything that has "
"happened since her demise..."
msgstr ""
"¿Por qué tuvo que hacer esto…? (suspiro) Supongo que ya no podremos estudiar "
"tranquilamente en Hiera'Laksha, Tenma; si sabían que veníamos aquí, seguro "
"vendrán en mayor número cuando no reciban noticias de los rebeldes que "
"acabamos de combatir. Discutamos nuestro próximo curso de acción después, "
"ahora debemos descansar —y informar a la dama Akashia de todo lo que ha "
"pasado desde su fallecimiento…"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:328
msgid ""
"It's no good, he's gone... But perhaps we can extract more information from "
"whoever is summoning all these undead"
msgstr ""
"No sirve de nada, se fue… Pero tal vez podamos extraer más información de "
"quien sea que está invocando a todos estos no-muertos."

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:376
msgid ""
"I knew it; only one person on this continent would have been able to summon "
"so many powerful undead at once: the 'God of Death', Wesir Amarnat."
msgstr ""
"Lo sabía; solo una persona en este continente habría podido invocar tantos "
"no-muertos poderosos a la vez: el «Dios de la Muerte», Wesir Amarnat."

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:380
msgid ""
"I'm flattered by such recognition of my skill, Master Ankhmare; "
"nevertheless, I must say I'm disappointed to see that you did not expect to "
"find any opposition to your schemes. Certainly you've noticed my enmity "
"towards you for a while now!"
msgstr ""
"Me halaga tal reconocimiento a mi habilidad, maestro Ankhmare; sin embargo, "
"debo decir que me decepciona ver que no esperabas encontrar oposición a tus "
"planes. ¡Seguro has notado mi enemistad hacia ti desde hace un tiempo!"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:384
msgid ""
"Of course I did, but I chose to believe that you would never stoop so low as "
"to ambush me in the middle of the wilderness, alone and unaided, and with a "
"bunch of dwarvish mercenaries!"
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto que sí, pero elegí creer que nunca caerías tan bajo como para "
"tender una emboscada en medio de la naturaleza, solo y sin ayuda, ¡y con un "
"montón de mercenarios enanos!"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:388
msgid ""
"And who said that I was trying to kill you? As unpleasant as it is to admit, "
"mere undead and dwarves would never have been enough to fell a Star Master "
"of New Maat'Kare. No, good Ankhmare, I've just set them as a hindrance to "
"you, so that I'd have enough time to complete my spell..."
msgstr ""
"¿Y quién dijo que intentaba matarte? Por desagradable que sea admitirlo, "
"simples no-muertos y enanos nunca habrían bastado para derribar a un Maestro "
"Estelar de Nueva Maat'Kare. No, buen Ankhmare, solo los puse como obstáculo "
"para ti, para tener tiempo suficiente de completar mi hechizo…"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:392
msgid ""
"Wesir, don't tell me... What are you going to do with Akashia's remains?"
msgstr "Wesir, no me digas… ¿Qué vas a hacer con los restos de Akashia?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:396
msgid "(surprised) Akashia... She's buried there...?!"
msgstr "(sorprendida) Akashia… ¿Está enterrada ahí…?!"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:400
msgid ""
"In that first audience with the girl Tenma Yozora I said that true "
"reincarnation is impossible. I spoke the truth... based on established lore. "
"But while you mused on the writings of Akhen Wadjet, I changed the "
"established lore and expanded it to new horizons..."
msgstr ""
"En esa primera audiencia con la chica Tenma Yozora dije que la verdadera "
"reencarnación es imposible. Dije la verdad… basada en el saber establecido. "
"Pero mientras tú meditabas sobre los escritos de Akhen Wadjet, yo cambié el "
"saber establecido y lo expandí a nuevos horizontes…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:418
msgid "(enraged) YOU CURSED MADMAN, DON'T YOU DARE LAY A FINGER ON HER BODY!!!"
msgstr ""
"(furiosa) ¡MALDITO LOCO, NO TE ATREVAS A PONERLE UN DEDO ENCIMA A SU CUERPO!"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:422
msgid ""
"Oh-ho, such revolt at my defiling of Akashia's tomb! It sounds almost as if "
"you really knew her... But we shall see what Akashia, Myra's most loyal "
"companion, has to say about your claim to being her reincarnation..."
msgstr ""
"Oh-ho, ¡qué revuelta por mi profanación de la tumba de Akashia! Casi suena "
"como si realmente la conocieras… Pero veremos qué tiene que decir Akashia, "
"la compañera más leal de Myra, sobre tu reclamo de ser su reencarnación…"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:426
msgid ""
"So you're doing that only to try and prove that Tenma is not the Dragon-"
"Slayer of the prophecy?!"
msgstr ""
"¿Entonces haces todo esto solo para intentar probar que Tenma no es la "
"Matadragones de la profecía?!"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:430
msgid ""
"Don't you play the fool on me, Ankhmare! I know, Ramoses knows, and everyone "
"who isn't in your pocket also knows that you're using this girl and the "
"prophecy to increase your own power and influence! But I shall not allow "
"another Menon Hekare to ruin what we have built! Now, Akashia of "
"Hiera'Shirsha, Founding Heroine, awaken from Death and help me unveil this "
"farce!"
msgstr ""
"¡No juegues al tonto conmigo, Ankhmare! Yo lo sé, Ramoses lo sabe, y todos "
"los que no están en tu bolsillo también saben que estás usando a esta chica "
"y la profecía para aumentar tu propio poder e influencia. ¡Pero no permitiré "
"que otro Menon Hekare arruine lo que hemos construido! ¡Ahora, Akashia de "
"Hiera’Shirsha, Heroína Fundadora, despierta de la Muerte y ayúdame a "
"desenmascarar esta farsa!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:469
msgid "Ak- Akashia...!"
msgstr "¡Ak- Akashia…!"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:473
msgid "He... He really did it, the fool!"
msgstr "Él… realmente lo hizo, ¡el loco!"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:477
msgid ""
"Excellent! Lady Akashia, my name is Wesir Amarnat; I have awakened you in an "
"age long after the one when you..."
msgstr ""
"¡Excelente! Dama Akashia, mi nombre es Wesir Amarnat; te he despertado en "
"una era mucho después de aquella en la que tú…"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:484
msgid "(shocked) AAAAAARRRRRRRGGGGHHHHHH!!! Lady Akashia...!!!"
msgstr "(impactado) ¡AAAAAAARRRRRRRGGGGHHHHHH! ¡Dama Akashia…!"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:496
msgid ""
"I care not about who you are, where I am, and what age it is; all I know is "
"that I was dead, as all beings are supposed to be when their time comes, "
"until you used some dark magic on me... Argh, to think that I'd become an "
"aberration like those of that disgusting lizard..."
msgstr ""
"No me importa quién eres, dónde estoy ni en qué era; lo único que sé es que "
"estaba muerta, como todos los seres deben estar cuando les llega su hora, "
"hasta que usaste alguna magia oscura en mí… Argh, pensar que me convertiría "
"en una aberración como esas del asqueroso lagarto…"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:500
msgid ""
"She managed to hit him with a physical weapon, even though he was wearing a "
"Robe of the Void...! The tales about the power of her sword were true, "
"then..."
msgstr ""
"¡Logró golpearlo con un arma física, aunque llevaba una Túnica del Vacío…! "
"Entonces las historias sobre el poder de su espada eran ciertas…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:504
msgid "Akashia, you..."
msgstr "Akashia, tú…"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:508
msgid "Tenma, wait! We're not sure she can tell friend and foe!"
msgstr ""
"¡Tenma, espera! ¡No estamos seguros de que pueda distinguir entre amigo y "
"enemigo!"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:515
msgid "Wait, stand back, you...!"
msgstr "¡Espera, retrocede, tú…!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:519
msgid "AKASHIA!!! (hugs her in tears)"
msgstr "¡¡¡AKASHIA!!! (la abraza llorando)"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:523
msgid "(stunned) Who the hell are you, and why are you soaking me in tears?!"
msgstr ""
"(atónita) ¿Quién demonios eres y por qué me estás empapando de lágrimas?!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:527
msgid ""
"(still crying) I'm so glad... I'm just so glad to see you... Wait, you're "
"wounded... By the Gods, what did that mad necromancer do to you?! It must be "
"hurting you so much..."
msgstr ""
"(todavía llorando) Estoy tan contenta… solo estoy tan contenta de verte… "
"Espera, estás herida… ¡Por los Dioses, qué le hizo ese nigromante loco?! "
"Debe dolerte muchísimo…"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:531
msgid ""
"This? This wasn't the necromancer's work, but a bird-winged bastard's... As "
"it was the wound that killed me, obviously it never healed. It's starting to "
"hurt like all hells, now that I'm thawing and my senses are fully "
"returning..."
msgstr ""
"¿Esto? Esto no fue obra del nigromante, sino de un bastardo alado… Como fue "
"la herida que me mató, obviamente nunca sanó. Está empezando a doler como "
"todos los infiernos, ahora que me estoy descongelando y mis sentidos "
"regresan por completo…"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:535
msgid ""
"(suddenly changing tone) Hold on, why the hell am I even bothering to tell "
"you that?! Get away from me at once, stranger!"
msgstr ""
"(cambiando de tono de repente) Espera, ¿por qué demonios me molesto en "
"contarte eso?! ¡Aléjate de mí de inmediato, extraña!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:539
msgid ""
"(suddenly changing tone as well) Yeah, hold on a sec you too, why am I "
"crying for seeing again someone I've never met before?! Damn you, 'another', "
"stop hijacking my emotions like this!"
msgstr ""
"(cambiando de tono también de repente) Sí, espera un segundo tú también, "
"¿por qué estoy llorando por ver de nuevo a alguien que nunca conocí antes?! "
"¡Maldita seas, «otra», deja de secuestrar mis emociones así!"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:543
msgid ""
"Lady Akashia, please allow me to explain everything. My name is Ankhmare, "
"and I'm a mage from New Maat'Kare; more than four thousand years have passed "
"since you, Myra and the other Heroes founded the original Maat'Kare. The "
"mage who brought you back to life wanted you to be part of his schemes, but "
"we're friends – if you so wish, we'll even help you peacefully return to the "
"sleep of death."
msgstr ""
"Dama Akashia, por favor permítame explicarlo todo. Mi nombre es Ankhmare y "
"soy un mago de Nueva Maat'Kare; han pasado más de cuatro mil años desde que "
"tú, Myra y los otros Héroes fundaron la Maat'Kare original. El mago que te "
"trajo de vuelta quería que formaras parte de sus planes, pero nosotros somos "
"amigos —si así lo deseas, incluso te ayudaremos a regresar pacíficamente al "
"sueño de la muerte."

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:547
msgid ""
"Argh... Now that I'm alive again, I don't feel like dying anytime soon... If "
"you're friends, then heal this damn wound; cursed Celestials, troubling me "
"even after all this time... And why am I even feeling so much pain, I "
"thought undead didn't feel anything!"
msgstr ""
"Argh… Ahora que estoy viva otra vez, no tengo ganas de morir pronto… Si son "
"amigos, entonces curen esta maldita herida; malditos Celestiales, "
"molestándome incluso después de tanto tiempo… ¿Y por qué estoy sintiendo "
"tanto dolor, pensaba que los no-muertos no sentían nada!"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:551
msgid ""
"I don't think you're an actual undead; Wesir has done something "
"unprecedented, so I can't tell you with certainty what has happened, but, if "
"you allow it, I may examine you."
msgstr ""
"No creo que seas una no-muerta real; Wesir ha hecho algo sin precedentes, "
"así que no puedo decirte con certeza qué ha pasado, pero, si me lo permites, "
"puedo examinarte."

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:555
msgid ""
"Then do that, please... Also, tell me what has happened during the time I "
"was out – especially the reason my Foundation lies in ruins in the middle of "
"a desert."
msgstr ""
"Entonces hazlo, por favor… También dime qué ha pasado durante el tiempo que "
"estuve fuera —especialmente la razón por la que mi Fundación está en ruinas "
"en medio de un desierto."

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:564
msgid ""
"I will, but first we must defeat these dwarves, they won't relent until "
"either us or them are dead."
msgstr ""
"Lo haré, pero primero debemos derrotar a estos enanos, no descansarán hasta "
"que uno de los dos bandos esté muerto."

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:568
msgid ""
"Fine, I could use this chance to exercise anyway, after having my body "
"frozen for so long..."
msgstr ""
"Está bien, de todos modos podría aprovechar esta oportunidad para "
"ejercitarme, después de tener mi cuerpo congelado tanto tiempo…"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:574
msgid "Defeat the rebel dwarves"
msgstr "Derrotar a los enanos rebeldes"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:586
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:35
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:41
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:41
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:492
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:716
msgid "Destruction of Akashia"
msgstr "Destrucción de Akashia"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:603
msgid ""
"I will, so please, follow me inside Hiera'Laksha; I really have a great deal "
"of things to tell you, after all..."
msgstr ""
"Lo haré, así que por favor sígueme dentro de Hiera'Laksha; realmente tengo "
"muchas cosas que contarte, después de todo…"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:626
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:553
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:778
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1480
msgid "How could I fail...?"
msgstr "¿Cómo pude fallar…?"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/31_Rekindling_Of_A_Flame.cfg:639
msgid ""
"If we keep taking so long to reach our goals, we'll never finish your "
"training, Tenma!"
msgstr ""
"¡Si seguimos tardando tanto en alcanzar nuestros objetivos, nunca "
"terminaremos tu entrenamiento, Tenma!"

#. [scenario], id=32_Fires_Of_Hatred
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:5
msgid "Fires of Hatred"
msgstr "Fuegos del Odio"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:23
msgid "Break the siege on Hammerstead by killing all enemy leaders"
msgstr "Romper el asedio a Hammerstead matando a todos los líderes enemigos"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:39
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:45
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:542
msgid "Death of Ansaxa"
msgstr "Muerte de Ansaxa"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:43
msgid ""
"NOTE: Both Tenma and Ankhmare can recruit from all hexes adjacent to their "
"initial keeps, including those on flat and lava terrain"
msgstr ""
"NOTA: Tanto Tenma como Ankhmare pueden reclutar desde todos los hexágonos "
"adyacentes a sus torreones iniciales, incluidos los de terreno plano y lava"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:78
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:109
msgid "Aigathol Dwarves"
msgstr "Enanos Aigathol"

#. [side], type=Dwarvish Dragonguard
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:117
msgid "Commander Acathus"
msgstr "Comandante Acathus"

#. [side], type=Dwarvish Sentinel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:137
msgid "Commander Thrithol"
msgstr "Comandante Thrithol"

#. [unit], id=Ragnur, type=Dwarvish Lord
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:178
msgid "Captain Ragnur"
msgstr "Capitán Ragnur"

#. [message], speaker=Glamdril
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:211
msgid ""
"Lady Ansaxa, I've received word that Star Master Ankhmare o' New Maat'Kare "
"has arrived to Hammerstead's gates; he says he wishes to speak with ye."
msgstr ""
"Dama Ansaxa, he recibido noticia de que el Maestro Estelar Ankhmare de Nueva "
"Maat'Kare ha llegado a las puertas de Hammerstead; dice que desea hablar "
"contigo."

#. [message], speaker=Ansaxa
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:215
msgid ""
"And why dinna ye let him in? He's an old n' trusted friend, he may come in "
"whenever he wants – though I wonder what brings him here so outta sudden..."
msgstr ""
"¿Y por qué no lo dejaste entrar? Es un viejo y confiable amigo, puede entrar "
"cuando quiera —aunque me pregunto qué lo trae aquí tan de repente…"

#. [message], speaker=Ragnur
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:219
msgid ""
"...Milady, I wish to retire now; my boys have recently returned from an "
"incursion on vampire territory, and so I need to talk with 'em."
msgstr ""
"…Milady, deseo retirarme ahora; mis muchachos acaban de regresar de una "
"incursión en territorio vampírico, así que necesito hablar con ellos."

#. [message], speaker=Ansaxa
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:223
msgid "You may go..."
msgstr "Puedes irte…"

#. [message], speaker=Ansaxa
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:235
msgid ""
"(laughing) My good ol' Ankhmare, it's good to see ye again after so long! "
"My, my, are those yer granddaughters? So big already, ye humans sure grow "
"quickly!"
msgstr ""
"(riendo) Mi buen viejo Ankhmare, ¡qué bueno verte de nuevo después de tanto "
"tiempo! Vaya, vaya, ¿esas son tus nietas? ¡Ya tan grandes, ustedes los "
"humanos crecen rápido!"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:239
msgid "I don't have children, my friend, remember?"
msgstr "No tengo hijos, amiga mía, ¿recuerdas?"

#. [message], speaker=Ansaxa
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:243
msgid ""
"Och, ye right, pardon my absent-mindedness... Anyway, what brings ye here "
"after so long and so suddenly? Do you want to start the Great Kinship "
"Festival earlier this year?"
msgstr ""
"Och, tienes razón, perdona mi despiste… De todos modos, ¿qué te trae aquí "
"después de tanto tiempo y tan de repente? ¿Quieres empezar el Gran Festival "
"del Parentela antes este año?"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:247
msgid ""
"I'm afraid that a much more serious matter brings me here, my friend. On my "
"way to Hiera'Laksha, I was attacked by a battalion of dwarves; they seemed "
"to be specifically targeting me and my friend Tenma..."
msgstr ""
"Me temo que un asunto mucho más serio me trae aquí, amiga mía. En mi camino "
"a Hiera'Laksha, fui atacado por un batallón de enanos; parecían estar "
"apuntando específicamente a mí y a mi amiga Tenma…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:251
msgid ""
"Not only that, but they called me a thief as well, and said that my friend, "
"Algil, had been dealt with for trying to rob something!"
msgstr ""
"No solo eso, también me llamaron ladrona y dijeron que ya se habían "
"encargado de mi amigo Algil por intentar robar algo!"

#. [message], speaker=Ansaxa
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:269
msgid ""
"(astonished) What devilry are ye talking about?! Surely ye know I'd never "
"send soldiers after ye?"
msgstr ""
"(asombrada) ¿De qué diablura estás hablando?! ¡Seguro sabes que nunca "
"enviaría soldados tras ustedes!"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:273
msgid ""
"Of course I do, I meant no accusation; in fact, those dwarves never claimed "
"to be under your orders. Still, the fact remains that we were ambushed by "
"dwarves seeking to kill us both; some of our elementals still bear marks of "
"their axes."
msgstr ""
"Por supuesto que sí, no quise acusarte; de hecho, esos enanos nunca "
"afirmaron estar bajo tus órdenes. Aun así, el hecho es que fuimos emboscados "
"por enanos que buscaban matarnos a ambos; algunos de nuestros elementales "
"todavía llevan marcas de sus hachas."

#. [message], speaker=Ansaxa
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:277
msgid "That puzzling, my friend... Unless..."
msgstr "Eso es desconcertante, amigo mío… A menos que…"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:281
msgid ""
"...Unless those rumours of a rebellious faction within your ranks are true. "
"I know you don't want to believe that there are traitors amongst your "
"people, but that is the only explanation. In my own city, powerful people "
"plot my downfall, and one amongst them went as far as to attack Tenma and I "
"at Hiera'Laksha. They could have joined forces expecting us to do the same "
"in order to suppress any opposition."
msgstr ""
"…A menos que esos rumores de una facción rebelde dentro de tus filas sean "
"ciertos. Sé que no quieres creer que hay traidores entre tu pueblo, pero esa "
"es la única explicación. En mi propia ciudad, gente poderosa trama mi caída, "
"y uno de ellos llegó tan lejos como para atacarnos a Tenma y a mí en "
"Hiera'Laksha. Podrían haberse aliado esperando que hiciéramos lo mismo para "
"suprimir cualquier oposición."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:285
msgid ""
"Also, what has happened to Algil? He left New Maat'Kare for these mountains "
"weeks ago, travelling by the Desert Road, which, according to you, is safe; "
"he should have arrived here already!"
msgstr ""
"Además, ¿qué pasó con Algil? Salió de Nueva Maat'Kare hacia estas montañas "
"hace semanas, viajando por el Camino del Desierto, que según tú es seguro; "
"¡ya debería haber llegado aquí!"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:303
msgid "*These dwarves sure are noisy...*"
msgstr "*Estos enanos sí que son ruidosos…*"

#. [message], speaker=Ansaxa
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:307
msgid ""
"Och, that lad did arrive here; I could never forget him, he brought such "
"earth-shattering talks... Now that I think about it, ye must be that girl "
"whom he followed from the Great Continent. Ye are friend of Ankhmare, so I "
"take it that ye are trustworthy; tell me, Tenma girl, what that lad said "
"about the Hammer of Ymer, is it true? Is it a troll relic by origin, stolen "
"from them by our ancestor Moradin?"
msgstr ""
"Och, ese muchacho sí llegó aquí; nunca podría olvidarlo, trajo unas charlas "
"que sacudieron la tierra… Ahora que lo pienso, debes ser esa chica a la que "
"siguió desde el Gran Continente. Eres amiga de Ankhmare, así que doy por "
"hecho que eres de fiar; dime, chica Tenma, lo que dijo ese muchacho sobre el "
"Martillo de Ymer, ¿es cierto? ¿Es una reliquia troll de origen, robada por "
"nuestro ancestro Moradin?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:311
msgid ""
"That's what Algil's father, the dwarf lord Aigcathil, has told me, and I "
"don't think he'd accuse his own people of such a heavy crime if that wasn't "
"true."
msgstr ""
"Eso es lo que me dijo el padre de Algil, el señor enano Aigcathil, y no creo "
"que acusara a su propio pueblo de un crimen tan grave si no fuera cierto."

#. [message], speaker=Ansaxa
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:315
msgid ""
"Och, my friends, I must tell ye that this has put me in a difficult "
"situation: if that's true, then justice demands we return the Hammer to the "
"trolls, but ye must understand how important that relic is for my people. "
"Not only is that a symbol of power and a safeguard, but we have an entire "
"order of warriors dedicated to protecting..."
msgstr ""
"Och, amigos míos, debo decirles que esto me pone en una situación difícil: "
"si eso es cierto, la justicia exige que devolvamos el Martillo a los trolls, "
"pero deben entender lo importante que es esa reliquia para mi pueblo. No "
"solo es un símbolo de poder y una salvaguarda, sino que tenemos toda una "
"orden de guerreros dedicada a proteger…"

#. [message], speaker=Ansaxa
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:333
msgid ""
"(angry) By all Nine Hells, dinna ye see we're having a conversation here?! "
"What's the meaning of all this fuss?!"
msgstr ""
"(enojada) ¡Por todos los Nueve Infiernos, no ves que estamos teniendo una "
"conversación aquí?! ¿Qué significa todo este alboroto?!"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:337
msgid ""
"(unsheathing sword) It means, Dwarf Lady, that we're being surrounded..."
msgstr "(desenvainando espada) Significa, dama enana, que nos están rodeando…"

#. [unit], id=Nardrus, type=Dwarvish Explorer
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:342
msgid "Captain Nardrus"
msgstr "Capitán Nardrus"

#. [message], speaker=Ansaxa
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:366
msgid ""
"Sentry Captain, what do ye think ye doing?! Do ye know the name of this act "
"of yours?!"
msgstr ""
"¡Capitán de centinelas, qué crees que estás haciendo?! ¿Sabes el nombre de "
"este acto tuyo?!"

#. [message], speaker=Nardrus
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:370
msgid ""
"Treason is the name, Arcanister, but not mine; mine is the fight to preserve "
"dwarfdom's integrity. Treason is what ye have done since ye were elected to "
"wield the Sceptre of Sigdral: putting the Aigathol at the service of the "
"humans, doing the bidding of vampires and orcs after they destroyed three of "
"our fortresses, and now having thoughts of yielding our greatest power to "
"foreigners emerged out of some hole! But no longer, Arcanister, no longer! "
"Now, boys, for our clan and for Lord Narthaol, attack!"
msgstr ""
"Traidora es el nombre, Arcanista, pero no el mío; el mío es la lucha por "
"preservar la integridad del enanismo. Traición es lo que has hecho desde que "
"fuiste elegida para empuñar el Cetro de Sigdral: poner a los Aigathol al "
"servicio de los humanos, cumplir los deseos de vampiros y orcos después de "
"que destruyeron tres de nuestras fortalezas, ¡y ahora tener pensamientos de "
"ceder nuestro mayor poder a extranjeros salidos de algún agujero! ¡Pero ya "
"no, Arcanista, ya no! ¡Ahora, muchachos, por nuestro clan y por el señor "
"Narthaol, ataquen!"

#. [message], speaker=Ansaxa
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:374
msgid ""
"Narthaol, you say? Ha! I should have know sooner that stupid midget had "
"Motsoghnir leanings; I just didn't expect him to go as low as this..."
msgstr ""
"¿Narthaol, dices? ¡Ja! Debí saber antes que ese estúpido enano tenía "
"inclinaciones motsoghnir; solo no esperaba que cayera tan bajo como esto…"

#. [message], speaker=Glamdril
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:378
msgid ""
"Worry not, Lady Ansaxa, ye still have legions of loyal dwarves by yer side – "
"and we shan't allow ye to fall before such dirty treachery!"
msgstr ""
"No te preocupes, dama Ansaxa, todavía tienes legiones de enanos leales a tu "
"lado —¡y no permitiremos que caigas ante tal sucia traición!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:382
msgid ""
"I'll help you break this ambush, but I need to search for Algil too, he must "
"be starving in a dungeon right now..."
msgstr ""
"Te ayudaré a romper esta emboscada, pero también necesito buscar a Algil, "
"debe estar muriendo de hambre en una mazmorra ahora mismo…"

#. [message], speaker=Ansaxa
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:386
msgid ""
"Fair enough, but don't waste time searching for him now; if the traitors "
"have captured him, he's either dead or in their main base, wherever it may "
"be."
msgstr ""
"Muy bien, pero no pierdas tiempo buscándolo ahora; si los traidores lo "
"capturaron, o está muerto o en su base principal, donde sea que esté."

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:397
msgid ""
"Huh, not bad. Seems like this age's magic really is not to be looked down "
"on. Then again, this age's magic has put a <i>second sun</i> up in the sky..."
msgstr ""
"Huh, no está mal. Parece que la magia de esta era realmente no debe "
"subestimarse. Aunque, por otro lado, la magia de esta era ha puesto un "
"<i>segundo sol</i> en el cielo…"

#. [message], speaker=Nardrus
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:409
msgid "Ugh!!!... At least now I go to the halls of the true dwarves..."
msgstr "¡Ugh!!!… Al menos ahora voy a los salones de los verdaderos enanos…"

#. [message], speaker=Ansaxa
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:413
msgid ""
"Poor idiot... I'll make sure Narthaol pays dearly for doing this to my "
"people...!"
msgstr ""
"Pobre idiota… ¡Me aseguraré de que Narthaol pague caro por hacerle esto a mi "
"pueblo…!"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:417
msgid ""
"Do not lower your guard, there are more traitor dwarves coming in the "
"distance!"
msgstr "¡No bajen la guardia, hay más enanos traidores viniendo a lo lejos!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:439
msgid "Erm, excuse me, but what did she mean by 'Motsoghnir leanings'?"
msgstr "Ehm, perdón, pero ¿qué quiso decir con «inclinaciones motsoghnir»?"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:443
msgid ""
"Ages ago, there was another dwarvish clan living in Netjer-Ta, called the "
"Motsoghnir; during the days of Akhen Wadjet, they went to war in a bid for "
"dwarven supremacy on this continent. Once defeated, most were absorbed into "
"the Aigathol, while those who refused to surrender formed roving bands that, "
"over the centuries, slowly died out. Since then, 'Motsoghnir' has become, "
"amongst dwarves, a synonym of inflated pride and hostility towards other "
"races."
msgstr ""
"Hace edades, había otro clan enano viviendo en Netjer-Ta, llamado los "
"Motsoghnir; durante los días de Akhen Wadjet, fueron a la guerra en un "
"intento por la supremacía enana en este continente. Una vez derrotados, la "
"mayoría fueron absorbidos por los Aigathol, mientras que los que se negaron "
"a rendirse formaron bandas errantes que, con los siglos, lentamente se "
"extinguieron. Desde entonces, «Motsoghnir» se ha convertido, entre los "
"enanos, en sinónimo de orgullo inflado y hostilidad hacia otras razas."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:465
msgid "... (stares at Akashia)"
msgstr "… (mira fijamente a Akashia)"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:469
msgid "... (pretends not to notice her)"
msgstr "… (finge no notarla)"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:473
msgid "... (keeps staring)"
msgstr "… (sigue mirando fijamente)"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:477
msgid "... (turns the other way)"
msgstr "… (se da la vuelta)"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:481
msgid "... Hrumph! (turns the other way as well)"
msgstr "… ¡Hrumph! (se da la vuelta también)"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:485
msgid ""
"(to himself) I bet they don't realise how much has been said between them "
"just now..."
msgstr ""
"(para sí mismo) Apuesto a que no se dan cuenta de cuánto se ha dicho entre "
"ellas justo ahora…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:499
msgid ""
"I wanted to ask it before, but you didn't let me: what's with this cave? I "
"mean, we simply appeared here from another cave, and there are all these "
"glowing rails..."
msgstr ""
"Quería preguntarlo antes, pero no me dejaste: ¿qué pasa con esta cueva? "
"Quiero decir, simplemente aparecimos aquí desde otra cueva, y hay todos "
"estos rieles brillantes…"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:503
msgid ""
"Hammerstead is a city completely enclosed by rock; its only openings to the "
"surface world are the ducts that constantly renews the air in these caves. "
"Thus, the only way of entering or leaving this place is through teleporting "
"runes, which, by their turn, are powered by energy received through the "
"rails from the magma fall at the centre of this room."
msgstr ""
"Hammerstead es una ciudad completamente encerrada por roca; sus únicas "
"aperturas al mundo superficial son los conductos que renuevan constantemente "
"el aire en estas cuevas. Por lo tanto, la única forma de entrar o salir de "
"este lugar es a través de runas de teletransportación, que, a su vez, son "
"alimentadas por energía recibida a través de los rieles desde la caída de "
"magma en el centro de esta sala."

#. [message], speaker=Ansaxa
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:512
msgid ""
"(disgusted) Curses upon curses on that traitor, I'll never forgive him for "
"making me do this..."
msgstr ""
"(asqueada) Maldiciones sobre maldiciones sobre ese traidor, nunca le "
"perdonaré por obligarme a hacer esto…"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:516
msgid ""
"Trust me, I do understand your feelings, but you must not back now; you must "
"find Narthaol and bring him to justice. I'm afraid, though, that even his "
"fall will not convince his followers to give up his ways..."
msgstr ""
"Créeme, entiendo tus sentimientos, pero no debes retroceder ahora; debes "
"encontrar a Narthaol y llevarlo ante la justicia. Me temo, sin embargo, que "
"incluso su caída no convencerá a sus seguidores de abandonar sus caminos…"

#. [message], speaker=Ansaxa
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:520
msgid ""
"I know, I know! (sigh) Sorry for screaming at you, you even helped saving "
"me..."
msgstr ""
"Lo sé, ¡lo sé! (suspiro) Perdón por gritarte, incluso ayudaste a salvarme…"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:524
msgid "Don't worry, I understand..."
msgstr "No te preocupes, entiendo…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:528
msgid ""
"Also, we'll help you find and defeat this Narthaol; I need to find out "
"what's happened to my friend, after all."
msgstr ""
"Además, te ayudaremos a encontrar y derrotar a este Narthaol; después de "
"todo, necesito saber qué le pasó a mi amigo."

#. [message], speaker=Ansaxa
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:532
msgid ""
"Thank you again, friends... Now, let us give the dead their deserved rest – "
"every single one of them; even if they were foolish and arrogant, in the end "
"they were still my people..."
msgstr ""
"Gracias de nuevo, amigos… Ahora, demos a los muertos el descanso que merecen "
"—a cada uno de ellos; aunque fueran necios y arrogantes, al final seguían "
"siendo mi pueblo…"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:570
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:795
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1502
msgid "Argh... If I just had my original power..."
msgstr "Argh… Si tan solo tuviera mi poder original…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:574
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:799
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1506
msgid "Akashia, no!!! How could I let her die again...?!"
msgstr "¡Akashia, no! ¿Cómo pude dejarla morir otra vez…?!"

#. [message], speaker=Ansaxa
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:591
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:816
msgid "I am... dying...?"
msgstr "¿Estoy… muriendo…?"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:595
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:820
msgid ""
"No! Without her, the rebels will take over the Aigathol! With them sided "
"with Ramoses, this entire continent will cease being a safe place for us..."
msgstr ""
"¡No! ¡Sin ella, los rebeldes tomarán el control de los Aigathol! Con ellos "
"aliados a Ramoses, todo este continente dejará de ser un lugar seguro para "
"nosotros…"

#. [message], speaker=Ansaxa
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/32_Fires_Of_Hatred.cfg:608
msgid ""
"We shoulda defeated the rebels sooner, more of them are coming! I dinna "
"think I can bear the sight of such fratricidal battle any longer...!"
msgstr ""
"¡Debimos derrotar a los rebeldes antes, vienen más de ellos! ¡No creo que "
"pueda soportar por más tiempo la vista de tal batalla fratricida…!"

#. [scenario], id=33_Crimson_Caves
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:5
msgid "Crimson Caves"
msgstr "Cuevas Carmesí"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:25
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:526
msgid "Find and defeat the rebel leader Narthaol"
msgstr "Encontrar y derrotar al líder rebelde Narthaol"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:29
msgid "Find Algil"
msgstr "Encontrar a Algil"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:49
msgid "HINT: Search for Algil at keeps and castles."
msgstr "PISTA: Busca a Algil en torreones y castillos."

#. [side], type=Dwarvish Runemaster
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:83
msgid "Lord Narthaol"
msgstr "Señor Narthaol"

#. [side], type=Sangel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:129
msgid "Aleron"
msgstr "Aleron"

#. [side], type=Sangel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:134
msgid "Vampire Mercenaries"
msgstr "Mercenarios vampiros"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:151
msgid "Vampires"
msgstr "Vampiros"

#. [message], speaker=Glamdril
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:328
msgid ""
"There, Lady Ansaxa: tis' the mountain where the scouts have sighted the "
"traitors."
msgstr ""
"Allí, dama Ansaxa: esa es la montaña donde los exploradores han avistado a "
"los traidores."

#. [message], speaker=Ansaxa
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:332
msgid ""
"Still, I see none around here; they're probably hiding in some hard shell of "
"a fortress deep inside the mountain. It shouldn't bother us, but I'm not "
"sure about ye, human friends..."
msgstr ""
"Aun así, no veo a ninguno por aquí; probablemente se están escondiendo en "
"algún caparazón duro de fortaleza dentro de la montaña. No debería "
"molestarnos, pero no estoy segura de ustedes, amigos humanos…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:336
msgid ""
"Don't worry, I've lost count of how many underground fights I've been to."
msgstr ""
"No te preocupes, he perdido la cuenta de cuántas peleas subterráneas he "
"tenido."

#. [message], speaker=Ansaxa
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:340
msgid ""
"In that case, let's get into this mountain and search for yer friend and for "
"Narthaol – but do not kill him; I've got a few things to discuss with him "
"first..."
msgstr ""
"En ese caso, entremos en esta montaña y busquemos a tu amigo y a Narthaol —"
"pero no lo maten; tengo unas cuantas cosas que discutir con él primero…"

#. [message], speaker=Ansaxa
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:344
msgid ""
"And beware of traps; Narthaol was a runemaster, surely he's riddled those "
"caves with them."
msgstr ""
"Y cuidado con las trampas; Narthaol era un maestro de runas, seguro que ha "
"llenado esas cuevas de ellas."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:359
msgid "Wait, are those humans fighting alongside the rebels?"
msgstr "Espera, ¿esos humanos están luchando junto a los rebeldes?"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:363
msgid ""
"Those are vampires, creatures born from a failed Windsong experiment from "
"ages ago. You're not totally wrong, though, as they were once human. "
"(smirking) Heh, fighting them truly brings back memories..."
msgstr ""
"Esos son vampiros, criaturas nacidas de un experimento fallido de las Hijas "
"del Viento hace edades. No estás del todo equivocada, sin embargo, pues "
"alguna vez fueron humanos. (sonriendo) Heh, luchar contra ellos realmente "
"trae recuerdos…"

#. [message], speaker=Glamdril
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:367
msgid ""
"Hypocritical Narthaol, they call us traitors for befriending humans and "
"dwarves, while he does the same with vampires!"
msgstr ""
"¡Hipócrita Narthaol, nos llaman traidores por hacernos amigos de humanos y "
"enanos, mientras él hace lo mismo con vampiros!"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:371
msgid ""
"The presence of vampires here trouble us, as it gives the rebels  greater "
"numbers."
msgstr ""
"La presencia de vampiros aquí nos preocupa, pues les da a los rebeldes "
"mayores números."

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:375
msgid ""
"Stop whining already, old man. Vampires are vulnerable to arcane and fire "
"spells; they will fall like Autumn leaves before these tricks of yours and "
"that girl!"
msgstr ""
"Deja de quejarte ya, viejo. Los vampiros son vulnerables a hechizos arcanos "
"y de fuego; caerán como hojas de otoño ante estos trucos tuyos y los de esa "
"chica."

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:379
msgid ""
"(whisper) To think that such a bellicose hothead was one of the people who "
"founded our peaceful civilization..."
msgstr ""
"(susurro) Pensar que una cabeza caliente tan belicosa fue una de las "
"personas que fundaron nuestra civilización pacífica…"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:394
msgid "(smirking) Oh, nice, more vampires to fight!"
msgstr "(sonriendo con ironía) ¡Oh, qué bien, más vampiros para pelear!"

#. [message], speaker=Ansaxa
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:398
msgid "Darn it, girl, tis' no joke! We can't take on so many enemies at once!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldición, chica, esto no es broma! ¡No podemos enfrentar a tantos enemigos "
"a la vez!"

#. [message], speaker=Krul
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:402
msgid ""
"I've always known the Kronig clan to be unworthy scum, but to think they'd "
"truly place themselves as mercenaries to the dwarves that have killed so "
"many of our folk... Noble warriors, let us wipe them out for good, my eyes "
"bear not such disgusting sight any longer..."
msgstr ""
"Siempre supe que el clan Kronig era una escoria indigna, pero pensar que "
"realmente se pondrían como mercenarios de los enanos que han matado a tantos "
"de los nuestros… ¡Guerreros nobles, acabemos con ellos de una vez por todas, "
"mis ojos ya no soportan tal visión repugnante!"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:406
msgid "Hold on, I recognize that vampire lord, he's one of our allies!"
msgstr "¡Espera, reconozco a ese señor vampiro, es uno de nuestros aliados!"

#. [message], speaker=Krul
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:410
msgid ""
"(surprised) This voice... But if it isn't the Star Master of Maat'Kare in "
"flesh and blood! I'm truly pleased for seeing that our southern allies have "
"bothered to come into these cold mountains to help us get rid of these "
"unworthy dwarves, even though we haven't asked for it!"
msgstr ""
"(sorprendido) Esta voz… ¡Pero si no es el Maestro Estelar de Maat'Kare en "
"carne y hueso! Realmente me alegra ver que nuestros aliados del sur se hayan "
"molestado en venir a estas frías montañas a ayudarnos a deshacernos de estos "
"enanos indignos, ¡aunque no se lo hayamos pedido!"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:414
msgid ""
"To be honest, Lord Krul, I came here following my friend, Ansaxa, Lady of "
"the Aigathol, as she chases after a vassal who has betrayed her. However, "
"now that I see that he's your foe as much as he's ours, I say let us fight "
"together against this common threat!"
msgstr ""
"Para ser honesto, señor Krul, vine aquí siguiendo a mi amiga Ansaxa, dama de "
"los Aigathol, ya que persigue a un vasallo que la traicionó. Sin embargo, "
"ahora que veo que él es enemigo tuyo tanto como nuestro, digo ¡luchemos "
"juntos contra esta amenaza común!"

#. [unit], id=Krul, type=Sire
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:423
msgid "Lord Krul"
msgstr "Señor Krul"

#. [unit], id=Tempest, type=Sword Dancer
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:438
msgid "Tempest"
msgstr "Tempestad"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:508
msgid "Wait, there's someone in this cell..."
msgstr "Espera, hay alguien en esta celda…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:512
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:739
msgid ""
"That's Algil! Great Gods, he looks awful... What have those stupid rebels "
"done to you, my friend?!"
msgstr ""
"¡Es Algil! ¡Grandes Dioses, se ve horrible…! ¿Qué te hicieron esos estúpidos "
"rebeldes, amigo mío?!"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:516
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:743
msgid ""
"(in pain) Argh... How pathetic... This is the second time... that you save "
"my arse..."
msgstr ""
"(con dolor) Argh… Qué patético… Esta es la segunda vez… que me salvas el "
"pellejo…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:520
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:747
msgid ""
"Pay me back later with some beer, now you must stay still while I heal you..."
msgstr ""
"Devuélvemelo después con unas cervezas, ahora quédate quieto mientras te "
"curo…"

#. [message], speaker=Ansaxa
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:569
msgid ""
"(enraged) NARTHAOL, YE BASTARD, WON'T YE EVEN HAVE THE DECENCY OF SHOWING "
"UP?!"
msgstr ""
"(furiosa) ¡NARTHAOL, MALDITO BASTARDO, ACASO NO TIENES NI LA DECENCIA DE "
"APARECER?!"

#. [message], speaker=Narthaol
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:573
msgid ""
"Ha ha, ye are one to talk about decency, ye who takes pleasure in bowing "
"dwarfdom to the likes of humans and orcs!"
msgstr ""
"Ja ja, tú eres la que habla de decencia, tú que te complace inclinar al "
"enanismo ante humanos y orcos."

#. [message], speaker=Glamdril
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:577
msgid ""
"Ye bring civil war to our nation, and yet ye talk about besmirching the "
"honour of our people?! Ye disgusting hypocrite, I shall crush this dung-"
"filled head of ye with my own hammer!"
msgstr ""
"¡Tú traes guerra civil a nuestra nación, y aun así hablas de mancillar el "
"honor de nuestro pueblo?! ¡Hipócrita asqueroso, aplastaré esa cabeza llena "
"de estiércol con mi propio martillo!"

#. [message], speaker=Ansaxa
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:581
msgid ""
"Glamdril, don't ye go disobeying me like he did! I told ye, I want him alive!"
msgstr "¡Glamdril, no me desobedezcas como él! Te dije, ¡lo quiero vivo!"

#. [message], speaker=Narthaol
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:593
msgid ""
"To the Nine Hells with ye... Once again treachery and shame have bested "
"honour..."
msgstr ""
"A los Nueve Infiernos contigo… Una vez más la traición y la vergüenza han "
"vencido al honor…"

#. [message], speaker=Ansaxa
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:597
msgid ""
"Narthaol, yer selfish and brutal actions have brought death and destruction "
"to the Aigathol; worse, ye have sown seeds of hatred in the hearts of too "
"many dwarves! Such crimes are more than enough to earn ye the punishment of "
"the Runes of Pain, but... I'm not one to judge ye, for I too have made "
"mistakes. Had I paid more attention to my own folk, I would have noticed yer "
"anger sooner, and so I could have prevented this tragedy from befalling us. "
"Thus, I'm willing to forgive yer crimes, if ye prove yourself willing to "
"compensate your mistakes..."
msgstr ""
"Narthaol, tus acciones egoístas y brutales han traído muerte y destrucción a "
"los Aigathol; peor aún, has sembrado semillas de odio en los corazones de "
"demasiados enanos. Tales crímenes son más que suficientes para ganarte el "
"castigo de las Runas del Dolor, pero… no soy quién para juzgarte, pues yo "
"también he cometido errores. Si hubiera prestado más atención a mi propio "
"pueblo, habría notado tu ira antes y así podría haber evitado que esta "
"tragedia nos cayera encima. Por eso, estoy dispuesta a perdonar tus "
"crímenes, si demuestras estar dispuesto a compensar tus errores…"

#. [message], speaker=Narthaol
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:601
msgid ""
"Ye... Ye think that ye will have it yer way? Thinking that, by breaking my "
"body, ye can break my spirit, my honour?! Foolish woman, ye don't know..."
msgstr ""
"Tú… ¿Crees que saldrás con la tuya? ¿Piensas que rompiendo mi cuerpo puedes "
"romper mi espíritu, mi honor?! Mujer necia, no sabes…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:605
msgid "SHUT UP, YOU IDIOT!!!"
msgstr "¡¡¡CÁLLATE, IDIOTA!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Narthaol
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:609
msgid "(livid) Human, how dare ye..."
msgstr "(lívido) Humana, ¿cómo te atreves…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:613
msgid ""
"How dare I what, call you to your senses?! Do you have any idea of what "
"you're doing, and of what is happening to the world outside this continent?! "
"I'll tell you then, dwarf lord, there is war after war in the Great "
"Continent; humans, dwarves, trolls, elves, drakes and saurians all killing "
"each other for pride and honour, and all the while this world dies under the "
"two suns! What's the point of fighting for your people's pride if they die?! "
"Where's the glory in leading your people to doom?!"
msgstr ""
"¿Cómo me atrevo a qué, a hacerte entrar en razón?! ¿Tienes idea de lo que "
"estás haciendo, y de lo que está pasando en el mundo fuera de este "
"continente?! Te lo diré entonces, señor enano: hay guerra tras guerra en el "
"Gran Continente; humanos, enanos, trolls, elfos, dracos y saurios matándose "
"unos a otros por orgullo y honor, ¡y mientras tanto este mundo muere bajo "
"los dos soles! ¿Cuál es el sentido de luchar por el orgullo de tu pueblo si "
"mueren?! ¿Dónde está la gloria en llevar a tu pueblo a la perdición?!"

#. [message], speaker=Narthaol
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:617
msgid ""
"If... If ye think I will bow to ye, puny human... let this be my answer... "
"Arcanister, I will never accept a traitor of their own kind like ye as my "
"ruler! I now go join the ranks of the true dwarves in the halls of our "
"forefathers; my people, if ye want to keep yer dignity and not become the "
"plaything of lesser creatures, this is yer only choice..."
msgstr ""
"Si… si piensas que me inclinaré ante ti, humana insignificante… que esta sea "
"mi respuesta… Arcanista, ¡nunca aceptaré a una traidora de su propia raza "
"como tú como mi gobernante! Ahora voy a unirme a las filas de los verdaderos "
"enanos en los salones de nuestros antepasados; mi pueblo, si quieren "
"conservar su dignidad y no convertirse en juguete de criaturas menores, esta "
"es su única opción…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:633
msgid ""
"So, what are you going to do now, dwarves? Will you follow this so-called "
"'leader' of yours and throw away your lives? From the caves of the Windy "
"Mountains in the Great Continent to Netjer-Ta, your ancestors have done "
"countless sacrifices, and spilled much of their own blood, and all for you "
"to throw your lives away because of this senseless hatred?"
msgstr ""
"Entonces, ¿qué van a hacer ahora, enanos? ¿Seguirán a este supuesto «líder» "
"suyo y arrojarán sus vidas? Desde las cuevas de las Montañas Ventosas en el "
"Gran Continente hasta Netjer-Ta, sus ancestros han hecho innumerables "
"sacrificios y derramado mucha de su propia sangre, ¿y todo para que ustedes "
"arrojen sus vidas por este odio sin sentido?"

#. [message], speaker=Ansaxa
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:637
msgid ""
"Foreign as she may be, her words are befitting the Aigathol's ears... "
"Followers of Narthaol, ye have helped him wreak destruction in our nation, "
"but ye are still my people; if he managed to sway so many of ye to his side, "
"it is also my fault for not fulfilling what ye expected of me as your "
"leader... And for this reason, I'll give ye another chance: stay here in "
"freedom if ye wish, and reflect on this girl's words; and in the end, if ye "
"still think Narthaol's ways were the best for dwarfdom, then I promise I "
"shall let ye go in peace. But, if ye feel regretful, know that each of ye "
"still has a place in our halls."
msgstr ""
"Por extranjera que sea, sus palabras son dignas de los oídos de los "
"Aigathol… Seguidores de Narthaol, ayudaron a causar destrucción en nuestra "
"nación, pero siguen siendo mi pueblo; si él logró convencer a tantos de "
"ustedes de su lado, también es mi culpa por no cumplir con lo que esperaban "
"de mí como su líder… Y por esta razón, les daré otra oportunidad: quédense "
"aquí en libertad si lo desean, y reflexionen sobre las palabras de esta "
"chica; y al final, si aún piensan que los caminos de Narthaol eran los "
"mejores para el enanismo, entonces prometo que los dejaré ir en paz. Pero si "
"sienten arrepentimiento, sepan que cada uno de ustedes aún tiene un lugar en "
"nuestros salones."

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:641
msgid ""
"To think that such fratricide would take place amongst us again after all "
"that happened in the War of the Jewel... Will we ever learn with the "
"mistakes of our ancestors...?"
msgstr ""
"Pensar que tal fratricidio ocurriría entre nosotros otra vez después de todo "
"lo que pasó en la Guerra de la Joya… ¿Alguna vez aprenderemos de los errores "
"de nuestros ancestros…?"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:645
msgid ""
"The memories of humans, dwarves and even elves last only as long as their "
"generations; even if a worldwide catastrophe were to happen, as long as the "
"minds and spirits that caused it remained the same, it would take few "
"centuries, maybe even decades, for the mistake to be repeated."
msgstr ""
"Los recuerdos de humanos, enanos e incluso elfos duran solo mientras duran "
"sus generaciones; incluso si ocurriera una catástrofe mundial, mientras las "
"mentes y espíritus que la causaron permanezcan iguales, bastarían pocos "
"siglos, tal vez incluso décadas, para que el error se repitiera."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:649
msgid ""
"So that means we have to keep reminding those who come after us of our "
"history; we can't end hatred, violence and injustice forever, but we sure as "
"the Suns can fight them all, and prevent them from taking over our world."
msgstr ""
"Entonces eso significa que tenemos que seguir recordándoles a los que vienen "
"después nuestra historia; no podemos acabar con el odio, la violencia y la "
"injusticia para siempre, pero seguro que sí podemos luchar contra todos "
"ellos, y evitar que se apoderen de nuestro mundo."

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:653
msgid ""
"If you say so... (smiles) *I see... Even after all this time, all the things "
"you've endured and even after being born as another person, you haven't "
"changed at all, Myra...*"
msgstr ""
"Si tú lo dices… (sonríe) *Ya veo… Incluso después de todo este tiempo, todas "
"las cosas que has soportado e incluso después de nacer como otra persona, no "
"has cambiado en absoluto, Myra…*"

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:735
msgid "Look, there's someone here..."
msgstr "Mira, hay alguien aquí…"

#. [message], speaker=Ansaxa
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/33_Crimson_Caves.cfg:833
msgid ""
"Besieging a well-guarded and well-provisioned enemy at his own fortress and "
"far from home can be risky; our forces are decreasing continuously, while "
"the rebels can block us with few warriors by using the narrowness of the "
"tunnels. At this rate, even a victory won't be worthwhile any more!"
msgstr ""
" sitiar a un enemigo bien protegido y bien abastecido en su propia fortaleza "
"y lejos de casa puede ser arriesgado; nuestras fuerzas disminuyen "
"continuamente, mientras que los rebeldes pueden bloquearnos con pocos "
"guerreros aprovechando la estrechez de los túneles. ¡A este ritmo, incluso "
"una victoria ya no valdrá la pena!"

#. [scenario], id=34_The_Seers_Prophecy
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:5
msgid "The Seer's Prophecy"
msgstr "La Profecía del Vidente"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:25
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:468
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:676
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:920
msgid "Defeat General Ramoses"
msgstr "Derrotar al general Ramoses"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:45
msgid ""
"Ramoses' death would cause civil war in New Maat'Kare; find another way to "
"defeat him, or else just wait for the opportunity to appear.\n"
"You may destroy many of the Wall's elementals by moving a unit next to one "
"of the Founders' statues"
msgstr ""
"La muerte de Ramoses causaría guerra civil en Nueva Maat'Kare; encuentra "
"otra forma de derrotarlo, o simplemente espera a que aparezca la "
"oportunidad.\n"
"Puedes destruir muchos de los elementales del Muro moviendo una unidad junto "
"a una de las estatuas de los Fundadores"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:140
msgid "Academy's Supernovae"
msgstr "Supernovas de la Academia"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:164
msgid "New Maat'Kare's Defences"
msgstr "Defensas de Nueva Maat'Kare"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:255
msgid "I've reached one of the statues! I'll destroy the crystal now!"
msgstr "¡He llegado a una de las estatuas! ¡Destruiré el cristal ahora!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:259
msgid "(crash!)"
msgstr "(¡crash!)"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:286
msgid ""
"I hadn't seen so many elementals since the Battle of the Founding... Is this "
"how Maat'Karians greet newcomers nowadays?"
msgstr ""
"No había visto tantos elementales desde la Batalla de la Fundación… ¿Así es "
"como saludan los maatkarianos a los recién llegados hoy en día?"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:290
msgid ""
"Certainly not. This is a defence formation known as Heaven and Earth's Wall, "
"in which the elements are turned into soldiers to defend the city. To see "
"our strongest defence used against us only confirms our fears..."
msgstr ""
"Desde luego que no. Esta es una formación defensiva conocida como Muro del "
"Cielo y la Tierra, en la que los elementos se convierten en soldados para "
"defender la ciudad. Ver nuestra defensa más fuerte usada contra nosotros "
"solo confirma nuestros temores…"

#. [message], speaker=Ramoses
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:294
msgid ""
"You've taken longer to return than I expected, imposters; you must have "
"prepared quite a well-woven story to deceive and manipulate my people, but "
"I'll make sure that your poisonous words no longer twists their hearts!"
msgstr ""
"Han tardado más en regresar de lo que esperaba, impostores; deben haber "
"preparado una historia muy bien tejida para engañar y manipular a mi pueblo, "
"¡pero me aseguraré de que sus palabras venenosas no tuerzan más sus "
"corazones!"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:298
msgid ""
"(angry) Ramoses, stop this insanity at once! Do you hate me so much as to "
"risk losing the best chance this world has ever had to destroy the Sky "
"Dragon?!"
msgstr ""
"(enojado) ¡Ramoses, detén esta locura de inmediato! ¿Me odias tanto como "
"para arriesgar la mejor oportunidad que este mundo ha tenido jamás de "
"destruir al Dragón del Cielo?!"

#. [message], speaker=Ramoses
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:302
msgid ""
"And yet you insist on that fairy tale... I shall not waste my time trying to "
"convince you of your own flaws, Ankhmare; rather, I'll let one of your most "
"direct victims speak for himself..."
msgstr ""
"Y aun así insistes en ese cuento de hadas… No perderé mi tiempo tratando de "
"convencerte de tus propios defectos, Ankhmare; más bien, dejaré que una de "
"tus víctimas más directas hable por sí misma"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:317
msgid "Wesir...!"
msgstr "¡Wesir…!"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:321
msgid ""
"Come now, don't say you're surprised for seeing me again! You didn't really "
"think that I, Wesir Amarnat, known as the God of Death, would have fallen so "
"easily even to Akashia's blade, or did you?"
msgstr ""
"Vamos, no digas que estás sorprendido de verme de nuevo. ¿De verdad pensaste "
"que yo, Wesir Amarnat, conocido como el Dios de la Muerte, caería tan "
"fácilmente incluso ante la espada de Akashia?"

#. [message], speaker=Ramoses
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:325
msgid ""
"Now I can confirm what you told me, Wesir; I've seen that face, made "
"perennial by Myra's ice coffin, with my own eyes once. To think that you'd "
"stoop so low as to defile our Founding Heroine to further your schemes... "
"You don't deserve to even call yourself a Maat'Karian, Ankhmare Ptahothep!"
msgstr ""
"Ahora puedo confirmar lo que me dijiste, Wesir; he visto ese rostro, hecho "
"perenne por el ataúd de hielo de Myra, con mis propios ojos una vez. Pensar "
"que caerías tan bajo como para profanar a nuestra Heroína Fundadora para "
"avanzar en tus planes… ¡No mereces ni llamarte maatkariano, Ankhmare "
"Ptahothep!"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:329
msgid ""
"And you don't deserve to be a Lord, my good Ramoses, if you're foolish and "
"misguided enough to believe Wesir's words. You couldn't have shown me a most "
"unwelcoming sight than the Heaven and Earth's Wall, but it won't stop me "
"from speaking to my countrymen and telling them my version of the story; I "
"don't think all of them share your views on me and on the Seer's Prophecy!"
msgstr ""
"Y tú no mereces ser un Señor, mi buen Ramoses, si eres lo suficientemente "
"necio y descarriado como para creer las palabras de Wesir. No podrías "
"haberme mostrado una visión más hostil que el Muro del Cielo y la Tierra, "
"pero eso no me impedirá hablar con mis compatriotas y contarles mi versión "
"de la historia; ¡no creo que todos compartan tus opiniones sobre mí y sobre "
"la Profecía del Vidente!"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:333
msgid ""
"(chuckling) So you're saying you'll go through the shield which has never "
"failed to defend New Maat'Kare? Verily, I must confess I've quite "
"underestimated your arrogance, Master Ankhmare!"
msgstr ""
"(riendo) ¿Entonces estás diciendo que atravesarás el escudo que nunca ha "
"fallado en defender Nueva Maat'Kare? En verdad, debo confesar que he "
"subestimado bastante tu arrogancia, ¡maestro Ankhmare!"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:337
msgid ""
"It's not arrogance, but reliance. I have the Dragon-Slayer, who was once "
"Myra herself, with me; with such ally on my side, I have nothing to fear – "
"especially from one such as you!"
msgstr ""
"No es arrogancia, sino confianza. Tengo a la Matadragones, que una vez fue "
"la propia Myra, a mi lado; con una aliada así, no tengo nada que temer —"
"¡especialmente de alguien como tú!"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:341
msgid ""
"Are you sure you want to rely so much on this girl's strength, old man? As "
"much as it displeases me to admit, this defence is formidable, probably the "
"strongest I've ever seen, and that means something."
msgstr ""
"¿Estás seguro de querer depender tanto de la fuerza de esta chica, viejo? "
"Por mucho que me disguste admitirlo, esta defensa es formidable, "
"probablemente la más fuerte que he visto jamás, y eso significa algo."

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:345
msgid ""
"Formidable it may be, but it has its weaknesses. Both the elementals and the "
"undead are summoned by special sigils which are powered by crystals hidden "
"inside four of the Founders' statues, the ones in each of the cardinal "
"points. By breaking just one crystal, we can destroy much of the defence. "
"Also, as the elementals are set to stand in a defensive position, they only "
"attack those who come near, meaning that we won't have to fight all of them "
"at once."
msgstr ""
"Puede ser formidable, pero tiene sus debilidades. Tanto los elementales como "
"los no-muertos son invocados por sigilos especiales que son alimentados por "
"cristales ocultos dentro de cuatro de las estatuas de los Fundadores, las "
"que están en cada uno de los puntos cardinales. Rompiendo solo un cristal, "
"podemos destruir gran parte de la defensa. Además, como los elementales "
"están puestos en posición defensiva, solo atacan a quienes se acercan, lo "
"que significa que no tendremos que pelear contra todos a la vez."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:349
msgid ""
"Well, I suppose we should, at the very least, thank Ramoses for using "
"elementals and undead instead of Maat'Karians... Geesh, it would be so good "
"if Olokun, Valerya and Derceto showed up out of a sudden to help us..."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, supongo que al menos deberíamos agradecerle a Ramoses por usar "
"elementales y no-muertos en vez de maatkarianos… Cielos, sería tan bueno si "
"Olokun, Valerya y Derceto aparecieran de repente para ayudarnos…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:361
msgid ""
"We really can't say a single good thing about you, can we, Ramoses?! Stop "
"sending Maat'Karians to fight me, I don't want to kill any of you!"
msgstr ""
"Realmente no podemos decir ni una sola cosa buena de ti, ¿verdad, Ramoses? "
"¡Deja de enviar maatkarianos a pelear contra mí, no quiero matar a ninguno "
"de ustedes!"

#. [message], speaker=Ramoses
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:365
msgid ""
"You need not pity us, pretender, every Maat'Karian soldier is ready to die "
"in defence of this city!"
msgstr ""
"No necesitas compadecernos, impostora, ¡cada soldado maatkariano está listo "
"para morir en defensa de esta ciudad!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:422
msgid "Did you miss us?"
msgstr "¿Nos extrañaron?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:426
msgid ""
"(smiling) And how! I was so afraid that something had happened to you, with "
"Ramoses having taken over the government and all..."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) ¡Y cómo! Tenía tanto miedo de que algo les hubiera pasado, con "
"Ramoses tomando el gobierno y todo…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:430
msgid "Pfff, it takes more than even the Heaven and Earth's Wall to stop us."
msgstr ""
"Pfff, se necesita más que el Muro del Cielo y la Tierra para detenernos."

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:434
msgid ""
"It's not like our life has been easy, though; had we not been warned by "
"Shirahel, we might have been caught by the mages and soldiers loyal to "
"Ramoses."
msgstr ""
"No es que nuestra vida haya sido fácil, sin embargo; si no nos hubiera "
"advertido Shirahel, podríamos haber sido atrapados por los magos y soldados "
"leales a Ramoses."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:438
msgid ""
"In any case, are you well? We searched for you in Hiera'Laksha, but all we "
"found there was piles and piles of bones... And, if I may ask, who's that "
"warrior?"
msgstr ""
"En cualquier caso, ¿están bien? Los buscamos en Hiera'Laksha, pero todo lo "
"que encontramos allí fueron pilas y pilas de huesos… Y, si me permiten "
"preguntar, ¿quién es esa guerrera?"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:442
msgid ""
"Much has happened, my friend; we were ambushed in Hiera'Laksha by Wesir and "
"by dwarves rebelling against Ansaxa, then we found ourselves involved in the "
"Aigathol's civil war... Yet we are well, and with your help we shall retake "
"our city!"
msgstr ""
"Ha pasado mucho, amigo mío; fuimos emboscados en Hiera'Laksha por Wesir y "
"por enanos rebeldes contra Ansaxa, luego nos vimos envueltos en la guerra "
"civil de los Aigathol… Aun así estamos bien, ¡y con tu ayuda retomaremos "
"nuestra ciudad!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:446
msgid ""
"As for this warrior lady here, she's your Founding Heroine, Akashia. Wesir "
"ressurrected her, hoping she'd denounce me; instead, she cut him down."
msgstr ""
"En cuanto a esta dama guerrera de aquí, es su Heroína Fundadora, Akashia. "
"Wesir la resucitó esperando que me denunciara; en cambio, ella lo cortó en "
"pedazos."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:450
msgid "You... You're Akashia the Strong...?! But... <i>how</i>...?!"
msgstr "Tú… ¿Eres Akashia la Fuerte…?! ¡Pero… <i>cómo</i>…?!"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:454
msgid ""
"Argh, you mages can argue about the 'hows' and 'whys' later, now we have a "
"battle to fight so focus!"
msgstr ""
"Argh, ustedes magos pueden discutir los «cómos» y «porqués» después, ¡ahora "
"tenemos una batalla que pelear, así que concéntrense!"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:458
msgid "I take that you've received no word from Cornelya and Kenshiro?"
msgstr "Supongo que no han tenido noticias de Cornelya y Kenshiro?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:462
msgid "No... here's hoping they didn't return while we were away, though."
msgstr "No… aunque esperemos que no hayan regresado mientras estuvimos fuera."

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:496
msgid ""
"You may now recall Olokun's veteran elementals.\n"
"Ramoses' death would cause civil war in New Maat'Kare; find another way to "
"defeat him, or else just wait for the opportunity to appear."
msgstr ""
"Ahora puedes reincorporar los elementales veteranos de Olokun.\n"
"La muerte de Ramoses causaría guerra civil en Nueva Maat'Kare; encuentra "
"otra forma de derrotarlo, o simplemente espera a que aparezca la oportunidad."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:604
msgid ""
"Well, this is an unexpected sight... But let us leave questions for later, "
"as it's clear that our hapless friends have once again gotten themselves "
"into trouble..."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, esta es una visión inesperada… Pero dejemos las preguntas para "
"después, ya que está claro que nuestros desafortunados amigos se han metido "
"en problemas otra vez…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:608
msgid "And speaking in the devil..."
msgstr "Y hablando del diablo…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:612
msgid "...Eh? What do you mean, 'devil'?"
msgstr "…¿Eh? ¿Qué quieres decir con «diablo»?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:616
msgid ""
"(smiling) Never mind, I'm just glad to see you again! How was the training "
"with the fauns and the faeries?"
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) No importa, ¡solo estoy contenta de verlos de nuevo! ¿Cómo fue "
"el entrenamiento con los faunos y las feéricas?"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:620
msgid "Probably not very good, as I sense no great power increase in her..."
msgstr ""
"Probablemente no muy bueno, ya que no siento un gran aumento de poder en "
"ella…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:624
msgid ""
"(smirking) On the other hand, I do feel a great closeness increase between "
"her and our shadowy friend..."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo con picardía) Por otro lado, sí siento un gran aumento de "
"cercanía entre ella y nuestro amigo sombrío…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:628
msgid "(blushing) Tsc, shut the hell up already..."
msgstr "(sonrojado) Tsc, cállate de una vez…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:632
msgid ""
"(blushing even more) F-for your information, yes, I couldn't increase my "
"power as I wanted, but I did learn many important things, not to mention "
"that I've got fauns and faeries on our side!"
msgstr ""
"(sonrojándose aún más) Para que lo sepas, sí, no pude aumentar mi poder como "
"quería, pero sí aprendí muchas cosas importantes, sin mencionar que ¡tengo "
"faunos y feéricos de nuestro lado!"

#. [message], speaker=Umbrius
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:636
msgid ""
"Lord Oberone and Lady Idunn, who guide our people, have ordered me, my "
"warriors and the brightest faeries to follow and protect the future Queen-in-"
"the-Woods in her quest to defend our world. I hope we are of use to her "
"friends as well."
msgstr ""
"El señor Oberone y la dama Idunn, que guían a nuestro pueblo, me han "
"ordenado a mí, a mis guerreros y a las feéricas más brillantes seguir y "
"proteger a la futura Reina-en-el-Bosque en su misión de defender nuestro "
"mundo. Espero que también seamos útiles para sus amigos."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:640
msgid "And I've told you to stop calling me that, Umbrius!"
msgstr "¡Y te he dicho que dejes de llamarme así, Umbrius!"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:644
msgid ""
"I see the fauns were not the only ones who decided to follow you, though; it "
"pleases me, Chief Bogor, to see that you've become friends with them!"
msgstr ""
"Veo que los faunos no fueron los únicos que decidieron seguirte; me "
"complace, jefe Bogor, ver que te has hecho amigo de ellos."

#. [message], speaker=Bogor
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:648
msgid ""
"Don't go that far, old man, I only came here to make sure you fulfilled your "
"end of our deal!"
msgstr ""
"No exageres, viejo, ¡solo vine aquí para asegurarme de que cumplieras tu "
"parte del trato!"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:652
msgid ""
"We already have, Chief Bogor. The dwarves who attacked your clan were "
"Aigathol rebels; Ansaxa has already dealt with them. You may leave now "
"should you wish, with no dishonour placed upon you."
msgstr ""
"Ya lo hemos hecho, jefe Bogor. Los enanos que atacaron a tu clan eran "
"rebeldes Aigathol; Ansaxa ya se encargó de ellos. Puedes irte ahora si lo "
"deseas, sin que caiga deshonra sobre ti."

#. [message], speaker=Bogor
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:656
msgid ""
"Really? Then... Argh, I'm not one to flee a battlefield. Let us fight side "
"by side a while longer, tree-huggers!"
msgstr ""
"¿En serio? Entonces… Argh, no soy de los que huyen de un campo de batalla. "
"¡Luchemos codo a codo un rato más, abrazárboles!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:660
msgid "Cornelya has brought 250 gold from Argea"
msgstr "Cornelya ha traído 250 de oro desde Argea"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:720
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:960
msgid ""
"You may now recall the units who followed Cornelya to Argea, and also "
"recruit fauns and faeries.\n"
"Ramoses' death would cause civil war in New Maat'Kare; find another way to "
"defeat him, or else just wait for the opportunity to appear."
msgstr ""
"Ahora puedes reincorporar a las unidades que siguieron a Cornelya a Argea, y "
"también reclutar faunos y feéricas.\n"
"La muerte de Ramoses causaría guerra civil en Nueva Maat'Kare; encuentra "
"otra forma de derrotarlo, o simplemente espera a que aparezca la oportunidad."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:743
msgid "I wish it had not come to this, friend..."
msgstr "Ojalá no hubiera llegado a esto, amigo…"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:758
msgid ""
"Rest in peace, poor soldier, for your only error was to follow a misguided "
"lord..."
msgstr ""
"Descansa en paz, pobre soldado, pues tu único error fue seguir a un señor "
"descarriado…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:773
msgid "Damn you for making me fight these people, Ramoses...!"
msgstr "¡Maldito seas por obligarme a pelear contra esta gente, Ramoses…!"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:786
msgid "Ha! You're a hundred years too young to destroy me, pretenders!"
msgstr "¡Ja! ¡Son cien años muy jóvenes para destruirme, impostores!"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:793
msgid ""
"Stand away from him! He clearly cannot be destroyed by normal means, so "
"fighting him head on is useless!"
msgstr ""
"¡Aléjense de él! Claramente no puede ser destruido por medios normales, ¡así "
"que pelear contra él de frente es inútil!"

#. [message], speaker=Ramoses
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:802
msgid ""
"I have to say, I'm impressed with your advance; I don't think any other foe "
"has managed to break through so much of this defence, not even the Crimson "
"Sorceress... But the real strength of the Heaven and Earth's Blessing, "
"traitors, lies on its ability to wear out even the most powerful armies and "
"mages..."
msgstr ""
"Debo decir que estoy impresionado con su avance; no creo que ningún otro "
"enemigo haya logrado atravesar tanto de esta defensa, ni siquiera la "
"Hechicera Carmesí… Pero la verdadera fuerza de la Bendición del Cielo y la "
"Tierra, traidores, radica en su capacidad de desgastar incluso a los "
"ejércitos y magos más poderosos"

#. [unit], id=Pawero, type=Tempest Mage
#. [unit], id=Pawero, type=Mage of Storms
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:808
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1047
msgid "Pawero"
msgstr "Pawero"

#. [unit], id=Sebek, type=Cleric
#. [unit], id=Sebek, type=Prophetess of Light
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:820
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1059
msgid "Sebek"
msgstr "Sebek"

#. [unit], id=Kemanut, type=Crimson Mage, gender=female
#. [unit], id=Kemanut, type=Crimson Master, gender=female
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:831
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1070
msgid "Kemanut"
msgstr "Kemanut"

#. [unit], id=Iumeri, type=Dark Sorcerer
#. [unit], id=Iumeri, type=Necromancer
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:844
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1083
msgid "Iumeri"
msgstr "Iumeri"

#. [message], speaker=Ramoses
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:860
msgid ""
"Young Masters of Three Lights, show us all the future of New Maat'Kare is "
"safe in your hands, and finish off the traitors and the pretenders!"
msgstr ""
"Jóvenes Maestros de las Tres Luces, muéstrennos a todos que el futuro de "
"Nueva Maat'Kare está seguro en sus manos, ¡y acaben con los traidores y los "
"impostores!"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:864
msgid ""
"Curses, after fighting the Heaven and Earth's Blessing and Wesir's undead "
"for so long, I don't think we'll have enough power to defeat the combined "
"powers of the Academy's prodigies...!"
msgstr ""
"Maldición, después de luchar tanto tiempo contra la Bendición del Cielo y la "
"Tierra y los no-muertos de Wesir, no creo que tengamos suficiente poder para "
"derrotar los poderes combinados de los prodigios de la Academia…!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:868
msgid ""
"C'mon, those puppies probably have never even been to a fight yet, a noisy "
"demonstration of magic should be enough to send them crying back to their "
"mother's arms!"
msgstr ""
"Vamos, esos cachorros probablemente ni siquiera han estado en una pelea "
"todavía, ¡una ruidosa demostración de magia debería bastar para enviarlos "
"llorando de vuelta a los brazos de su madre!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:872
msgid ""
"Do not underestimate those guys! We call them the 'Supernovae' of the "
"Academy, students who managed to master three of the four arts taught by us "
"before the age of twenty-five!"
msgstr ""
"¡No subestimen a esos tipos! Los llamamos las «Supernovas» de la Academia, "
"estudiantes que lograron dominar tres de las cuatro artes que enseñamos "
"antes de los veinticinco años."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:876
msgid ""
"Olokun's right, we can't underestimate them just because they're young... "
"Maybe we should retreat for now; who knows, we could even get Ansaxa to help "
"us..."
msgstr ""
"Olokun tiene razón, no podemos subestimarlos solo porque son jóvenes… Tal "
"vez deberíamos retirarnos por ahora; quién sabe, incluso podríamos conseguir "
"que Ansaxa nos ayude…"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:880
msgid "(snorting) Damn, you're so hopelessly weak..."
msgstr "(bufando) Maldición, son tan desesperadamente débiles…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:884
msgid "And what does the 'mighty' Akashia the Strong suggest that we do?!"
msgstr "¿Y qué sugiere la «poderosa» Akashia la Fuerte que hagamos?!"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:888
msgid ""
"If you don't know what to do yourself, I don't think anything I say will "
"have any effect, girl. But I know what I was once taught about what one must "
"do when one is fighting for those they care about... Watch it, Tenma, and "
"try to learn it!"
msgstr ""
"Si tú misma no sabes qué hacer, no creo que nada de lo que diga tenga "
"efecto, chica. Pero sé lo que una vez me enseñaron sobre lo que uno debe "
"hacer cuando lucha por aquellos que le importan… Míralo, Tenma, ¡e intenta "
"aprenderlo!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:902
msgid "Akashia, watch out!!!"
msgstr "¡Akashia, cuidado!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:906
msgid ""
"What the hell is she trying to do, plunging into enemy lines like that?!"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué demonios está intentando hacer, lanzándose a las líneas enemigas así?!"

#. [message], speaker=Ramoses
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:910
msgid ""
"She may have been brainwashed by the pretender, but her valour is just as "
"described in the ancient scrolls... Mages, we can't let our Founding Heroine "
"be used as a puppet; let's give her a befitting end!"
msgstr ""
"Puede que haya sido lavada el cerebro por la impostora, pero su valor es "
"justo como se describe en los pergaminos antiguos… ¡Magos, no podemos dejar "
"que nuestra Heroína Fundadora sea usada como títere; démosle un final digno!"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:914
msgid ""
"Ha! Bring it then, Maat'Karians! I have fought dragons and Celestials, "
"survived Garet-Desh and Hiera'Shirsha, anything less than your very best "
"will be useless against me!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ja! ¡Entonces tráiganlo, maatkarianos! He luchado contra dragones y "
"Celestiales, sobreviví Garet-Desh y Hiera’Shirsha, ¡cualquier cosa menos que "
"su mejor esfuerzo será inútil contra mí!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:986
msgid "AKASHIA!!!"
msgstr "¡¡¡AKASHIA!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Akashia
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:990
msgid ""
"Ugh...! (smirking) No less than expected from the descendants of the Last "
"War's survivors...!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ugh…! (sonriendo con ironía) ¡Nada menos de lo esperado de los "
"descendientes de los sobrevivientes de la Última Guerra…!"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1016
msgid "This is bad, we're too far to reach her before the enemy does!"
msgstr ""
"Esto es malo, ¡estamos demasiado lejos para alcanzarla antes que el enemigo!"

#. [message], speaker=Ramoses
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1020
msgid "Akashia the Strong, may you finally rest in..."
msgstr "Akashia la Fuerte, que por fin descanses en…"

#. [message], speaker=Bogor
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1058
msgid ""
"What the hell was that?! And why are clouds gathering so quickly? The sky "
"was blue clean until a while ago!"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué demonios fue eso?! ¿Y por qué se están juntando nubes tan rápido? ¡El "
"cielo estaba completamente azul hace un rato!"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1062
msgid "T-Tenma...!"
msgstr "¡T-Tenma…!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1066
msgid "What... What is this sudden outflow of energy...?"
msgstr "¿Qué… qué es este repentino flujo de energía…?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1070
msgid "(trembling in rage) I... won't... allow it... to happen.... AGAIN!!!"
msgstr "(temblando de rabia) Yo… no… permitiré… que ocurra… ¡OTRA VEZ!"

#. [message], speaker=Ramoses
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1078
msgid "(fearful) Just what is going on here?!"
msgstr "(temeroso) ¡¿Qué demonios está pasando aquí?!"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1082
msgid "T-that girl, she's...!"
msgstr "¡E-esa chica, ella…!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1089
msgid "(astonished) Tenma, you..."
msgstr "(asombrado) Tenma, tú…"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1093
msgid ""
"She did it! She finally managed to access the full power of nature's spirits!"
msgstr ""
"¡Lo hizo! ¡Finalmente logró acceder al poder completo de los espíritus de la "
"naturaleza!"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1097
msgid " So that means...!"
msgstr "¡Entonces eso significa…!"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1217
msgid ""
"What... just what is this power...?! I feel like my own strength is "
"disappearing, as if running away from this monster...!"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué… qué es este poder…?! ¡Siento que mi propia fuerza está desapareciendo, "
"como si huyera de este monstruo…!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1221
msgid "So this is the strength which may destroy the Sky Dragon...?"
msgstr "¿Entonces esta es la fuerza que puede destruir al Dragón del Cielo…?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1225
msgid ""
"Ramoses... You should withdraw your soldiers and mages while you still "
"can... I cannot guarantee their safety when I come for you..."
msgstr ""
"Ramoses… Deberías retirar a tus soldados y magos mientras aún puedas… No "
"puedo garantizar su seguridad cuando venga por ti…"

#. [message], speaker=Ramoses
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1229
msgid ""
"*What is happening here...? I've never trembled like this, not even when I "
"faced Vagdrash the Bloody in my youth...!* Tsc! Fear not this noisy "
"demonstration of power, young masters, she's still nothing more than a "
"pretender, while we're the People of Myra!"
msgstr ""
"*¿Qué está pasando aquí…? ¡Nunca he temblado así, ni siquiera cuando "
"enfrenté a Vagdrash el Sangriento en mi juventud…!* ¡Tsc! ¡No teman esta "
"ruidosa demostración de poder, jóvenes maestros, ella sigue siendo nada más "
"que una impostora, mientras que nosotros somos el Pueblo de Myra!"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1233
msgid ""
"This is our chance, everyone! Fear not the enemy, for we have the Dragon-"
"Slayer by our side!"
msgstr ""
"¡Esta es nuestra oportunidad, todos! ¡No teman al enemigo, pues tenemos a la "
"Matadragones a nuestro lado!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1239
msgid "Attack Ramoses with Tenma"
msgstr "Atacar a Ramoses con Tenma"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1279
msgid "Watch out: Tenma may have become stronger, but she's still mortal!"
msgstr ""
"¡Cuidado: Tenma puede haberse vuelto más fuerte, pero sigue siendo mortal!"

#. [message], speaker=Ramoses
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1303
msgid ""
"Y-you...! (shouting) You're just... you're just a pretender! How can you "
"wield such incredible power?!"
msgstr ""
"¡T-tú…! (gritando) ¡Solo eres… solo eres una impostora! ¡¿Cómo puedes "
"manejar un poder tan increíble?!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1307
msgid ""
"I was never a pretender, Ramoses; from the moment I arrived at this city, I "
"have been telling you that I am not Myra, but I do share her soul, and also "
"her burden and her feelings..."
msgstr ""
"Nunca fui una impostora, Ramoses; desde el momento en que llegué a esta "
"ciudad, te he estado diciendo que no soy Myra, pero sí comparto su alma, y "
"también su carga y sus sentimientos…"

#. [message], speaker=Ramoses
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1311
msgid ""
"I... I don't know what to believe in any more...! But I admit that I... "
"cannot compete against your power... Just kill me at once and be done with "
"it..."
msgstr ""
"Yo… ya no sé en qué creer… ¡Pero admito que… no puedo competir contra tu "
"poder… Mátame de una vez y terminemos con esto…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1315
msgid "Wait, Tenma, don't...!"
msgstr "¡Espera, Tenma, no…!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1319
msgid ""
"Tenma stared coldly at the man standing defeated before her; the "
"Maat'Karians all stared anxiously at the two contenders, their fiercest "
"defender and their supposed heroine reborn; and, as the latter raised her "
"hand, everybody held their breaths in shock..."
msgstr ""
"Tenma miró fríamente al hombre derrotado frente a ella; todos los "
"maatkarianos miraron ansiosamente a los dos contendientes, su defensor más "
"feroz y su supuesta heroína renacida; y, cuando esta última levantó la mano, "
"todos contuvieron el aliento por la conmoción…"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1323
msgid ""
"...But no slashing blast of energy shone in that moment. Instead of cutting "
"the air like a beast's claw, Tenma's hand lay calmly on the shoulder of the "
"general."
msgstr ""
"…Pero ningún estallido cortante de energía brilló en ese momento. En lugar "
"de cortar el aire como la garra de una bestia, la mano de Tenma se posó "
"tranquilamente sobre el hombro del general."

#. [message], speaker=Ramoses
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1330
msgid "W-what are you doing?"
msgstr "¿Q-qué estás haciendo?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1334
msgid ""
"I cannot say that I forgive you for attacking my friends, but, as I have "
"just said, I share Myra's feelings: I know how it feels like, to have an "
"entire nation on your shoulders; you just opposed me because you feared that "
"I would bring harm to your fellows, and because you didn't want to see "
"anyone dying a meaningless death, like it happened with the expeditionary "
"force sent to examine the Caves of Light in Arajunna."
msgstr ""
"No puedo decir que te perdono por atacar a mis amigos, pero, como acabo de "
"decir, comparto los sentimientos de Myra: sé lo que se siente tener toda una "
"nación sobre los hombros; solo te opusiste a mí porque temías que trajera "
"daño a tus compatriotas, y porque no querías ver a nadie morir de una muerte "
"sin sentido, como pasó con la fuerza expedicionaria enviada a examinar las "
"Cuevas de la Luz en Arajunna."

#. [message], speaker=Ramoses
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1338
msgid "...!"
msgstr "¡...!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1342
msgid ""
"But I want you to understand that I am not your foe, Ramoses; if once I "
"wanted to come here only to get answers for my questions, now I am willing "
"to fulfil Akhen's Prophecy and end what Nitiballi, Agniballi, Maat and Myra "
"have started in the past. More than that, I want to make this world be like "
"it must have been before the Sky Dragon's corruption: a world where peace "
"and understanding were the norm, and war and strife were the exception. And "
"for this, I need your help, and that of all Maat'Karians; may I count on "
"you, general?"
msgstr ""
"Pero quiero que entiendas que no soy tu enemiga, Ramoses; si alguna vez vine "
"aquí solo para obtener respuestas a mis preguntas, ahora estoy dispuesta a "
"cumplir la Profecía de Akhen y terminar lo que Nitiballi, Agniballi, Maat y "
"Myra comenzaron en el pasado. Más que eso, quiero hacer que este mundo sea "
"como debió haber sido antes de la corrupción del Dragón del Cielo: un mundo "
"donde la paz y la comprensión fueran la norma, y la guerra y el conflicto la "
"excepción. Y para esto necesito tu ayuda, y la de todos los maatkarianos; "
"¿puedo contar contigo, general?"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1346
msgid ""
"The seasoned, sullen general and the young woman faced each other for what "
"seemed like hours; and then, the mighty General Ramoses, the dread of all "
"foes of New Maat'Kare, fell to his knees before Tenma."
msgstr ""
"El curtido y sombrío general y la joven se miraron fijamente durante lo que "
"parecieron horas; y entonces, el poderoso general Ramoses, el terror de "
"todos los enemigos de Nueva Maat'Kare, cayó de rodillas ante Tenma."

#. [message], speaker=Ramoses
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1350
msgid ""
"I... I was wrong, after all... Myra or not, you certainly are someone worth "
"following... Tenma Yozora, you may count on me to make this world a better "
"place."
msgstr ""
"Yo… después de todo me equivoqué… Myra o no, ciertamente eres alguien digno "
"de seguir… Tenma Yozora, puedes contar conmigo para hacer de este mundo un "
"lugar mejor."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1354
msgid "(smiling) Thank you, Ram..."
msgstr "(sonriendo) Gracias, Ram…"

#. [message], speaker=Ramoses
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1407
msgid ""
"She fainted; such a sudden and massive outburst of energy has strained her a "
"lot..."
msgstr ""
"Se desmayó; un estallido tan repentino y masivo de energía la ha agotado "
"mucho"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1411
msgid ""
"Lord Ramoses, I think it's time we've settled our scores. You have "
"acknowledged your mistakes, so now it's my turn to acknowledge mine... I "
"don't blame you for hating me because of that failed expedition; I was a "
"fool back then, fanatically searching for something which I convinced myself "
"would save our world, but careless about the safety of my own comrades. I "
"was the one who should have died in the Caves of Light, not those soldiers, "
"not your brother..."
msgstr ""
"Señor Ramoses, creo que es hora de que arreglemos nuestras cuentas. Tú has "
"reconocido tus errores, así que ahora me toca reconocer los míos… No te "
"culpo por odiarme por esa expedición fallida; fui un necio entonces, "
"buscando fanáticamente algo que me convencí de que salvaría nuestro mundo, "
"pero descuidado con la seguridad de mis propios compañeros. Fui yo quien "
"debió morir en las Cuevas de la Luz, no esos soldados, no tu hermano…"

#. [message], speaker=Ramoses
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1415
msgid ""
"And I should have been able to see your regret sooner, Master Ankhmare, "
"instead of feeding this hatred for so many years and destroying the harmony "
"of our city because of it... (shouting) Supernovae and other mages, I order "
"you to call off the Heaven and Earth's Wall! Master Ankhmare and his allies "
"are henceforth allowed to enter our city! And I... I relinquish my authority "
"as Protector of New Maat'Kare and as Neb, and yield myself to the judgment "
"of the Court of Anpu."
msgstr ""
"Y yo debí haber visto tu arrepentimiento antes, maestro Ankhmare, en lugar "
"de alimentar este odio durante tantos años y destruir la armonía de nuestra "
"ciudad por eso… (gritando) ¡Supernovas y demás magos, les ordeno desactivar "
"el Muro del Cielo y la Tierra! ¡El maestro Ankhmare y sus aliados de ahora "
"en adelante tienen permiso para entrar en nuestra ciudad! Y yo… renuncio a "
"mi autoridad como Protector de Nueva Maat'Kare y como Neb, y me entrego al "
"juicio de la Corte de Anpu."

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1419
msgid ""
"So... So this is how it ends, after all that we've planned?! You yield "
"yourself, your titles, to Ankhmare just because some girl can do tricks that "
"we cannot?!"
msgstr ""
"Entonces… ¿así es como termina todo, después de todo lo que planeamos?! ¿Te "
"rindes a ti mismo, tus títulos, ante Ankhmare solo porque una chica puede "
"hacer trucos que nosotros no?!"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1423
msgid "Lord Ramoses, I assure you it is not necessary to go this far-"
msgstr "Señor Ramoses, te aseguro que no es necesario llegar tan lejos—"

#. [message], speaker=Ramoses
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1427
msgid ""
"Yes, Master Ankhmare, it is. I have led my people to senseless death "
"fighting their own, and for no other reason than my own stubbornness and "
"blindness."
msgstr ""
"Sí, maestro Ankhmare, sí lo es. He llevado a mi pueblo a una muerte sin "
"sentido luchando contra los suyos, y por ninguna otra razón que mi propia "
"terquedad y ceguera."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1431
msgid ""
"Heed his example, Master Wesir. The fight is over, and I believe we have "
"proved beyond any doubt that we're not your enemies, let alone our city's."
msgstr ""
"Sigue su ejemplo, maestro Wesir. La lucha terminó, y creo que hemos "
"demostrado más allá de toda duda que no somos tus enemigos, ni mucho menos "
"los de nuestra ciudad."

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1435
msgid ""
"Do not patronise me, boy! Ramoses may have decided to forget everything "
"Ankhmare has done to put our country under his thrall, but I haven't! If "
"your cabal of imposters are to be allowed to fester in my city, then I "
"forsake it! I shall not stand witness to this new Menon's rise to absolute "
"power!"
msgstr ""
"¡No me trates con condescendencia, muchacho! Ramoses puede haber decidido "
"olvidar todo lo que Ankhmare ha hecho para poner a nuestro país bajo su "
"dominio, ¡pero yo no! Si se permite que su camarilla de impostores se pudra "
"en mi ciudad, ¡entonces la abandono! ¡No seré testigo de la ascensión de "
"este nuevo Menon al poder absoluto!"

#. [message], speaker=Ramoses
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1439
msgid ""
"(sigh) I should have noticed the magnitude of your resentment when you set "
"out to ambush him at Hiera'Laksha on your own... If that is your wish, then "
"you're free to go, Wesir. However, know that I deeply lament that you choose "
"to leave your land and people because of such personal rivalry."
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) Debí haber notado la magnitud de tu resentimiento cuando saliste a "
"emboscarlo en Hiera'Laksha por tu cuenta… Si ese es tu deseo, entonces eres "
"libre de irte, Wesir. Sin embargo, sabe que lamento profundamente que elijas "
"abandonar tu tierra y tu pueblo por una rivalidad tan personal."

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1449
msgid ""
"It consternates me, that one of our brightest citizens prefers leaving us "
"rather than make peace; this schism amongst our people has endured for too "
"long to be healed overnight, but I'm certain we'll overcome it, just as "
"we've overcome so many other trials. Now, we must take Tenma to the healers, "
"or else her newly-found connection to nature's spirits may be compromised."
msgstr ""
"Me consterna que uno de nuestros ciudadanos más brillantes prefiera "
"abandonarnos antes que hacer las paces; este cisma entre nuestro pueblo ha "
"durado demasiado tiempo como para sanarlo de la noche a la mañana, pero "
"estoy seguro de que lo superaremos, tal como hemos superado tantas otras "
"pruebas. Ahora debemos llevar a Tenma con los sanadores, o de lo contrario "
"su recién encontrada conexión con los espíritus de la naturaleza podría "
"verse comprometida."

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1453
msgid ""
"We should also take Akashia in as well; I sense some energy in her still, "
"and I'm sure she wants to give Tenma a proper farewell..."
msgstr ""
"También deberíamos llevar a Akashia; aún siento algo de energía en ella, y "
"estoy segura de que quiere darle a Tenma una despedida apropiada…"

#. [message], speaker=Ramoses
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1559
msgid ""
"I have fallen... soldiers, fight on... to the last man... protect New "
"Maat'Kare..."
msgstr ""
"He caído… soldados, sigan luchando… hasta el último hombre… protejan Nueva "
"Maat'Kare…"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1563
msgid ""
"We shouldn't have killed him! Now, there will really be a civil war in New "
"Maat'Kare!"
msgstr ""
"¡No debimos matarlo! ¡Ahora sí habrá realmente una guerra civil en Nueva "
"Maat'Kare!"

#. [message], speaker=Ramoses
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1576
msgid ""
"You are worthy opponents, I give you that; but this battle must not drag on "
"for any longer. Soldiers, mages, I want every last one of you to attack now!"
msgstr ""
"Son oponentes dignos, les concedo eso; pero esta batalla no debe prolongarse "
"más. ¡Soldados, magos, quiero que todos y cada uno de ustedes ataquen ahora!"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/34_The_Seers_Prophecy.cfg:1580
msgid ""
"No, we cannot win against New Maat'Kare's full forces! We should have ended "
"this battle sooner!"
msgstr ""
"¡No, no podemos ganar contra todas las fuerzas de Nueva Maat'Kare! ¡Debimos "
"terminar esta batalla antes!"

#. [scenario], id=35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_I
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_I.cfg:5
msgid "Dawn of Another Day - Leaving Netjer-Ta"
msgstr "Amanecer de Otro Día - Abandonando Netjer-Ta"

#. [unit], id=Neptun, type=Merman Hoplite
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_I.cfg:102
msgid "Neptun"
msgstr "Neptun"

#. [unit], id=Kytherea, type=Mermaid Enchantress
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_I.cfg:118
msgid "Kytherea"
msgstr "Kytherea"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_I.cfg:144
msgid ""
"For thousands of years we have kept this jewel, waiting for the time it "
"could be destroyed; never would I have thought that I'd live to see it with "
"my own eyes... Good luck, Tenma Yozora; whenever you need aid, remember that "
"you have loyal friends here in Netjer-Ta."
msgstr ""
"Durante miles de años hemos custodiado esta joya, esperando el momento en "
"que pudiera ser destruida; nunca habría pensado que viviría para verla con "
"mis propios ojos… Buena suerte, Tenma Yozora; cuando necesites ayuda, "
"recuerda que tienes amigos leales aquí en Netjer-Ta."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_I.cfg:148
msgid "(smirks) Well, that <i>is</i> my city too, right?"
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo con picardía) Bueno, esa <i>también</i> es mi ciudad, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_I.cfg:152
msgid ""
"Shall we go now? I mean no offence, but I can't wait to return to cooler, "
"wetter realms."
msgstr ""
"¿Nos vamos ya? No quiero ofender, pero no puedo esperar a regresar a reinos "
"más frescos y húmedos."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_I.cfg:156
msgid ""
"Poor Derceto, you've been through so much to bring us all here and make sure "
"we were all safe, and we never properly thanked you for it... So please, "
"accept this humble gift with our apologies and our gratitude. (hands the "
"Trident of the Seas to her)"
msgstr ""
"Pobre Derceto, has pasado por tanto para traernos a todos aquí y asegurarte "
"de que estuviéramos a salvo, y nunca te lo agradecimos como corresponde… Así "
"que por favor, acepta este humilde regalo con nuestras disculpas y nuestra "
"gratitud. (le entrega el Tridente de los Mares)"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_I.cfg:160
msgid ""
"What... Hold on, the Trident... It was given to Myra by Atargatis, you "
"shouldn't-"
msgstr "¿Qué… espera, el Tridente… Fue dado a Myra por Atargatis, no deberías—"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_I.cfg:164
msgid ""
"...shouldn't what, return to the merfolk their own Regalia? I get it, "
"Atargatis wanted Myra to keep it, and I'm sure she had her reasons to; but "
"<i>I</i> say this Trident should never have left merfolk hands. It deserves "
"to be wielded by a sea queen; and besides, Olokun said it would suit you "
"really well."
msgstr ""
"…¿no debería qué, devolver a los sirenidos su propio Regalia? Lo entiendo, "
"Atargatis quería que Myra lo conservara, y estoy segura de que tenía sus "
"razones; pero <i>yo</i> digo que este Tridente nunca debió salir de manos "
"sirenidas. Merece ser empuñado por una reina del mar; y además, Olokun dijo "
"que te quedaría realmente bien."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_I.cfg:168
msgid "I didn't, actually..."
msgstr "En realidad no lo dije…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_I.cfg:172
msgid "But you do agree that it suits her better?"
msgstr "¿Pero sí estás de acuerdo en que le queda mejor a ella?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_I.cfg:176
msgid "(blushing) Well, I can't deny that..."
msgstr "(sonrojado) Bueno, no puedo negarlo…"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_I.cfg:180
msgid ""
"(smiling) If the Trident's current owner wills it to me, then all I can do "
"is accept it with all my gratitude. My first act with the Regalia of the "
"Merfolk will be... to ensure that our friends have a safe crossing of our "
"realm!"
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Si la actual dueña del Tridente me lo entrega por voluntad "
"propia, entonces todo lo que puedo hacer es aceptarlo con toda mi gratitud. "
"Mi primer acto con el Regalia de los Sirenidos será… ¡asegurarme de que "
"nuestros amigos tengan un cruce seguro por nuestro reino!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_I.cfg:184
msgid ""
"Saying that, Derceto pointed the Trident skywards; a strong wind gust blew "
"suddenly, gathering the clouds in heaven just above them, and then bringing "
"them down in a spiral. For a moment, it looked as if a tornado was about to "
"be formed right on the spot where the mighty Naiad stood, but the clouds "
"disappeared into the crystals inlaid all over the Trident. Moments later, "
"the sky was as blue as they were above New Maat'Kare, and the Regalia of the "
"Merfolk glowed eerily in the hands of the new Queen-in-the-Ocean."
msgstr ""
"Diciendo eso, Derceto apuntó el Tridente hacia el cielo; una fuerte ráfaga "
"de viento sopló de repente, reuniendo las nubes en el cielo justo encima de "
"ellos, y luego las bajó en espiral. Por un momento, pareció que un tornado "
"estaba a punto de formarse justo en el lugar donde estaba la poderosa "
"náyade, pero las nubes desaparecieron en los cristales incrustados por todo "
"el Tridente. Momentos después, el cielo estaba tan azul como sobre Nueva "
"Maat'Kare, y el Regalia de los Sirenidos brillaba de forma inquietante en "
"las manos de la nueva Reina-del-Océano."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_I.cfg:230
msgid "Well, one Regalia returned to its rightful owner, another to go..."
msgstr "Bueno, un Regalia devuelto a su legítimo dueño, falta otro…"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_I.cfg:234
msgid ""
"So, let's not tarry 'ere any longer, and return the Hammer of Ymer to the "
"trolls as soon as we can!"
msgstr ""
"Entonces, no nos demoremos más aquí, ¡y devolvamos el Martillo de Ymer a los "
"trolls lo antes posible!"

#. [message], speaker=Umbrius
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_I.cfg:238
msgid ""
"I wish I could follow you and make sure that no harm comes to you, my queen, "
"but for now there's no protection we could offer that you don't have already "
"– after all, as you said it yourself at Heartwood Valley, you have friends "
"to rely on. Still, some of the fauns and the faeries have insisted so "
"ardently on following you, that I feel obliged to at least intervene in "
"their favour."
msgstr ""
"Ojalá pudiera seguirte y asegurarme de que no te pase ningún daño, mi reina, "
"pero por ahora no hay protección que podamos ofrecer que no tengas ya —"
"después de todo, como dijiste tú misma en el Valle del Corazón de Madera, "
"tienes amigos en quienes confiar. Aun así, algunos faunos y feéricos han "
"insistido tan ardientemente en seguirte, que me siento obligado a intervenir "
"al menos a su favor."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_I.cfg:242
msgid ""
"Fine, I'll let them follow me - if you stop calling me queen. I am no such "
"thing, and you're making me look like a narcissistic idiot in front of my "
"friends!"
msgstr ""
"Está bien, dejaré que me sigan —si dejas de llamarme reina. No soy tal cosa, "
"¡y me haces parecer una idiota narcisista delante de mis amigos!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_I.cfg:246
msgid ""
"(hugging Cornelya) So, faun, tell us what else our princess said about her "
"'friends she can rely on'."
msgstr ""
"(abrazando a Cornelya) Entonces, fauno, dinos qué más dijo nuestra princesa "
"sobre sus «amigos en quienes puede confiar»."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_I.cfg:250
msgid ""
"Tsc! Onboard, all of you, we have a new journey ahead! And you, Bogor, think "
"better about what I told you back at Heartwood Valley."
msgstr ""
"¡Tsc! ¡Todos a bordo, tenemos un nuevo viaje por delante! Y tú, Bogor, "
"piensa mejor en lo que te dije en el Valle del Corazón de Madera."

#. [message], speaker=Bogor
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_I.cfg:254
msgid ""
"Hrumph! I might as well do that, elf, though I don't think you are ready to "
"see that actually happen... But you were a surprisingly fine sister-in-arms, "
"so you have my respect. May your path be covered in victories and glory."
msgstr ""
"¡Hrumph! Bien podría hacerlo, elfa, aunque no creo que estés lista para ver "
"que eso ocurra de verdad… Pero fuiste una hermana de armas sorprendentemente "
"buena, así que tienes mi respeto. Que tu camino esté cubierto de victorias y "
"gloria."

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_I.cfg:258
msgid ""
"Goodbye, Tenma! Never forget that we're here for you - and take good care of "
"Olokun for us!"
msgstr ""
"¡Adiós, Tenma! Nunca olvides que estamos aquí para ti —¡y cuida bien de "
"Olokun por nosotros!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_I.cfg:262
msgid ""
"I promise I'll come back, and don't worry about your disciple, Master "
"Ankhmare, he has a Queen-in-the-Ocean watching over him!"
msgstr ""
"Prometo que volveré, y no te preocupes por tu discípulo, maestro Ankhmare, "
"¡tiene a una Reina-del-Océano cuidándolo!"

#. [scenario], id=35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:4
msgid "Dawn of Another Day"
msgstr "Amanecer de Otro Día"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:24
msgid "Defeat the Wesnothian general and his allies"
msgstr "Derrotar al general wesnothiano y a sus aliados"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:56
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:660
msgid "Death of Father Yroko"
msgstr "Muerte del padre Yroko"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:61
msgid ""
"NOTE: Tenma may transform into Dragon-Slayer mode once every scenario by "
"right-clicking on her; the transformation will last for 3 turns, after which "
"she'll go back to normal.\n"
"\n"
"Also, Cornelya may still recruit the same units as in the last battle."
msgstr ""
"NOTA: Tenma puede transformarse en modo Matadragones una vez por escenario "
"haciendo clic derecho sobre ella; la transformación durará 3 turnos, después "
"de los cuales volverá a la normalidad.\n"
"\n"
"Además, Cornelya todavía puede reclutar las mismas unidades que en la última "
"batalla."

#. [side], type=Babalawo
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:93
msgid "Father Yroko"
msgstr "Padre Yroko"

#. [side], type=Babalawo
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:98
msgid "Ifeh"
msgstr "Ifeh"

#. [side], type=Grand Marshal
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:120
msgid "Lord Aethenvan"
msgstr "Señor Aethenvan"

#. [side], type=Necromancer
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:144
msgid "Master Dar-Val"
msgstr "Maestro Dar-Val"

#. [side], type=Necromancer
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:149
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:123
msgid "White Necromancers"
msgstr "Nigromantes Blancos"

#. [side], type=Washraha Lightning Striker
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:168
msgid "Commander Seruya"
msgstr "Comandante Seruya"

#. [unit], id=Ayo, type=Chomi Hero
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:244
msgid "Captain Ayo"
msgstr "Capitán Ayo"

#. [effect]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:289
msgid "Sowilo Rune"
msgstr "Runa Sowilo"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:348
msgid ""
"Land! By the beard of Moradin, I've had it with sea trips, I'm going to find "
"an underground way from this continent to the Heart Mountains, even if I "
"have to dig one myself! Now, excuse me everyone, but I need to get off this "
"ship and..."
msgstr ""
"¡Tierra! ¡Por la barba de Moradin, ya estoy harto de viajes por mar, voy a "
"encontrar un camino subterráneo desde este continente hasta las Montañas del "
"Corazón, aunque tenga que cavarlo yo mismo! Ahora, perdónenme todos, pero "
"necesito bajarme de este barco y…"

#. [message], speaker=Ayo
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:352
msgid ""
"Halt! Guards, there are Wesnothians trying to sneak into the city from the "
"sea!"
msgstr ""
"¡Alto! ¡Guardias, hay wesnothianos intentando colarse en la ciudad desde el "
"mar!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:356
msgid ""
"Wait! Lower your weapon, friend, we're not Wesnothians! I am Olokun Maahes, "
"son of Princess Aqualtune, and I request permission to land into Ifeh!"
msgstr ""
"¡Espera! Baja tu arma, amigo, ¡no somos wesnothianos! Soy Olokun Maahes, "
"hijo de la princesa Aqualtune, ¡y solicito permiso para desembarcar en Ifeh!"

#. [message], speaker=Ayo
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:360
msgid ""
"Oh, apologies, Prince Olokun... Please, forgive my aggressiveness, we're "
"currently under attack by Wesnothians, and I mistook your pale friend for a "
"Wesnothian..."
msgstr ""
"Oh, disculpas, príncipe Olokun… Por favor, perdona mi agresividad, estamos "
"actualmente bajo ataque de wesnothianos, y confundí a tu amigo pálido con un "
"wesnothiano…"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:364
msgid ""
"(livid) You fool, how can you mistake me for a human?! I'm a dwarf, know the "
"difference already!"
msgstr ""
"(lívido) ¡Idiota, cómo puedes confundirme con un humano?! ¡Soy un enano, ya "
"aprende la diferencia!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:368
msgid ""
"Please, forgive him, Algil, dwarves are not known in Arajunna... Captain, "
"tell me more about this attack; if I remember correctly, the Wesnothian "
"colony was in peace with the Chomi Confederation, so why are they attacking "
"it now – and Ifeh of all cities?"
msgstr ""
"Por favor, perdónalo, Algil, los enanos no son conocidos en Arajunna… "
"Capitán, cuéntame más sobre este ataque; si recuerdo correctamente, la "
"colonia wesnothiana estaba en paz con la Confederación Chomi, entonces ¿por "
"qué la atacan ahora —y a Ifeh de entre todas las ciudades?"

#. [message], speaker=Ayo
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:372
msgid ""
"Alas, peace died along with the old viceroy; his successor is a mage called "
"Dargamyr, and rumour has it that he was sent by Emperor Taryen to conquer "
"all of Arajunna."
msgstr ""
"¡Ay, la paz murió junto con el viejo virrey; su sucesor es un mago llamado "
"Dargamyr, y corre el rumor de que fue enviado por el emperador Taryen para "
"conquistar toda Arajunna."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:376
msgid ""
"I see... Wesnoth lost their colonies in the Far North, so now it wants to "
"make up for that with new colonies."
msgstr ""
"Ya veo… Wesnoth perdió sus colonias en el Lejano Norte, así que ahora quiere "
"compensarlo con nuevas colonias."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:380
msgid ""
"Then that's all the more reason we must help Ifeh defend itself. And don't "
"waste your time trying to convince us not to do that, Olokun, you know it "
"won't work."
msgstr ""
"Entonces eso es aún más razón para que ayudemos a Ifeh a defenderse. Y no "
"pierdas tu tiempo intentando convencernos de no hacerlo, Olokun, sabes que "
"no funcionará."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:384
msgid ""
"(smiling) After travelling along with you for so long, it would be insulting "
"if I tried to convince you otherwise. Still, I must ask you, Derceto, to "
"avoid fighting here; this is not the merfolk's battle, and they'll only risk "
"themselves by fighting on land."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Después de viajar tanto tiempo contigo, sería insultante si "
"intentara convencerte de lo contrario. Aun así, debo pedirte, Derceto, que "
"evites pelear aquí; esta no es la batalla de los sirenidos, y solo se "
"pondrían en riesgo luchando en tierra."

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:388
msgid ""
"Well, I'll do as you ask, but only to make sure that your city is protected "
"against attacks from the sea. Please, take care of him for me, Tenma!"
msgstr ""
"Bueno, haré como pides, pero solo para asegurarme de que tu ciudad esté "
"protegida contra ataques desde el mar. ¡Por favor, cuídalo por mí, Tenma!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:392
msgid ""
"Don't worry, I've got some new tricks to use on whoever tries to touch "
"him... By the way, what's this 'Prince Olokun' story all about?"
msgstr ""
"No te preocupes, tengo algunos trucos nuevos para usar contra quien intente "
"tocarlo… Por cierto, ¿qué es eso de «príncipe Olokun»?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:396
msgid ""
"In this city, every nobleman and noblewoman is called a 'prince' or a "
"'princess'; as it happens, my mother was one of these princesses."
msgstr ""
"En esta ciudad, a todo noble y noble se le llama «príncipe» o «princesa»; "
"resulta que mi madre era una de esas princesas."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:400
msgid ""
"Then it's time we repay our debt. As you once fought to defend our village "
"from the Wesnothians, we now fight to defend your mother's city."
msgstr ""
"Entonces es hora de pagar nuestra deuda. Como una vez luchaste para defender "
"nuestra aldea de los wesnothianos, ahora luchamos para defender la ciudad de "
"tu madre."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:404
msgid ""
"I never saw that as a debt to be repaid... But I'm glad for the aid "
"nonetheless. Come, then: for Ilê Ifeh!"
msgstr ""
"Nunca lo vi como una deuda que pagar… Pero de todos modos me alegra la "
"ayuda. Vamos entonces: ¡por Ilê Ifeh!"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:438
msgid ""
"(smirking) Now this looks like a fun opponent... Everyone, you can have the "
"small fry, but this one is mine!"
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo con ironía) Ahora este sí parece un oponente divertido… Todos, "
"pueden quedarse con los pececitos, ¡pero este es mío!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:442
msgid ""
"Wait! I mean... (blushes) be careful, understand? Don't go and get squished "
"just yet..."
msgstr ""
"¡Espera! Quiero decir… (sonrojada) ten cuidado, ¿entiendes? No vayas a ser "
"aplastado todavía…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:446
msgid ""
"(smiling) Don't worry, I promised you that I'd see the Glimmering Willows "
"with you, didn't I?"
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) No te preocupes, te prometí que vería los Sauces Relucientes "
"contigo, ¿no es así?"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:450
msgid ""
"(blushes violently) ...!!! You idiot, don't talk so loudly about it in front "
"of everyone, or they'll..."
msgstr ""
"(sonrojándose violentamente) …¡¡¡Idiota, no hables tan fuerte de eso delante "
"de todos, o van a…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:454
msgid "(smiling) ...hear it? Too late, princess, too late..."
msgstr "(sonriendo) …¿oirlo? Demasiado tarde, princesa, demasiado tarde…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:458
msgid "(mortified) Kenshiro, you <i>will</i> pay for this..."
msgstr "(mortificada) Kenshiro, <i>vas</i> a pagar por esto…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:486
msgid "Now there comes an opponent of magnitude!"
msgstr "¡Ahora viene un oponente de magnitud!"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:490
msgid ""
"Cornelya, be ca- I mean... (blushes) Don't get overconfident, a giant is not "
"an opponent to be underestimated!"
msgstr ""
"Cornelya, ten cu- quiero decir… (sonrojado) No te confíes demasiado, ¡un "
"gigante no es un oponente para subestimar!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:494
msgid ""
"Nor am I – or do you think I'm not worthy of such a challenge? (smiling) "
"Anyway, I'm happy to know that you care about me; don't worry, I told you I "
"would show you the Glimmering Willows..."
msgstr ""
"Ni yo tampoco —o ¿crees que no soy digna de tal desafío? (sonriendo) De "
"todos modos, me alegra saber que te preocupas por mí; no te preocupes, te "
"dije que te mostraría los Sauces Relucientes…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:498
msgid "Glimmering Willows... That sure is a fancy name for a dating place..."
msgstr ""
"Sauces Relucientes… Ese sí que es un nombre elegante para un lugar de citas…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:502
msgid "(surprised) T-T-Tenma...! Don't tell me you w-were..."
msgstr "(sorprendida) ¡T-T-Tenma…! No me digas que t-tú estabas…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:506
msgid ""
"...listening to your conversation? (smirking) Ah, well, sorry, I couldn't "
"avoid it, my senses have gotten somewhat sharp after my transformation at "
"New Maat'Kare... Don't worry, though, I promise I'll keep it a secret!"
msgstr ""
"…¿escuchando su conversación? (sonriendo con picardía) Ah, bueno, perdón, no "
"pude evitarlo, mis sentidos se han agudizado un poco después de mi "
"transformación en Nueva Maat'Kare… No te preocupes, sin embargo, ¡prometo "
"que lo mantendré en secreto!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:510
msgid ""
"(mortified) Y-you better keep to your word, Tenma Yozora, or else I'll make "
"you regret having ever crossed paths with me...!"
msgstr ""
"(mortificada) M-mejor cumple tu palabra, Tenma Yozora, ¡o de lo contrario "
"haré que lamentes haberte cruzado en mi camino…!"

#. [unit], id=Flagship, type=Imperial Flagship
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:527
msgid "Elense Star"
msgstr "Estrella Elense"

#. [message], speaker=Aethenvan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:561
msgid ""
"I expected to take this city with our land forces only, but you force us to "
"employ the Imperial Navy as well, Chomi. I congratulate you for your "
"strength, but now not even your strange allies will..."
msgstr ""
"Esperaba tomar esta ciudad solo con nuestras fuerzas terrestres, pero nos "
"obligan a emplear también la Marina Imperial, chomi. Los felicito por su "
"fuerza, pero ahora ni siquiera sus extraños aliados…"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:580
msgid ""
"You have committed a fatal mistake by daring to enter the sea realm, "
"Wesnothians. Merfolk, naga, Children of the Waters, sink these invaders of "
"your world into the oblivion of the deep!"
msgstr ""
"Han cometido un error fatal al atreverse a entrar en el reino del mar, "
"wesnothianos. Sirenidos, nagas, Hijos de las Aguas, ¡hundan a estos "
"invasores de su mundo en el olvido de las profundidades!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:584
msgid ""
"With Derceto's forces joining the battle, your side has received 300 gold."
msgstr ""
"Con las fuerzas de Derceto uniéndose a la batalla, tu bando ha recibido 300 "
"de oro."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:588
msgid "(smiling) What would be of us without you, Derceto..."
msgstr "(sonriendo) ¿Qué sería de nosotros sin ti, Derceto…?"

#. [message], speaker=Yroko
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:602
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:620
msgid ""
"To think that the sea-people, whom we've harmed in the past, would come to "
"our aid... You've truly made wonderful friends in your travels, Olokun. But "
"we will not allow you to fight on the sea on your own; Ayo, you are "
"henceforth in charge of the Ibeji fleet!"
msgstr ""
"Pensar que los pueblos del mar, a quienes hemos dañado en el pasado, "
"vendrían en nuestra ayuda… Realmente has hecho amigos maravillosos en tus "
"viajes, Olokun. Pero no permitiremos que luches en el mar solo; Ayo, ¡de "
"ahora en adelante estás a cargo de la flota Ibeji!"

#. [message], speaker=Ayo
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:606
msgid "I was just waiting for this order..."
msgstr "Solo estaba esperando esta orden…"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:628
msgid "Defeat all enemy commanders"
msgstr "Derrotar a todos los comandantes enemigos"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:665
msgid ""
"Tenma may transform into Dragon-Slayer mode once every scenario by right-"
"clicking on her; the transformation will last for 3 turns, after which "
"she'll go back to normal.\n"
"\n"
"Derceto may recruit merfolk, naga and sea monsters from now on!"
msgstr ""
"Tenma puede transformarse en modo Matadragones una vez por escenario "
"haciendo clic derecho sobre ella; la transformación durará 3 turnos, después "
"de los cuales volverá a la normalidad.\n"
"\n"
"¡Derceto puede reclutar sirenidos, nagas y monstruos marinos de ahora en "
"adelante!"

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:686
msgid ""
"The enemy is no more! Once again we've managed to repel the hordes of "
"Wesnoth!"
msgstr ""
"¡El enemigo ya no existe! ¡Una vez más hemos logrado repeler a las hordas de "
"Wesnoth!"

#. [message], speaker=Yroko
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:690
msgid ""
"Yes, victory is ours, but we owe much of it to these brave young travellers "
"– and also to this noble sea-queen. I, Yroko, thousandth-hundredth-twelfth "
"of Ifeh's Babalawos, wish to offer you my soulful gratitude."
msgstr ""
"Sí, la victoria es nuestra, pero le debemos mucho a estos valientes jóvenes "
"viajeros —y también a esta noble reina del mar. Yo, Yroko, milésimo-"
"centésimo-duodécimo de los Babalawos de Ifeh, deseo ofrecerles mi más "
"sincera gratitud."

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:694
msgid ""
"Consider my aid a token of friendship. While it's true that our people have "
"bad blood between them, for the sake of survival in this increasingly "
"harsher world we must learn to leave past enmities aside."
msgstr ""
"Consideren mi ayuda como un gesto de amistad. Aunque es cierto que nuestros "
"pueblos tienen mala sangre entre ellos, por el bien de la supervivencia en "
"este mundo cada vez más duro debemos aprender a dejar de lado las viejas "
"enemistades."

#. [message], speaker=Yroko
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:698
msgid ""
"Well said, sea-queen. Let us seize this chance, then, and start building "
"better ties between earth-people and sea-people with an alliance; for a "
"single defeat will not scare Wesnoth away from our land. For now, you may "
"rest in our city; I'll provide that you find comfort inside our walls and on "
"our shores."
msgstr ""
"Bien dicho, reina del mar. Aprovechemos entonces esta oportunidad y "
"empecemos a construir mejores lazos entre los pueblos de la tierra y los del "
"mar con una alianza; pues una sola derrota no asustará a Wesnoth lejos de "
"nuestra tierra. Por ahora, pueden descansar en nuestra ciudad; me encargaré "
"de que encuentren comodidad dentro de nuestras murallas y en nuestras costas."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:702
msgid ""
"I wonder, would you have fought so fiercely today if Aetheryon was leading "
"the attack, Tenma?"
msgstr ""
"Me pregunto, ¿habrías luchado tan ferozmente hoy si Aetheryon estuviera "
"liderando el ataque, Tenma?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:706
msgid ""
"Actually, no; I'd have fought even more fiercely, to make sure that the foot "
"that kicked his ass was my own. (after a while) *Still... I'm glad you're "
"not the one in charge of this campaign, Aetheryon...*"
msgstr ""
"En realidad, no; habría luchado aún más ferozmente, para asegurarme de que "
"el pie que le pateara el trasero fuera el mío. (después de un rato) *Aun "
"así… me alegra que no seas tú quien esté a cargo de esta campaña, Aetheryon…*"

#. [message], speaker=Yroko
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:729
msgid "I have fallen... Who will protect Ifeh now...?"
msgstr "He caído… ¿Quién protegerá Ifeh ahora…?"

#. [message], speaker=Yroko
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/35_Dawn_Of_Another_Day_II.cfg:742
msgid ""
"I can see... the rest of the Wesnothian armies are coming to our city, "
"reinforced by scores of Washrahan and Deshra mercenaries, in numbers far "
"higher than we can possibly withstand... This is a disaster!"
msgstr ""
"Puedo ver… el resto de los ejércitos wesnothianos vienen hacia nuestra "
"ciudad, reforzados por montones de mercenarios washrahan y deshra, en "
"números mucho mayores de los que podemos resistir… ¡Esto es un desastre!"

#. [scenario], id=36_Clash_Of_Powers
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:4
msgid "Clash of Fates"
msgstr "Choque de Destinos"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:25
msgid "Reach the Deva Mountains in the southeast"
msgstr "Llegar a las Montañas Deva en el sureste"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:58
msgid ""
"Tenma may transform into Dragon-Slayer mode once every scenario by right-"
"clicking on her; the transformation will last for 3 turns, after which "
"she'll go back to normal.\n"
"\n"
"NOTE: Invoking Tenma's Dragon-Slayer mode too early in this scenario may not "
"be a wise idea..."
msgstr ""
"Tenma puede transformarse en modo Matadragones una vez por escenario "
"haciendo clic derecho sobre ella; la transformación durará 3 turnos, después "
"de los cuales volverá a la normalidad.\n"
"\n"
"NOTA: Invocar el modo Matadragones de Tenma demasiado temprano en este "
"escenario puede no ser una buena idea…"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:92
msgid "Bandit Fortress"
msgstr "Fortaleza de Bandidos"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:113
msgid "Washraha"
msgstr "Washraha"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:134
msgid "Deshrai"
msgstr "Deshrai"

#. [unit], id=Elcadar, type=Great Mage
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:245
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/characters.cfg:188
msgid "Master Elcadar"
msgstr "Maestro Elcadar"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:279
msgid ""
"(smiling) That makes, in my count, thirteen victories against Masters alone. "
"But worry not, Grand Master, I won't challenge you to test yourself against "
"her."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Eso hace, en mi cuenta, trece victorias solo contra Maestros. "
"Pero no te preocupes, Gran Maestro, no te desafiaré para que te pruebes "
"contra ella."

#. [message], speaker=Elcadar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:283
msgid ""
"(stung) I have to admit, you've found quite the freak of nature in that "
"southern continent..."
msgstr ""
"(picado) Debo admitir que has encontrado toda una rareza de la naturaleza en "
"ese continente sureño…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:287
msgid ""
"She isn't a 'freak of nature', Grand Master, she's a young girl; will you be "
"as courteous as not to make me repeat that a fourth time?"
msgstr ""
"Ella no es una «rareza de la naturaleza», Gran Maestro, es una chica joven; "
"¿serás tan cortés como para no obligarme a repetirlo una cuarta vez?"

#. [message], speaker=Elcadar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:291
msgid ""
"It doesn't matter what we call her, she's not someone we can classify into "
"the categories of living or magical beings that we've had for centuries. Her "
"body is flesh, bone and blood, and yet she seems to feed on... <i>magic "
"energy</i>... just as magical constructs do. And yet, she shows none of the "
"weaknesses common to magical creatures; in fact, hardly any magic we throw "
"at this girl seems to faze her."
msgstr ""
"No importa cómo la llamemos, no es alguien que podamos clasificar en las "
"categorías de seres vivos o mágicos que hemos tenido durante siglos. Su "
"cuerpo es carne, hueso y sangre, y sin embargo parece alimentarse de… "
"<i>energía mágica</i>… justo como lo hacen las construcciones mágicas. Y aun "
"así, no muestra ninguna de las debilidades comunes a las criaturas mágicas; "
"de hecho, apenas hay magia que le lancemos que parezca afectarla."

#. [message], speaker=Elcadar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:295
msgid ""
"But that's not what puzzles me most – no, not even her aberrations have "
"astonished me as much as the mystery of her age has. It is possible to "
"measure the approximate age of anything, magic beings included, by detecting "
"certain traces left by the passing of time. When we tried to estimate this "
"girl's age – and I made sure to oversee the examination myself – we "
"discovered that, while her body is that of a twenty-years-old, her magic "
"aura feels older than the magic currents that impregnate this world."
msgstr ""
"Pero eso no es lo que más me intriga —no, ni siquiera sus aberraciones me "
"han asombrado tanto como el misterio de su edad. Es posible medir la edad "
"aproximada de cualquier cosa, incluidos los seres mágicos, detectando "
"ciertas huellas dejadas por el paso del tiempo. Cuando intentamos estimar la "
"edad de esta chica —y me aseguré de supervisar el examen yo mismo— "
"descubrimos que, aunque su cuerpo es el de una joven de veinte años, su aura "
"mágica se siente más antigua que las corrientes mágicas que impregnan este "
"mundo."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:299
msgid ""
"Which, in short, means that either she's possessed by a being older than the "
"planet itself, or that she <i>is</i> that being..."
msgstr ""
"Lo que, en resumen, significa que o está poseída por un ser más antiguo que "
"el planeta mismo, o que ella <i>es</i> ese ser…"

#. [message], speaker=Elcadar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:303
msgid ""
"If she were possessed, we would have been able to detect her own magic aura "
"mixed with the older one, but that's not the case, my prince..."
msgstr ""
"Si estuviera poseída, habríamos podido detectar su propia aura mágica "
"mezclada con la más antigua, pero ese no es el caso, príncipe…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:307
msgid ""
"That is all very interesting indeed, but even if she is such an ancient "
"being, we won't get anywhere if she remains unable to remember her past. "
"Have the Silver Masters had any progress in peering into her mind?"
msgstr ""
"Eso es muy interesante en efecto, pero incluso si es un ser tan antiguo, no "
"llegaremos a ninguna parte si sigue sin poder recordar su pasado. ¿Han "
"tenido algún progreso los Maestros Plateados al intentar escrutar su mente?"

#. [message], speaker=Elcadar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:311
msgid ""
"Alas, Prince Aetheryon, it's easier to look into Knalga through the eternal "
"rock of the Heart Mountains than into that girl's mind. I made no "
"overstatement when I said that you have found quite the... phenomenon in the "
"caves of Arajunna."
msgstr ""
"¡Ay, príncipe Aetheryon, es más fácil mirar hacia Knalga a través de la roca "
"eterna de las Montañas del Corazón que mirar dentro de la mente de esa "
"chica! No exageré cuando dije que has encontrado todo un… fenómeno en las "
"cuevas de Arajunna."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:315
msgid ""
"Well, the Heart Mountains are like a cracked shell nowadays, so I want to "
"believe that there's a way to find out what's going on in her..."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, las Montañas del Corazón son como una cáscara agrietada hoy en día, "
"así que quiero creer que hay una forma de descubrir qué está pasando dentro "
"de ella…"

#. [message], speaker=Guard
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:330
msgid "All hail Emperor Taryen!"
msgstr "¡Todos saluden al emperador Taryen!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:334
msgid "(sigh)... Ah, I could only remain in peace for so long..."
msgstr "(suspiro)… Ah, solo pude permanecer en paz por tanto tiempo…"

#. [message], speaker=Taryen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:341
msgid ""
"The northern provinces, a wreck beset by Knalgans and orcs; the southern "
"provinces, ever preyed upon by the Dunefolk hordes; the eastern provinces "
"experiencing another Sogen uprising; the very heart of the empire plagued by "
"dissidents and traitors; and my own son, who supposedly is the one I can "
"trust the most, sits amongst book shelves and discusses the gender of woses "
"while sipping Kerlathian tea..."
msgstr ""
"Las provincias del norte, un desastre acosado por knalgans y orcos; las "
"provincias del sur, siempre presa de las hordas barjanas; las provincias del "
"este sufriendo otro levantamiento sogen; el mismísimo corazón del imperio "
"plagado de disidentes y traidores; y mi propio hijo, que supuestamente es en "
"quien más puedo confiar, se sienta entre estanterías de libros y discute el "
"género de los woses mientras toma té kerlathiano…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:345
msgid "(drily) It is good to see you again, father..."
msgstr "(secamente) Qué bueno verte de nuevo, padre…"

#. [message], speaker=Taryen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:349
msgid ""
"Enough with the sarcasm, you bookworm! You have ignored two letters of mine, "
"and forced me to come to this island myself to talk with you; you owe your "
"sister that you stand here right now, and not in a Dan'Tonk dungeon!"
msgstr ""
"¡Basta de sarcasmo, ratón de biblioteca! Has ignorado dos cartas mías y me "
"has obligado a venir a esta isla yo mismo para hablar contigo; le debes a tu "
"hermana que estés aquí ahora mismo y no en una mazmorra de Dan’Tonk!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:353
msgid ""
"I will make sure to thank her properly later. As for the letters, I'm afraid "
"to say that I simply did not receive them; certainly the messenger got "
"confused by my constant travelling, and was unable to..."
msgstr ""
"Me aseguraré de agradecerle como corresponde más tarde. En cuanto a las "
"cartas, me temo decir que simplemente no las recibí; seguro que el mensajero "
"se confundió por mis constantes viajes y no pudo…"

#. [message], speaker=Taryen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:357
msgid ""
"Be silent already, I did not come all the way to this old island to hear "
"your excuses! I want to know how the experiences with the freak girl you "
"found in Arajunna are going. (smiling) Yes, I am aware of that; good Master "
"Elcadar has loyally informed me on everything that has been occurring in "
"this island."
msgstr ""
"¡Cállate ya, no vine hasta esta vieja isla para escuchar tus excusas! Quiero "
"saber cómo van los experimentos con la chica fenómeno que encontraste en "
"Arajunna. (sonriendo) Sí, estoy al tanto; el buen maestro Elcadar me ha "
"informado lealmente de todo lo que ha ocurrido en esta isla."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:361
msgid ""
"(glaring at Elcadar) We could not learn much more about Galdra, other than "
"she's much more powerful than we initially believed."
msgstr ""
"(mirando fijamente a Elcadar) No pudimos averiguar mucho más sobre Galdra, "
"aparte de que es mucho más poderosa de lo que inicialmente creíamos."

#. [message], speaker=Elcadar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:365
msgid ""
"Furthermore, my Lord Emperor, I believe that we have barely scratched the "
"surface of her true potential. She has easily defeated every mage we've sent "
"to duel her; I quake to imagine what kind of things she can do if pushed to "
"her limit."
msgstr ""
"Además, mi señor emperador, creo que apenas hemos rascado la superficie de "
"su verdadero potencial. Ha derrotado fácilmente a cada mago que le hemos "
"enviado a duelos; tiemblo al imaginar qué clase de cosas puede hacer si la "
"llevan a su límite."

#. [message], speaker=Taryen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:369
msgid ""
"It is very unwise, to keep a beast that is so much stronger than yourself; "
"are you sure that she can be properly tamed?"
msgstr ""
"Es muy imprudente conservar a una bestia que es mucho más fuerte que uno "
"mismo; ¿estás seguro de que puede ser domada adecuadamente?"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:373
msgid ""
"Would both of you be kind enough to stop treating her as if she were an "
"animal?!"
msgstr ""
"¿Podrían ambos ser tan amables de dejar de tratarla como si fuera un animal?!"

#. [message], speaker=Taryen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:377
msgid ""
"From the vantage of an emperor, there is little difference between a peasant "
"and a beast of burden. Indeed, peasant behave very like beasts: brutalise "
"them, and they will cower from you, perhaps even bite at you; pet them, and "
"they will happily lick your hand and obey your every command."
msgstr ""
"Desde la perspectiva de un emperador, hay poca diferencia entre un campesino "
"y una bestia de carga. En efecto, los campesinos se comportan muy como "
"bestias: brutalízalos y se acobardarán ante ti, tal vez incluso te muerdan; "
"acarícialos y lamerán felizmente tu mano y obedecerán cada uno de tus "
"mandatos."

#. [message], speaker=Taryen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:381
msgid ""
"But I digress; I can see that you have developed a bond with that Arajunnan "
"freak, Aetheryon, and I shall trust that to serve as a yoke on her. This "
"brings us to the second reason that brought me here: I want you to return to "
"the southern continent and help Lord Dargamyr in his campaign."
msgstr ""
"Pero me desvío; veo que has desarrollado un vínculo con esa rareza arajunna, "
"Aetheryon, y confiaré en que eso sirva como yugo para ella. Esto nos lleva a "
"la segunda razón que me trajo aquí: quiero que regreses al continente sur y "
"ayudes al señor Dargamyr en su campaña."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:385
msgid ""
"Is that really necessary? As our wise Emperor has said with his own mouth, "
"not long ago, Lord Dargamyr, with his mighty mages and armoured troopers, "
"was more than enough to deal with the southerner rabble..."
msgstr ""
"¿Es realmente necesario? Como nuestro sabio emperador dijo con su propia "
"boca no hace mucho, el señor Dargamyr, con sus poderosos magos y tropas "
"acorazadas, era más que suficiente para lidiar con la chusma sureña…"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:389
msgid "<i>(punch!)</i>"
msgstr "<i>(¡golpe!)</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Taryen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:393
msgid ""
"(angrily) I warned you to put an end to your sarcasm, boy. Dargamyr's troops "
"were about to conquer the Chomi capital of Ifeh; the only reason they "
"failed, according to survivors, was the appearance of an unknown faction "
"wielding powers as vast as they were strange."
msgstr ""
"(enojado) Te advertí que pusieras fin a tu sarcasmo, muchacho. Las tropas de "
"Dargamyr estaban a punto de conquistar la capital chomi de Ifeh; la única "
"razón por la que fallaron, según los sobrevivientes, fue la aparición de una "
"facción desconocida que empuñaba poderes tan vastos como extraños."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:397
msgid ""
"(repressing anger) Does the report describe this faction... my Lord Emperor? "
"Depending on this description, I may even be able to identify it."
msgstr ""
"(reprimidiendo la ira) ¿El informe describe a esta facción… mi señor "
"emperador? Dependiendo de esa descripción, tal vez incluso pueda "
"identificarla."

#. [message], speaker=Taryen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:401
msgid ""
"A small group of humans followed by an elf, a dwarf, and a mermaid "
"sorceress. Does it sound familiar to you?"
msgstr ""
"Un pequeño grupo de humanos seguido por una elfa, un enano y una hechicera "
"sirena. ¿Te suena familiar?"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:405
msgid ""
"Indeed, it has to be them... Very well, my Lord Emperor, I will go to "
"Arajunna and make sure that Lord Dargamyr stands victorious, but I have one "
"condition: that I stand as his equal, and not as a subordinate. On my own, I "
"have brought war to the Emerald Plains and thwarted Aelvar's rebellion; I do "
"not wish to be commanded by one whom I do not recognise as being more "
"capable than myself."
msgstr ""
"En efecto, tienen que ser ellos… Muy bien, mi señor emperador, iré a "
"Arajunna y me aseguraré de que el señor Dargamyr salga victorioso, pero "
"tengo una condición: que esté como su igual, no como subordinado. Por mi "
"cuenta he llevado la guerra a las Llanuras Esmeralda y frustrado la rebelión "
"de Aelvar; no deseo ser comandado por alguien a quien no reconozco como más "
"capaz que yo."

#. [message], speaker=Taryen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:409
msgid ""
"At long last, you have spoken like a true member of the Iron Dinasty... And "
"for this reason alone I shall accept your condition. Prepare yourself and "
"your Arajunnan pet, you shall depart before nightfall; worry not about your "
"soldiers or about provisions, for I have brought both already."
msgstr ""
"Por fin has hablado como un verdadero miembro de la Dinastía de Hierro… Y "
"solo por esta razón aceptaré tu condición. Prepárate a ti y a tu mascota "
"arajunna, partirás antes del anochecer; no te preocupes por tus soldados ni "
"por provisiones, pues ya he traído ambas."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:424
msgid "(kindly) Galdra, I have something to ask you..."
msgstr "(amablemente) Galdra, tengo algo que pedirte…"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:428
msgid ""
"About going to Arajunna? I'm sorry, I couldn't help but overhear what you "
"and your father were saying..."
msgstr ""
"¿Sobre ir a Arajunna? Lo siento, no pude evitar oír lo que tú y tu padre "
"estaban diciendo…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:432
msgid ""
"Then I'm the one who should apologise, for subjecting you to the trash "
"spewed by the emperor's mouth... Anyway, I'm not taking you to fight; I'd "
"never even risk having you get hurt for the sake of that disgusting "
"Dargamyr... I just want you to meet some people who have recently gone "
"there. Who knows, they might even be able to help you recover your memories!"
msgstr ""
"Entonces soy yo quien debería disculparse por someterte a la basura que "
"escupió la boca del emperador… De todos modos, no te llevo para pelear; "
"nunca arriesgaría que te lastimaran por culpa de ese asqueroso Dargamyr… "
"Solo quiero que conozcas a unas personas que han ido allí recientemente. "
"Quién sabe, tal vez incluso puedan ayudarte a recuperar tus recuerdos."

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:436
msgid ""
"We have no time to waste, then; I'm really eager to meet these people..."
msgstr ""
"Entonces no tenemos tiempo que perder; realmente tengo muchas ganas de "
"conocer a esas personas…"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:512
msgid ""
"Blessed be Arajunna and it's endless river basins, never would I have "
"guessed that it was possible to go this deep inland without suffering from "
"dehydration and dragging my scales through dry earth...!"
msgstr ""
"Bendita sea Arajunna y sus infinitas cuencas fluviales, ¡nunca habría "
"adivinado que era posible adentrarse tanto tierra adentro sin sufrir "
"deshidratación ni arrastrar mis escamas por tierra seca…!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:516
msgid ""
"Be honest, you're just glad that you're able to follow your beloved without "
"having to leave your people behind, aren't you?"
msgstr ""
"Sé honesta, solo estás contenta de poder seguir a tu amado sin tener que "
"dejar atrás a tu pueblo, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:520
msgid "(haughtily) Maybe I am, and so what?"
msgstr "(altivamente) Tal vez sí, ¿y qué?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:524
msgid ""
"She's just jealous of you, Derceto; I bet she, too, wanted to have someone "
"who she could follow to the ends of the earth and the sea..."
msgstr ""
"Solo está celosa de ti, Derceto; apuesto a que ella también quería tener a "
"alguien a quien seguir hasta los confines de la tierra y el mar…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:528
msgid "But I do have someone like this – right, Algil?"
msgstr "Pero yo sí tengo a alguien así —verdad, Algil?"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:532
msgid ""
"What?! Och, Crimson Sorceress, stop saying such things, I have a wife and "
"children!"
msgstr ""
"¿¡Qué!? ¡Och, Hechicera Carmesí, deja de decir esas cosas, tengo esposa e "
"hijos!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:536
msgid "Really?! Oh my, I'm sorry, I had no idea that you..."
msgstr "¿¡En serio!? ¡Oh cielos, lo siento, no tenía idea de que tú…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:540
msgid ""
"Wait, can it be? The mighty, sly Crimson Sorceress, caught off guard at last?"
msgstr ""
"Espera, ¿puede ser? ¿La poderosa y astuta Hechicera Carmesí, pillada "
"desprevenida al fin?"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:544
msgid ""
"I'll never understand how you can be so laid-back, especially after the "
"battles we've just fought - and more so as we have the Sky Soul among us."
msgstr ""
"Nunca entenderé cómo puedes estar tan relajada, especialmente después de las "
"batallas que acabamos de librar —y más aún teniendo el Alma del Cielo entre "
"nosotros."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:548
msgid ""
"It's <i>because</i> we're in such a dangerous mission that we should enjoy "
"whatever moment of calm and camaraderie we can afford, Cornelya. War is "
"brutal no matter how you paint it, and yet sometimes it's inevitable if we "
"don't want to allow cruel people to do whatever they want. Still, if we "
"allow ourselves to be twisted by the brutality around us, we might become "
"the very monsters we set out to fight."
msgstr ""
"Es <i>precisamente porque</i> estamos en una misión tan peligrosa que "
"deberíamos disfrutar cada momento de calma y camaradería que podamos "
"permitirnos, Cornelya. La guerra es brutal no importa cómo la pintes, y aun "
"así a veces es inevitable si no queremos permitir que personas crueles hagan "
"lo que quieran. Sin embargo, si nos dejamos torcer por la brutalidad que nos "
"rodea, podríamos convertirnos en los mismos monstruos contra los que salimos "
"a luchar."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:552
msgid ""
"Still, Cornelya has got point; we can't linger here for so long, as we're in "
"the territory of Chomi outlaws, Washraha and Deshrai. Not to mention that "
"the Wesnothians must be trying to secure this region too, since it's a "
"strategically important one. Come on, we're not that far from the Deva "
"Mountains now."
msgstr ""
"Aun así, Cornelya tiene razón; no podemos quedarnos aquí tanto tiempo, ya "
"que estamos en territorio de forajidos chomi, washraha y deshra. Sin "
"mencionar que los wesnothianos también deben estar intentando asegurar esta "
"región, ya que es estratégicamente importante. Vamos, ya no estamos tan "
"lejos de las Montañas Deva."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:565
msgid "Are you fine, Tenma? You made a weird face out of a sudden..."
msgstr "¿Estás bien, Tenma? Hiciste una cara extraña de repente…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:569
msgid ""
"Yes, it's just... I had a weird feeling just now, but it's nothing, don't "
"worry..."
msgstr ""
"Sí, es solo que… tuve una sensación extraña ahora mismo, pero no es nada, no "
"te preocupes…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:573
msgid ""
"If you sensed something strange, then it can't be nothing. From now on, we "
"should be even more careful with what may lie ahead..."
msgstr ""
"Si sentiste algo extraño, entonces no puede ser nada. De ahora en adelante, "
"deberíamos ser aún más cuidadosos con lo que pueda haber por delante…"

#. [unit], id=Humri, type=Washraja
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:593
msgid "Humri"
msgstr "Humri"

#. [unit], id=Arkkus, type=Deshra Juggernaut
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:620
msgid "Arkkus"
msgstr "Arkkus"

#. [unit], id=Aluwemi, type=Chomi Hero
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:647
msgid "Aluwemi"
msgstr "Aluwemi"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:668
msgid ""
"There seems to an entrance into a system of caves here... I'm a bit afraid "
"of going in there, though, what if I find giants...?"
msgstr ""
"Parece que hay una entrada a un sistema de cuevas aquí… Estoy un poco "
"asustado de entrar ahí, sin embargo, ¿y si encuentro gigantes…?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:672
msgid ""
"Don't worry, the Deshrai avoid caves. It could be a good idea to explore "
"where this entrance leads to; if there is a shortcut through these "
"mountains, it would save us a lot of time."
msgstr ""
"No te preocupes, los deshra evitan las cuevas. Podría ser buena idea "
"explorar a dónde lleva esta entrada; si hay un atajo a través de estas "
"montañas, nos ahorraría mucho tiempo."

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:676
msgid "Well, let me see.."
msgstr "Bueno, déjame ver…"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:692
msgid "Argh, I nearly got lost in there..."
msgstr "Argh, casi me pierdo ahí dentro…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:696
msgid "So how do we know where that merfolk ended at now?"
msgstr "Entonces, ¿cómo sabemos dónde terminó esa sirena ahora?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:700
msgid "Not far away, judging by what I can hear..."
msgstr "No muy lejos, a juzgar por lo que puedo oír…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:780
msgid ""
"Long time no see, travellers. I am sincerely glad to see that you have "
"managed to stay alive and well; still, I wonder where you have been hiding "
"in this world, that only recently did I hear any word on you."
msgstr ""
"Hace mucho que no nos vemos, viajeros. Me alegra sinceramente ver que han "
"logrado mantenerse vivos y bien; aun así, me pregunto dónde se han estado "
"escondiendo en este mundo, ya que solo recientemente he oído algo de ustedes."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:784
msgid ""
"And you still haven't given up on discovering the secrets of my background..."
msgstr "Y tú todavía no has renunciado a descubrir los secretos de mi origen…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:788
msgid ""
"Those who seek knowledge are always hungry for it, as every answer leads to "
"another question; so yes, I still want to learn about your origins and your "
"magic. This time, though, I have knowledge to trade with you; knowledge "
"which even you may ignore. Galdra, please come here."
msgstr ""
"Los que buscan conocimiento siempre tienen hambre de él, pues cada respuesta "
"lleva a otra pregunta; así que sí, aún quiero aprender sobre tus orígenes y "
"tu magia. Esta vez, sin embargo, tengo conocimiento para intercambiar "
"contigo; conocimiento que incluso tú podrías ignorar. Galdra, por favor ven "
"aquí."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:801
msgid "(puzzled) That girl...!"
msgstr "(perpleja) ¡Esa chica…!"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:805
msgid "(serious) I thought you'd notice that as well..."
msgstr "(seria) Pensé que también lo notarías…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:809
msgid "Erm, we, lesser beings, have not, though. What's with that girl?"
msgstr ""
"Ehm, nosotros, los seres menores, no lo hemos notado, sin embargo. ¿Qué pasa "
"con esa chica?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:813
msgid ""
"Remember that weird feeling I had as we entered this region? Truth is, I had "
"sensed some kind of energy which I'd never felt before. I don't know how to "
"explain it, but... it's a power so unnatural and insidious, it makes me a "
"bit dizzy..."
msgstr ""
"¿Recuerdan esa sensación extraña que tuve cuando entramos en esta región? La "
"verdad es que sentí algún tipo de energía que nunca había sentido antes. No "
"sé cómo explicarlo, pero… es un poder tan antinatural e insidioso que me "
"marea un poco…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:817
msgid ""
"I have met this girl, Galdra, in the depths of the Caves of Light, not too "
"far from here; she followed me to Wesnoth, and there she was tested by our "
"best and wisest mages. Not only did she prove herself mightier than some of "
"our finest masters, but the power she displayed is of a kind that is unknown "
"to us. I returned to this continent in hopes of meeting you, for I believed "
"that you might know something about Galdra's powers... but I now see that "
"you're as puzzled as everyone else who's witnessed her skills, or am I wrong?"
msgstr ""
"He conocido a esta chica, Galdra, en las profundidades de las Cuevas de la "
"Luz, no muy lejos de aquí; me siguió hasta Wesnoth, y allí fue puesta a "
"prueba por nuestros mejores y más sabios magos. No solo demostró ser más "
"poderosa que algunos de nuestros mejores maestros, sino que el poder que "
"mostró es de un tipo desconocido para nosotros. Regresé a este continente "
"con la esperanza de encontrarlos, pues creía que podrían saber algo sobre "
"los poderes de Galdra… pero ahora veo que están tan perplejos como todos los "
"que han presenciado sus habilidades, ¿o me equivoco?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:821
msgid ""
"Fine, you've got a point there; the magic aura coming from that girl is "
"really something we can't identify – and, modesty aside, this means "
"something. So, what do you suggest? Do you plan on trading her for our "
"knowledge?"
msgstr ""
"Está bien, tienes razón en eso; el aura mágica que emana de esa chica es "
"realmente algo que no podemos identificar —y, modestia aparte, eso significa "
"algo. Entonces, ¿qué sugieres? ¿Planeas intercambiarla por nuestro "
"conocimiento?"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:825
msgid "(scared) Aetheryon..."
msgstr "(asustada) Aetheryon…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:829
msgid ""
"Don't worry, Galdra, I won't do that. (chuckles) I thought only my father "
"and those old bastards of Alduin would treat her as a thing; I am "
"disappointed to see you do the same."
msgstr ""
"No te preocupes, Galdra, no haré eso. (ríe) Pensé que solo mi padre y esos "
"viejos bastardos de Alduin la tratarían como una cosa; me decepciona ver que "
"tú haces lo mismo."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:833
msgid ""
"You know very well what she meant, Aetheryon. But our answer remains the "
"same as before: we won't give you any more means with which you may conquer "
"and enslave the rest of the world. On the other hand, if you wish our aid in "
"trying to decipher this girl's mystery, then we may come to an agreement."
msgstr ""
"Sabes muy bien a qué se refería, Aetheryon. Pero nuestra respuesta sigue "
"siendo la misma que antes: no te daremos más medios con los que puedas "
"conquistar y esclavizar al resto del mundo. Por otro lado, si deseas nuestra "
"ayuda para intentar descifrar el misterio de esta chica, entonces podríamos "
"llegar a un acuerdo."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:837
msgid ""
"So you want all without yielding anything? For someone who speaks so loftily "
"against Wesnothian greed, you're quite the greedy one yourself! As much as I "
"want to understand Galdra, I think it is very unfair to..."
msgstr ""
"¿Entonces quieres todo sin ceder nada? ¡Para alguien que habla tan "
"altivamente contra la codicia wesnothiana, tú mismo eres bastante codicioso! "
"Por mucho que quiera entender a Galdra, creo que es muy injusto…"

#. [unit], id=Dargamyr, type=Great Mage
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:856
msgid "Lord Dargamyr"
msgstr "Señor Dargamyr"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:879
msgid ""
"(annoyed) With a thousand curses, couldn't their timing be any worse...?! "
"(shouting) I thought that the Lord Emperor had made it clear that you were "
"to respect my command, Lord Dargamyr!"
msgstr ""
"(molesto) ¡Con mil maldiciones, no podrían haber llegado en peor momento…?! "
"(gritando) ¡Pensé que el señor emperador había dejado claro que debías "
"respetar mi mando, señor Dargamyr!"

#. [message], speaker=Dargamyr
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:883
msgid ""
"Prince Aetheryon, do not misunderstand me; I had decided to conquer this "
"region even before you arrived, and, since I had not been informed of your "
"own intention of coming here... Notwithstanding, we have no reason to "
"quarrel, do we? Even if your... girl is as prodigious as rumours claim, you "
"may welcome some aid against this infamous mongrel faction..."
msgstr ""
"Príncipe Aetheryon, no me malinterprete; había decidido conquistar esta "
"región incluso antes de que usted llegara, y como no había sido informado de "
"su propia intención de venir aquí… No obstante, no tenemos razón para "
"pelearnos, ¿verdad? Incluso si su… chica es tan prodigiosa como dicen los "
"rumores, podría agradecer algo de ayuda contra esta infame facción mestiza…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:887
msgid ""
"*Damn, I can't let this idiot capture Tenma and her companions, let alone "
"kill them; but, if I refuse to fight them, I may as well be branded a "
"traitor...* Very well, let us fight together – but I want them alive, each "
"one of them! There are things I wish to ask them, for the sake of your "
"campaign's success."
msgstr ""
"*Maldición, no puedo dejar que este idiota capture a Tenma y sus compañeros, "
"mucho menos que los mate; pero si me niego a pelear contra ellos, bien "
"podría ser tildado de traidor…* Muy bien, luchemos juntos —¡pero los quiero "
"vivos, a cada uno de ellos! Hay cosas que deseo preguntarles, por el bien "
"del éxito de tu campaña."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:891
msgid "(sigh) For a moment, I had forgotten which side you were on..."
msgstr "(suspiro) Por un momento olvidé de qué lado estabas…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:895
msgid ""
"Don't let that little alliance in the Far North make you forget everything "
"he and his nation have done to Kodakuni! If we still wish to free our "
"country, we were always bound to fight him again!"
msgstr ""
"¡No dejes que esa pequeña alianza en el Lejano Norte te haga olvidar todo lo "
"que él y su nación le hicieron a Kodakuni! Si aún deseamos liberar nuestro "
"país, ¡siempre estuvimos destinados a enfrentarlo de nuevo!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:899
msgid ""
"By the way, <i>nephew</i>, your father is well. Wasted in a small frontier "
"outpost overlooking the scorching Sandy Wastes, but otherwise healthy."
msgstr ""
"Por cierto, <i>sobrino</i>, tu padre está bien. Perdido en un pequeño puesto "
"fronterizo con vista a los abrasadores Desiertos Arenoso, pero por lo demás "
"sano."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:903
msgid "(unsheathing sword) Tsc, as if I cared about him!"
msgstr "(desenvainando espada) Tsc, ¡como si me importara él!"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:907
msgid "(still scared) Aetheryon..."
msgstr "(todavía asustada) Aetheryon…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:911
msgid ""
"Sorry, Galdra, if I had listened to you before we might have been able to "
"avoid Dargamyr and this whole fight..."
msgstr ""
"Lo siento, Galdra, si te hubiera escuchado antes tal vez podríamos haber "
"evitado a Dargamyr y toda esta pelea…"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:915
msgid ""
"That's not it... That girl, whom you called Tenma... I don't like her... "
"She's got a fearsome power in her..."
msgstr ""
"No es eso... Esa chica a la que llaman Tenma... no me agrada... Tiene un "
"poder temible dentro de ella..."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:919
msgid ""
"*As I guessed, only Tenma could match her in power...* I agree, but I assure "
"you she isn't an evil person. If you just hide and protect yourself..."
msgstr ""
"*Como supuse, solo Tenma podría igualarla en poder...* Estoy de acuerdo, "
"pero les aseguro que no es una persona malvada. Si solo se escondieran y se "
"protegieran..."

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:923
msgid ""
"(suddenly resolute) You misunderstood me, Aetheryon, I don't want to hide, "
"it wouldn't work anyway. This time I <i>want</i> to fight."
msgstr ""
"(de repente resuelta) Me malinterpretaste, Aetheryon, no quiero esconderme, "
"de todos modos no funcionaría. Esta vez <i>quiero</i> pelear."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:927
msgid ""
"If you wish so, then I'll make sure that you find a way to reach her. *That "
"was not in the plan, but it may bring interesting results. Will I finally be "
"able to witness her true power...?*"
msgstr ""
"Si eso deseas, entonces me aseguraré de que encuentres una forma de "
"alcanzarla. *Eso no estaba en el plan, pero podría traer resultados "
"interesantes. ¿Por fin podré presenciar su verdadero poder…?*"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:933
msgid "Defeat Prince Aetheryon and Lord Dargamyr"
msgstr "Derrotar al príncipe Aetheryon y al señor Dargamyr"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:937
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:26
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:711
msgid "Defeat Galdra"
msgstr "Derrotar a Galdra"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:970
msgid ""
"Tenma may transform into Dragon-Slayer mode once every scenario by right-"
"clicking on her; the transformation will last for 3 turns, after which "
"she'll go back to normal.\n"
"\n"
"Galdra is not a normal being, so a normal attack may not work on her..."
msgstr ""
"Tenma puede transformarse en modo Matadragones una vez por escenario "
"haciendo clic derecho sobre ella; la transformación durará 3 turnos, después "
"de los cuales volverá a la normalidad.\n"
"\n"
"Galdra no es un ser normal, por lo que un ataque normal podría no funcionar "
"contra ella…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:991
msgid ""
"I forgot to tell you, travellers, one of Galdra's abilities is the summoning "
"of these creatures; I wonder which is stronger, her 'Nightmares' or your "
"elementals!"
msgstr ""
"Olvidé decirles, viajeros, una de las habilidades de Galdra es la invocación "
"de estas criaturas; me pregunto cuál es más fuerte, sus «Pesadillas» o sus "
"elementales."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:995
msgid ""
"Nightmares... Akhen's Scrolls describe similar creatures living in the Caves "
"of Light..."
msgstr ""
"Pesadillas… Los Pergaminos de Akhen describen criaturas similares viviendo "
"en las Cuevas de la Luz…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1013
msgid "Damn...! I should have been more careful..."
msgstr "¡Maldición…! Debí haber sido más cuidadoso…"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1017
msgid "Aetheryon, wait! I won't let you be harmed like this..."
msgstr "¡Aetheryon, espera! No dejaré que te lastimen así…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1024
msgid "Galdra, you've... you've just saved my life...!"
msgstr "¡Galdra, tú… acabas de salvarme la vida…!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1028
msgid ""
"Aetheryon is being protected by that girl, we should take her down before "
"attacking him!"
msgstr ""
"Aetheryon está siendo protegido por esa chica, ¡deberíamos derribarla antes "
"de atacarlo a él!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1034
msgid ""
"Argh! A thousand curses upon you and your impertinence, travellers...! I "
"will withdraw now, but only to recover my strength; Galdra, please hold on "
"until I return..."
msgstr ""
"¡Argh! ¡Mil maldiciones sobre ustedes y su impertinencia, viajeros…! Me "
"retiraré ahora, pero solo para recuperar mis fuerzas; Galdra, por favor "
"aguanta hasta que regrese…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1051
msgid "Damned be his teleportation, he escaped again!"
msgstr "¡Maldita sea su teletransportación, escapó otra vez!"

#. [message], speaker=Dargamyr
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1065
msgid "No...! Prince Aetheryon, please ask your girl to heal me..."
msgstr "¡No…! Príncipe Aetheryon, por favor pídele a tu chica que me cure…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1069
msgid ""
"Sending her to you would break my formation, Lord Dargamyr; I told you to "
"stay at Mumbari and let me deal with this threat."
msgstr ""
"Enviarla contigo rompería mi formación, señor Dargamyr; te dije que te "
"quedaras en Mumbari y me dejaras lidiar con esta amenaza."

#. [message], speaker=Dargamyr
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1073
msgid "Prince Aet...!!!"
msgstr "¡Príncipe Aet…!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1093
msgid "What...? Has she just renewed her own strength?!"
msgstr "¿Qué…? ¿Acaba de renovar su propia fuerza?!"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1097
msgid ""
"Whatever ill you try to cause me shall not work, stranger! Now I beg you, do "
"not try and attack me, the only one I want to fight is the one you call "
"Tenma!"
msgstr ""
"¡Cualquier mal que intentes causarme no funcionará, extraña! Ahora te ruego, "
"no intentes atacarme, ¡la única a quien quiero pelear es a la que llamas "
"Tenma!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1101
msgid "Leave her to me, I'll find a way to knock her out!"
msgstr "Déjenmela a mí, ¡encontraré una forma de dejarla fuera de combate!"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1125
msgid "Not... yet!"
msgstr "¡Todavía… no!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1132
msgid ""
"Normal spells don't seem to affect her; I think I have no choice byt to use "
"the Dragon-Slaying techniques..."
msgstr ""
"Los hechizos normales no parecen afectarla; creo que no tengo más opción que "
"usar las técnicas Matadragones…"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1156
msgid "AAAAHHHHHHH!!!"
msgstr "¡¡¡AAAAHHHHHHH!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1160
msgid "GALDRA!!! I... can't believe she was defeated this easily?!"
msgstr ""
"¡¡¡GALDRA!!! Yo… ¡no puedo creer que haya sido derrotada tan fácilmente?!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1164
msgid ""
"I don't know why you want to fight me that badly, girl, but I have no reason "
"or desire to hurt you. If you wish, we could heal you, and then we can talk "
"and settle whatever score you have with me in..."
msgstr ""
"No sé por qué quieres pelear conmigo con tanta intensidad, chica, pero no "
"tengo razón ni deseo de lastimarte. Si quieres, podríamos curarte, y luego "
"podemos hablar y arreglar cualquier cuenta que tengas conmigo en…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1188
msgid "What... What was that just now?"
msgstr "¿Qué… qué fue eso justo ahora?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1192
msgid "(scared) W-what is happening...?!"
msgstr "(asustada) ¡¿Q-qué está pasando…?! "

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1196
msgid ""
"In an instant, the roar of the battle was silenced as every contender stood "
"still; a stillness broken only by the frightened screams of those who stood "
"near Galdra – or what was left of her. Her body lay on the ground, twisting "
"violently and impossibly, her smooth skin split like dry earth, a purple "
"light shining through the cracks; her once kind, girlish face was now "
"contorted in an almost demonic roar, and her eyes, shining like two purple "
"stars, were fixed on Tenma."
msgstr ""
"En un instante, el rugido de la batalla se silenció mientras todos los "
"contendientes se quedaron inmóviles; una quietud rota solo por los gritos "
"asustados de quienes estaban cerca de Galdra —o de lo que quedaba de ella. "
"Su cuerpo yacía en el suelo, retorciéndose violentamente e imposiblemente, "
"su piel suave se partió como tierra seca, una luz púrpura brillando a través "
"de las grietas; su rostro una vez amable y juvenil ahora estaba "
"contorsionado en un rugido casi demoníaco, y sus ojos, brillando como dos "
"estrellas púrpuras, estaban fijos en Tenma."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1200
msgid "(in shock) N-no, I... W-what have I...?"
msgstr "(en shock) N-no, yo… ¿Q-qué he…?"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1204
msgid ""
"(in coarse voice) The... Heiress... has... come... I... have... to... "
"AWAKE!!!"
msgstr "(con voz ronca) La… Heredera… ha… llegado… Yo… tengo… que… ¡DESPERTAR!"

#. [message], speaker=Dargamyr
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1219
msgid ""
"W-What on the wide green world is happening here... What's happened to the "
"skies?! Aetheryon, what kind of monster have you unleashed?!"
msgstr ""
"¿Q-qué demonios está pasando aquí en el vasto mundo verde… qué le pasó a los "
"cielos?! Aetheryon, ¿qué clase de monstruo has desatado?!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1238
msgid "AARRGGHH!!! W-what was that...?!"
msgstr "¡¡¡AARRGGHH!!! ¿¡Q-qué fue eso…?! "

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1242
msgid "(panting) My power...! It felt like... burning me from within...!"
msgstr "(jadeando) ¡Mi poder…! ¡Se sintió como… quemándome desde dentro…!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1246
msgid ""
"Damn it, why have all the mages been knocked out so suddenly?! Just what is "
"that girl...?!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldición, por qué todos los magos han quedado fuera de combate tan de "
"repente?! ¡¿Qué es exactamente esa chica…?! "

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1250
msgid "I am..."
msgstr "Yo soy…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1289
msgid "(in pain) Galdra, you...!!!"
msgstr "(con dolor) ¡Galdra, tú…!"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1293
msgid ""
"It is little use to tell you who I am, daughter of Tithanya, for no living "
"being on this world truly remembers those who gave shape to this universe. "
"However... In those days when they still walked on Irdya, I was known as the "
"Avatar Vanadya, and from my essence magic was created."
msgstr ""
"De poco sirve decirte quién soy, hija de Tithanya, pues ningún ser vivo en "
"este mundo recuerda verdaderamente a aquellos que dieron forma a este "
"universo. Sin embargo… En aquellos días cuando aún caminaban por Irdya, fui "
"conocida como el Avatar Vanadya, y de mi esencia se creó la magia."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1297
msgid "A... No... No, you... You can't be... The Avatars are all dead..."
msgstr "Un… No… No, tú… No puedes ser… Los Avatares están todos muertos…"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1301
msgid ""
"So you say, Heiress, but you seem unaware that the source of the Avatars' "
"existence is everything that exists; I exist on Magic, the eternal energy "
"which accesses the realms of the impossible, so let me ask you..."
msgstr ""
"Eso dices, Heredera, pero pareces ignorar que la fuente de la existencia de "
"los Avatares es todo lo que existe; yo existo en la Magia, la energía eterna "
"que accede a los reinos de lo imposible, así que permíteme preguntarte…"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1305
msgid "...How can something that never disappears ever truly perish?"
msgstr "…¿Cómo puede algo que nunca desaparece perecer verdaderamente?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1366
msgid "Tenma! No, no, that's not good...! Hold on, we're going to..."
msgstr "¡Tenma! No, no, eso no está bien… ¡Aguanta, vamos a…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1370
msgid ""
"(frightened) STAY AWAY, ALL OF YOU! SHE'S NOT SOMEONE YOU CAN HOPE TO DEFEAT!"
msgstr ""
"(asustada) ¡ALÉJENSE TODOS! ¡NO ES ALGUIEN A QUIEN PUEDAN ESPERAR DERROTAR!"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1374
msgid ""
"So at least you know who you are dealing with, Heiress; I commend your "
"wisdom. But I wonder, how will you get out of this predicament?"
msgstr ""
"Así que al menos sabes con quién estás tratando, Heredera; alabo tu "
"sabiduría. Pero me pregunto, ¿cómo saldrás de este aprieto?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1378
msgid ""
"Just like I've gotten out of every predicament so far: by fighting my way "
"through to my friends!"
msgstr ""
"¡Igual que he salido de cada aprieto hasta ahora: luchando mi camino hasta "
"mis amigos!"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1382
msgid ""
"(laughing) Fighting for those you love is a powerful motivational force, "
"Heiress, but I am afraid you'll need much more to defeat me... I will give "
"you a chance to prove yourself. Come, Heiress, let us see if you are ready "
"to fight for Her will!"
msgstr ""
"(riendo) Luchar por aquellos que amas es una fuerza motivacional poderosa, "
"Heredera, pero me temo que necesitarás mucho más para derrotarme… Te daré "
"una oportunidad de probarte. Ven, Heredera, veamos si estás lista para "
"luchar por Su voluntad!"

#. [message], speaker=Dargamyr
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1392
msgid ""
"(trembling) It seems that the monster has somehow shifted her attention to "
"someone else... Quick, soldiers, we must use this chance to crush our foes "
"while their strongest fighter is busy!"
msgstr ""
"(temblando) Parece que el monstruo de alguna forma ha desviado su atención "
"hacia otra persona… ¡Rápido, soldados, debemos aprovechar esta oportunidad "
"para aplastar a nuestros enemigos mientras su luchadora más fuerte está "
"ocupada!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1396
msgid ""
"He still wants to fight, the fool...! Friends, we have no choice but to win "
"this battle while Tenma deals with Galdra!"
msgstr ""
"¡Todavía quiere pelear, el idiota…! Amigos, no tenemos más opción que ganar "
"esta batalla mientras Tenma se encarga de Galdra."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1400
msgid ""
"I did not wish things to turn out this way, but I cannot simply withdraw and "
"leave Galdra behind like this... But my orders remain the same, Dargamyr! "
"Don't you dare kill them, they're mine!"
msgstr ""
"No deseaba que las cosas terminaran así, pero no puedo simplemente retirarme "
"y dejar a Galdra atrás de esta forma… ¡Pero mis órdenes siguen siendo las "
"mismas, Dargamyr! ¡No te atrevas a matarlos, son míos!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1406
msgid ""
"Aetheryon, are you sure that you still want to fight? I can see that you "
"like Galdra, as we like Tenma; shouldn't we be working together to find a "
"way to stop them?"
msgstr ""
"Aetheryon, ¿estás seguro de que todavía quieres pelear? Veo que aprecias a "
"Galdra, así como nosotros apreciamos a Tenma; ¿no deberíamos trabajar juntos "
"para encontrar una forma de detenerlas?"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1410
msgid ""
"I... I did not wish things to turn out this way, but I cannot simply "
"withdraw now... I trust that Galdra will take care of herself and win, thus "
"I will fight and win as well, so that she will not have to see me defeated!"
msgstr ""
"Yo… no deseaba que las cosas terminaran así, pero no puedo simplemente "
"retirarme ahora… Confío en que Galdra sabrá cuidarse y ganar, por eso yo "
"también pelearé y ganaré, ¡para que ella no tenga que verme derrotado!"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1414
msgid ""
"Forget about being nice to him, Olokun, it's about time we settled scores "
"with him anyway!"
msgstr ""
"Olvídate de ser amable con él, Olokun, ¡de todos modos ya es hora de ajustar "
"cuentas con él!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1422
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:28
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:700
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:733
msgid "Withstand Galdra's attack"
msgstr "Resistir el ataque de Galdra"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1455
msgid ""
"Tenma may transform into Dragon-Slayer mode once every scenario by right-"
"clicking on her; the transformation will last for 3 turns, after which "
"she'll go back to normal."
msgstr ""
"Tenma puede transformarse en modo Matadragones una vez por escenario "
"haciendo clic derecho sobre ella; la transformación durará 3 turnos, después "
"de los cuales volverá a la normalidad."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1486
msgid "No way... Not even the Dragon-Slayer's power was enough to win...?"
msgstr ""
"¿No puede ser… ni siquiera el poder de la Matadragones fue suficiente para "
"ganar…?"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1490
msgid ""
"You have put up a good fight, Heiress, I will give you that. Nevertheless, I "
"am sorry to tell you that, with the strength you have displayed today, you "
"will always lose to the Sky Dragon, whose true power is akin to that of an "
"Avatar like myself..."
msgstr ""
"Has luchado bien, Heredera, te lo concedo. Sin embargo, lamento decirte que, "
"con la fuerza que has mostrado hoy, siempre perderás contra el Dragón del "
"Cielo, cuyo verdadero poder es similar al de un Avatar como yo…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1494
msgid "I'm... not... done... yet!"
msgstr "¡Aún… no… he… terminado!"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1498
msgid "(sigh) Unfortunately, you still have much to learn..."
msgstr "(suspiro) Lamentablemente, aún tienes mucho que aprender…"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1515
msgid ""
"Farewell, Heiress; we will meet again when you are ready. Take your time, I "
"will be waiting. However..."
msgstr ""
"Adiós, Heredera; nos volveremos a encontrar cuando estés lista. Tómate tu "
"tiempo, estaré esperando. Sin embargo…"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1519
msgid "<i>picks the Sky Soul from Tenma</i>"
msgstr "<i>toma el Alma del Cielo de Tenma</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1523
msgid ""
"...my patience will not be extended to those who have used my essence to "
"besmirch and break this world. If you care about them so much, you may want "
"to hurry a little..."
msgstr ""
"…mi paciencia no se extenderá a aquellos que han usado mi esencia para "
"manchar y romper este mundo. Si te importan tanto, tal vez quieras "
"apresurarte un poco…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#. [message], speaker=Gelendras
#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1527
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:587
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:972
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:896
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:932
msgid "No..."
msgstr "No…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1531
msgid "Tenma, NO!!!"
msgstr "¡Tenma, NO!"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1535
msgid ""
"Olokun, we... we have to flee while we can... We cannot hope to defeat a "
"goddess...!"
msgstr ""
"Olokun, nosotros… tenemos que huir mientras podamos… ¡No podemos esperar "
"derrotar a una diosa…!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1539
msgid "GALDRA...!!!"
msgstr "¡¡¡GALDRA!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1585
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:528
msgid "No way... How could I have fallen...?"
msgstr "¿No puede ser… cómo pude caer…?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1601
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:374
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:542
msgid ""
"I can't die now... I must keep my promise of helping Tenma... and of living "
"with her..."
msgstr ""
"No puedo morir ahora… Debo cumplir mi promesa de ayudar a Tenma… y de vivir "
"con ella…"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1605
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:378
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:546
msgid "OLOKUN, NO!!!"
msgstr "¡¡¡OLOKUN, NO!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1620
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:561
msgid "How could I fail my friends... and her...?"
msgstr "¿Cómo pude fallarles a mis amigos… y a ella…?"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1624
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1449
msgid "KENSHIRO, NO!!!"
msgstr "¡¡¡KENSHIRO, NO!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1639
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:580
msgid "I've fallen... Alas, I wish I could see you grow more, young friends..."
msgstr "He caído… Ay, ojalá pudiera verlos crecer más, jóvenes amigos…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1653
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:426
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:594
msgid "Curses, I cannot die, not now...! I haven't even told him what I..."
msgstr ""
"¡Maldición, no puedo morir, no ahora…! ¡Ni siquiera le he dicho lo que yo…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1657
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:430
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:598
msgid "CORNELYA!!! No... How could I fail to protect her?!"
msgstr "¡¡¡CORNELYA!!! No… ¿cómo pude fallar en protegerla?!"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1672
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:445
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:613
msgid "I'm... dying...?!"
msgstr "¿Estoy… muriendo…?"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1691
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:632
msgid ""
"Arrgghh!!! I fall before fulfilling my promise to Udhark... alas, we had "
"such a great chance to end the... war between dwarves and trolls..."
msgstr ""
"¡¡¡Arrgghh!!! Caigo antes de cumplir mi promesa a Udhark… ay, tuvimos una "
"gran oportunidad para terminar la… guerra entre enanos y trolls…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1708
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:60
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:175
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:318
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:481
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:649
msgid "MIDORI!!!"
msgstr "¡¡¡MIDORI!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Midori
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1712
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:64
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:179
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:322
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:485
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:653
msgid "Sorry, Tenma, I couldn't help you as I wanted..."
msgstr "Lo siento, Tenma, no pude ayudarte como quería…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1716
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1736
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:68
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:88
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:183
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:203
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:326
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:346
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:489
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:509
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:657
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:677
msgid ""
"(crying) I'm the one who should apologize for not being able to protect "
"you... Rest in peace, my friend, I promise you I will free our village..."
msgstr ""
"(llorando) Soy yo quien debería disculparse por no haber podido protegerte… "
"Descansa en paz, amiga mía, te prometo que liberaré nuestra aldea…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1728
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:80
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:195
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:338
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:501
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:669
msgid "AKANE!!!"
msgstr "¡¡¡AKANE!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Akane
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1732
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:84
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:199
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:342
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:505
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:673
msgid ""
"Ugh! These darn idiots caught me... Sorry, friend, I won't be able to follow "
"you further..."
msgstr ""
"¡Ugh! Estos malditos idiotas me atraparon… Lo siento, amiga, no podré "
"seguirte más…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/36_Clash_Of_Powers.cfg:1745
msgid ""
"We shouldn't have wasted so much time crossing these plains, we might be "
"caught by the main Wesnothian armies now!"
msgstr ""
"¡No debimos perder tanto tiempo cruzando estas llanuras, ahora podríamos ser "
"atrapados por los ejércitos principales wesnothianos!"

#. [scenario], id=37_Dead_World
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:4
msgid "Dead World"
msgstr "Mundo Muerto"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:20
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:592
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:908
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:987
msgid "Cross the Land of the Dead to find the Veil of Dreams"
msgstr "Cruzar la Tierra de los Muertos para encontrar el Velo de los Sueños"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:28
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:600
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:916
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:995
msgid "Destruction of Ashura"
msgstr "Destrucción de Ashura"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:34
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:610
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:930
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1013
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1643
msgid ""
"In this scenario, Tenma may neither transform into Dragon-Slayer, nor "
"recruit, nor recall.\n"
"The Land of the Dead's atmosphere will cause her to lose some hp every "
"turn.\n"
"There are no villages in this scenario.\n"
"There will be no gold carryover to the next scenario"
msgstr ""
"En este escenario, Tenma no puede transformarse en Matadragones, ni "
"reclutar, ni reincorporar.\n"
"La atmósfera de la Tierra de los Muertos le hará perder algo de vida cada "
"turno.\n"
"No hay aldeas en este escenario.\n"
"No habrá traspaso de oro al siguiente escenario."

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:57
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:71
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:86
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:101
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:116
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:131
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:146
msgid "Souls"
msgstr "Almas"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:275
msgid "It's so dark..."
msgstr "Está tan oscuro…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:279
msgid "...silent..."
msgstr "…silencioso…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:283
msgid "...and so...tactless..."
msgstr "…y tan… insensible…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:287
msgid "...as if I had no senses... I can't even open my eyes... and yet..."
msgstr ""
"…como si no tuviera sentidos… ni siquiera puedo abrir los ojos… y aun así…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:291
msgid "...I can feel presences everywhere..."
msgstr "…puedo sentir presencias por todas partes…"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:295
msgid "Use your soul senses, girl..."
msgstr "Usa tus sentidos del alma, chica…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:299
msgid "...What?... All right, I will try..."
msgstr "…¿Qué…? Está bien, lo intentaré…"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:324
msgid "How about now?"
msgstr "¿Qué tal ahora?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:328
msgid "I- wait, you...! What... Where...?!"
msgstr "Yo— espera, ¡tú…! ¿Qué… dónde…?!"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:332
msgid ""
"Still yourself, I bear you no ill intent; I have nothing to gain from "
"harming you. As for your other questions... I know not how you ended up "
"here, with your physical body, but as it stands, you're the newest arrival "
"to the Land of the Dead."
msgstr ""
"Tranquilízate, no te deseo ningún mal; no gano nada lastimándote. En cuanto "
"a tus otras preguntas… no sé cómo terminaste aquí con tu cuerpo físico, pero "
"tal como están las cosas, eres la recién llegada a la Tierra de los Muertos."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:336
msgid ""
"So I'm... dead?! No way, I can't die now, I've got so much more to do...!"
msgstr ""
"¿Entonces estoy… muerta?! ¡No puede ser, no puedo morir ahora, tengo tantas "
"cosas más por hacer…!"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:340
msgid ""
"(impatient) Stupid girl, have you paid no any attention to what I said? "
"You've arrived at this plane with your physical, living body; such is a very "
"basic, stupid mistake committed by those who have just begun dabbling in the "
"Dark Arts..."
msgstr ""
"(impaciente) Chica estúpida, ¿acaso no prestaste atención a lo que dije? Has "
"llegado a este plano con tu cuerpo físico y vivo; tal es un error básico y "
"estúpido cometido por aquellos que apenas han comenzado a incursionar en las "
"Artes Oscuras…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:344
msgid ""
"I'm no necromancer, I was sent here by... Damn, I can't even tell what she "
"is now..."
msgstr ""
"No soy nigromante, fui enviada aquí por… Maldición, ni siquiera puedo decir "
"qué es ella ahora…"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:348
msgid ""
"It must have been an expert dark mage indeed, to have hurled someone into "
"this world; as the first master of Necromancy, it always fills me with "
"pride, to see my acolytes reach such heights... But I digress. As I was "
"saying, you should have been utterly destroyed by entering this realm with "
"your physical body, but I sense you're protected by some unique aura..."
msgstr ""
"Debe haber sido un mago oscuro experto, para haber arrojado a alguien a este "
"mundo; como la primera maestra de la Nigromancia, siempre me llena de "
"orgullo ver a mis acólitos alcanzar tales alturas… Pero me desvío. Como "
"decía, deberías haber sido destruida por completo al entrar a este reino con "
"tu cuerpo físico, pero percibo que estás protegida por algún aura única…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:352
msgid ""
"It must be the power of the spirits of nature; Master Ankhmare did say my "
"body was infused with their energy..."
msgstr ""
"Debe ser el poder de los espíritus de la naturaleza; el maestro Ankhmare "
"dijo que mi cuerpo estaba infundido con su energía…"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:356
msgid ""
"Nevertheless, you should find a way back to the Living World as soon as you "
"can, for even this aura will not last for long here. This is the Dead World, "
"where the spirits of all living beings dwell; I know your spirits from our "
"little fight in Hiera'Duath, they are of a different essence, one that "
"doesn't belong here at all."
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, deberías encontrar una forma de regresar al Mundo de los Vivos "
"lo antes posible, pues incluso este aura no durará mucho aquí. Este es el "
"Mundo de los Muertos, donde moran los espíritus de todos los seres vivos; "
"conozco tus espíritus de nuestra pequeña pelea en Hiera’Duath, son de una "
"esencia diferente, una que no pertenece aquí en absoluto."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:360
msgid ""
"I see... So, will you help me get out of here, or will you happily float "
"away laughing at me?"
msgstr ""
"Ya veo… Entonces, ¿me ayudarás a salir de aquí, o te irás flotando feliz "
"riéndote de mí?"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:364
msgid ""
"(chuckles) The second option is quite tempting, after what you did to me. "
"Still... I think there is mutual profit to be had from helping each other."
msgstr ""
"(ríe) La segunda opción es bastante tentadora, después de lo que me hiciste. "
"Aun así… creo que hay beneficio mutuo en ayudarnos el uno al otro."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:368
msgid ""
"I'm not helping you out of this plane, you know. I'd rather take my chances "
"by myself."
msgstr ""
"No te ayudaré a salir de este plano, sabes. Prefiero correr mis riesgos sola."

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:372
msgid ""
"The choice is yours, girl... but if it comforts you, there is no way I can "
"escape this realm as I am right now, a soul without a physical body. Such is "
"a fundamental rule of existence, one even I cannot violate. As you're still "
"very much alive, you may yet leave this plane."
msgstr ""
"La elección es tuya, chica… pero si te consuela, no hay forma de que escape "
"de este reino tal como estoy ahora, un alma sin cuerpo físico. Tal es una "
"regla fundamental de la existencia, una que ni siquiera yo puedo violar. "
"Como sigues muy viva, aún puedes dejar este plano."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:376
msgid ""
"I do recall Olokun explaining the same once... Argh... Fine, have it your "
"way; there might not even be a world to protect you from unless I get out as "
"soon as I can. So, how do you propose we escape?"
msgstr ""
"Recuerdo que Olokun explicó lo mismo una vez… Argh… Está bien, hazlo a tu "
"manera; tal vez ni siquiera haya un mundo que proteger si no salgo lo antes "
"posible. Entonces, ¿cómo propones que escapemos?"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:380
msgid ""
"We'll need someone in the Living Realm to pull you through the barrier; and, "
"to reach out to someone in there, we'll have to find yet another realm: the "
"Akashic Plane, or, if you prefer, the Dreamland."
msgstr ""
"Necesitaremos a alguien en el Reino de los Vivos que te tire a través de la "
"barrera; y, para contactar a alguien allí, tendremos que encontrar otro "
"reino más: el Plano Akáshico, o, si prefieres, la Tierra de los Sueños."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:384
msgid "All right, I'll pretend that I understood everything..."
msgstr "Está bien, fingiré que entendí todo…"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:388
msgid ""
"(sigh) I'll try to enlighten your ignorant mind... Perhaps your rustic "
"culture has tales of deceased people visiting the living on their dreams?"
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) Intentaré iluminar tu mente ignorante… Tal vez tu cultura rústica "
"tenga cuentos de personas fallecidas visitando a los vivos en sus sueños?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:392
msgid "We're not rustic, but yes..."
msgstr "No somos rústicos, pero sí…"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:396
msgid ""
"Sometimes, that is all it is: a dream. But sometimes, it is the very soul of "
"the deceased you speak with. That is possible because both realms, Death and "
"Dream, are tied to one another, kept apart only by a veil which the "
"strongest souls may be able to cross. Staying in that realm for long is "
"dangerous, as souls are not meant to dwell in there; but you are no mere "
"soul."
msgstr ""
"A veces, eso es todo: un sueño. Pero a veces, es realmente el alma del "
"fallecido con quien hablas. Eso es posible porque ambos reinos, Muerte y "
"Sueño, están unidos entre sí, separados solo por un velo que las almas más "
"fuertes pueden cruzar. Permanecer en ese reino por mucho tiempo es "
"peligroso, ya que las almas no están destinadas a habitar allí; pero tú no "
"eres una simple alma."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:400
msgid "I get it, beings from one realm cannot survive for long in another one."
msgstr ""
"Entiendo, los seres de un reino no pueden sobrevivir mucho tiempo en otro."

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:404
msgid ""
"So you have some wit on you, after all... What I propose is this: together "
"we shall carve a path to the Veil of Dreams. I am... not as strong as I was, "
"so I cannot reach it by myself; you have that strength, but not the "
"knowledge of how to reach out across the Veil. I will help you do that, and "
"once you're gone I'll set myself to seeking some necromancer to tether me "
"back to the Living Realm. One day, we shall have a rematch... but not any "
"time soon."
msgstr ""
"Así que después de todo tienes algo de ingenio… Lo que propongo es esto: "
"juntos abriremos un camino hacia el Velo de los Sueños. Yo… no estoy tan "
"fuerte como antes, así que no puedo llegar sola; tú tienes esa fuerza, pero "
"no el conocimiento de cómo cruzar el Velo. Yo te ayudaré a hacerlo, y una "
"vez que te hayas ido me dedicaré a buscar algún nigromante que me ate de "
"nuevo al Reino de los Vivos. Algún día tendremos una revancha… pero no "
"pronto."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:408
msgid "Well, at least you're honest... Let's get going then."
msgstr "Bueno, al menos eres honesta… Pongámonos en marcha entonces."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:443
msgid "Whoa, what's with these flames?"
msgstr "¡Vaya, qué pasa con estas llamas?"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:447
msgid ""
"These are outbursts of soul essence accumulated in the soil; as you have "
"noticed, by stepping on them you may drain some of their power."
msgstr ""
"Estas son erupciones de esencia de alma acumulada en el suelo; como has "
"notado, al pisarlas puedes drenar algo de su poder."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:475
msgid ""
"I have another question: does the word 'Akashic' mean anything in particular?"
msgstr ""
"Tengo otra pregunta: ¿la palabra «Akáshico» significa algo en particular?"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:479
msgid ""
"In a tongue spoken long ago by the Asherah tribe of Arajunna, it meant "
"'memory'. Are you familiar with them?"
msgstr ""
"En una lengua hablada hace mucho por la tribu Asherah de Arajunna, "
"significaba «memoria». ¿Estás familiarizada con ellos?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:483
msgid ""
"A little; I had a... friend with a similar name, but she lived long after "
"these Asherah... Did they know these weird realms as well?"
msgstr ""
"Un poco; tuve una… amiga con un nombre similar, pero ella vivió mucho "
"después de estos Asherah… ¿Ellos también conocían estos reinos extraños?"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:487
msgid ""
"They were aware, yes. The very first human mage, and possibly the most "
"powerful of all, was one of them: An-Usrukhar. His was the wisdom that "
"established the very fundaments of the arcane lore that humankind has used "
"through the ages since."
msgstr ""
"Estaban al tanto, sí. El primer mago humano, y posiblemente el más poderoso "
"de todos, fue uno de ellos: An-Usrukhar. Su sabiduría estableció los "
"fundamentos mismos del saber arcano que la humanidad ha usado a lo largo de "
"las edades desde entonces."

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:511
msgid ""
"The Land of the Dead is full of wandering souls lately, I don't recall "
"meeting this one when I last crossed this region... but it is no threat to "
"us. Let us get rid of it presently and be on our way."
msgstr ""
"La Tierra de los Muertos está llena de almas errantes últimamente, no "
"recuerdo haber conocido a esta cuando crucé esta región por última vez… pero "
"no es una amenaza para nosotros. Deshagámonos de ella ahora y sigamos "
"nuestro camino."

#. [message], speaker=Addraryn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:515
msgid ""
"We don't need to fight, fellow lost soul; you may pass through, I won't "
"raise my blade against you... Unless you force my hand."
msgstr ""
"No necesitamos pelear, alma perdida compañera; puedes pasar, no levantaré mi "
"espada contra ti… A menos que me obligues."

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:519
msgid ""
"The time you've wasted with your useless words could have won you an escape "
"from our wrath, little soul. Now, embrace oblivion-"
msgstr ""
"El tiempo que perdiste con tus palabras inútiles podría haberte ganado una "
"escapatoria de nuestra ira, pequeña alma. Ahora, abraza el olvido—"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:523
msgid "Stop right there, Ashura, that soul isn't hostile, just leave it be."
msgstr "Para ahí, Ashura, esa alma no es hostil, solo déjala en paz."

#. [message], speaker=Addraryn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:527
msgid "And you... you're not a soul, you're... alive?!"
msgstr "Y tú… no eres un alma, estás… ¡¿viva?!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:531
msgid ""
"Yeah, well, I've been thrown here against my will and I'm trying to find my "
"way back to the Living World. You don't happen to know a way to the Veil of "
"Dreams, do you?"
msgstr ""
"Sí, bueno, fui arrojada aquí en contra de mi voluntad y estoy intentando "
"encontrar el camino de regreso al Mundo de los Vivos. No sabrás por "
"casualidad una forma al Velo de los Sueños, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:535
msgid "Yes, girl, do reveal our secrets to all..."
msgstr "Sí, chica, revela todos nuestros secretos…"

#. [message], speaker=Addraryn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:539
msgid ""
"I do not... But perhaps I could be of aid still. This realm is dangerous "
"even to one who belongs here; but a living person like you will attract "
"souls like a fire does moths, and not all will simply let you pass unharmed."
msgstr ""
"No lo sé… Pero tal vez aún pueda ser de ayuda. Este reino es peligroso "
"incluso para quien pertenece aquí; pero una persona viva como tú atraerá "
"almas como el fuego atrae a las polillas, y no todas te dejarán pasar sin "
"hacerte daño."

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:543
msgid ""
"And, naturally, by following us you expect to find a way back to the Living "
"World."
msgstr ""
"Y, naturalmente, siguiéndonos esperas encontrar una forma de regresar al "
"Mundo de los Vivos."

#. [message], speaker=Addraryn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:547
msgid ""
"I... I'll be honest, a part of me desires nothing more than to return: to "
"life, to my friends, to my wife... But I know I'm dead, and it's not natural "
"for me to walk the Living World again. I'm no necro'er, and I never will be. "
"But you're alive, and if I can help <i>you</i> return to your loved ones, "
"perhaps... Perhaps I can find peace at last."
msgstr ""
"Yo… seré honesto, una parte de mí no desea nada más que regresar: a la vida, "
"a mis amigos, a mi esposa… Pero sé que estoy muerto, y no es natural para mí "
"volver a caminar por el Mundo de los Vivos. No soy nigromante, y nunca lo "
"seré. Pero tú estás viva, y si puedo ayudarte <i>a ti</i> a regresar con tus "
"seres queridos, tal vez… tal vez pueda encontrar paz al fin."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:551
msgid ""
"Well, I won't say no to a local's offer of help! And don't look at me like "
"that, Ashura; I accepted <i>your</i> help, after all... Anyway, my name is "
"Tenma Yozora; who are... or <i>were</i>... you?"
msgstr ""
"Bueno, no diré que no a la oferta de ayuda de un local. Y no me mires así, "
"Ashura; después de todo acepté <i>tu</i> ayuda… De todos modos, mi nombre es "
"Tenma Yozora; ¿quién eres… o <i>fuiste</i>… tú?"

#. [message], speaker=Addraryn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:558
msgid ""
"(chuckles) I still have my memories, so I guess I'm still who I've always "
"been. You may call me Addraryn, pleased to meet you."
msgstr ""
"(ríe) Aún conservo mis recuerdos, así que supongo que sigo siendo quien "
"siempre he sido. Puedes llamarme Addraryn, encantado de conocerte."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:562
msgid ""
"Addraryn... Wait, you wouldn't happen to be Addraryn of Kerlath, would you? "
"The 'Wyvern of Wesnoth', the ancient hero who saved the empire from an "
"invasion?"
msgstr ""
"Addraryn… Espera, ¿no serás Addraryn de Kerlath, verdad? ¿El «Guiverno de "
"Wesnoth», el héroe antiguo que salvó al imperio de una invasión?"

#. [message], speaker=Addraryn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:566
msgid ""
"I... Yes, I was called that, but what I saved was the <i>kingdom</i> of "
"Wesnoth... and did you say 'ancient hero'?"
msgstr ""
"Yo… Sí, me llamaban así, pero lo que salvé fue el <i>reino</i> de Wesnoth… "
"¿y dijiste «héroe antiguo»?"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:570
msgid ""
"You should know, girl, that this is a timeless realm; aeons may pass in the "
"Living World, and the denizens of this world will never notice."
msgstr ""
"Deberías saber, chica, que este es un reino sin tiempo; eones pueden pasar "
"en el Mundo de los Vivos, y los habitantes de este mundo nunca lo notarán."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:574
msgid ""
"Ugh... I'm sorry, Addraryn, I should've been more tactful... Yes, it's been "
"centuries since your time: Wesnoth is now a mighty empire, and-"
msgstr ""
"Ugh… Lo siento, Addraryn, debí ser más delicada… Sí, han pasado siglos desde "
"tu época: Wesnoth ahora es un poderoso imperio, y—"

#. [message], speaker=Addraryn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:578
msgid ""
"Wait... please, I'd rather... This is too much to process, and I'll need my "
"full focus if I'm to be useful to you."
msgstr ""
"Espera… por favor, preferiría… Esto es demasiado para procesar, y necesitaré "
"toda mi concentración si voy a ser útil para ti."

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:582
msgid "At last, a pragmatic soul. Perhaps we will get along well, lost one."
msgstr "Al fin, un alma pragmática. Tal vez nos llevemos bien, perdido."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:586
msgid "All right..."
msgstr "Está bien…"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:604
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:920
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:999
msgid "Destruction of Addraryn"
msgstr "Destrucción de Addraryn"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:628
msgid ""
"Here we have the first obstacle in our little journey: the Wailing River, "
"the greatest of all rivers in the Land of the Dead..."
msgstr ""
"Aquí tenemos el primer obstáculo en nuestro pequeño viaje: el Río Llorón, el "
"mayor de todos los ríos en la Tierra de los Muertos…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:632
msgid "Wait, if this is a world of spirits, why does it have rivers?"
msgstr "Espera, si este es un mundo de espíritus, ¿por qué tiene ríos?"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:636
msgid ""
"(sigh) When I use words such as 'river' or 'valley' or 'sky' to describe "
"places, o ignorant fool, I'm simply using a language that one from the "
"Living World may understand. I call it the Wailing River, but it's nothing "
"more than a stream of 'soul essence', the matter of which souls are made of."
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) Cuando uso palabras como «río» o «valle» o «cielo» para describir "
"lugares, oh necia ignorante, simplemente estoy usando un lenguaje que "
"alguien del Mundo de los Vivos pueda entender. Lo llamo el Río Llorón, pero "
"no es más que un flujo de «esencia de alma», la materia de la que están "
"hechas las almas."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:640
msgid ""
"So this is where souls are born... Heh, the Hachiman Priestess would kill to "
"see this river..."
msgstr ""
"Entonces aquí es donde nacen las almas… Je, la sacerdotisa Hachiman mataría "
"por ver este río…"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:644
msgid ""
"This is not merely the birthplace of spirits, but the place where they are "
"cleansed and restored so that they may return to the Living World. Those "
"strong-willed and knowledgeable enough, however, may avoid this ignoble "
"fate, as do souls laden with regret."
msgstr ""
"Este no es solo el lugar de nacimiento de los espíritus, sino el lugar donde "
"son purificados y restaurados para que puedan regresar al Mundo de los "
"Vivos. Sin embargo, aquellos con suficiente voluntad y conocimiento pueden "
"evitar este destino innoble, al igual que las almas cargadas de "
"arrepentimiento."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:648
msgid ""
"It seems to flow from somewhere... unless it doesn't work like an actual "
"river?"
msgstr ""
"Parece que fluye desde algún lugar… ¿a menos que no funcione como un río "
"real?"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:652
msgid ""
"It doesn't, but your question is one I have already asked myself. In order "
"to answer it, I followed this river to its origin once; all I found there "
"was the carcass of some mystical creature unknown even to me. But this is of "
"no relevance to our current objective; what matters is how we'll cross this "
"river, as it will wipe out our minds and turn us into raw soul material "
"should we try to wade through. I know someone who succeeded; we must locate, "
"and quite possibly fight him in order to do the same..."
msgstr ""
"No lo hace, pero tu pregunta es una que ya me hice a mí misma. Para "
"responderla, seguí este río hasta su origen una vez; todo lo que encontré "
"allí fue el cadáver de alguna criatura mística desconocida incluso para mí. "
"Pero esto no tiene relevancia para nuestro objetivo actual; lo que importa "
"es cómo cruzaremos este río, ya que borrará nuestras mentes y nos convertirá "
"en materia prima de almas si intentamos vadearlo. Conozco a alguien que lo "
"logró; debemos localizarlo, y muy posiblemente pelear contra él para hacer "
"lo mismo…"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:694
msgid ""
"And I present you Aegaion, so-called emperor of some human empire called "
"Skiron..."
msgstr ""
"Y te presento a Aegaion, autoproclamado emperador de algún imperio humano "
"llamado Skiron…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:698
msgid ""
"I've heard of him! According to the Maat'Karians, he was a very powerful "
"dark mage..."
msgstr ""
"¡He oído de él! Según los maatkarianos, fue un nigromante muy poderoso…"

#. [message], speaker=Aegaion
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:702
msgid ""
"I warned you not to dare show up again in my domains, Ashura; do you really "
"wish to be part of my Soul Bridge this much?"
msgstr ""
"Te advertí que no te atrevieras a aparecer de nuevo en mis dominios, Ashura; "
"¿realmente deseas tanto formar parte de mi Puente de Almas?"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:706
msgid ""
"Of all souls, the ones I hate the most are those who insist on behaving like "
"they're still alive... You may have commanded respect in your little empire, "
"'Dark Saint', but here you're just another wandering soul. Still, you have "
"done a commendable deed by creating your Soul Bridge; for that, I shall "
"remember you after you are gone."
msgstr ""
"De todas las almas, las que más odio son aquellas que insisten en "
"comportarse como si aún estuvieran vivas… Pudiste haber comandado respeto en "
"tu pequeño imperio, «Santo Oscuro», pero aquí solo eres otra alma errante. "
"Aun así, has hecho una acción encomiable al crear tu Puente de Almas; por "
"eso te recordaré después de que te hayas ido."

#. [message], speaker=Aegaion
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:710
msgid ""
"Come then, Demon! I shall humiliate you with the very arts you pioneered!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ven entonces, Demonio! ¡Te humillaré con las mismas artes que tú iniciaste!"

#. [message], speaker=Aegaion
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:723
msgid "No! How... how can anyone be stronger than me in this world...?!"
msgstr "¡No! ¿Cómo… cómo puede alguien ser más fuerte que yo en este mundo…?!"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:727
msgid ""
"The dead need not learn what is not useful for them, Aegaion. All you need "
"is to join the bridge you have crafted; now and forevermore, all that you "
"were will be merely another stepping stone for lost souls seeking to cross "
"the Wailing River."
msgstr ""
"Los muertos no necesitan aprender lo que no les es útil, Aegaion. Todo lo "
"que necesitas es unirte al puente que has creado; ahora y para siempre, todo "
"lo que fuiste será tan solo otro peldaño para almas perdidas que buscan "
"cruzar el Río Llorón."

#. [message], speaker=Aegaion
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:731
msgid "NOOOOOOO!!!"
msgstr "¡¡¡NOOOOOOO!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:735
msgid "Now, for the bridge..."
msgstr "Ahora, por el puente…"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:782
msgid ""
"We now arrive at the Forest of Spirits; these, as you ought to have noticed, "
"are not real trees, but ramifications of the Wailing River which go "
"underground and which, after absorbing certain substances from this 'soil', "
"blossom into these tree-like structures. This is where new souls are truly "
"born. See those 'fruits' dangling from the 'branches'? Each of them is a new "
"soul; when they're 'ripe', they fall down and are taken by the wind to the "
"Living World."
msgstr ""
"Ahora llegamos al Bosque de los Espíritus; estos, como habrás notado, no son "
"árboles reales, sino ramificaciones del Río Llorón que se adentran bajo "
"tierra y que, después de absorber ciertas sustancias de este «suelo», "
"florecen en estas estructuras parecidas a árboles. Aquí es donde realmente "
"nacen las nuevas almas. ¿Ves esos «frutos» colgando de las «ramas»? Cada uno "
"de ellos es una nueva alma; cuando están «maduros», caen y son llevados por "
"el viento al Mundo de los Vivos."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:786
msgid "If this wind blows to the Living World, couldn't we use it to go there?"
msgstr ""
"Si este viento sopla hacia el Mundo de los Vivos, ¿no podríamos usarlo para "
"ir allí?"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:790
msgid ""
"(sigh) This is no actual wind, but an energy which flows between the various "
"planes of existence, stemming from a special dimension the Windsong called "
"the 'Raw'. To put it in a way that even your simple mind may fathom, the Raw "
"is a medium which binds all planes of existence together. Think of it as a "
"river that flows through mountains, washing various valleys which would "
"otherwise be inaccessible. As for your suggestion, it won't work, as souls "
"burdened by mind and memories are too heavy to be carried away by this "
"'wind'."
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) Esto no es un viento real, sino una energía que fluye entre los "
"diversos planos de existencia, proveniente de una dimensión especial que las "
"Hijas del Viento llamaron el «Crudo». Para decirlo de una forma que incluso "
"tu mente simple pueda comprender, el Crudo es un medio que une todos los "
"planos de existencia. Piensa en él como un río que fluye a través de "
"montañas, lavando diversos valles que de otra forma serían inaccesibles. En "
"cuanto a tu sugerencia, no funcionará, ya que las almas cargadas por mente y "
"recuerdos son demasiado pesadas para ser llevadas por este «viento»."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:814
msgid "Look, another lost soul!"
msgstr "¡Mira, otra alma perdida!"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:818
msgid "This one...!"
msgstr "¡Esta…!"

#. [message], speaker=Raihien
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:822
msgid ""
"You... You're the Demon of Hiera'Duath...! Could this be a path to "
"redemption...? Ready yourself, Demon, we shall sink into oblivion together!"
msgstr ""
"Tú… ¡Eres el Demonio de Hiera’Duath…! ¿Podría esto ser un camino a la "
"redención…? Prepárate, Demonio, ¡nos hundiremos en el olvido juntos!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:826
msgid "Well, if he's your enemy, he must've been a good guy..."
msgstr "Bueno, si es tu enemigo, debió haber sido un buen tipo…"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:830
msgid ""
"Good? <i>Good</i>?! Ha! That soul, ignorant girl, belonged to a man whose "
"deeds could have easily eclipsed my own, had he not been stopped. For he was "
"Angra-Mazda, a mage at the service of much greater, crueller being than I "
"ever was; a being <i>he</i> unleashed upon existence!"
msgstr ""
"¿Bueno? ¿<i>Bueno</i>?! ¡Ja! Esa alma, chica ignorante, perteneció a un "
"hombre cuyas acciones fácilmente podrían haber eclipsado las mías, si no lo "
"hubieran detenido. Porque él fue Angra-Mazda, un mago al servicio de un ser "
"mucho mayor y más cruel que yo jamás fui; ¡un ser que <i>él</i> desató sobre "
"la existencia!"

#. [message], speaker=Raihien
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:834
msgid ""
"And for that I shall endure an eternity of torment in this realm, never to "
"join the cycle of souls. Have you ever felt regret for your actions, Demon? "
"Have you ever sought redemption for the dark legacy you left?"
msgstr ""
"Y por eso soportaré una eternidad de tormento en este reino, nunca para "
"unirme al ciclo de las almas. ¿Alguna vez has sentido arrepentimiento por "
"tus acciones, Demonio? ¿Alguna vez has buscado redención por el oscuro "
"legado que dejaste?"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:838
msgid ""
"I have nothing to regret, Angra-Mazda. You would have brought ruin to all of "
"existence; I left a legacy of power and knowledge that to this day is "
"embraced by many!"
msgstr ""
"No tengo nada de qué arrepentirme, Angra-Mazda. Tú habrías traído la ruina a "
"toda la existencia; ¡yo dejé un legado de poder y conocimiento que hasta el "
"día de hoy es abrazado por muchos!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:842
msgid "Ahem! If I may have a word... Angra-Mazda, right?"
msgstr "¡Ejem! Si me permiten una palabra… Angra-Mazda, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Raihien
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:846
msgid ""
"You... You're a living soul... Have you come to this realm to release your "
"master, foul necromancer?"
msgstr ""
"Tú… Eres un alma viva… ¿Has venido a este reino a liberar a tu maestra, vil "
"nigromante?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:850
msgid ""
"Ew, no! I'm not her friend; in fact, I <i>fought</i> her a while ago. She's "
"the reason she's even here as a spirit, as I destroyed her physical body. Is "
"that not true, Ashura?"
msgstr ""
"¡Puaj, no! No soy su amiga; de hecho, la <i>luché</i> hace un tiempo. Ella "
"es la razón por la que siquiera está aquí como espíritu, ya que destruí su "
"cuerpo físico. ¿No es cierto, Ashura?"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:854
msgid "(glares)"
msgstr "(mira fijamente)"

#. [message], speaker=Raihien
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:858
msgid ""
"Then why do you walk by her side? In fact, how come you even stand here as a "
"living soul? I sense no Raw aura on you, so you can't be a traveller of the "
"Worlds' Weave..."
msgstr ""
"Entonces, ¿por qué caminas a su lado? De hecho, ¿cómo es que estás aquí como "
"un alma viva? No siento aura Cruda en ti, así que no puedes ser una viajera "
"del Tejido de los Mundos…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:862
msgid ""
"I was sent here against my will by a very powerful enemy, one who may be "
"about to unleash an even worse enemy upon the world. I need to return in "
"order to stop them; Ashura says I may be able to do so through Dreamland, "
"but I'll need help getting there... help such as yours, I mean."
msgstr ""
"Fui enviada aquí en contra de mi voluntad por un enemigo muy poderoso, uno "
"que quizá esté a punto de desatar un enemigo aún peor sobre el mundo. "
"Necesito regresar para detenerlos; Ashura dice que tal vez pueda hacerlo a "
"través de la Tierra de los Sueños, pero necesitaré ayuda para llegar allí… "
"ayuda como la tuya, quiero decir."

#. [message], speaker=Raihien
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:866
msgid ""
"So you claim, and yet, like I said, you walk by Ashura's side. At best, "
"you're naively being led to providing her a way out of this realm, so why "
"should I help you?"
msgstr ""
"Eso afirmas, y aun así, como dije, caminas al lado de Ashura. En el mejor de "
"los casos, ingenuamente estás siendo guiada para darle una salida de este "
"reino, entonces ¿por qué debería ayudarte?"

#. [message], speaker=Addraryn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:870
msgid ""
"Fellow soul, we don't know each other, but in this realm, where our souls "
"are bared, you can look into mine and see if there's ill intent in it. I see "
"none in Tenma's, and that's why I've decided to help her - even if it means "
"fighting by this necro'er's side. Are we going to let an innocent rot in "
"this dead world because of the company she's forced to keep?"
msgstr ""
"Alma compañera, no nos conocemos, pero en este reino, donde nuestras almas "
"están al descubierto, puedes mirar dentro de la mía y ver si hay mala "
"intención en ella. No veo ninguna en la de Tenma, y por eso he decidido "
"ayudarla —incluso si eso significa luchar al lado de esta nigromante. ¿Vamos "
"a dejar que una inocente se pudra en este mundo muerto por la compañía que "
"se ve obligada a mantener?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:874
msgid ""
"Please, Angra-Mazda, the enemy I'm fighting is much, much worse than Ashura. "
"If she escapes we can defeat her, like people did in the past; but only I "
"can defeat the enemy I speak of. For that enemy is the High Dragon of the "
"Sky, Svarballi, who has the power of the Ancient Ones themselves."
msgstr ""
"Por favor, Angra-Mazda, el enemigo contra el que lucho es mucho, mucho peor "
"que Ashura. Si ella escapa podemos derrotarla, como la gente hizo en el "
"pasado; pero solo yo puedo derrotar al enemigo del que hablo. Porque ese "
"enemigo es el Alto Dragón del Cielo, Svarballi, que tiene el poder de los "
"Antiguos mismos."

#. [message], speaker=Raihien
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:878
msgid ""
"Svarballi, I know his tale... The Warden of Irdya, the Jewel of Ananke's "
"creation, corrupted from his original purpose by his own sense of justice... "
"<i>That</i> is your enemy?"
msgstr ""
"Svarballi, conozco su historia… El Guardián de Irdya, la Joya de la creación "
"de Ananke, corrompido de su propósito original por su propio sentido de "
"justicia… ¿<i>Ese</i> es tu enemigo?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:882
msgid ""
"Yes. He was unleashed long ago; a woman called Maat managed to seal him "
"again, but from his new prison he's spent millennia scheming a way out - and "
"right now, in the Living World, the person who sent me here may be about to "
"help him achieve that."
msgstr ""
"Sí. Fue desatado hace mucho tiempo; una mujer llamada Maat logró sellarlo de "
"nuevo, pero desde su nueva prisión ha pasado milenios tramando una forma de "
"escapar —y justo ahora, en el Mundo de los Vivos, la persona que me envió "
"aquí podría estar a punto de ayudarlo a lograrlo."

#. [message], speaker=Raihien
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:886
msgid "Maat... Now that is another familiar name... Very well, girl..."
msgstr "Maat… Ahora ese es otro nombre familiar… Muy bien, chica…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:890
msgid "It's Tenma, Tenma Yozora."
msgstr "Es Tenma, Tenma Yozora."

#. [message], speaker=Raihien
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:894
msgid ""
"Tenma Yozora, I shall help you reach the Veil of Dreams. You'll need a more "
"reliable companion than Ashura the Demon, in any case."
msgstr ""
"Tenma Yozora, te ayudaré a llegar al Velo de los Sueños. De todos modos "
"necesitarás un compañero más confiable que Ashura la Demonio."

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:898
msgid ""
"I suppose his powers should be useful on the way ahead. A threat, at the "
"very least, he should not be; he can no longer be used as a portal by "
"goddesses of destruction, now can he?"
msgstr ""
"Supongo que sus poderes deberían ser útiles en el camino por delante. Una "
"amenaza, al menos, no debería ser; ya no puede ser usado como portal por "
"diosas de la destrucción, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:902
msgid "Let's... <i>try</i> not to fight, all right?"
msgstr "Intentemos… <i>intentemos</i> no pelear, ¿de acuerdo?"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:924
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1003
msgid "Destruction of Angra-Mazda"
msgstr "Destrucción de Angra-Mazda"

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:957
msgid ""
"And yet another lost soul seeks to perish by my blade... I thought that I "
"had concluded my judgement by now, but if the Gods are unsatisfied with me "
"still, then I shall send another into oblivion for them!"
msgstr ""
"Y otra alma perdida más busca perecer bajo mi espada… Pensé que ya había "
"concluido mi juicio, pero si los Dioses aún no están satisfechos conmigo, "
"¡entonces enviaré a otra al olvido por ellos!"

#. [message], speaker=Addraryn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:961
msgid "Watch out, Tenma, I don't think that one is willing to speak!"
msgstr "¡Cuidado, Tenma, no creo que ese quiera hablar!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:965
msgid ""
"Wait a minute, Addraryn, I think... This soul feels familiar... You, lost "
"soul, please do not attack us, we're not here to harm you! My name is Tenma "
"Yozora, I'm alive and I seek a way out of this world; what's your name?"
msgstr ""
"Espera un momento, Addraryn, creo que… Esta alma se siente familiar… Tú, "
"alma perdida, por favor no nos ataques, ¡no estamos aquí para hacerte daño! "
"Mi nombre es Tenma Yozora, estoy viva y busco una forma de salir de este "
"mundo; ¿cuál es tu nombre?"

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:969
msgid ""
"I... Alas, it's been so long since I was last asked such question, I don't "
"even remember who I am – or who I used to be... All I remember is the other "
"lost ones, those who sought to destroy me. But I cannot remember how long I "
"have fought; I can't even tell any more what, or who, I was fighting for..."
msgstr ""
"Yo… Ay, ha pasado tanto tiempo desde que me hicieron esa pregunta por última "
"vez, que ni siquiera recuerdo quién soy —o quién fui… Todo lo que recuerdo "
"son los otros perdidos, aquellos que buscaron destruirme. Pero no puedo "
"recordar cuánto tiempo he luchado; ni siquiera puedo decir ya por qué, o por "
"quién, estaba luchando…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:973
msgid ""
"Well, if fight is what you want, I can give you a good reason to! I'm "
"looking for a way out of this world, as I clearly don't belong here; I need "
"to go to the Veil of Dreams, but I could use whatever help I can get to "
"reach it. Why don't you follow us?"
msgstr ""
"Bueno, si lo que quieres es pelear, ¡puedo darte una buena razón! Estoy "
"buscando una forma de salir de este mundo, ya que claramente no pertenezco "
"aquí; necesito ir al Velo de los Sueños, pero podría usar cualquier ayuda "
"que pueda obtener para llegar. ¿Por qué no nos sigues?"

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:977
msgid ""
"You're on a fool's quest, girl; there is no way out of this Dead World... "
"But I have nothing to lose from following you; who knows, through your path "
"I may even find the promised eternal rest... *This girl, why does she feel "
"so familiar...?*"
msgstr ""
"Estás en una búsqueda de tontos, chica; no hay salida de este Mundo Muerto… "
"Pero no tengo nada que perder siguiéndote; quién sabe, a través de tu camino "
"tal vez incluso encuentre el descanso eterno prometido… *Esta chica, ¿por "
"qué se siente tan familiar…?*"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:981
msgid ""
"My, we have gathered quite the ragtag band of lost souls, haven't we? You... "
"did well, though. For the next stage of our journey is where danger truly "
"lies..."
msgstr ""
"Vaya, hemos reunido toda una banda heterogénea de almas perdidas, ¿no es "
"así? Aunque… lo hiciste bien. Porque la siguiente etapa de nuestro viaje es "
"donde realmente acecha el peligro…"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1007
msgid "Destruction of the Nameless"
msgstr "Destrucción del Sin Nombre"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1081
msgid ""
"Tell me, Tenma, do you believe that a life of evil earns you an eternity of "
"punishment? If you don't, cross the Hell's Maw with me and, at the end of "
"the journey, should you still endure, tell me if you still believe so..."
msgstr ""
"Dime, Tenma, ¿crees que una vida de maldad te gana una eternidad de castigo? "
"Si no lo crees, cruza la Boca del Infierno conmigo y, al final del viaje, si "
"aún resistes, dime si todavía lo crees…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1085
msgid ""
"This region feels different from the others we've been through; it feels "
"somewhat... overwhelming, as if the atmosphere of this world was heavier "
"here than anywhere else."
msgstr ""
"Esta región se siente diferente de las otras por las que hemos pasado; se "
"siente algo… abrumadora, como si la atmósfera de este mundo fuera más pesada "
"aquí que en cualquier otro lugar."

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1089
msgid ""
"I believe this region was once a nexus connecting this realm to another. The "
"lost souls must have sensed the same, for here they gather in hopes of "
"finding a way out. But that nexus has not existed since times immemorial; "
"the strongest souls thus enslaved those weaker than themselves, mustering "
"their forces in a vain attempt to reopen the nexus."
msgstr ""
"Creo que esta región fue alguna vez un nexo que conectaba este reino con "
"otro. Las almas perdidas debieron sentir lo mismo, pues aquí se reúnen con "
"la esperanza de encontrar una salida. Pero ese nexo no ha existido desde "
"tiempos inmemoriales; las almas más fuertes esclavizaron así a las más "
"débiles, reuniendo sus fuerzas en un vano intento de reabrir el nexo."

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1093
msgid ""
"You may think the enslaved souls are the ones who suffer the most, but I "
"disagree. It is not them who spend eternity driven by vain hope, slowly "
"losing it until the spark of their spirit is snuffed. By then, they have "
"become too strong to vanish into the Wailing River; but deprived of hope, "
"ambition, or anything that might drive them forward, they do nothing but "
"wander aimlessly for all eternity, neither returning to the cycle of souls "
"nor joining the Akashic Realm."
msgstr ""
"Puedes pensar que las almas esclavizadas son las que más sufren, pero no "
"estoy de acuerdo. No son ellas las que pasan la eternidad impulsadas por una "
"esperanza vana, perdiéndola lentamente hasta que la chispa de su espíritu se "
"apaga. Para entonces, se han vuelto demasiado fuertes para desvanecerse en "
"el Río Llorón; pero privadas de esperanza, ambición o cualquier cosa que las "
"impulse hacia adelante, no hacen más que vagar sin rumbo por toda la "
"eternidad, sin regresar al ciclo de las almas ni unirse al Reino Akáshico."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1097
msgid "I suppose this is where we should start being very careful, then?"
msgstr ""
"Supongo que aquí es donde deberíamos empezar a ser muy cuidadosos, ¿entonces?"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1101
msgid ""
"No, hopeless puppy, you should've started being careful the moment you "
"plunged into this world."
msgstr ""
"No, cachorro sin esperanza, debiste empezar a tener cuidado desde el momento "
"en que te sumergiste en este mundo."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1123
msgid "Would it be a bother if I asked you a question?"
msgstr "¿Sería una molestia si te hago una pregunta?"

#. [message], speaker=Raihien
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1127
msgid "You just did..."
msgstr "Acabas de hacerlo…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1131
msgid ""
"Anyway... You mentioned being familiar with the name 'Maat'. Could it be the "
"same Maat who was a Windsong Ascendant of Hiera'Shirsha?"
msgstr ""
"De todos modos… Mencionaste estar familiarizado con el nombre «Maat». "
"¿Podría ser la misma Maat que fue una Ascendente de las Hijas del Viento de "
"Hiera’Shirsha?"

#. [message], speaker=Raihien
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1135
msgid ""
"She was no Ascendant when I knew her, but there is only one Maat of "
"Hiera'Shirsha I've ever known. We... we were enemies. Ashura was not lying "
"when she claimed I was a danger to all of existence."
msgstr ""
"No era Ascendente cuando la conocí, pero solo hay una Maat de Hiera’Shirsha "
"que haya conocido. Nosotros… éramos enemigos. Ashura no mentía cuando afirmó "
"que yo era un peligro para toda la existencia."

#. [message], speaker=Raihien
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1142
msgid "Did <i>you</i> know Maat?"
msgstr "¿<i>Tú</i> conociste a Maat?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1146
msgid ""
"Not exactly. It might be difficult to believe, but I'm the reincarnation of "
"someone who lived thousands of years before my time..."
msgstr ""
"No exactamente. Puede ser difícil de creer, pero soy la reencarnación de "
"alguien que vivió miles de años antes de mi tiempo…"

#. [message], speaker=Raihien
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1150
msgid ""
"So you're a recurrence? An extremely rare phenomenon, but not unheard of. "
"Maat's own sister was one... sort of."
msgstr ""
"¿Entonces eres una recurrencia? Un fenómeno extremadamente raro, pero no "
"inaudito. La propia hermana de Maat fue una… más o menos."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1154
msgid ""
"Oh... well, in my previous life I was Maat's daughter. So in a way I did "
"know her."
msgstr ""
"Oh… bueno, en mi vida anterior fui la hija de Maat. Así que de alguna forma "
"sí la conocí."

#. [message], speaker=Raihien
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1158
msgid ""
"Interesting indeed; perhaps it is truly fate that made our paths cross... "
"Then I suppose your father was Abhai of Garet-Desh?"
msgstr ""
"Interesante en efecto; tal vez realmente sea el destino lo que hizo que "
"nuestros caminos se cruzaran… Entonces supongo que tu padre fue Abhai de "
"Garet-Desh."

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1162
msgid "*Abhai of Garet-Desh... why is that name so familiar?*"
msgstr "*Abhai de Garet-Desh… ¿por qué ese nombre me resulta tan familiar?*"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1166
msgid "No... I should've specified that I was her <i>adopted</i> daughter."
msgstr "No… Debí haber especificado que fui su hija <i>adoptiva</i>."

#. [message], speaker=Raihien
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1170
msgid ""
"If you saw her as your mother and she saw you as her daughter, you were as "
"true a family as any one bound by blood. "
msgstr ""
"Si la veías como tu madre y ella te veía como su hija, fueron tan familia "
"verdadera como cualquiera unida por sangre."

#. [message], speaker=Assix
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1185
msgid ""
"And sso more foolss have sstepped into my domain... Good, more sslavess for "
"my forcess... But one amongsst them...!"
msgstr ""
"Y así más tontos han pisado mi dominio… Bien, más esclavos para mis fuerzas… "
"¡Pero uno entre ellos…!"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1189
msgid "Seems like you've stumbled upon another old friend, girl."
msgstr "Parece que te has topado con otra vieja amiga, chica."

#. [message], speaker=Assix
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1193
msgid ""
"(enraged) Not even all of eternity would be enough to make me forget thiss "
"aura... Of all ssoulss, thiss wass the one I craved the mosst! Thank you, "
"Godss of Darknesss, for finally ssending her to me! You may have bessted me "
"in the Living World, Myra of Hiera'Shirsha, but you're in MY domain now!!!"
msgstr ""
"(enfurecido) Ni toda la eternidad sería suficiente para hacerme olvidar esta "
"aura… ¡De todas las almas, esta era la que más ansiaba! ¡Gracias, Dioses de "
"la Oscuridad, por finalmente enviármela! Pudiste haberme derrotado en el "
"Mundo de los Vivos, Myra de Hiera’Shirsha, ¡pero ahora estás en MI dominio!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1197
msgid ""
"I remember this one: the saurian who caused the death of one of Myra's best "
"friends... It does not matter what world we are, I'll never fail to destroy "
"you, Assix!"
msgstr ""
"Recuerdo a este: el saurio que causó la muerte de uno de los mejores amigos "
"de Myra… No importa en qué mundo estemos, nunca fallaré en destruirte, "
"¡Assix!"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1212
msgid "I knew that presence was familiar... It has been a while, Ravanal."
msgstr ""
"Sabía que esa presencia me resultaba familiar… Ha pasado un tiempo, Ravanal."

#. [message], speaker=Addraryn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1216
msgid "Ravanal? <i>Mal</i>-Ravanal, the Terror of the East?!"
msgstr "¿Ravanal? ¿<i>Mal</i>-Ravanal, el Terror del Este?!"

#. [message], speaker=Ravanal
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1220
msgid ""
"My, my, to receive a visit from Ashura herself, she who laid out the "
"foundations of the arts to which I've dedicated my life... But you seem a "
"bit... worn out, compared to the last time I saw you. Could it be that "
"you've been defeated in the Living World...?"
msgstr ""
"Vaya, vaya, recibir una visita de la propia Ashura, ella que estableció los "
"fundamentos de las artes a las que he dedicado mi vida… Pero pareces un "
"poco… desgastada, comparada con la última vez que te vi. ¿Podría ser que "
"hayas sido derrotada en el Mundo de los Vivos…?"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1224
msgid ""
"(stung) This is none of your concern, boy; have your souls step aside and "
"let me pass, I have better things to do than extinguish your petty minions!"
msgstr ""
"(picada) Esto no es de tu incumbencia, muchacho; haz que tus almas se "
"aparten y déjame pasar, tengo cosas mejores que hacer que extinguir a tus "
"insignificantes subordinados."

#. [message], speaker=Ravanal
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1228
msgid ""
"I don't think so, old master; I've always craved to have you beside me – "
"just imagine the empire we could create if we joined forces! In the past, "
"you have rejected my offer; now, if you refuse to join me, I'll make you "
"mine by force!"
msgstr ""
"No lo creo, vieja maestra; siempre he anhelado tenerte a mi lado —¡imagina "
"el imperio que podríamos crear si uniéramos fuerzas! En el pasado rechazaste "
"mi oferta; ahora, si te niegas a unirte a mí, ¡te haré mía por la fuerza!"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1243
msgid ""
"More souls arrive into my domains, and strong ones... You shall be part of "
"my army soon enough, wanderers; together we shall escape this prison and "
"conquer the Living World once again!"
msgstr ""
"Más almas llegan a mis dominios, y fuertes… Pronto serán parte de mi "
"ejército, errantes; ¡juntos escaparemos de esta prisión y conquistaremos el "
"Mundo de los Vivos una vez más!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1258
msgid ""
"*This feeling... It's just like when I found Assix and the nameless guy, but "
"why do I feel so... sad...?*"
msgstr ""
"*Esta sensación… Es justo como cuando encontré a Assix y al tipo sin nombre, "
"pero ¿por qué me siento tan… triste…?*"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1262
msgid "...Myra...?"
msgstr "…¿Myra…?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1266
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1254
msgid "!!!"
msgstr "!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1270
msgid ""
"...Myra, is that you...? Did you...! No, Myra would never get killed... "
"So... have you come for me, Myra?..."
msgstr ""
"…Myra, ¿eres tú…? ¿Tú…! No, Myra nunca sería asesinada… Entonces… ¿has "
"venido por mí, Myra?…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1274
msgid "(shocked) No... Why... what have you done to be in such place, Veela?!"
msgstr ""
"(impactada) No… ¿Por qué… qué hiciste para estar en un lugar así, Veela?!"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1278
msgid ""
"You... You feel like Myra, but you don't look like her... (suddenly enraged) "
"You imposter, I'll make you pay for posing up as her!!!"
msgstr ""
"Tú… Te sientes como Myra, pero no te ves como ella… (de repente enfurecida) "
"¡Impostora, haré que pagues por hacerte pasar por ella!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1282
msgid "(crying) Veela, I'm... I'm so-sorry, I never..."
msgstr "(llorando) Veela, yo… lo siento tanto, nunca…"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1286
msgid ""
"Girl, get a hold of yourself! That soul is blocking the way out of the "
"Hell's Maw, we need to destroy her in order to reach our goal!"
msgstr ""
"¡Chica, contrólate! Esa alma está bloqueando la salida de la Boca del "
"Infierno, ¡necesitamos destruirla para alcanzar nuestro objetivo!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1290
msgid ""
"Destroy her...?! (enraged) I'll destroy <i>you</i> if you dare lay a single "
"finger on Veela!!!"
msgstr ""
"¿¡Destruirla…?! (enfurecida) ¡Te destruiré <i>a ti</i> si te atreves a "
"ponerle un solo dedo encima a Veela!"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1294
msgid ""
"Listen, do you know why some souls wander aimlessly around this world "
"without ever finding peace? It's because some deep regret binds them so "
"strongly to their past lives, that it becomes engraved on their souls, "
"preventing them from peacefully separating from their minds and rejoining "
"the cycle of reincarnation. I don't know what happened between you and that "
"child, but I can see that she has some deep regret regarding you, so, if you "
"truly love her, you have a duty of helping her soul find peace!"
msgstr ""
"Escucha, ¿sabes por qué algunas almas vagan sin rumbo por este mundo sin "
"encontrar nunca paz? Es porque un profundo arrepentimiento las ata tan "
"fuertemente a sus vidas pasadas, que se graba en sus almas, impidiéndoles "
"separarse pacíficamente de sus mentes y reincorporarse al ciclo de "
"reencarnación. No sé qué pasó entre tú y esa niña, pero veo que tiene un "
"profundo arrepentimiento respecto a ti, así que, si realmente la amas, "
"tienes el deber de ayudar a su alma a encontrar paz."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1301
msgid ""
"I... I understand. If that is so, then putting her to rest is the least I "
"can do..."
msgstr ""
"Yo… entiendo. Si es así, entonces dejarla descansar es lo mínimo que puedo "
"hacer…"

#. [message], speaker=Addraryn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1313
msgid "Finally, he who brought Wesnoth so much suffering is gone for good."
msgstr ""
"Por fin, el que trajo tanto sufrimiento a Wesnoth se ha ido para siempre."

#. [message], speaker=Ravanal
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1317
msgid "Defeated... by a puny Wesnothian... in my own domain...?!"
msgstr "Derrotado… ¿por un débil wesnothiano… en mi propio dominio…?"

#. [message], speaker=Jevyan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1334
msgid ""
"Once again I fail before reaching my goals... Curses upon you, strangers..."
msgstr ""
"Una vez más fallo antes de alcanzar mis objetivos… Malditos sean ustedes, "
"extraños…"

#. [message], speaker=Assix
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1352
msgid ""
"Curssess upon curssess upon you, Myra of Hiera'Shirsha! I hope all of your "
"friends die a horrible, gory death!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldiciones sobre maldiciones sobre ti, Myra de Hiera’Shirsha! ¡Espero que "
"todos tus amigos mueran de una muerte horrible y sangrienta!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1371
msgid ""
"Weird... the fortress where he was standing changed shape after his "
"destruction."
msgstr ""
"Qué raro… la fortaleza donde estaba parado cambió de forma después de su "
"destrucción."

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1375
msgid ""
"This 'fortress', as you call it, is merely a manifestation of Aegaion's will "
"and power. With him gone, so will this manifestation begin to crumble."
msgstr ""
"Esta «fortaleza», como la llamas, no es más que una manifestación de la "
"voluntad y el poder de Aegaion. Con él desaparecido, esta manifestación "
"también comenzará a desmoronarse."

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1388
msgid "I... can't... fade away now, I..."
msgstr "Yo… no puedo… desvanecerme ahora, yo…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1392
msgid ""
"Veela, please, don't do that to yourself! What happened to that kind, "
"cheerful, loving girl that condemned her to such fate?"
msgstr ""
"Veela, por favor, ¡no te hagas esto! ¿Qué le pasó a esa chica amable, alegre "
"y amorosa que la condenó a tal destino?"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1396
msgid "Myra... I have to... make sure... she has survived... the war..."
msgstr "Myra… Tengo que… asegurarme… de que sobrevivió… a la guerra…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1400
msgid "You were so worried about Myra that you couldn't even rest in peace..."
msgstr ""
"Estabas tan preocupada por Myra que ni siquiera pudiste descansar en paz…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1407
msgid ""
"(smiling tearfully) If that's so, then I have good news, Veela. Myra did "
"survive the war, together with Jevyan, Alenya, Dvalin and Ravyan; she took "
"the surviving Windsong, and even some Aragwaithi, to a continent beyond the "
"ocean, safe from the dragons' threat, and there she founded a great city "
"which survives till this day. And you, Veela, helped make it possible, for "
"you saved her that day – better, you saved me..."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo entre lágrimas) Si es así, entonces tengo buenas noticias, Veela. "
"Myra sí sobrevivió a la guerra, junto con Jevyan, Alenya, Dvalin y Ravyan; "
"llevó a las Hijas del Viento sobrevivientes, e incluso a algunos aragwaithi, "
"a un continente más allá del océano, a salvo de la amenaza de los dragones, "
"y allí fundó una gran ciudad que sobrevive hasta el día de hoy. Y tú, Veela, "
"ayudaste a hacer eso posible, porque la salvaste ese día —mejor dicho, me "
"salvaste a mí…"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1411
msgid "W-what do you mean...?"
msgstr "¿Q-qué quieres decir…?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1415
msgid ""
"Now I'm Tenma Yozora, but in a past life, I was your friend, the one whom "
"you met at Hashira's Valley, whom you admired so much, who shunned you at "
"first, but who, in the end, loved you as a sister... And who owes everything "
"that she had – her friends, her family, her people – to you..."
msgstr ""
"Ahora soy Tenma Yozora, pero en una vida pasada fui tu amiga, la que "
"conociste en el Valle de Hashira, a quien admirabas tanto, que al principio "
"te rechazó, pero que al final te amó como a una hermana… Y quien le debe "
"todo lo que tuvo —sus amigos, su familia, su pueblo— a ti…"

#. [message], speaker=Veela
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1419
msgid ""
"(shocked) M-Myra...! (crying in happiness) I'm... so glad... that you were "
"well, after all... I just wish that... I could have seen your family and "
"everyone else..."
msgstr ""
"(impactada) ¡M-Myra…! (llorando de felicidad) Estoy… tan contenta… de que al "
"final estuvieras bien… Solo desearía… haber podido ver a tu familia y a "
"todos los demás…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1423
msgid ""
"(crying) I wish too, my friend... Now, please, rest in peace; you deserve "
"it..."
msgstr ""
"(llorando) Yo también lo deseo, amiga mía… Ahora, por favor, descansa en "
"paz; te lo mereces…"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1445
msgid ""
"When you're ready, we shall proceed into the Meadows of Memory; that will be "
"the last stage of our journey towards the Veil of Dreams."
msgstr ""
"Cuando estés lista, avanzaremos hacia los Prados de la Memoria; esa será la "
"última etapa de nuestro viaje hacia el Velo de los Sueños."

#. [message], speaker=Raihien
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1449
msgid ""
"Regret is a powerful, terrible force. Weep for meeting a beloved friend in "
"such state, but be happy that you could at least help her overcome her "
"regret; rare are the lost souls that encounter such peace."
msgstr ""
"El arrepentimiento es una fuerza poderosa y terrible. Llora por encontrarte "
"con una amiga querida en tal estado, pero alégrate de que al menos pudiste "
"ayudarla a superar su arrepentimiento; raras son las almas perdidas que "
"encuentran tal paz."

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1453
msgid ""
"We should all be so lucky... *Somehow, this friend of hers has made me "
"remember a little more about my own past; could I have known her too...?*"
msgstr ""
"Todos deberíamos tener tanta suerte… *De alguna forma, esta amiga suya me ha "
"hecho recordar un poco más de mi propio pasado; ¿podría haberla conocido "
"también…?*"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1476
msgid ""
"At long last, we've reached the borderland between the realms of Death and "
"of Dreams; these flower-like structures you see, blanketing these the "
"'meadows', in fact are memory fragments left by lost souls across the ages. "
"The next flowers shall bloom presently, after you fall...!"
msgstr ""
"Por fin hemos llegado a la frontera entre los reinos de la Muerte y de los "
"Sueños; estas estructuras parecidas a flores que ves, cubriendo estos "
"«prados», en realidad son fragmentos de memoria dejados por almas perdidas a "
"lo largo de las edades. ¡Las próximas flores florecerán en breve, después de "
"que caigan…!"

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1512
msgid "(in pain) I knew... you couldn't be trusted..."
msgstr "(con dolor) Lo sabía… no se podía confiar en ti…"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1516
msgid ""
"Ah, you had to get in the way, hadn't you... How ironic that I was so "
"concerned about the fool priest and the knight in shining armour, yet it was "
"you, <i>Prince Varthan</i>, who once rivalled Myra of Hiera'Shirsha, who "
"became her shield!"
msgstr ""
"Ah, tenías que interponerte, ¿verdad…? Qué irónico que estuviera tan "
"preocupada por el estúpido sacerdote y el caballero de brillante armadura, y "
"sin embargo fuiste tú, <i>príncipe Varthan</i>, quien una vez rivalizó con "
"Myra de Hiera’Shirsha, ¡quien se convirtió en su escudo!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1520
msgid "Varthan? Then, you're..."
msgstr "¿Varthan? Entonces, tú eres…"

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1527
msgid ""
"<i>King</i> Varthan of Garet-Desh, Exiled High King of the Aragwaithi, "
"killed in combat against dragons in the Heart Mountains while fighting in "
"defence of my people! Angra-Mazda is right; regret is a powerful, terrible "
"force, and mine is dying before making sure my people was safe. Were it not "
"for you, Myra, I might have been reduced to the same flower shards we now "
"tread upon – or, worse still, to an ignoble slave in the Hell's Maw."
msgstr ""
"<i>Rey</i> Varthan de Garet-Desh, Rey Supremo Exiliado de los Aragwaithi, "
"¡muerto en combate contra dragones en las Montañas del Corazón mientras "
"luchaba en defensa de mi pueblo! Angra-Mazda tiene razón; el arrepentimiento "
"es una fuerza poderosa y terrible, y el mío es morir antes de asegurarme de "
"que mi pueblo estuviera a salvo. De no ser por ti, Myra, podría haber sido "
"reducido a los mismos fragmentos de flores que ahora pisamos —o, peor aún, a "
"un esclavo innoble en la Boca del Infierno."

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1531
msgid ""
"So you've recovered your memory – but what is that going to avail you? Once "
"I destroy you, your memories will blanket these meadows just as you feared "
"they would!"
msgstr ""
"Así que has recuperado tu memoria —pero ¿de qué te va a servir? ¡Una vez que "
"te destruya, tus recuerdos cubrirán estos prados tal como temías que lo "
"harían!"

#. [message], speaker=Addraryn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1535
msgid ""
"Recovering his identity will make him stronger, and his strength will be "
"joined by ours - while you, necro'er, stands alone!"
msgstr ""
"Recuperar su identidad lo hará más fuerte, y su fuerza se unirá a la nuestra "
"—¡mientras tú, nigromante, estás sola!"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1539
msgid ""
"You're right, peasant, I stand alone... Alone as the ultimate master of "
"death, standing on the realm of Death itself! What do <i>you</i> have that "
"could possibly challenge me?"
msgstr ""
"Tienes razón, campesino, estoy sola… Sola como la maestra suprema de la "
"muerte, ¡de pie en el reino de la Muerte misma! ¿Qué tienen <i>ustedes</i> "
"que pueda posiblemente desafiarme?"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1543
msgid ""
"They have each other, Ashura of Hiera'Duath... You may underestimate such "
"bonds, but it is them that push people to achieve the impossible, and them "
"that keep people connected through Time and Distance..."
msgstr ""
"Tienen el uno al otro, Ashura de Hiera’Duath… Puedes subestimar tales lazos, "
"pero son ellos los que empujan a las personas a lograr lo imposible, y son "
"ellos los que mantienen a las personas conectadas a través del Tiempo y la "
"Distancia…"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1547
msgid "This presence...!"
msgstr "¡Esta presencia…!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1551
msgid "No... There's more than one!"
msgstr "No… ¡Hay más de una!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1569
msgid "Mother...!"
msgstr "¡Madre…!"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1573
msgid "(smiling) Long time no see, my dear."
msgstr "(sonriendo) Hace mucho que no nos vemos, querida."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1577
msgid "And you too, Akhen...!"
msgstr "¡Y tú también, Akhen…!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1581
msgid ""
"You've once saved me when everything seemed lost, grandma, now it's my turn "
"to return the favour!"
msgstr ""
"Una vez me salvaste cuando todo parecía perdido, abuela, ¡ahora me toca a mí "
"devolverte el favor!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1585
msgid "But... Oh, no, don't tell me, you too became lost...?"
msgstr "Pero… Oh, no, no me digas, ¿tú también te perdiste…?"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1589
msgid ""
"Not lost, no. We were both too worried about you to simply move on, so we "
"lingered elsewhere... But there'll be time to talk later; the enemy ahead is "
"dangerous, and we shall need our best if we hope to win... Yours too, "
"Raihien."
msgstr ""
"No perdidos, no. Ambos estábamos demasiado preocupados por ti como para "
"simplemente seguir adelante, así que nos quedamos en otro lugar… Pero habrá "
"tiempo para hablar después; el enemigo que está adelante es peligroso, y "
"necesitaremos lo mejor de nosotros si esperamos ganar… La tuya también, "
"Raihien."

#. [message], speaker=Raihien
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1593
msgid ""
"I am, now and forever, Angra-Mazda - just as you've always known me as, "
"Maat. That name you uttered is one I've long lost the right to use."
msgstr ""
"Soy, ahora y para siempre, Angra-Mazda —tal como siempre me has conocido, "
"Maat. Ese nombre que pronunciaste es uno al que hace mucho perdí el derecho "
"a usar."

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1597
msgid ""
"That name was given you by a mother who loved you, Raihien - and who loved "
"you till the end. Let ancient deeds and resentments rest; it's time you "
"found peace and joined the cycle of souls."
msgstr ""
"Ese nombre te lo dio una madre que te amaba, Raihien —y que te amó hasta el "
"final. Deja que las antiguas acciones y resentimientos descansen; es hora de "
"que encuentres paz y te unas al ciclo de las almas."

#. [message], speaker=Raihien
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1607
msgid ""
"So be it... But not before I help your daughter return to the Living Realm."
msgstr ""
"Que así sea… Pero no antes de ayudar a tu hija a regresar al Reino de los "
"Vivos."

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1611
msgid ""
"Useless, meaningless pledges. I shall shatter your bonds and destroy you, "
"and then I shall tear the Veil of Dreams apart and conquer the Living World "
"forevermore!"
msgstr ""
"Promesas inútiles y sin sentido. ¡Romperé sus lazos y los destruiré, y luego "
"desgarraré el Velo de los Sueños y conquistaré el Mundo de los Vivos para "
"siempre!"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1633
msgid "Destruction of Maat"
msgstr "Destrucción de Maat"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1637
msgid "Destruction of Akhen"
msgstr "Destrucción de Akhen"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1662
msgid ""
"NO...!!! I am Ashura, Final Ascendant of the Windsong, I have walked the "
"ages and the realms... Only to fade into oblivion... like this...?"
msgstr ""
"¡NO…! Soy Ashura, Ascendente Final de las Hijas del Viento, he caminado por "
"las edades y los reinos… ¿Solo para desvanecerme en el olvido… así…?"

#. [message], speaker=Ashura
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1668
msgid ""
"NO...!!! I fade into oblivion, girl, but your fate is far worse, as you'll "
"wander through this realm and slowly disintegrate into oblivion too!"
msgstr ""
"¡NO…! Me desvanezco en el olvido, chica, pero tu destino es mucho peor, pues "
"vagarás por este reino y lentamente te desintegrarás en el olvido también."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1672
msgid ""
"She was disgusting, but without her guidance I really won't be able to "
"return to the Living World!"
msgstr ""
"Ella era repugnante, pero sin su guía realmente no podré regresar al Mundo "
"de los Vivos."

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1697
msgid ""
"At long last, she who was the grimmest stain in the History of the Windsong "
"is gone for good..."
msgstr ""
"Por fin, ella que fue la mancha más sombría en la Historia de las Hijas del "
"Viento se ha ido para siempre…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1701
msgid ""
"Mother, Akhen, I can't believe you're really here... But how did you find "
"me? I crossed the whole Land of the Dead and couldn't even sense your "
"presence..."
msgstr ""
"Madre, Akhen, no puedo creer que estén realmente aquí… Pero ¿cómo me "
"encontraron? Crucé toda la Tierra de los Muertos y ni siquiera pude sentir "
"su presencia…"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1705
msgid ""
"We were never in this realm, grandma, but in the Dreamland. Perhaps Lady "
"Maat can explain everything better than I?"
msgstr ""
"Nunca estuvimos en este reino, abuela, sino en la Tierra de los Sueños. Tal "
"vez la dama Maat pueda explicarlo todo mejor que yo."

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1709
msgid ""
"My dear, you've certainly asked yourself more than once how I managed to "
"lock Svarballi inside that jewel, haven't you?"
msgstr ""
"Querida, seguro que te has preguntado más de una vez cómo logré encerrar a "
"Svarballi dentro de esa joya, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1713
msgid "Yes, of course I have."
msgstr "Sí, por supuesto que sí."

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1717
msgid ""
"I knew I couldn't destroy him, and I knew that no earthly cell could contain "
"him; so I opened a portal through the Raw, reaching for the Land of the "
"Dead. However, I quickly realised what a foolish mistake it would be, to "
"leave Svarballi where Ashura could find him. So, I decided to leave him – as "
"well as the three dragons who fought along with him – in a plane where he "
"would be completely isolated from all other realms..."
msgstr ""
"Sabía que no podía destruirlo, y sabía que ninguna celda terrenal podía "
"contenerlo; así que abrí un portal a través del Crudo, llegando a la Tierra "
"de los Muertos. Sin embargo, rápidamente me di cuenta de qué error tan "
"estúpido sería dejar a Svarballi donde Ashura pudiera encontrarlo. Así que "
"decidí dejarlo —así como a los tres dragones que lucharon junto a él— en un "
"plano donde estaría completamente aislado de todos los demás reinos…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1721
msgid "The Dreamland..."
msgstr "La Tierra de los Sueños…"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1725
msgid ""
"Exactly. The Dreamland is a realm which you may enter, but which you can't "
"possibly leave once you enter it completely – that is, by both mind and "
"soul. That's one reason so many ancient Ascendants disappeared and were "
"never heard of again."
msgstr ""
"Exacto. La Tierra de los Sueños es un reino al que puedes entrar, pero del "
"que no puedes salir una vez que entras completamente —es decir, con mente y "
"alma. Esa es una de las razones por las que tantos Ascendentes antiguos "
"desaparecieron y nunca más se supo de ellos."

#. [message], speaker=Raihien
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1729
msgid ""
"The way you used yourself as a gateway for others... This is very akin to "
"what Kaliyuga did to me - only she used my soul, and its connection to "
"herself, as a gateway to enter Irdya."
msgstr ""
"La forma en que te usaste a ti misma como puerta para otros… Esto es muy "
"parecido a lo que Kaliyuga me hizo —solo que ella usó mi alma, y su conexión "
"consigo misma, como puerta para entrar en Irdya."

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1733
msgid ""
"And it was the memory of what she did to you, Raihien, that made me realise "
"that, by sending Svarballi and the dragons there, I had opened a huge tunnel "
"through the Raw, one which I wouldn't be able to seal without letting them "
"escape again. So I used the essence of my soul as a 'gate' to keep it "
"closed; as I did that, this essence materialised into a crystal. "
"Unfortunately, though I could block Svarballi himself, I was unable to block "
"all of his power, which could thus be channelled out of the jewel."
msgstr ""
"Y fue el recuerdo de lo que ella te hizo, Raihien, lo que me hizo darme "
"cuenta de que, al enviar a Svarballi y a los dragones allí, había abierto un "
"enorme túnel a través del Crudo, uno que no podría sellar sin dejarlos "
"escapar de nuevo. Así que usé la esencia de mi alma como «puerta» para "
"mantenerlo cerrado; al hacerlo, esa esencia se materializó en un cristal. "
"Desafortunadamente, aunque pude bloquear al propio Svarballi, no pude "
"bloquear todo su poder, que así pudo ser canalizado fuera de la joya."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1737
msgid ""
"I see... But, if your soul is blocking that tunnel, why are you here? Also, "
"how did that dark mage, Ayraton, manage to separate the souls of the Fire "
"Dragons from Svarballi's?"
msgstr ""
"Ya veo… Pero, si tu alma está bloqueando ese túnel, ¿por qué estás aquí? "
"Además, ¿cómo logró ese mago oscuro, Ayraton, separar las almas de los "
"Dragones de Fuego de las de Svarballi?"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1741
msgid ""
"He understood how Maat had created the Sky Soul, and then, with the aid of "
"the Ascendant Hashira and using a Windsong with strong Raw affinity as "
"vessel, he made another tunnel through the Raw and let the Fire Dragons' "
"souls cross it. But that was a trick: before the dragons could escape, he "
"killed the apprentice Ascendant, thus trapping them in the tunnel, and then "
"he condensed her soul into that which became the Ruby of Fire."
msgstr ""
"Él entendió cómo Maat había creado el Alma del Cielo, y luego, con la ayuda "
"de la Ascendente Hashira y usando una Hija del Viento con fuerte afinidad al "
"Crudo como recipiente, hizo otro túnel a través del Crudo y dejó que las "
"almas de los Dragones de Fuego lo cruzaran. Pero fue un engaño: antes de que "
"los dragones pudieran escapar, mató a la aprendiz Ascendente, atrapándolos "
"así en el túnel, y luego condensó su alma en lo que se convirtió en el Rubí "
"de Fuego."

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1745
msgid ""
"As for your other question... Well, as you may have guessed already, by "
"essentially turning myself into a gate to the Dreamland passage, my soul "
"remained bound to it. My mind should've been gone, but it was saved by the "
"very Dreamland's guardian whom I've just mentioned. Akhen, by his turn, was "
"allowed into the Dreamland because he had already been there once..."
msgstr ""
"En cuanto a tu otra pregunta... Bueno, como tal vez ya habrás adivinado, al "
"convertirme esencialmente en una puerta hacia el pasaje de la Tierra de los "
"Sueños, mi alma quedó atada a ella. Mi mente debió haber desaparecido, pero "
"fue salvada por el mismo guardián de la Tierra de los Sueños que acabo de "
"mencionar. Akhen, por su parte, fue permitido entrar en la Tierra de los "
"Sueños porque ya había estado allí una vez..."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1749
msgid "And should I know who this guardian is...?"
msgstr "¿Y debería saber quién es este guardián…?"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1753
msgid ""
"This brings us to the other reason we've come here. The guardian seems to be "
"expecting you; he never told us why, so you must find out by yourself."
msgstr ""
"Esto nos lleva a la otra razón por la que hemos venido aquí. El guardián "
"parece estar esperándote; nunca nos dijo por qué, así que debes descubrirlo "
"por ti misma."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1757
msgid ""
"Don't worry, grandma, you can trust him; if he wished you any harm, he would "
"have moved against you already."
msgstr ""
"No te preocupes, abuela, puedes confiar en él; si quisiera hacerte daño, ya "
"habría actuado en tu contra."

#. [message], speaker=Addraryn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1761
msgid ""
"Then you must hurry and meet him - and so this is where our paths diverge..."
msgstr ""
"Entonces debes apresurarte y encontrarlo —y así es donde nuestros caminos se "
"separan"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1765
msgid ""
"Addraryn, Raihien, Varthan, I would never have made it this far without you. "
"I know you have your own burdens and regrets, but I hope it helps a little "
"to know that I'll always remember you as companions..."
msgstr ""
"Addraryn, Raihien, Varthan, nunca habría llegado tan lejos sin ustedes. Sé "
"que tienen sus propias cargas y arrepentimientos, pero espero que les ayude "
"un poco saber que siempre los recordaré como compañeros…"

#. [message], speaker=Raihien
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1769
msgid ""
"Don't underestimate yourself, Tenma. I have made countless mistakes and "
"brought unspeakable suffering to many; but now I can say I helped the one "
"who will stop the last inheritor of Ananke's destructive legacy. For the "
"first time since I've arrived here... I feel no burden. Who knows, perhaps "
"I'm finally ready to join the cycle of souls..."
msgstr ""
"No te subestimes, Tenma. He cometido innumerables errores y he causado "
"sufrimiento indecible a muchos; pero ahora puedo decir que ayudé a quien "
"detendrá al último heredero del legado destructivo de Ananke. Por primera "
"vez desde que llegué aquí… no siento ninguna carga. Quién sabe, tal vez por "
"fin estoy listo para unirme al ciclo de las almas…"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1773
msgid ""
"I wish you to know this, Raihien: your ashes were spread on your native "
"Riverlands, along with those of Raika. It... seemed fitting, to me, to leave "
"you both to rest where you once were so happy."
msgstr ""
"Quiero que sepas esto, Raihien: tus cenizas fueron esparcidas en tus Tierras "
"Fluviales nativas, junto con las de Raika. Me pareció… apropiado dejarte "
"descansar a ambos donde una vez fueron tan felices."

#. [message], speaker=Raihien
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1777
msgid ""
"Is that so...? Then you've done me a greater kindness than I deserved. Thank "
"you, from the bottom of my soul, Maat of Hiera'Shirsha..."
msgstr ""
"¿Es así…? Entonces me has hecho una bondad mayor de la que merecía. Gracias, "
"desde lo más profundo de mi alma, Maat de Hiera’Shirsha"

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1787
msgid ""
"There is but one thing I wish to ask, Tenma... I believe aeons have passed "
"since my time, but do you know anything about the fate of the Aragwaithi?"
msgstr ""
"Hay una sola cosa que deseo preguntarte, Tenma… Creo que han pasado eones "
"desde mi época, pero ¿sabes algo sobre el destino de los aragwaithi?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1791
msgid ""
"In the Living World, more than four thousand years have passed since your "
"time, and just months ago I fought alongside them myself; they seemed to be "
"quite prosperous."
msgstr ""
"En el Mundo de los Vivos han pasado más de cuatro mil años desde tu época, y "
"hace apenas meses luché junto a ellos yo misma; parecían bastante prósperos."

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1795
msgid ""
"(smiling) So she managed to lead them without me... Thank you so much, "
"Myra... I mean, Tenma Yozora. I may now go in peace to my father's side..."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Así que logró guiarlos sin mí… Muchas gracias, Myra… quiero "
"decir, Tenma Yozora. Ahora puedo ir en paz al lado de mi padre"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1805
msgid ""
"And what about you, Addraryn? There's no battle ahead any more, you can "
"afford to get distracted a little..."
msgstr ""
"Y tú, Addraryn, ¿qué hay de ti? Ya no hay batalla por delante, puedes "
"permitirte distraerte un poco"

#. [message], speaker=Addraryn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1809
msgid ""
"(chuckles) True, but... I'm afraid the answer to my questions may not bring "
"me any peace, Tenma. You say Wesnoth is now an empire, and empires conquer, "
"empires tyrannise, empires corrupt. Was that what I fought for? Was that my "
"legacy? And if that's so, then what happened to the people I cared about? We "
"weren't great heroes, or powerful kings, or mages with powers beyond "
"comprehension; we were just a band of soldiers and outlaws..."
msgstr ""
"(ríe) Cierto, pero… me temo que las respuestas a mis preguntas podrían no "
"traerme paz, Tenma. Dices que Wesnoth ahora es un imperio, y los imperios "
"conquistan, los imperios tiranizan, los imperios corrompen. ¿Eso fue por lo "
"que luché? ¿Ese fue mi legado? Y si es así, ¿qué pasó con la gente que me "
"importaba? No éramos grandes héroes, ni reyes poderosos, ni magos con "
"poderes más allá de la comprensión; solo éramos una banda de soldados y "
"forajidos…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1813
msgid ""
"Do you want to know your legacy, Wyvern? Then I'll tell you. Your legacy "
"lives on still, using her power and wisdom to fight for those who cannot "
"defend themselves. Her name is Valerya; she's a pretty good friend of mine, "
"and an amazingly powerful mage. So powerful, in fact, she's been alive - "
"really alive, and not as a necromancer - for seven centuries, since she was "
"born in a small Northern town called Zlexen, where she was raised by her "
"mother Elyniver."
msgstr ""
"¿Quieres saber cuál es tu legado, Guiverno? Entonces te lo diré. Tu legado "
"sigue vivo, usando su poder y sabiduría para luchar por aquellos que no "
"pueden defenderse. Su nombre es Valerya; es una muy buena amiga mía, y una "
"maga increíblemente poderosa. Tan poderosa, de hecho, que ha estado viva —"
"realmente viva, y no como nigromante— durante siete siglos, desde que nació "
"en un pequeño pueblo del norte llamado Zlexen, donde fue criada por su madre "
"Elyniver."

#. [message], speaker=Addraryn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1817
msgid "Elyniver...?"
msgstr "¿Elyniver…?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1821
msgid ""
"She never knew her dad, mind you, since he died before she was born; but I "
"just know he was an even bigger hero to her than he was to everyone else."
msgstr ""
"Nunca conoció a su papá, ten en cuenta, ya que murió antes de que ella "
"naciera; pero sé que él fue un héroe aún mayor para ella que para todos los "
"demás."

#. [message], speaker=Addraryn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1825
msgid "I... I have a daughter... and her name's Valerya?!"
msgstr "Yo… tengo una hija… ¿y se llama Valerya?!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1829
msgid "She's black-haired, with big blue eyes..."
msgstr "Tiene cabello negro, con grandes ojos azules…"

#. [message], speaker=Addraryn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1833
msgid "(laughs) The hair of her grandpa, but the eyes of her mother..."
msgstr "(ríe) El cabello de su abuelo, pero los ojos de su madre…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1837
msgid "...she has a penchant for fire magic..."
msgstr "…tiene inclinación por la magia de fuego…"

#. [message], speaker=Addraryn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1841
msgid "She must've been Meranoic's pupil..."
msgstr "Debe haber sido alumna de Meranoic…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1845
msgid ""
"...she loves the Northlands, loves partying and drinking, and always speaks "
"her mind, but never to hurt anyone..."
msgstr ""
"…ama las Tierras del Norte, ama las fiestas y beber, y siempre dice lo que "
"piensa, pero nunca para herir a nadie…"

#. [message], speaker=Addraryn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1849
msgid "Then I just know she got along really well with her aunts..."
msgstr "Entonces sé que se llevaba muy bien con sus tías…"

#. [message], speaker=Addraryn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1856
msgid ""
"Tenma, you have no idea what a gift you've given me. I would have followed "
"you to the very ends of the earth; but I know the world is safe in this new "
"age, because you're in it. If you meet my daughter again, tell her... Just "
"tell her this: 'I love you'."
msgstr ""
"Tenma, no tienes idea del regalo que me has dado. Te habría seguido hasta "
"los confines de la tierra; pero sé que el mundo está a salvo en esta nueva "
"era, porque tú estás en él. Si vuelves a encontrarte con mi hija, dile… Solo "
"dile esto: «Te amo»."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1860
msgid "Leave it to me, friend."
msgstr "Déjamelo a mí, amigo."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1870
msgid ""
"Now I guess it's my turn to move on... After all, I won't ever see you "
"again, will I?"
msgstr ""
"Ahora supongo que me toca a mí seguir adelante… Después de todo, nunca más "
"los veré, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1874
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, it is so. But, my dear, don't you ever forget that, even if "
"our bodies and souls are gone, as long as you don't forget us, we shall live "
"on in your memory and in your heart."
msgstr ""
"Desafortunadamente, así es. Pero, querida, nunca olvides que, aunque "
"nuestros cuerpos y almas se hayan ido, mientras no nos olvides, viviremos en "
"tu memoria y en tu corazón."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1878
msgid ""
"(crying) Well, I suppose I should be thankful that I've got a chance to say "
"goodbye in a proper manner, shouldn't I...?"
msgstr ""
"(llorando) Bueno, supongo que debería estar agradecida por tener la "
"oportunidad de despedirme como corresponde, ¿no es así…?"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1882
msgid ""
"(smiling) Farewell, my daughter; fear not whatever obstacle that comes your "
"way – after all, you have friends to count with."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Adiós, hija mía; no temas ningún obstáculo que se cruce en tu "
"camino —después de todo, tienes amigos en quienes confiar."

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1886
msgid "Farewell, grandma; may the spirits of Nature be with you!"
msgstr "¡Adiós, abuela; que los espíritus de la Naturaleza estén contigo!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1909
msgid ""
"(wiping away tears) Now, let's see what this 'Dream Guardian' wants with "
"me..."
msgstr ""
"(secándose las lágrimas) Ahora, veamos qué quiere este «Guardián de los "
"Sueños» conmigo…"

#. [message], speaker=Varthan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1931
msgid "Alas, this cursed existence has ended..."
msgstr "Ay, esta existencia maldita ha terminado…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1935
msgid "This is not good, we needed his aid in crossing this world!"
msgstr "Esto no está bien, ¡necesitábamos su ayuda para cruzar este mundo!"

#. [message], speaker=Maat
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1951
msgid "I... failed..?"
msgstr "Yo… ¿fallé…?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1955
msgid "Mother, NO!!! Damn, how could I let her be destroyed like this?!"
msgstr "¡Madre, NO! Maldición, ¿cómo pude dejar que la destruyeran así?!"

#. [message], speaker=Akhen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1971
msgid "I'm sorry, grandma, but I may no longer continue..."
msgstr "Lo siento, abuela, pero ya no puedo continuar…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1975
msgid "Akhen, NO!!! Damn, how could I let him be destroyed like this?!"
msgstr "¡Akhen, NO! Maldición, ¿cómo pude dejar que lo destruyeran así?!"

#. [message], speaker=Addraryn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1991
msgid "I'm sorry, my friend, I can't help you any more..."
msgstr "Lo siento, amiga mía, ya no puedo ayudarte más…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:1995
msgid "No, we needed him to survive this realm!"
msgstr "¡No, lo necesitábamos para sobrevivir a este reino!"

#. [message], speaker=Raihien
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:2011
msgid "Alas, I have failed before redeeming myself..."
msgstr "Ay, he fallado antes de redimirme…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:2015
msgid "No! We needed his power to survive this realm!"
msgstr "¡No! ¡Necesitábamos su poder para sobrevivir a este reino!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/37_Dead_World.cfg:2028
msgid ""
"Damn, I spent too much time to cross this realm, I don't think I'll have "
"enough energy to cross the Dreamland..."
msgstr ""
"Maldición, pasé demasiado tiempo cruzando este reino, no creo que tenga "
"suficiente energía para cruzar la Tierra de los Sueños…"

#. [scenario], id=38_Memory_Of_The_Ages
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:4
msgid "Memory of the Ages"
msgstr "Memoria de las Edades"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:20
msgid "Voyage through the Akashic Realm in search for the Dream Guardian"
msgstr "Viaje a través del Reino Akáshico en busca del Guardián de los Sueños"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:24
msgid "In this scenario, Tenma may not transform into Dragon-Slayer."
msgstr "En este escenario, Tenma no puede transformarse en Matadragones."

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:45
msgid "Akashic Realm"
msgstr "Reino Akáshico"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:55
msgid ""
"*Geesh, to think that I used to consider the universe a complicated place "
"when I was a child... I can clearly feel solid ground beneath me, and yet "
"there's no ground; the whole place feels very spacious, and yet there's "
"these light walls limiting the areas I can walk to... Well, sitting idly "
"won't do any good, so it's better to get going already; I want to find that "
"'Dream Guardian' anyway...*"
msgstr ""
"*Cielos, pensar que de niña consideraba el universo un lugar complicado… "
"Puedo sentir claramente suelo sólido bajo mis pies, y sin embargo no hay "
"suelo; todo el lugar se siente muy espacioso, y aun así hay estas paredes de "
"luz que limitan las áreas por las que puedo caminar… Bueno, quedarme sentada "
"sin hacer nada no servirá de nada, así que mejor ponerme en marcha ya; de "
"todos modos quiero encontrar a ese «Guardián de los Sueños»…*"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:59
msgid ""
"*Strange, though, that I don't feel my energies wearing out in this realm; "
"maybe the spirits of nature are immune to this world's atmosphere...*"
msgstr ""
"*Qué extraño, sin embargo, que no sienta mis energías agotarse en este "
"reino; tal vez los espíritus de la naturaleza sean inmunes a la atmósfera de "
"este mundo…*"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:74
msgid "Heiress, I welcome you into the Akashic Realm."
msgstr "Heredera, te doy la bienvenida al Reino Akáshico."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:78
msgid "Whoa! Who are you...?"
msgstr "¡Vaya! ¿Quién eres…?"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:82
msgid ""
"I am An-Usrukhar, a human who was allowed to remain in this world; I will "
"answer your questions, but first you must witness some of the memories kept "
"in the Aether."
msgstr ""
"Soy An-Usrukhar, un humano al que se le permitió permanecer en este mundo; "
"responderé tus preguntas, pero primero debes presenciar algunas de las "
"memorias guardadas en el Éter."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:86
msgid ""
"What do you mean by 'memories'? I thought I was in the realm of dreams..."
msgstr ""
"¿Qué quieres decir con «memorias»? Pensé que estaba en el reino de los "
"sueños…"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:90
msgid ""
"The Akashic Realm is not the dimension where dreams take place only; this is "
"where all thoughts and experiences ever witnessed by living eyes are kept; a "
"catalogue of every knowledge ever gathered by living beings across the ages."
msgstr ""
"El Reino Akáshico no es solo la dimensión donde ocurren los sueños; aquí se "
"guardan todos los pensamientos y experiencias que alguna vez presenciaron "
"ojos vivos; un catálogo de todo conocimiento reunido por seres vivos a lo "
"largo de las edades."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:94
msgid ""
"So I have to see someone else's memories before meeting you... Well, so be "
"it; I just hope I don't have to wander around this world for long in order "
"to meet you..."
msgstr ""
"Entonces tengo que ver las memorias de otra persona antes de conocerte… "
"Bueno, que así sea; solo espero no tener que vagar por este mundo mucho "
"tiempo para encontrarte"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:111
msgid "*This area is larger than the others... I hope it's not a trap...?*"
msgstr ""
"*Esta área es más grande que las otras… Espero que no sea una trampa…?*"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:167
msgid ""
"Erm, excuse me, I don't mean to intrude, but could you please tell me what..."
msgstr "Ehm, disculpe, no quiero entrometerme, pero ¿podría decirme qué…"

#. [message], speaker=Demere
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:171
msgid "I am glad that you came in the end, Tithanya..."
msgstr "Me alegra que al final hayas venido, Tithanya…"

#. [message], speaker=Tithanya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:175
msgid ""
"(sulking) Well, you <i>are</i> my mother after all, are you not? A pity the "
"same cannot be said of those lizards of yours..."
msgstr ""
"(haciendo pucheros) Bueno, después de todo <i>eres</i> mi madre, ¿no es así? "
"Lástima que no pueda decirse lo mismo de esos lagartos tuyos…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:179
msgid ""
"*They don't seem to notice me... Hold on, though, I've heard about "
"'Tithanya' before, hasn't Cornelya recently told me about her? Now, if this "
"girl is the same Tithanya of whom she talked about, then her mother should "
"be...!*"
msgstr ""
"*No parecen notarme… Espera, sin embargo, he oído hablar de «Tithanya» "
"antes, ¿no me contó Cornelya recientemente sobre ella? Ahora, si esta chica "
"es la misma Tithanya de la que habló, entonces su madre debería ser…!*"

#. [message], speaker=Demere
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:183
msgid "(chuckling) Worry not, they are on their way..."
msgstr "(riendo) No te preocupes, ya están en camino…"

#. [message], speaker=Demere
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:204
msgid "See?"
msgstr "¿Ves?"

#. [message], speaker=Nitiballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:208
msgid "Mother, we're deeply sorry that we couldn't arrive sooner..."
msgstr "Madre, lamentamos profundamente no haber llegado antes…"

#. [message], speaker=Agniballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:212
msgid ""
"Why... Why are you in this state, Mother?! Don't tell me that you're "
"really..."
msgstr ""
"¿Por qué… por qué estás en este estado, Madre? ¡No me digas que realmente "
"estás…!"

#. [message], speaker=Demere
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:216
msgid "Yes, my children, the time of my passing has finally come, but..."
msgstr "Sí, hijos míos, por fin ha llegado el momento de mi partida, pero…"

#. [message], speaker=Agniballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:220
msgid ""
"(angry) But <i>how</i> can you die?! You're the Avatar of all life in this "
"world, you should... you <i>had</i> to..."
msgstr ""
"(enojado) ¡¿Pero <i>cómo</i> puedes morir?! Eres el Avatar de toda la vida "
"en este mundo, deberías… <i>tenías</i> que…"

#. [message], speaker=Demere
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:224
msgid ""
"I think I have given you an erroneous impression of Avatars, my children... "
"Even though we have built this universe, as individual beings we have a "
"lifespan just like you and everything else in existence. We might have been "
"virtually eternal had we not used our essence to create everything that is, "
"but I can warrant you, I doubt that any of us has ever regretted doing "
"that..."
msgstr ""
"Creo que les he dado una impresión errónea de los Avatares, hijos míos… "
"Aunque hemos construido este universo, como seres individuales tenemos una "
"duración de vida igual que ustedes y todo lo demás en la existencia. "
"Podríamos haber sido prácticamente eternos si no hubiéramos usado nuestra "
"esencia para crear todo lo que es, pero les aseguro que dudo que alguno de "
"nosotros haya lamentado alguna vez haberlo hecho…"

#. [message], speaker=Vanadya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:236
msgid ""
"Speak for yourself, sister; I have never regretted keeping my power to "
"myself, and in return I shall live on for a few more aeons."
msgstr ""
"Habla por ti misma, hermana; nunca he lamentado conservar mi poder para mí, "
"y a cambio viviré unos pocos eones más."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:240
msgid ""
"*This aura, it's the same as Galdra's! So this is really her original "
"self...*"
msgstr ""
"*¡Esta aura es la misma que la de Galdra! Entonces esta es realmente su yo "
"original…*"

#. [message], speaker=Demere
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:244
msgid ""
"But are you certain that you want to live such lonely existence? Yansa, "
"Quezatla, Moriann, Ymira, even Ananke... All gone, as I myself presently "
"will be. You will remain as the last Avatar, unable to find any peer to "
"share your joy or your memories..."
msgstr ""
"Pero ¿estás segura de que quieres vivir una existencia tan solitaria? Yansa, "
"Quezatla, Moriann, Ymira, incluso Ananke… Todos se han ido, como yo misma lo "
"haré en breve. Quedarás como la última Avatar, incapaz de encontrar a nadie "
"con quien compartir tu alegría o tus recuerdos…"

#. [message], speaker=Vanadya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:248
msgid ""
"Which matters not, as I have never needed to share such things; I suffice to "
"myself."
msgstr ""
"Lo cual no importa, pues nunca he necesitado compartir tales cosas; me basto "
"a mí misma."

#. [message], speaker=Demere
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:252
msgid ""
"We both know this to be untrue, but I shall not insist on the matter, I have "
"no time for that... And, also, because I sense that you have come here for "
"something other than saying your last farewell..."
msgstr ""
"Ambas sabemos que eso no es cierto, pero no insistiré en el asunto, no tengo "
"tiempo para eso… Y también porque siento que has venido aquí por algo más "
"que despedirte por última vez…"

#. [message], speaker=Vanadya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:256
msgid ""
"Indeed. I thought that you would be happy to know that your beloved Ananke "
"has left, unbeknownst to us all, a gift for you..."
msgstr ""
"En efecto. Pensé que te alegraría saber que tu amada Ananke ha dejado, sin "
"que ninguno de nosotros lo supiera, un regalo para ti…"

#. [unit], id=Metatron, type=High Seraph
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:262
msgid "Metatron"
msgstr "Metatrón"

#. [unit], id=Seraphiel, type=High Seraph
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:271
msgid "Seraphiel"
msgstr "Serafiel"

#. [message], speaker=Demere
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:286
msgid "You are Ananke's children...!"
msgstr "¡Ustedes son hijos de Ananke…!"

#. [message], speaker=Metatron
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:290
msgid ""
"You are correct, Lady Demere. I am Metatron, chosen leader of the "
"Celestials, retainers of the Avatar of Will during her existence. Before her "
"passing, she used her last powers to create a being of power and reason, "
"filling it with her own essence. She shaped this being in the image of the "
"ones you call dragons, for she wanted it to live here, helping your own "
"children to protect your favoured world once you were gone."
msgstr ""
"Está en lo correcto, dama Demere. Soy Metatrón, líder elegido de los "
"Celestiales, guardianes del Avatar de la Voluntad durante su existencia. "
"Antes de su partida, usó sus últimos poderes para crear un ser de poder y "
"razón, llenándolo con su propia esencia. Dio forma a este ser a imagen de "
"aquellos que ustedes llaman dragones, pues quería que viviera aquí, ayudando "
"a sus propios hijos a proteger su mundo predilecto una vez que ella se "
"hubiera ido."

#. [message], speaker=Demere
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:294
msgid ""
"Ananke...! To think that you would leave your Heir to protect my precious "
"children... Heir of Ananke, please tell me, do you have a name?"
msgstr ""
"¡Ananke…! Pensar que dejarías a tu Heredero para proteger a mis preciosos "
"hijos… Heredero de Ananke, por favor dime, ¿tienes un nombre?"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:298
msgid ""
"I... (looks troubled) I am afraid that my Mother has left me no such thing..."
msgstr "Yo… (parece preocupado) Me temo que mi Madre no me dejó tal cosa…"

#. [message], speaker=Demere
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:302
msgid ""
"Then allow me to give you one. From now on, you will live on this world, and "
"you will count Nitiballi, who rules over the waters, and Agniballi, the "
"absolute master of fire, as brothers. You are pure and has a powerful sense "
"of justice, so you shall watch over them and all those who live on this "
"planet, protecting them from death and destruction. You will be the sky "
"which guards the earth beneath its wings; you shall be known as Svarballi, "
"the High Dragon of the Sky."
msgstr ""
"Entonces permíteme darte uno. De ahora en adelante vivirás en este mundo, y "
"contarás a Nitiballi, quien reina sobre las aguas, y a Agniballi, el amo "
"absoluto del fuego, como hermanos. Eres puro y tienes un poderoso sentido de "
"justicia, así que velarás por ellos y por todos los que viven en este "
"planeta, protegiéndolos de la muerte y la destrucción. Serás el cielo que "
"guarda la tierra bajo sus alas; serás conocido como Svarballi, el Gran "
"Dragón del Cielo."

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:306
msgid ""
"Thank you, Lady Demere. I promise I will do my best to protect your children "
"– but I confess I will need some advice, in the beginning, as I have never "
"had such task on my shoulders..."
msgstr ""
"Gracias, dama Demere. Prometo que haré lo mejor para proteger a tus hijos —"
"pero confieso que necesitaré algunos consejos al principio, ya que nunca he "
"tenido tal tarea sobre mis hombros…"

#. [message], speaker=Nitiballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:310
msgid ""
"Don't worry, brother, Agniballi and I shall give you whatever support you "
"need."
msgstr ""
"No te preocupes, hermano, Agniballi y yo te daremos todo el apoyo que "
"necesites."

#. [message], speaker=Metatron
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:314
msgid ""
"Lady Demere, I, in the name of all Celestials, wish to follow the Heir of "
"Ananke and, settling on this planet, help watch over it as well. Now that "
"our Mother is no longer with us, we have nowhere to go, and so we think "
"there is no better cause to dedicate ourselves to than guarding the precious "
"children of our Mother's beloved."
msgstr ""
"Dama Demere, yo, en nombre de todos los Celestiales, deseo seguir al "
"Heredero de Ananke y, estableciéndonos en este planeta, ayudar a vigilarlo "
"también. Ahora que nuestra Madre ya no está con nosotros, no tenemos a dónde "
"ir, y por eso pensamos que no hay mejor causa a la que dedicarnos que "
"proteger a los preciosos hijos de la amada de nuestra Madre."

#. [message], speaker=Demere
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:318
msgid ""
"(smiling) And I am deeply grateful to you for that. I am so glad... To be "
"able to go away surrounded by so much love... Oblivion does not seem "
"frightening, not now..."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Y les estoy profundamente agradecida por eso. Estoy tan "
"contenta… de poder irme rodeada de tanto amor… El olvido no parece "
"aterrador, no ahora…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:333
msgid ""
"*Her remains, the material of which they're made, I'm sure I've seen it "
"somewhere...*"
msgstr ""
"*Sus restos, el material del que están hechos, estoy segura de haberlo visto "
"en alguna parte…*"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:381
msgid "*Well, I suppose I got more memories to witness...*"
msgstr "*Bueno, supongo que tengo más memorias por presenciar…*"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:398
msgid "*Oh, another memory...*"
msgstr "*Oh, otra memoria…*"

#. [message], speaker=Usrukhar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:427
msgid ""
"(angry) No... It doesn't matter what you say, I won't accept it – I will "
"enter the realm of the dead itself if I have to, so that I can stay by your "
"side!"
msgstr ""
"(enojado) No… No importa lo que digas, no lo aceptaré —¡entraré al reino de "
"los muertos mismo si es necesario, para poder quedarme a tu lado!"

#. [message], speaker=Vanadya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:431
msgid ""
"(smiling) Human, how dare you make the life of an Avatar so hard... Even if "
"you do manage to reach the Land of the Dead, you will not find me; when an "
"Avatar dies, her mind fades away entirely; only her essence remains."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Humano, ¿cómo te atreves a hacer tan difícil la vida de un "
"Avatar…? Incluso si logras llegar a la Tierra de los Muertos, no me "
"encontrarás; cuando un Avatar muere, su mente se desvanece por completo; "
"solo queda su esencia."

#. [message], speaker=Usrukhar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:435
msgid ""
"But yours is the essence of Magic, the one thing in this universe which is "
"truly eternal!"
msgstr ""
"¡Pero la tuya es la esencia de la Magia, la única cosa en este universo que "
"es verdaderamente eterna!"

#. [message], speaker=Vanadya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:439
msgid ""
"Not really... I owe you an apology, An, I have not been completely honest "
"with you. You see, Avatars could have lived virtually forever, had they not "
"shared their true essence with the rest of existence. This 'true essence' is "
"the very source of our power; and that is what we have shared with creation: "
"Demere gave her Spark of Life to all creatures, Moriann gave her own Soul so "
"that new souls could be created for them, Ananke gave them her Will so they "
"could be truly free..."
msgstr ""
"No realmente… Te debo una disculpa, An, no he sido completamente honesta "
"contigo. Verás, los Avatares podrían haber vivido prácticamente para "
"siempre, de no haber compartido su verdadera esencia con el resto de la "
"existencia. Esta «verdadera esencia» es la fuente misma de nuestro poder; y "
"eso es lo que hemos compartido con la creación: Demere dio su Chispa de Vida "
"a todas las criaturas, Moriann dio su propia Alma para que nuevas almas "
"pudieran crearse para ellas, Ananke les dio su Voluntad para que fueran "
"verdaderamente libres…"

#. [message], speaker=Usrukhar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:443
msgid "So... that means that you will die because..."
msgstr "Entonces… eso significa que morirás porque…"

#. [message], speaker=Vanadya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:447
msgid ""
"...Because I have, after so long, given to others the ability to control the "
"magic that impregnaes this whole universe. But, An, I do not wish to see you "
"blaming yourself; you did convince me to share my gifts with others, but the "
"decision to do that is still mine alone."
msgstr ""
"…Porque después de tanto tiempo he dado a otros la capacidad de controlar la "
"magia que impregna todo este universo. Pero, An, no deseo verte culpándote; "
"tú me convenciste de compartir mis dones con otros, pero la decisión de "
"hacerlo sigue siendo solo mía."

#. [message], speaker=Usrukhar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:451
msgid ""
"Poor comfort... I did that because I wanted my people to be safe; had I "
"known this would be the consequence..."
msgstr ""
"Pobre consuelo… Lo hice porque quería que mi pueblo estuviera a salvo; si "
"hubiera sabido que esta sería la consecuencia…"

#. [message], speaker=Vanadya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:455
msgid ""
"You have done the right thing, An – better, you inspired me do the right "
"thing. As an Avatar, I was not supposed to keep this power to myself only. "
"Thanks to you, I was able to finally fulfil my destiny; better still, thanks "
"to you, I was able to experience that feeling which my sisters told me so "
"much about, but which I refused to understand: love..."
msgstr ""
"Has hecho lo correcto, An —mejor dicho, me inspiraste a hacer lo correcto. "
"Como Avatar, no debía conservar este poder solo para mí. Gracias a ti pude "
"finalmente cumplir mi destino; mejor aún, gracias a ti pude experimentar ese "
"sentimiento del que mis hermanas me hablaban tanto, pero que me negaba a "
"entender: el amor…"

#. [message], speaker=Usrukhar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:459
msgid "(fighting tears) So... Do you already know when you will..."
msgstr "(luchando contra las lágrimas) Entonces… ¿ya sabes cuándo tú…"

#. [message], speaker=Vanadya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:463
msgid ""
"Yes, and it will not take long. That is why I wanted to meet you so much; I "
"have three wishes which only you may attend. The first is to hide my body; "
"as you know, when an Avatar's mystical body falls lifeless, it becomes "
"orichalcum. However, much of the Avatar's former power remains inside it, "
"due to that metal's magic properties..."
msgstr ""
"Sí, y no tardará mucho. Por eso quería verte tanto; tengo tres deseos que "
"solo tú puedes cumplir. El primero es ocultar mi cuerpo; como sabes, cuando "
"el cuerpo místico de un Avatar cae sin vida, se convierte en oricalco. Sin "
"embargo, gran parte del antiguo poder del Avatar permanece dentro, debido a "
"las propiedades mágicas de ese metal…"

#. [message], speaker=Usrukhar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:467
msgid ""
"And you don't want your remains to be used for wicked means... You needed "
"not ask me such thing, my love, one would have to kill my body and "
"extinguish my soul before touching you."
msgstr ""
"Y no quieres que tus restos sean usados para fines malvados… No tenías que "
"pedirme tal cosa, mi amor, tendrían que matar mi cuerpo y extinguir mi alma "
"antes de tocarte."

#. [message], speaker=Vanadya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:471
msgid ""
"(smiling) Silly human... My second wish is that you deliver this blade to "
"the worthiest champion of the orcs. I sense a time of turmoil about to "
"descend upon this world. I do not trust Svarballi any more; I know not what "
"has happened to him, but the pure Sky Dragon whom I met at Demere's deathbed "
"no longer exists – worse, I fear that he has been utterly subverted... And, "
"if my fears are confirmed, the children of this world will need powers which "
"they do not possess, not yet. Humans have your guidance, merfolk have "
"Nitiballi's, dragons have Agniballi's, and the elves have Tithanya's power "
"in their veins; but orcs, dwarves and trolls are defenceless, and so I have "
"crafted weapons with which they may defend themselves."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Tonto humano… Mi segundo deseo es que entregues esta espada al "
"campeón más digno de los orcos. Siento que un tiempo de agitación está por "
"descender sobre este mundo. Ya no confío en Svarballi; no sé qué le ha "
"pasado, pero el puro Dragón del Cielo que conocí en el lecho de muerte de "
"Demere ya no existe —peor aún, temo que ha sido completamente subvertido… Y, "
"si mis temores se confirman, los hijos de este mundo necesitarán poderes que "
"aún no poseen. Los humanos tienen tu guía, los sirenidos la de Nitiballi, "
"los dragones la de Agniballi, y los elfos tienen el poder de Tithanya en sus "
"venas; pero los orcos, enanos y trolls están indefensos, y por eso he "
"forjado armas con las que puedan defenderse."

#. [message], speaker=Usrukhar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:475
msgid ""
"I do not understand, who are 'trolls' and 'dwarves'? I have never even heard "
"of such nations..."
msgstr ""
"No entiendo, ¿quiénes son los «trolls» y los «enanos»? Nunca he oído hablar "
"de tales naciones…"

#. [message], speaker=Vanadya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:479
msgid ""
"They are denizens of the underground world, and shall emerge soon. I have "
"delivered them their weapons, but I fear the orcs will not trust me as they "
"will trust you."
msgstr ""
"Son habitantes del mundo subterráneo, y emergerán pronto. Les he entregado "
"sus armas, pero temo que los orcos no confiarán en mí como confiarán en ti."

#. [message], speaker=Usrukhar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:483
msgid "I understand. And what of your third wish?"
msgstr "Entiendo. ¿Y cuál es tu tercer deseo?"

#. [message], speaker=Vanadya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:487
msgid ""
"I wish... I wish to spend my last moments alongside you. But I wonder... "
"does the widely-famed An-Usrukhar, whose guidance is requested by all, have "
"any time to spend with his beloved...?"
msgstr ""
"Deseo… deseo pasar mis últimos momentos a tu lado. Pero me pregunto… ¿el "
"ampliamente famoso An-Usrukhar, cuya guía es solicitada por todos, tiene "
"tiempo para pasar con su amada…?"

#. [message], speaker=Usrukhar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:491
msgid "(smiling) Silly goddess, for you I have all the time in the world..."
msgstr "(sonriendo) Tonta diosa, para ti tengo todo el tiempo del mundo…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:515
msgid ""
"*I guess it's not only in our tales that a mortal and a goddess fall in love "
"with one another... Well, it doesn't seem like that An-something guy will "
"appear yet, so let's get going...*"
msgstr ""
"*Supongo que no solo en nuestros cuentos un mortal y una diosa se enamoran "
"el uno del otro… Bueno, no parece que ese tal An-algo vaya a aparecer "
"todavía, así que pongámonos en marcha…*"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:596
msgid ""
"*That's Nitiballi... and some spirits of nature... Wait, I think I know this "
"cave...*"
msgstr ""
"*Ese es Nitiballi… y algunos espíritus de la naturaleza… Espera, creo que "
"conozco esta cueva…*"

#. [message], speaker=Agni
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:600
msgid ""
"Foolish child, you were chosen by the Mother to watch over this world! How "
"can you think so little of her will, to waste your life like this? What if "
"the Destroyer rises again – as you know he will, sooner or later?!"
msgstr ""
"Niño necio, ¡fuiste elegido por la Madre para velar por este mundo! ¿Cómo "
"puedes pensar tan poco en su voluntad, desperdiciando tu vida así? ¿Y si el "
"Destructor vuelve a levantarse —como sabes que lo hará, tarde o temprano?!"

#. [message], speaker=Nitiballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:604
msgid ""
"I trust that Agniballi shall watch over Svarballi's imprisoned soul well; "
"until someone stronger than him appears – and it should take some time until "
"that day comes – the Sky Dragon will not threaten this world. As for the "
"Mother's will... You will find out that I am fulfilling it, spirits. Our "
"battle against Svarballi has wrecked this world's balance: vast expanses of "
"land have become sterile, and the volcanoes and earthquakes have covered the "
"planet in a veil of darkness the sun itself cannot pierce. If no measure is "
"taken, all life on this world will perish."
msgstr ""
"Confío en que Agniballi vigilará bien el alma encarcelada de Svarballi; "
"hasta que alguien más fuerte que él aparezca —y debería tomar algún tiempo "
"hasta que llegue ese día— el Dragón del Cielo no amenazará este mundo. En "
"cuanto a la voluntad de la Madre… Descubrirán que la estoy cumpliendo, "
"espíritus. Nuestra batalla contra Svarballi ha destrozado el equilibrio de "
"este mundo: vastas extensiones de tierra se han vuelto estériles, y los "
"volcanes y terremotos han cubierto el planeta con un velo de oscuridad que "
"ni el sol mismo puede atravesar. Si no se toma ninguna medida, toda la vida "
"en este mundo perecerá."

#. [message], speaker=Gali
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:608
msgid ""
"And so you will use your healing powers to renew the land so that it will "
"yield fruits even if there is no sun for the next thousand years... Indeed, "
"your sacrifice is the only way to prevent a catastrophe from happening."
msgstr ""
"Y así usarás tus poderes curativos para renovar la tierra de modo que dé "
"frutos incluso si no hay sol durante los próximos mil años… En efecto, tu "
"sacrificio es la única forma de evitar que ocurra una catástrofe."

#. [message], speaker=Bhumi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:612
msgid ""
"Still, the Agni has a point; what will happen if the Destroyer is released "
"and you are not here to help fight him?"
msgstr ""
"Aun así, Agni tiene razón; ¿qué pasará si el Destructor es liberado y tú no "
"estás aquí para ayudar a luchar contra él?"

#. [message], speaker=Nitiballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:616
msgid ""
"The Mother has once told me that life is still far from reaching its true "
"potential, that it has yet much to evolve. If primordial beings such as "
"ourselves were able to defeat Svarballi, I am certain that the future holds "
"heroes and heroines who will not only repeat the deed, but surpass it. To "
"these children of the future I legate the will of the Mother; they will "
"protect this world as she has done, and as both Agniballi and I have after "
"her..."
msgstr ""
"La Madre una vez me dijo que la vida aún está lejos de alcanzar su verdadero "
"potencial, que aún tiene mucho por evolucionar. Si seres primordiales como "
"nosotros pudimos derrotar a Svarballi, estoy seguro de que el futuro guarda "
"héroes y heroínas que no solo repetirán la hazaña, sino que la superarán. A "
"estos hijos del futuro lego la voluntad de la Madre; protegerán este mundo "
"como ella lo hizo, y como tanto Agniballi como yo lo hemos hecho después de "
"ella…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:654
msgid ""
"*You've left us one hell of a mission, haven't you, Water Dragon... "
"(smiling) You didn't even need to say that, protecting this world is "
"everyone's job; now, let's see what comes next...*"
msgstr ""
"*Nos dejaste una misión tremenda, ¿verdad, Dragón del Agua…? (sonriendo) Ni "
"siquiera tenías que decirlo, proteger este mundo es el trabajo de todos; "
"ahora, veamos qué viene después…*"

#. [message], speaker=Usrukhar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:678
msgid "At long last we meet in person, Heiress."
msgstr "Por fin nos encontramos en persona, Heredera."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:682
msgid ""
"I tell you the same; I've heard a lot about you already, First of Mages... "
"But I still don't understand why you wanted to meet me – better, I guess I "
"do, but I still need your confirmation..."
msgstr ""
"Te digo lo mismo; ya he oído mucho sobre ti, Primero de los Magos… Pero "
"todavía no entiendo por qué querías conocerme —mejor dicho, supongo que sí, "
"pero aún necesito tu confirmación…"

#. [message], speaker=Usrukhar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:686
msgid ""
"Speak your doubts, then; you were brought to this realm for this very reason."
msgstr ""
"Expresa tus dudas, entonces; fuiste traída a este reino precisamente por "
"esta razón."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:690
msgid ""
"(surprised) You mean that Galdra sent me to the Land of the Dead so that I "
"could come here and learn more about the past?"
msgstr ""
"(sorprendida) ¿Quieres decir que Galdra me envió a la Tierra de los Muertos "
"para que pudiera venir aquí y aprender más sobre el pasado?"

#. [message], speaker=Usrukhar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:694
msgid ""
"This I cannot say, for I haven't managed to fathom Galdra's mind, even if "
"she spent so much time dwelling in this realm."
msgstr ""
"Eso no puedo decirlo, pues no he logrado comprender la mente de Galdra, "
"aunque pasó tanto tiempo habitando en este reino."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:698
msgid "But isn't she the same as Vanadya?"
msgstr "¿Pero no es ella lo mismo que Vanadya?"

#. [message], speaker=Usrukhar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:702
msgid ""
"You have seen the memory, Tenma; Vanadya died in my time... If anything, "
"Galdra is an inheritor of her power over the essence of magic."
msgstr ""
"Has visto la memoria, Tenma; Vanadya murió en mi época… Si acaso, Galdra es "
"una heredera de su poder sobre la esencia de la magia."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:706
msgid ""
"An inheritor, you say... Does that mean, then... When you call me an "
"Heiress, you mean that I'm supposed to inherit the power of an Avatar?"
msgstr ""
"¿Una heredera, dices…? Entonces… cuando me llamas Heredera, ¿quieres decir "
"que se supone que debo heredar el poder de un Avatar?"

#. [message], speaker=Usrukhar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:710
msgid ""
"Not the power, but the will: the will of a mother who wants her children to "
"grow and live as they were meant to. But this, Tenma, you have inherited "
"long ago, in the time you were still known as Myra; the fact the spirits of "
"nature have chosen you as their kin proves that."
msgstr ""
"No el poder, sino la voluntad: la voluntad de una madre que quiere que sus "
"hijos crezcan y vivan como estaban destinados a hacerlo. Pero esto, Tenma, "
"lo heredaste hace mucho, en la época en que aún eras conocida como Myra; el "
"hecho de que los espíritus de la naturaleza te hayan elegido como su "
"pariente lo demuestra."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:714
msgid ""
"But will I be able to kill Svarballi with their power alone? The High "
"Dragons, Maat and myself have used it against him in the past, and all it "
"did was temporarily stop him..."
msgstr ""
"Pero ¿podré matar a Svarballi solo con su poder? Los Grandes Dragones, Maat "
"y yo misma lo hemos usado contra él en el pasado, y todo lo que hizo fue "
"detenerlo temporalmente…"

#. [message], speaker=Usrukhar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:718
msgid ""
"At the time, you were but vessels of their power; but as you are now, you "
"have become one of them, and so you have become far stronger than either the "
"High Dragons, Maat or Myra. Besides, you now have a knowledge which none of "
"your predecessors had: knowledge of a weapon which carries, within it, the "
"reminiscent of a true Avatar's power..."
msgstr ""
"En aquel entonces no eran más que recipientes de su poder; pero tal como "
"eres ahora, te has convertido en una de ellas, y por eso eres mucho más "
"fuerte que los Grandes Dragones, Maat o Myra. Además, ahora tienes un "
"conocimiento que ninguno de tus predecesores tuvo: el conocimiento de un "
"arma que lleva dentro el recuerdo del poder de un verdadero Avatar"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:722
msgid ""
"Akashia's Deva Sword... To think that we had a weapon capable of killing "
"Svarballi with us for all that time..."
msgstr ""
"La Espada Deva de Akashia… Pensar que hemos tenido un arma capaz de matar a "
"Svarballi con nosotros todo ese tiempo"

#. [message], speaker=Usrukhar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:726
msgid ""
"The blame is not yours. The knowledge of the power held by orichalcum was "
"one I made sure to erase from the world's memory after a mage from my era "
"crafted a set of weapons from the Mother's holy remains. I thought I had "
"destroyed those weapons, but evidently one survived: the one fate guided "
"Akashia's parents to find in the mountains of their home, and which the "
"Windsong Deianira brought to Hiera'Shirsha along with Akashia herself."
msgstr ""
"La culpa no es tuya. El conocimiento del poder que contiene el oricalco fue "
"algo que me aseguré de borrar de la memoria del mundo después de que un mago "
"de mi época forjara un conjunto de armas con los restos sagrados de la "
"Madre. Pensé que había destruido esas armas, pero evidentemente una "
"sobrevivió: la que el destino guió a los padres de Akashia a encontrar en "
"las montañas de su hogar, y que la Hija del Viento Deianira llevó a "
"Hiera’Shirsha junto con la propia Akashia."

#. [message], speaker=Usrukhar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:730
msgid ""
"Besides, and most importantly, not just anyone can access the blade's true "
"power. In Akashia's hands it was a powerful weapon, but not enough to kill "
"Svarballi. In your hands, however..."
msgstr ""
"Además, y lo más importante, no cualquiera puede acceder al verdadero poder "
"de la hoja. En las manos de Akashia era un arma poderosa, pero no suficiente "
"para matar a Svarballi. En las tuyas, sin embargo"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:734
msgid ""
"Then that gives me two weapons with which I may kill Svarballi, right? My "
"Dragon-Slayer spells and Akashia's Sword..."
msgstr ""
"Entonces eso me da dos armas con las que puedo matar a Svarballi, ¿verdad? "
"Mis hechizos Matadragones y la Espada de Akashia"

#. [message], speaker=Usrukhar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:738
msgid ""
"Yes, Heiress, but I must warn you – and that is of utmost importance: when "
"you saw Svarballi at Garet-Desh and even at the Crystal Tower, he was "
"weakened by the aeons spent in the prison built by his fellow High Dragons. "
"Maat's prison, by its turn, could not dampen his power."
msgstr ""
"Sí, Heredera, pero debo advertirte —y esto es de suma importancia—: cuando "
"viste a Svarballi en Garet-Desh e incluso en la Torre de Cristal, estaba "
"debilitado por los eones pasados en la prisión construida por sus compañeros "
"Grandes Dragones. La prisión de Maat, por su parte, no pudo amortiguar su "
"poder."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:742
msgid ""
"And so, when I fight him again, he'll be much stronger than before... Then I "
"guess I'll only have to destroy him while he's still within the Sky Soul, "
"right?"
msgstr ""
"Y entonces, cuando vuelva a enfrentarlo, será mucho más fuerte que antes… "
"Supongo que solo tendré que destruirlo mientras aún esté dentro del Alma del "
"Cielo, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Usrukhar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:746
msgid ""
"This is the last thing I wanted to tell you, Tenma... Maat certainly told "
"you that Svarballi was sent to this dimension, the Akashic Realm; haven't "
"you wondered why you haven't met him since you arrived here...?"
msgstr ""
"Esto es lo último que quería decirte, Tenma… Maat sin duda te dijo que "
"Svarballi fue enviado a esta dimensión, el Reino Akáshico; ¿no te has "
"preguntado por qué no lo has encontrado desde que llegaste aquí…?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:750
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1287
msgid "I..."
msgstr "Yo…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:757
msgid "An-Usrukhar... Don't tell me that..."
msgstr "An-Usrukhar… No me digas que…"

#. [message], speaker=Usrukhar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:761
msgid ""
"You should hurry up, Heiress; for better or for worse, the gears of fate "
"have been accelerated, and you are the only hope Irdya has to survive the "
"oncoming cataclysm."
msgstr ""
"Debes apresurarte, Heredera; para bien o para mal, los engranajes del "
"destino se han acelerado, y eres la única esperanza que tiene Irdya para "
"sobrevivir al cataclismo que se avecina."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:765
msgid ""
"Then this is not where I'm supposed to be! Please, open a portal to the "
"Living World at once, or it'll be too late!"
msgstr ""
"¡Entonces este no es el lugar donde debería estar! ¡Por favor, abre un "
"portal al Mundo de los Vivos de inmediato, o será demasiado tarde!"

#. [message], speaker=Usrukhar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:769
msgid ""
"Go forward along this pathway, and you shall find yourself back to your "
"world."
msgstr "Avanza por este camino y te encontrarás de regreso en tu mundo."

#. [message], speaker=Usrukhar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:776
msgid ""
"And Tenma... I cannot return to that world, not yet, but that's still my "
"world too... Even if I'm unable to help you with my power, I may lend it to "
"you – better, to your friends. If you go to the White Woods, where the great "
"of Wesnoth are laid to rest, search for the tomb of Delfador the Great; "
"there lies my staff. Whoever is deemed worthy of wielding it shall have "
"access to powers akin to my own."
msgstr ""
"Y Tenma… No puedo regresar a ese mundo, todavía no, pero ese también sigue "
"siendo mi mundo… Aunque no pueda ayudarte con mi poder, puedo prestártelo —"
"mejor dicho, a tus amigos. Si vas a los Bosques Blancos, donde descansan los "
"grandes de Wesnoth, busca la tumba de Delfador el Grande; allí yace mi "
"bastón. Quien sea considerado digno de empuñarlo tendrá acceso a poderes "
"similares a los míos."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:780
msgid "Right, I know exactly who could wield it..."
msgstr "Cierto, sé exactamente quién podría empuñarlo…"

#. [message], speaker=Usrukhar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/38_Memory_Of_The_Ages.cfg:784
msgid ""
"Good luck, Tenma Yozora; please, save the world which we have fought so much "
"for..."
msgstr ""
"Buena suerte, Tenma Yozora; por favor, salva el mundo por el que tanto hemos "
"luchado…"

#. [scenario], id=39_Odysseys_End_I
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_I.cfg:4
msgid "Odyssey's End: Return"
msgstr "El Fin de la Odisea: Regreso"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_I.cfg:48
msgid "*No... No way... Was I too late...?!*"
msgstr "*No… No puede ser… ¿Llegué demasiado tarde…?!*"

#. [scenario], id=39_Independence_Day
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:4
msgid "Independence Day"
msgstr "Día de la Independencia"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:23
msgid "Defeat Governor Roddryr"
msgstr "Derrotar al gobernador Roddryr"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:31
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:34
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:754
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:866
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1303
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1430
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:45
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:835
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1761
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:48
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1112
msgid "Death of Natsu"
msgstr "Muerte de Natsu"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:35
msgid "Death of Elder Yamamoto"
msgstr "Muerte del anciano Yamamoto"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:39
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:38
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:762
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:874
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1311
msgid "Death of Ikki"
msgstr "Muerte de Ikki"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:43
msgid "NOTE: Tenma can recruit/recall from the hexes adjacent to 17,31"
msgstr ""
"NOTA: Tenma puede reclutar/reincorporar desde los hexágonos adyacentes a "
"17,31"

#. [side], type=Grand Marshal
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:73
msgid "Governor Roddryr"
msgstr "Gobernador Roddryr"

#. [side], type=Sogen Elder Priest
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:98
msgid "Elder Yamamoto"
msgstr "Anciano Yamamoto"

#. [side], type=Sogen Elder Priest
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:103
msgid "Umashima"
msgstr "Umashima"

#. [label]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:142
msgid "Daikami Temple"
msgstr "Templo Daikami"

#. [label]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:146
msgid "Mount Orihime"
msgstr "Monte Orihime"

#. [label]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:150
msgid "Mount Hikoboshi"
msgstr "Monte Hikoboshi"

#. [message], speaker=Kaede
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:167
msgid ""
"Elder, look! The Wesnothians are sending another demon to harass our city!"
msgstr ""
"¡Anciano, mira! ¡Los wesnothianos están enviando otro demonio a hostigar "
"nuestra ciudad!"

#. [message], speaker=Yamamoto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:171
msgid ""
"Then what are you waiting for?! Focus your senses on the next arrow, and "
"shoot..."
msgstr ""
"¡Entonces qué esperas?! ¡Concentra tus sentidos en la próxima flecha y "
"dispara…!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:175
msgid ""
"Wait, wait, don't shoot! I know I may look a bit different, but it's me, "
"Tenma Yozora!"
msgstr ""
"¡Espera, espera, no disparen! Sé que puedo verme un poco diferente, ¡pero "
"soy yo, Tenma Yozora!"

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:179
msgid ""
"(astonished) Tenma!!! By the Heavens, I thought... I was afraid... Wait, "
"where's...?"
msgstr ""
"(asombrada) ¡Tenma! ¡Por los Cielos, pensé… tenía miedo… Espera, ¿dónde "
"está…?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:183
msgid ""
"He's fine, we just got separated... by some hundreds of miles... I promise "
"I'll tell you everything you want, but first I need to know, what happened "
"here that the village of Aiyama was burnt to a cinder?"
msgstr ""
"Él está bien, solo nos separamos… por unos cientos de millas… Prometo que te "
"contaré todo lo que quieras, pero primero necesito saber qué pasó aquí para "
"que el pueblo de Aiyama quedara reducido a cenizas."

#. [message], speaker=Yamamoto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:187
msgid ""
"Wesnothians, that is what happened. But why they've decided to go on this "
"senseless rampage, we cannot tell. We had recently signed a truce-"
msgstr ""
"Wesnothianos, eso es lo que pasó. Pero por qué decidieron emprender esta "
"masacre sin sentido, no podemos decirlo. Recientemente habíamos firmado una "
"tregua"

#. [message], speaker=Ikki
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:191
msgid ""
"Don't pay this old man any attention, Tenma Yozora, it was because of that "
"truce that we had our guard lowere! I knew we should've kept fighting on "
"until either them or us lay dead, at least then we'd have a glorious death! "
"But now that you're with us again, Tenma Yozora, we shall triumph, just like "
"you triumphed that day at Kuroi against Prince Aetheryon himself!"
msgstr ""
"¡No le prestes atención a este viejo, Tenma Yozora, fue por esa tregua que "
"bajamos la guardia! ¡Sabía que debimos seguir luchando hasta que uno de los "
"dos quedara muerto, al menos entonces tendríamos una muerte gloriosa! Pero "
"ahora que estás con nosotros otra vez, Tenma Yozora, triunfaremos, ¡tal como "
"triunfaste aquel día en Kuroi contra el propio príncipe Aetheryon!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:195
msgid ""
"I'm afraid that there must some other reason behind this sudden attack; the "
"empire just recently suffered heavy losses in the west, it makes no sense "
"that they'd start another war here, even if to wipe us out, when they've "
"always kept us under control... But you're right about one thing, warrior: "
"we must stand our ground, fight the Wesnothians and free our country from "
"their rule once and for all!"
msgstr ""
"Me temo que debe haber alguna otra razón detrás de este ataque repentino; el "
"imperio acaba de sufrir grandes pérdidas en el oeste, no tiene sentido que "
"empiecen otra guerra aquí, ni siquiera para exterminarnos, cuando siempre "
"nos han mantenido bajo control… Pero tienes razón en una cosa, guerrero: "
"debemos mantenernos firmes, luchar contra los wesnothianos y liberar nuestro "
"país de su dominio de una vez por todas"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:199
msgid "<i>Thunderous roar</i>"
msgstr "<i>Rugido atronador</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Yamamoto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:203
msgid ""
"Natsu has told me of what you're capable of, my girl, and I trust my old "
"apprentice; with such power on our side, we may stand a chance. But you must "
"know that the Empire has strengthened its grip on Kodakuni these last "
"months: they now have mages, beasts and unholy creatures the likes of which "
"they never fielded against us before!"
msgstr ""
"Natsu me ha hablado de lo que eres capaz, muchacha, y confío en mi antigua "
"aprendiz; con tal poder de nuestro lado, podríamos tener una oportunidad. "
"Pero debes saber que el Imperio ha reforzado su control sobre Kodakuni estos "
"últimos meses: ahora tienen magos, bestias y criaturas impías del tipo que "
"nunca habían desplegado contra nosotros antes."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:207
msgid "Don't worry, Elder, I too have gotten stronger since I left..."
msgstr ""
"No te preocupes, Anciano, yo también me he vuelto más fuerte desde que me "
"fui…"

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:229
msgid "But, tell me, Tenma, is Kenshiro-"
msgstr "Pero dime, Tenma, ¿Kenshiro está—"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:233
msgid ""
"Geesh, Natsu, for a former Hachiman Priestess you really lose your focus "
"pretty easily, don't you? There's a battle going on, we'll have plenty of "
"time to... Ouch! Why did you hit me?!"
msgstr ""
"Cielos, Natsu, para ser una exsacerdotisa Hachiman realmente pierdes el "
"enfoque con facilidad, ¿no? Hay una batalla en curso, tendremos mucho tiempo "
"para… ¡Ay! ¿Por qué me pegaste?!"

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:237
msgid ""
"(menacing) Tenma Yozora, I don't care if you've become the strongest person "
"in the world, you <i>will</i> watch out how you talk to me, understand?"
msgstr ""
"(amenazante) Tenma Yozora, no me importa si te has convertido en la persona "
"más fuerte del mundo, <i>vas</i> a cuidar cómo me hablas, ¿entendido?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:241
msgid ""
"Fine, fine, whatever... Anyway, he couldn't be any better: he's healthy, "
"strong, happy, he's even got a beautiful elven princess as girlfriend..."
msgstr ""
"Está bien, está bien, como quieras… De todos modos, no podría estar mejor: "
"está sano, fuerte, feliz, incluso tiene una hermosa princesa elfa como novia…"

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:245
msgid ""
"He WHAT?! How dare he start a relationship with a woman without my "
"consent... Ah, I bet she took advantage of his innocence..."
msgstr ""
"¿¡QUÉ!? ¿Cómo se atreve a empezar una relación con una mujer sin mi "
"consentimiento…? Ah, apuesto a que ella se aprovechó de su inocencia…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:249
msgid ""
"Eh, well, she does take advantage of him sometimes... But anyway, don't get "
"all worried about him, he's no longer a little kid who needs protection; our "
"little boy has grown, Natsu, just deal with it."
msgstr ""
"Eh, bueno, a veces sí se aprovecha de él… Pero de todos modos, no te "
"preocupes tanto por él, ya no es un niño pequeño que necesita protección; "
"nuestro pequeño ha crecido, Natsu, solo acéptalo."

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:253
msgid "(pouting) But, still..."
msgstr "(haciendo pucheros) Pero, aun así…"

#. [message], speaker=Roddryr
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:271
msgid ""
"What the...?! How can this peasant be so powerful, even our mages cannot do "
"that!!!"
msgstr ""
"¿¡Qué demonios…?! ¿Cómo puede esta campesina ser tan poderosa, ni siquiera "
"nuestros magos pueden hacer eso!"

#. [message], speaker=Yamamoto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:275
msgid ""
"(astonished) Natsu, my dear, you told me she was strong, but I had no idea "
"just <i>how</i> strong..."
msgstr ""
"(asombrado) Natsu, querida, me dijiste que era fuerte, pero no tenía idea de "
"<i>cuán</i> fuerte…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:279
msgid ""
"(smirking) Well, I did have excellent teachers... Now, People of the "
"Steppes, follow me! Today we shall become the masters of our fates once "
"again!"
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo con picardía) Bueno, tuve excelentes maestros… ¡Ahora, Pueblo de "
"las Estepas, síganme! ¡Hoy volveremos a ser dueños de nuestro destino!"

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:283
msgid ""
"*Seems like our little boy wasn't the only one who has grown, Tenma... "
"Motoko, how I wish that you could see the woman your daughter has become...*"
msgstr ""
"*Parece que nuestro pequeño no fue el único que ha crecido, Tenma… Motoko, "
"cómo desearía que pudieras ver en qué mujer se ha convertido tu hija…*"

#. [message], speaker=Ikki
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:296
msgid ""
"VICTORY! With their main army destroyed, and with Tenma Yozora on our side, "
"nothing stands between us and our independence!"
msgstr ""
"¡VICTORIA! ¡Con su ejército principal destruido y con Tenma Yozora de "
"nuestro lado, nada se interpone entre nosotros y nuestra independencia!"

#. [message], speaker=Yamamoto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:308
msgid ""
"After so many years of suffering, we are the masters of our own fates once "
"again – and all thanks to you, Tenma Yozora, who first showed us that "
"Wesnoth could be defeated and... My girl, what are you doing? Do you want to "
"take the general as prisoner?"
msgstr ""
"Después de tantos años de sufrimiento, volvemos a ser dueños de nuestro "
"propio destino —y todo gracias a ti, Tenma Yozora, quien primero nos mostró "
"que Wesnoth podía ser derrotado y… Muchacha, ¿qué estás haciendo? ¿Quieres "
"tomar al general como prisionero?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:312
msgid ""
"Not exactly, I just need to know a few things... (to the general) Firstly, I "
"want to know why you've tried to destroy our very capital; I wouldn't be "
"surprised if that was an order by the emperor, but something tells me "
"there's more to that than it may seem – am I right?"
msgstr ""
"No exactamente, solo necesito saber algunas cosas… (al general) Primero, "
"quiero saber por qué intentaron destruir nuestra propia capital; no me "
"sorprendería si eso fue una orden del emperador, pero algo me dice que hay "
"más detrás de eso de lo que parece —tengo razón, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Roddryr
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:316
msgid ""
"(chuckling) The emperor, you say? Stupid yokels, are you even aware that "
"there is a world beyond those mountains...?"
msgstr ""
"(riendo) ¿El emperador, dices? Estúpidos palurdos, ¿siquiera son conscientes "
"de que hay un mundo más allá de esas montañas…?"

#. [message], speaker=Roddryr
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:320
msgid ""
"(coughs) Well, that won't make any difference now, will it... For many "
"weeks, we received no news, not even supplies, from the West. Then we "
"noticed that, of all the caravans we sent to Estfort, none returned. It was "
"then that we decided to send a messenger there, and see what was happening..."
msgstr ""
"(tosiendo) Bueno, eso ya no hará ninguna diferencia ahora, ¿verdad…? Durante "
"muchas semanas no recibimos noticias, ni siquiera suministros, del Oeste. "
"Luego notamos que, de todas las caravanas que enviamos a Estfort, ninguna "
"regresó. Fue entonces cuando decidimos enviar un mensajero allí, para ver "
"qué estaba pasando…"

#. [message], speaker=Roddryr
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:324
msgid ""
"He returned fifteen days later, much sooner than we expected, and we "
"rejoiced when we sighted him on the road; but when he got nearer, we could "
"see that he was covered in blood and burnings... He only had enough breath "
"to say that the emperor wouldn't come to our aid, and that, no matter what, "
"we must not go west, that we should rather go as far east as possible..."
msgstr ""
"Regresó quince días después, mucho antes de lo que esperábamos, y nos "
"alegramos al verlo en el camino; pero cuando se acercó, pudimos ver que "
"estaba cubierto de sangre y quemaduras… Solo tuvo aliento suficiente para "
"decir que el emperador no vendría en nuestra ayuda, y que, pasara lo que "
"pasara, no debíamos ir al oeste, que más bien debíamos ir lo más al este "
"posible…"

#. [message], speaker=Roddryr
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:328
msgid ""
"It was then that we knew... that something terrible had happened in Wesnoth, "
"and that it was probably lost to us... And so we decided to sack your little "
"towns and gather enough provisions for journeying into the Untamed East... "
"But now..."
msgstr ""
"Fue entonces cuando supimos… que algo terrible había sucedido en Wesnoth, y "
"que probablemente lo habíamos perdido… Y así decidimos saquear sus pequeños "
"pueblos y reunir suficientes provisiones para viajar hacia el Este Indómito… "
"Pero ahora…"

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:340
msgid "He's dead... Tenma, do you know the meaning of his words?"
msgstr "Está muerto… Tenma, ¿sabes qué significan sus palabras?"

#. [message], speaker=Ikki
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:344
msgid ""
"Bah, who cares about a tyrant's last words? If it's true that Wesnoth is "
"being destroyed, then all the better for us, as we won't have to worry about "
"retaliation!"
msgstr ""
"Bah, ¿a quién le importan las últimas palabras de un tirano? Si es cierto "
"que Wesnoth está siendo destruido, mejor para nosotros, ¡así no tendremos "
"que preocuparnos por represalias!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:348
msgid ""
"(serious) This is not as simple as it may seem, Ikki. I think I know what's "
"happening in the West, and I can assure you, the destruction won't stop at "
"that empire, it'll engulf us eventually – and when it does, we won't stand a "
"chance, not on our own, not even with my power."
msgstr ""
"(seria) Esto no es tan simple como parece, Ikki. Creo que sé qué está "
"pasando en el Oeste, y te aseguro que la destrucción no se detendrá en ese "
"imperio, eventualmente nos alcanzará —y cuando lo haga, no tendremos ninguna "
"oportunidad, no solos, ni siquiera con mi poder."

#. [message], speaker=Yamamoto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:352
msgid ""
"Is there a foe stronger than you, who made the Wesnothian mages look like "
"mere tricksters?!"
msgstr ""
"¿Hay un enemigo más fuerte que tú, que hizo que los magos wesnothianos "
"parecieran meros charlatanes?!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:356
msgid ""
"Yes... And because of him I can't tarry here any longer; I must go west "
"again and see what exactly is happening, and do what I can to stop him..."
msgstr ""
"Sí… Y por su culpa no puedo quedarme aquí más tiempo; debo ir al oeste otra "
"vez y ver exactamente qué está pasando, y hacer lo que pueda para detenerlo…"

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:360
msgid ""
"Wait, why do you need to? There are many powerful kingdoms in the West; why "
"don't you let them deal with this foe first?"
msgstr ""
"Espera, ¿por qué necesitas hacerlo? Hay muchos reinos poderosos en el Oeste; "
"¿por qué no los dejas lidiar con este enemigo primero?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:364
msgid ""
"Dwarves, trolls, elves, Wesnothians – they could all unite their entire "
"armies against this foe, and they'd still fail. This enemy I'm talking about "
"is no normal creature: many powerful beings have tried to destroy him "
"through the ages, and they've all failed. What is worse, now he may have an "
"equally terrible enemy by his side..."
msgstr ""
"Enanos, trolls, elfos, wesnothianos —todos podrían unir sus ejércitos "
"enteros contra este enemigo y aun así fallarían. El enemigo del que hablo no "
"es una criatura normal: muchos seres poderosos han intentado destruirlo a lo "
"largo de las edades, y todos han fallado. Peor aún, ahora podría tener a un "
"enemigo igualmente terrible a su lado…"

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:368
msgid ""
"In that case, I'm going with you, Tenma. I refuse to sit idly while both you "
"and Kenshiro risk your lives, not again. I know I'm not a great aid in "
"pitched battle, but I can heal nearly every wound and illness, and if this "
"enemy is so powerful, you'll need every friendly hand you can afford. I'd "
"even say that the Sogen warriors should follow you as well."
msgstr ""
"En ese caso, voy contigo, Tenma. Me niego a quedarme de brazos cruzados "
"mientras tanto tú como Kenshiro arriesgan sus vidas, no otra vez. Sé que no "
"soy de gran ayuda en batalla campal, pero puedo curar casi cualquier herida "
"y enfermedad, y si este enemigo es tan poderoso, necesitarás toda mano amiga "
"que puedas tener. Incluso diría que los guerreros sogen deberían seguirte "
"también."

#. [message], speaker=Ikki
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:372
msgid ""
"What?! Do you seriously want us leave our homes which we've just reconquered "
"to fight a distant war that doesn't concern us?!"
msgstr ""
"¿¡Qué!? ¿En serio quieres que dejemos nuestros hogares que acabamos de "
"reconquistar para pelear una guerra lejana que no nos concierne?!"

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:376
msgid ""
"Didn't you hear what Tenma said? This war in the West has everything to do "
"with us; you may rejoice that Wesnoth is in danger, but if it falls to such "
"enemy, soon we may be facing an even worse tyrant!"
msgstr ""
"¿No escuchaste lo que dijo Tenma? Esta guerra en el Oeste tiene todo que ver "
"con nosotros; puedes alegrarte de que Wesnoth esté en peligro, ¡pero si cae "
"ante tal enemigo, pronto podríamos enfrentarnos a un tirano aún peor!"

#. [message], speaker=Ikki
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:380
msgid "Yeah, well, that's what <i>she</i> says..."
msgstr "Sí, bueno, eso es lo que <i>ella</i> dice…"

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:384
msgid ""
"And <i>I</i> trust her with my own life! I know the girl I've raised, and "
"there's no person more honest than her in this entire world!"
msgstr ""
"¡Y <i>yo</i> confío en ella con mi propia vida! ¡Conozco a la chica que "
"crié, y no hay persona más honesta que ella en todo este mundo!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:388
msgid "Natsu...!"
msgstr "¡Natsu…!"

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:396
msgid ""
"I... I too believe our saviour. She's one of us, after all, and she's fought "
"and bled to win us our independence; I don't think she'd lead us to our "
"deaths, not for an unworthy cause."
msgstr ""
"Yo… yo también creo en nuestra salvadora. Después de todo es una de "
"nosotros, y ha luchado y sangrado para ganarnos nuestra independencia; no "
"creo que nos llevaría a la muerte por una causa indigna."

#. [message], speaker=Yamamoto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:400
msgid ""
"I sense wisdom and honesty in young Tenma's words; I'm too old for "
"journeying and battling, but I will put half of Umashima's warriors and "
"priestesses in your care; please, lead them well, and lead them back to our "
"home."
msgstr ""
"Siento sabiduría y honestidad en las palabras de la joven Tenma; soy "
"demasiado viejo para viajar y luchar, pero pondré a la mitad de los "
"guerreros y sacerdotisas de Umashima bajo tu cuidado; por favor, guíalos "
"bien y llévalos de regreso a nuestro hogar."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:404
msgid ""
"I promise I'll do my best, Elder... What about you, Ikki? You're a disciple "
"of Mad Dog Kyouken, and you've fought for our people for much longer than I "
"have; you deserve to be the leader of our warriors much more than I do."
msgstr ""
"Prometo que haré lo mejor, Anciano… ¿Y tú, Ikki? Eres discípulo del Perro "
"Loco Kyouken, y has luchado por nuestro pueblo mucho más tiempo que yo; "
"mereces ser el líder de nuestros guerreros mucho más que yo."

#. [message], speaker=Ikki
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:408
msgid ""
"I... (sigh) Well, I too don't think that you'd ask such a thing of us "
"without an excellent reason, and I too see no deceit in your eyes. Besides, "
"I've always wanted to see the world beyond the mountains... So, yes, I will "
"follow you to the west."
msgstr ""
"Yo… (suspiro) Bueno, tampoco creo que nos pedirías algo así sin una "
"excelente razón, y tampoco veo engaño en tus ojos. Además, siempre he "
"querido ver el mundo más allá de las montañas… Así que sí, te seguiré al "
"oeste."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:412
msgid "Thank you, Ikki, everyone..."
msgstr "Gracias, Ikki, todos…"

#. [message], speaker=Ikki
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:416
msgid ""
"So it shall be, but not even you can ask us to leave before due celebration; "
"we've fought too hard for our Independence Day not to enjoy it!"
msgstr ""
"Así será, pero ni siquiera tú puedes pedirnos que nos vayamos sin la "
"celebración debida; ¡hemos luchado demasiado por nuestro Día de la "
"Independencia como para no disfrutarlo!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:433
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:289
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:694
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1395
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1730
msgid "How could I have fallen now...?"
msgstr "¿Cómo pude caer ahora…?"

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:447
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:303
msgid "I... can't... die..."
msgstr "Yo… no puedo… morir…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:451
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:307
msgid "NATSU, NO!!!"
msgstr "¡¡¡NATSU, NO!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Ikki
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:465
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:321
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1497
msgid "Argh! Curses on these Wesnothians...!"
msgstr "¡Argh! ¡Malditos wesnothianos…!"

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:469
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:325
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1501
msgid ""
"Ikki was an important leader amongst our people, without him we'll have a "
"hard time fighting the Wesnothians!"
msgstr ""
"Ikki era un líder importante entre nuestro pueblo, ¡sin él tendremos muchas "
"dificultades para luchar contra los wesnothianos!"

#. [message], speaker=Yamamoto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:483
msgid "Alas, I have failed to defend our ancient city..."
msgstr "Ay, he fallado en defender nuestra antigua ciudad…"

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:487
msgid "Elder, no!"
msgstr "¡Anciano, no!"

#. [message], speaker=Ikki
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:491
msgid ""
"Damn it, the old man was the only one with enought authority to command all "
"of the Sogen clans! Without him, we're bound to be disunited!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldición, el viejo era el único con suficiente autoridad para comandar a "
"todos los clanes sogen! ¡Sin él estamos condenados a la desunión!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/39_Odysseys_End_II.cfg:502
msgid ""
"Damn it all, I can't waste so much time when Galdra and Svarballi may be "
"destroying the world already!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldita sea todo, no puedo perder tanto tiempo cuando Galdra y Svarballi ya "
"podrían estar destruyendo el mundo!"

#. [scenario], id=40_Tides_Of_Destruction_I
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:4
msgid "Father and Son"
msgstr "Padre e Hijo"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:19
msgid "Defeat Emperor Taryen"
msgstr "Derrotar al emperador Taryen"

#. [message], speaker=Aethra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:121
msgid "Brother..."
msgstr "Hermano…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:125
msgid ""
"Aethra, please stop. I will no longer stand idle while our father sends "
"soldiers to their deaths; he <i>will</i> hear me, whether he wants to or "
"not..."
msgstr ""
"Aethra, por favor para. No seguiré de brazos cruzados mientras nuestro padre "
"envía soldados a su muerte; <i>me escuchará</i>, quiera o no…"

#. [message], speaker=Caer
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:133
msgid "(surprised) Y-your Highness...!"
msgstr "(sorprendido) ¡S-su Alteza…!"

#. [message], speaker=Taryen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:137
msgid "(darkly) I do not recall summoning you to my presence, boy."
msgstr "(sombrío) No recuerdo haberte convocado a mi presencia, muchacho."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:141
msgid ""
"I came here on my own accord, Emperor. You have nothing to complain, after "
"all I am just showing initiative, like a 'true heir of the Iron Dynasty' is "
"wont to do."
msgstr ""
"Vine aquí por mi propia voluntad, Emperador. No tienes nada de qué quejarte, "
"después de todo solo estoy mostrando iniciativa, como corresponde a un "
"«verdadero heredero de la Dinastía de Hierro»."

#. [message], speaker=Taryen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:145
msgid ""
"(smiling sardonically) And what relevant information does the new Crown "
"Prince has to offer his father and emperor?"
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo sarcásticamente) ¿Y qué información relevante tiene el nuevo "
"Príncipe Heredero para ofrecer a su padre y emperador?"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:149
msgid ""
"*Speaking as if Aeldhoryan's already dead, so typical of him...* I request "
"that you give me command over the army. Many legions have been lost already "
"to Galdra's rampage because nobody knows how to deal with her creations, let "
"alone with the summoner herself. But I know her better than anyone else, and "
"so I know how to counter her. Thus, I deem myself the one most fitting to "
"lead our forces against her."
msgstr ""
"*Hablando como si Aeldhoryan ya estuviera muerto, tan típico de él…* "
"Solicito que me des el mando del ejército. Muchas legiones ya se han perdido "
"por la masacre de Galdra porque nadie sabe cómo lidiar con sus creaciones, "
"ni mucho menos con la invocadora misma. Pero yo la conozco mejor que nadie, "
"y por eso sé cómo contrarrestarla. Por lo tanto, me considero el más apto "
"para liderar nuestras fuerzas contra ella."

#. [message], speaker=Taryen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:153
msgid ""
"You 'deem yourself the one most fitting'... Very well, boy, my turn to speak "
"my mind. I deem you the one <i>least</i> fitting in this kingdom to lecture "
"anyone on how to deal with this problem, as you were the one who brought it "
"upon us, to begin with."
msgstr ""
"Tú «te consideras el más apto»… Muy bien, muchacho, me toca hablar a mí. Te "
"considero el <i>menos</i> apto en este reino para dar lecciones a nadie "
"sobre cómo lidiar con este problema, ya que fuiste tú quien lo trajo sobre "
"nosotros, para empezar."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:157
msgid "I know that I have some responsibility to take, but..."
msgstr "Sé que tengo cierta responsabilidad que asumir, pero…"

#. [message], speaker=Taryen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:161
msgid ""
"Now, your request does have an interesting timing. I have tormented myself "
"with doubts for the last months, for I refused to believe that even the "
"least of my sons would dare so much, but your words have now betrayed you. I "
"see through your schemes, son: you have unleashed your Arajunnan whore upon "
"my country, to make people doubt my ability to steer my empire, and now you "
"seek to lead us to 'victory' so as to present yourself as the one <i>most "
"fitting</i> to rule!"
msgstr ""
"Ahora, tu petición tiene un momento muy interesante. Me he atormentado con "
"dudas durante los últimos meses, porque me negaba a creer que incluso el "
"menor de mis hijos se atreviera tanto, pero tus palabras ahora te han "
"traicionado. Veo a través de tus planes, hijo: has desatado a tu ramera "
"arajunna sobre mi país, para hacer que la gente dude de mi capacidad para "
"gobernar mi imperio, ¡y ahora buscas llevarnos a la «victoria» para "
"presentarte como el <i>más apto</i> para gobernar!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:165
msgid ""
"The Iron Crown has damaged your brains, emperor. You should know how much I "
"hate ruling: it was begrudgingly that I accepted to govern even small "
"Kodakuni; were I ti rule the whole empire for even three weeks, I would go "
"madder than even you."
msgstr ""
"La Corona de Hierro te ha dañado el cerebro, emperador. Deberías saber "
"cuánto odio gobernar: de mala gana acepté gobernar incluso el pequeño "
"Kodakuni; si tuviera que gobernar todo el imperio aunque fuera tres semanas, "
"me volvería más loco que tú."

#. [message], speaker=Taryen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:169
msgid "(enraged) Impudent boy, it is about time I gave you a LESSON!"
msgstr "(enfurecido) ¡Muchacho insolente, ya es hora de que te dé una LECCIÓN!"

#. [message], speaker=Aethra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:183
msgid "Father, brother...!!!"
msgstr "¡Padre, hermano…!"

#. [message], speaker=Taryen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:187
msgid ""
"I hereby disown my offspring, the twins Aetheryon and Aethra, and brand the "
"both of them traitors to the empire! Guards, arrest her; I shall deal with "
"this vermin myself..."
msgstr ""
"Por la presente repudio a mi descendencia, los gemelos Aetheryon y Aethra, "
"¡y los declaro a ambos traidores al imperio! ¡Guardias, arréstenla; yo mismo "
"me encargaré de esta alimaña…!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:191
msgid ""
"(enraged) How dare you do that to you daughter?! She hasn't done anything!"
msgstr ""
"(enfurecido) ¿¡Cómo te atreves a hacerle eso a tu hija?! ¡Ella no ha hecho "
"nada!"

#. [message], speaker=Fethanir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:195
msgid "M-my lord Emperor, please rethink yo-"
msgstr "M-mi señor Emperador, por favor reconsidérelo—"

#. [message], speaker=Elcadar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:202
msgid "(shocked) Fe-Fethanir...!!!"
msgstr "(impactado) ¡Fe-Fethanir…!"

#. [message], speaker=Taryen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:206
msgid "Nobody is to interfere; this is a matter between father and son!"
msgstr "¡Nadie debe interferir; esto es un asunto entre padre e hijo!"

#. [message], speaker=Aethra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:227
msgid "(screams in pain) Stop...!"
msgstr "(grita de dolor) ¡Para…!"

#. [message], speaker=Ruddryn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:231
msgid ""
"Apologies, Your Majesty, she would not restrain herself, and so we had to "
"stun her..."
msgstr "Disculpas, Su Majestad, no se contenía, así que tuvimos que aturdirla…"

#. [message], speaker=Taryen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:235
msgid ""
"Let it not trouble you, guard; you may use force to contain her – and if she "
"keeps fighting, I allow you to kill her."
msgstr ""
"Que no te preocupe, guardia; puedes usar la fuerza para contenerla —y si "
"sigue luchando, te permito matarla."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:239
msgid "(trembling in rage) You... how... how DARE YOU!!!"
msgstr "(temblando de rabia) Tú… cómo… ¡¿CÓMO TE ATREVES?!"

#. [message], speaker=Taryen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:249
msgid "(astonished) Y-you...!"
msgstr "(asombrado) ¡T-tú…!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:253
msgid "(darkly) Farewell, father..."
msgstr "(sombrío) Adiós, padre…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:264
msgid ""
"(coldly) I have slain the Emperor of Wesnoth in fair duel; I invoke the Law "
"of Strength and the Law of Inheritance to claim the Iron Crown for myself. "
"Is there anyone here who stands in opposition my claim?"
msgstr ""
"(fríamente) He matado al Emperador de Wesnoth en duelo justo; invoco la Ley "
"de la Fuerza y la Ley de la Herencia para reclamar la Corona de Hierro para "
"mí. ¿Hay alguien aquí que se oponga a mi reclamo?"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:273
msgid "Good. Now..."
msgstr "Bien. Ahora…"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:277
msgid ""
"<i>picks the Iron Crown and the Sceptre of Fire from his father's corpse</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>toma la Corona de Hierro y el Cetro de Fuego del cadáver de su padre</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Elcadar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:306
msgid "M-my prince, it is not the custom that a new emperor crowns himself..."
msgstr ""
"M-mi príncipe, no es la costumbre que un nuevo emperador se corone a sí "
"mismo…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:310
msgid ""
"If the customs do not conform to my will, I will bend them to it; and if "
"anyone disagrees with that, I will either convince them to see my point, or "
"wave them aside. After all, it is within my power to do so – and power, in "
"this empire, is everything. Do you disagree, Elcadar?"
msgstr ""
"Si las costumbres no se ajustan a mi voluntad, las doblegaré a ella; y si "
"alguien no está de acuerdo, o los convenceré de ver mi punto, o los "
"apartaré. Después de todo, está dentro de mi poder hacerlo —y el poder, en "
"este imperio, lo es todo. ¿Estás en desacuerdo, Elcadar?"

#. [message], speaker=Elcadar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:314
msgid "N-no, absolutely not, my prin... I mean, my Emperor..."
msgstr "N-no, absolutamente no, mi prin… quiero decir, mi Emperador…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:318
msgid "Good..."
msgstr "Bien…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:325
msgid ""
"I'm sorry that you had to see all this, sister, but now everything will be "
"fine..."
msgstr ""
"Lamento que hayas tenido que ver todo esto, hermana, pero ahora todo va a "
"estar bien..."

#. [message], speaker=Aethra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:329
msgid ""
"No... <i>nothing</i> will be fine, brother, you... you've just killed our "
"father!"
msgstr ""
"No... <i>nada</i> va a estar bien, hermano, tú... ¡acabas de matar a nuestro "
"padre!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:333
msgid ""
"Did you not hear him, sister? He did not see us as his children any more, "
"which means that he was no longer our father. But I will not be harsh on "
"you; I just ask you to try and understand it, and most importantly... Stay "
"by my side... please. I need you now more than ever before. Elcadar and one "
"of the guards will escort you to the healing chambers; as for the other one, "
"I shall have him take the former emperor's body to the funerary chamber."
msgstr ""
"¿No lo escuchaste, hermana? Ya no nos veía como sus hijos, lo que significa "
"que él ya no era nuestro padre. Pero no voy a ser duro contigo; solo te pido "
"que intentes entenderlo, y lo más importante… quédate a mi lado… por favor. "
"Te necesito ahora más que nunca. Elcadar y uno de los guardias te escoltarán "
"a las cámaras de sanación; en cuanto al otro, haré que lleve el cuerpo del "
"antiguo emperador a la cámara funeraria."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:357
msgid "Now, Galdra, it's just the two of us..."
msgstr "Ahora, Galdra, solo quedamos nosotros dos..."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction.cfg:383
msgid "I... die...?!"
msgstr "Yo… ¿morir…?"

#. [scenario], id=40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:5
msgid "Tides of Destruction"
msgstr "Mareas de la Destrucción"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:26
msgid "Destroy the undead general"
msgstr "Destruye al general no muerto"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:42
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:39
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:374
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:626
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:46
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:735
msgid "Death of Veshtar Joohn"
msgstr "Muerte de Veshtar Joohn"

#. [side], type=Death Knight
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:94
msgid "Lord Gaios"
msgstr "Señor Gaios"

#. [side], type=Death Knight
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:100
msgid "Undead Army"
msgstr "Ejército No Muerto"

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:145
msgid "Careful, everyone, I see some dangerous-looking beasts ahead!"
msgstr "¡Cuidado, todos, veo unas bestias de aspecto peligroso más adelante!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:149
msgid ""
"Wait, those are drakes, and I know their leader... Hail, Mother Queen "
"Veshtar Joohn! Do you remember me?"
msgstr ""
"Espera, son dracos, y conozco a su líder… ¡Saludos, Reina Madre Veshtar "
"Joohn! ¿Te acuerdas de mí?"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:153
msgid ""
"Even in a hundred years I would not forget you, Tenma Yozora. I also "
"remember that you were always in the company of the Crimson Sorceress and of "
"two other humans; have you split up?"
msgstr ""
"Ni en cien años te olvidaría, Tenma Yozora. También recuerdo que siempre "
"estabas acompañada de la Hechicera Carmesí y de otros dos humanos; ¿se "
"separaron?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:157
msgid ""
"Yes, but not because we wanted to... Anyway, why are you so far south? Has "
"it anything to do with whatever is happening in Wesnoth?"
msgstr ""
"Sí, pero no porque quisiéramos… De todos modos, ¿por qué estás tan al sur? "
"¿Tiene algo que ver con lo que está pasando en Wesnoth?"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:161
msgid ""
"I care not about that country; what I know is that a new necromancer has "
"risen in the north, leading an army of undead the likes of which I have "
"never seen before. He invaded the Emerald Plains about four weeks ago; I "
"sent some warriors to Dragana Vasilya's aid, but we haven't fully recovered "
"from the war against my brother, so our numbers are very reduced. Mhreghost "
"fell shortly later."
msgstr ""
"No me importa ese país; lo que sé es que un nuevo nigromante ha surgido en "
"el norte, liderando un ejército de no muertos como nunca antes había visto. "
"Invadió las Llanuras Esmeralda hace unas cuatro semanas; envié algunos "
"guerreros en ayuda de Dragana Vasilya, pero aún no nos hemos recuperado del "
"todo de la guerra contra mi hermano, así que nuestros números son muy "
"reducidos. Mhreghost cayó poco después."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:165
msgid "Then, Dragana is...?"
msgstr "¿Entonces Dragana está…?"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:169
msgid ""
"Ah, that woman would gladly die beneath the ruins of her city, but her "
"subjects know better: they knocked her out and evacuated Mhreghost and all "
"other Baryag cities, withdrawing into the Lins-Elens. I prepared my army to "
"oppose the necromancer, but..."
msgstr ""
"Ah, esa mujer moriría gustosa bajo las ruinas de su ciudad, pero sus "
"súbditos saben más: la dejaron inconsciente y evacuaron Mhreghost y todas "
"las demás ciudades barjanas, retirándose a los Lins-Elens. Preparé mi "
"ejército para enfrentarme al nigromante, pero…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:173
msgid "Not even the drakes were able to stop him, then?!"
msgstr "¿Entonces ni siquiera los dracos pudieron detenerlo?"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:177
msgid ""
"(annoyed) Well, to put it briefly, I followed the Baryags' example and took "
"my people out of the Kehshakaar before he reached my capital. I ordered "
"three-quarters of my army to reinforce the elves and the Baryags, and then I "
"came here myself, to ask for Valerya's aid; but not only did I fail to find "
"her, I've also been caught by one of the necromancer's undead generals. I've "
"been fighting him alongside Valerya's students for three days already, to no "
"avail."
msgstr ""
"(molesta) Bueno, para decirlo brevemente, seguí el ejemplo de los barjanes y "
"saqué a mi pueblo de Kehshakaar antes de que llegara a mi capital. Ordené "
"que tres cuartas partes de mi ejército reforzaran a los elfos y a los "
"barjanes, y luego vine yo misma a pedir ayuda a Valerya; pero no solo no la "
"encontré, sino que además fui alcanzada por uno de los generales no muertos "
"del nigromante. Llevo tres días luchando contra él junto a los estudiantes "
"de Valerya, sin éxito."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:181
msgid ""
"Well, you may not have found her, but you have found me! Come, we'll help "
"you get rid of those undead; afterwards, I have a few things I want to talk "
"with you about..."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, puede que no la hayas encontrado a ella, ¡pero me encontraste a mí! "
"Ven, te ayudaremos a deshacerte de esos no muertos; después quiero hablar "
"contigo de algunas cosas…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:193
msgid "These undead seem strangely familiar..."
msgstr "Estos no muertos me parecen extrañamente familiares…"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:197
msgid ""
"You can confirm their owner's identity if you follow me to the Lins-Elens. "
"They should still be battling by now; I fear not even the King-in-the-Woods' "
"power can easily destroy that necromancer."
msgstr ""
"Puedes confirmar la identidad de su dueño si me sigues a los Lins-Elens. "
"Deberían seguir luchando todavía; temo que ni siquiera el poder del Rey-en-"
"el-Bosque pueda destruir fácilmente a ese nigromante."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:201
msgid ""
"That's exactly what I intend to do, but there's something else I'm concerned "
"about right now – something that concerns you, Veshtar Joohn."
msgstr ""
"Eso es exactamente lo que pienso hacer, pero hay algo más que me preocupa en "
"este momento… algo que te concierne a ti, Veshtar Joohn."

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:205
msgid ""
"Speak it, then; I have seen enough of you to trust the wisdom of your words."
msgstr ""
"Habla entonces; he visto suficiente de ti como para confiar en la sabiduría "
"de tus palabras."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:209
msgid ""
"See, do you know anything about the Brilliant Flame? I know that it was a "
"powerful artefact owned by Agniballi, and which was considered the drakes' "
"greatest power..."
msgstr ""
"Mira, ¿sabes algo sobre la Llama Brillante? Sé que era un artefacto poderoso "
"que poseía Agniballi, y que se consideraba el mayor poder de los dracos…"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:213
msgid ""
"You never tire of impressing me, Tenma Yozora... Indeed, the Brilliant Flame "
"is our people's greatest power, though it wasn't an artefact, but a magical "
"flame, given life by Great Agniballi himself. According to the legend, the "
"Brilliant Flame is made of the same fire that burns in the sun - and like "
"the sun itself, it burns eternal."
msgstr ""
"Nunca dejas de impresionarme, Tenma Yozora… En efecto, la Llama Brillante es "
"el mayor poder de nuestro pueblo, aunque no era un artefacto, sino una llama "
"mágica, dotada de vida por el propio Gran Agniballi. Según la leyenda, la "
"Llama Brillante está hecha del mismo fuego que arde en el sol… y como el sol "
"mismo, arde eternamente."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:217
msgid ""
"Then, if it's eternal, is it still burning somewhere in this world? Or has "
"it disappeared along with Agniballi?"
msgstr ""
"Entonces, si es eterna, ¿sigue ardiendo en algún lugar de este mundo? ¿O "
"desapareció junto con Agniballi?"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:221
msgid ""
"It is told that the flame still burned when the dragons abandoned Aghayu, "
"the old seat of power of Dragons' Land, by which time Great Agniballi was no "
"longer alive... But why do you ask me about my people's history when we have "
"far more urgent matters to attend?"
msgstr ""
"Se cuenta que la llama aún ardía cuando los dragones abandonaron Aghayu, la "
"antigua sede del poder de la Tierra de los Dragones, para entonces el Gran "
"Agniballi ya no estaba vivo… Pero ¿por qué me preguntas por la historia de "
"mi pueblo cuando tenemos asuntos mucho más urgentes que atender?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:225
msgid ""
"I'm asking that because you'll need it for what is going to happen in a very "
"near future. You-"
msgstr ""
"Te lo pregunto porque lo vas a necesitar para lo que va a ocurrir en un "
"futuro muy cercano. Tú—"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:229
msgid ""
"Hold on, are you suggesting I should lay my claws on our most sacred "
"treasure, which not even the great dragons of old could handle?! Do not "
"overestimate me, Tenma Yozora; I am strong and capable, but I am also humble "
"enough to see that I am not worthy of such power!"
msgstr ""
"Espera, ¿estás sugiriendo que debería poner mis garras sobre nuestro tesoro "
"más sagrado, que ni siquiera los grandes dragones antiguos pudieron manejar? "
"¡No me sobreestimes, Tenma Yozora! Soy fuerte y capaz, pero también lo "
"suficientemente humilde como para ver que no soy digna de tal poder."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:233
msgid ""
"Think about it, Veshtar Joohn. I know that Agniballi cared deeply about his "
"people, but he still had enough kindness to respect other beings' right to "
"exist and live freely. Besides, surely other dragons sought the Flame after "
"Agniballi was gone, and yet your tales claim none ever managed to wield it. "
"My guess is that, just like Nitiballi didn't allow certain beings to draw "
"from what was left of his powers in the Fountain of Life; Agniballi made "
"sure that the Flame would never be used for ends which he wouldn't approve."
msgstr ""
"Piénsalo, Veshtar Joohn. Sé que Agniballi quería profundamente a su pueblo, "
"pero aún así tuvo la bondad suficiente para respetar el derecho de otros "
"seres a existir y vivir libremente. Además, seguro que otros dragones "
"buscaron la Llama después de que Agniballi desapareciera, y sin embargo las "
"leyendas dicen que ninguno logró manejarla. Mi teoría es que, igual que "
"Nitiballi no permitió que ciertos seres extrajeran lo que quedaba de sus "
"poderes en la Fuente de la Vida, Agniballi se aseguró de que la Llama nunca "
"fuera usada para fines que él no aprobaría."

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:237
msgid "I see... But why would I even use it? If it's about the necromancer..."
msgstr ""
"Entiendo… Pero ¿por qué siquiera iba a usarla? Si es por el nigromante…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:241
msgid ""
"This necromancer is nothing compared to the beings which have recently been "
"awakened. I'm talking about the High Dragon of the Sky, Svarballi..."
msgstr ""
"Este nigromante no es nada comparado con los seres que han sido despertados "
"recientemente. Estoy hablando del Alto Dragón del Cielo, Svarballi…"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:245
msgid ""
"(frightened) Do you mean the Sky Dragon? Has he... Has he been freed again?! "
"(after a while) Still, even if I do manage to master the Flame, how will it "
"be enough to destroy Svarballi, when even Great Agniballi himself failed to "
"do so?"
msgstr ""
"(asustada) ¿Te refieres al Dragón del Cielo? ¿Acaso… ha sido liberado otra "
"vez? (tras una pausa) Aun así, aunque lograra dominar la Llama, ¿cómo sería "
"suficiente para destruir a Svarballi, cuando ni siquiera el Gran Agniballi "
"pudo hacerlo?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:249
msgid ""
"You won't be alone. I plan on gathering all of the greatest powers of this "
"world's people, the Kings' Regalia, so that we can face this threat together "
"– because, this time, we won't be fighting only Svarballi."
msgstr ""
"No estarás sola. Planeo reunir todos los mayores poderes de los pueblos de "
"este mundo, las Regalias de los Reyes, para que podamos enfrentar esta "
"amenaza juntos… porque esta vez no lucharemos solo contra Svarballi."

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:256
msgid ""
"I sense that you speak the truth, Tenma Yozora; although it goes against my "
"people's traditions, I will search for the lost city of Aghayu and find "
"Great Agniballi's relic. I only hope that the Agnirakshai who guarded that "
"city are not as strong as legend has them..."
msgstr ""
"Siento que hablas con verdad, Tenma Yozora; aunque va en contra de las "
"tradiciones de mi pueblo, buscaré la ciudad perdida de Aghayu y encontraré "
"la reliquia del Gran Agniballi. Solo espero que los Agnirakshai que "
"custodiaban esa ciudad no sean tan fuertes como dice la leyenda…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:260
msgid ""
"Then I'll go with you, and make sure that you're unharmed. Ikki, Natsu, "
"please stay at the academy with the others, our warriors are too tired and "
"wounded to go into such a hot desert; I'll leave some spirits guarding it "
"until we're back."
msgstr ""
"Entonces iré contigo y me aseguraré de que no sufras daño. Ikki, Natsu, por "
"favor quédense en la academia con los demás, nuestros guerreros están "
"demasiado cansados y heridos para entrar en un desierto tan caluroso; dejaré "
"algunos espíritus vigilándolo hasta que regresemos."

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:264
msgid ""
"If you say so... (suddenly threatening) You, big one! Tenma is risking her "
"life to help you and your people, so don't you dare let her get harmed, "
"understand?"
msgstr ""
"Si tú lo dices… (de repente amenazante) ¡Tú, grandote! Tenma está "
"arriesgando su vida para ayudarte a ti y a tu pueblo, así que no te atrevas "
"a dejar que le pase algo, ¿entendido?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:268
msgid "Natsu, stop embarrassing me...!"
msgstr "¡Natsu, deja de avergonzarme…!"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:272
msgid ""
"(laughing) Mothers really are all the same, regardless of race... I am a "
"mother myself, tiny one, so I understand your feelings. Worry not, for I do "
"not allow my friends to die when I can do anything about it. Now, Tenma "
"Yozora, climb on my hand; we have no time to waste, and so we shall fly!"
msgstr ""
"(riendo) Las madres realmente son todas iguales, sin importar la raza… Yo "
"también soy madre, pequeña, así que entiendo tus sentimientos. No te "
"preocupes, no permito que mis amigos mueran cuando puedo hacer algo al "
"respecto. Ahora, Tenma Yozora, súbete a mi mano; no tenemos tiempo que "
"perder, ¡así que volaremos!"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:339
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:723
msgid "How shameful that I could not protect my children...!"
msgstr "¡Qué vergüenza que no pude proteger a mis hijos…!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:343
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:727
msgid "No! Without the Mother Queen on our side, we've lost a powerful ally!"
msgstr ""
"¡No! ¡Sin la Reina Madre de nuestro lado hemos perdido una aliada poderosa!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/40_Tides_Of_Destruction_II.cfg:356
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:740
msgid ""
"Damn it all, we can't waste so much time here, not when Galdra and Svarballi "
"are probably destroying the world already!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldición, no podemos perder tanto tiempo aquí, no cuando Galdra y "
"Svarballi probablemente ya están destruyendo el mundo!"

#. [scenario], id=41_Brilliant_Flame
#. [attack], type=fire, range=ranged
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:5
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/irdya-kings/Queen_in_the_Air.cfg:81
msgid "Brilliant Flame"
msgstr "Llama Brillante"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:27
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:362
msgid "Locate the Brilliant Flame"
msgstr "Localiza la Llama Brillante"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:31
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:366
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:618
msgid ""
"NOTE: The heatwave of Aghayu scorches everyone (except drakes, fire "
"elementals, nightmares and aberrations) causing them to lose hp and 2 attack "
"points every turn. The effect happens during both day and night, but can be "
"stalled by healers or avoided by standing in a village."
msgstr ""
"NOTA: La ola de calor de Aghayu abrasa a todos (excepto dracos, elementales "
"de fuego, pesadillas y aberraciones) haciéndoles perder PV y 2 puntos de "
"ataque cada turno. El efecto ocurre tanto de día como de noche, pero puede "
"detenerse con sanadores o evitarse permaneciendo en una aldea."

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:43
msgid "NOTE: Tenma may recruit at the hexes adjacent to 49,12."
msgstr "NOTA: Tenma puede reclutar en los hexágonos adyacentes a 49,12."

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:91
msgid "Ruins"
msgstr "Ruinas"

#. [side], type=Eternal Night
#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:105
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:146
msgid "Nightmare Swarm"
msgstr "Enjambre de Pesadillas"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:159
msgid "Geesh, to think this entire region used to be a volcano in the past..."
msgstr "Caray, pensar que toda esta región solía ser un volcán en el pasado…"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:163
msgid ""
"Impressed by its magnitude, are you? Now, picture this crater overcrowded "
"with the mightiest drakes, the air heavy with the wingbeat of dragons; "
"imagine these ruined towers as they must have looked before they crumbled "
"down, rising high into the skies, filled with newborn dragons and drakes; "
"and imagine the mightiest of all fire dragons, Agniballi himself, standing "
"atop the highest tower, the legendary Agni-Tavar... Such was the lost city "
"of Aghayu at the peak of its glory."
msgstr ""
"¿Impresionada por su magnitud? Ahora imagina este cráter abarrotado con los "
"dracos más poderosos, el aire cargado con el batir de alas de dragones; "
"imagina estas torres en ruinas como debían verse antes de derrumbarse, "
"elevándose alto en el cielo, llenas de dragones y dracos recién nacidos; e "
"imagina al más poderoso de todos los dragones de fuego, el propio Agniballi, "
"de pie en lo alto de la torre más elevada, la legendaria Agni-Tavar… Así era "
"la ciudad perdida de Aghayu en el apogeo de su gloria."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:167
msgid "And what was so great about this Agni-Tavar tower?"
msgstr "¿Y qué tenía de tan grandioso esta torre Agni-Tavar?"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:171
msgid ""
"As tradition has it, it was a sky-high column of the purest blood of the "
"earth, so that only true children of dragons could stand on it."
msgstr ""
"Según la tradición, era una columna altísima hecha de la sangre más pura de "
"la tierra, de modo que solo los verdaderos hijos de dragones podían pisarla."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:175
msgid ""
"Am I right to think that the Brilliant Flame is somewhere amidst the debris "
"of Agni-Tavar?"
msgstr ""
"¿Tengo razón al pensar que la Llama Brillante está en algún lugar entre los "
"escombros de Agni-Tavar?"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:179
msgid ""
"All I can tell with some certainty is that the Flame is here; nothing else "
"would elevate the temperature to such levels... Tenma Yozora, I advise you "
"to keep your magic about you, or else you will not survive this heat. That "
"said, let us start searching at once!"
msgstr ""
"Lo único que puedo decir con cierta seguridad es que la Llama está aquí; "
"nada más elevaría la temperatura a estos niveles… Tenma Yozora, te aconsejo "
"que mantengas tu magia activa, o no sobrevivirás a este calor. Dicho esto, "
"¡empecemos a buscar de inmediato!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:194
msgid ""
"Whoa, what the hell is that thing? It's as large as my strongest earth "
"spirits!"
msgstr ""
"¡Vaya, qué demonios es esa cosa! ¡Es tan grande como mis espíritus de tierra "
"más fuertes!"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:198
msgid ""
"The Agnirakshai, beings born from the blood of the earth and trained by Lord "
"Agniballi to defend the dragon nests. Dragons – and drakes too – had a "
"penchant for destroying a rival clan's nests, thus dooming their entire "
"lineages. No greater injury can be inflicted upon one of our kind."
msgstr ""
"Los Agnirakshai, seres nacidos de la sangre de la tierra y entrenados por el "
"Señor Agniballi para defender los nidos de dragones. Los dragones —y también "
"los dracos— tenían una afición por destruir los nidos de clanes rivales, "
"condenando así a todas sus linajes. No hay mayor ofensa que se le pueda "
"infligir a uno de los nuestros."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:202
msgid ""
"They seem content to let us walk around as long as we don't get too close, "
"so maybe we should avoid them as much as we can..."
msgstr ""
"Parecen conformes con dejarnos caminar mientras no nos acerquemos demasiado, "
"así que tal vez deberíamos evitarlos todo lo que podamos…"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:218
msgid ""
"I hear movement coming from that direction... and it doesn't sound like an "
"Agniraksha."
msgstr ""
"Escucho movimiento viniendo de esa dirección… y no suena como un Agniraksha."

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:222
msgid "Who else could be wandering around the ruins of Aghayu...?"
msgstr "¿Quién más podría estar vagando por las ruinas de Aghayu…?"

#. [unit], id=Alaenyver, type=Mage of Light, gender=female
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:234
msgid "Alaenyver"
msgstr "Alaenyver"

#. [unit], id=Hayad, type=Dune Wayfarer
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:249
msgid "Hayad"
msgstr "Hayad"

#. [unit], id=Samira, type=Dune Harrier
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:263
msgid "Samira"
msgstr "Samira"

#. [unit], id=Zayna, type=Dune Sky Hunter
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:277
msgid "Zayna"
msgstr "Zayna"

#. [unit], id=Ibrahim, type=Dune Luminary
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:291
msgid "Ibrahim"
msgstr "Ibrahim"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:307
msgid ""
"Why, it's a group of humans! I have no idea of what brought them to this "
"inferno, but it cannot be good intentions! Drakes, burn them to a..."
msgstr ""
"¡Vaya, es un grupo de humanos! No tengo idea de qué los trajo a este "
"infierno, ¡pero no pueden tener buenas intenciones! Dracos, quemenlos hasta—"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:311
msgid ""
"Wait, please! I know that man... Prince Aeldhoryan, what are you doing here? "
"Better, how did you manage to come so deep into this frying pan?"
msgstr ""
"¡Espera, por favor! Conozco a ese hombre… Príncipe Aeldhoryan, ¿qué haces "
"aquí? Mejor aún, ¿cómo lograron llegar tan profundo en este sartén?"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:315
msgid "(panting) You're... Tenma Yozora...! Run... Run before they..."
msgstr ""
"(jadeando) Tú eres… ¡Tenma Yozora…! ¡Corran… corran antes de que ellos…"

#. [message], speaker=Alaenyver
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:330
msgid ""
"My prince...! You seem to be his friend, girl, so please help us! We're from "
"the Ysoldelyn garrison, protectors of the Empire's southern frontier, but we "
"were uprooted by monsters, the likes of which we've never seen before..."
msgstr ""
"¡Mi príncipe…! Parece que eres su amiga, muchacha, ¡así que por favor "
"ayúdanos! Somos de la guarnición de Ysoldelyn, protectores de la frontera "
"sur del Imperio, pero fuimos desplazados por monstruos como nunca antes "
"habíamos visto…"

#. [message], speaker=Samira
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:334
msgid ""
"Hear us, strangers: we ignored the Wesnothian prince's warnings, too "
"confident in our power and too satisfied to keep him prisoner. Now, our city "
"stands a graveyard as testament to our foolishness."
msgstr ""
"Escúchenos, extraños: ignoramos las advertencias del príncipe de Wesnoth, "
"demasiado confiados en nuestro poder y demasiado satisfechos con mantenerlo "
"prisionero. Ahora nuestra ciudad es un cementerio como testimonio de nuestra "
"estupidez."

#. [message], speaker=Hayad
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:338
msgid ""
"Our falconers scouted the way to Th'arwya, but even that great city "
"anguishes beneath the monsters' fury. We entered the deeper desert, but a "
"swarm of them caught our scent and has chased us ever since. Not even the "
"heat seems to faze them...!"
msgstr ""
"Nuestros halconeros exploraron el camino hacia Th'arwya, pero incluso esa "
"gran ciudad agoniza bajo la furia de los monstruos. Entramos más profundo en "
"el desierto, pero un enjambre de ellos captó nuestro olor y nos ha "
"perseguido desde entonces. ¡Ni siquiera el calor parece afectarles…!"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:342
msgid ""
"Which means that you bring destruction to whoever you come across... Are you "
"certain that you want to aid them, Tenma Yozora? Searching for the Flame "
"will be dangerous enough already without fighting these 'abominations' they "
"talk about."
msgstr ""
"Lo que significa que traen destrucción a quienquiera que se crucen… ¿Estás "
"segura de que quieres ayudarlos, Tenma Yozora? Buscar la Llama ya será lo "
"suficientemente peligroso sin tener que luchar contra esas «abominaciones» "
"de las que hablan."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:346
msgid ""
"I think I know who these abominations are... and they won't stop at these "
"people. Besides, I can't just leave them to die - especially Aeldhoryan."
msgstr ""
"Creo que sé quiénes son esas abominaciones… y no se detendrán con esta "
"gente. Además, no puedo simplemente dejarlos morir… especialmente a "
"Aeldhoryan."

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:350
msgid ""
"We owe you, Tenma... and I for one owe you even more. The Dunefolk had items "
"that protected us from the heat for most of our journey; they ceased "
"functioning as we entered this caldera, scorching as it is, but we still "
"have enough strength to fight by your side!"
msgstr ""
"Te debemos una, Tenma… y yo en particular te debo aún más. Los barjanes "
"tenían objetos que nos protegían del calor durante la mayor parte del viaje; "
"dejaron de funcionar cuando entramos en esta caldera tan abrasadora, pero "
"todavía tenemos fuerzas suficientes para luchar a tu lado."

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:378
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:630
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:750
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:862
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1299
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:44
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:771
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1091
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1169
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:50
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:739
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1426
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:41
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:831
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:712
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:745
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1757
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:44
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1108
msgid "Death of Aeldhoryan"
msgstr "Muerte de Aeldhoryan"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:402
msgid ""
"Just as I thought... Aeldhoryan, you're certain that it was just these "
"monsters chasing you, right? Was there any girl around my age leading them?"
msgstr ""
"Tal como pensaba… Aeldhoryan, estás seguro de que solo estos monstruos los "
"perseguían, ¿verdad? ¿Había alguna chica de mi edad liderándolos?"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:406
msgid ""
"No... I apologise for doubting you, but are you confident that we can defeat "
"them?"
msgstr ""
"No… Lamento haber dudado de ti, pero ¿estás segura de que podemos vencerlos?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:410
msgid ""
"They're scary, but they can be destroyed just like anything else. Though "
"they don't seem affected by this heatwave, which is a big disadvantage for "
"us..."
msgstr ""
"Son aterradores, pero pueden ser destruidos como cualquier otra cosa. Aunque "
"no parecen afectados por esta ola de calor, lo cual es una gran desventaja "
"para nosotros…"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:445
msgid ""
"The Agni-Tavar....! To think that this is all that was left of the ultimate "
"seat of dragonkin's power..."
msgstr ""
"¡La Agni-Tavar…! Pensar que esto es todo lo que queda del asiento supremo "
"del poder de los dragones…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:449
msgid "Do you think the Flame is really in there?"
msgstr "¿Crees que la Llama realmente está ahí dentro?"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:453
msgid ""
"Yes... This is where the heat is most intense; don't you dare come close, or "
"else you'll get fried..."
msgstr ""
"Sí… Aquí es donde el calor es más intenso; no te atrevas a acercarte, o te "
"freirás…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:474
msgid "Argh, so hot...!"
msgstr "¡Argh, qué calor…!"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:478
msgid ""
"(astonished) It's... It's the Brilliant Flame! We have found it at last! "
"now, Eternal Fire, judge me worthy to wield you, or burn me to ash should I "
"be found unworthy..."
msgstr ""
"(asombrada) Es… ¡Es la Llama Brillante! ¡Por fin la encontramos! Ahora, "
"Fuego Eterno, júzgame digna de empuñarte, o conviérteme en cenizas si "
"resulto indigna…"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:499
msgid "(roars in pain) AAAAAARRGGGGHHHHH!!!"
msgstr "(ruge de dolor) ¡AAAAAARRRRGGGGHHHHH!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:503
msgid ""
"VESHTAR! No... No, no, damn it, you stupid Flame, how can you do that to "
"her?!"
msgstr ""
"¡VESHTAR! No… No, maldita sea, estúpida Llama, ¿cómo puedes hacerle eso?"

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:511
msgid ""
"What will we do now? Our Dominant is in danger, and we cannot possibly save "
"her from Great Agniballi's own power!"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué hacemos ahora? ¡Nuestra Dominante está en peligro y no podemos salvarla "
"del propio poder del Gran Agniballi!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:515
msgid ""
"I can still sense Veshtar Joohn's life energy... Drakes, Aeldhoryan, please "
"hold off the enemy while I go there myself; I'll wrestle her from that Flame "
"even if I have to-"
msgstr ""
"Aún puedo sentir la energía vital de Veshtar Joohn… Dracos, Aeldhoryan, por "
"favor contengan al enemigo mientras voy yo misma; la arrancaré de esa Llama "
"aunque tenga que—"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:540
msgid "What was that now?!"
msgstr "¿Qué fue eso ahora?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:544
msgid "(surprised) Veshtar...!"
msgstr "(sorprendida) ¡Veshtar…!"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:596
msgid ""
"Thank you, Great Agniballi, for judging me worthy of wielding your power. I "
"promise I shall use it to protect our people, but never to the detriment of "
"the other children of this earth..."
msgstr ""
"Gracias, Gran Agniballi, por juzgarme digna de empuñar tu poder. Prometo que "
"lo usaré para proteger a nuestro pueblo, pero nunca en detrimento de los "
"demás hijos de esta tierra…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:600
msgid "Damn you, Veshtar Joohn, you really scared us all!"
msgstr "¡Maldita seas, Veshtar Joohn, realmente nos asustaste a todos!"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:604
msgid ""
"I was indeed brought to death's frozen gates as the flame possessed me; even "
"now, I can't completely control such vast power. To think this was the power "
"and glory once beheld by our people..."
msgstr ""
"En verdad fui llevada hasta las puertas heladas de la muerte mientras la "
"llama me poseía; incluso ahora no puedo controlar completamente un poder tan "
"vasto. Pensar que este era el poder y la gloria que una vez contempló "
"nuestro pueblo…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:608
msgid ""
"Fine, fine, now please use all this power and glory to get us out of this "
"mess, before we're all turned to ash!"
msgstr ""
"Está bien, está bien, ahora por favor usa todo ese poder y gloria para "
"sacarnos de este lío ¡antes de que todos terminemos convertidos en cenizas!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:614
msgid "Destroy the Nightmares"
msgstr "Destruye a las Pesadillas"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:651
msgid ""
"You've done it... Hundreds of soldiers and mages have failed to stop that "
"horde, and yet you've succeeded!"
msgstr ""
"¡Lo lograron…! Cientos de soldados y magos fallaron en detener esa horda, ¡y "
"aun así ustedes lo consiguieron!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:655
msgid "(smirking) She's awesome, isn't she?"
msgstr "(sonriendo) Es increíble, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:659
msgid ""
"It was under your guidance that I have seized this power, Tenma Yozora; and "
"with the Brilliant Flame, a new hope has been lit for my people - and for "
"our friends in the north. Now, no necromancer can hope to stand against us!"
msgstr ""
"Fue bajo tu guía que tomé este poder, Tenma Yozora; y con la Llama "
"Brillante, se ha encendido una nueva esperanza para mi pueblo… y para "
"nuestros amigos del norte. ¡Ahora ningún nigromante puede esperar "
"enfrentarse a nosotros!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:663
msgid ""
"Then I have something to ask of you, Veshtar Joohn. I'd like you to go to "
"the Northlands, find the leaders of the Northern Alliance, and help them "
"hold off against whatever threat that shows up. One of my friends, Algil, "
"wanted to meet the troll chieftain Udhark, so I bet that's where my friends "
"will be. I'll go to the Lins-Elens myself, and help the elves and the "
"Baryags deal with this necromancer."
msgstr ""
"Entonces tengo algo que pedirte, Veshtar Joohn. Quiero que vayas a las "
"Tierras del Norte, encuentres a los líderes de la Alianza del Norte y los "
"ayudes a resistir cualquier amenaza que aparezca. Uno de mis amigos, Algil, "
"quería conocer al jefe trol Udhark, así que apuesto a que mis amigos estarán "
"allí. Yo iré personalmente a los Lins-Elens para ayudar a los elfos y a los "
"barjanes a lidiar con este nigromante."

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:667
msgid ""
"I will do as you ask, little friend – but then you must promise me to take "
"care of the drakes I've sent to the elves' aid."
msgstr ""
"Haré lo que me pides, pequeña amiga… pero entonces debes prometerme que "
"cuidarás de los dracos que envié en ayuda de los elfos."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:671
msgid "Wouldn't you rather have me tell them to follow you?"
msgstr "¿No preferirías que les dijera que te sigan?"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:675
msgid ""
"I have promised King Gil-Thelyon that I would aid him; also, on my way to "
"the north I will locate as many scattered saurian and drake clans as I can; "
"we shall need their strength too. Now come, I will fly you and your friends "
"to the Crimson Sorceress' academy; there is nothing else left for us in "
"here. At long last, Aghayu may rest in peace..."
msgstr ""
"Le prometí al rey Gil-Thelyon que lo ayudaría; además, de camino al norte "
"localizaré tantos clanes saurios y dracos dispersos como pueda; también "
"necesitaremos su fuerza. Ahora ven, te llevaré volando a ti y a tus amigos a "
"la academia de la Hechicera Carmesí; ya no queda nada más para nosotros "
"aquí. Por fin, Aghayu puede descansar en paz…"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/41_Brilliant_Flame.cfg:708
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1409
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1744
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:713
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:810
msgid "I have failed... my people..."
msgstr "He fallado… a mi pueblo…"

#. [scenario], id=42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:5
msgid "The Daughter of Tithanya"
msgstr "La Hija de Tithanya"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:27
msgid "Defend Metheldur from Wesir's attack"
msgstr "Defiende Metheldur del ataque de Wesir"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:39
msgid "Death of Gil-Thelyon"
msgstr "Muerte de Gil-Thelyon"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:43
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:758
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:870
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1307
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1765
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:52
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1116
msgid "Death of Dragana"
msgstr "Muerte de Dragana"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:47
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:766
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:878
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1315
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1442
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1773
msgid "Death of Gelendras"
msgstr "Muerte de Gelendras"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:51
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1319
msgid "Death of Garlin Ohn"
msgstr "Muerte de Garlin Ohn"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:58
msgid ""
"In this scenario, units exposed to the elements will suffer the effects of "
"the Wesir's death blizzard, losing 2 HP per turn unless protected by "
"healers. Staying inside a castle, village or keep, or taking shelter beneath "
"the trees, will nullify the freezing's effects. Woses are immune to this "
"effect."
msgstr ""
"En este escenario, las unidades expuestas a los elementos sufrirán los "
"efectos de la ventisca mortal de Wesir, perdiendo 2 PV por turno a menos que "
"estén protegidas por sanadores. Permanecer dentro de un castillo, aldea o "
"torreón, o refugiarse bajo los árboles, anulará los efectos del "
"congelamiento. Los woses son inmunes a este efecto."

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:91
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/characters.cfg:283
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/characters.cfg:297
msgid "Wesir Amarnat"
msgstr "Wesir Amarnat"

#. [side], type=Inferno Drake
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:161
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:167
msgid "Garlin Ohn"
msgstr "Garlin Ohn"

#. [message], speaker=Thelyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:329
msgid ""
"And so the monster who brings this unnatural winter finally reveals his "
"face... Tell us, necromancer: who are you, and who do you fight for? Are you "
"another one of Wesnoth's 'White Necromancers', sent to expand the empire's "
"frontiers?"
msgstr ""
"Y así el monstruo que trae este invierno antinatural finalmente muestra su "
"rostro… Dinos, nigromante: ¿quién eres y por quién luchas? ¿Eres otro de los "
"«Nigromantes Blancos» de Wesnoth, enviado para expandir las fronteras del "
"imperio?"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:333
msgid ""
"I do not fight for that petty empire, elf king; I am Wesir Amarnat, known in "
"my native New Maat'Kare as the 'God of Death', and I fight only for myself!"
msgstr ""
"No lucho por ese insignificante imperio, rey elfo; soy Wesir Amarnat, "
"conocido en mi tierra natal Nueva Maat'Kare como el «Dios de la Muerte», ¡y "
"solo lucho por mí mismo!"

#. [message], speaker=Kaldan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:337
msgid ""
"Yours must be an insignificant nation indeed, for I have never even heard of "
"it before. Just as ignominious shall be your end, if you dare attack "
"Metheldur!"
msgstr ""
"La tuya debe ser una nación realmente insignificante, pues nunca había oído "
"hablar de ella. Igualmente ignominioso será tu final si te atreves a atacar "
"Metheldur."

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:341
msgid ""
"You may not know my homeland, but I have read about yours: my people's "
"writings on you are ancient, but elven civilisation seems hostile to the "
"idea of progress, even of the magic kind, for you are just as I expected you "
"to be..."
msgstr ""
"Tal vez no conozcas mi patria, pero yo he leído sobre la tuya: los escritos "
"de mi pueblo sobre ustedes son antiguos, pero la civilización élfica parece "
"hostil a la idea del progreso, incluso del tipo mágico, pues eres "
"exactamente como esperaba que fueras…"

#. [message], speaker=Thelyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:345
msgid ""
"We strive for peace and balance, necromancer; we have reached both long ago, "
"and so we have endured the aeons - while those who practice the dark arts "
"invariably fall under the weight of their own corruption."
msgstr ""
"Nos esforzamos por la paz y el equilibrio, nigromante; alcanzamos ambos hace "
"mucho tiempo, y por eso hemos perdurado a través de los eones… mientras que "
"aquellos que practican las artes oscuras invariablemente caen bajo el peso "
"de su propia corrupción."

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:349
msgid ""
"And so even the wise elves are blinded by the same prejudices of every other "
"primitive culture. My people have long learned to master the dark arts "
"without being mastered by them; this is why we are so powerful. Your failure "
"to understand that, like your failure to know the powers that thrive beyond "
"the oceans, shall be your undoing, elves."
msgstr ""
"Y así incluso los sabios elfos están cegados por los mismos prejuicios que "
"todas las demás culturas primitivas. Mi pueblo aprendió hace mucho a dominar "
"las artes oscuras sin ser dominado por ellas; por eso somos tan poderosos. "
"Su incapacidad para entender eso, al igual que su incapacidad para conocer "
"los poderes que prosperan más allá de los océanos, será su perdición, elfos."

#. [message], speaker=Kaldan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:353
msgid ""
"Let loose your foul hordes, then, and see how they crash hopelessly against "
"the might of the Lins-Elens!"
msgstr ""
"Suelta entonces tus hordas inmundas y verás cómo se estrellan sin esperanza "
"contra el poder de los Lins-Elens."

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:357
msgid ""
"So they would, had I attacked another time... But I know you've been through "
"a terrible war not that long ago. Shall we see if your might can still "
"withstand mine?"
msgstr ""
"Así sería si hubiera atacado en otro momento… Pero sé que pasaron por una "
"terrible guerra no hace mucho. ¿Veremos si su poder aún puede resistir al "
"mío?"

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:361
msgid ""
"Damn it...! It's bad enough he's chosen our weakest moment to attack, but "
"his power truly is no jest. I have seen it with my own eyes, friends: it's "
"as if he opens the gates to the Beyond itself to pour all its endless hordes "
"into our world, along with its freezing gales. I'm almost forced to believe "
"that he is Czernabog the Dark himself..."
msgstr ""
"¡Maldición…! Ya es bastante malo que haya elegido nuestro momento más débil "
"para atacar, pero su poder realmente no es ninguna broma. Lo he visto con "
"mis propios ojos, amigos: es como si abriera las puertas al Más Allá mismo "
"para verter todas sus hordas interminables en nuestro mundo, junto con sus "
"vientos helados. Casi me veo obligada a creer que él es el propio Czernabog "
"el Oscuro…"

#. [message], speaker=Gelendras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:365
msgid ""
"Many were the necromancers throughout history who wielded uncanny powers; as "
"they all fell, so will he. Elves, Baryags, let us fight side by side against "
"this-"
msgstr ""
"Muchos fueron los nigromantes a lo largo de la historia que manejaron "
"poderes sobrenaturales; como todos cayeron, también caerá él. Elfos, "
"barjanes, luchamos codo a codo contra este—"

#. [message], speaker=Thelyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:369
msgid ""
"(frowning) Gelendras, hold on, please... (brief pause) This presence... "
"Could it be...?"
msgstr ""
"(frunciendo el ceño) Gelendras, espera un momento, por favor… (breve pausa) "
"Esta presencia… ¿Podría ser…?"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:373
msgid ""
"Father, you ordered me to protect the humans until the end of their journey; "
"so I have done, and so I return home!"
msgstr ""
"Padre, me ordenaste proteger a los humanos hasta el final de su viaje; así "
"lo he hecho, ¡y por eso regreso a casa!"

#. [message], speaker=Thelyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:377
msgid ""
"My heart sings to see you returned safe and sound, daughter; would that we "
"had time for a calm conversation, but alas, I must ask you to help in the "
"defence of our city!"
msgstr ""
"Mi corazón canta al verte regresar sana y salva, hija; ojalá tuviéramos "
"tiempo para una conversación tranquila, pero ay, debo pedirte que nos ayudes "
"a defender nuestra ciudad."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:381
msgid ""
"That was the very reason we hurried here, father - and I do not come alone. "
"Fauns, faeries, this is the moment of reunion that you have sought for so "
"long: let the Children of the Forest fight side by side once more!"
msgstr ""
"Esa fue precisamente la razón por la que nos apresuramos a venir, padre, y "
"no vengo sola. Faunos, hadas, este es el momento de reencuentro que han "
"buscado durante tanto tiempo: ¡que los Hijos del Bosque luchen hombro con "
"hombro una vez más!"

#. [message], speaker=Gelendras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:385
msgid ""
"Those are the Lost Folk! To think we reunite just as Metheldur faces its "
"gravest challenge in aeons..."
msgstr ""
"¡Son el Pueblo Perdido! Pensar que nos reunimos justo cuando Metheldur "
"enfrenta su mayor desafío en eones…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:389
msgid ""
"(to Kenshiro) Listen, I know that you have nothing to do with the Lins-"
"Elens, so I'll understand if you choose to stay out, but-"
msgstr ""
"(a Kenshiro) Escucha, sé que no tienes nada que ver con los Lins-Elens, así "
"que entenderé si decides quedarte fuera, pero—"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:393
msgid ""
"Do you seriously believe I'd flee a battlefield and leave you fighting "
"alone? This may not be my country, but it's yours, and it means everything "
"to you, so it means everything to me as well."
msgstr ""
"¿De verdad crees que huiría de un campo de batalla y te dejaría luchar sola? "
"Este puede no ser mi país, pero es el tuyo, y significa todo para ti, así "
"que también significa todo para mí."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:397
msgid ""
"(smiling) You fool, don't make me blush like this in front of my warriors... "
"Still, I'm glad to have you by my side, Kenshiro. Now, to battle!"
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Tonto, no me hagas sonrojar así delante de mis guerreros… Aun "
"así, me alegra tenerte a mi lado, Kenshiro. ¡Ahora, a la batalla!"

#. [message], speaker=Thelyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:401
msgid ""
"*So not only have you managed to reunite the Children of Faerie after "
"thousands of years, you've also learned to love again... Tenma Yozora, you "
"have no idea of how grateful I am to you and your friends...*"
msgstr ""
"*Así que no solo lograste reunir a los Hijos de las Hadas después de miles "
"de años, sino que también aprendiste a amar de nuevo… Tenma Yozora, no "
"tienes idea de cuánto te agradezco a ti y a tus amigos…*"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:410
msgid ""
"I never thought I'd see Metheldur like this, blanketed in snow... Even when "
"the worst winter storms blow from the north, these forests remain ever "
"green, but now..."
msgstr ""
"Nunca pensé que vería Metheldur así, cubierto de nieve… Incluso cuando las "
"peores tormentas invernales soplan desde el norte, estos bosques permanecen "
"siempre verdes, pero ahora…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:414
msgid ""
"Olokun did say Wesir was one of New Maat'Kare's most celebrated mages; I "
"hate to admit, but he's held back a lot when we fought him back then."
msgstr ""
"Olokun sí dijo que Wesir era uno de los magos más célebres de Nueva "
"Maat'Kare; odio admitirlo, pero se contuvo mucho cuando lo enfrentamos en "
"aquel entonces."

#. [unit]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:434
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:456
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:479
msgid "Fallen Friend"
msgstr "Amigo Caído"

#. [message], speaker=Kaldan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:501
msgid ""
"What profanity is that? He brings our fallen under his dark sway as soon as "
"they die!"
msgstr ""
"¿Qué profanación es esa? ¡Trae a nuestros caídos bajo su oscuro dominio tan "
"pronto como mueren!"

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:505
msgid ""
"Just like that Wesnothian prince did in the service of the drakes. Good "
"thing we're practised against such a tactic!"
msgstr ""
"Exactamente como hizo aquel príncipe de Wesnoth al servicio de los dracos. "
"¡Menos mal que ya estamos practicados contra esa táctica!"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:514
msgid ""
"You fight well, as I expected of the people of Alenya... Perhaps I should "
"stop holding back and start fighting more seriously..."
msgstr ""
"Luchan bien, como esperaba de la gente de Alenya… Tal vez debería dejar de "
"contenerme y empezar a pelear más en serio…"

#. [message], speaker=Gelendras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:518
msgid ""
"I don't believe it... During all this time, was he just toying with us?!"
msgstr "No lo puedo creer… ¿Todo este tiempo solo estaba jugando con nosotros?"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:522
msgid "Behold the might of Maat'Kare's lore! Let the Reign of Darkness begin!"
msgstr ""
"¡Contemplen el poder del saber de Maat'Kare! ¡Que comience el Reinado de la "
"Oscuridad!"

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:540
msgid "Damn him, he's managed to cloud even the sun!"
msgstr "¡Maldito, logró nublar hasta el sol!"

#. [message], speaker=Thelyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:544
msgid ""
"This bodes badly, neither the Baryags nor the woses fight well in this "
"darkness... My people, let the symphony of your steel echo at its highest!"
msgstr ""
"Esto pinta mal, ni los barjanes ni los woses luchan bien en esta oscuridad… "
"¡Mi pueblo, que la sinfonía de su acero resuene al máximo!"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:558
msgid ""
"I will acknowledge this, elves; if this is you at your weakest, I would "
"never have posed a threat to you at your strongest. But you are weak "
"nonetheless, whilst I am at the peak of my powers. This is the end for you, "
"'Children of the Forest'..."
msgstr ""
"Reconozco esto, elfos; si este es su momento más débil, nunca habría "
"representado una amenaza para ustedes en su mayor fuerza. Pero son débiles "
"de todos modos, mientras yo estoy en la cima de mis poderes. Este es el fin "
"para ustedes, «Hijos del Bosque»…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:567
msgid "Damn it, how can he make so many undead appear all over the forest?!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldición, cómo puede hacer aparecer tantos no muertos por todo el bosque!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:571
msgid ""
"He's raising long-dead elves from their graves, elves who remains we never "
"purified because we never believed a necromancer would one day reach "
"Metheldur's own walls... Wesir, you will pay for defiling the corpses of our "
"ancestors!"
msgstr ""
"Está levantando elfos muertos hace mucho de sus tumbas, elfos cuyos restos "
"nunca purificamos porque nunca creímos que un nigromante llegaría algún día "
"a las mismas murallas de Metheldur… Wesir, pagarás por profanar los "
"cadáveres de nuestros ancestros."

#. [message], speaker=Thelyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:575
msgid ""
"Worse still, it has caught our warriors by surprise; everyone, find the "
"nearest comrade and stay together, or else-"
msgstr ""
"Peor aún, tomó a nuestros guerreros por sorpresa; todos, busquen al "
"compañero más cercano y permanezcan juntos, o si no—"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:591
msgid "Father, watch out!"
msgstr "¡Padre, cuidado!"

#. [message], speaker=Thelyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:595
msgid ""
"Even the Sylvan Blades have been affected by his curse...! (shouting) "
"Gelendras, Cornelya, this is an order: do not risk your own lives for me, "
"protect yourselves and the ones next to you, lest we are all doomed!"
msgstr ""
"¡Incluso las Hojas Silvanas han sido afectadas por su maldición…! (gritando) "
"Gelendras, Cornelya, esta es una orden: no arriesguen sus vidas por mí, "
"protéjanse a ustedes mismos y a los que están a su lado, ¡o todos estaremos "
"perdidos!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:607
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1413
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1431
msgid "FATHER, NO!!!"
msgstr "¡PADRE, NO!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Thelyon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:611
msgid ""
"My son... Please, protect our city... And you, my daughter... Do not let "
"darkness... overcome you..."
msgstr ""
"Mi hijo… Por favor, protege nuestra ciudad… Y tú, mi hija… No dejes que la "
"oscuridad… te venza…"

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:621
msgid ""
"No... No way... Even the King-in-the-Woods has fallen before this "
"necromancer...!"
msgstr ""
"No… De ninguna manera… ¡Incluso el Rey-en-el-Bosque ha caído ante este "
"nigromante…!"

#. [message], speaker=Gelendras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:625
msgid ""
"(fighting tears) What is the meaning of that, warrior?! Why do you lose "
"heart?! Our king has fallen, but our city still stands, our people still "
"live, and our hearts still beat with fury! Fight on!"
msgstr ""
"(luchando contra las lágrimas) ¿Qué significa eso, guerrero? ¿Por qué te "
"desanimas? ¡Nuestro rey ha caído, pero nuestra ciudad aún se mantiene, "
"nuestra gente aún vive y nuestros corazones aún laten con furia! ¡Sigan "
"luchando!"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:700
msgid "(enraged) You!!!"
msgstr "(furioso) ¡Tú!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:704
msgid ""
"(panting) Good thing we made it in time... Just as I thought, the "
"necromancer is the 'God of Jealousy' of New Maat'Kare... Wesir, your quarrel "
"with me and Ankhmare has nothing to do with elves, Baryags or drakes, so why "
"are you trying to destroy them?"
msgstr ""
"(jadeando) Menos mal que llegamos a tiempo… Tal como pensaba, el nigromante "
"es el «Dios de los Celos» de Nueva Maat'Kare… Wesir, tu pleito conmigo y con "
"Ankhmare no tiene nada que ver con elfos, barjanes ni dracos, entonces ¿por "
"qué intentas destruirlos?"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:708
msgid ""
"Every new empire rises over the corpse of a weakened predecessor; the elves' "
"kingdom would have been the biggest obstacle to me, but it's grown weaker by "
"war - and now its corpse shall be the foundation of my empire. Now, be a "
"good girl and DIE!"
msgstr ""
"Todo imperio nuevo se levanta sobre el cadáver de un predecesor debilitado; "
"el reino de los elfos habría sido el mayor obstáculo para mí, pero se ha "
"debilitado por la guerra… y ahora su cadáver será la base de mi imperio. "
"¡Ahora, sé buena chica y MUERE!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:712
msgid ""
"Give it your worst, you corrupt bag of bones! (to her friends) Kenshiro, "
"Cornelya, I'm so glad you're safe... But where are the others?"
msgstr ""
"¡Dame lo peor que tengas, saco de huesos corrupto! (a sus amigos) Kenshiro, "
"Cornelya, estoy tan contenta de que estén a salvo… Pero ¿dónde están los "
"demás?"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:716
msgid ""
"They've gone searching for Udhark in the Heart Mountains... Wait, are those "
"my mother and... Prince Aeldhoryan?"
msgstr ""
"Se fueron a buscar a Udhark en las Montañas del Corazón… Espera, ¿esos son "
"mi madre y… el príncipe Aeldhoryan?"

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:720
msgid ""
"(smiling radiantly) Is that the way you speak to your father? Come here, "
"son, I missed you so..."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo radiante) ¿Así le hablas a tu padre? Ven aquí, hijo, te extrañé "
"tanto…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:724
msgid "(embarrassed) Not now, mother, we're in the middle of a battle!"
msgstr "(avergonzado) ¡Ahora no, madre, estamos en medio de una batalla!"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:728
msgid ""
"He's right, my love, he can't abandon his position. That means we'll have to "
"open our way to him. Come, I'll shield you while you smite the undead!"
msgstr ""
"Tiene razón, mi amor, no puede abandonar su posición. Eso significa que "
"tendremos que abrirnos paso hasta él. Ven, te cubriré mientras golpeas a los "
"no muertos."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:734
msgid "Destroy Wesir"
msgstr "Destruye a Wesir"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:806
msgid ""
"I'd already lost two parents to senseless violence... And now, because you "
"bring war to our home, I have lost another...! Hide behind your monsters "
"like the coward you are, it shall not avail you; it's by my hand that you'll "
"be destroyed, Wesir of Maat'Kare!!!"
msgstr ""
"Ya había perdido a dos padres por violencia sin sentido… ¡Y ahora, porque "
"traes la guerra a nuestro hogar, he perdido a otro más…! Escóndete detrás de "
"tus monstruos como el cobarde que eres, no te servirá de nada; ¡serás "
"destruido por mi mano, Wesir de Maat'Kare!"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:810
msgid ""
"A coward, you call me... Very well, little princess, I accept your challenge."
msgstr "¿Cobarde me llamas…? Muy bien, pequeña princesa, acepto tu desafío."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:832
msgid "Cornelya, WATCH OUT!"
msgstr "¡Cornelya, CUIDADO!"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:836
msgid ""
"I have killed your father, desecrated your ancestors, and butchered your "
"people; what are you going to do about it, little elf?"
msgstr ""
"He matado a tu padre, profanado a tus ancestros y masacrado a tu pueblo; "
"¿qué vas a hacer al respecto, pequeña elfa?"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:840
msgid "You...!!!"
msgstr "¡Tú…!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:846
msgid "Destroy Wesir with Cornelya"
msgstr "Destruye a Wesir con Cornelya"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:906
msgid ""
"Pathetic... Is this what you made me leave my camp for, little princess? Is "
"this what you call fighting? The path of steel was never mine, but perhaps I "
"could teach you a lesson or two..."
msgstr ""
"Patético… ¿Esto es por lo que me hiciste abandonar mi campamento, pequeña "
"princesa? ¿Esto es lo que llamas luchar? El camino del acero nunca fue el "
"mío, pero tal vez podría enseñarte una o dos lecciones…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:913
msgid "CORNELYA!!!"
msgstr "¡CORNELYA!"

#. [message], speaker=Gelendras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:917
msgid "Sister, not you too!!!"
msgstr "¡Hermana, no tú también!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:921
msgid "Damn it, there are so many cursed undead on the way...!"
msgstr "¡Maldición, hay demasiados no muertos malditos en el camino…!"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:925
msgid ""
"Perhaps you assessed me from our clash in New Maat'Kare, but then, little "
"princess, I was holding back. <i>This</i> is the true difference in our "
"powers. Learn it, and understand how little hope you, and your kingdom, have "
"of defeating me!"
msgstr ""
"Tal vez me evaluaste por nuestro enfrentamiento en Nueva Maat'Kare, pero "
"entonces, pequeña princesa, me estaba conteniendo. <i>Esto</i> es la "
"verdadera diferencia en nuestros poderes. Apréndelo y entiende cuán poca "
"esperanza tienes tú, y tu reino, de derrotarme."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:929
msgid "(in pain) I... won't..."
msgstr "(con dolor) No… me rendiré…"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:933
msgid ""
"Stubborn to the end... Very well, for your spirit and your defiance, you "
"shall be made an example of. You won't merely die; your very soul shall be "
"crushed with despair and humiliation, and once you have become lower than "
"the vermin that feed off carcasses, then you will die and be instilled with "
"dark magic. You will make a fine Banebow for my army, perhaps even a Ghast; "
"your people will look at you and they will know the reward for Metheldur's "
"defiance..."
msgstr ""
"Terca hasta el final… Muy bien, por tu espíritu y tu desafío serás "
"convertida en ejemplo. No solo morirás; tu propia alma será aplastada con "
"desesperación y humillación, y una vez que hayas caído más abajo que las "
"alimañas que se alimentan de carroña, entonces morirás y serás imbuida con "
"magia oscura. Serás un excelente Arco Maldito para mi ejército, tal vez "
"incluso un Ghast; tu pueblo te mirará y sabrá cuál es el premio por la "
"rebeldía de Metheldur…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:937
msgid "YOU SICK BASTARD, DON'T YOU DARE LAY A FINGER ON HER!!!"
msgstr "¡MALDITO ENFERMO, NO TE ATREVAS A PONERLE UN DEDO ENCIMA!"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:959
msgid "(grinning) And I know how to begin your destruction..."
msgstr "(sonriendo) Y sé cómo comenzar tu destrucción…"

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:976
msgid "Kenshiro...!"
msgstr "¡Kenshiro…!"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:980
msgid "C-Cor..."
msgstr "C-Cor…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:987
msgid "St-t-top..."
msgstr "Para…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:994
msgid "(in despair) No.. stop it..."
msgstr "(desesperada) No… para…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1001
msgid "(crying) STOP IT!!! I beg you... don't...!"
msgstr "(llorando) ¡PARA! ¡Te lo suplico… no…!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1005
msgid "No... no way...."
msgstr "No… de ninguna manera…"

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1013
msgid "Kenshiro..."
msgstr "Kenshiro…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1017
msgid "C-Corn-nelya, I..."
msgstr "C-Cornelya, yo…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1021
msgid "No... please, spare your energies... I'll call a druid to heal you..."
msgstr ""
"No… por favor, ahorra tus energías… Llamaré a un druida para que te sane…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1025
msgid "I... l-lov-"
msgstr "Yo… te a-amo—"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1038
msgid "K-Kenshiro...?"
msgstr "¿K-Kenshiro…?"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1047
msgid "Hold on, Kenshiro... I'll heal you myself..."
msgstr "Aguanta, Kenshiro… Yo misma te sanaré…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1051
msgid "(crying) Cornelya...!"
msgstr "(llorando) ¡Cornelya…!"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1055
msgid ""
"If you want to blame anyone, little elf, blame Ankhmare and his puppy, Tenma "
"Yozora; had they not forced me to leave my city, none of this would have "
"happened..."
msgstr ""
"Si quieres culpar a alguien, pequeña elfa, culpa a Ankhmare y a su "
"cachorrita, Tenma Yozora; si no me hubieran obligado a abandonar mi ciudad, "
"nada de esto habría pasado…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1059
msgid "(crying) No..."
msgstr "(llorando) No…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1068
msgid ""
"(crying) Kenshiro, you... You promised to always stay by my side, didn't "
"you... So why aren't you...?"
msgstr ""
"(llorando) Kenshiro, tú… Me prometiste que siempre estarías a mi lado, "
"¿verdad…? Entonces ¿por qué no estás…?"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1077
msgid "KENSHIRO, DON'T LEAVE ME!!!"
msgstr "¡KENSHIRO, NO ME DEJES!"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1085
msgid "Arcane tempest...!"
msgstr "¡Tempestad arcana…!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1097
msgid ""
"*Tithanya... I won't flee my destiny any more... I won't forsake your blood "
"any more... I'll be whatever you meant me to be... So I beg you... give me "
"the power to save him...!!!*"
msgstr ""
"*Tithanya… Ya no huiré de mi destino… Ya no renegaré de tu sangre… Seré lo "
"que quisiste que fuera… Así que te suplico… ¡dame el poder para salvarlo…!*"

#. [message], speaker=Gelendras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1141
msgid "(astonished) Sister, what are you...?"
msgstr "(asombrado) Hermana, ¿qué estás…?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1145
msgid ""
"She's finally embraced the faerie plane again... and so awakened her true "
"power..."
msgstr ""
"Por fin ha abrazado de nuevo el plano feérico… y con eso ha despertado su "
"verdadero poder…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1204
msgid "(panting heavily) What... What has...?!"
msgstr "(jadeando fuertemente) ¿Qué… qué ha…?"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1208
msgid "(smiling radiantly) Kenshiro...! How are you feeling...?"
msgstr "(sonriendo radiante) ¡Kenshiro…! ¿Cómo te sientes…?"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1212
msgid "I'm fine, but... <i>Should</i> I be fine? Last time I remember was-"
msgstr ""
"Estoy bien, pero… ¿<i>debería</i> estar bien? Lo último que recuerdo fue—"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1216
msgid "<i>Cornelya hugs him</i>"
msgstr "<i>Cornelya lo abraza</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1220
msgid ""
"(crying) You idiot, don't you ever scare me like this again, understand?! I "
"nearly... I nearly..."
msgstr ""
"(llorando) Idiota, ¡nunca más me des un susto así, ¿entendido?! Casi… casi…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1224
msgid ""
"(smiling) He's just come back to the Living World and already you're trying "
"to kill him again, that's so like you... (louder) Anyway, I'm sorry to break "
"the mood, but this is not the time for that, Queen-in-the-Woods! Your people "
"awaits your command!"
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Acaba de volver al Mundo de los Vivos y ya estás intentando "
"matarlo otra vez, eso es tan tú… (más fuerte) De todos modos, lamento romper "
"el momento, ¡pero no es hora para eso, Reina-en-el-Bosque! ¡Tu pueblo espera "
"tus órdenes!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1228
msgid "Queen-in-the-Woods? Why..."
msgstr "¿Reina-en-el-Bosque? ¿Por qué…?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1232
msgid ""
"Oh, come on, don't tell me you haven't noticed that you're literally "
"bursting with faerie power?! This is what you were always meant to become, "
"Cornelya – what you refused to become for so many years. But now you finally "
"have, and so the blood of Tithanya could finally manifest itself."
msgstr ""
"Vamos, no me digas que no te has dado cuenta de que estás literalmente "
"rebosando de poder feérico… ¡Esto es lo que siempre estuviste destinada a "
"ser, Cornelya! Lo que te negaste a ser durante tantos años. Pero ahora por "
"fin lo has aceptado, y así la sangre de Tithanya pudo manifestarse al fin."

#. [message], speaker=Gelendras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1236
msgid ""
"Elves, the King-in-the-Woods may have fallen, but he left us a fitting "
"heiress! All hail Cornelya, the Queen-in-the-Woods!!!"
msgstr ""
"¡Elfos, el Rey-en-el-Bosque puede haber caído, pero nos dejó una heredera "
"digna! ¡Todos aclamen a Cornelya, la Reina-en-el-Bosque!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1246
msgid ""
"I'm not sure I deserve a crown, but one thing I know: this forest is my "
"domain, and I shall not allow these undead to soil it any longer!"
msgstr ""
"No estoy segura de merecer una corona, pero una cosa sé: este bosque es mi "
"dominio, ¡y no permitiré que estos no muertos lo manchen por más tiempo!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1250
msgid "By the way, Natsu, Aeldhoryan, that elf is your daughter-in-law."
msgstr "Por cierto, Natsu, Aeldhoryan, esa elfa es su nuera."

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1258
msgid ""
"Damn it all, I cannot fight this new power and the pretender at the same "
"time... You have caught me off guard, little elf; enjoy your victory, if you "
"can!"
msgstr ""
"Maldición, no puedo luchar contra este nuevo poder y contra la impostora al "
"mismo tiempo… Me has tomado desprevenido, pequeña elfa; disfruta tu "
"victoria, si puedes."

#. [unit], id=Skeledragon, type=Skeletal Dragon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1263
msgid "Undead Dragon"
msgstr "Dragón No Muerto"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1277
msgid ""
"And so he's fled, predictably, and left us a parting gift. He thinks an "
"undead dragon will give us pause? We have destroyed a greater one already. "
"Elves, follow me to victory!"
msgstr ""
"Y así ha huido, como era de esperarse, y nos ha dejado un regalo de "
"despedida. ¿Cree que un dragón no muerto nos detendrá? Ya destruimos uno "
"mayor. ¡Elfos, síganme hacia la victoria!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1283
msgid "Destroy the Skeletal Dragon"
msgstr "Destruye al Dragón Esquelético"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1334
msgid "I have... lost...?"
msgstr "¿He… perdido…?"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1338
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:627
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:710
msgid "CORNELYA, NO!!!"
msgstr "¡CORNELYA, NO!"

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1360
msgid "At last, we stand victorious!"
msgstr "¡Por fin, salimos victoriosos!"

#. [message], speaker=Gelendras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1364
msgid ""
"Yes, but this was not a final victory. The necromancer has escaped, and half "
"of the Lins-Elens has been destroyed. Still, now that we have a Queen-in-the-"
"Woods by our side, we shall be unchallenged in our forest!"
msgstr ""
"Sí, pero esta no fue una victoria definitiva. El nigromante escapó y la "
"mitad de los Lins-Elens ha sido destruida. Aun así, ahora que tenemos a una "
"Reina-del-Bosque de nuestro lado, ¡seremos imbatibles en nuestro bosque!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1368
msgid ""
"Like I said, I'm not sure I deserve a crown. But whatever power I have, I "
"will put it to defend our people and nurture our forests. Right now, the "
"soils of Metheldur must be purified..."
msgstr ""
"Como dije, no estoy segura de merecer una corona. Pero cualquier poder que "
"tenga, lo usaré para defender a nuestro pueblo y cuidar nuestros bosques. "
"Ahora mismo, los suelos de Metheldur deben ser purificados…"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1372
msgid ""
"With those words, Cornelya closed her eyes; soon her whole body began to "
"shine like a star, filling the forest with a warm white light. Then, a "
"myriad streams of pearl-white arcane energy sprouted from the ground: faerie "
"fire, the same one wielded by elven sylphs, but on the scale of a "
"conflagration. The white flames ran the whole forest, seeping into every "
"dead body that lay on the bloodied grass, purging them of dark magic. They "
"vanished along with the light – but their effect remained, as the corpses of "
"elves, horses and trees were suddenly blanketed in blossoming, vibrant "
"flowers."
msgstr ""
"Con esas palabras, Cornelya cerró los ojos; pronto todo su cuerpo comenzó a "
"brillar como una estrella, llenando el bosque con una cálida luz blanca. "
"Entonces, miríadas de corrientes de energía arcana blanco perla brotaron del "
"suelo: fuego feérico, el mismo que manejan las sílfides élficas, pero a "
"escala de una conflagración. Las llamas blancas recorrieron todo el bosque, "
"filtrándose en cada cuerpo muerto que yacía sobre la hierba ensangrentada, "
"purgándolos de magia oscura. Desaparecieron junto con la luz… pero su efecto "
"permaneció, pues los cadáveres de elfos, caballos y árboles quedaron de "
"pronto cubiertos de flores vibrantes y florecientes."

#. [message], speaker=Gelendras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1376
msgid ""
"*This is far beyond anything father could do... So this is be what he meant "
"by 'being a true King-in-the-Woods'... Tenma Yozora, you have no idea of how "
"much we all owe you...*"
msgstr ""
"*Esto está muy por encima de cualquier cosa que padre pudiera hacer… Así que "
"esto es lo que quiso decir con «ser un verdadero Rey-en-el-Bosque»… Tenma "
"Yozora, no tienes idea de cuánto te debemos todos…*"

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1427
msgid "Ugh...! My... son..."
msgstr "¡Ugh…! Mi… hijo…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1445
msgid "How could I die... Cornelya..."
msgstr "¿Cómo pude morir… Cornelya…"

#. [message], speaker=Gelendras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1463
msgid "I fall... Please, do not allow the enemy to destroy Metheldur..."
msgstr "Caigo… Por favor, no permitan que el enemigo destruya Metheldur…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1467
msgid "Brother, no!"
msgstr "¡Hermano, no!"

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1482
msgid "Argh...! I shouldn't have died..."
msgstr "¡Argh…! No debería morir…"

#. [message], speaker=Kaldan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1515
msgid "I die...?! Perhaps I was... too arrogant this time..."
msgstr "¿Muero…?! Tal vez esta vez fui… demasiado arrogante…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1531
msgid ""
"No! I promised to protect Veshtar Joohn's drakes! Now, her army will be "
"considerably weakened!"
msgstr ""
"¡No! ¡Prometí proteger a los dracos de Veshtar Joohn! ¡Ahora su ejército "
"quedará considerablemente debilitado!"

#. [message], speaker=Gelendras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1537
msgid ""
"No! Without the aid of the drakes, we will be far too outnumbered by these "
"undead hordes!"
msgstr ""
"¡No! ¡Sin la ayuda de los dracos estaremos muy en desventaja numérica ante "
"estas hordas de no muertos!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/42_The_Daughter_Of_Tithanya.cfg:1551
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1832
msgid ""
"We should have been quicker, we still have far greater enemies to fight!"
msgstr ""
"Debimos haber sido más rápidos, ¡todavía tenemos enemigos mucho mayores que "
"enfrentar!"

#. [scenario], id=43_Twin_Hammers
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:5
msgid "Twin Hammers"
msgstr "Martillos Gemelos"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:28
msgid "Find the defenders of the Dwarven Doors"
msgstr "Encuentra a los defensores de las Puertas Enanas"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:48
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:783
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1103
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1181
msgid "Death of Garlinn Ohn"
msgstr "Muerte de Garlinn Ohn"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:52
msgid ""
"NOTE: The drake Garlinn Ohn is leading a considerable fraction of Veshtar "
"Joohn's army, and so he must not die! Also, plan well when to use Tenma's "
"Dragon-Slayer form, you may prefer to use it near the end of the battle..."
msgstr ""
"NOTA: ¡El draco Garlinn Ohn lidera una fracción considerable del ejército de "
"Veshtar Joohn, por lo que no debe morir! Además, planea bien cuándo usar la "
"forma Matadragones de Tenma, tal vez prefieras usarla cerca del final de la "
"batalla…"

#. [side], type=General
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:84
msgid "General Uther"
msgstr "General Uther"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:197
msgid "Dokkor Army"
msgstr "Ejército Dokkor"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:220
msgid "Northern Trolls"
msgstr "Trolls del Norte"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:241
msgid "Northern Orcs"
msgstr "Orcos del Norte"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:263
msgid "Knalgan Dwarves"
msgstr "Enanos Knalganos"

#. [unit], id=Aenvan, type=Necromancer
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:462
msgid "Aenvan"
msgstr "Aenvan"

#. [label]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:487
msgid "Pillars of Thunedain"
msgstr "Pilares de Thunedain"

#. [label]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:491
msgid "North Gate"
msgstr "Puerta Norte"

#. [label]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:495
msgid "West Gate"
msgstr "Puerta Oeste"

#. [label]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:499
msgid "East Gate"
msgstr "Puerta Este"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:508
msgid ""
"Tenma, I do not wish to unsettle you, but I have a bad feeling about what "
"lies ahead in this mist..."
msgstr ""
"Tenma, no quiero inquietarte, pero tengo un mal presentimiento sobre lo que "
"hay adelante en esta niebla…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:512
msgid "Yeah, I feel the same... Wait, I sense someone approaching...!"
msgstr "Sí, siento lo mismo… ¡Espera, percibo que alguien se acerca…!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:530
msgid "TENMA! See, Algil, I told you she was here! "
msgstr "¡TENMA! ¡Mira, Algil, te dije que estaba aquí!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:534
msgid ""
"Algil, Valerya, thank the heavens you're well! What's going on in the "
"Dwarven Doors, why's everything so quiet, where are the others..."
msgstr ""
"Algil, Valerya, ¡gracias al cielo que están bien! ¿Qué pasa en las Puertas "
"Enanas, por qué todo está tan silencioso, dónde están los demás…"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:538
msgid ""
"Wait, wait, first let me recover from the surprise of finding you and all "
"these drakes out of nowhere! Och, girl, I too am glad that you're fine, you "
"sure scared the hell outta us back in Arajunna..."
msgstr ""
"Espera, espera, ¡primero déjame recuperarme de la sorpresa de encontrarte a "
"ti y a todos estos dracos de la nada! Muchacha, también me alegra que estés "
"bien, nos diste un susto de muerte allá en Arajunna…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:542
msgid ""
"Yeah, I was scared too, but that still wasn't enough to knock me down. Now "
"tell me, where are Olokun and Derceto? I met Kenshiro and Cornelya in the "
"Lins-Elens, they told me you had come to the Heart Mountains to find "
"Udhark..."
msgstr ""
"Sí, también tuve miedo, pero eso no fue suficiente para tumbarme. Ahora "
"dime, ¿dónde están Olokun y Derceto? Encontré a Kenshiro y Cornelya en los "
"Lins-Elens, me dijeron que vinieron a las Montañas del Corazón a buscar a "
"Udhark…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:546
msgid ""
"So we did. After you disappeared, we saw Galdra fly to the east; we had no "
"idea of how to even start searching for you, but we agreed that she was "
"heading for the Great Continent, and that our friends here would be in "
"danger."
msgstr ""
"Así fue. Después de que desapareciste, vimos a Galdra volar hacia el este; "
"no teníamos idea de cómo empezar a buscarte, pero coincidimos en que ella se "
"dirigía al Gran Continente y que nuestros amigos aquí estarían en peligro."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:550
msgid ""
"You were right; I was sent straight to the Land of the Dead, there was "
"nothing you could do for me."
msgstr ""
"Tenían razón; me enviaron directamente a la Tierra de los Muertos, no había "
"nada que pudieran hacer por mí."

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:554
msgid ""
"Once we got to Tirigaz we heard news that a horde of abominations was "
"wreaking chaos in Wesnoth. It was then that we split: Cornelya and Kenshiro "
"went east, but Derceto wanted to search for some Merfolk city called Jotha; "
"Olokun followed her, and so we came here on our own."
msgstr ""
"Cuando llegamos a Tirigaz oímos que una horda de abominaciones estaba "
"causando caos en Wesnoth. Fue entonces cuando nos separamos: Cornelya y "
"Kenshiro fueron al este, pero Derceto quería buscar alguna ciudad sirénida "
"llamada Jotha; Olokun la siguió, y así llegamos aquí por nuestra cuenta."

#. [message], speaker=Garlin
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:558
msgid "Crimson Sorceress, have you met our Mother Queen, Veshtar Joohn?"
msgstr "Hechicera Carmesí, ¿has conocido a nuestra Reina Madre, Veshtar Joohn?"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:562
msgid ""
"We haven't, we just arrived at this region... All we've seen is that "
"something is horribly wrong here, as neither this dense mist, nor this "
"calmness is normal."
msgstr ""
"No, acabamos de llegar a esta región… Todo lo que hemos visto es que algo "
"está terriblemente mal aquí, pues ni esta niebla densa ni esta calma son "
"normales."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:566
msgid ""
"I agree... Let's get moving, then; I fear the Dwarven Doors are in need of "
"us... Before that, though, I have a message for you, Valerya."
msgstr ""
"Estoy de acuerdo… Entonces pongámonos en marcha; temo que las Puertas Enanas "
"nos necesiten… Pero antes, tengo un mensaje para ti, Valerya."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:570
msgid "Don't leave me in suspense, then, out with it!"
msgstr "¡No me dejes en ascuas, entonces, suéltalo!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:574
msgid ""
"Back in the Land of the Dead, I couldn't access most of my powers or even "
"the spirits of nature. I don't think I'd have made it through that place "
"without the souls who helped me; one of them was Addraryn of Kerlath."
msgstr ""
"Allá en la Tierra de los Muertos no podía acceder a la mayoría de mis "
"poderes ni siquiera a los espíritus de la naturaleza. No creo que hubiera "
"salido de ese lugar sin las almas que me ayudaron; una de ellas fue Addraryn "
"de Kerlath."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:578
msgid "Addraryn... Tenma, did you... Did you speak with...?"
msgstr "Addraryn… Tenma, ¿tú… hablaste con…?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:582
msgid ""
"Your father, yes. I'm sorry, you're the one who should've had a chance to "
"speak with him... but I told him about you, about who you are, and how "
"important you are to so many people; he was kind of bursting with pride as I "
"spoke, mind you. And then he asked me to give you this message: 'I love you'."
msgstr ""
"Tu padre, sí. Lo siento, tú eras quien debería haber tenido la oportunidad "
"de hablar con él… pero le hablé de ti, de quién eres y de lo importante que "
"eres para tanta gente; estaba como reventando de orgullo mientras hablaba, "
"créeme. Y luego me pidió que te diera este mensaje: «Te amo»."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:589
msgid ""
"You don't apologise, lassie, you've just given me one of the best gifts "
"ever... (hugs Tenma) Thank you... from the bottom of my heart, thank you."
msgstr ""
"No te disculpes, muchacha, acabas de darme uno de los mejores regalos que he "
"recibido nunca… (abraza a Tenma) Gracias… de todo corazón, gracias."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:593
msgid "(wiping away tears) Now, onwards, that we have a city to save!"
msgstr ""
"(secándose las lágrimas) ¡Ahora, adelante, tenemos una ciudad que salvar!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:613
msgid ""
"Wait, these are Wesnothians... Don't tell me they're attacking the Northern "
"Alliance even now!"
msgstr ""
"Espera, estos son de Wesnoth… ¡No me digas que están atacando a la Alianza "
"del Norte incluso ahora!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:617
msgid ""
"Perhaps they're not attacking for the same old reasons... Let's capture one "
"of them, I have many questions to ask..."
msgstr ""
"Tal vez no estén atacando por las mismas razones de siempre… Capturémos a "
"uno de ellos, tengo muchas preguntas que hacerles…"

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:637
msgid "Argh! I guess it's really all over for us..."
msgstr "¡Argh! Supongo que realmente todo terminó para nosotros…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:641
msgid ""
"Perhaps it's not over for you; we could help you get out of this mess, if "
"you enlighten some things for us. Firstly, why is Wesnoth attacking the "
"Northern Alliance when there's a monster wreaking chaos at the heart of the "
"empire?"
msgstr ""
"Tal vez no haya terminado para ti; podríamos ayudarte a salir de este lío si "
"nos aclaras algunas cosas. Primero, ¿por qué Wesnoth está atacando a la "
"Alianza del Norte cuando hay un monstruo causando caos en el corazón del "
"imperio?"

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:645
msgid ""
"The Alliance is just an obstacle; our true goal is to hide in the deepest "
"caves we can find, because there is no haven on the surface world, not any "
"more, not while that monster is on the loose!"
msgstr ""
"La Alianza es solo un obstáculo; nuestro verdadero objetivo es escondernos "
"en las cuevas más profundas que podamos encontrar, porque ya no hay refugio "
"en la superficie del mundo, no mientras ese monstruo esté suelto."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:649
msgid ""
"So you thought you'd just take the Knalgans' home from them? So darn "
"typical..."
msgstr ""
"¿Entonces pensaron que simplemente les quitarían su hogar a los knalganos? "
"Qué típico…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:653
msgid "This monster, what is it? Is it a dragon, a young woman...?"
msgstr "¿Ese monstruo, qué es? ¿Es un dragón, una joven mujer…?"

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:657
msgid ""
"It <i>looks</i> like a young woman alright, but it's anything but. I have "
"seen it with my own eyes... We were one of the legions sent to deal with it, "
"and we were amongst the Empire's finest. We even had the Akladian Corps and "
"a regiment of Alduin's mightiest mages to help us, but... When we saw that "
"beast wearing a girl's face set every single of those great mages ablaze "
"with just a movement of her hand, we knew we stood no chance against it...!"
msgstr ""
"<i>Parece</i> una joven mujer, sí, pero no lo es en absoluto. Lo vi con mis "
"propios ojos… Fuimos una de las legiones enviadas para enfrentarlo, y "
"estábamos entre lo mejor del Imperio. Incluso teníamos el Cuerpo Akladiano y "
"un regimiento de los magos más poderosos de Alduin para ayudarnos, pero… "
"cuando vimos que esa bestia con rostro de chica incendió a cada uno de esos "
"grandes magos con solo un movimiento de su mano, supimos que no teníamos "
"ninguna oportunidad contra ella…"

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:661
msgid ""
"I won't make excuses; personally I think we should have struck some peaceful "
"deal with the Knalgans, but I'm just a soldier, I do as my general orders me."
msgstr ""
"No pondré excusas; personalmente creo que deberíamos haber llegado a un "
"acuerdo pacífico con los knalganos, pero soy solo un soldado, hago lo que mi "
"general me ordena."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:665
msgid ""
"One always has a choice, Wesnothian; you could have deserted your army and "
"asked the Alliance for refuge if you had so wished, but I won't judge you so "
"harshly. Rather, if you disagree with your commander's ways so much, I'll "
"let you join us; we're seeking a way to defeat that monster too. Or else you "
"may go in peace, but as you have said yourself, nowhere in the surface world "
"is safe right now."
msgstr ""
"Siempre hay una elección, wesnothiano; podrías haber desertado de tu "
"ejército y pedido refugio a la Alianza si así lo hubieras querido, pero no "
"te juzgaré tan duramente. Más bien, si tanto desacuerdas con los métodos de "
"tu comandante, te dejaré unirte a nosotros; también estamos buscando una "
"forma de derrotar a ese monstruo. O si prefieres, puedes irte en paz, pero "
"como tú mismo dijiste, ahora mismo ningún lugar en la superficie del mundo "
"es seguro."

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:669
msgid ""
"Tenma, leave the rogue general to me; as a Prince of Wesnoth, it is my duty "
"to take care of my people when they go astray. Besides, if I am the one to "
"take down their general, they may still be convinced to fight for us."
msgstr ""
"Tenma, déjame al general renegado a mí; como príncipe de Wesnoth, es mi "
"deber cuidar de mi pueblo cuando se desvía. Además, si soy yo quien derriba "
"a su general, tal vez todavía puedan convencerse de luchar por nosotros."

#. [message], speaker=Tallin
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:697
msgid "Everyone, watch out! Another wave crashes against our walls!"
msgstr "¡Todos, cuidado! ¡Otra oleada se estrella contra nuestras murallas!"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:701
msgid ""
"Those are not enemies, those are my brother and Tenma Yozora, the girl who "
"helped us defeat the Iron Giant! Grim Gods of Darkness you lot, I thought "
"you were dead by now!"
msgstr ""
"¡Esos no son enemigos, ese es mi hermano y Tenma Yozora, la chica que nos "
"ayudó a derrotar al Gigante de Hierro! ¡Por los Dioses Sombríos, pensé que "
"ya estaban muertos!"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:705
msgid ""
"Stupid brat, how dare you kill me off so easily?! Well, in any case... I've "
"come to fulfil my promise to Chief Udhark, but I don't see him anywhere? "
"Don't tell me something has happened to him...?"
msgstr ""
"¡Mocoso estúpido, cómo te atreves a matarme tan fácilmente! Bueno, en todo "
"caso… Vine a cumplir mi promesa al jefe Udhark, pero no lo veo por ningún "
"lado. ¿No me digas que le pasó algo…?"

#. [message], speaker=Tallin
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:709
msgid ""
"Eh, it would take much more than mere Wesnothians to take that one down... "
"He is well, but he's remained inside the caves, protecting our rear against "
"dwarves, orcs and other trolls attacking from the underground."
msgstr ""
"Eh, haría falta mucho más que simples wesnothianos para derribar a ese… Está "
"bien, pero se quedó dentro de las cuevas, protegiendo nuestra retaguardia "
"contra enanos, orcos y otros trolls que atacan desde el subsuelo."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:713
msgid "Hold on, why are dwarves and trolls attacking you?"
msgstr "Espera, ¿por qué enanos y trolls los están atacando?"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:717
msgid ""
"(bitter) Crimson Sorceress, you once told me that catastrophe should unite "
"trolls and dwarves, as survival would demand, but you were wrong. If "
"anything, it only made them all even more paranoid than they already were."
msgstr ""
"(amargado) Hechicera Carmesí, una vez me dijiste que la catástrofe debería "
"unir a trolls y enanos, como lo exigiría la supervivencia, pero estabas "
"equivocada. Si acaso, solo los hizo aún más paranoicos de lo que ya eran."

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:721
msgid ""
"Alas, when the world crumbles down and death stalks from every corner, even "
"those who were once the closest of friends may turn on each other seeking "
"their own survival..."
msgstr ""
"Ay, cuando el mundo se desmorona y la muerte acecha desde cada rincón, "
"incluso aquellos que alguna vez fueron los amigos más cercanos pueden "
"volverse unos contra otros en busca de su propia supervivencia…"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:725
msgid ""
"Chief Udhark may be strong, but if he's taking on so many enemies at once, "
"he'll need the Hammer of Ymer more than ever... Friends, fight on without "
"me, I'm heading underground to find him myself!"
msgstr ""
"El jefe Udhark puede ser fuerte, pero si está enfrentando a tantos enemigos "
"a la vez, necesitará el Martillo de Ymer más que nunca… Amigos, sigan "
"luchando sin mí, ¡voy bajo tierra a buscarlo yo mismo!"

#. [message], speaker=Thrith
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:729
msgid ""
"And ye shan't go alone, boy; I'll order three runesmiths to escort ye to yer "
"goal!"
msgstr ""
"Y no irás solo, muchacho; ordenaré a tres forjarrunas que te escolten hasta "
"tu objetivo."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:749
msgid ""
"Come on, everyone! Let's finish this battle before Chief Udhark and Algil "
"return!"
msgstr ""
"¡Vamos, todos! ¡Terminemos esta batalla antes de que regresen el jefe Udhark "
"y Algil!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:755
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1157
msgid "Defend the Dwarven Doors"
msgstr "Defiende las Puertas Enanas"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:759
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1071
msgid "Defeat General Uther with Aeldhoryan"
msgstr "Derrota al General Uther con Aeldhoryan"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:787
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1107
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1185
msgid ""
"NOTE: The drake Garlinn Ohn is leading a considerable fraction of Veshtar "
"Joohn's army, and so he must not die!"
msgstr ""
"NOTA: ¡El draco Garlinn Ohn lidera una fracción considerable del ejército de "
"Veshtar Joohn, por lo que no debe morir!"

#. [unit], id=Grokk, type=Great Troll
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:820
msgid "Groff"
msgstr "Groff"

#. [unit], id=Dashnuk, type=Orcish Sovereign
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:831
msgid "Dashnuk"
msgstr "Dashnuk"

#. [unit], id=Ancathas, type=Dwarvish Lord
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:840
msgid "Ancathas"
msgstr "Ancathas"

#. [message], speaker=Tallin
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:877
msgid ""
"Oh, no... Orcs and trolls pour out of the West Gate... and dwarves out of "
"the East Gate! Can it be that Udhark has fallen...?"
msgstr ""
"Oh, no… Orcos y trolls salen a raudales por la Puerta Oeste… ¡y enanos por "
"la Puerta Este! ¿Será posible que Udhark haya caído…?"

#. [message], speaker=Ancathas
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:881
msgid ""
"Ye mean that stinkin' troll beast? Eh, he dinna stand our might, and fled "
"like the maggot he is, along with a bunch of unworthy un-dwarves! D'ye see "
"it now, 'Lord Protector', how treacherous and unreliable those animals are?!"
msgstr ""
"¿Te refieres a esa bestia troll apestosa? Eh, no resistió nuestro poder y "
"huyó como la larva que es, junto con un montón de indignos no-enanos. ¿Lo "
"ves ahora, «Señor Protector», qué traicioneros e indignos de confianza son "
"esos animales?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:885
msgid ""
"Don't you dare talk about Algil like that, you bastard! Everyone, let us "
"trust Algil and Udhark, they would never abandon us!"
msgstr ""
"¡No te atrevas a hablar así de Algil, maldito! Todos, confiemos en Algil y "
"Udhark, ¡ellos nunca nos abandonarían!"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:889
msgid "I do not doubt them, but I do hope they return presently..."
msgstr "No dudo de ellos, pero sí espero que regresen pronto…"

#. [message], speaker=Thrith
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:909
msgid ""
"(surprised) My hammer...! I've never seen it glow like this before... Could "
"it mean that...?"
msgstr ""
"(sorprendido) ¡Mi martillo…! Nunca lo había visto brillar así antes… ¿Podría "
"significar que…?"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:913
msgid "About time they returned!"
msgstr "¡Ya era hora de que regresaran!"

#. [message], speaker=Thrith
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:917
msgid ""
"That's not all, captain... It's not glowing like it usually does when "
"Thursagan's Hammer is nearby, not even like when Algil showed up with that "
"other hammer..."
msgstr ""
"No es solo eso, capitán… No está brillando como suele hacerlo cuando el "
"Martillo de Thursagan está cerca, ni siquiera como cuando Algil apareció con "
"el otro martillo…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:921
msgid "I can feel it too, Arcanister... (smirking) This will be interesting..."
msgstr ""
"Yo también lo siento, Arcanister… (sonriendo) Esto va a ser interesante…"

#. [message], speaker=Thrith
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:950
msgid "(astonished) That's... that's..."
msgstr "(asombrado) Eso es… eso es…"

#. [message], speaker=Tallin
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:954
msgid ""
"...the Hammer of Thursagan! But its shrine had been sunken in lava... How "
"did you manage to rescue it?!"
msgstr ""
"…¡el Martillo de Thursagan! Pero su santuario se hundió en lava… ¿Cómo "
"lograron rescatarlo?"

#. [message], speaker=Udhark
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:958
msgid ""
"The same way my people's forefathers have managed to open their way through "
"the sea of lava towards the surface world, aeons ago, when the world was "
"still young: with the Relic of Griknagh the Great, which finally returns to "
"Troll-kind!"
msgstr ""
"Del mismo modo que los antepasados de mi pueblo lograron abrirse paso a "
"través del mar de lava hacia la superficie del mundo, eones atrás, cuando el "
"mundo aún era joven: con la Reliquia de Griknagh el Grande, ¡que por fin "
"regresa al pueblo trol!"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:962
msgid ""
"And Chief Udhark saw it fitting that the Regalia of Trolls' first act be the "
"recovery of the Hammer of Thursagan, or the Hammer of Buri. And what's more, "
"do you know what we found out? That the runic verses on both Relics complete "
"one another. Behold:"
msgstr ""
"Y el jefe Udhark consideró apropiado que el primer acto de las Regalias de "
"los trolls fuera la recuperación del Martillo de Thursagan, o Martillo de "
"Buri. Y además, ¿saben qué descubrimos? Que los versos rúnicos de ambas "
"reliquias se completan mutuamente. Miren:"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:966
msgid ""
"With those words, the troll and the dwarf placed their respective hammers "
"side by side; and that was enough to make them come alive: with a clanging "
"noise, they stuck to another, and the runes that adorned them glimmered "
"brightly for all of Dwarven Doors to see."
msgstr ""
"Con esas palabras, el trol y el enano colocaron sus respectivos martillos "
"uno al lado del otro; y eso fue suficiente para hacerlos cobrar vida: con un "
"ruido metálico, se unieron, y las runas que los adornaban brillaron "
"intensamente para que todos en las Puertas Enanas lo vieran."

#. [message], speaker=Udhark
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:970
msgid "'Eight runes have I carved from the womb of Earth...'"
msgstr "«Ocho runas tallé del vientre de la Tierra…»"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:974
msgid "'Eight runes have I carved from the Halls of Earth...'"
msgstr "«Ocho runas tallé de los Salones de la Tierra…»"

#. [message], speaker=Udhark
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:978
msgid "'Eight runes have we carved...'"
msgstr "«Ocho runas hemos tallado…»"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:982
msgid "'...Together on the lap of the Mother...'"
msgstr "«…Juntos en el regazo de la Madre…»"

#. [message], speaker=Udhark
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:986
msgid "'To ascend to the archways of Heaven, together...'"
msgstr "«Para ascender a los arcos del Cielo, juntos…»"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:990
msgid "'...To claim our rightful place on Earth, together!'"
msgstr "«…¡Para reclamar nuestro lugar legítimo en la Tierra, juntos!»"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1035
msgid ""
"About time the Twin Hammers were reunited! King-in-the-Earth, King-in-the-"
"Abyss, does any of you have any crowning speech?"
msgstr ""
"¡Ya era hora de que los Martillos Gemelos se reunieran! Rey-en-la-Tierra, "
"Rey-en-el-Abismo, ¿alguno de ustedes tiene un discurso de coronación?"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1039
msgid ""
"(laughing) Actually we do, Dragon-Slayer! Chief Udhark, I think we speak by "
"the both of us when I say that we do not claim sovereignty over all of dwarf-"
"kind or troll-kind; but for those who feel confused and lost in this "
"crumbling world, we shall build a better home with these very hammers!"
msgstr ""
"(riendo) ¡En realidad sí, Matadragones! Jefe Udhark, creo que hablamos por "
"los dos cuando digo que no reclamamos soberanía sobre todos los enanos ni "
"sobre todos los trolls; pero para aquellos que se sienten confundidos y "
"perdidos en este mundo que se desmorona, ¡construiremos un hogar mejor con "
"estos mismos martillos!"

#. [message], speaker=Udhark
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1043
msgid ""
"But to those who threaten our people, be it orc or human, elf or drake; and "
"to any dwarf or troll who seeks to sow discord among us, I say this: we "
"shall crush you with these very hammers!"
msgstr ""
"Pero a aquellos que amenazan a nuestro pueblo, sea orco o humano, elfo o "
"draco; y a cualquier enano o trol que busque sembrar discordia entre "
"nosotros, les digo esto: ¡los aplastaremos con estos mismos martillos!"

#. [message], speaker=Grokk
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1047
msgid ""
"The Great Chieftain of legend...! Could it be that he has returned to guide "
"us through this chaos?! Such as mysteries for the shamans... but even I can "
"see that we can't stand against his power... Trolls, I've changed my mind, "
"we now fight for Udhark and the Northern Alliance!"
msgstr ""
"¡El Gran Jefe de la leyenda…! ¿Será posible que haya regresado para guiarnos "
"a través de este caos? Misterios para los chamanes… pero incluso yo puedo "
"ver que no podemos resistir contra su poder… ¡Trolls, he cambiado de "
"opinión, ahora luchamos por Udhark y la Alianza del Norte!"

#. [message], speaker=Ancathas
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1057
msgid ""
"You... You dare use the holy Hammer of Thursagan on behalf of these "
"maggots... I will never forgive you, Algil of Thursaz!"
msgstr ""
"Tú… ¿Te atreves a usar el santo Martillo de Thursagan en nombre de estas "
"larvas…? ¡Nunca te perdonaré, Algil de Thursaz!"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1061
msgid ""
"We'll see how you think when you witness the power of Moradin, Ancathas of "
"Kal Kartha..."
msgstr ""
"Veremos qué piensas cuando seas testigo del poder de Moradin, Ancathas de "
"Kal Kartha…"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1067
msgid "Defeat all enemies"
msgstr "Derrota a todos los enemigos"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1087
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:54
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:743
msgid "Death of Udhark"
msgstr "Muerte de Udhark"

#. [message], speaker=Uther
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1131
msgid "P-prince Aeldhoryan...?! What are you..."
msgstr "¿P-príncipe Aeldhoryan…?! ¿Qué estás…?"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1135
msgid ""
"I am here to fulfil my duty as the one responsible for the citizens of the "
"Empire. I am aware of the reasons that forced you to abandon your country, "
"but know this, general: there will be no safe place on this world unless we "
"defeat that enemy – but there's no hope for that if we keep turning our "
"blades to the wrong opponents!"
msgstr ""
"Estoy aquí para cumplir con mi deber como responsable de los ciudadanos del "
"Imperio. Conozco las razones que los obligaron a abandonar su país, pero "
"saben esto, general: no habrá lugar seguro en este mundo a menos que "
"derrotemos a ese enemigo… ¡pero no hay esperanza de eso si seguimos "
"volviendo nuestras espadas contra los oponentes equivocados!"

#. [message], speaker=Uther
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1139
msgid ""
"If Prince Aeldhoryan says that, we believe him and pledge our loyalty to him "
"- as well as our sincerest apologies. After we were routed by the Arajunnan "
"summoner, all I could think of was to lead my men and their families to "
"safety, and I thought there would be no safer place than the deepest caves..."
msgstr ""
"Si el príncipe Aeldhoryan lo dice, le creemos y le juramos lealtad… así como "
"nuestras más sinceras disculpas. Después de que el invocador de Arajunna nos "
"derrotara, lo único en lo que podía pensar era en llevar a mis hombres y a "
"sus familias a un lugar seguro, y pensé que no habría lugar más seguro que "
"las cuevas más profundas…"

#. [message], speaker=Tallin
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1143
msgid ""
"You could have approached us under a banner of peace, general... then again, "
"I acknowledge you had no reason to expect us to welcome you. There is much "
"bad blood between us, and I see no friendship blooming between us any time "
"soon. But from all I have heard, we stand no chance against the oncoming "
"chaos if we stand alone. You're an honourable man, Prince Aeldhoryan, and "
"you have your people's loyalty; to you I propose a truce, so that we may "
"fight side by side this danger that threatens us all."
msgstr ""
"Podrían habernos acercado bajo bandera de paz, general… aunque reconozco que "
"no tenían razón para esperar que los recibiéramos bien. Hay mucha sangre "
"mala entre nosotros, y no veo amistad floreciendo entre nosotros en el corto "
"plazo. Pero por todo lo que he oído, no tenemos ninguna oportunidad contra "
"el caos que se avecina si permanecemos solos. Es usted un hombre honorable, "
"príncipe Aeldhoryan, y tiene la lealtad de su pueblo; a usted le propongo "
"una tregua, para que podamos luchar codo a codo contra este peligro que nos "
"amenaza a todos."

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1147
msgid ""
"And I accept, Lord Protector, hoping that this is, at the very least, the "
"foundation stone of a lasting peace between our people."
msgstr ""
"Y acepto, Señor Protector, esperando que esto sea, al menos, la piedra "
"fundamental de una paz duradera entre nuestros pueblos."

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1208
msgid "No! We need his army to join ours! "
msgstr "¡No! ¡Necesitamos que su ejército se una al nuestro!"

#. [message], speaker=Ancathas
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1224
msgid "(seething) You... disgusting... <i>maggots</i>...!"
msgstr "(furioso) ¡Ustedes… repugnantes… <i>larvas</i>…!"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1228
msgid ""
"Frankly, Ancathas, I can't understand yer hatred... But I will not kill ye "
"for that. Rather, I'll let ye go and live; and I hope that ye live long "
"enough to understand how much better Knalga would be, if trolls and dwarves "
"coexisted in peace instead of bleeding each other."
msgstr ""
"Francamente, Ancathas, no entiendo tu odio… Pero no te mataré por eso. Más "
"bien, te dejaré ir y vivir; y espero que vivas lo suficiente para entender "
"cuán mejor sería Knalga si trolls y enanos coexistieran en paz en lugar de "
"desangrarse mutuamente."

#. [message], speaker=Tallin
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1243
msgid ""
"Once again, Tenma Yozora, your intervention has proved essential for our "
"victory; in all sincerity, I don't know how to properly thank you..."
msgstr ""
"Una vez más, Tenma Yozora, tu intervención ha resultado esencial para "
"nuestra victoria; con toda sinceridad, no sé cómo agradecerte adecuadamente…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1247
msgid "(smirking) Well, a barrel of Knalgan beer would be a good start."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Bueno, un barril de cerveza knalgana sería un buen comienzo."

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1251
msgid ""
"I must also thank you for bringing my brother in safety; knowing his "
"recklessness, I'm sure you must have saved his arse a few times..."
msgstr ""
"También debo agradecerte por traer a mi hermano a salvo; conociendo su "
"temeridad, estoy seguro de que le salvaste el pellejo varias veces…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1255
msgid "Fifteen times, to be more precise."
msgstr "Quince veces, para ser más precisos."

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1259
msgid ""
"Tch, I won't argue with ye any more; the wielder of Buri's Hammer must "
"maintain a worthy composure..."
msgstr ""
"Tch, no discutiré más contigo; el portador del Martillo de Buri debe "
"mantener una compostura digna…"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1263
msgid "And now we won't hear the end of it..."
msgstr "Y ahora no nos dejará en paz con eso…"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1267
msgid ""
"Rest easy, I won't keep it for myself beyond this crisis. Here, Arcanister; "
"I leave the Hammer of Thursagan in our order's care, with my deepest "
"apologies for taking it without permission."
msgstr ""
"Descansen tranquilos, no lo guardaré para mí más allá de esta crisis. Aquí, "
"Arcanister; dejo el Martillo de Thursagan al cuidado de nuestra orden, con "
"mis más profundas disculpas por tomarlo sin permiso."

#. [message], speaker=Thrith
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1275
msgid ""
"Are ye truly this clueless?! Ye brought justice that had been yearned for "
"aeons and restored dwarfdom's honour, none is worthier to wield this Hammer "
"than ye – and the Hammer itself has decreed that by letting you unlock its "
"true power!"
msgstr ""
"¿De verdad eres tan despistado? ¡Trajiste justicia que se anhelaba desde "
"hace eones y restauraste el honor de los enanos! Nadie es más digno de "
"empuñar este Martillo que tú… ¡y el propio Martillo lo ha decretado al "
"permitirte desbloquear su verdadero poder!"

#. [message], speaker=Udhark
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1279
msgid ""
"And if you doubt your worth, that you are so ready to part with such power "
"shows how much stronger you are than even Moradin. Now come, friend, we have "
"work to do!"
msgstr ""
"Y si dudas de tu valía, el hecho de que estés tan dispuesto a desprenderte "
"de tal poder demuestra cuán más fuerte eres incluso que Moradin. ¡Ahora ven, "
"amigo, tenemos trabajo por hacer!"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1283
msgid "Tenma, is something the matter?"
msgstr "Tenma, ¿pasa algo?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1296
msgid "Guys..."
msgstr "Chicos…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1300
msgid ""
"(suddenly alarmed) Guys, we must... we must flee this place right now! "
"Gather as many people you can, and run!"
msgstr ""
"(de repente alarmada) ¡Chicos, debemos… debemos huir de este lugar ahora "
"mismo! ¡Reúnan a tanta gente como puedan y corran!"

#. [message], speaker=Tallin
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1304
msgid "But..."
msgstr "Pero..."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1308
msgid "I HAVE NO TIME TO EXPLAIN, JUST D-"
msgstr "¡NO TENGO TIEMPO PARA EXPLICAR, SOLO—"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1329
msgid ""
"(alarmed) W-what the hell...?! Don't tell me Galdra has arrived already?!"
msgstr "(alarmada) ¿Q-qué demonios…?! ¡No me digas que Galdra ya llegó!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1333
msgid "No... it's someone far, far worse..."
msgstr "No… es alguien mucho, mucho peor…"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1337
msgid ""
"Everyone looked around in fear after the cause of that cataclysm, but it was "
"only when someone remembered to look upward that they could see it. And "
"everyone, from the weakest soldier to Udhark himself, shuddered before what "
"they saw..."
msgstr ""
"Todos miraron a su alrededor con miedo buscando la causa de ese cataclismo, "
"pero solo cuando alguien recordó mirar hacia arriba pudieron verlo. Y todos, "
"desde el soldado más débil hasta el propio Udhark, temblaron ante lo que "
"vieron…"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1341
msgid ""
"Down from the heavens, tearing open the thick vault of clouds, descended a "
"colossal beast, cloaked in lightning, wings casting vast shadows on the "
"valley below. It landed on the highest mountain with a booming noise, and it "
"raised its head, facing the smaller beings with eyes like stars; and then it "
"roared, a roar that made the earth itself shiver."
msgstr ""
"Desde los cielos, desgarrando la gruesa bóveda de nubes, descendió una "
"bestia colosal envuelta en relámpagos, con alas que proyectaban vastas "
"sombras sobre el valle inferior. Aterrizó en la montaña más alta con un "
"estruendo atronador, alzó la cabeza, enfrentando a los pequeños seres con "
"ojos como estrellas; y entonces rugió, un rugido que hizo temblar a la "
"tierra misma."

#. [message], speaker=Udhark
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1366
msgid "W-what is that beast?!"
msgstr "¿Q-qué es esa bestia?"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1370
msgid "It can't be a dragon... It's too large to be one..."
msgstr "No puede ser un dragón… Es demasiado grande para ser uno…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1374
msgid ""
"That's not just any dragon, Valerya... That's the one who nearly destroyed "
"this world in the past: the High Dragon of the Sky, Svarballi."
msgstr ""
"Ese no es cualquier dragón, Valerya… Ese es el que casi destruyó este mundo "
"en el pasado: el Alto Dragón del Cielo, Svarballi."

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1378
msgid ""
"It has been a long time, has it not, Myra of Hiera'Shirsha... I have been "
"watching you from afar since I was released, and now I finally get to face "
"you again..."
msgstr ""
"Ha pasado mucho tiempo, ¿no es así, Myra de Hiera'Shirsha…? Te he estado "
"observando desde lejos desde que fui liberado, y ahora por fin puedo "
"enfrentarte de nuevo…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1382
msgid ""
"Well, Sky Dragon, here I am. I've been looking forward to our meet too; I've "
"been preparing to kill you for a good while now, you see."
msgstr ""
"Bueno, Dragón del Cielo, aquí estoy. También he estado esperando nuestro "
"encuentro; llevo un buen rato preparándome para matarte, ¿sabes?"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1386
msgid ""
"(roaring in amusement) Indeed, I have seen your power in your last battles; "
"you have grown more powerful than you used to be. But, Myra of "
"Hiera'Shirsha... You do not think that I am the same as before either, do "
"you?"
msgstr ""
"(rugiendo divertido) En efecto, he visto tu poder en tus últimas batallas; "
"te has vuelto más poderosa de lo que solías ser. Pero, Myra de "
"Hiera'Shirsha… tú tampoco crees que yo sea el mismo de antes, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1390
msgid ""
"I know better than that, Svarballi; I have learned a lot since our last "
"meeting, and I know that even at Garet-Desh you were a shadow of your true "
"power. But now I also know why neither Nitiballi, nor Agniballi, nor Maat, "
"nor myself were able to completely destroy you in the past. And now, "
"Svarballi, I know how to finish what we all started in the past!"
msgstr ""
"Sé más que eso, Svarballi; he aprendido mucho desde nuestro último "
"encuentro, y sé que incluso en Garet-Desh eras solo una sombra de tu "
"verdadero poder. Pero ahora también sé por qué ni Nitiballi, ni Agniballi, "
"ni Maat, ni yo misma pudimos destruirte por completo en el pasado. ¡Y ahora, "
"Svarballi, sé cómo terminar lo que todos comenzamos en el pasado!"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1394
msgid ""
"I am very curious indeed to see what else you will attempt... Send your "
"'friends' away at once, Myra of Hiera'Shirsha; I want to face you alone, and "
"I want you unburdened by concern for them."
msgstr ""
"Estoy muy curioso por ver qué más intentarás… Envía lejos a tus «amigos» de "
"inmediato, Myra de Hiera'Shirsha; quiero enfrentarte a solas, y quiero que "
"estés libre de preocupaciones por ellos."

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1398
msgid ""
"Girl, I won't try and stop you from fighting him, but are you sure you don't "
"want us to help you? This is what we've been searching the Regalia for, was "
"it not?"
msgstr ""
"Chica, no intentaré detenerte de pelear contra él, pero ¿estás segura de que "
"no quieres que te ayudemos? Esto es para lo que hemos estado buscando las "
"Regalias, ¿no es así?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1402
msgid ""
"Yes, but we needed all of them, not just two. Please, everyone, go; find "
"Olokun and Derceto, reunite with Cornelya and Kenshiro... And tell Olokun to "
"find the tomb of Delfador the Great; with his staff, we'll have six out of "
"seven Regalia on our side. With them, you should be able to defeat Galdra..."
msgstr ""
"Sí, pero necesitábamos todas, no solo dos. Por favor, todos, váyanse; "
"busquen a Olokun y Derceto, reúnanse con Cornelya y Kenshiro… Y díganle a "
"Olokun que busque la tumba de Delfador el Grande; con su bastón, tendremos "
"seis de las siete Regalias de nuestro lado. Con ellas, deberían poder "
"derrotar a Galdra…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1406
msgid ""
"We'll do that, Tenma... And then we'll be waiting for you at Weldyn. Do you "
"understand that?"
msgstr "Lo haremos, Tenma… Y luego te esperaremos en Weldyn. ¿Entiendes eso?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1410
msgid "(smiling reassuringly) I do, Valerya."
msgstr "(sonriendo tranquilizadora) Lo entiendo, Valerya."

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1414
msgid ""
"Let us go, friends; as harsh as it is to admit, this is no battle for us..."
msgstr ""
"Vámonos, amigos; por duro que sea admitirlo, esta no es una batalla para "
"nosotros…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1529
msgid "Now, Sky Dragon, let us continue what we stopped at the Crystal Tower."
msgstr ""
"Ahora, Dragón del Cielo, continuemos lo que detuvimos en la Torre de Cristal."

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1533
msgid "Ages have I waited for that...!"
msgstr "¡Edades he esperado por esto…!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1539
msgid "Fight Svarballi"
msgstr "Luchar contra Svarballi"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1572
msgid "Argh...! No... way...!"
msgstr "¡Argh…! ¡De ninguna… manera…!"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1576
msgid ""
"And so, after all this time, you are still the same weak, pathetic little "
"creature as you have always been..."
msgstr ""
"Y así, después de todo este tiempo, sigues siendo la misma criatura débil y "
"patética que siempre has sido…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1580
msgid "Why... Why is my power... not enough to... destroy you...?"
msgstr "¿Por qué… por qué mi poder… no es suficiente para… destruirte…?"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1584
msgid ""
"You are like a child armed with a sword, Myra; it matters not how powerful "
"the sword is, the child will never be able to use it to full effect. Worse "
"still: your so-called 'Dragon-Slaying power' is nothing more than a power "
"you have borrowed from the spirits of Nature; a power which you must return "
"after the blink of an eye. I, the Heir of Ananke, would never fall to a fake "
"power like that. This, Myra, is what true power feels like..."
msgstr ""
"Eres como un niño armado con una espada, Myra; no importa cuán poderosa sea "
"la espada, el niño nunca podrá usarla a pleno efecto. Peor aún: tu llamado "
"«poder Mata Dragones» no es más que un poder que has tomado prestado de los "
"espíritus de la Naturaleza; un poder que debes devolver en un abrir y cerrar "
"de ojos. Yo, el Heredero de Ananke, nunca caería ante un poder falso como "
"ese. Esto, Myra, es lo que se siente el verdadero poder…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1591
msgid "(in despair) Aaahhh...!"
msgstr "(desesperada) ¡Aaahhh…!"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1595
msgid ""
"Cry, Myra of Hiera'Shirsha, cry, because the fate you are about to "
"experience is worse than death itself..."
msgstr ""
"Llora, Myra de Hiera'Shirsha, llora, porque el destino que estás a punto de "
"experimentar es peor que la muerte misma…"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1608
msgid ""
"*That girl...! I was so distracted toying with her, I did not pay attention "
"to the proximity of such vermin – but I commend her for being quick enough "
"to snatch my prey from me, even if only for a short while...*"
msgstr ""
"*¡Esa chica…! Estaba tan distraído jugando con ella que no presté atención a "
"la cercanía de tal alimaña… pero la felicito por ser lo suficientemente "
"rápida para arrebatarme mi presa, aunque solo sea por un corto rato…*"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1667
msgid "What... Who..."
msgstr "¿Qué… quién…"

#. [message], speaker=Yiwen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1671
msgid ""
"That was a close call, wasn't it? Before you ask: my name is Yiwen, I'm a "
"Windsong, and I'm a friend."
msgstr ""
"Eso estuvo cerca, ¿verdad? Antes de que preguntes: me llamo Yiwen, soy una "
"Hija del Viento, y soy una amiga."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1675
msgid "A Windsong? But... What are you doing here?"
msgstr "¿Una Hija del Viento? Pero… ¿qué haces aquí?"

#. [message], speaker=Yiwen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1679
msgid ""
"Weeks ago, our Ascendant detected a strange and unprecedented disturbance in "
"the magic currents of this world, followed by a similar one just a couple of "
"days later. The first was in the continent of Arajunna; the second, in the "
"Heart Mountains. I was sent to investigate its cause along with the "
"Foundation's best scouts, but only today did I find it out... Damn it all, "
"to think that mine would be the generation to face the Sky Dragon..."
msgstr ""
"Hace semanas, nuestra Ascendente detectó una perturbación extraña e inédita "
"en las corrientes mágicas de este mundo, seguida de una similar apenas un "
"par de días después. La primera fue en el continente de Arajunna; la "
"segunda, en las Montañas del Corazón. Fui enviada a investigar su causa "
"junto con los mejores exploradores de la Fundación, pero solo hoy descubrí "
"de qué se trataba… Maldición, pensar que mi generación sería la que "
"enfrentaría al Dragón del Cielo…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1683
msgid ""
"Look, I'm thankful that you saved me, truly, but I need to get moving, my "
"friends-"
msgstr ""
"Mira, estoy agradecida de que me hayas salvado, de verdad, pero necesito "
"moverme, mis amigos—"

#. [message], speaker=Yiwen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1687
msgid ""
"Wait! You can repay me by following me to our Foundation, Hiera'Kyria! The "
"way you were fighting, perhaps you know things we ignore - and I'm sure we "
"know things you might make use of!"
msgstr ""
"¡Espera! Puedes pagármelo siguiéndome a nuestra Fundación, ¡Hiera'Kyria! Por "
"la forma en que estabas luchando, tal vez sepas cosas que nosotros "
"ignoramos… ¡y estoy segura de que nosotros sabemos cosas que podrías "
"aprovechar!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1691
msgid "As I said, I have no time to-"
msgstr "Como dije, no tengo tiempo para—"

#. [message], speaker=Yiwen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1695
msgid ""
"(impatient) If you truly care about your friends, then they're the last ones "
"you must meet right now! Or haven't you noticed that the Sky Dragon is after "
"you?"
msgstr ""
"(impaciente) ¡Si realmente te importan tus amigos, entonces son los últimos "
"a los que debes ver ahora mismo! ¿O no te has dado cuenta de que el Dragón "
"del Cielo va tras de ti?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1699
msgid "Doesn't that work the same way for your Foundation?"
msgstr "¿Eso no funciona igual para tu Fundación?"

#. [message], speaker=Yiwen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1703
msgid ""
"Yes, but that's exactly what we've been preparing ourselves all these "
"centuries for. But now I'm the one without time for explanations; I was "
"lucky to snatch you from the Sky Dragon's claws, if we manage to make it to "
"Hiera'Kyria soon enough for the engine to be activated, it'll be a miracle. "
"But we <i>need</i> to hurry!"
msgstr ""
"Sí, pero eso es exactamente para lo que nos hemos estado preparando todos "
"estos siglos. Pero ahora soy yo la que no tiene tiempo para explicaciones; "
"tuve suerte de arrebatarte de las garras del Dragón del Cielo, si logramos "
"llegar a Hiera'Kyria lo suficientemente pronto para activar el motor, será "
"un milagro. ¡Pero <i>debemos</i> apresurarnos!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1707
msgid "(hesitant) Let's... let's go then..."
msgstr "(titubeante) Entonces… vamos…"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1758
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:680
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:777
msgid "Argh...! Curse them all..."
msgstr "¡Argh…! Malditos todos…"

#. [message], speaker=Udhark
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1772
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:732
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:829
msgid "I cannot fail my people now..."
msgstr "No puedo fallarle a mi pueblo ahora…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1786
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:744
msgid ""
"So... after so long, this is how I die...? I wish I could see them grow a "
"little more..."
msgstr ""
"Entonces… después de tanto tiempo, ¿así es como muero…? Ojalá pudiera verlos "
"crecer un poco más…"

#. [message], speaker=Talinn
#. [message], speaker=Tallin
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1800
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:953
msgid "I fall, and with me goes the Northern Alliance...!"
msgstr "¡Caigo, y conmigo se va la Alianza del Norte…!"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1815
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:843
msgid "Argh...! Curse these damn...!"
msgstr "¡Argh…! ¡Malditos sean estos…!"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/43_Twin_Hammers.cfg:1819
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:847
msgid "My brother...!"
msgstr "¡Mi hermano…!"

#. [scenario], id=44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:5
msgid "Prelude of the Final War"
msgstr "Preludio de la Guerra Final"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:89
msgid "Nightmare Army"
msgstr "Ejército de Pesadillas"

#. [side], type=Arch Mage
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:112
msgid "Master Gweniver"
msgstr "Maestra Gweniver"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:138
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:80
msgid "Umbra Army"
msgstr "Ejército Umbra"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:177
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:188
msgid "Knalgan Union"
msgstr "Unión Knalgana"

#. [message], speaker=Gweniver
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:473
msgid ""
"A hard-won victory, but a victory all the same... I cannot express my "
"gratitude with words only, strangers. We've been completely cut off from "
"Weldyn for weeks; without your aid, Dan'Tonk would have become a pile of "
"rubble by now."
msgstr ""
"Una victoria duramente ganada, pero victoria al fin… No puedo expresar mi "
"gratitud solo con palabras, extraños. Llevamos semanas completamente "
"aislados de Weldyn; sin su ayuda, Dan'Tonk ya sería un montón de escombros a "
"estas alturas."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:477
msgid ""
"We're simply helping you face a common foe, and one that will destroy us all "
"unless we stop her."
msgstr ""
"Solo estamos ayudándolos a enfrentar a un enemigo común, uno que nos "
"destruirá a todos si no la detenemos."

#. [message], speaker=Gweniver
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:481
msgid ""
"Still, to think that we would ever be aided by drakes... I mean no "
"disrespect, Queen Mother, it's merely that, after what the empire has done "
"to your kin in the Arkan-Thoria, I thought..."
msgstr ""
"Aun así, pensar que alguna vez seríamos ayudados por dracos… No pretendo "
"faltarles al respeto, Reina Madre, es solo que, después de lo que el imperio "
"le hizo a su pueblo en Arkan-Thoria, pensé…"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:485
msgid ""
"You are right to be surprised by our help, human, as we would not have "
"offered it under any other circumstance. But it is as Olokun has said: we "
"are in a danger far greater than we could pose one another, and the only way "
"to survive it is by standing together."
msgstr ""
"Tienes razón al sorprenderte por nuestra ayuda, humano, pues no la habríamos "
"ofrecido en ninguna otra circunstancia. Pero es como dijo Olokun: "
"enfrentamos un peligro mucho mayor que el que podríamos representarnos "
"mutuamente, y la única forma de sobrevivirlo es uniéndonos."

#. [message], speaker=Tayn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:489
msgid "Enemies coming from the north!"
msgstr "¡Enemigos viniendo del norte!"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:493
msgid ""
"(staring into the distance) Not enemies, but allies: the Northern "
"Alliance... (smirking) And they have some of our friends with them."
msgstr ""
"(mirando a la distancia) No son enemigos, sino aliados: la Alianza del "
"Norte… (sonriendo) Y traen a algunos de nuestros amigos con ellos."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:506
msgid ""
"This is the last time we let you design our strategies, Derceto. We were "
"lucky to find refugees in the Ford of Abez who said you were in Dan'Tonk, or "
"we'd still be on the way to the Fields of War - you know, where you told us "
"to meet you!"
msgstr ""
"Esta es la última vez que te dejamos diseñar nuestras estrategias, Derceto. "
"Tuvimos suerte de encontrar refugiados en el Vado de Abez que dijeron que "
"estabas en Dan'Tonk, o todavía estaríamos en camino a los Campos de Guerra… "
"ya sabes, ¡donde nos dijiste que nos encontraríamos!"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:510
msgid ""
"(stung) Well, my heartfelt apologies for realising Galdra's nightmares were "
"heading north and deciding to help the Wesnothians stop them before the "
"swarms poured into the Northlands!"
msgstr ""
"(picada) Bueno, mis más sinceras disculpas por darme cuenta de que las "
"pesadillas de Galdra se dirigían al norte y decidir ayudar a los "
"wesnothianos a detenerlas antes de que los enjambres se derramaran en las "
"Tierras del Norte."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:514
msgid ""
"Ladies, please, let's not fight among ourselves. We should be glad that "
"we're all safe; I for one am very glad to see that you've managed to fulfil "
"your mission, Algil. Not only that, but you've also harnessed the power of "
"Thursagan's Hammer! That means we now have four Regalia on our side..."
msgstr ""
"Damas, por favor, no peleemos entre nosotros. Deberíamos alegrarnos de que "
"todos estemos a salvo; yo por mi parte estoy muy contento de ver que "
"lograste cumplir tu misión, Algil. ¡Y no solo eso, sino que también has "
"dominado el poder del Martillo de Thursagan! Eso significa que ahora tenemos "
"cuatro Regalias de nuestro lado…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:518
msgid ""
"Five, actually; Cornelya has obtained the Regalia of the elves, or so Tenma "
"said."
msgstr ""
"Cinco, en realidad; Cornelya obtuvo la Regalia de los elfos, o eso dijo "
"Tenma."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:522
msgid ""
"And where is she? Veshtar Joohn told me she was back, but I thought she was "
"going to join you in the Heart Mountains?"
msgstr ""
"¿Y dónde está ella? Veshtar Joohn me dijo que había regresado, pero pensé "
"que se uniría a ustedes en las Montañas del Corazón."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:526
msgid ""
"Olokun, we... we've got bad news. We believed that Galdra had seized the Sky "
"Soul to resort to its power should she ever find herself on the brink of "
"defeat, but we were wrong..."
msgstr ""
"Olokun, tenemos… malas noticias. Creíamos que Galdra había tomado el Alma "
"del Cielo para recurrir a su poder si alguna vez se encontraba al borde de "
"la derrota, pero nos equivocamos…"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:530
msgid ""
"See, we had just defeated our enemies when the monster of yer people's "
"legends descended from the skies... We stood no chance against him, so that "
"girl, well..."
msgstr ""
"Verás, acabábamos de derrotar a nuestros enemigos cuando el monstruo de las "
"leyendas de tu pueblo descendió de los cielos… No teníamos ninguna "
"oportunidad contra él, así que esa chica, bueno…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:534
msgid "(appalled) No... You can't be... <i>Svarballi has been released</i>?!"
msgstr "(horrorizado) No… No puede ser… <i>¿Svarballi ha sido liberado</i>?"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:538
msgid ""
"And you left Tenma Yozora to fight him by herself?! You fools, how could you "
"do that?!"
msgstr ""
"¿Y dejaron a Tenma Yozora pelear contra él sola? ¡Idiotas, cómo pudieron "
"hacer eso!"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:542
msgid ""
"The only thing they could've achieved against Svarballi, by themselves, was "
"to die. This is Tenma's fight, in no small part because only she has any "
"hope of prevailing against the Sky Dragon at this point... But when did that "
"happen? Their battle should've been over by now, and either she'd have found "
"you already or..."
msgstr ""
"Lo único que podrían haber logrado contra Svarballi, por su cuenta, era "
"morir. Esta es la pelea de Tenma, en gran parte porque solo ella tiene "
"alguna esperanza de prevalecer contra el Dragón del Cielo en este momento… "
"Pero ¿cuándo pasó eso? Su batalla ya debería haber terminado, y o ella ya "
"los habría encontrado o…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:546
msgid ""
"Don't even... don't even think of that, Derceto! Lady Gweniver, I apologise "
"but we must leave now, our friend needs our aid..."
msgstr ""
"Ni siquiera… ni siquiera pienses en eso, Derceto. Señora Gweniver, me "
"disculpo, pero debemos irnos ahora, nuestra amiga necesita nuestra ayuda…"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:550
msgid "But, Olokun..."
msgstr "Pero, Olokun…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:554
msgid ""
"I don't care we still don't have all the Regalia, I refuse to sit idly while "
"she's fighting that monster alone!"
msgstr ""
"No me importa que todavía no tengamos todas las Regalias, ¡me niego a "
"quedarme de brazos cruzados mientras ella lucha contra ese monstruo sola!"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:565
msgid ""
"Worry not about Tenma, children; I can tell you that she is alive – though "
"for how long is beyond even my foresight..."
msgstr ""
"No se preocupen por Tenma, pequeños; puedo decirles que está viva… aunque "
"por cuánto tiempo está más allá incluso de mi visión…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:569
msgid "About time you showed your face on the battlefield, 'Avatar of Magic'."
msgstr ""
"Ya era hora de que mostraras tu rostro en el campo de batalla, «Avatar de la "
"Magia»."

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:573
msgid ""
"(chuckling) Were you that eager for me to enter the scene? Interesting, I "
"did not know you were in such a hurry for my judgment to fall on you..."
msgstr ""
"(riendo) ¿Tanto ansiabas que entrara en escena? Interesante, no sabía que "
"tenías tanta prisa por que mi juicio cayera sobre ti…"

#. [message], speaker=Gweniver
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:577
msgid ""
"Prince Aeldhoryan, we're so relieved to see with our own eyes that the "
"rumours were not true...! Please, lead us to victory!"
msgstr ""
"¡Príncipe Aeldhoryan, estamos tan aliviados de ver con nuestros propios ojos "
"que los rumores no eran ciertos…! ¡Por favor, llévenos a la victoria!"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:581
msgid ""
"Protecting you is nothing but my duty. Now, follow me! Let the Banner of the "
"West-North fly in triumph once more!"
msgstr ""
"Protegerlos no es más que mi deber. ¡Ahora, síganme! ¡Que el Estandarte del "
"Oeste-Norte vuelva a ondear en triunfo!"

#. [message], speaker=Udhark
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:606
msgid ""
"Do not lose heart now, warriors, we're close to meeting the monster face to "
"face!"
msgstr ""
"¡No pierdan el ánimo ahora, guerreros, estamos cerca de enfrentar al "
"monstruo cara a cara!"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:610
msgid ""
"Ignorant little children, you still have not the slightest idea of who you "
"are dealing with..."
msgstr ""
"Ignorantes pequeños, todavía no tienen la menor idea de con quién están "
"tratando…"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:626
msgid ""
"Curses...! Retreat, everyone! We must not face this new wave on open field!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldición…! ¡Retirada, todos! ¡No debemos enfrentar esta nueva oleada en "
"campo abierto!"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:685
msgid ""
"Damn that necromancer, again he shows up at the most inconvenient of times!"
msgstr "¡Maldito nigromante, otra vez aparece en el momento más inconveniente!"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:689
msgid ""
"The blame is yours and your companions, Wesnothian prince. My forces have "
"been dilapidated in Metheldur, so now I must restore them - and restore them "
"I shall, but with the bones of this empire that placed a second sun in the "
"heavens!"
msgstr ""
"La culpa es tuya y de tus compañeros, príncipe wesnothiano. Mis fuerzas "
"fueron devastadas en Metheldur, así que ahora debo restaurarlas… y las "
"restauraré, ¡pero con los huesos de este imperio que colocó un segundo sol "
"en los cielos!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:693
msgid ""
"Wesir, you were a renowned master of New Maat'Kare yourself once! We should "
"be joining forces against Galdra and Svarballi; or do you think that there "
"will even be a world for you to rule should they prevail?"
msgstr ""
"¡Wesir, tú mismo fuiste un maestro renombrado de Nueva Maat'Kare alguna vez! "
"Deberíamos unir fuerzas contra Galdra y Svarballi; ¿o crees que siquiera "
"habrá un mundo para que lo gobiernes si ellos prevalecen?"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:697
msgid ""
"Mine is the realm of death, puppy of Ankhmare; it means nothing to me if "
"this entire world dies. In fact, let the Sky Dragon and this new aberration "
"have their way; once their rampage is completed, I shall have an entire "
"planet's worth of corpses to raise - and no one left to challenge me!"
msgstr ""
"Mío es el reino de la muerte, cachorro de Ankhmare; no me significa nada si "
"todo este mundo muere. De hecho, que el Dragón del Cielo y esta nueva "
"aberración hagan lo que quieran; una vez que terminen su devastación, tendré "
"un planeta entero de cadáveres para levantar… ¡y nadie que me desafíe!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:701
msgid ""
"And so you shall be the king of the ashes. A goal worthy of any petty "
"necromancer; bravo!"
msgstr ""
"Y así serás el rey de las cenizas. Un objetivo digno de cualquier nigromante "
"insignificante; ¡bravo!"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:705
msgid ""
"The one petty mind here is yours, Crimson Sorceress, who can see no further "
"than the earth you tread on. This is not the only world out there, and my "
"ambition is as vast as the Existence that encompasses them..."
msgstr ""
"La mente insignificante aquí es la tuya, Hechicera Carmesí, que no puede ver "
"más allá de la tierra que pisas. Este no es el único mundo que existe, y mi "
"ambición es tan vasta como la Existencia que los abarca a todos…"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:715
msgid "Defeat Wesir"
msgstr "Derrota a Wesir"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:763
msgid "Curses, is this another trickery of that girl?!"
msgstr "¡Maldición, es otra artimaña de esa chica!"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:767
msgid "(alarmed) No... I think... it's something far worse..."
msgstr "(alarmado) No… creo… que es algo mucho peor…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:771
msgid ""
"Then what was that? Was it caused by the battle between Tenma and the Sky "
"Dragon?"
msgstr ""
"Entonces ¿qué fue eso? ¿Fue causado por la batalla entre Tenma y el Dragón "
"del Cielo?"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:775
msgid ""
"That we can't say for sure; what we can say is that the currents of magic of "
"this entire world have just suffered a cataclysmic disturbance..."
msgstr ""
"Eso no podemos afirmarlo con seguridad; lo que sí podemos decir es que las "
"corrientes mágicas de todo este mundo acaban de sufrir una perturbación "
"cataclísmica…"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:779
msgid "And its echoes come from the north, where..."
msgstr "Y sus ecos vienen del norte, donde…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:783
msgid ""
"...Where one of the currents' convergences lie – and where Tenma must be..."
msgstr ""
"…donde se encuentra una de las convergencias de las corrientes… y donde debe "
"estar Tenma…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:787
msgid ""
"Speaking of which, she asked me to give you a message. She says you should "
"search for the tomb of Delfador the Great and find his staff; according to "
"her, that's the Regalia of the humans."
msgstr ""
"A propósito de eso, me pidió que te diera un mensaje. Dice que deberías "
"buscar la tumba de Delfador el Grande y encontrar su bastón; según ella, ese "
"es la Regalia de los humanos."

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:791
msgid "Delfador's staff, a Regalia...?!"
msgstr "¡El bastón de Delfador, una Regalia…?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:795
msgid ""
"Then go and find it yourself; I'm going north and search for Tenma. In any "
"case, I'm sure the staff takes a great level of power and wisdom to be "
"wielded..."
msgstr ""
"Entonces ve y encuéntralo tú mismo; yo voy al norte a buscar a Tenma. De "
"todos modos, estoy seguro de que el bastón requiere un gran nivel de poder y "
"sabiduría para ser empuñado…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:799
msgid ""
"Now you're being obtuse, Olokun. There was a reason she wanted you, of all "
"people, to wield it. A Regalia must be wielded by one who commands the "
"respect of his people. I may be respected by Northerners, Ankhmare by "
"Maat'Karians, Aeldhoryan by Wesnothians, Dragana by the Baryags, and Natsu "
"by the Sogen; but you have fought alongside all these people, and they have "
"all noticed how you've risked your own life for them, even though you were "
"not one of them."
msgstr ""
"Ahora estás siendo obtuso, Olokun. Había una razón por la que ella quería "
"que tú, de entre todos, lo empuñaras. Una Regalia debe ser empuñada por "
"alguien que comande el respeto de su pueblo. Yo puedo ser respetada por los "
"norteños, Ankhmare por los maat’karianos, Aeldhoryan por los wesnothianos, "
"Dragana por los barjanes y Natsu por los sogen; pero tú has luchado junto a "
"toda esta gente, y todos han notado cómo arriesgaste tu propia vida por "
"ellos, aunque no eras uno de los suyos."

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:803
msgid ""
"She's right. Tales of how he fought against Aetheryon along with Tenma are "
"famous amongst us; if we were to choose a representative of the humans in "
"this alliance, we'd choose him."
msgstr ""
"Tiene razón. Las historias de cómo luchó contra Aetheryon junto a Tenma son "
"famosas entre nosotros; si tuviéramos que elegir a un representante de los "
"humanos en esta alianza, lo elegiríamos a él."

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:807
msgid ""
"I have witnessed, as did every Baryag, how bravely he fought in defence of "
"Mhreghost. Such a powerful, fearless and loyal fighter is the kind our "
"people strive to become. He has earned our respect, loyalty, and admiration."
msgstr ""
"Yo misma fui testigo, como cada barjano, de lo valientemente que luchó en "
"defensa de Mhreghost. Un luchador tan poderoso, valiente y leal es el tipo "
"al que nuestro pueblo aspira a parecerse. Se ha ganado nuestro respeto, "
"lealtad y admiración."

#. [message], speaker=Tallin
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:816
msgid ""
"Olokun helped us fight Aelvar, even descending into the depths of Knalga to "
"prevent him from destroying the Earth's Core. Although he was unable to "
"succeed, we of the Northern Alliance were thankful that such a powerful mage "
"had willingly joined our fight. As the Alliance's human representative, I "
"make the Baryag Queen's words my own."
msgstr ""
"Olokun nos ayudó a luchar contra Aelvar, incluso descendiendo a las "
"profundidades de Knalga para evitar que destruyera el Núcleo de la Tierra. "
"Aunque no pudo tener éxito, nosotros de la Alianza del Norte estuvimos "
"agradecidos de que un mago tan poderoso se uniera voluntariamente a nuestra "
"lucha. Como representante humano de la Alianza, hago mías las palabras de la "
"reina barjana."

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:822
msgid ""
"Olokun helped us fight Aelvar, even descending into the depths of Knalga to "
"prevent him from destroying the Earth's Core. In spite of how that affair "
"ended, we of the Northern Alliance are thankful that such a powerful mage "
"joined our fight. As the Alliance's last human authority, I make Vasilya's "
"words my own."
msgstr ""
"Olokun nos ayudó a luchar contra Aelvar, incluso descendiendo a las "
"profundidades de Knalga para evitar que destruyera el Núcleo de la Tierra. A "
"pesar de cómo terminó ese asunto, nosotros de la Alianza del Norte estamos "
"agradecidos de que un mago tan poderoso se uniera a nuestra lucha. Como "
"última autoridad humana de la Alianza, hago mías las palabras de Vasilya."

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:828
msgid ""
"Gweniver has told me of how fiercely you fought to defend Dan'Tonk; even if "
"you say that you only wanted to relieve the Northerners of more enemies, "
"only someone who truly cared about these people would have risked so much "
"for them. I, Crown Prince Aeldhoryan of Wesnoth, accept you as our paramount "
"leader."
msgstr ""
"Gweniver me ha contado lo ferozmente que luchaste para defender Dan'Tonk; "
"incluso si dices que solo querías aliviar a los norteños de más enemigos, "
"solo alguien que realmente se preocupara por esta gente habría arriesgado "
"tanto por ellos. Yo, príncipe heredero Aeldhoryan de Wesnoth, te acepto como "
"nuestro líder supremo."

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:832
msgid ""
"And what can Maat'Karians and Chomi say about you? We all have known you "
"from childhood, and we all know the person you have grown to be: "
"accomplished and brave, but also kind and generous. You journeyed a world in "
"turmoil for the slimmest hope of finding the one who could relieve us of our "
"ancient burden. I should no longer address you as my disciple, but as my "
"fellow Master. You, Olokun, truly are the one most fitting to stand for us "
"all."
msgstr ""
"¿Y qué pueden decir los maat’karianos y los chomi de ti? Todos te conocemos "
"desde la infancia, y todos sabemos en qué persona te has convertido: "
"accomplished y valiente, pero también amable y generoso. Recorriste un mundo "
"en agitación por la más mínima esperanza de encontrar a quien pudiera "
"aliviar nuestra antigua carga. Ya no debería dirigirme a ti como mi "
"discípulo, sino como mi compañero Maestro. Tú, Olokun, realmente eres el más "
"apto para representarnos a todos."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:836
msgid ""
"Well... After such words, how could I even think of refusing? If this is "
"everyone's will, then I, Olokun of Ifeh and New Maat'Kare, before all of "
"you, vow to honour your trust to the fullest of my abilities. I will find "
"the Regalia of humans and use it for the sake of all of you!"
msgstr ""
"Bueno… Después de tales palabras, ¿cómo podría siquiera pensar en negarme? "
"Si esta es la voluntad de todos, entonces yo, Olokun de Ifeh y Nueva "
"Maat'Kare, ante todos ustedes, juro honrar su confianza con todo lo que esté "
"a mi alcance. ¡Encontraré la Regalia de los humanos y la usaré por el bien "
"de todos ustedes!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:840
msgid "<i>Thunderous approval</i>"
msgstr "<i>Aprobación atronadora</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:844
msgid ""
"I know where Delfador's tomb lies; with my seal, we'll have safe-conduct "
"through Wesnothian lands."
msgstr ""
"Sé dónde yace la tumba de Delfador; con mi sello, tendremos salvoconducto "
"por las tierras de Wesnoth."

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:848
msgid ""
"Please, allow some of my warriors to escort you; your Wesnothians have been "
"fighting fiercely for hours, but my Baryags are well rested."
msgstr ""
"Por favor, permite que algunos de mis guerreros te escolten; tus "
"wesnothianos han estado luchando ferozmente durante horas, pero mis barjanes "
"están bien descansados."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:852
msgid ""
"I'll go north and see what has happened there; Bogor, you might benefit from "
"following me, as the north is where the orcs of this continents live in "
"greatest numbers."
msgstr ""
"Yo iré al norte a ver qué ha pasado allí; Bogor, podrías beneficiarte de "
"seguirme, ya que el norte es donde viven la mayor cantidad de orcos de este "
"continente."

#. [message], speaker=Bogor
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:856
msgid ""
"Well thought; I really want to put our distant cousins to the test of my "
"sword arm... Also, I need to find out if this blade will work like the "
"shamans predicted it would..."
msgstr ""
"Bien pensado; realmente quiero poner a prueba a nuestros primos lejanos con "
"mi brazo de espada… Además, necesito descubrir si esta hoja funcionará como "
"predijeron los chamanes…"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:865
msgid ""
"I've spoken with Udhark, Algil and Tallinn, and we've agreed to stay here, "
"tend to the wounded and protect Dan'Tonk against further aggression. Should "
"you come across refugees in the countryside, prince, send them here and we "
"shall protect them too."
msgstr ""
"Hablé con Udhark, Algil y Tallin, y acordamos quedarnos aquí, atender a los "
"heridos y proteger Dan'Tonk de más agresiones. Si encuentras refugiados en "
"el campo, príncipe, envíalos aquí y también los protegeremos."

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:871
msgid ""
"I've spoken with Udhark, Algil and Donar, and we've agreed to stay here, "
"tend to the wounded and protect Dan'Tonk against further aggression. Should "
"you come across refugees in the countryside, prince, send them here and we "
"shall protect them too."
msgstr ""
"Hablé con Udhark, Algil y Donar, y acordamos quedarnos aquí, atender a los "
"heridos y proteger Dan'Tonk de más agresiones. Si encuentras refugiados en "
"el campo, príncipe, envíalos aquí y también los protegeremos."

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:877
msgid "Thank you for helping my people, friends..."
msgstr "Gracias por ayudar a mi pueblo, amigos…"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:881
msgid ""
"(hugging Olokun) And please, return as soon as you can, I'm only staying "
"here not to slow you down, but I swear I'll flood all of Wesnoth to search "
"for you if I have to!"
msgstr ""
"(abrazando a Olokun) Y por favor, regresa lo antes posible; solo me quedo "
"aquí para no retrasarlos, ¡pero juro que inundaré todo Wesnoth para buscarte "
"si es necesario!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:885
msgid "(smiling) All right, I promise I'll be back in a blink..."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Está bien, prometo que volveré en un abrir y cerrar de ojos…"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:947
msgid ""
"By all Nine Hells, we're surrounded by swarms of abominations from all "
"sides...!"
msgstr ""
"¡Por todos los Nueve Infiernos, estamos rodeados por enjambres de "
"abominaciones desde todos lados…!"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:951
msgid ""
"We have no choice but to fight on! If we want to protect our world and our "
"people, we have no choice but to win this battle!"
msgstr ""
"¡No tenemos más opción que seguir luchando! Si queremos proteger nuestro "
"mundo y a nuestra gente, ¡no tenemos más opción que ganar esta batalla!"

#. [message], speaker=Tallin
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:963
msgid "No, not another enemy...!"
msgstr "¡No, otro enemigo no…!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:967
msgid "(surprised) Wait... Those banners, they're...!"
msgstr "(sorprendido) Espera… ¡Esos estandartes, son…!"

#. [unit], id=Oluwinde, type=Chomi Hero
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1001
msgid "Captain Oluwinde"
msgstr "Capitán Oluwinde"

#. [unit], id=Shamut, type=Washraha Lightning Striker
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1019
msgid "Commander Shamut"
msgstr "Comandante Shamut"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1145
msgid ""
"Blessed heavens, they're our friends from beyond the ocean! But why are they "
"here...?"
msgstr ""
"¡Cielos benditos, son nuestros amigos de más allá del océano! Pero ¿por qué "
"están aquí…?"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1149
msgid ""
"A few weeks ago, we received a messenger from the fauns and the faeries in "
"Argea, warning us that the great storm we have been preparing for was about "
"to make landfall in the Great Continent. Our fleet stopped at Ifeh, where "
"Father Yroko reinforced our army with his own soldiers. We were also joined "
"by this Washrahani warrior, Shamut, who was more than willing to help us "
"when she learned we were going to Wesnoth..."
msgstr ""
"Hace unas semanas recibimos un mensajero de los faunos y las hadas en Argea, "
"advirtiéndonos que la gran tormenta para la que nos hemos estado preparando "
"estaba a punto de llegar al Gran Continente. Nuestra flota se detuvo en "
"Ifeh, donde el padre Yroko reforzó nuestro ejército con sus propios "
"soldados. También se nos unió esta guerrera washrahani, Shamut, que estaba "
"más que dispuesta a ayudarnos cuando supo que íbamos a Wesnoth…"

#. [message], speaker=Shamut
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1153
msgid "(says something in her own language)"
msgstr "(dice algo en su propio idioma)"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1157
msgid ""
"She says that her sister was a commander fighting for Wesnothians, and that "
"they let her die, so she wants to avenge her."
msgstr ""
"Dice que su hermana era una comandante que luchaba por los wesnothianos, y "
"que la dejaron morir, así que quiere vengarla."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1161
msgid ""
"The more allies we get, the better. And you, Chief Bogor, have you come "
"because you've begun to consider us your friends?"
msgstr ""
"Cuanto más aliados tengamos, mejor. Y tú, jefe Bogor, ¿has venido porque "
"empezaste a considerarnos tus amigos?"

#. [message], speaker=Bogor
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1165
msgid ""
"(smirking) Don't go that far, human... though it has been fun, to fight "
"alongside you. You sure stumble on the best battles. Speaking of which, "
"where is that elf girl, Cornelya? Don't tell me I came all this way only to "
"find her dead?"
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) No exageres, humano… aunque ha sido divertido luchar a tu lado. "
"Seguro que tropiezas con las mejores batallas. A propósito, ¿dónde está esa "
"chica elfa, Cornelya? No me digas que vine hasta aquí solo para encontrarla "
"muerta."

#. [message], speaker=Bogor
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1345
msgid "Ha! Speaking of the devil!"
msgstr "¡Ja! ¡Hablando del diablo!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1349
msgid ""
"(laughs) I shouldn't be surprised that you have found your way to the "
"biggest battle of our time, Bogor!"
msgstr ""
"(ríe) No debería sorprenderme que hayas encontrado el camino hacia la "
"batalla más grande de nuestra era, ¡Bogor!"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1353
msgid "Och, how did she...?"
msgstr "¡Och, cómo lo hizo…?"

#. [message], speaker=Umbrius
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1357
msgid ""
"As the Queen-in-the-Woods, she's able to open the Sidhe, or the pathway "
"connecting the mundane and the faerie worlds, which can be accessed through "
"any Great Tree anywhere on Irdya. Thus we were able to move from the "
"Heartwood Valley to the Lins-Elens, and then here, in no time."
msgstr ""
"Como Reina-en-el-Bosque, es capaz de abrir el Sidhe, o el camino que conecta "
"el mundo mundano con el mundo feérico, al que se puede acceder a través de "
"cualquier Gran Árbol en cualquier parte de Irdya. Así pudimos movernos desde "
"el Valle del Corazón de Madera a los Lins-Elens, y luego aquí, en un abrir y "
"cerrar de ojos."

#. [message], speaker=Idunn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1361
msgid ""
"It's impressive that she's managed to let even humans cross it. Never had I "
"heard of anyone other than the Children of the Forests being able to walk it "
"unscathed."
msgstr ""
"Es impresionante que haya logrado que incluso humanos lo crucen. Nunca había "
"oído de nadie más que de los Hijos del Bosque que pudiera caminarlo sin "
"sufrir daño."

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1365
msgid "Not <i>unscathed</i>; I've never felt so nauseated in my life..."
msgstr ""
"No <i>sin sufrir daño</i>; nunca me había sentido tan mareada en mi vida…"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1374
msgid ""
"And so another Irdyan Queen has appeared... (giggles) The tides are taking "
"an interesting turn..."
msgstr ""
"Y así ha aparecido otra reina de Irdya… (ríe) Las mareas están tomando un "
"giro interesante…"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1378
msgid ""
"Indeed they are, Avatar of Magic, for now we have more friends on our side. "
"Everyone, CHARGE!"
msgstr ""
"En efecto lo están, Avatar de la Magia, pues ahora tenemos más amigos de "
"nuestro lado. ¡Todos, AL ATAQUE!"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1389
msgid ""
"And you, Wesir... Once I deemed you the brightest mind of our generation, "
"and one of the finest in all our history; now I see how severely I have "
"overestimated you. You are no longer an Umbra Master; you are nothing but a "
"lowly necromancer, mastered by his own shadows, and so you shall have the "
"only end worthy of one!"
msgstr ""
"Y tú, Wesir… Una vez te consideré la mente más brillante de nuestra "
"generación, y una de las mejores en toda nuestra historia; ahora veo cuán "
"gravemente te sobreestimé. Ya no eres un Maestro Umbra; no eres más que un "
"vil nigromante, dominado por sus propias sombras, ¡y así tendrás el único "
"final que merece uno!"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1393
msgid "I will relish having your bones in my army, Ankhmare...!"
msgstr "¡Disfrutaré teniendo tus huesos en mi ejército, Ankhmare…!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1406
msgid "Repel the attack on Dan'Tonk"
msgstr "Repele el ataque a Dan'Tonk"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1422
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1737
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:32
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1100
msgid "Death of any of the Kings and Queens"
msgstr "Muerte de cualquiera de los Reyes y Reinas"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1446
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1769
msgid "Death of Idunn"
msgstr "Muerte de Idunn"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1469
msgid "Arrrgh!!! I... must... retreat...!"
msgstr "¡Arrrgh!!! ¡Debo… retirarme…!"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1473
msgid "Beware, he can teleport!"
msgstr "¡Cuidado, puede teletransportarse!"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1484
msgid "Curses, he escaped again..."
msgstr "Maldición, escapó otra vez…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1488
msgid ""
"Judging by the damage he's taken, however, he won't be able to go far this "
"time."
msgstr ""
"A juzgar por el daño que ha recibido, sin embargo, esta vez no podrá ir muy "
"lejos."

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1513
msgid ""
"And so you have managed to turn the tides of battle and even lay a hand on "
"me, children... Very well, you have won yourselves another chance; let us "
"see if you can surprise me yet again..."
msgstr ""
"Y así lograron cambiar las mareas de la batalla e incluso ponerme una mano "
"encima, pequeños… Muy bien, se han ganado otra oportunidad; veamos si pueden "
"sorprenderme una vez más…"

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1524
msgid "Wait, was that it...? Has Galdra been defeated?"
msgstr "Espera, ¿eso fue todo…? ¿Galdra ha sido derrotada?"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1528
msgid ""
"Most certainly not; in fact, I fear we haven't even seen her full power "
"yet..."
msgstr ""
"Definitivamente no; de hecho, temo que ni siquiera hemos visto su poder "
"completo aún…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1532
msgid "Still, for some reason she's decided to give us a truce..."
msgstr "Aun así, por alguna razón decidió darnos una tregua…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/44_Prelude_Of_The_Final_War.cfg:1543
msgid "How could we waste so much time here when Tenma is in need?!"
msgstr "¡Cómo pudimos perder tanto tiempo aquí cuando Tenma nos necesita!"

#. [scenario], id=45_Return_Of_The_King
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:5
msgid "Return of the King"
msgstr "El Regreso del Rey"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:25
msgid "Find the Tomb of Delfador the Great"
msgstr "Encuentra la Tumba de Delfador el Grande"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:49
msgid "NOTE: Olokun may now recruit Baryags and Maat'Karians"
msgstr "NOTA: Olokun ahora puede reclutar barjanes y maat’karianos"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:337
msgid "Snowfall in the middle of spring? Is even the weather going crazy now?"
msgstr "¿Nieve en pleno primavera? ¿Hasta el clima se ha vuelto loco ahora?"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:341
msgid ""
"This is a spell cast by an ancient elven enchantress. According to legend, "
"she lived in what we now call Glyn's Forest before Haldric I's arrival; at "
"first, she was suspicious of humans, but then she fell in love with Prince "
"Glyn as he walked amidst these same trees. It is said that he loved her too, "
"but the bad blood between elves and humans forced them apart."
msgstr ""
"Este es un hechizo lanzado por una antigua encantadora elfa. Según la "
"leyenda, vivía en lo que ahora llamamos Bosque de Glyn antes de la llegada "
"de Haldric I; al principio desconfiaba de los humanos, pero luego se enamoró "
"del príncipe Glyn mientras caminaba entre estos mismos árboles. Se dice que "
"él también la amaba, pero la mala sangre entre elfos y humanos los separó."

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:345
msgid ""
"One day, he was severely wounded in battle, and his last command was for his "
"soldiers to bring him here, where he died in the enchantress' arms. To "
"honour their love, Glyn's younger brother buried him here, and the "
"enchantress cast a spell on this valley that blankets it in perennial snow; "
"for it is said that Prince Glyn loved watching ice flowers falling from the "
"sky."
msgstr ""
"Un día quedó gravemente herido en batalla, y su último mandato fue que sus "
"soldados lo trajeran aquí, donde murió en brazos de la encantadora. Para "
"honrar su amor, el hermano menor de Glyn lo enterró aquí, y la encantadora "
"lanzó un hechizo sobre este valle que lo cubre de nieve perenne; pues se "
"dice que al príncipe Glyn le encantaba ver caer flores de hielo del cielo."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:349
msgid ""
"And now a human of Glyn's bloodline, one whose love for an elf blossoms "
"freely, walks amongst these same white trees... Times do change, "
"fortunately..."
msgstr ""
"Y ahora un humano de la sangre de Glyn, uno cuyo amor por una elfa florece "
"libremente, camina entre estos mismos árboles blancos… Los tiempos cambian, "
"afortunadamente…"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:353
msgid ""
"Even more fortunate is the fact that, after so long, I am finally able to "
"walk on Wesnothian soil with my beloved and my son by my side... Thank you "
"for accepting to come with us, Kenshiro, it truly means the world for me."
msgstr ""
"Aún más afortunado es el hecho de que, después de tanto tiempo, por fin "
"pueda caminar en suelo wesnothiano con mi amada y mi hijo a mi lado… Gracias "
"por aceptar venir con nosotros, Kenshiro, realmente significa el mundo para "
"mí."

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:357
msgid "(smiles)"
msgstr "(sonríe)"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:361
msgid ""
"Don't get the wrong idea, old man, I just accepted because Cornelya "
"insisted..."
msgstr ""
"No te hagas ideas equivocadas, viejo, solo acepté porque Cornelya insistió…"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:365
msgid ""
"Friends, beware; knowing Wesir, he's certainly set undead guards all over "
"these woods. Speaking of which, Prince Aeldhoryan, didn't you say the rulers "
"of Wesnoth are all buried here?"
msgstr ""
"Amigos, cuidado; conociendo a Wesir, seguro que ha colocado guardias no "
"muertos por todo este bosque. A propósito, príncipe Aeldhoryan, ¿no dijiste "
"que todos los gobernantes de Wesnoth están enterrados aquí?"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:369
msgid ""
"They are, but no matter how powerful Wesir is, he will not be able to defile "
"their corpses with his arts, as they were filled with holy magic before "
"their burial."
msgstr ""
"Así es, pero no importa cuán poderoso sea Wesir, no podrá profanar sus "
"cadáveres con sus artes, pues fueron imbuidos con magia sagrada antes de su "
"entierro."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:373
msgid "And so we must cleanse these woods of Wesir and his undead alone..."
msgstr "Y así debemos limpiar estos bosques de Wesir y sus no muertos solos…"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:390
msgid ""
"Give up, Wesir. You are cornered, your armies are dust, and you are too "
"weakened to teleport beyond our reach. Surrender peacefully now, so that you "
"may retain some of your dignity!"
msgstr ""
"Ríndete, Wesir. Estás acorralado, tus ejércitos son polvo y estás demasiado "
"debilitado para teletransportarte fuera de nuestro alcance. ¡Ríndete "
"pacíficamente ahora, para que puedas conservar algo de tu dignidad!"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:394
msgid ""
"I am cornered and wounded, that is true, but to say that my armies have been "
"destroyed... The power of the Umbra Arts is everlasting and absolute, "
"Ankhmare; as long as there is Death, it shall never fade!"
msgstr ""
"Estoy acorralado y herido, eso es cierto, pero decir que mis ejércitos han "
"sido destruídos… El poder de las Artes Umbra es eterno y absoluto, Ankhmare; "
"mientras exista la Muerte, ¡nunca se desvanecerá!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:401
msgid ""
"Wesir, you fool, what do you think you've just done?! Don't you know the "
"effects of opening a portal to the Land of the Dead?!"
msgstr ""
"¡Wesir, idiota, qué crees que acabas de hacer! ¿No conoces los efectos de "
"abrir un portal a la Tierra de los Muertos?"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:405
msgid ""
"Better than you do, boy, but I don't care about this world, or the other, "
"not any more. If I'm to die, I shall take existence itself down with me!"
msgstr ""
"Mejor que tú, muchacho, pero ya no me importa este mundo ni el otro. Si voy "
"a morir, ¡me llevaré a la existencia misma conmigo!"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:409
msgid ""
"Damn him, now every minute that passes a new swarm of undead will be "
"unleashed!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldito, ahora cada minuto que pasa se desatará un nuevo enjambre de no "
"muertos!"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:413
msgid ""
"Olokun, what exactly did you mean by 'effects of opening a portal to the "
"Land of the Dead'?"
msgstr ""
"Olokun, ¿qué quisiste decir exactamente con «efectos de abrir un portal a la "
"Tierra de los Muertos»?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:417
msgid ""
"Realms that have been apart from one another since the dawn of time are not "
"supposed to be bound together like this. If this portal remains open, both "
"the Living and the Dead Worlds shall be merged, leading to mutual "
"annihilation."
msgstr ""
"Reinos que han estado separados desde el amanecer de los tiempos no deberían "
"unirse de esta manera. Si este portal permanece abierto, tanto el Mundo de "
"los Vivos como el de los Muertos se fusionarán, llevando a una aniquilación "
"mutua."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:421
msgid ""
"Then finding Delfador's tomb has become even more urgent. Olokun, "
"concentrate on reaching it, we'll cover you!"
msgstr ""
"Entonces encontrar la tumba de Delfador se ha vuelto aún más urgente. "
"Olokun, concéntrate en llegar a ella, ¡te cubriremos!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:440
msgid ""
"<i>Here the bodies of King Haldric I and Queen Jessene rest until the day "
"the stars fall from the Heavens and engulf the world in flames.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Aquí descansan los cuerpos del rey Haldric I y la reina Jessene hasta el "
"día en que las estrellas caigan de los Cielos y envuelvan al mundo en llamas."
"</i>"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:457
msgid ""
"<i>Here the bodies of King Haldric II and Queen Elga rests until the day the "
"stars fall from the Heavens and engulf the world in flames.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Aquí descansan los cuerpos del rey Haldric II y la reina Elga hasta el "
"día en que las estrellas caigan de los Cielos y envuelvan al mundo en llamas."
"</i>"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:474
msgid ""
"<i>Here the body of King Glyn rests until the day the stars fall from the "
"Heavens and engulf the world in flames.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Aquí descansa el cuerpo del rey Glyn hasta el día en que las estrellas "
"caigan de los Cielos y envuelvan al mundo en llamas.</i>"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:491
msgid ""
"<i>Here the bodies of King Haldus and Queen Erida rest until the day the "
"stars fall from the Heavens and engulf the world in flames.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Aquí descansan los cuerpos del rey Haldus y la reina Erida hasta el día "
"en que las estrellas caigan de los Cielos y envuelvan al mundo en llamas.</i>"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:507
msgid ""
"<i>Here the bodies of King Haldric III and Queen Ethelyann rest until the "
"day the stars fall from the Heavens and engulf the world in flames.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Aquí descansan los cuerpos del rey Haldric III y la reina Ethelyann hasta "
"el día en que las estrellas caigan de los Cielos y envuelvan al mundo en "
"llamas.</i>"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:523
msgid ""
"<i>Here the bodies of Queen Li'sar and King Konrad I rest until the day the "
"stars fall from the Heavens and engulf the world in flames.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Aquí descansan los cuerpos de la reina Li'sar y el rey Konrad I hasta el "
"día en que las estrellas caigan de los Cielos y envuelvan al mundo en llamas."
"</i>"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:539
msgid ""
"<i>Here the bodies of King Vortern Decthor and Queen Reana rest until the "
"day the stars fall from the Heavens and engulf the world in flames.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Aquí descansan los cuerpos del rey Vortern Decthor y la reina Reana hasta "
"el día en que las estrellas caigan de los Cielos y envuelvan al mundo en "
"llamas.</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:543
msgid "Oh, look, that's my aunt!"
msgstr "¡Oh, mira, esa es mi tía!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:559
msgid ""
"<i>Here the bodies of King Elemyrion the Half-Elf and Queen Alaevyanne rest "
"until the day the stars fall from the Heavens and engulf the world in flames."
"</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Aquí descansan los cuerpos del rey Elemyrion el Medio Elfo y la reina "
"Alaevyanne hasta el día en que las estrellas caigan de los Cielos y "
"envuelvan al mundo en llamas.</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:563
msgid ""
"She was my cousin, and he was a good friend. Together we ventured into the "
"lands beyond the Estmark once, it was such fun - even though  Alaevyanne "
"wouldn't stop complaining at everything. Great times..."
msgstr ""
"Ella era mi prima, y él un buen amigo. Juntos exploramos las tierras más "
"allá de las Colinas de la Marca Oriental una vez, fue muy divertido… aunque "
"Alaevyanne no dejaba de quejarse por todo. Grandes tiempos…"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:579
msgid ""
"<i>Here the bodies of King Gawen Haldric Hagarthen and Queen Messene rest "
"until the day the stars fall from the Heavens and engulf the world in flames."
"</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Aquí descansan los cuerpos del rey Gawen Haldric Hagarthen y la reina "
"Messene hasta el día en que las estrellas caigan de los Cielos y envuelvan "
"al mundo en llamas.</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:583
msgid ""
"Gawen the Unifier, as he became known. In his reign, Wesnothians regained "
"control over their own lands and lives; but he made sure that the Akladians "
"were just as part of the new Wesnoth."
msgstr ""
"Gawen el Unificador, como se le conoció. Durante su reinado, los "
"wesnothianos recuperaron el control de sus propias tierras y vidas; pero se "
"aseguró de que los akladianos también formaran parte del nuevo Wesnoth."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:599
msgid ""
"<i>Here the body of King Kalyen Hagarthen rests until the day the stars fall "
"from the Heavens and engulf the world in flames.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Aquí descansa el cuerpo del rey Kalyen Hagarthen hasta el día en que las "
"estrellas caigan de los Cielos y envuelvan al mundo en llamas.</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:603
msgid ""
"And with him the Hagarthen Dinasty ended, being replaced by the Iron "
"Dinasty..."
msgstr ""
"Y con él terminó la dinastía Hagarthen, siendo reemplazada por la dinastía "
"del Hierro…"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:619
msgid ""
"<i>Here the body of Delfador the Great rests until the day the stars fall "
"from the Heavens and engulf the world in flames.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Aquí descansa el cuerpo de Delfador el Grande hasta el día en que las "
"estrellas caigan de los Cielos y envuelvan al mundo en llamas.</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:623
msgid ""
"That is the one! Be careful, though, as it is not unlikely that protective "
"spells have been cast on it."
msgstr ""
"¡Esa es! Ten cuidado, sin embargo, no es improbable que se hayan lanzado "
"hechizos protectores sobre ella."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:630
msgid ""
"It does have magical wards around it, but nothing I can't dispel... I "
"disturb your eternal rest now, Delfador of Wesnoth, but I promise I shall "
"compensate it by making sure our world endures... (seizes the staff)"
msgstr ""
"Sí tiene wardas mágicas a su alrededor, pero nada que no pueda disipar… "
"Perturbo tu descanso eterno ahora, Delfador de Wesnoth, pero prometo "
"compensarlo asegurándome de que nuestro mundo perdure… (toma el bastón)"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:634
msgid "So? Do you feel anything different?"
msgstr "¿Y? ¿Sientes algo diferente?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:638
msgid ""
"I don't; in fact, I can't even feel any great power within this staff. Could "
"it be that it's not the actual Reg-"
msgstr ""
"No; de hecho, ni siquiera siento un gran poder dentro de este bastón. ¿Será "
"posible que no sea la verdadera Re—"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:647
msgid "Olokun?! Damn it, where did he go?!"
msgstr "¡¿Olokun?! ¡Maldición, a dónde se fue?!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:663
msgid "...What... Where..."
msgstr "…¿Qué… dónde…"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:667
msgid "So you are the one chosen to wield my power..."
msgstr "Así que tú eres el elegido para empuñar mi poder…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:671
msgid "Who are you...? "
msgstr "¿Quién eres…?"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:675
msgid ""
"I am he whose legacy you seek to claim. The Heiress has chosen you to wield "
"my staff, but whether I will make the same choice is another matter. I ask "
"you, Olokun Maahes, are you a servant of the Light?"
msgstr ""
"Soy aquel cuyo legado buscas reclamar. La Heredera te ha elegido para "
"empuñar mi bastón, pero si yo haré la misma elección es otro asunto. Te "
"pregunto, Olokun Maahes, ¿eres un servidor de la Luz?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:679
msgid "I have dedicated my entire life to studying it..."
msgstr "He dedicado toda mi vida a estudiarla…"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:683
msgid ""
"Dissecting a flower does not equal understanding either its beauty or its "
"role in the chain of life; likewise, the study of Light magic alone will not "
"enable you to understand its essence. I ask you again, Olokun Maahes, are "
"you a servant of the Light?"
msgstr ""
"Disecar una flor no equivale a entender ni su belleza ni su papel en la "
"cadena de la vida; de igual modo, el estudio de la magia de la Luz por sí "
"solo no te permitirá comprender su esencia. Te pregunto de nuevo, Olokun "
"Maahes, ¿eres un servidor de la Luz?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:687
msgid ""
"I fight to protect life and justice; I fight so that the innocent may have a "
"chance to live freely and peacefully."
msgstr ""
"Lucho para proteger la vida y la justicia; lucho para que los inocentes "
"tengan la oportunidad de vivir libre y pacíficamente."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:691
msgid ""
"So you say, and yet your path is littered with the lives you have ended to "
"come this far. How can a defender of peace be so ruthless? I ask you again, "
"Olokun Maahes, and on your answer hangs the fate of this entire world: are "
"you a servant of the Light?"
msgstr ""
"Eso dices, y sin embargo tu camino está lleno de las vidas que has terminado "
"para llegar hasta aquí. ¿Cómo puede un defensor de la paz ser tan "
"despiadado? Te pregunto una vez más, Olokun Maahes, y de tu respuesta "
"depende el destino de todo este mundo: ¿eres un servidor de la Luz?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:695
msgid ""
"I... I know that I'm not innocent myself; I have never forgotten any of the "
"beings I killed, be it human, orc, elf, minotaur, dwarf or troll... I have "
"no pretence of posing as a paladin of Good, I know my flaws – but I also "
"know that I can try and become a better person everyday, in order to protect "
"what I cherish."
msgstr ""
"Yo… sé que yo mismo no soy inocente; nunca he olvidado a ninguno de los "
"seres que maté, ya sean humanos, orcos, elfos, minotauros, enanos o trolls… "
"No pretendo posar de paladín del Bien, conozco mis defectos… pero también sé "
"que puedo intentar ser mejor persona cada día, para proteger lo que amo."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:699
msgid "I see..."
msgstr "Entiendo..."

#. [message], speaker=Usrukhar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:715
msgid ""
"Indeed, Olokun Maahes, it is nigh impossible for a mortal, limited creature "
"to know exactly what is the right thing to do; often do we cause harm when "
"we mean good, and benefit others when we meant to wound them. Life is a "
"puzzle, one which we must try and decipher little by little everyday. "
"Because you have accepted that, and because of your unwavering dedication to "
"the cause of the Light, I shall legate to you my two greatest powers: my "
"staff and my knowledge..."
msgstr ""
"En efecto, Olokun Maahes, es casi imposible para una criatura mortal y "
"limitada saber exactamente qué es lo correcto; a menudo causamos daño cuando "
"queremos hacer el bien, y beneficiamos a otros cuando pretendíamos herirlos. "
"La vida es un rompecabezas que debemos intentar descifrar poco a poco cada "
"día. Porque has aceptado eso, y por tu inquebrantable dedicación a la causa "
"de la Luz, te legaré mis dos mayores poderes: mi bastón y mi conocimiento…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:724
msgid "Argh...!!!"
msgstr "¡Argh…!"

#. [message], speaker=Usrukhar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:728
msgid ""
"The Heiress has chosen well, son. Now, awake! Lead the many nations of "
"humankind into this new war as one!"
msgstr ""
"La Heredera ha elegido bien, hijo. ¡Ahora, despierta! ¡Guía a las muchas "
"naciones de la humanidad en esta nueva guerra como una sola!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:770
msgid ""
"(relieved) Thank the heavens, he's waking up! What happened to you, Olokun? "
"You fell unconscious all of a sudden..."
msgstr ""
"(aliviada) ¡Gracias al cielo, está despertando! ¿Qué te pasó, Olokun? Te "
"desmayaste de repente…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:774
msgid ""
"(rising to his feet) Well, the former King wanted to make sure the claimant "
"to his staff was worthy of it... First of Mages, friends, I promise once "
"again, upon the memory of my father and mother, to use this power to the "
"benefit of humankind and of Irdya!"
msgstr ""
"(poniéndose de pie) Bueno, el antiguo rey quería asegurarse de que el "
"reclamante de su bastón fuera digno de él… Primeros de los Magos, amigos, "
"prometo una vez más, sobre la memoria de mi padre y mi madre, ¡usar este "
"poder en beneficio de la humanidad y de Irdya!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:778
msgid ""
"As he said that, Olokun raised the ancient staff in the air. Soon his body "
"glowed with a warm, golden light that grew so intense as to bathe even the "
"surrounding mountaintops. Then, a beam of light emerged from the staff, "
"piercing the thick vault of storm clouds. As the humans watched in awe, more "
"flashes of light pierced through from above, so bright that the clouds "
"themselves glowed with the same golden hue."
msgstr ""
"Mientras decía eso, Olokun levantó el antiguo bastón en el aire. Pronto su "
"cuerpo brilló con una cálida luz dorada que se intensificó tanto que bañó "
"incluso las cumbres de las montañas circundantes. Entonces, un rayo de luz "
"emergió del bastón, atravesando la gruesa bóveda de nubes de tormenta. "
"Mientras los humanos miraban asombrados, más destellos de luz perforaron "
"desde arriba, tan brillantes que las mismas nubes brillaron con el mismo "
"tono dorado."

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:801
msgid ""
"Incredible... These are the Sacred Skies, possibly the most powerful Lucent "
"spell known to us Maat'Karians, and he's cast it single-handedly...!"
msgstr ""
"Increíble… Estos son los Cielos Sagrados, posiblemente el hechizo Luciente "
"más poderoso conocido por nosotros los maat’karianos, ¡y lo ha lanzado él "
"solo…!"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:805
msgid ""
"Cursed Lucent Arts...! It matters not how much light you bring down upon "
"this forest, Olokun, it will be useless if you don't have the numbers to "
"oppose my undead!"
msgstr ""
"¡Malditas Artes Lucientes…! No importa cuánta luz hagas caer sobre este "
"bosque, Olokun, será inútil si no tienes los números para oponerte a mis no "
"muertos."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:809
msgid ""
"Your undead are like a swarm of flies before a blazing flame, Wesir, and "
"they shall be burned away accordingly. Now, friends, let us end his menace "
"once and for all!"
msgstr ""
"Tus no muertos son como un enjambre de moscas ante una llama ardiente, "
"Wesir, y serán incinerados en consecuencia. ¡Ahora, amigos, terminemos con "
"su amenaza de una vez por todas!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:815
msgid "Destroy Wesir with Olokun"
msgstr "Destruye a Wesir con Olokun"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:860
msgid "Hopeless fools, don't you know when to give up?!"
msgstr "¡Necios sin esperanza, no saben cuándo rendirse!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:872
msgid ""
"Wesir Amarnat will not fall so easily, friends - but I doubt that even he "
"will survive against the power of the First of Mages!"
msgstr ""
"Wesir Amarnat no caerá tan fácilmente, amigos… pero dudo que siquiera él "
"sobreviva al poder del Primero de los Magos."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:878
msgid ""
"Let me find Delfador's staff before taking on Wesir head on, it must have "
"enough power to destroy him!"
msgstr ""
"Déjenme encontrar el bastón de Delfador antes de enfrentarme directamente a "
"Wesir, ¡debe tener suficiente poder para destruirlo!"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:901
msgid "Ankhmare's pet, I shall give you the worst of deaths for this!"
msgstr "¡Mascota de Ankhmare, te daré la peor de las muertes por esto!"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:908
msgid "Olokun, find Delfador's staff before fighting him one on one!"
msgstr ""
"¡Olokun, encuentra el bastón de Delfador antes de enfrentarlo uno a uno!"

#. [message], speaker=Wesir
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:914
msgid "AAARRRGHHHH!!! I WILL NOT - I <i>CANNOT</i> - FALL TO THIS WORM...!!!"
msgstr ""
"¡¡¡AAAARRRRGGGGHHHH!!! ¡NO CAERÉ… NO <i>PUEDO</i> CAER ANTE ESTE GUSANO…!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:933
msgid "Now..."
msgstr "Ahora…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:946
msgid "Eh, I'm still not calling you <i>Majesty</i>, though."
msgstr "Eh, sigo sin llamarte <i>Majestad</i>, eso sí."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:950
msgid ""
"Yeah, everyone's powering up, perhaps we should find some ancient artefacts "
"for ourselves too, don't you agree?"
msgstr ""
"Sí, todos están potenciándose, tal vez también deberíamos encontrar algunos "
"artefactos antiguos para nosotros, ¿no crees?"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:954
msgid ""
"But it's not that the staff is powerful; what makes it the best of all "
"magical staffs is that it channels the mage's might in its most pure form, "
"without any loss of power. In other words, the power comes not from the "
"staff, but from the mage."
msgstr ""
"Pero no es que el bastón sea poderoso; lo que lo hace el mejor de todos los "
"bastones mágicos es que canaliza el poder del mago en su forma más pura, sin "
"pérdida alguna. En otras palabras, el poder no viene del bastón, sino del "
"mago."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:958
msgid ""
"Ooohh, I get it, so it's not the staff that's awesome, it's you... Being the "
"King-Under-the-Sun has gotten to your head very quickly, hasn't it, Olokun "
"Maahes?"
msgstr ""
"Oooh, entiendo, entonces no es el bastón el que es genial, eres tú… Ser el "
"Rey-Bajo-el-Sol se te ha subido rápido a la cabeza, ¿verdad, Olokun Maahes?"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:962
msgid ""
"I'm telling you, soon enough he'll be collecting taxes from us poor "
"peasants..."
msgstr ""
"Te lo digo, pronto estará cobrándonos impuestos a nosotros los pobres "
"campesinos…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:966
msgid ""
"(chuckles) Anyway... Let's return to Dan'Tonk, and hope that Cornelya has "
"returned safe and sound from the Northlands..."
msgstr ""
"(ríe) En fin… Volvamos a Dan'Tonk, y esperemos que Cornelya haya regresado "
"sana y salva de las Tierras del Norte…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/45_Return_Of_The_King.cfg:992
msgid ""
"We're taking too long to defeat Wesir and close the portal; at this rate, "
"the worlds of the Living and of the Dead will be merged forever!"
msgstr ""
"Estamos tardando demasiado en derrotar a Wesir y cerrar el portal; a este "
"paso, ¡los mundos de los Vivos y de los Muertos se fusionarán para siempre!"

#. [scenario], id=46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:5
msgid "The Light of Irdya"
msgstr "La Luz de Irdya"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:26
msgid "Defend Hiera'Kirya for 12 turns"
msgstr "Defiende Hiera'Kyria durante 12 turnos"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:34
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:695
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:33
msgid "Death of Yiwen"
msgstr "Muerte de Yiwen"

#. [objective], condition=lose
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:38
msgid "Death of Vasheera"
msgstr "Muerte de Vasheera"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:42
msgid ""
"NOTE: Do not leave any unit at the central Windsong keep, or it shall be "
"trapped when the Light is activated!\n"
"Also, Tenma may recruit from 43,34"
msgstr ""
"NOTA: ¡No dejes ninguna unidad en el torreón central de las Hijas del "
"Viento, o quedará atrapada cuando se active la Luz!\n"
"Además, Tenma puede reclutar desde 43,34"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:73
msgid "Hiera'Kyria"
msgstr "Hiera'Kyria"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:96
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:71
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:237
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:57
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/characters.cfg:922
msgid "Svarballi"
msgstr "Svarballi"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:247
msgid "<i>One week before the Battle of Dan'Tonk...</i>"
msgstr "<i>Una semana antes de la Batalla de Dan'Tonk…</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Elcadar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:251
msgid ""
"My Emperor, the last group of mages has arrived an hour ago; some bear grave "
"wounds, and so they may need a few days before returning to full health..."
msgstr ""
"Mi Emperador, el último grupo de magos llegó hace una hora; algunos traen "
"heridas graves, y podrían necesitar unos días antes de recuperar la salud "
"completa…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:255
msgid ""
"Then task every single white mage in this city to treat them. Also, tell the "
"White Necromancers to set their strongest undead to digging beneath Mount "
"Sunna immediately; we have not a single second to waste."
msgstr ""
"Entonces ordena a cada mago blanco de esta ciudad que los atienda. Además, "
"dile a los Nigromantes Blancos que pongan a sus no muertos más fuertes a "
"cavar bajo el Monte Sunna de inmediato; no tenemos ni un segundo que perder."

#. [message], speaker=Elcadar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:259
msgid ""
"I will do that, but, my Emperor... Are you sure that you want to go further "
"with this project? It is true that it worked once, but that was in a time "
"when we still counted with a myriad archmages. This crisis has taken many of "
"our brightest; of the ships that evacuated Alduin, only a third has made it "
"to this city, not to mention the disaster of Okladia. I have assessed the "
"remaining mages myself, and I am afraid that they may not... be ready for "
"the task. And this is to say nothing of this disturbance in the magic "
"currents, which has dampened even our masters."
msgstr ""
"Lo haré, pero, mi Emperador… ¿está seguro de querer seguir adelante con este "
"proyecto? Es cierto que funcionó una vez, pero fue en una época en que aún "
"contábamos con miríadas de archimagos. Esta crisis se ha llevado a muchos de "
"los más brillantes; de las naves que evacuaron Alduin, solo un tercio llegó "
"a esta ciudad, sin mencionar el desastre de Okladia. Yo mismo he evaluado a "
"los magos restantes, y temo que no estén… preparados para la tarea. Y eso "
"sin mencionar esta perturbación en las corrientes mágicas, que ha debilitado "
"incluso a nuestros maestros."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:263
msgid ""
"The disturbance is indeed a problem, but we'll have to bear with it. As for "
"the mages, they will have to, Elcadar. You have always boasted about the "
"indomitable focus and dedication of our mages – mages you have taught "
"yourself, I recall you saying -; I am counting on you to make them live up "
"to those words."
msgstr ""
"La perturbación es ciertamente un problema, pero tendremos que soportarla. "
"En cuanto a los magos, tendrán que estarlo, Elcadar. Siempre has presumido "
"del enfoque indomable y la dedicación de nuestros magos… magos que tú mismo "
"has enseñado, recuerdo que dijiste; cuento contigo para que estén a la "
"altura de esas palabras."

#. [message], speaker=Elcadar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:267
msgid "It's true, but..."
msgstr "Es cierto, pero…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:271
msgid "If that is so, then I ask you to hurry and do as I told you."
msgstr "Si es así, entonces te pido que te apresures y hagas lo que te dije."

#. [message], speaker=Elcadar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:275
msgid "V-very well, my Emperor..."
msgstr "M-muy bien, mi Emperador…"

#. [message], speaker=Aethra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:287
msgid ""
"Brother, is that truly the right thing to do? Raising a second sun has "
"affected the natural balance in dangerous ways already, or so the sages say; "
"what will be of the world if we raise a <i>third</i> one?"
msgstr ""
"Hermano, ¿es realmente lo correcto? Elevar un segundo sol ya ha afectado el "
"equilibrio natural de formas peligrosas, o eso dicen los sabios; ¿qué será "
"del mundo si elevamos un <i>tercero</i>?"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:291
msgid ""
"I don't take the complete abolition of the night lightly, sister, but that "
"is our only chance of surviving this crisis. Galdra's swarms are endless; we "
"cannot hope to match them with numbers. But we can weaken them, and sunlight "
"achieves that effect - just as it allows our soldiers to fight at their "
"best. When this is all over, we will work a way to bring the third sun down. "
"Or maybe we could use it for a few years more, until we've rebuilt the "
"empire's strength-"
msgstr ""
"No tomo a la ligera la abolición completa de la noche, hermana, pero es "
"nuestra única oportunidad de sobrevivir a esta crisis. Los enjambres de "
"Galdra son interminables; no podemos esperar igualarlos en número. Pero "
"podemos debilitarlos, y la luz solar logra ese efecto… al igual que permite "
"a nuestros soldados luchar al máximo. Cuando todo esto termine, "
"encontraremos una forma de derribar el tercer sol. O tal vez podríamos "
"usarlo unos años más, hasta que hayamos reconstruido la fuerza del imperio—"

#. [message], speaker=Aethra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:295
msgid ""
"No! Please, brother, promise me you'll have the third sun destroyed as soon "
"as Galdra is defeated! I... I don't want you becoming a belligerent man, "
"like brother Aelvar and father used to be!"
msgstr ""
"¡No! Por favor, hermano, ¡prométeme que harás destruir el tercer sol tan "
"pronto como Galdra sea derrotada! Yo… no quiero que te conviertas en un "
"hombre beligerante, ¡como lo fueron el hermano Aelvar y padre!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:299
msgid ""
"(smiling) Very well, sister, the third sun will shine only for as long as it "
"needs to. Now, I need to ask you to leave me alone, I must confer with my "
"generals..."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Muy bien, hermana, el tercer sol brillará solo mientras sea "
"necesario. Ahora, te pido que me dejes solo, debo conferenciar con mis "
"generales…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:309
msgid "*For as long as it needs to...*"
msgstr "*Mientras sea necesario…*"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:327
msgid ""
"Cornelya returned to Dan'Tonk a week after Olokun's retinue did – and, to "
"the city sentries' dismay, followed by an immense orcish host. But that "
"fearsome force was led by Bogor, who now wielded a sword engulfed in green "
"flames. That blade, the Rakshasa, had been his reward for succeeding a trial "
"of legend: as it went, the sword had belonged to the mythical orc warrior "
"known as the 'World-Burner', who had set a series of gauntlets to determine "
"who would be worthy of wielding it after his passing. Not a single orc had "
"succeeded, and as the ages went by it fell into the realm of folk tale - "
"until Bogor's belief led him to find the trial, and his strength led him to "
"overcome it."
msgstr ""
"Cornelya regresó a Dan'Tonk una semana después de la comitiva de Olokun… y, "
"para desmayo de los centinelas de la ciudad, seguida por una inmensa hueste "
"orca. Pero esa temible fuerza estaba liderada por Bogor, quien ahora "
"empuñaba una espada envuelta en llamas verdes. Esa hoja, la Rakshasa, había "
"sido su recompensa por superar una prueba legendaria: según se cuenta, la "
"espada perteneció al mítico guerrero orco conocido como el «Quemamundos», "
"quien estableció una serie de desafíos para determinar quién sería digno de "
"empuñarla tras su partida. Ningún orco lo logró, y con el paso de los siglos "
"cayó en el reino de la leyenda popular… hasta que la fe de Bogor lo llevó a "
"encontrar la prueba, y su fuerza lo llevó a superarla."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:331
msgid ""
"He'd always known the blade to be special, but it was only after learning "
"about the Regalia from Cornelya that it occurred to him the Rakshasa might "
"be one. His people's legends again guided his actions: as it was said the "
"Rakshasa's true power could only be unlocked if it 'imbibed the willing "
"blood of ten thousand orcs', so did Bogor earn that number of loyal warriors "
"by beating them in single combat."
msgstr ""
"Siempre supo que la hoja era especial, pero solo después de aprender sobre "
"las Regalias de Cornelya se le ocurrió que la Rakshasa podría ser una. Las "
"leyendas de su pueblo volvieron a guiar sus acciones: como se decía que el "
"verdadero poder de la Rakshasa solo podía desbloquearse si «bebía la sangre "
"voluntaria de diez mil orcos», Bogor ganó ese número de guerreros leales "
"derrotándolos en combate singular."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:335
msgid ""
"That meant that they now had all seven Kings of Irdya reunited inside the "
"walls of Dan'Tonk – but their enthusiasm was not complete, for Cornelya did "
"not bring only good news from her own mission. Though she had find traces of "
"an unusual power in the ruined Dwarven Doors, she could not find a clue as "
"to Tenma's fate. Having to deal with the double threat of Galdra and "
"Svarballi and without their strongest fighter, the Kings and Queens found "
"themselves indecisive about what to do next."
msgstr ""
"Eso significaba que ahora tenían a los siete Reyes de Irdya reunidos dentro "
"de las murallas de Dan'Tonk… pero su entusiasmo no era completo, pues "
"Cornelya no trajo solo buenas noticias de su propia misión. Aunque encontró "
"rastros de un poder inusual en las ruinas de las Puertas Enanas, no pudo "
"hallar ninguna pista sobre el destino de Tenma. Teniendo que lidiar con la "
"doble amenaza de Galdra y Svarballi y sin su luchadora más fuerte, los Reyes "
"y Reinas se encontraron indecisos sobre qué hacer a continuación."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:339
msgid ""
"Cornelya could not have known Tenma's whereabouts; while the elf and the "
"others fought Galdra and Wesir, the Dragon-Slayer was far away, beyond the "
"shores of the Great Continent, at the North Pole of the world - among those "
"who, in another life, she had counted as sisters..."
msgstr ""
"Cornelya no podía saber el paradero de Tenma; mientras la elfa y los demás "
"luchaban contra Galdra y Wesir, la Matadragones estaba muy lejos, más allá "
"de las costas del Gran Continente, en el Polo Norte del mundo… entre "
"aquellos que, en otra vida, había contado como hermanas…"

#. [message], speaker=Tainah
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:385
msgid ""
"It is believable enough that the Sky Dragon has broken free from High "
"Ascendant Maat's prison; but to think that you, Tenma Yozora, is the "
"reincarnation of Myra of Hiera'Shirsha... Not only can we not test this "
"claim, it also goes against the very foundations of our knowledge..."
msgstr ""
"Es bastante creíble que el Dragón del Cielo haya escapado de la prisión de "
"la Alta Ascendente Maat; pero pensar que tú, Tenma Yozora, eres la "
"reencarnación de Myra de Hiera'Shirsha… No solo no podemos probar esa "
"afirmación, sino que también va en contra de los mismos fundamentos de "
"nuestro conocimiento…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:389
msgid ""
"As far as I can remember, the Windsong were always receptive of new "
"knowledge, strange and controversial as it might be. Besides, would I know "
"so much about this Order, about Maat or about the Last War unless I had "
"Myra's memories?"
msgstr ""
"Por lo que recuerdo, las Hijas del Viento siempre fueron receptivas al nuevo "
"conocimiento, por extraño y controvertido que fuera. Además, ¿cómo sabría "
"tanto sobre esta Orden, sobre Maat o sobre la Última Guerra si no tuviera "
"los recuerdos de Myra?"

#. [message], speaker=Tainah
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:393
msgid ""
"All these things could've been learned from the Maat'Karians that you "
"yourself claimed to be acquainted with. In any case, if the Sky Dragon's "
"destruction is what you seek, then you have come to the right place. For "
"centuries, we have been developing and perfecting that which is grandest "
"creation of the Windsong: the Light of Irdya."
msgstr ""
"Todas esas cosas podrían haberse aprendido de los maat’karianos con los que "
"dices estar familiarizada. En cualquier caso, si lo que buscas es la "
"destrucción del Dragón del Cielo, has venido al lugar correcto. Durante "
"siglos hemos estado desarrollando y perfeccionando lo que es la creación más "
"grandiosa de las Hijas del Viento: la Luz de Irdya."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:397
msgid ""
"I have... vague memories of some engine built by the Windsong to destroy "
"Svarballi..."
msgstr ""
"Tengo… recuerdos vagos de algún motor construido por las Hijas del Viento "
"para destruir a Svarballi…"

#. [message], speaker=Tainah
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:401
msgid ""
"The Light of Irdya is, essentially, a magical conduit: its main body is a "
"series of concentric rings which, so long as they work together, can channel "
"and muster immense energy levels; they are connected to the planet's mantle "
"by chains crafted for the goal of absorbing magic from air and earth "
"currents."
msgstr ""
"La Luz de Irdya es, esencialmente, un conducto mágico: su cuerpo principal "
"es una serie de anillos concéntricos que, mientras trabajen juntos, pueden "
"canalizar y reunir niveles inmensos de energía; están conectados al manto "
"del planeta mediante cadenas creadas con el propósito de absorber magia de "
"las corrientes de aire y tierra."

#. [message], speaker=Tainah
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:405
msgid ""
"But the Light's main function is to allow an Ascendant to bond with the "
"spirits of nature and channel their power. By standing at the core of the "
"engine's main body, one will be at the centre of a vortex of pure natural "
"energy, through which one is able to speak with the spirits as if with "
"another person."
msgstr ""
"Pero la función principal de la Luz es permitir que una Ascendente se "
"vincule con los espíritus de la naturaleza y canalice su poder. Al colocarse "
"en el núcleo del cuerpo principal del motor, uno estará en el centro de un "
"vórtice de energía natural pura, a través del cual se puede hablar con los "
"espíritus como si fueran otra persona."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:409
msgid "And are you sure it will work...?"
msgstr "¿Y estás segura de que funcionará…?"

#. [message], speaker=Tainah
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:413
msgid ""
"Many Ascendants have been able to go as far as to summon elementals, despite "
"having none of the training usually required; so yes, we believe it will "
"work as intended."
msgstr ""
"Muchas Ascendentes han logrado llegar hasta invocar elementales, a pesar de "
"no tener el entrenamiento usualmente requerido; así que sí, creemos que "
"funcionará como está previsto."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:417
msgid ""
"There's a difference between true spirits of nature and elementals, though. "
"The latter are more like 'proxies' of true spirits, elemental constructs "
"through which they interact with the material plane. Being able to summon "
"them is not the same as to speak with them. More importantly... For this "
"engine to work, it looks like it'll require a lot of energy, energy that "
"will be drained from its very source; in other words, from the spirits of "
"nature themselves."
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, hay una diferencia entre los verdaderos espíritus de la "
"naturaleza y los elementales. Estos últimos son más bien «proxies» de los "
"espíritus verdaderos, constructos elementales a través de los cuales "
"interactúan con el plano material. Poder invocarlos no es lo mismo que "
"hablar con ellos. Más importante aún… Para que este motor funcione, parece "
"que requerirá mucha energía, energía que será drenada de su propia fuente; "
"en otras palabras, de los mismos espíritus de la naturaleza."

#. [message], speaker=Tainah
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:421
msgid ""
"It is as you say; in effect, we have replicated what Myra did at the Crystal "
"Tower, where she became a pure vessel of nature's power."
msgstr ""
"Es como dices; en efecto, hemos replicado lo que Myra hizo en la Torre de "
"Cristal, donde se convirtió en un recipiente puro del poder de la naturaleza."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:425
msgid ""
"That's the thing, you haven't. I... well, Myra became that vessel because "
"she was <i>chosen</i> to become one by the spirits themselves. They have "
"their own will, and they can be very wilful; that you can summon elementals "
"doesn't mean they've accepted you, and if you drain so much of their power "
"just like that, I don't think they'll take kindly to it."
msgstr ""
"Ese es el problema, no lo han hecho. Yo… bueno, Myra se convirtió en ese "
"recipiente porque fue <i>elegida</i> por los mismos espíritus para serlo. "
"Ellos tienen su propia voluntad, y pueden ser muy obstinados; que puedas "
"invocar elementales no significa que te hayan aceptado, y si drenas tanto de "
"su poder así como así, no creo que lo tomen bien."

#. [message], speaker=Tainah
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:429
msgid ""
"(chuckles) You are not even aware of how pretentious you sound, are you? "
"Well, it matters not; the Sky Dragon's presence has been confirmed by our "
"sister Yiwen, and that is enough evidence that-"
msgstr ""
"(ríe) Ni siquiera eres consciente de lo pretenciosa que suenas, ¿verdad? "
"Bueno, no importa; la presencia del Dragón del Cielo ha sido confirmada por "
"nuestra hermana Yiwen, y eso es suficiente evidencia de que—"

#. [message], speaker=Yiwen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:436
msgid "(frightened) Damn it, it's him...!"
msgstr "(asustada) ¡Maldición, es él…!"

#. [message], speaker=Tainah
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:440
msgid ""
"(alarmed) He is much faster than I anticipated... Yiwen, tell Vasheera to "
"organise Hiera'Kyria's defences; Talia, Lyra, follow me to the Light..."
msgstr ""
"(alarmada) Es mucho más rápido de lo que anticipé… Yiwen, dile a Vasheera "
"que organice las defensas de Hiera'Kyria; Talia, Lyra, síganme a la Luz…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:444
msgid ""
"I'd like to stay and help you, Ascendant Tainah; but I'm really worried "
"about this engine of yours. I know other ways, safer ways, to destroy the "
"Sky Dragon; if you just help me, I could-"
msgstr ""
"Me gustaría quedarme y ayudarte, Ascendente Tainah; pero estoy realmente "
"preocupada por este motor tuyo. Conozco otras formas, más seguras, de "
"destruir al Dragón del Cielo; si solo me ayudaran, podría—"

#. [message], speaker=Tainah
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:448
msgid ""
"If you truly wish to aid us, then join Vasheera and delay the Sky Dragon "
"while we activate the Spear; that is where you can be useful, not by "
"counselling me."
msgstr ""
"Si realmente deseas ayudarnos, entonces únete a Vasheera y retrasa al Dragón "
"del Cielo mientras activamos la Lanza; ahí es donde puedes ser útil, no "
"aconsejándome."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:452
msgid "(snorts) Fine..."
msgstr "(bufa) Está bien…"

#. [message], speaker=Vasheera
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:526
msgid ""
"(frightened) W-what is that thing...?! Is <i>that</i> the monster the High "
"Ascendant Maat gave up her life to imprison?!"
msgstr ""
"(asustada) ¿Q-qué es esa cosa…?! ¿<i>Eso</i> es el monstruo por el que la "
"Alta Ascendente Maat dio su vida para aprisionarlo?"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:530
msgid ""
"So this is what is left of great Maat's people? How I wish that she was "
"alive, to see what all her efforts and sacrifices have earned!"
msgstr ""
"¿Así que esto es lo que queda del gran pueblo de Maat? ¡Cómo desearía que "
"estuviera viva, para ver lo que todos sus esfuerzos y sacrificios han "
"logrado!"

#. [message], speaker=Vasheera
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:534
msgid ""
"All the joint efforts of generations of Windsong have not been in vain, "
"Destroyer, this we swear! Sisters, this is what we've been preparing for "
"since the Age of the Epics! We must delay him while the Light of Irdya is "
"prepared!"
msgstr ""
"¡Todos los esfuerzos conjuntos de generaciones de Hijas del Viento no han "
"sido en vano, Destructor, esto lo juramos! ¡Hermanas, esto es para lo que "
"nos hemos estado preparando desde la Era de las Épicas! ¡Debemos retrasarlo "
"mientras se prepara la Luz de Irdya!"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:538
msgid ""
"Running back to your old sisters will be of no avail to you, Myra – unless "
"you wish to die among your own!"
msgstr ""
"Regresar corriendo con tus antiguas hermanas no te servirá de nada, Myra… ¡a "
"menos que desees morir entre las tuyas!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:542
msgid ""
"*Damn him...! I really hope the Light of Irdya can at the very least weaken "
"him, then maybe I can finish him off...*"
msgstr ""
"*¡Maldito…! Realmente espero que la Luz de Irdya pueda al menos debilitarlo, "
"entonces tal vez pueda terminarlo…*"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:551
msgid ""
"I remember a time when you were led by the mighty, Windsong – people who "
"earned even my respect. Now you are but a fading shadow of your former self, "
"unworthy even to be felled by my own claws. Your end shall come by the hands "
"of beings of similar worth..."
msgstr ""
"Recuerdo un tiempo en que eras liderada por los poderosos, Hijas del Viento… "
"gente que se ganó incluso mi respeto. Ahora no eres más que una sombra "
"desvanecida de lo que fuiste, indigna incluso de ser abatida por mis propias "
"garras. ¡Tu fin vendrá de las manos de seres de valor similar…!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:555
msgid ""
"With those words, Svarballi raised his head skywards. For some seconds, the "
"Windsong simply stared at him, puzzled; then one of them screamed while "
"pointing at the heavens, and everyone else saw the rain of ethereal meteors "
"come down upon Hiera'Kyria."
msgstr ""
"Con esas palabras, Svarballi alzó la cabeza hacia el cielo. Durante algunos "
"segundos, las Hijas del Viento simplemente lo miraron, desconcertadas; "
"entonces una gritó mientras señalaba los cielos, y todos los demás vieron la "
"lluvia de meteoros etéreos caer sobre Hiera'Kyria."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:562
msgid ""
"The magic shield protecting the Foundation disintegrated some, but many fell "
"all around it. And then..."
msgstr ""
"El escudo mágico que protegía la Fundación se desintegró en parte, pero "
"muchos cayeron todo alrededor. Y entonces…"

#. [message], speaker=Yiwen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:570
msgid "What on Irdya are those things...?"
msgstr "¿Qué demonios son esas cosas en Irdya…?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:574
msgid "They're... Celestials?!"
msgstr "¡Son… Celestiales?!"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:578
msgid ""
"Once a noble race with the blood of the Avatars, they bastardised themselves "
"by mingling with the vermin of this world, debasing themselves both in body "
"and in spirit. Now, not even ashes remain of what they were, an ignoble end "
"to those with such high origins. But their souls have sought vengeance, and "
"some have reached me. It is only fitting that they are the ones to finish "
"Myra and her people!"
msgstr ""
"Una vez una noble raza con la sangre de los Avatares, se bastardearon al "
"mezclarse con la vermina de este mundo, degradándose tanto en cuerpo como en "
"espíritu. Ahora ni siquiera cenizas quedan de lo que fueron, un final "
"ignominioso para quienes tenían orígenes tan altos. Pero sus almas han "
"buscado venganza, y algunas han llegado a mí. ¡Es apropiado que sean ellas "
"las que terminen con Myra y su pueblo!"

#. [message], speaker=Vasheera
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:582
msgid ""
"They're strange lifeforms indeed, but as long as they can materialise upon "
"our plane, they can be destroyed. Slow them down with ciphers, study their "
"weaknesses, and destroy them before they reach the Utmost Tower!"
msgstr ""
"Son formas de vida extrañas, en efecto, pero mientras puedan materializarse "
"en nuestro plano, pueden ser destruidas. Retrasen su avance con cifrados, "
"estudien sus debilidades y destrúyanlas antes de que lleguen a la Torre "
"Suprema."

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:591
msgid ""
"You cross the gates of oblivion with dignity, Windsong, fighting to your "
"last. But you only delay the inevitable..."
msgstr ""
"Cruzan las puertas del olvido con dignidad, Hijas del Viento, luchando hasta "
"el final. Pero solo retrasan lo inevitable…"

#. [unit], id=Tainah, type=Irdya_Spear
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:634
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/characters.cfg:406
msgid "Ascendant Tainah"
msgstr "Ascendente Tainah"

#. [message], speaker=Vasheera
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:644
msgid ""
"At long last! Behold, Sky Dragon, the weapon that shall put an end to your "
"menace!"
msgstr ""
"¡Por fin! ¡Contempla, Dragón del Cielo, el arma que pondrá fin a tu amenaza!"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:648
msgid "We shall see about that..."
msgstr "Ya veremos eso…"

#. [message], speaker=Tainah
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:652
msgid ""
"My sisters, the Light is almost ready, but I need to gather more energy, to "
"make sure the Destroyer is obliterated forever! Please, hold on a little "
"longer!"
msgstr ""
"¡Hermanas mías, la Luz está casi lista, pero necesito reunir más energía "
"para asegurarme de que el Destructor sea obliterado para siempre! ¡Por "
"favor, resistan un poco más!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:656
msgid ""
"I have a bad feeling about this... That vortex of natural energy, it rages "
"worse than even an Agni..."
msgstr ""
"Tengo un mal presentimiento sobre esto… Ese vórtice de energía natural ruge "
"peor que incluso un Agni…"

#. [message], speaker=Yiwen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:660
msgid ""
"It's this or nothing; you were unable to destroy him yourself, so either the "
"Light works or we're all doomed!"
msgstr ""
"Es esto o nada; tú no pudiste destruirlo por tu cuenta, ¡así que o la Luz "
"funciona o todos estamos condenados!"

#. [message], speaker=Tainah
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:671
msgid ""
"At last! My sisters, please stay as far from the Light as you can, it is "
"ready to be unleash!"
msgstr ""
"¡Por fin! Hermanas mías, por favor manténganse lo más lejos posible de la "
"Luz, ¡está lista para ser desatada!"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:675
msgid ""
"So that is the weapon you have raised against me, Windsong; I haven't felt "
"such intense natural energy since... (roars) Very well then, people of Maat, "
"let us see how your power fares against mine!"
msgstr ""
"Así que esa es el arma que han levantado contra mí, Hijas del Viento; no he "
"sentido una energía natural tan intensa desde… (ruge) Muy bien entonces, "
"pueblo de Maat, ¡veamos cómo se compara su poder con el mío!"

#. [message], speaker=Vasheera
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:679
msgid "The Sky Dragon is flying towards us!"
msgstr "¡El Dragón del Cielo está volando hacia nosotros!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:687
msgid "Evacuate Hiera'Kirya (you have 2 turns)"
msgstr "Evacúa Hiera'Kyria (tienes 2 turnos)"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:712
msgid "Damn it...! Ascendant, whatever you're going to do, do it now!!!"
msgstr "¡Maldición…! ¡Ascendente, lo que sea que vayas a hacer, hazlo ahora!"

#. [message], speaker=Tainah
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:726
msgid "Now... Do not abandon me, spirits of Irdya...!"
msgstr "Ahora… ¡No me abandonen, espíritus de Irdya…!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:730
msgid ""
"The Windsong held their breaths as they watched the colossal engine come to "
"life in full. The ciphers on its rings glowed brighter and brighter, and the "
"rings' howled as they spun and drained from the world's core. Svarballi "
"roared as he lunged towards the Foundation; for a moment, it seemed as if he "
"truly feared the engine, and his fear filled all those women with hope..."
msgstr ""
"Las Hijas del Viento contuvieron el aliento mientras observaban el colosal "
"motor cobrar vida por completo. Los cifrados en sus anillos brillaron cada "
"vez más intensamente, y los anillos aullaron mientras giraban y drenaban "
"energía del núcleo del mundo. Svarballi rugió al lanzarse hacia la "
"Fundación; por un momento, pareció que realmente temía al motor, y su miedo "
"llenó a todas esas mujeres de esperanza…"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:734
msgid ""
"...But there was no shot, no beam of light crossing the air to strike the "
"Sky Dragon down. Instead, the Light of Irdya continued to draw more and more "
"energy from the earth, causing the rings to gyrate dangerously faster, their "
"howl now frighteningly deafening."
msgstr ""
"…Pero no hubo disparo, ni rayo de luz cruzando el aire para abatir al Dragón "
"del Cielo. En cambio, la Luz de Irdya siguió extrayendo cada vez más energía "
"de la tierra, haciendo que los anillos giraran peligrosamente más rápido, y "
"su aullido ahora era ensordecedoramente aterrador."

#. [message], speaker=Yiwen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:741
msgid "My ears...! Is that how it is supposed to work?!"
msgstr "¡Mis oídos…! ¿Así es como se supone que debe funcionar?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:745
msgid ""
"(alarmed) No... No, it's draining too much energy, and it's hurting the "
"spirits...!"
msgstr ""
"(alarmada) No… No, está drenando demasiada energía, ¡y está lastimando a los "
"espíritus…!"

#. [message], speaker=Tainah
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:749
msgid ""
"(frightened) No way... Spirits, before you stands the Destroyer! You "
"<i>will</i> lend me your power, or else we're all doomed!"
msgstr ""
"(asustada) De ninguna manera… ¡Espíritus, ante ustedes está el Destructor! "
"<i>Me</i> prestarán su poder, ¡o todos estaremos condenados!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:753
msgid "YOU'RE DESTROYING THEM, ASCENDANT, STOP RIGHT NOW!!!"
msgstr "¡LOS ESTÁS DESTRUYENDO, ASCENDENTE, DETENTE AHORA MISMO!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:757
msgid "But the spirits would not allow themselves to be destroyed."
msgstr "Pero los espíritus no permitirían que se les destruyera."

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:900
msgid ""
"And so, all your aeons of preparation have led to a resounding failure... "
"Like Myra of Hiera'Shirsha, and like every being on this world, you cannot "
"handle the power you have access to - and so you have destroyed yourselves!"
msgstr ""
"Y así, todos sus eones de preparación han llevado a un fracaso rotundo… Como "
"Myra de Hiera'Shirsha, y como todo ser en este mundo, no pueden manejar el "
"poder al que tienen acceso… ¡y así se han destruido a sí mismas!"

#. [message], speaker=Yiwen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:904
msgid "(crying in despair) No... No way... No damn way!!!"
msgstr ""
"(llorando desesperada) No… De ninguna manera… ¡Maldita sea, de ninguna "
"manera!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:908
msgid "Yiwen, hear me out..."
msgstr "Yiwen, escúchame…"

#. [message], speaker=Yiwen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:912
msgid ""
"T-this is the end... We've failed to protect this world... Svarballi will "
"destroy us all!!!"
msgstr ""
"E-esto es el fin… Hemos fallado en proteger este mundo… ¡Svarballi nos "
"destruirá a todos!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:916
msgid ""
"YIWEN, LISTEN! This is not the end, we still have ways to fight him, but not "
"here! Please, take me back to the Great Continent, I need to meet my friends!"
msgstr ""
"¡YIWEN, ESCÚCHAME! Esto no es el fin, todavía tenemos formas de luchar "
"contra él, ¡pero no aquí! Por favor, llévame de vuelta al Gran Continente, "
"¡necesito encontrar a mis amigos!"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:920
msgid ""
"You stopped the fallen Avatar Tiamat, and you stopped me once... But now you "
"crumble, Windsong, beneath the weight of your own hubris. Fitting, then, "
"that your destruction be the death knell of this world..."
msgstr ""
"Detuvieron al Avatar caído Tiamat, y me detuvieron una vez… Pero ahora se "
"derrumban, Hijas del Viento, bajo el peso de su propia arrogancia. "
"Apropiado, entonces, que su destrucción sea el toque de difuntos de este "
"mundo…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:927
msgid "Yiwen, HURRY! We must escape this place!"
msgstr "¡Yiwen, APÚRATE! ¡Debemos escapar de este lugar!"

#. [message], speaker=Yiwen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:931
msgid "And leave my sisters behind?! No way I'll..."
msgstr "¿Y dejar a mis hermanas atrás? ¡De ninguna manera voy a…!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:935
msgid ""
"Do you think I want that? Do you think I'm not burning in anger and shame "
"for fleeing like this?! But I don't care if I'm a coward, I won't allow "
"myself to die when there are people counting on me, not when there is still "
"a chance to save this world! I... I hate to say this, but we must survive "
"this day to fight again tomorrow!"
msgstr ""
"¿Crees que quiero eso? ¿Crees que no estoy ardiendo de rabia y vergüenza por "
"huir así? ¡Pero no me importa si soy una cobarde, no me permitiré morir "
"cuando hay gente contando conmigo, no cuando todavía hay una oportunidad de "
"salvar este mundo! Yo… odio decir esto, ¡pero debemos sobrevivir este día "
"para luchar mañana!"

#. [message], speaker=Yiwen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:939
msgid ""
"You... You are right... But listen to me, Tenma, Myra, whoever the hell you "
"are: you must promise that you will destroy that monster, even if that costs "
"you life itself, do you understand?!"
msgstr ""
"Tú… tienes razón… Pero escúchame, Tenma, Myra, quienquiera que seas: debes "
"prometerme que destruirás a ese monstruo, ¡aunque te cueste la vida misma, "
"entiendes?!"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:954
msgid ""
"Your time is over, Myra of Hiera'Shirsha; come and join your sisters in "
"death!"
msgstr ""
"Tu tiempo ha terminado, Myra de Hiera'Shirsha; ¡ven y únete a tus hermanas "
"en la muerte!"

#. [message], speaker=Vasheera
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:988
msgid "How... could I..."
msgstr "¿Cómo… pude…?"

#. [message], speaker=Yiwen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/46_The_Spear_Of_Irdya.cfg:992
msgid ""
"No! Vasheera was leading Hiera'Laksha's defence, without her we won't be "
"able to protect it until the Light's activation!"
msgstr ""
"¡No! Vasheera estaba liderando la defensa de Hiera'Laksha, ¡sin ella no "
"podremos protegerla hasta que se active la Luz!"

#. [scenario], id=47_Sky_Chase
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:5
msgid "Sky Chase"
msgstr "Persecución en el Cielo"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:25
msgid "Reach the Hammermounts' entrance in the far south"
msgstr "Alcanza la entrada de los Hammermounts en el lejano sur"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:37
msgid ""
"NOTE: Svarballi will appear soon; you have not a single turn to waste!\n"
"\n"
"In order to delay him, you can invoke/recall true elementals from any "
"mountain or shallow water terrain.\n"
"\n"
"Yiwen may teleport at certain mountain tops; two of them are near the "
"starting point."
msgstr ""
"NOTA: ¡Svarballi aparecerá pronto; no tienes ni un turno que perder!\n"
"\n"
"Para retrasarlo, puedes invocar/reincorporar elementales verdaderos desde "
"cualquier terreno de montaña o agua poco profunda.\n"
"\n"
"Yiwen puede teletransportarse en ciertas cumbres montañosas; dos de ellas "
"están cerca del punto de inicio."

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:107
msgid "Hammermounts"
msgstr "Hammermounts"

#. [message], speaker=Yiwen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:130
msgid ""
"(panting) Damn monster, he's been chasing us since the North Pole... Doesn't "
"he ever tire?!"
msgstr ""
"(jadeando) ¡Maldito monstruo, nos ha estado persiguiendo desde el Polo "
"Norte…! ¿Nunca se cansa?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:134
msgid ""
"I doubt he does... Though we did manage to lose him temporarily... I owe you "
"one, Yiwen, were it not for your teleporting we'd have been caught long ago. "
"Look, I think we're getting close to the Heart Mountains, I can see them in "
"the distance already..."
msgstr ""
"Dudo que lo haga… Aunque logramos perderlo temporalmente… Te debo una, "
"Yiwen, sin tu teletransportación nos habrían atrapado hace rato. Mira, creo "
"que nos estamos acercando a las Montañas del Corazón, ya las puedo ver a lo "
"lejos…"

#. [message], speaker=Yiwen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:138
msgid "That can't be, the Heart Mountains are much taller than those..."
msgstr "No puede ser, las Montañas del Corazón son mucho más altas que esas…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:142
msgid ""
"Really? But what other range in the northern Great Continent is as large as "
"the Heart Mountains?"
msgstr ""
"¿De verdad? Pero ¿qué otra cadena montañosa en el norte del Gran Continente "
"es tan grande como las Montañas del Corazón?"

#. [message], speaker=Yiwen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:146
msgid ""
"If I recall it correctly, and considering our current latitude, those would "
"be the Hammermounts..."
msgstr ""
"Si recuerdo bien, y considerando nuestra latitud actual, esas serían los "
"Hammermounts…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:150
msgid ""
"Hammermounts?! By the Kami, we're too far from Wesnoth... (recomposing) "
"Well, I know there are deep caves inside those mountains, caves inhabited by "
"friends of mine; perhaps we could be safe from Svarballi if we go "
"underground, even he would have trouble catching us if there are miles of "
"sheer rock in between..."
msgstr ""
"¿Hammermounts? ¡Por los Kami, estamos demasiado lejos de Wesnoth…! "
"(recomponiéndose) Bueno, sé que hay cuevas profundas dentro de esas "
"montañas, cuevas habitadas por amigos míos; tal vez podríamos estar a salvo "
"de Svarballi si vamos bajo tierra, incluso él tendría problemas para "
"atraparnos si hay kilómetros de roca sólida de por medio…"

#. [message], speaker=Yiwen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:154
msgid ""
"Let's get moving, then, we won't be able to outpace him for long... Damn it, "
"this region is so remote there are no villages nearby..."
msgstr ""
"Entonces pongámonos en marcha, no podremos dejarlo atrás por mucho tiempo… "
"Maldición, esta región es tan remota que no hay aldeas cerca…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:158
msgid "So you can't teleport?!"
msgstr "¿Entonces no puedes teletransportarte?"

#. [message], speaker=Yiwen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:162
msgid ""
"Maybe if I reach out to wild Raw streams, but I'd have to reach a high place "
"- and won't be able to take you along..."
msgstr ""
"Tal vez si me conecto a corrientes Raw salvajes, pero tendría que llegar a "
"un lugar alto… y no podré llevarte conmigo…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:166
msgid ""
"You worry about yourself, I can outrun him with my dragon wings... at least "
"for a time..."
msgstr ""
"Preocúpate por ti, yo puedo dejarlo atrás con mis alas de dragón… al menos "
"por un tiempo…"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:187
msgid ""
"There you are, Myra of Hiera'Shirsha! It shames me, to admit that I was "
"defeated once, even if in a weakened state, by a vermin like you, who runs "
"for its life squeaking in terror... Stand your ground and fight! Or have you "
"given up on this world?"
msgstr ""
"¡Ahí estás, Myra de Hiera'Shirsha! Me avergüenza admitir que fui derrotado "
"una vez, aunque en un estado debilitado, por una alimaña como tú, que huye "
"por su vida chillando de terror… ¡Plantéate y lucha! ¿O ya has renunciado a "
"este mundo?"

#. [message], speaker=Yiwen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:195
msgid ""
"Do not let him distract you, Tenma! You said it yourself, we must live today "
"in order to fight tomorrow!"
msgstr ""
"¡No dejes que te distraiga, Tenma! Tú misma lo dijiste, ¡debemos vivir hoy "
"para luchar mañana!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:199
msgid ""
"I know, I know! Still, I won't simply run without doing anything to stop "
"him; if I just manage to reach mountains, water bodies of forests, I may be "
"able to summon some spirits to delay Svarballi..."
msgstr ""
"Lo sé, lo sé. Aun así, no voy a simplemente huir sin hacer nada para "
"detenerlo; si logro llegar a montañas, cuerpos de agua o bosques, tal vez "
"pueda invocar algunos espíritus para retrasar a Svarballi…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:213
msgid ""
"A settlement...! I have to warn whoever lives there of what is coming..."
msgstr ""
"¡Un asentamiento…! Tengo que advertir a quien viva allí de lo que se acerca…"

#. [message], speaker=Old_Ally
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:245
msgid "You damn trespasser, prepare to..."
msgstr "Maldita intrusa, prepárate para…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:249
msgid ""
"Wait, wait! It's me, Tenma Yozora! We fought against Ashura together, don't "
"you remember me?"
msgstr ""
"¡Espera, espera! ¡Soy yo, Tenma Yozora! Luchamos juntos contra Ashura, ¿no "
"me recuerdas?"

#. [message], speaker=Old_Ally
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:253
msgid ""
"(surprised) Yeah, I do remember your face, you helped us a great deal back "
"then. What brings you..."
msgstr ""
"(sorprendido) Sí, recuerdo tu cara, nos ayudaste muchísimo en aquel "
"entonces. ¿Qué te trae…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:257
msgid ""
"I have no time to explain; just tell me if there's any entrance to the "
"underground around here?"
msgstr ""
"No tengo tiempo para explicaciones; solo dime si hay alguna entrada al "
"subsuelo por aquí cerca."

#. [message], speaker=Old_Ally
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:261
msgid "(suspicious) And why do you want to..."
msgstr "(sospechoso) ¿Y por qué quieres…"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:265
msgid "(roaring) Your time is running, Myra, at this rate I will catch you...!"
msgstr "(rugiendo) ¡Tu tiempo se acaba, Myra, a este ritmo te atraparé…!"

#. [message], speaker=Old_Ally
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:269
msgid "(frightened) What is that thing...?!"
msgstr "(asustado) ¿Qué es esa cosa…?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:273
msgid "That monster is coming for me and for all of you, that's why we must..."
msgstr "Ese monstruo viene por mí y por todos ustedes, por eso debemos…"

#. [message], speaker=Yiwen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:282
msgid "Hey, come back here! Damn him, the coward locked the doors...!"
msgstr "¡Oye, vuelve aquí! ¡Maldito cobarde, cerró las puertas…!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:286
msgid "There... There must be an entrance nearby, we have to keep looking..."
msgstr "Allí… Tiene que haber una entrada cerca, debemos seguir buscando…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:302
msgid "THERE! Now, hurry! We have to go as deep as we can!"
msgstr "¡ALLÍ! ¡Ahora, apúrense! ¡Tenemos que ir lo más profundo posible!"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:318
msgid ""
"(roaring) Sneaky vermin, tuck yourselves in the underground if you so wish! "
"Next time you emerge, only a dead land shall greet you!"
msgstr ""
"(rugiendo) ¡Alimañas astutas, escóndanse bajo tierra si así lo desean! ¡La "
"próxima vez que emerjan, solo una tierra muerta las recibirá!"

#. [message], speaker=Yiwen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:327
msgid "(exhausted) I... can't... believe... we did... it..."
msgstr "(agotada) No… puedo… creer… que lo logramos…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:331
msgid ""
"We're very lucky to be alive, but we can't be relieved yet; hiding in these "
"caves will not help us defeat him. Now, let's find..."
msgstr ""
"Tuvimos mucha suerte de seguir vivas, pero aún no podemos relajarnos; "
"escondernos en estas cuevas no nos ayudará a derrotarlo. Ahora, busquemos…"

#. [message], speaker=Shwarzel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:354
msgid "My, my, look who we have here... It has been a while, human! "
msgstr "Vaya, vaya, mira quién tenemos aquí… ¡Ha pasado tiempo, humana!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:358
msgid ""
"Svaryarna, Thrur, Augdras...! I'm sorry for intruding in your battle, but..."
msgstr "¡Svaryarna, Thrur, Augdras…! Lamento irrumpir en su batalla, pero…"

#. [message], speaker=Thrur
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:362
msgid ""
"Battle? What are you talking about, little human? We have simply gathered "
"because a scout has spread rumours that Tenma Yozora was on her way to the "
"Hammermounts, chased by a monster."
msgstr ""
"¿Batalla? ¿De qué hablas, pequeña humana? Solo nos hemos reunido porque un "
"explorador difundió rumores de que Tenma Yozora venía hacia los "
"Hammermounts, perseguida por un monstruo."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:366
msgid ""
"Yes, that's true... We've managed to lose him in the underground, but hiding "
"here will do me no good... Damn it, I didn't want to bring him to your home, "
"I meant to go to the Heart Mountains but lost my way..."
msgstr ""
"Sí, es cierto… Logramos perderlo en el subsuelo, pero esconderme aquí no me "
"servirá de nada… Maldición, no quería traerlo a su hogar, mi intención era "
"ir a las Montañas del Corazón pero perdí el camino…"

#. [message], speaker=Augdras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:370
msgid ""
"Still looking for them? Well, the under-roads to Knalga are still sealed... "
"but we have been clearing some of the under-roads that lead west."
msgstr ""
"¿Todavía buscándolas? Bueno, los caminos subterráneos a Knalga siguen "
"sellados… pero hemos estado despejando algunos de los caminos subterráneos "
"que llevan al oeste."

#. [message], speaker=Shwarzel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:374
msgid ""
"Not without help, was it, my good dwarven friend? Never would you have "
"managed your work pace without our logistics."
msgstr ""
"No sin ayuda, ¿verdad, mi buen amigo enano? Nunca habrías logrado ese ritmo "
"de trabajo sin nuestra logística."

#. [message], speaker=Thrur
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:378
msgid "Or our help in lifting the biggest rocks."
msgstr "O nuestra ayuda para levantar las rocas más grandes."

#. [message], speaker=Augdras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:382
msgid ""
"Aye, ye are right. We've already cleared the under-roads to the ancient "
"Dulatus caves, which we tried to clear for generations, but never could - "
"not by ourselves."
msgstr ""
"Aye, tienen razón. Ya hemos despejado los caminos subterráneos hacia las "
"antiguas cuevas Dulatus, que intentamos despejar durante generaciones, pero "
"nunca pudimos… no por nosotros solos."

#. [message], speaker=Shwarzel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:386
msgid ""
"So you see, my pretty human, you were right all along about the worth of "
"working together, so rejoice... (puzzled) Now why is water flowing so "
"effusively out of your eyes...?"
msgstr ""
"Así que ves, mi bonita humana, tenías razón desde el principio sobre el "
"valor de trabajar juntos, así que alégrate… (desconcertada) Ahora, ¿por qué "
"está saliendo tanta agua de tus ojos…?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:390
msgid ""
"(sobbing) T-thank you, f-friends... T-thank you for making it all w-"
"worthwhile..."
msgstr ""
"(sollozando) G-gracias, a-amigos… G-gracias por hacer que todo v-valga la "
"pena…"

#. [message], speaker=Augdras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:394
msgid ""
"I dunno exactly why ye are so glad, but stop thanking us, or we'll never be "
"able to repay ye! Now, prepare yourself, that we shall take you west as if "
"flying!"
msgstr ""
"No sé exactamente por qué estás tan contenta, pero deja de agradecernos o "
"nunca podremos pagarte. ¡Ahora prepárate, te llevaremos al oeste como si "
"voláramos!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/47_Sky_Chase.cfg:415
msgid ""
"Damn it all, we took too long to reach the caves! We're too tired to go on "
"any longer...!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldición, tardamos demasiado en llegar a las cuevas! ¡Estamos demasiado "
"cansados para seguir!"

#. [scenario], id=48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:7
msgid "The Sun Sets over Wesnoth"
msgstr "El Sol se Pone sobre Wesnoth"

#. [side], type=Grand Knight
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:93
msgid "Sir Rugar"
msgstr "Sir Rugar"

#. [side], type=Grand Knight
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:98
msgid "Horse Clans"
msgstr "Clanes de Jinetes"

#. [side], type=Necromancer
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:117
msgid "Mal-Ardrya"
msgstr "Mal-Ardrya"

#. [label]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:284
msgid "King Haldric I's Gate"
msgstr "Puerta del Rey Haldric I"

#. [label]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:289
msgid "Addraryn's Gate"
msgstr "Puerta de Addraryn"

#. [label]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:294
msgid "Delfador's Gate"
msgstr "Puerta de Delfador"

#. [label]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:299
msgid "Konrad I' Gate"
msgstr "Puerta de Konrad I"

#. [label]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:304
msgid "Iron Gate"
msgstr "Puerta de Hierro"

#. [label]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:309
msgid "Akladian Gate"
msgstr "Puerta Akladiana"

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:338
msgid ""
"Iron Guard, stand ready! Someone approaches, a young woman with strange "
"magical powers, just as the witch from Arajunna is described!"
msgstr ""
"¡Guardia de Hierro, listos! ¡Alguien se acerca, una joven mujer con extraños "
"poderes mágicos, justo como describen a la bruja de Arajunna!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:342
msgid ""
"I'm not...! Wesnothians, please hear me! I'm a friend, and I come to warn "
"you of a danger that is about to come to your gates!"
msgstr ""
"¡No soy…! ¡Wesnothianos, por favor escúchenme! Soy una amiga, ¡y vengo a "
"advertirles de un peligro que está a punto de llegar a sus puertas!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:346
msgid ""
"You, on Weldyn, claiming to come as a friend... Now that's something I never "
"thought I'd see <i>you</i> do, Rebel of Kodakuni."
msgstr ""
"Tú, en Weldyn, afirmando venir como amiga… Eso es algo que nunca pensé que "
"te vería hacer, Rebelde de Kodakuni."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:350
msgid ""
"Not the time, Aetheryon. Please, I need your help; you must warn your father "
"that-"
msgstr ""
"No es el momento, Aetheryon. Por favor, necesito tu ayuda; debes advertir a "
"tu padre que—"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:354
msgid ""
"My father is dead, Tenma; I am the new Emperor of Wesnoth, so whatever "
"warning you have to give this empire, you can give it to me directly. We may "
"not be friends, but you've earned enough of my respect to deserve my full "
"attention."
msgstr ""
"Mi padre está muerto, Tenma; yo soy el nuevo Emperador de Wesnoth, así que "
"cualquier advertencia que tengas para este imperio, puedes dármela "
"directamente a mí. Puede que no seamos amigos, pero te has ganado suficiente "
"de mi respeto como para merecer toda mi atención."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:358
msgid ""
"Aetheryon, I know what Galdra's been wreaking in this country, but there's "
"another enemy on the way, one just as dangerous, if not worse: the Sky "
"Dragon Svarballi, a monster who's tried to destroy this world thrice in the "
"past. All this time I'd been training to destroy him in his prison, but "
"Galdra has released him..."
msgstr ""
"Aetheryon, sé lo que Galdra ha estado causando en este país, pero hay otro "
"enemigo en camino, uno igual de peligroso, si no peor: el Dragón del Cielo "
"Svarballi, un monstruo que ha intentado destruir este mundo tres veces en el "
"pasado. Todo este tiempo he estado entrenando para destruirlo en su prisión, "
"pero Galdra lo ha liberado…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:362
msgid ""
"Sky Dragon... The name is familiar to me, but I cannot help you unless you "
"tell me the whole story, Tenma - the story Olokun so insisted on hiding from "
"me."
msgstr ""
"Dragón del Cielo… El nombre me resulta familiar, pero no puedo ayudarte a "
"menos que me cuentes toda la historia, Tenma… la historia que Olokun tanto "
"insistió en ocultarme."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:366
msgid ""
"(sigh) Very well. Olokun's people come from a continent beyond Arajunna; "
"their ancestors fought against Svarballi, and managed to seal him in a "
"magical jewel. They called it the Sky Soul; that's what Galdra took from me "
"when she defeated me in Arajunna."
msgstr ""
"(suspiro) Muy bien. El pueblo de Olokun viene de un continente más allá de "
"Arajunna; sus ancestros lucharon contra Svarballi y lograron sellarlo en una "
"joya mágica. La llamaron Alma del Cielo; eso es lo que Galdra me quitó "
"cuando me derrotó en Arajunna."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:370
msgid ""
"Interesting indeed; it matches what I had discovered from ghosts during the "
"time I was Kodakuni's overseer... If this Sky Dragon has been defeated "
"before, surely Olokun's people know how to do it again, do they not?"
msgstr ""
"Interesante en verdad; coincide con lo que descubrí de fantasmas durante el "
"tiempo que fui supervisor de Kodakuni… Si este Dragón del Cielo ha sido "
"derrotado antes, seguro que el pueblo de Olokun sabe cómo hacerlo de nuevo, "
"¿no es así?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:374
msgid ""
"They do, but this time we must destroy him, otherwise he'll continue to "
"threaten this world. I have the power to do that, but I need aid – "
"especially to deal with Galdra. My friends should be near Wesnoth's "
"frontier, perhaps they've crossed it already, and they have powerful weapons "
"with them; with the power of Wesnoth, we could face both Galdra and "
"Svarballi."
msgstr ""
"Lo saben, pero esta vez debemos destruirlo, de lo contrario seguirá "
"amenazando este mundo. Tengo el poder para hacerlo, pero necesito ayuda… "
"especialmente para lidiar con Galdra. Mis amigos deberían estar cerca de la "
"frontera de Wesnoth, tal vez ya la hayan cruzado, y traen armas poderosas "
"consigo; con el poder de Wesnoth, podríamos enfrentar tanto a Galdra como a "
"Svarballi."

#. [message], speaker=Aethra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:378
msgid ""
"Brother, please, consider her offer, we cannot fight two such monsters on "
"our own!"
msgstr ""
"¡Hermano, por favor, considera su oferta, no podemos luchar contra dos "
"monstruos así solos!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:382
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, the Heartlands of Wesnoth are completely cut off the rest of "
"the empire. Galdra's monsters, rebellions and desertions have all left our "
"communication routes in tatters. But Aethra is right; we have barely been "
"able to withstand Galdra alone... I have decided: you may fight by Wesnoth's "
"side once more."
msgstr ""
"Desafortunadamente, las Tierras Centrales de Wesnoth están completamente "
"aisladas del resto del imperio. Los monstruos de Galdra, las rebeliones y "
"las deserciones han dejado nuestras rutas de comunicación hechas trizas. "
"Pero Aethra tiene razón; apenas hemos podido resistir a Galdra solos… He "
"decidido: puedes luchar al lado de Wesnoth una vez más."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:386
msgid ""
"Thank you so much... I will send some spirits to find the others, then. Now, "
"if I may ask, shouldn't those mages be preparing to fight Galdra's swarms?"
msgstr ""
"Muchas gracias… Entonces enviaré algunos espíritus a buscar a los demás. "
"Ahora, si me permites preguntar, ¿no deberían esos magos estar preparándose "
"para luchar contra los enjambres de Galdra?"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:398
msgid ""
"They are casting a spell on that mountain, to make it shine over this entire "
"region. As you must have noticed, Galdra's monsters are vulnerable to the "
"light."
msgstr ""
"Están lanzando un hechizo sobre esa montaña para hacerla brillar sobre toda "
"esta región. Como debes haber notado, los monstruos de Galdra son "
"vulnerables a la luz."

#. [message], speaker=Aethra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:402
msgid "(whisper) Aetheryon...!"
msgstr "(susurro) ¡Aetheryon…!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:412
msgid "Galdra...!"
msgstr "¡Galdra…!"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:416
msgid ""
"Your time is over, Aetheryon. I have allowed you to try and mount a proper "
"defence for your kingdom; now, let us see whether this nation of humankind "
"deserves to endure."
msgstr ""
"Tu tiempo ha terminado, Aetheryon. Te he permitido intentar montar una "
"defensa adecuada para tu reino; ahora veamos si esta nación de humanos "
"merece perdurar."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:420
msgid ""
"(chuckling) My entire life, I believed my father a monster for preaching "
"that might makes right, including one's right to live. But I now realise "
"that he spoke truth – and I learn it from the mouth of she whom I once "
"thought the purest of creatures..."
msgstr ""
"(riendo) Toda mi vida creí que mi padre era un monstruo por predicar que la "
"fuerza hace el derecho, incluyendo el derecho a vivir. Pero ahora me doy "
"cuenta de que decía la verdad… y lo aprendo de la boca de aquella que una "
"vez pensé era la criatura más pura…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:427
msgid ""
"So be it, Galdra! Wesnoth has been founded on death and destruction, risen "
"through blood and steel, and now, through fire and brimstone, it shall "
"reassert its supremacy over this world! Soldiers of the West-North, prepare "
"for battle!"
msgstr ""
"¡Que así sea, Galdra! Wesnoth fue fundado sobre muerte y destrucción, se "
"levantó con sangre y acero, ¡y ahora, a través de fuego y azufre, reafirmará "
"su supremacía sobre este mundo! ¡Soldados del Oeste-Norte, prepárense para "
"la batalla!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:431
msgid ""
"Aetheryon, I forgot to warn you of the Ruby of Fire's true nature: it's a "
"prison, similar to the one that contained Svarballi, and which contains the "
"souls of three great dragons from the ancient age. You must be extremely "
"careful with it; in fact, it might be best if you just left it aside-"
msgstr ""
"Aetheryon, olvidé advertirte sobre la verdadera naturaleza del Rubí de "
"Fuego: es una prisión, similar a la que contenía a Svarballi, y que contiene "
"las almas de tres grandes dragones de la era antigua. Debes ser "
"extremadamente cuidadoso con él; de hecho, sería mejor si simplemente lo "
"dejaras de lado—"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:435
msgid ""
"(coldly) It is time you knew your place, Sogen; you have no authority to "
"counsel the Emperor of Wesnoth, so choose your words carefully!"
msgstr ""
"(fríamente) Es hora de que conozcas tu lugar, Sogen; no tienes autoridad "
"para aconsejar al Emperador de Wesnoth, ¡así que elige tus palabras con "
"cuidado!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:439
msgid "Aetheryon, why you...!"
msgstr "¡Aetheryon, cómo tú…!"

#. [message], speaker=Aethra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:443
msgid "Tenma, I-I'm..."
msgstr "Tenma, yo… estoy…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:447
msgid ""
"And you, sister, please take shelter inside the palace; this is no place for "
"you to be right now."
msgstr ""
"Y tú, hermana, por favor refúgiate dentro del palacio; este no es lugar para "
"ti en este momento."

#. [message], speaker=Aethra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:451
msgid "Y-yes, brother..."
msgstr "S-sí, hermano…"

#. [message], speaker=Yiwen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:460
msgid ""
"Tenma, if you wish, I could go and find your friends; I'm faster than your "
"spirits, and you'll need every single one of them in this battle."
msgstr ""
"Tenma, si lo deseas, podría ir a buscar a tus amigos; soy más rápida que tus "
"espíritus, y necesitarás cada uno de ellos en esta batalla."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:464
msgid "Thank you, Yiwen..."
msgstr "Gracias, Yiwen…"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:484
msgid ""
"Tenma, are you in agreement with Aetheryon on his plans for that mountain to "
"the east?"
msgstr ""
"Tenma, ¿estás de acuerdo con Aetheryon en sus planes para esa montaña al "
"este?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:488
msgid "And why should I not be?"
msgstr "¿Y por qué no debería estarlo?"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:492
msgid "(chuckling) As I thought, you know nothing..."
msgstr "(riendo) Como pensaba, no sabes nada…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:496
msgid "(angry) Pay her no heed, Tenma! She's trying to distract us!"
msgstr "(enojado) ¡No le hagas caso, Tenma! ¡Está intentando distraernos!"

#. [message], speaker=Elcadar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:511
msgid "My Emperor..."
msgstr "Mi Emperador…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:515
msgid "Speak at once, you fool! Don't you see I'm in the middle of a battle?"
msgstr "¡Habla de una vez, idiota! ¿No ves que estoy en medio de una batalla?"

#. [message], speaker=Elcadar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:519
msgid ""
"T-the Necromancers have finished digging beneath the mountain; and, as you "
"can see, it is almost completely lit."
msgstr ""
"L-los Nigromantes han terminado de cavar bajo la montaña; y, como puedes "
"ver, ya está casi completamente iluminada."

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:523
msgid ""
"Excellent. As soon as the spell is completed, give the order to... conclude "
"the project. Do not waste time coming here to tell me that, at the speed you "
"move I will be dead by the time the mountain... Wait, Aethra, where are you "
"going?!"
msgstr ""
"Excelente. Tan pronto como el hechizo esté completo, da la orden de… "
"concluir el proyecto. No pierdas tiempo viniendo aquí a decírmelo, a la "
"velocidad que te mueves estaré muerto para cuando la montaña… ¡Espera, "
"Aethra, a dónde vas!"

#. [message], speaker=Aethra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:534
msgid "Sorry, brother, but I can't let it go on..."
msgstr "Lo siento, hermano, pero no puedo permitir que continúe…"

#. [message], speaker=Aethra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:541
msgid ""
"(shouting) Tenma, hear me! That mountain is not going to lit this region "
"only, it will be raised as a third sun!"
msgstr ""
"(gritando) ¡Tenma, escúchame! ¡Esa montaña no solo va a iluminar esta "
"región, será elevada como un tercer sol!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:545
msgid ""
"(shocked) What...?! Aetheryon, are you <i>insane</i>?! Two suns have been "
"bad enough already for this world, and you want to raise another one?! Do "
"you think that banishing the night won't have consequences?!"
msgstr ""
"(impactada) ¿Qué…?! ¡Aetheryon, estás <i>loco</i>! ¡Dos soles ya han sido "
"suficientemente malos para este mundo, y quieres elevar otro más! ¿Crees que "
"desterrar la noche no tendrá consecuencias?"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:549
msgid ""
"Do not underestimate me, I am well aware of the consequences of raising a "
"third sun! Trust me, this is the lesser of two evils: with the strength "
"given us by the third sun, we shall be able to defeat Galdra and then "
"restore our empire's power and stability!"
msgstr ""
"¡No me subestimes, estoy plenamente consciente de las consecuencias de "
"elevar un tercer sol! Confía en mí, esto es el menor de dos males: con la "
"fuerza que nos dé el tercer sol, podremos derrotar a Galdra y luego "
"restaurar el poder y la estabilidad de nuestro imperio."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:553
msgid ""
"(furious) So, in the end, it all comes down to the 'glory of Wesnoth' "
"doesn't it?! Damn you, Aetheryon... After what we've been through in the "
"Northlands, I started to believe you were, at heart, a good and sensible "
"man, even if reckless. What a disappointment..."
msgstr ""
"(furiosa) Entonces, al final, todo se reduce a la «gloria de Wesnoth», "
"¿verdad? ¡Maldito seas, Aetheryon…! Después de todo lo que pasamos en las "
"Tierras del Norte, empecé a creer que en el fondo eras un hombre bueno y "
"sensato, aunque imprudente. Qué decepción…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:557
msgid ""
"You were not wrong, Tenma; I was such person, a 'sensible' fool who believed "
"there was worth in being kind. But kindness did not protect my mother, or my "
"sister, from my father's violence and contempt; nor did it prevent Galdra "
"from betraying me as if I was nobody...! Now, if you disagree with my plans, "
"by all means, try and stop me!"
msgstr ""
"No estabas equivocada, Tenma; fui esa persona, un tonto «sensato» que creía "
"que había valor en ser amable. Pero la amabilidad no protegió a mi madre ni "
"a mi hermana de la violencia y el desprecio de mi padre; ¡ni impidió que "
"Galdra me traicionara como si no fuera nadie…! Ahora, si no estás de acuerdo "
"con mis planes, ¡adelante, intenta detenerme!"

#. [message], speaker=Aethra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:561
msgid "Aetheryon, don't..."
msgstr "Aetheryon, no…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:565
msgid ""
"(coldly) And you, sister, go back to your chambers – and this is an order by "
"your emperor; disobey it, and you shall be sent to the dungeons instead!"
msgstr ""
"(fríamente) Y tú, hermana, regresa a tus aposentos… ¡y esto es una orden de "
"tu emperador! Desobedece y serás enviada a las mazmorras en su lugar."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:581
msgid "*What should I do...?*"
msgstr "*¿Qué debo hacer…?*"

#. [option]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:584
msgid "Stay on Aetheryon's side"
msgstr "Mantente del lado de Aetheryon"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:589
msgid ""
"I will not fight you, Aetheryon, not now. But I cannot let you go on with "
"this madness either; as soon as we're done with Galdra, I'll take care of "
"you!"
msgstr ""
"No lucharé contra ti, Aetheryon, no ahora. Pero tampoco puedo permitir que "
"continúes con esta locura; tan pronto terminemos con Galdra, ¡me encargaré "
"de ti!"

#. [option]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:594
msgid "Turn against Aetheryon"
msgstr "Vuélvete contra Aetheryon"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:617
msgid ""
"Aetheryon, I can't simply stand by and watch as you doom this world; if I "
"have to kill you to stop this madness, then I'll do it!"
msgstr ""
"Aetheryon, no puedo quedarme de brazos cruzados viendo cómo condenas este "
"mundo; ¡si tengo que matarte para detener esta locura, lo haré!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:621
msgid "You will <i>try</i>..."
msgstr "Lo <i>intentará</i>…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:656
msgid "Blessed be Yiwen...! But where are the others?"
msgstr "¡Bendita sea Yiwen…! Pero ¿dónde están los demás?"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:660
msgid ""
"They're on their way, I simply came ahead of them because I needed to see it "
"with my own eyes... Is it true then, brother? Have you inherited the Iron "
"Crown through the Law of Strength? Have you fought against father for it?"
msgstr ""
"Están en camino, solo vine antes que ellos porque necesitaba verlo con mis "
"propios ojos… ¿Es cierto entonces, hermano? ¿Has heredado la Corona de "
"Hierro mediante la Ley de la Fuerza? ¿Luchaste contra padre por ella?"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:664
msgid ""
"Father was growing mad, brother; his orders were dooming our kingdom and "
"people, and so I decided to act."
msgstr ""
"Padre se estaba volviendo loco, hermano; sus órdenes estaban condenando a "
"nuestro reino y a nuestra gente, así que decidí actuar."

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:668
msgid ""
"If that is true, then father deserved to be deposed – but killed?! "
"Aetheryon, you are his blood! How could you do that to him?!"
msgstr ""
"Si eso es cierto, entonces padre merecía ser depuesto… ¿pero asesinado? "
"¡Aetheryon, eres su sangre! ¿Cómo pudiste hacerle eso?!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:672
msgid ""
"How could I what, give a man who brutalised my mother, my sister and myself "
"for years what he deserved? He was no true father, he was merely a sire. "
"Now, brother, leave your lecture for a later hour, we have more urgent "
"matters to be concerned about!"
msgstr ""
"¿Cómo pude qué, darle a un hombre que maltrató a mi madre, a mi hermana y a "
"mí durante años lo que merecía? No era un verdadero padre, solo era un "
"progenitor. Ahora, hermano, deja tu sermón para más tarde, ¡tenemos asuntos "
"mucho más urgentes de los que preocuparnos!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:676
msgid ""
"Indeed, <i>Emperor</i>, you must be very busy, commanding the raising of a "
"third sun into the sky..."
msgstr ""
"En efecto, <i>Emperador</i>, debes estar muy ocupado dando órdenes para "
"levantar un tercer sol en el cielo…"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:680
msgid "What... (looks at the mountain) Aetheryon, you can't be seriously..."
msgstr "Qué… (mira la montaña) Aetheryon, no puedes estar hablando en serio…"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:684
msgid ""
"(angry) Yes, brother, I am raising another sun – and I recommend you to "
"accept it, or else I will be forced to take measures against you too!"
msgstr ""
"(enojado) Sí, hermano, estoy levantando otro sol… ¡y te recomiendo que lo "
"aceptes, o me veré obligado a tomar medidas contra ti también!"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:694
msgid ""
"I used to think you the best of us, brother; it grieves me to see that the "
"darkness of our dynasty has tainted even you... If you're set on this path, "
"then you leave me no choice but to oppose you!"
msgstr ""
"Antes pensaba que eras el mejor de nosotros, hermano; me duele ver que la "
"oscuridad de nuestra dinastía te ha corrompido también a ti… Si estás "
"decidido a seguir este camino, entonces no me dejas otra opción más que "
"oponerme a ti."

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:716
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:749
msgid ""
"NOTE: Once again, it might be better to invoke the Dragon-Slayer mode later "
"in the scenario - though it is not obligatory."
msgstr ""
"NOTA: Una vez más, podría ser mejor activar el modo Cazadragones más "
"adelante en el escenario, aunque no es obligatorio."

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:727
msgid ""
"Never would I approve such madness! For now we shall fight together, "
"Aetheryon, but when this battle is over, we <i>will</i> settle this between "
"ourselves!"
msgstr ""
"¡Jamás aprobaría semejante locura! Por ahora lucharemos juntos, Aetheryon, "
"pero cuando esta batalla termine, <i>resolveremos</i> esto entre nosotros."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:780
msgid "Oh, no, no, no...!"
msgstr "¡Oh, no, no, no…!"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:784
msgid "(frightened) So <i>that</i> is the Sky Dragon...?"
msgstr "(asustado) ¿Entonces <i>ese</i> es el Dragón del Cielo…?"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:788
msgid ""
"Have you decided at last to stop running and fight, Myra? What happened to "
"that woman who once so bravely faced me and a horde of dragons?"
msgstr ""
"¿Al fin decidiste dejar de huir y pelear, Myra? ¿Qué pasó con aquella mujer "
"que una vez me enfrentó tan valientemente a mí y a una horda de dragones?"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:792
msgid "Svarballi, I hope you have not forgotten our non-aggression agreement?"
msgstr "Svarballi, espero que no hayas olvidado nuestro pacto de no agresión."

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:796
msgid ""
"I have not, as I hope you have not forgotten that Myra of Hiera'Shirsha is "
"mine, and that you shall not stand against me no matter your judgment."
msgstr ""
"No lo he olvidado, como espero que tú no hayas olvidado que Myra de "
"Hiera'Shirsha es mía, y que no te interpondrás en mi camino sin importar tu "
"juicio."

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:800
msgid ""
"It seems he won't fight, not for the time being; that gives us some time to "
"deal with Galdra. I just hope the Kings and the Queens do not arrive too "
"late..."
msgstr ""
"Parece que no va a pelear, al menos por ahora; eso nos da algo de tiempo "
"para encargarnos de Galdra. Solo espero que los Reyes y las Reinas no "
"lleguen demasiado tarde…"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:816
msgid "Damn it, were we too late to stop it...?!"
msgstr "¡Maldición, llegamos demasiado tarde para detenerlo…!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:838
msgid ""
"Aetheryon, I beg you, stop this insanity! What good is there in fighting an "
"evil with another evil?!"
msgstr ""
"Aetheryon, te lo suplico, ¡detén esta locura! ¿De qué sirve combatir un mal "
"con otro mal?"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:842
msgid ""
"(furious) I told you to KNOW YOUR PLACE, SOGEN!!! (shouting) Mages, waste "
"not a further second, and let the new sun rise!"
msgstr ""
"(furioso) ¡Te dije que conozcas tu lugar, SOGEN! (gritando) ¡Magos, no "
"pierdan ni un segundo más, que el nuevo sol ascienda!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:846
msgid ""
"Tenma tried to think of a way to stop the mountain from taking off the "
"ground; but, before she could even scream something, the huge mass of sheer "
"rock began its slow ascension."
msgstr ""
"Tenma intentó pensar en una forma de evitar que la montaña despegara del "
"suelo; pero, antes de que pudiera siquiera gritar algo, la enorme masa de "
"roca pura comenzó su lenta ascensión."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:850
msgid "Aeldhoryan, by his turn, had another worry in mind."
msgstr "Aeldhoryan, por su parte, tenía otra preocupación en mente."

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:854
msgid ""
"Tenma... Get away from there... Everyone, we must evacuate this place NOW!"
msgstr "Tenma… ¡Aléjate de ahí…! ¡Todos, debemos evacuar este lugar AHORA!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:858
msgid "Flee if you so wish, brother! I shall stay and fight for our people!"
msgstr ""
"¡Huye si así lo deseas, hermano! ¡Yo me quedaré y lucharé por nuestra gente!"

#. [message], speaker=Aethra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:862
msgid ""
"(crying) Aetheryon, please open your eyes! You are becoming the very monster "
"that father once was!"
msgstr ""
"(llorando) Aetheryon, por favor, ¡abre los ojos! ¡Te estás convirtiendo en "
"el mismo monstruo que una vez fue padre!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:866
msgid ""
"If I must become a monster in order to protect what is important to me, then "
"I have no regrets!"
msgstr ""
"¡Si debo convertirme en un monstruo para proteger lo que es importante para "
"mí, entonces no tengo remordimientos!"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:870
msgid "Everyone, run away from Weldyn NOW!!!"
msgstr "¡Todos, huyan de Weldyn AHORA!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:894
msgid "Wait... Aethra...!"
msgstr "¡Espera… Aethra…!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:898
msgid ""
"And now, I banish thee, Night! New Sun, claim your place beside your "
"brothers, and shine a new era upon us!"
msgstr ""
"Y ahora, ¡te destierro, Noche! ¡Nuevo Sol, reclama tu lugar junto a tus "
"hermanos y alumbra una nueva era sobre nosotros!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:902
msgid ""
"The mages' faces were contorted with the effort of lifting the mountain, "
"which ascended increasingly faster, bathing the land in light, turning night "
"into day. Everyone watched that momentous event in awe; even Galdra halted "
"her swarms' advance to behold it. After reaching the height of the clouds, "
"the third sun moved westwards, beginning its first orbit."
msgstr ""
"Los rostros de los magos estaban contraídos por el esfuerzo de levantar la "
"montaña, que ascendía cada vez más rápido, bañando la tierra en luz y "
"convirtiendo la noche en día. Todos observaron aquel momento trascendental "
"con asombro; incluso Galdra detuvo el avance de sus enjambres para "
"contemplarlo. Al alcanzar la altura de las nubes, el tercer sol se desplazó "
"hacia el oeste, iniciando su primera órbita."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:909
msgid "And only then did everyone notice something was very wrong."
msgstr "Y solo entonces todos notaron que algo estaba muy mal."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:913
msgid "Is it my impression, or is the new sun growing brighter...?"
msgstr "¿Es impresión mía, o el nuevo sol se está volviendo más brillante…?"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:917
msgid ""
"It's not growing brighter... (terrified) By the Gods of Light, I knew those "
"mages would not be enough, it is falling again!!!"
msgstr ""
"No se está volviendo más brillante… (aterrado) ¡Por los Dioses de la Luz, ya "
"sabía que esos magos no serían suficientes, está cayendo otra vez!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:921
msgid ""
"Aeldhoryan was not the first to notice that the raising of the sun had "
"failed; shocked, terrified screams echoed all over Weldyn even before the "
"eldest prince had finished his sentence. The mages desperately tried to "
"change the sun's trajectory, but they stood powerless as it descended upon "
"the ancient capital of Wesnoth like a meteor..."
msgstr ""
"Aeldhoryan no fue el primero en notar que el levantamiento del sol había "
"fracasado; gritos de shock y terror resonaron por todo Weldyn incluso antes "
"de que el príncipe mayor terminara su frase. Los magos intentaron "
"desesperadamente cambiar la trayectoria del sol, pero quedaron impotentes "
"mientras descendía sobre la antigua capital de Wesnoth como un meteoro…"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:936
msgid "AETHERYON, AETHRA...!!!"
msgstr "¡AETHERYON, AETHRA…!"

#. [message], speaker=Aethra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:940
msgid "(crying) Brother...!"
msgstr "(llorando) ¡Hermano…!"

#. [message], speaker=Aetheryon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:944
msgid "I... have..."
msgstr "Yo… he…"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1030
msgid ""
"(roaring) Ha! Like the Windsong, you create a weapon to destroy your foe, "
"and all you manage to do is to destroy yourselves and break this world's "
"balance irreversibly! Do you see why I want to purge this planet, "
"Nitiballi?! Do you see what Mother's creations are truly made of?!"
msgstr ""
"(rugiendo) ¡Ja! Al igual que las Hijas del Viento, crean un arma para "
"destruir a su enemigo, ¡y lo único que logran es destruirse a sí mismas y "
"romper irreversiblemente el equilibrio de este mundo! ¿Ven ahora por qué "
"quiero purgar este planeta, Nitiballi? ¿Ven de qué están hechas realmente "
"las creaciones de la Madre?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1034
msgid "(in pain) AAAAAAAAAHHHHHHHH!!!"
msgstr "(de dolor) ¡AAAAAAAAAHHHHHHH!"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1038
msgid ""
"As I thought... Such heavy impact has wounded the very soul of this world – "
"and, thus, all those bound to it..."
msgstr ""
"Tal como pensé… Un impacto tan fuerte ha herido el alma misma de este mundo… "
"y, por lo tanto, a todos los que están ligados a él…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1042
msgid "TENMA! Damn it, hold on, we're here with you!"
msgstr "¡TENMA! ¡Maldición, aguanta, estamos aquí contigo!"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1046
msgid "She's still managed to summon this earthen elemental to protect us...!"
msgstr "¡Aún logró invocar a este elemental de tierra para protegernos…!"

#. [message], speaker=Bhumi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1050
msgid "Do... not... give... up... Heiress..."
msgstr "No… te… rindas… Heredera…"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1060
msgid ""
"Once again, the children of Life wield Vanadya's gift to bring nothing but "
"harm upon themselves, forever breaking this world in the process. How "
"disappointing..."
msgstr ""
"Una vez más, los hijos de la Vida empuñan el don de Vanadya para no traer "
"más que daño sobre sí mismos, rompiendo este mundo para siempre en el "
"proceso. Qué decepción…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1064
msgid ""
"(crying in anguish) No... No... Aetheryon, what... what have you done..."
msgstr "(llorando de angustia) No… No… Aetheryon, ¿qué… qué has hecho…?"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1098
msgid "This power..."
msgstr "Este poder…"

#. [message], speaker=Niddhon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1102
msgid "At last... After so many aeons, we are free at last!"
msgstr "¡Por fin…! Después de tantos eones, ¡al fin somos libres!"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1106
msgid "Those dragons... Could they be the three dragons of the Ruby?"
msgstr "Esos dragones… ¿Podrían ser los tres dragones del Rubí?"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1110
msgid ""
"Like the Sky Soul itself, the Ruby of Fire was a locked gate to the "
"Worldsweave plane where the three dragons had been locked. Shattered by the "
"impact of a falling sun, it could no longer contain its prisoners..."
msgstr ""
"Al igual que el Alma del Cielo, el Rubí de Fuego era una puerta cerrada al "
"plano del Tejido del Mundo donde los tres dragones habían sido encerrados. "
"Destrozado por el impacto de un sol en caída, ya no pudo contener a sus "
"prisioneros…"

#. [message], speaker=Agadhor
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1114
msgid ""
"Lord Svarballi, we apologise for not being able to awaken earlier, but now "
"that we stand on earth, we shall follow you every command - just as we once "
"did!"
msgstr ""
"Señor Svarballi, nos disculpamos por no haber despertado antes, pero ahora "
"que estamos en la tierra, seguiremos cada uno de sus órdenes, ¡tal como lo "
"hicimos en el pasado!"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1118
msgid "(in despair) Damn it all, this is too much...!"
msgstr "(desesperado) ¡Maldición, esto es demasiado…!"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1122
msgid ""
"Will you insist on fighting even now, Myra? You call me the Destroyer, but "
"behold the desolation before you, the work of the very people you fight for. "
"This is the inevitable fate of the world, should it be left to the devices "
"of its children; all I do is to offer the mercy of a quick, painless end, to "
"spare you from a lengthened, torturous death. Know this, Myra, as you "
"finally die, in despair and alone..."
msgstr ""
"¿Aún insistes en luchar, Myra? Me llamas el Destructor, pero contempla la "
"desolación frente a ti, obra de la misma gente por la que luchas. Este es el "
"destino inevitable del mundo si se deja a merced de sus hijos; todo lo que "
"hago es ofrecer la misericordia de un final rápido e indoloro, para "
"ahorrarles una muerte prolongada y tortuosa. Sepan esto, Myra, mientras "
"mueres al fin, en desesperación y sola…"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1126
msgid "What makes you think she's alone, Sky Dragon?"
msgstr "¿Qué te hace pensar que está sola, Dragón del Cielo?"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1553
msgid "At long last...!"
msgstr "¡Por fin…!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1557
msgid "Ev-Everyone..."
msgstr "To-Todos…"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1561
msgid ""
"To think that, after all these aeons, the Kings of Irdya would reunite "
"again... Nevertheless, even if you rally every single being on this planet, "
"there is no way to avert your fate, maggots!"
msgstr ""
"Pensar que, después de todos estos eones, los Reyes de Irdya se reunirían de "
"nuevo… Sin embargo, aunque convoquen a cada ser de este planeta, no hay "
"forma de evitar su destino, ¡gusanos!"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1565
msgid "Svarballi, stand aside; I will be the one to fight them."
msgstr "Svarballi, apártate; seré yo quien luche contra ellos."

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1569
msgid ""
"After what they have done, still you require further judgment? <i>You</i> "
"stand aside, Heiress of Vanadya, these vermin are mine to crush-"
msgstr ""
"¿Después de lo que han hecho todavía necesitas más juicio? <i>Tú</i> "
"apártate, Heredera de Vanadya, estas alimañas son mías para aplastar—"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1580
msgid "Och, has she killed the dragons?!"
msgstr "¡Och, los ha matado a los dragones?!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1584
msgid ""
"No, I can still sense them... She's just placed them inside a barrier – and "
"a powerful one."
msgstr ""
"No, aún puedo sentirlos… Solo los ha colocado dentro de una barrera… y una "
"muy poderosa."

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1588
msgid ""
"Now we can face each other undisturbed. Rise, Heiress; this will be your "
"final chance to prove yourself worthy of upholding Demere's will, so rise up "
"and fight!"
msgstr ""
"Ahora podemos enfrentarnos sin interrupciones. Levántate, Heredera; esta "
"será tu última oportunidad de demostrar que eres digna de sostener la "
"voluntad de Demere, ¡así que levántate y lucha!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1607
msgid "As..."
msgstr "Como…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1620
msgid "...you wish..."
msgstr "…desees…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1633
msgid "...Avatar of Magic!"
msgstr "¡…Avatar de la Magia!"

#. [message], speaker=Bogor
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1637
msgid "That's the spirit, girl!"
msgstr "¡Ese es el espíritu, muchacha!"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1641
msgid "As expected from the only human whom I have ever followed!"
msgstr "¡Tal como esperaba de la única humana a la que he seguido jamás!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1645
msgid ""
"But this time we shall fight together, and don't you even try and convince "
"us otherwise!"
msgstr ""
"¡Pero esta vez lucharemos juntos, y ni siquiera intentes convencernos de lo "
"contrario!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1649
msgid "And Tenma, I think you will need this..."
msgstr "Y Tenma, creo que vas a necesitar esto…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1653
msgid "Akashia's Sword... Thanks for holding on to it, Olokun..."
msgstr "La Espada de Akashia… Gracias por haberla guardado, Olokun…"

#. [object], id=akashia_sword
#. [effect]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1658
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1668
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:249
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:258
msgid "Akashia's Sword"
msgstr "Espada de Akashia"

#. [object], id=akashia_sword
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1660
msgid ""
"Akashia's Sword is made of orichalcum, the sacred material originated from "
"an Avatar's death; as such, it has the power to destroy any physical, "
"magical or divine defence."
msgstr ""
"La Espada de Akashia está hecha de oricalco, el material sagrado que surge "
"de la muerte de un Avatar; por ello, tiene el poder de destruir cualquier "
"defensa física, mágica o divina."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1682
msgid ""
"This is it, friends! For the last two years, we have travelled the world and "
"prepared ourselves for this very moment! This is what the Kings and Queens "
"of Irdya have been reunited for – this is the final battle for the future of "
"this world! Now, CHARGE!!!"
msgstr ""
"¡Este es el momento, amigos! Durante los últimos dos años hemos recorrido el "
"mundo y nos hemos preparado para este preciso instante. ¡Para esto se han "
"reunido los Reyes y Reinas de Irdya: esta es la batalla final por el futuro "
"de este mundo! ¡Ahora, AL ATAQUE!"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1729
msgid "Destroy Galdra with Tenma's Dragon-Slayer spells or Akashia's Sword"
msgstr ""
"Destruye a Galdra con los hechizos Cazadragones de Tenma o con la Espada de "
"Akashia"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1777
msgid ""
"NOTE: In order to defeat Galdra without many losses, you may want to wear "
"her down with the Kings and Queens; Tenma only needs to inflict the death "
"blow.\n"
"Tenma's Elementals managed to escape Weldyn's destruction and may be "
"recalled again.\n"
"There will be no gold carryover to next scenario."
msgstr ""
"NOTA: Para derrotar a Galdra con pocas pérdidas, puedes desgastarla con los "
"Reyes y Reinas; Tenma solo necesita dar el golpe de gracia.\n"
"Los Elementales de Tenma lograron escapar de la destrucción de Weldyn y "
"pueden ser reincorporados nuevamente.\n"
"No habrá transferencia de oro al siguiente escenario."

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1794
msgid ""
"So you are An-Usrukhar's heir... Our predecessors were bound by heart and "
"soul; how tragic that we should stand as enemies on the field of battle..."
msgstr ""
"Entonces tú eres la heredera de An-Usrukhar… Nuestros predecesores estaban "
"unidos por el corazón y el alma; qué trágico que debamos enfrentarnos como "
"enemigos en el campo de batalla…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1798
msgid ""
"The real tragedy is that you have decided to destroy this world that your "
"predecessor sought to protect, Galdra."
msgstr ""
"La verdadera tragedia es que hayas decidido destruir este mundo que tu "
"predecesora buscó proteger, Galdra."

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1802
msgid "Either of us was wrong to do so; all that is left to prove is which..."
msgstr "Uno de nosotros estaba equivocado al hacerlo; solo queda probar cuál…"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1826
msgid "Too weak..."
msgstr "Demasiado débil…"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1849
msgid "...!!!"
msgstr "…!!!"

#. [message], speaker=Udhark
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1853
msgid ""
"This is it! Now, if this was not enough to destroy her, then nothing is!"
msgstr ""
"¡Esto es todo! Ahora, si esto no fue suficiente para destruirla, nada lo "
"será."

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1857
msgid ""
"No, I can feel her life energy starting to fade away; in the end, not even "
"gods are invincible..."
msgstr ""
"No, puedo sentir que su energía vital comienza a desvanecerse; al final, ni "
"siquiera los dioses son invencibles…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1864
msgid ""
"Galdra, tell me... Vanadya's will was not the destruction of the world of "
"Demere and An-Usrukhar, was it?"
msgstr ""
"Galdra, dime… La voluntad de Vanadya no era la destrucción del mundo de "
"Demere y An-Usrukhar, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1868
msgid ""
"*cough* Her will was that I had a will of my own, and used it to help the "
"Heiress of Demere when the time came..."
msgstr ""
"*tos* Su voluntad era que yo tuviera voluntad propia, y que la usara para "
"ayudar a la Heredera de Demere cuando llegara el momento…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1872
msgid ""
"Then why did you fight us?! Why did you unleash all this terror on Wesnoth?!"
msgstr ""
"¡Entonces por qué nos combatiste! ¿Por qué desataste todo este terror sobre "
"Wesnoth?"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1876
msgid ""
"Vanadya also instilled in me the memory of the love she experienced, "
"Tenma... But I have witnessed everything that's happened in this world since "
"my creation through the Akashic Realm; every war, every horror, every pain "
"needlessly inflicted upon a fellow being... every use of Vanadya's essence, "
"of magic itself, for perverse ends... I was born knowing nothing but love, "
"but this world's Children have taught me hatred as well."
msgstr ""
"Vanadya también implantó en mí el recuerdo del amor que ella experimentó, "
"Tenma… Pero he sido testigo de todo lo que ha sucedido en este mundo desde "
"mi creación a través del Reino Akáshico: cada guerra, cada horror, cada "
"dolor infligido innecesariamente a un semejante… cada uso de la esencia de "
"Vanadya, de la magia misma, para fines perversos… Nací sin conocer nada más "
"que amor, pero los Hijos de este mundo también me han enseñado el odio."

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1880
msgid ""
"Yet I have also witnessed how the Children band together when the tides of "
"destruction threaten all, and how understanding and true bonds are formed "
"from such gauntlets. You would never defeat Svarballi and his Death Dragons "
"by standing alone; even now, victory is not guaranteed..."
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo, también he visto cómo los Hijos se unen cuando las mareas de la "
"destrucción amenazan a todos, y cómo se forman la comprensión y los lazos "
"verdaderos a partir de tales pruebas. Nunca habrían derrotado a Svarballi y "
"a sus Dragones de la Muerte estando solos; incluso ahora, la victoria no "
"está garantizada…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1884
msgid "So you became the 'tide of destruction' that forced us to unite..."
msgstr ""
"Entonces te convertiste en la «marea de destrucción» que nos obligó a "
"unirnos…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1888
msgid ""
"No, I don't buy it. We had already brought many people together, we had the "
"Sky Soul in our hands, and the spells to destroy it. All you have done was "
"weaken us as we prepared to fight Svarballi!"
msgstr ""
"No, no me lo creo. Ya habíamos unido a mucha gente, teníamos el Alma del "
"Cielo en nuestras manos y los hechizos para destruirlo. ¡Todo lo que hiciste "
"fue debilitarnos mientras nos preparábamos para enfrentar a Svarballi!"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1892
msgid ""
"Your rampage too has all but destroyed a nation that could've been an ally "
"instead - and brought my brother to his breaking point, pushing him towards "
"a desperate measure that further wounded this world!"
msgstr ""
"Tu devastación también ha destruido casi por completo a una nación que pudo "
"haber sido una aliada… ¡y llevó a mi hermano al límite, empujándolo a una "
"medida desesperada que hirió aún más a este mundo!"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1896
msgid ""
"Do not misunderstand me, Children. Like I said, I am a being of free will, "
"born of a mother that created me with love, but also born to a world that "
"has taught me violence and hatred; a world that has turned the Avatars' "
"gifts of love and self-sacrifice into depravity."
msgstr ""
"No me malinterpreten, Hijos. Como dije, soy un ser de libre albedrío, nacido "
"de una madre que me creó con amor, pero también nacido en un mundo que me ha "
"enseñado violencia y odio; un mundo que ha convertido los dones de amor y "
"autosacrificio de los Avatares en depravación."

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1900
msgid ""
"'Pushed to the breaking point', you say? Svarballi shall presently teach you "
"the true meaning of destruction; I merely posed a challenge, and rather than "
"unite, your people have descended into petty squabblings, standing alone as "
"they massed as much power as they could in face of annihilation, raising a "
"third sun rather than simply seek each other. Now, if destruction is all you "
"know, then destruction is all that awaits you, and Vanadya was wrong to have "
"ever believed in you..."
msgstr ""
"¿«Llevado al límite», dices? Pronto Svarballi les enseñará el verdadero "
"significado de la destrucción; yo solo planteé un desafío, y en lugar de "
"unirse, su gente ha caído en disputas mezquinas, permaneciendo solos "
"mientras acumulaban todo el poder que podían frente a la aniquilación, "
"levantando un tercer sol en vez de simplemente buscarse unos a otros. Ahora, "
"si la destrucción es todo lo que conocen, entonces la destrucción es todo lo "
"que les espera, y Vanadya se equivocó al creer alguna vez en ustedes…"

#. [message], speaker=Galdra
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1904
msgid ""
"Then again... (looks around herself) In the end, perhaps she <i>was</i> "
"right to have believed in you..."
msgstr ""
"Sin embargo… (mira a su alrededor) Al final, tal vez <i>sí</i> tenía razón "
"al creer en ustedes…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1916
msgid ""
"Rest in peace, Heiress of Vanadya, I... better, <i>we</i> will keep proving "
"her right."
msgstr ""
"Descansa en paz, Heredera de Vanadya, yo… mejor dicho, <i>nosotros</i> "
"seguiremos demostrando que tenía razón."

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1949
msgid ""
"(enraged) That cursed creature...! So you have managed to destroy her, Myra; "
"that is good. Now, we shall continue our duel unbothered... unless you would "
"rather hide behind these Kings and Queens and let them die for you?"
msgstr ""
"(furioso) ¡Esa criatura maldita…! Así que lograste destruirla, Myra; eso "
"está bien. Ahora continuaremos nuestro duelo sin interrupciones… a menos que "
"prefieras esconderte detrás de estos Reyes y Reinas y dejar que mueran por "
"ti."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1953
msgid ""
"I will not flee any more, Svarballi; better still, I say we move to another "
"place, so that we can fight without interference."
msgstr ""
"Ya no huiré más, Svarballi; mejor aún, propongo que nos traslademos a otro "
"lugar, para que podamos luchar sin interferencias."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1957
msgid "But, Tenma...!"
msgstr "¡Pero, Tenma…!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1961
msgid "Weren't we supposed to fight alongside you?!"
msgstr "¡No íbamos a luchar a tu lado?!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1965
msgid ""
"You must fight those three dragons; after so much time bound in both the "
"Land of the Dead and the Dreamland, they've been changed to the point that "
"their very beings have become portals between this world and that of the "
"dead. If they're let loose, they'll cause just as much destruction as "
"Svarballi."
msgstr ""
"Ustedes deben combatir a esos tres dragones; después de tanto tiempo "
"encadenados tanto en la Tierra de los Muertos como en la Tierra de los "
"Sueños, han cambiado hasta el punto de que sus propios seres se han "
"convertido en portales entre este mundo y el de los muertos. Si se les deja "
"sueltos, causarán tanta destrucción como Svarballi."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1969
msgid ""
"Tenma, I don't want to discourage you, but how will you manage fight him "
"alone, when you've done that once and lost?"
msgstr ""
"Tenma, no quiero desanimarte, pero ¿cómo vas a lograr enfrentarlo sola, "
"cuando ya lo hiciste una vez y perdiste?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1973
msgid ""
"That time, there was yet something left for me to learn; a lesson Galdra had "
"already tried to teach me, but which only now I understand. Now, I'm as "
"ready to fight Svarballi as I'll ever be."
msgstr ""
"En aquel entonces aún me quedaba algo por aprender; una lección que Galdra "
"ya había intentado enseñarme, pero que solo ahora entiendo. Ahora estoy tan "
"preparada para enfrentar a Svarballi como alguna vez lo estaré."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1977
msgid "Still, to let you fight him alone..."
msgstr "Aun así, dejarte luchar sola contra él…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1981
msgid ""
"I won't be alone, friends; you will be with me, as I will be with you. Not "
"physically, but in a much more lasting manner: you'll all be in my heart and "
"in my memory, and there you will stay until beyond the Unmaking of this "
"world."
msgstr ""
"No estaré sola, amigos; ustedes estarán conmigo, como yo estaré con ustedes. "
"No físicamente, sino de una forma mucho más duradera: todos estarán en mi "
"corazón y en mi memoria, y ahí permanecerán hasta más allá de la Deshacedora "
"de este mundo."

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1985
msgid ""
"If you are done saying your last farewell, Myra, follow me. Niddhon, "
"Shakkha, Agadhor, I permit you to deal with these so-called <i>Kings and "
"Queens</i>."
msgstr ""
"Si ya terminaste de decir tus últimas despedidas, Myra, sígueme. Niddhon, "
"Shakkha, Agadhor, les permito encargarse de estos supuestos <i>Reyes y "
"Reinas</i>."

#. [message], speaker=Shakkha
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1989
msgid "As you command, my lord."
msgstr "Como ordene, mi señor."

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1993
msgid ""
"Tenma did not look at Svarballi; her eyes were fixed at each of those people "
"turned to her, people who cared about her and whom she cared about: Natsu, "
"Kenshiro, Olokun, Cornelya, Valerya, Algil, Ankhmare, Dragana, Donar, "
"Veshtar Joohn... But after a while, she turned her back to them; with a "
"brusque move, she invoked her wings and ascended into the heavens."
msgstr ""
"Tenma no miró a Svarballi; sus ojos estaban fijos en cada una de aquellas "
"personas que se volvieron hacia ella, personas que se preocupaban por ella y "
"a quienes ella quería: Natsu, Kenshiro, Olokun, Cornelya, Valerya, Algil, "
"Ankhmare, Dragana, Donar, Veshtar Joohn… Pero después de un rato, les dio la "
"espalda; con un movimiento brusco invocó sus alas y ascendió hacia los "
"cielos."

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/48_The_Sun_Sets_Over_Wesnoth.cfg:1997
msgid "Let's end this once and for all, Sky Dragon..."
msgstr "Terminemos esto de una vez por todas, Dragón del Cielo…"

#. [scenario], id=49_The_Children_Of_Demere
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:5
msgid "The Children of Demere"
msgstr "Los Hijos de Demere"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:28
msgid "Destroy the Dragons of Death"
msgstr "Destruye a los Dragones de la Muerte"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:56
msgid ""
"NOTE: Only the heroes and heroines mentioned in the Objectives must be kept "
"alive.\n"
"\n"
"Also, in this scenario, you have the choice to control the Kings and the "
"Queens, and/or their armies, by right-clicking anywhere on the screen. When "
"controlling the armies, you will play as their sides in addition to your "
"original side."
msgstr ""
"NOTA: Solo deben mantenerse con vida los héroes y heroínas mencionados en "
"los Objetivos.\n"
"\n"
"Además, en este escenario puedes elegir controlar a los Reyes y Reinas, y/o "
"a sus ejércitos, haciendo clic derecho en cualquier parte de la pantalla. Al "
"controlar los ejércitos, jugarás también como sus bandos además de tu bando "
"original."

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:72
msgid "Human Legion"
msgstr "Legión Humana"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:82
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:198
msgid "Fallen Dragon Army"
msgstr "Ejército de Dragones Caídos"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:103
msgid "Sylvan Host"
msgstr "Hueste Silvana"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:119
msgid "Children of Morogor"
msgstr "Hijos de Morogor"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:135
msgid "Offspring of the Earth"
msgstr "Hijos de la Tierra"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:151
msgid "Offspring of the Abyss"
msgstr "Hijos del Abismo"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:167
msgid "Folk of the Oceans"
msgstr "Pueblo de los Océanos"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:183
msgid "The Great Horde"
msgstr "La Gran Horda"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:594
msgid ""
"Dragons, stand where you are and face us! Or have you become afraid of "
"'inferior beings' after your defeat to Maat?"
msgstr ""
"¡Dragones, quédense donde están y enfréntennos! ¿O se han vuelto temerosos "
"de los «seres inferiores» después de su derrota ante Maat?"

#. [message], speaker=Agadhor
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:598
msgid ""
"Fleeing? Afraid? Pitiful worm, we had no reason to fear you when we were "
"mere Fire Dragons; now that we have become even greater than we were, you "
"have no hope of surviving!"
msgstr ""
"¿Huyendo? ¿Con miedo? Patético gusano, no teníamos razón para temerte cuando "
"éramos simples Dragones de Fuego; ahora que nos hemos vuelto aún más grandes "
"de lo que éramos, ¡no tienes ninguna esperanza de sobrevivir!"

#. [message], speaker=Niddhon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:602
msgid ""
"Now, fallen warriors from the Dragon Age, this is our chance to achieve what "
"we could not in the past! Let the world burn in your fire once more!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ahora, guerreros caídos de la Era de los Dragones, esta es nuestra "
"oportunidad de lograr lo que no pudimos en el pasado! ¡Que el mundo arda de "
"nuevo en su fuego!"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:606
msgid ""
"It shames me that my people were once pledged their loyalty to the likes of "
"you. Drakes and saurians, we are guilty for all this horror that haunts us "
"from the olden days, so we must fight more fiercely than everyone else!"
msgstr ""
"Me avergüenza que mi pueblo alguna vez jurara lealtad a seres como ustedes. "
"Dracos y saurios, somos culpables de todo este horror que nos persigue desde "
"los viejos tiempos, ¡así que debemos luchar con más ferocidad que todos los "
"demás!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:610
msgid ""
"No, Queen-in-the-Air, we must all fight with equal fierceness, for we are "
"all children of Mother Demere, and this world is ours to defend! Now, to "
"battle!"
msgstr ""
"No, Reina-en-el-Aire, todos debemos luchar con la misma ferocidad, ¡porque "
"todos somos hijos de la Madre Demere y este mundo es nuestro para "
"defenderlo! ¡Ahora, a la batalla!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:623
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:706
msgid "Mother, I can't join you again yet...!"
msgstr "¡Madre, aún no puedo reunirme contigo…!"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:642
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:725
msgid "C-Cornelya...!"
msgstr "¡C-Cornelya…!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:646
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:729
msgid "KENSHIRO!!!"
msgstr "¡KENSHIRO!"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:661
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:758
msgid "I can't... die... Olokun, I'm-"
msgstr "No puedo… morir… Olokun, yo—"

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:694
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:791
msgid "Aahhh!!! My... son..."
msgstr "¡Aahhh! Mi… hijo…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:698
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:795
msgid "Mother, no!!!"
msgstr "¡Madre, no!"

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:717
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:814
msgid "AELDHORYAN!!!"
msgstr "¡AELDHORYAN!"

#. [message], speaker=Bogor
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:746
msgid "How could I fall to these puny maggots...?!"
msgstr "¿Cómo pude caer ante estos míseros gusanos…?"

#. [message], speaker=Dragana
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:761
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:934
msgid "Argh...! To fall... in the greatest of battles...!"
msgstr "¡Argh…! ¡Caer… en la mayor de las batallas…!"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:765
msgid "No! We needed Dragana Vasilya to rebuild our nations!"
msgstr ""
"¡No! ¡Necesitábamos a Dragana Vasilya para reconstruir nuestras naciones!"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:782
msgid "DONAR!!!"
msgstr "¡DONAR!"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:786
msgid "Argh! Damn, how pathetic of me to die before you..."
msgstr "¡Argh! Maldición, qué patético morir antes que tú…"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:790
msgid "My brother...! How... how could I let my little brother die?!"
msgstr "¡Mi hermano…! ¿Cómo… cómo pude dejar que mi hermanito muriera?"

#. [message], speaker=Donar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:794
msgid ""
"Gonna cry now, King-in-the-Earth...? Don't do that, not for me, for I fall "
"covered in glory; when I arrive at the Halls of Heroes, I'll be amongst the "
"few who can boast having died in the greatest battle of the ages, and by the "
"side of the King-in-the-Earth who redeemed dwarf-kind..."
msgstr ""
"¿Vas a llorar ahora, Rey-en-la-Tierra…? No lo hagas, no por mí, porque caigo "
"cubierto de gloria; cuando llegue a los Salones de los Héroes, estaré entre "
"los pocos que pueden jactarse de haber muerto en la mayor batalla de las "
"edades, y al lado del Rey-en-la-Tierra que redimió al pueblo enano…"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:798
msgid ""
"Then make sure to make even Hamel the Brave raise a horn in your honour! As "
"for us who stay behind, we will make sure that the last thing our foes hear "
"is your name!"
msgstr ""
"¡Entonces asegúrate de que incluso Hamel el Valiente levante un cuerno en tu "
"honor! En cuanto a nosotros que nos quedamos atrás, nos encargaremos de que "
"lo último que escuchen nuestros enemigos sea tu nombre!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:809
msgid "Brother, no!!!"
msgstr "¡Hermano, no!"

#. [message], speaker=Gelendras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:813
msgid ""
"(panting) I go to father's side... But I go in peace, for I know... That I "
"leave our people... in good hands..."
msgstr ""
"(jadeando) Voy al lado de padre… Pero voy en paz, porque sé… que dejo a "
"nuestra gente… en buenas manos…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:817
msgid ""
"You were one of the most important people in my life, Gelendras... You "
"accepted me with open arms, sharing father's love with a girl who didn't "
"even share your blood... Rest with the First, my brother..."
msgstr ""
"Fuiste una de las personas más importantes en mi vida, Gelendras… Me "
"aceptaste con los brazos abiertos, compartiendo el amor de padre con una "
"chica que ni siquiera compartía tu sangre… Descansa con los Primeros, mi "
"hermano…"

#. [message], speaker=Umbrius
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:828
msgid "My love...!"
msgstr "¡Amor mío…!"

#. [message], speaker=Idunn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:832
msgid "Alas, we will never see our beloved valley again, husband..."
msgstr "Ay, nunca volveremos a ver nuestro querido valle, esposo…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:836
msgid ""
"Idunn, you were the closest I had to a mother after my blood mother died; "
"you helped me heal my worst wounds, and so you helped me come to peace with "
"myself. Rest with the First, for I promise I will not let your sacrifice be "
"in vain."
msgstr ""
"Idunn, fuiste lo más cercano que tuve a una madre después de que mi madre de "
"sangre muriera; me ayudaste a sanar mis peores heridas y así me ayudaste a "
"encontrar paz conmigo misma. Descansa con los Primeros, porque prometo que "
"no dejaré que tu sacrificio sea en vano."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:847
msgid "Master, no!!!"
msgstr "¡Maestro, no!"

#. [message], speaker=Ankhmare
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:851
msgid ""
"(smiling) Alas, my time on this world is over... But I have no regrets; I "
"fall in the battle our people have been preparing for since our very first "
"sunrise. Also, I go with the knowledge that I helped raise he who became the "
"King-Under-the-Sun..."
msgstr ""
"(sonriendo) Ay, mi tiempo en este mundo ha terminado… Pero no tengo "
"remordimientos; caigo en la batalla para la que nuestro pueblo se ha "
"preparado desde nuestro primer amanecer. Además, me voy sabiendo que ayudé a "
"criar a quien se convirtió en el Rey-Bajo-el-Sol…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:855
msgid ""
"And I am proud to have been your disciple, master... Now, rest in peace; I "
"will make sure that New Maat'Kare still stands for generations to count."
msgstr ""
"Y estoy orgulloso de haber sido tu discípulo, maestro… Ahora, descansa en "
"paz; me aseguraré de que Nueva Maat'Kare siga en pie por generaciones."

#. [message], speaker=Tallin
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:866
msgid ""
"Thus dies the last Lord Protector of the Northern Alliance... Fight on, my "
"friends..."
msgstr ""
"Así muere el último Señor Protector de la Alianza del Norte… Sigan luchando, "
"amigos míos…"

#. [message], speaker=Udhark
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:870
msgid ""
"I am deeply sorry that you could not enter the new era with us, my friend; "
"but rest assured that, even if the Northern Alliance ends, its values shall "
"live on through us!"
msgstr ""
"Lamento profundamente que no puedas entrar en la nueva era con nosotros, mi "
"amigo; pero ten por seguro que, aunque la Alianza del Norte termine, ¡sus "
"valores vivirán a través de nosotros!"

#. [message], speaker=Ikki
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:881
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/heroes-last-breath.cfg:968
msgid "Agh! Natsu, please tell my daughter... I died with honour..."
msgstr "¡Agh! Natsu, por favor dile a mi hija… que morí con honor…"

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:885
msgid ""
"I wish we could've returned to Kodakuni and see the cherry trees as free "
"people, but unfortunately, all I can do is promise I'll make sure your name "
"is made immortal by the scrolls of Umashima. Rest in peace, noble Ikki."
msgstr ""
"Ojalá hubiéramos podido regresar a Kodakuni y ver los cerezos como personas "
"libres, pero lamentablemente, lo único que puedo hacer es prometer que me "
"aseguraré de que tu nombre sea inmortalizado en los pergaminos de Umashima. "
"Descansa en paz, noble Ikki."

#. [message], speaker=Idunn
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:896
msgid "Umbrius...!"
msgstr "¡Umbrius…!"

#. [message], speaker=Umbrius
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:900
msgid ""
"Ugh...! Apologies, my beloved... apologies, my queen... I can fight no "
"longer...!"
msgstr ""
"¡Ugh…! Perdóname, mi amada… perdóname, mi reina… ¡ya no puedo seguir "
"luchando…!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:904
msgid ""
"It is I who must apologise for not being able to return you to your valley, "
"Umbrius. Without you, I might never have fulfilled my destiny... Rest "
"assured that your sacrifice will not be in vain – this I swear."
msgstr ""
"Soy yo quien debe disculparse por no haber podido devolverte a tu valle, "
"Umbrius. Sin ti, tal vez nunca habría cumplido mi destino… Ten por seguro "
"que tu sacrificio no será en vano, esto lo juro."

#. [message], speaker=Yiwen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:921
msgid ""
"Argh...! So this is how the last of the Windsong dies... (smirking) in the "
"greatest of battles... I hope I've made you all proud, my sisters across the "
"ages..."
msgstr ""
"¡Argh…! Así muere la última de las Hijas del Viento… (sonriendo) en la mayor "
"de las batallas… Espero haberlas hecho sentir orgullosas a todas, mis "
"hermanas a través de las edades…"

#. [message], speaker=Shwarzel
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:932
msgid ""
"To think that I'd fall so easily... But I regret nothing... Queen-in-the-"
"Woods, please, do not forget your cousins from the underground..."
msgstr ""
"Pensar que caería tan fácilmente… Pero no me arrepiento de nada… Reina-en-el-"
"Bosque, por favor, no olvides a tus primas del subsuelo…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:936
msgid ""
"Worry not, fair Svaryarna; our tribes have remained apart for far too long, "
"I will not allow them to remain like this."
msgstr ""
"No te preocupes, bella Svaryarna; nuestras tribus han estado separadas "
"demasiado tiempo, no permitiré que sigan así."

#. [message], speaker=Augdras
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:947
msgid ""
"To think that I would die fighting gloriously by the King-in-the-Earth's "
"side... Thank you, Lord Algil, for giving me this honour..."
msgstr ""
"Pensar que moriría luchando gloriosamente al lado del Rey-en-la-Tierra… "
"Gracias, señor Algil, por darme este honor…"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:951
msgid ""
"Go to the Halls of Heroes with pride, good Augdras, for your death has won "
"our people their very lives."
msgstr ""
"Ve a los Salones de los Héroes con orgullo, buen Augdras, porque tu muerte "
"ha ganado a nuestro pueblo sus propias vidas."

#. [message], speaker=Thrur
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:962
msgid ""
"Alas, I die... But there is no shame or sadness in dying next to the long-"
"awaited King-in-the-Abyss..."
msgstr ""
"Ay, muero… Pero no hay vergüenza ni tristeza en morir junto al tan esperado "
"Rey-en-el-Abismo…"

#. [message], speaker=Udhark
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:966
msgid ""
"Return to the abyss in peace, brave Thrur, for you have died fighting for "
"all the future generations of trolls."
msgstr ""
"Regresa al abismo en paz, valiente Thrur, porque moriste luchando por todas "
"las generaciones futuras de trolls."

#. [message], speaker=Bogor
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1014
msgid ""
"What devilry is this?! I'm sure that dragon got hit hard enough to "
"disappear, and yet he's back at it again!?"
msgstr ""
"¡¿Qué clase de brujería es esta?! ¡Estoy seguro de que ese dragón recibió un "
"golpe lo suficientemente fuerte como para desaparecer, y sin embargo está de "
"vuelta otra vez!"

#. [message], speaker=Agadhor
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1018
msgid "Pitiful vermin, I told you that our new power was beyond you!"
msgstr ""
"¡Miserables alimañas, les dije que nuestro nuevo poder estaba más allá de "
"ustedes!"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1022
msgid ""
"I know what they're doing: whenever one of them is about to be destroyed, "
"the other two recover him with an influx of soul energy..."
msgstr ""
"Sé lo que están haciendo: cada vez que uno de ellos está a punto de ser "
"destruido, los otros dos lo recuperan con una afluencia de energía de almas…"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1026
msgid "So we have to kill them at once?"
msgstr "¿Entonces tenemos que matarlos al mismo tiempo?"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1030
msgid ""
"It won't be easy, though; we'd have to do that at exactly the same time, and "
"they're too far from each other for us to do that with a single attack..."
msgstr ""
"No será fácil, sin embargo; tendríamos que hacerlo exactamente al mismo "
"tiempo, y están demasiado lejos unos de otros para lograrlo con un solo "
"ataque…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1034
msgid ""
"So, in the end, there <i>is</i> something that the mighty Kings and Queens "
"of Irdya need of a mere mortal like myself?"
msgstr ""
"Entonces, al final, <i>sí</i> hay algo que los poderosos Reyes y Reinas de "
"Irdya necesitan de una simple mortal como yo?"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1042
msgid ""
"I think I've told some of you once that I own a Staff of Righteous Flame..."
msgstr ""
"Creo que les conté a algunos de ustedes alguna vez que poseo un Bastón de "
"Llama Justa…"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1046
msgid "(astonished) Did you say Righteous Flame? Does such art still exist?!"
msgstr "(asombrado) ¿Dijiste Llama Justa? ¿¡Aún existe ese arte?!"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1050
msgid ""
"I know this staff causes a massive explosion if its owner is killed, but "
"what exactly it is?"
msgstr ""
"Sé que este bastón causa una explosión masiva si su dueño muere, pero ¿qué "
"es exactamente?"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1054
msgid ""
"The Righteous Flame is an ancient lost technique of the dragons. When one "
"who had mastered it perished, he could release all of his inner fire at "
"once, in pure form. Legends say that it was a fire so intense that even "
"dragons could be killed by it. I had heard that saurian mages in olden times "
"had concentrated that fire into staffs, but I had no idea that such "
"dangerous artefacts still existed..."
msgstr ""
"La Llama Justa es una antigua técnica perdida de los dragones. Cuando "
"alguien que la había dominado perecía, podía liberar todo su fuego interior "
"de una vez, en forma pura. Las leyendas dicen que era un fuego tan intenso "
"que incluso los dragones podían morir por él. Había oído que los magos "
"saurios en tiempos antiguos concentraron ese fuego en bastones, pero no "
"tenía idea de que tales artefactos peligrosos aún existieran…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1058
msgid ""
"This might be the last of the kind, though. We're lucky to have this one; I "
"found it by accident during one of my escapades from the Alduin Academy; "
"I've always known skipping that class was a wise decision..."
msgstr ""
"Este podría ser el último de su clase. Tenemos suerte de tener este; lo "
"encontré por accidente durante una de mis escapadas de la Academia de "
"Alduin; siempre supe que saltarme esa clase era una decisión sabia…"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1062
msgid "But, if this staff only works when it's owner is killed..."
msgstr "Pero, si este bastón solo funciona cuando su dueño muere…"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1066
msgid "Eh, well, that's the downside of it..."
msgstr "Eh, bueno, ese es el inconveniente…"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1070
msgid "No! Don't you even try it, Valerya, I won't let you do it!"
msgstr "¡No! ¡Ni siquiera lo intentes, Valerya, no te dejaré hacerlo!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1074
msgid ""
"Hush, I'm no folk of the forest and you're not my queen! Listen, friends, I "
"may have mentioned this once or twice, but I'm very, very old. My time has "
"long passed; I have seen so many friends of mine die, my mother, my aunts, "
"my husband, my cousins... I don't know for how long the Fountain of Life "
"will keep me going, but I know it'll be long enough to watch you, the first "
"true friends I've had in centuries, die as well, and I've definitely had my "
"share of losing loved ones..."
msgstr ""
"Silencio, ¡no soy del pueblo del bosque y tú no eres mi reina! Escuchen, "
"amigos, puede que lo haya mencionado una o dos veces, pero soy muy, muy "
"vieja. Mi tiempo pasó hace mucho; he visto morir a tantos amigos míos, a mi "
"madre, a mis tías, a mi esposo, a mis primos… No sé cuánto tiempo más me "
"mantendrá la Fuente de la Vida, pero sé que será suficiente para verlos "
"morir a ustedes también, los primeros amigos verdaderos que he tenido en "
"siglos, y definitivamente ya he tenido suficiente de perder a seres queridos…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1078
msgid "Valerya...!"
msgstr "¡Valerya…!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1082
msgid ""
"And if I'm to die... well, I can think of no worthier way to die than this, "
"helping you save our world. "
msgstr ""
"Y si voy a morir… bueno, no se me ocurre una forma más digna de morir que "
"esta, ayudándolos a salvar nuestro mundo."

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1086
msgid ""
"If this is your decision, Crimson Sorceress, then we, the Kings and the "
"Queens of Irdya, shall open the way for you."
msgstr ""
"Si esta es tu decisión, Hechicera Carmesí, entonces nosotros, los Reyes y "
"las Reinas de Irdya, abriremos el camino para ti."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1090
msgid ""
"(suddenly energetic) Then, to business! All I need you to do is to carve a "
"path to the dragon in the middle; only from there will the Staff's range "
"engulf the other two dragons. Also, make sure they are all weakened "
"beforehand, otherwise even the Staff's explosion won't be enough to destroy "
"them."
msgstr ""
"(de repente enérgica) ¡Entonces, manos a la obra! Lo único que necesito es "
"que abran un camino hasta el dragón del medio; solo desde allí el alcance "
"del bastón abarcará a los otros dos dragones. Además, asegúrense de "
"debilitarlos antes, de lo contrario ni siquiera la explosión del bastón será "
"suficiente para destruirlos."

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1096
msgid ""
"Valerya must die next to Agadhor, and all the three dragons must have their "
"HP lower than 100, for the Righteous Flame to destroy them"
msgstr ""
"Valerya debe morir junto a Agadhor, y los tres dragones deben tener sus PV "
"por debajo de 100 para que la Llama Justa los destruya"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1120
msgid ""
"NOTE: Only the heroes and heroines mentioned in the Objectives must be kept "
"alive.\n"
"\n"
"Also, in this scenario, you have the choice to control the Kings and the "
"Queens, and also their armies, by right-clicking anywhere on the screen."
msgstr ""
"NOTA: Solo deben mantenerse con vida los héroes y heroínas mencionados en "
"los Objetivos.\n"
"\n"
"Además, en este escenario puedes elegir controlar a los Reyes y Reinas, y "
"también a sus ejércitos, haciendo clic derecho en cualquier parte de la "
"pantalla."

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1148
msgid ""
"(in pain) That's right, dragon... You have beaten me; here is your reward...!"
msgstr "(de dolor) Eso es, dragón… Me has vencido; ¡aquí está tu recompensa…!"

#. [message], speaker=Agadhor
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1169
msgid "What... This brilliance...!"
msgstr "¿Qué… esta brillantez…!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1173
msgid ""
"It's just as Agnash used to say... In order to kill a dragon, you must learn "
"to fight like one...!"
msgstr ""
"Tal como solía decir Agnash… Para matar a un dragón, debes aprender a luchar "
"como uno…"

#. [message], speaker=Niddhon
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1177
msgid "Human... How... <i>dare you</i>!"
msgstr "¡Humana… cómo… <i>te atreves</i>!"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1181
msgid ""
"From a safe distance, the fighters, bloodied and exhausted, watched as "
"Valerya and the three ancient dragons were engulfed in light brighter than "
"the suns; and then, the light became fire, and the fire shook the very earth "
"as it erupted..."
msgstr ""
"Desde una distancia segura, los combatientes, ensangrentados y exhaustos, "
"observaron cómo Valerya y los tres dragones antiguos eran envueltos en una "
"luz más brillante que los soles; y luego, la luz se convirtió en fuego, y el "
"fuego sacudió la misma tierra al estallar…"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1228
msgid ""
"As the flames subsided, a northern gale dispersed the smoke, revealing the "
"crater where Valerya, the Crimson Sorceress, had made her last stand."
msgstr ""
"Cuando las llamas disminuyeron, un vendaval del norte dispersó el humo, "
"revelando el cráter donde Valerya, la Hechicera Carmesí, había hecho su "
"última resistencia."

#. [message]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1255
msgid ""
"Pathetic! You gave up your life trying to destroy us, and yet here we stand!"
msgstr ""
"¡Patético! Entregaste tu vida intentando destruirnos, ¡y sin embargo aquí "
"seguimos en pie!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1259
msgid "No! How could we let her die in vain?!"
msgstr "¡No! ¿Cómo pudimos dejar que muriera en vano?"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1275
msgid ""
"The Dragons of Death are no more, and so their foul hordes are reduced to "
"ash!"
msgstr ""
"¡Los Dragones de la Muerte ya no existen, y por eso sus hordas inmundas se "
"han reducido a cenizas!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1279
msgid "Thank you, Valerya... Thank you for everything..."
msgstr "Gracias, Valerya… Gracias por todo…"

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1283
msgid "I am honoured to have fought by your side, my friend..."
msgstr "Me siento honrado de haber luchado a tu lado, mi amiga…"

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1287
msgid ""
"Like the High Ascendant Maat long ago, you gave your life to stop the Three "
"Dragons; and like Maat's, your name shall be forever engraved in the memory "
"of our people..."
msgstr ""
"Al igual que la Alta Ascendente Maat hace mucho tiempo, diste tu vida para "
"detener a los Tres Dragones; y como el de Maat, tu nombre quedará grabado "
"para siempre en la memoria de nuestro pueblo…"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1294
msgid "This noise... It came from where Tenma has gone!"
msgstr "Este ruido… ¡Vino de donde fue Tenma!"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1298
msgid "Then, that means...!"
msgstr "¡Entonces eso significa…!"

#. [message], speaker=Valerya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/49_The_Children_Of_Demere.cfg:1467
msgid "Not... yet...!"
msgstr "¡Aún… no…!"

#. [scenario], id=50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:5
msgid "The Dragon and the Slayer"
msgstr "El Dragón y la Cazadora"

#. [objective], condition=win
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:23
msgid "Destroy the High Dragon of the Sky once and for all"
msgstr "Destruye al Alto Dragón del Cielo de una vez por todas"

#. [objectives]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:31
msgid ""
"NOTE: Remember that only Akashia's Sword and the Dragon-Slayer spells can "
"kill Svarballi"
msgstr ""
"NOTA: Recuerda que solo la Espada de Akashia y los hechizos Cazadragones "
"pueden matar a Svarballi"

#. [side]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:47
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/51_End_Of_An_Era.cfg:24
msgid "Tenma Yozora"
msgstr "Tenma Yozora"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:204
msgid ""
"I... I do not... understand... It was my will that this world was to end... "
"How could it... not be fulfilled... I am the Warden... who inherited "
"Ananke's power..."
msgstr ""
"Yo… no… entiendo… Era mi voluntad que este mundo terminara… ¿Cómo pudo… no "
"cumplirse…? Yo soy el Guardián… quien heredó el poder de Ananke…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:208
msgid ""
"You may have some of her power, but you're not her Heir. Ananke's will was "
"that the world and the offspring of her sister Demere be protected; but you "
"could never succeed at that, Svarballi, because you never understood the "
"people you meant to protect. You looked on us from above, demanding us to "
"conform to your own vision of who we should be. We're capable of terrible "
"things, true, but we're just as capable of beauty, of kindness, of love... "
"You could've guided us to always strive for our best, but you refused to "
"accept us with our qualities <i>and</i> flaws... and, in the end, you became "
"a greater danger to Demere's creation than any of us ever have."
msgstr ""
"Puede que tengas parte de su poder, pero no eres su Heredera. La voluntad de "
"Ananke era que el mundo y la descendencia de su hermana Demere fueran "
"protegidos; pero nunca pudiste lograrlo, Svarballi, porque nunca entendiste "
"a la gente que pretendías proteger. Nos mirabas desde arriba, exigiendo que "
"nos ajustáramos a tu propia visión de quiénes deberíamos ser. Somos capaces "
"de cosas terribles, es cierto, pero también somos capaces de belleza, de "
"bondad, de amor… Pudiste habernos guiado a siempre buscar lo mejor de "
"nosotros, pero te negaste a aceptarnos con nuestras cualidades <i>y</i> "
"defectos… y, al final, te convertiste en un peligro mayor para la creación "
"de Demere que cualquiera de nosotros."

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:212
msgid "Have I... failed... the Mother...?"
msgstr "¿He… fallado… a la Madre…?"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:226
msgid ""
"We have stood together on many battlefields over the world and across the "
"aeons, Myra; Garet-Desh, Ughure, the Crystal Tower, the Heart Mountains, the "
"North Pole... But this is the last of all. Only one of us shall stand alive "
"on this plain when this is over!"
msgstr ""
"Hemos estado juntos en muchos campos de batalla a lo largo del mundo y a "
"través de los eones, Myra; Garet-Desh, Ughure, la Torre de Cristal, las "
"Montañas del Corazón, el Polo Norte… Pero esta es la última de todas. ¡Solo "
"uno de nosotros quedará vivo en esta llanura cuando esto termine!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:230
msgid "No, Svarballi..."
msgstr "No, Svarballi…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:272
msgid "<i>None</i> of us shall be standing on this plain when this is over."
msgstr ""
"<i>Ninguno</i> de nosotros quedará en pie en esta llanura cuando esto "
"termine."

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:276
msgid ""
"Will you enter this state of power so early? You know you cannot bear it for "
"long with your weak human body, do you not?"
msgstr ""
"¿Vas a entrar en este estado de poder tan pronto? Sabes que no puedes "
"soportarlo por mucho tiempo con tu débil cuerpo humano, ¿verdad?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:280
msgid ""
"That was when I was afraid of being consumed by this power if I wielded it "
"for too long; but I'm no longer afraid."
msgstr ""
"Eso era cuando temía ser consumida por este poder si lo usaba demasiado "
"tiempo; pero ya no tengo miedo."

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:284
msgid ""
"Sacrificing yourself in order to defeat me... Are you not tired of this old "
"strategy, Myra of Hiera'Shirsha?"
msgstr ""
"Sacrificarte para derrotarme… ¿No estás cansada de esta vieja estrategia, "
"Myra de Hiera'Shirsha?"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:288
msgid "Well, it has worked so far, hasn't it? And for the last time..."
msgstr "Bueno, ha funcionado hasta ahora, ¿no es así? Y por última vez…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:350
msgid "I am <i>Tenma Yozora of Kodakuni</i>!!!"
msgstr "¡Yo soy <i>Tenma Yozora de Kodakuni</i>!"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:374
msgid "Too weak!"
msgstr "¡Demasiado débil!"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:391
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:412
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:445
msgid "(shocked) How... How dare you wound me, the Warden of Irdya...!"
msgstr "(impactado) ¿Cómo… cómo te atreves a herirme, al Guardián de Irdya…!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:395
msgid ""
"Akashia, this is for you... (plunges the Deva Sword into Svarballi's chest"
msgstr ""
"Akashia, esto es por ti… (hunde la Espada Deva en el pecho de Svarballi"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:416
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:449
msgid ""
"You have abandoned this task long ago, Sky Dragon; now, it is up to a child "
"of Demere to protect this world from you..."
msgstr ""
"Abandonaste esta tarea hace mucho tiempo, Dragón del Cielo; ahora le "
"corresponde a una hija de Demere proteger este mundo de ti…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:420
msgid "'Far-reaching spearhead of Heaven, Earth and Sea, shine...'"
msgstr "«Lanza de alcance lejano del Cielo, la Tierra y el Mar, brilla…»"

#. [message], speaker=Svarballi
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:424
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:457
msgid "You... impudent... VERMIN...!"
msgstr "¡Tú… insolente… ALIMAÑA…!"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:428
msgid ""
"'Sacred Lance that pierces through dimensions, fly across the skies and slay "
"your every target! RYUSHINI NO YARI!!!'"
msgstr ""
"«¡Lanza Sagrada que atraviesa dimensiones, vuela por los cielos y mata a "
"todos tus objetivos! ¡RYUSHINI NO YARI!»"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:453
msgid "'Warden, who gave up your life for the sake of life, awake…'"
msgstr "«Guardián, que entregaste tu vida por el bien de la vida, despierta…»"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:461
msgid ""
"'Dragon God from the ancient days, rise! Roar once more, and split the skies "
"in your wake! RYUUJIN TENSHOU!!!'"
msgstr ""
"«¡Dios Dragón de los días antiguos, levántate! ¡Ruge una vez más y parte los "
"cielos a tu paso! ¡RYUUJIN TENSHOU!»"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:481
msgid "At long last... It is over..."
msgstr "Por fin… Todo ha terminado…"

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:485
msgid ""
"<i>You have done well, my child; we are all so proud of you... Now, you have "
"earned a rest; we await you back in this earth's bosom...</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Lo has hecho bien, hija mía; todos estamos muy orgullosos de ti… Ahora "
"has ganado un descanso; te esperamos de vuelta en el seno de esta tierra…</i>"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:498
msgid "(smiling) The wind... It feels so good..."
msgstr "(sonriendo) El viento… se siente tan bien…"

#. [message], speaker=Tenma
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/50_The_Dragon_And_The_Slayer.cfg:521
msgid "I have... failed...?!"
msgstr "¿He… fallado…?"

#. [scenario], id=51_End_Of_An_Era
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/51_End_Of_An_Era.cfg:5
msgid "End of an Era"
msgstr "Fin de una Era"

#. [message], speaker=Veshtar
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/51_End_Of_An_Era.cfg:112
msgid "You may come, friends; I sense no one around..."
msgstr "Pueden venir, amigos; no percibo a nadie cerca…"

#. [message], speaker=Algil
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/51_End_Of_An_Era.cfg:116
msgid "No one at all? Not even Tenma?"
msgstr "¿Nadie en absoluto? ¿Ni siquiera Tenma?"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/51_End_Of_An_Era.cfg:120
msgid ""
"Wait, I can feel her presence in that direction... Though it's very faint..."
msgstr ""
"Espera, puedo sentir su presencia en esa dirección… Aunque es muy tenue…"

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/51_End_Of_An_Era.cfg:127
msgid "Wait for me...!"
msgstr "¡Espérenme…!"

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/51_End_Of_An_Era.cfg:148
msgid " But... Where is she?"
msgstr "Pero… ¿dónde está ella?"

#. [message], speaker=Cornelya
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/51_End_Of_An_Era.cfg:152
msgid "(tears welling up her eyes) She is not here..."
msgstr "(con lágrimas en los ojos) No está aquí…"

#. [message], speaker=Udhark
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/51_End_Of_An_Era.cfg:156
msgid ""
"The presence you felt must have been an echo of her power, a remnant which "
"still lingers due to how intense it was."
msgstr ""
"La presencia que sentiste debe haber sido un eco de su poder, un remanente "
"que aún perdura por lo intenso que fue."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/51_End_Of_An_Era.cfg:160
msgid "Then, that means..."
msgstr "Entonces eso significa…"

#. [message], speaker=Natsu
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/51_End_Of_An_Era.cfg:164
msgid "(crying) No... Tenma, why... How could I have let you...!?"
msgstr "(llorando) No… Tenma, ¿por qué… cómo pude dejarte…?"

#. [message], speaker=Aeldhoryan
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/51_End_Of_An_Era.cfg:168
msgid ""
"(hugging Natsu) She is not dead, my love. Remember what she said: she will "
"remain in our hearts and in our memory, and so she cannot ever be truly dead."
msgstr ""
"(abrazando a Natsu) No está muerta, mi amor. Recuerda lo que dijo: "
"permanecerá en nuestros corazones y en nuestra memoria, y por eso nunca "
"podrá estar realmente muerta."

#. [message], speaker=Kenshiro
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/51_End_Of_An_Era.cfg:172
msgid "(fighting tears) You're right, father..."
msgstr "(luchando contra las lágrimas) Tienes razón, padre…"

#. [message], speaker=Derceto
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/51_End_Of_An_Era.cfg:176
msgid ""
"We must never forget her, nor Valerya, nor anyone else who died so that this "
"threat that haunted Irdya for so long could be brought to an end; and, most "
"importantly, we must strive to honour the gifts the Ancient Ones gave us, "
"and make this world one where peace rules over war, and where understanding "
"rules over hatred."
msgstr ""
"Nunca debemos olvidarla a ella, ni a Valerya, ni a nadie más que murió para "
"que esta amenaza que atormentó a Irdya durante tanto tiempo pudiera llegar a "
"su fin; y, lo más importante, debemos esforzarnos por honrar los dones que "
"los Antiguos nos dieron, y hacer de este mundo uno donde la paz reine sobre "
"la guerra, y donde la comprensión reine sobre el odio."

#. [message], speaker=Olokun
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/51_End_Of_An_Era.cfg:180
msgid ""
"(crying) Thank you, Tenma... Thank you for protecting this world and "
"ourselves... And more than anything, thank you for having been our friend..."
msgstr ""
"(llorando) Gracias, Tenma… Gracias por proteger este mundo y a nosotros… Y "
"más que nada, gracias por haber sido nuestra amiga…"

#. [scenario], id=Aria_Epilogue
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/Epilogue_AotDS.cfg:4
msgid "Epilogue"
msgstr "Epílogo"

#. [part]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/Epilogue_AotDS.cfg:11
msgid ""
"The outcome of the final duel between Tenma and Svarballi was received with "
"bittersweet celebration, especially by the Maat'Karians and the Sogen. None "
"was more devastated than Natsu and Kenshiro, but none was prouder of she who "
"had been their family in feeling if not in blood."
msgstr ""
"El resultado del duelo final entre Tenma y Svarballi fue recibido con una "
"celebración agridulce, especialmente por los maat'karianos y los sogen. "
"Nadie estuvo más devastado que Natsu y Kenshiro, pero nadie estuvo más "
"orgulloso de aquella que había sido su familia en sentimiento aunque no en "
"sangre."

#. [part]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/Epilogue_AotDS.cfg:15
msgid ""
"From Dan'Tonk, the allies sent many scouting parties all over the country to "
"gather survivors. But even though Galdra's swarms had disappeared with her "
"death, the harm to the empire was irreversible: after so many weeks "
"receiving no order from Weldyn, various noble factions gathered their own "
"loyalists and declared themselves independent from the Iron Crown."
msgstr ""
"Desde Dan'Tonk, los aliados enviaron muchas partidas de exploración por todo "
"el país para reunir sobrevivientes. Pero aunque los enjambres de Galdra "
"desaparecieron con su muerte, el daño al imperio fue irreversible: después "
"de tantas semanas sin recibir órdenes de Weldyn, varias facciones nobles "
"reunieron a sus propios leales y se declararon independientes de la Corona "
"de Hierro."

#. [part]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/Epilogue_AotDS.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Cornelya herself travelled to the great elven enclave in the Wesmere Forest. "
"However, she found no elf there: the great halls were all empty, and the "
"forests were eerily silent but for the ruffle of dry leaves. Finding not "
"even a hint of where the Wesmere elves had gone, and all too conscious of "
"how weary her Sylvan Host was, Cornelya withdrew for the time being."
msgstr ""
"La propia Cornelya viajó al gran enclave élfico en el Bosque de Wesmere. Sin "
"embargo, no encontró ningún elfo allí: las grandes salas estaban todas "
"vacías, y los bosques estaban inquietantemente silenciosos salvo por el roce "
"de las hojas secas. Al no encontrar ni siquiera una pista de adónde habían "
"ido los elfos de Wesmere, y muy consciente de lo agotada que estaba su "
"Hueste Silvana, Cornelya se retiró por el momento."

#. [part]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/Epilogue_AotDS.cfg:23
msgid ""
"In the following months, new threats rose. With the fall of the third sun, "
"seismic activity became more intense on the western half of the Great "
"Continent; the smoke of the volcanoes, along with the dust lifted by the "
"fallen sun's impact, created a thick layer of dust in the atmosphere that "
"blocked much of sunlight. In the following years, the planet's temperature "
"dropped, but the lack of sunlight harmed plant life as badly as the two "
"suns' heat did."
msgstr ""
"En los meses siguientes surgieron nuevas amenazas. Con la caída del tercer "
"sol, la actividad sísmica se intensificó en la mitad occidental del Gran "
"Continente; el humo de los volcanes, junto con el polvo levantado por el "
"impacto del sol caído, creó una gruesa capa de polvo en la atmósfera que "
"bloqueó gran parte de la luz solar. En los años siguientes, la temperatura "
"del planeta bajó, pero la falta de luz solar dañó la vida vegetal tan "
"gravemente como lo había hecho el calor de los dos soles."

#. [part]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/Epilogue_AotDS.cfg:27
msgid ""
"The Kings and Queens of Irdya did what they could to avert the damage. "
"Olokun travelled across both Arajunna and the Great Continent, helping crops "
"and forests bask in light with the Sacred Sky spell; Cornelya sent trained "
"druids to breathe new life into as many lands as they could; and Veshtar "
"Joohn, who had settled with her people near the ruins of Aghayu, lit many "
"perennial bonfires around the coldest regions. Derceto, by her turn, worked "
"tirelessly on the cleansing of the atmosphere."
msgstr ""
"Los Reyes y Reinas de Irdya hicieron lo que pudieron para evitar el daño. "
"Olokun viajó por Arajunna y el Gran Continente, ayudando a los cultivos y "
"bosques a recibir luz con el hechizo Cielo Sagrado; Cornelya envió druidas "
"entrenados para infundir nueva vida en tantas tierras como pudieron; y "
"Veshtar Joohn, que se había establecido con su pueblo cerca de las ruinas de "
"Aghayu, encendió muchas hogueras perennes alrededor de las regiones más "
"frías. Derceto, por su parte, trabajó incansablemente en la limpieza de la "
"atmósfera."

#. [part]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/Epilogue_AotDS.cfg:31
msgid ""
"Alas, there was only so much that they could do. Because many forests had "
"died during the Cold Years, large areas were left bare; once the atmosphere "
"had been cleansed, those lands were unshielded against the two suns' "
"scorching light. As the years passed, new deserts were born, growing wider "
"every year."
msgstr ""
"Ay, solo pudieron hacer hasta cierto punto. Porque muchos bosques murieron "
"durante los Años Fríos, grandes áreas quedaron desnudas; una vez que la "
"atmósfera fue limpiada, esas tierras quedaron sin protección contra la luz "
"abrasadora de los dos soles. Con el paso de los años, nacieron nuevos "
"desiertos, que se expandían cada año más."

#. [part]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/Epilogue_AotDS.cfg:35
msgid ""
"As the environment deteriorated, so did the already fragile stability of the "
"surviving nations. Aeldhoryan's loyalists had made Dan'Tonk their new "
"capital, and for thirty years it stood as a beacon of what the empire had "
"been; but the passing of the Iron Dynasty's last member led to a succession "
"squabbling that left Dan'Tonk vulnerable. The great city eventually fell to "
"rival noble houses - but not before Natsu had led a considerable portion of "
"the peasantry, and even some soldiers and nobles, safely away. Those "
"remnants of Wesnoth travelled north-east, to the Emerald Plains, where they "
"joined Dragana's Baryags - who still reeled from all the losses to both "
"Vladnir Ohn and Wesir - in a new nation."
msgstr ""
"A medida que el ambiente se deterioraba, también lo hacía la ya frágil "
"estabilidad de las naciones sobrevivientes. Los leales a Aeldhoryan habían "
"convertido Dan'Tonk en su nueva capital, y durante treinta años se mantuvo "
"como un faro de lo que había sido el imperio; pero el fallecimiento del "
"último miembro de la Dinastía de Hierro llevó a disputas sucesorias que "
"dejaron a Dan'Tonk vulnerable. La gran ciudad finalmente cayó ante casas "
"nobles rivales, pero no antes de que Natsu hubiera conducido a una "
"considerable porción de la campesinería, e incluso a algunos soldados y "
"nobles, a un lugar seguro. Esos remanentes de Wesnoth viajaron al noreste, a "
"las Llanuras Esmeralda, donde se unieron a los Baryags de Dragana —que aún "
"se recuperaban de todas las pérdidas ante Vladnir Ohn y Wesir— en una nueva "
"nación."

#. [part]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/Epilogue_AotDS.cfg:39
msgid ""
"Arajunna, where the weather had always been harsh, became a desert "
"continent. Although Ifeh endured, most other cities of the Chomi and the "
"Washraha slowly fell into ruin, their people becoming scattered nomadic "
"bands. Some even dared sail into the Dragons' Maelstrom, but were never "
"heard of again. The Sogen remained in Kodakuni for many generations; once "
"their beautiful cherry trees had all died, however, they did as their "
"ancestors from the steppes once had and set out for a new home - that time "
"heading north."
msgstr ""
"Arajunna, donde el clima siempre había sido duro, se convirtió en un "
"continente desértico. Aunque Ifeh resistió, la mayoría de las otras ciudades "
"de los Chomi y los Washraha cayeron lentamente en ruinas, y su gente se "
"convirtió en bandas nómadas dispersas. Algunos incluso se atrevieron a "
"navegar hacia el Maelstrom de los Dragones, pero nunca más se supo de ellos. "
"Los Sogen permanecieron en Kodakuni por muchas generaciones; sin embargo, "
"una vez que todos sus hermosos cerezos murieron, hicieron lo que sus "
"ancestros de las estepas habían hecho alguna vez y partieron en busca de un "
"nuevo hogar, esta vez hacia el norte."

#. [part]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/Epilogue_AotDS.cfg:43
msgid ""
"Having forsaken his birthright as imperial prince, Kenshiro stayed with "
"Cornelya in Metheldur. They had three children, one of whom preferred the "
"company of the humans and even wedded Dragana Vasilya's daughter, "
"strengthening the bonds between their people through those difficult years. "
"Though much of the forest died in the next centuries, Cornelya's power "
"ensured that the heart of the Lins-Elens endured, standing as a haven for "
"the Folk of the Forest."
msgstr ""
"Al renunciar a su derecho de nacimiento como príncipe imperial, Kenshiro se "
"quedó con Cornelya en Metheldur. Tuvieron tres hijos, uno de los cuales "
"prefirió la compañía de los humanos e incluso se casó con la hija de Dragana "
"Vasilya, fortaleciendo los lazos entre sus pueblos durante esos años "
"difíciles. Aunque gran parte del bosque murió en los siglos siguientes, el "
"poder de Cornelya aseguró que el corazón de los Lins-Elens perdurara, "
"permaneciendo como un refugio para el Pueblo del Bosque."

#. [part]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/Epilogue_AotDS.cfg:47
msgid ""
"Algil and Udhark relocated those dwarves and trolls willing to follow them "
"to the Hammermounts, for not even the Regalia could avert Knalga's "
"crumbling. In the great eastern range, they built new cities in the "
"underground - cities where dwarves, trolls and black elves dwelled freely. "
"In them, the spirit of the fallen Northern Alliance lived on."
msgstr ""
"Algil y Udhark reubicaron a los enanos y trolls dispuestos a seguirlos hacia "
"los Hammermounts, pues ni siquiera las Regalias pudieron evitar el derrumbe "
"de Knalga. En la gran cordillera oriental construyeron nuevas ciudades "
"subterráneas —ciudades donde enanos, trolls y elfos negros vivían "
"libremente. En ellas, el espíritu de la caída Alianza del Norte perduró."

#. [part]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/Epilogue_AotDS.cfg:51
msgid ""
"Bogor returned to Netjer-Ta, followed by the hosts he had gathered in the "
"Great Continent. He ruled his people with a firm, but just fist for many "
"decades. He also established a new tradition: the Garland Wars, controlled "
"skirmishes between the various orc clans that sated their lust for battle "
"while sparing their non-orc neighbours from becoming targets, thus ensuring "
"relative peace in the continent."
msgstr ""
"Bogor regresó a Netjer-Ta, seguido por las huestes que había reunido en el "
"Gran Continente. Gobernó a su pueblo con mano firme pero justa durante "
"muchas décadas. También estableció una nueva tradición: las Guerras de "
"Guirnaldas, escaramuzas controladas entre los diversos clanes orcos que "
"saciaban su sed de batalla mientras evitaban que sus vecinos no-orcos se "
"convirtieran en blancos, asegurando así una paz relativa en el continente."

#. [part]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/Epilogue_AotDS.cfg:55
msgid ""
"The seas were not spared the suns' wrath, as the increased temperatures "
"killed much of the oceans' plant life, breaking the fragile balance of their "
"ecosystems. Under Derceto's leadership, however, the merfolk and the naga "
"were possibly the least harmed of Irdya's races in those years. And though "
"she was ever busy watching over the people, the Queen-in-the-Oceans always "
"found time for her beloved. The difference in their races did prevent them "
"from having children, but it did not prevent their love from continuing "
"until their death – and possibly even beyond."
msgstr ""
"Los mares no se libraron de la ira de los soles, ya que las temperaturas "
"aumentadas mataron gran parte de la vida vegetal de los océanos, rompiendo "
"el frágil equilibrio de sus ecosistemas. Bajo el liderazgo de Derceto, sin "
"embargo, los sirénidos y los naga fueron posiblemente las razas de Irdya "
"menos dañadas en esos años. Y aunque siempre estuvo ocupada cuidando de su "
"pueblo, la Reina-en-los-Océanos siempre encontraba tiempo para su amado. La "
"diferencia en sus razas les impidió tener hijos, pero no impidió que su amor "
"continuara hasta su muerte —y posiblemente incluso más allá."

#. [part]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/Epilogue_AotDS.cfg:65
msgid ""
"Yiwen, who had returned to the North Pole after the war's end, appeared in "
"New Maat'Kare some years after the Fall, bringing along the survivors of "
"Hiera'Kyria as well as refugees who had joined them on their pilgrimage. "
"Granted asylum at the Haven of Maat, they became professors and historians; "
"for, with the destruction of their last great library, the Order of the "
"Windsong could no longer be restored – though its memory and its spirit "
"lived on in the very continent that once had shunned them."
msgstr ""
"Yiwen, que había regresado al Polo Norte al terminar la guerra, apareció en "
"Nueva Maat'Kare algunos años después de la Caída, trayendo consigo a los "
"sobrevivientes de Hiera'Kyria así como a refugiados que se habían unido a "
"ellos en su peregrinación. Concedidos asilo en el Refugio de Maat, se "
"convirtieron en profesores e historiadores; pues, con la destrucción de su "
"última gran biblioteca, la Orden de las Hijas del Viento ya no pudo ser "
"restaurada —aunque su memoria y su espíritu perduraron en el mismo "
"continente que una vez las había rechazado."

#. [part]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/Epilogue_AotDS.cfg:71
msgid ""
"Although civilisation endured in such havens as the Lins-Elens, the Emerald "
"Plains, the Hammermounts and New Maat'Kare, everywhere else - from the Far "
"North to the Sandy Wastes and the Great Inner Sea of the Great Continent, "
"from the Deva Mountains to the Sapphire Bay in Arajunna - a reign of chaos "
"began. Many of the dynasties born from Wesnoth's fall migrated north as the "
"lands that had once been Irdya's mightiest human empire became a desert. "
"Inheriting the belligerent ways of the Iron Dinasty, those humans created a "
"new nation headed by the so-called Iron Triad, turning a land that once "
"prided itself in its freedom into a realm of tyranny."
msgstr ""
"Aunque la civilización perduró en refugios como los Lins-Elens, las Llanuras "
"Esmeralda, los Hammermounts y Nueva Maat'Kare, en todos los demás lugares —"
"desde el Lejano Norte hasta los Yermos Arenoso y el Gran Mar Interior del "
"Gran Continente, desde las Montañas Deva hasta la Bahía Zafiro en Arajunna— "
"comenzó un reinado de caos. Muchas de las dinastías nacidas de la caída de "
"Wesnoth migraron al norte mientras las tierras que alguna vez fueron el "
"imperio humano más poderoso de Irdya se convertían en desierto. Heredando "
"las costumbres beligerantes de la Dinastía de Hierro, esos humanos crearon "
"una nueva nación encabezada por la llamada Tríada de Hierro, convirtiendo "
"una tierra que alguna vez se enorgullecía de su libertad en un reino de "
"tiranía."

#. [part]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/Epilogue_AotDS.cfg:75
msgid ""
"Furthermore, with the heavy losses in the third sun's fall as well as the "
"disturbance in the magic currents, very few mages appeared in the following "
"years and centuries. That, along with the continued warfare and the "
"destruction of cities, led to the loss of the near entirety of the wisdom "
"gathered by the Wesnothians over the course of fourteen centuries. The "
"necromantic arts, by their turn, not only endured but also thrived in that "
"new world, as the dark arts remained mysteriously unaffected - and there was "
"never a shortage of demand for bodies to send to war, living or dead."
msgstr ""
"Además, con las graves pérdidas en la caída del tercer sol así como la "
"perturbación en las corrientes mágicas, muy pocos magos aparecieron en los "
"años y siglos siguientes. Eso, junto con la guerra continua y la destrucción "
"de ciudades, llevó a la pérdida de casi toda la sabiduría acumulada por los "
"wesnothianos a lo largo de catorce siglos. Las artes nigrománticas, por su "
"parte, no solo perduraron sino que prosperaron en ese nuevo mundo, ya que "
"las artes oscuras permanecieron misteriosamente intactas —y nunca faltó "
"demanda de cuerpos para enviar a la guerra, vivos o muertos."

#. [part]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/Epilogue_AotDS.cfg:79
msgid ""
"Valerya's Fire Sanctuary, built on the slopes of the Firecloud Peak, "
"survived longer than any other magic academy; in time, it too was abandoned, "
"as not even magic could maintain its lands inhabitable. But the last of the "
"mages to walk its halls ensured that the lore it had gathered would not be "
"lost: preserved within magic domes, and protected from the greedy by "
"powerful wards, their scrolls endure the ages, until the day comes when the "
"world is ready to learn their secrets once more."
msgstr ""
"El Santuario de Fuego de Valerya, construido en las laderas del Pico Nube de "
"Fuego, sobrevivió más tiempo que cualquier otra academia de magia; con el "
"tiempo también fue abandonado, ya que ni siquiera la magia podía mantener "
"sus tierras habitables. Pero los últimos magos que caminaron por sus salas "
"se aseguraron de que el conocimiento acumulado no se perdiera: preservado "
"dentro de cúpulas mágicas y protegido de los codiciosos por poderosos "
"resguardos, sus pergaminos perduran a través de las edades, hasta el día en "
"que el mundo esté listo para aprender sus secretos una vez más."

#. [part]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/Epilogue_AotDS.cfg:83
msgid ""
"Many years after the Fall, the elves of the Aethenwood emerged from the "
"secret caves inside the Mountains of Peril in the Far South, where they had "
"taken refuge during Galdra's Crisis. Back to the surface, however, all they "
"found was a vast desert stretching towards all directions. Going north, they "
"met the Wesmere elves and fought a terrible war against them. Those who "
"survived settled in the seas of sands, adapting to the new weather."
msgstr ""
"Muchos años después de la Caída, los elfos del Bosque de Edén emergieron de "
"las cuevas secretas dentro de las Montañas del Peligro en el Lejano Sur, "
"donde se habían refugiado durante la Crisis de Galdra. De vuelta a la "
"superficie, sin embargo, todo lo que encontraron fue un vasto desierto "
"extendiéndose en todas direcciones. Al ir hacia el norte, se encontraron con "
"los elfos de Wesmere y libraron una terrible guerra contra ellos. Los que "
"sobrevivieron se establecieron en mares de arena, adaptándose al nuevo clima."

#. [part]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/Epilogue_AotDS.cfg:87
msgid ""
"And many more centuries later, long after the Kings and Queens who had "
"defended Irdya from that great crisis were gone, those desert elves would be "
"forced out of their land, journeying northwards through the ruins of what "
"was once Knalga, even facing the Iron Triad. But this is another story, to "
"be told by another."
msgstr ""
"Y muchos siglos más tarde, mucho después de que los Reyes y Reinas que "
"habían defendido a Irdya de aquella gran crisis hubieran partido, esos elfos "
"del desierto serían obligados a abandonar su tierra, viajando hacia el norte "
"a través de las ruinas de lo que alguna vez fue Knalga, incluso enfrentando "
"a la Tríada de Hierro. Pero esa es otra historia, que deberá contar otro."

#. [part]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/Epilogue_AotDS.cfg:91
msgid ""
"As for the Regalia, their power faded as their last wielders passed on; for "
"the Avatar of Magic had made them to protect the world from the Sky Dragon, "
"and with him gone, so was their purpose fulfilled forever."
msgstr ""
"En cuanto a las Regalias, su poder se desvaneció a medida que sus últimos "
"portadores fallecían; pues el Avatar de la Magia las había creado para "
"proteger al mundo del Dragón del Cielo, y con él desaparecido, su propósito "
"se cumplió para siempre."

#. [part]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/Epilogue_AotDS.cfg:96
msgid ""
"And through the chaos and the destruction, the world slowly but surely heals "
"itself; for life is a stubborn force, which rises from the ashes of "
"destruction stronger than ever before. One day, the gold of the deserts "
"shall be replaced by the green of the forests and the meadows once more, and "
"this Age of Chaos shall be replaced by a new Golden Age for all the Children "
"of Demere."
msgstr ""
"Y a través del caos y la destrucción, el mundo se sana lentamente pero con "
"seguridad; porque la vida es una fuerza obstinada, que surge de las cenizas "
"de la destrucción más fuerte que nunca. Algún día, el oro de los desiertos "
"volverá a ser reemplazado por el verde de los bosques y los prados, y esta "
"Era de Caos será reemplazada por una nueva Edad de Oro para todos los Hijos "
"de Demere."

#. [part]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/Epilogue_AotDS.cfg:100
msgid ""
"Now, traveller, that I have sung to you the song of fire, the war of the "
"jewel and the aria of the Dragon-Slayer, you may be wondering how can "
"someone know so much of what has taken place on this world of ours..."
msgstr ""
"Ahora, viajero, que te he cantado la canción del fuego, la guerra de la joya "
"y el aria del Cazadragones, tal vez te preguntes cómo alguien puede saber "
"tanto de lo que ha sucedido en este nuestro mundo…"

#. [part]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/scenarios/Epilogue_AotDS.cfg:104
msgid "...Well, who better to tell a story than someone who lived it?"
msgstr ""
"…Bueno, ¿quién mejor para contar una historia que alguien que la vivió?"

#. [side]
