msgstr "Mago Ancestral"

#. [unit_type], id=An_Usrukhar, race=human, gender=male
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/An_Usrukhar.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Asleep in a death beyond death, An-Usrukhar, the First of all Mages, waits "
"for the day the world reaches its end - a day when he will be needed once "
"again. What he shall do is a mystery that will only be revealed in the right "
"time."
msgstr ""
"Dormido en una muerte más allá de la muerte, An-Usrukhar, el Primero de "
"todos los Magos, espera el día en que el mundo llegue a su fin —un día en "
"que volverá a ser necesario. Lo que hará es un misterio que solo se revelará "
"en el momento adecuado."

#. [unit_type], id=Ancient Heroine, race=windsong, gender=female
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/Ancient_Heroine.cfg:5
msgid "female^Ancient Heroine"
msgstr "Heroína Antigua"

#. [unit_type], id=Ancient Heroine, race=windsong, gender=female
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/Ancient_Heroine.cfg:40
msgid ""
"Reborn after a long slumber, this heroine has performed deeds of legend in "
"the ancient ages. Though her body has grown frail after such a long period "
"of inactivity, the heroic spirit she arouses in her allies, as well as the "
"dread she instils in her foes, make her an even greater presence on the "
"battlefield than in her old days of glory."
msgstr ""
"Renacida tras un largo letargo, esta heroína realizó hazañas legendarias en "
"las edades antiguas. Aunque su cuerpo se ha debilitado tras tanto tiempo de "
"inactividad, el espíritu heroico que despierta en sus aliados, así como el "
"temor que infunde en sus enemigos, la convierten en una presencia aún mayor "
"en el campo de batalla que en sus días de gloria."

#. [attack], type=blade, range=melee
