#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/Ancient_Heroine.cfg:61
msgid "Deva Sword"
msgstr "Espada Deva"

#. [attack], type=fire, range=ranged
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/Ancient_Heroine.cfg:74
msgid "sunburst"
msgstr "estallido solar"

#. [unit_type], id=Ansaxa, race=dwarf, gender=female
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/Ansaxa.cfg:5
msgid "Runic Arcanister"
msgstr "Arcanista Rúnica"

#. [unit_type], id=Ansaxa, race=dwarf, gender=female
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/Ansaxa.cfg:19
msgid ""
"There was a time when the life of a female dwarf was confined to a domestic "
"setting; because of their physical frailty, they found no place in the "
"warlike society in which they lived. Nevertheless, that changed in the time "
"of Sigdral of the Aigathol Clan: she studied ancient Windsong cipher magic "
"in order to carve runes even without a runesmith's hammer - which is too "
"heavy for any dwarf female to wield properly. Her method proved not only as "
"efficient as the runesmith's in regards to the carving of magic runes, but "
"it also made their use in battle much more dangerous for their enemies. "
"Having proven their worth, the Runic Arcanisters of the Aigathol Clan are "
"often entrusted with guarding and administering their greatest libraries; "
"the wisest amongst them have even become chieftains, leading their clan as "
"skilfully as any dwarvish lord."
msgstr ""
"Hubo un tiempo en que la vida de una enana se limitaba al ámbito doméstico; "
"debido a su fragilidad física, no encontraban lugar en la sociedad guerrera "
"en la que vivían. Sin embargo, eso cambió en la época de Sigdral del Clan "
"Aigathol: ella estudió la antigua magia cifrada de las Hijas del Viento para "
"tallar runas incluso sin el martillo de un tallarunas —que es demasiado "
"pesado para que cualquier enana lo maneje adecuadamente. Su método demostró "
"ser no solo tan eficiente como el de los tallarunas en cuanto al tallado de "
"runas mágicas, sino que también hizo su uso en batalla mucho más peligroso "
"para los enemigos. Habiendo probado su valía, las Arcanistas Rúnicas del "
"Clan Aigathol a menudo son encargadas de guardar y administrar sus mayores "
"bibliotecas; las más sabias entre ellas incluso se han convertido en jefas, "
"liderando su clan con tanta habilidad como cualquier señor enano."

