#. [unit_type], id=Legion Knight
#. [unit_type], id=Legion Cavalier
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/Dokkor.cfg:417
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/Dokkor.cfg:446
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/Dokkor.cfg:476
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/Dokkor.cfg:505
msgid ""
"The Dokkors are a special military unit of the Northern Alliance. They "
"distinguish themselves from others for basing their equipment and tactics on "
"their anti-Two-Suns philosophy - something which is made clear by their use "
"of black armour and their preference for nocturnal warfare. Clad in dwarven "
"armour and wielding dwarven weapons, they're more resilient than most human "
"soldiers.\n"
"\n"
"During skirmishes with elves, the Dokkors have noticed how their horses "
"managed to gallop through even the thickest of woods almost like the wind; "
"by capturing elvish horse trainers, Dokkor riders have learned their "
"secrets, and started training their horses to cross the difficult terrains "
"of the Northlands as easily as those of the elves. The only downside of this "
"greater mobility is their lesser armoured protection."
msgstr ""
"Los Dokkors son una unidad militar especial de la Alianza del Norte. Se "
"diferencian de los demás por basar su equipo y tácticas en su filosofía anti-"
"Dos Soles —algo que queda claro por su uso de armadura negra y su "
"preferencia por la guerra nocturna. Vestidos con armadura enana y empuñando "
"armas enanas, son más resistentes que la mayoría de los soldados humanos.\n"
"\n"
"Durante escaramuzas con elfos, los Dokkors notaron cómo sus caballos "
"lograban galopar incluso por los bosques más densos casi como el viento; al "
"capturar entrenadores de caballos élficos, los jinetes Dokkor aprendieron "
"sus secretos y comenzaron a entrenar a sus caballos para cruzar los terrenos "
"difíciles de las Tierras del Norte con la misma facilidad que los de los "
"elfos. El único inconveniente de esta mayor movilidad es su menor protección "
"blindada."

