"than is normally possible on the battlefield.\n"
"\n"
"A unit cared for by this healer may heal up to 9 HP per turn, or stop poison "
"from taking effect for that turn.\n"
"A poisoned unit cannot be cured of its poison by a healer, and must seek the "
"care of a village or a unit that can cure."
msgstr ""
"Esta unidad combina remedios herbales con magia para sanar unidades más "
"rápidamente de lo que normalmente es posible en el campo de batalla.\n"
"\n"
