#. [unit_type], id=Tenma_Dummy, race=sogen, gender=female
#. [unit_type], id=Yasai Peasant, race=sogen
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/Tenma.cfg:375
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/Tenma_Farmer.cfg:6
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/sogen/Yasai.cfg:5
msgid "Yasai Peasant"
msgstr "Campesino Yasai"

#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/Tenma.cfg:384
msgid ""
"Tenma Yozora was born in the small Sogen village of Kuroi; her parents, "
"Yusuke and Motoko, died during Wesnoth's invasion of Kodakuni, and she has "
"been raised by her fellow villagers ever since, though she was unoficially "
"adopted by Natsu, a former priestess who was Motoko's closest friend. Albeit "
"her usual demeanour is playful and childish, she has a spirit as strong and "
"courageous as that of any warrior, though her brashness is her greatest "
"flaw.\n"
"\n"
"After awakening powers which she never dreamed herself to wield, she will do "
"whatever she can to free her country and people from Wesnothian oppression."
msgstr ""
"Tenma Yozora nació en la pequeña aldea sogen de Kuroi; sus padres, Yusuke y "
"Motoko, murieron durante la invasión de Wesnoth a Kodakuni, y desde entonces "
"ha sido criada por sus compañeros aldeanos, aunque fue adoptada de manera no "
"oficial por Natsu, una antigua sacerdotisa que era la amiga más cercana de "
"Motoko. Aunque su comportamiento habitual es juguetón e infantil, tiene un "
"espíritu tan fuerte y valiente como el de cualquier guerrero, aunque su "
"impulsividad es su mayor defecto.\n"
"\n"
"Tras despertar poderes que nunca soñó poseer, hará todo lo que pueda para "
"liberar a su país y a su gente de la opresión wesnothiana."

#. [variation], id=Tenma_Yozora
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/Tenma.cfg:448
msgid "Yasai Farmer"
msgstr "Granjera Yasai"

#. [variation], id=Tenma2
#. [variation], id=Tenma3
#. [variation], id=Tenma4
#. [variation], id=Tenma5
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/Tenma.cfg:478
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/Tenma.cfg:489
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/Tenma.cfg:500
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/Tenma.cfg:511
msgid "Yasai Traveller"
msgstr "Viajera Yasai"

#. [variation], id=Tenma5
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/Tenma.cfg:512
msgid ""
"Tenma Yozora was born in the small Sogen village of Kuroi; her parents, "
"Yusuke and Motoko, died during Wesnoth's invasion of Kodakuni, and she has "
"been raised by her fellow villagers ever since, though she was unoficially "
"adopted by Natsu, a former priestess who was Motoko's closest friend. Albeit "
"her usual demeanour is playful and childish, she has a spirit as strong and "
"courageous as that of any warrior, though her brashness is her greatest "
"flaw.\n"
"\n"
"After awakening powers which she never dreamed herself to wield, she will do "
"whatever she can to free her country and people from Wesnothian oppression; "
"and those powers currently hold the promise of being a match for Alduin's "
"mages themselves."
msgstr ""
"Tenma Yozora nació en la pequeña aldea sogen de Kuroi; sus padres, Yusuke y "
"Motoko, murieron durante la invasión de Wesnoth a Kodakuni, y desde entonces "
"ha sido criada por sus compañeros aldeanos, aunque fue adoptada de manera no "
"oficial por Natsu, una antigua sacerdotisa que era la amiga más cercana de "
"Motoko. Aunque su comportamiento habitual es juguetón e infantil, tiene un "
"espíritu tan fuerte y valiente como el de cualquier guerrero, aunque su "
"impulsividad es su mayor defecto.\n"
"\n"
"Tras despertar poderes que nunca soñó poseer, hará todo lo que pueda para "
"liberar a su país y a su gente de la opresión wesnothiana; y esos poderes "
"actualmente prometen ser un rival digno incluso para los magos de Alduin."

#. [variation], id=Tenma6
#. [variation], id=Tenma7
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/Tenma.cfg:547
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/Tenma.cfg:562
msgid "Sogen Wanderer"
msgstr "Errante Sogen"

#. [variation], id=Tenma6
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/Tenma.cfg:548
msgid ""
"Tenma Yozora was born in the small Sogen village of Kuroi; her parents, "
"Yusuke and Motoko, died during Wesnoth's invasion of Kodakuni, and she has "
"been raised by her fellow villagers ever since, though she was unoficially "
"adopted by Natsu, a former priestess who was Motoko's closest friend. Albeit "
"her usual demeanour is playful and childish, she has a spirit as strong and "
"courageous as that of any warrior, though her brashness is her greatest "
"flaw.\n"
"\n"
"After awakening powers which she never dreamed herself to wield, she set out "
"of her village with the goal of honing her powers so that she could free her "
"country. However, her journey has shown her a world much more vast than in "
"her wildest of dreams, leading her to meet a diversity of people and "
"friends; while she remains concerned with Kodakuni, Tenma's world has grown "
"as vast as the world beyond her own country, and she is gradually finding "
"herself to care about it as much as her homeland."
msgstr ""
"Tenma Yozora nació en la pequeña aldea sogen de Kuroi; sus padres, Yusuke y "
"Motoko, murieron durante la invasión de Wesnoth a Kodakuni, y desde entonces "
"ha sido criada por sus compañeros aldeanos, aunque fue adoptada de manera no "
"oficial por Natsu, una antigua sacerdotisa que era la amiga más cercana de "
"Motoko. Aunque su comportamiento habitual es juguetón e infantil, tiene un "
"espíritu tan fuerte y valiente como el de cualquier guerrero, aunque su "
"impulsividad es su mayor defecto.\n"
"\n"
"Tras despertar poderes que nunca soñó poseer, partió de su aldea con el "
"objetivo de perfeccionar sus habilidades para poder liberar a su país. Sin "
"embargo, su viaje le ha mostrado un mundo mucho más vasto que en sus sueños "
"más locos, llevándola a conocer una diversidad de personas y amigos; aunque "
"sigue preocupada por Kodakuni, el mundo de Tenma ha crecido tan vasto como "
"el mundo más allá de su propio país, y poco a poco se encuentra "
"preocupándose por él tanto como por su tierra natal."

#. [variation], id=Tenma8
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/Tenma.cfg:574
msgid "Dragon Wanderer"
msgstr "Errante del Dragón"

#. [variation], id=Tenma8
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/Tenma.cfg:575
msgid ""
"Tenma Yozora was born in the small Sogen village of Kuroi; her parents, "
"Yusuke and Motoko, died during Wesnoth's invasion of Kodakuni, and she has "
"been raised by her fellow villagers ever since, though she was unoficially "
"adopted by Natsu, a former priestess who was Motoko's closest friend. Albeit "
"her usual demeanour is playful and childish, she has a spirit as strong and "
"courageous as that of any warrior, though her brashness is her greatest "
"flaw.\n"
"\n"
"After awakening powers which she never dreamed herself to wield, she set out "
"of her village with the goal of honing her powers so that she could free her "
"country. However, her journey has shown her a world much more vast than in "
"her wildest of dreams, leading her to meet a diversity of people and "
"friends; while she will always be concerned with Kodakuni, fighting for so "
"many people and nations to which she had never had any relation has shown "
"her that one does not need to belong to a particular ethnicity or culture to "
"care about it.\n"
"\n"
"From a playful girl, Tenma has matured into brave woman; and from a brash "
"peasant, she has grown into a powerful mage and leader. Now, if she once "
"followed a prophecy, Tenma now follows her heart, and she will do everything "
"in her power to protect not only Kodakuni and the Sogen, but Irdya and all "
"its inhabitants."
msgstr ""
"Tenma Yozora nació en la pequeña aldea sogen de Kuroi; sus padres, Yusuke y "
"Motoko, murieron durante la invasión de Wesnoth a Kodakuni, y desde entonces "
"ha sido criada por sus compañeros aldeanos, aunque fue adoptada de manera no "
"oficial por Natsu, una antigua sacerdotisa que era la amiga más cercana de "
"Motoko. Aunque su comportamiento habitual es juguetón e infantil, tiene un "
"espíritu tan fuerte y valiente como el de cualquier guerrero, aunque su "
"impulsividad es su mayor defecto.\n"
"\n"
"Tras despertar poderes que nunca soñó poseer, partió de su aldea con el "
"objetivo de perfeccionar sus habilidades para poder liberar a su país. Sin "
"embargo, su viaje le ha mostrado un mundo mucho más vasto que en sus sueños "
"más locos, llevándola a conocer una diversidad de personas y amigos; aunque "
"siempre estará preocupada por Kodakuni, luchar por tantas personas y "
"naciones con las que nunca tuvo relación le ha mostrado que no es necesario "
"pertenecer a una etnia o cultura particular para preocuparse por ellas.\n"
"\n"
"De niña juguetona, Tenma ha madurado en una mujer valiente; y de campesina "
"impulsiva, ha crecido hasta convertirse en una poderosa maga y líder. Ahora, "
"si alguna vez siguió una profecía, Tenma sigue su corazón, y hará todo lo "
"que esté en su poder para proteger no solo a Kodakuni y a los Sogen, sino a "
"Irdya y a todos sus habitantes."

#. [unit_type], id=Tenma_Dummy, race=sogen, gender=female
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/Tenma_Farmer.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Tenma Yozora was born in the small Sogen village of Kuroi; her parents, "
"Yusuke and Motoko, died during Wesnoth's invasion of Kodakuni, and she has "
"been raised by her fellow villagers ever since, though she was unoficially "
"adopted by Natsu, a former priestess who was Motoko's closest friend. Albeit "
"her usual demeanour is playful and childish, she has a spirit as strong and "
"courageous as that of any warrior, though her brashness is her greatest flaw."
msgstr ""
"Tenma Yozora nació en la pequeña aldea sogen de Kuroi; sus padres, Yusuke y "
"Motoko, murieron durante la invasión de Wesnoth a Kodakuni, y desde entonces "
"ha sido criada por sus compañeros aldeanos, aunque fue adoptada de manera no "
"oficial por Natsu, una antigua sacerdotisa que era la amiga más cercana de "
"Motoko. Aunque su comportamiento habitual es juguetón e infantil, tiene un "
"espíritu tan fuerte y valiente como el de cualquier guerrero, aunque su "
"impulsividad es su mayor defecto."

#. [unit_type], id=Udhark, race=troll
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/Udhark.cfg:4
msgid "Troll Chieftain"
msgstr "Jefe trol"

#. [unit_type], id=Udhark, race=troll
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/Udhark.cfg:25
msgid ""
"Legends from the Northlands tell of trolls who possess a level of power, "
"skill and cunning that is unusual for their race. With a strength that can "
"literally crack open large rocks, a control of fire magic that rivals even "
"the highest human mages and a intelligence for leading and learning that is "
"matchless amongst their brethren, such trolls become natural leaders amongst "
"their people. Nevertheless, few such trolls are born over the centuries - "
"which is fortunate for the other dwellers of the Northlands."
msgstr ""
"Las leyendas de las Tierras del Norte hablan de trolls que poseen un nivel "
"de poder, habilidad y astucia inusual para su raza. Con una fuerza que puede "
"literalmente romper grandes rocas, un control de la magia de fuego que "
"rivaliza incluso con los magos humanos más altos y una inteligencia para "
"liderar y aprender que no tiene igual entre sus hermanos, tales trolls se "
"convierten en líderes naturales entre su pueblo. Sin embargo, pocos trolls "
"de este tipo nacen a lo largo de los siglos —lo cual es afortunado para los "
"demás habitantes de las Tierras del Norte."

