#. [unit_type], id=Dragana, race=baryag, gender=female
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/baryags/Battle_Queen.cfg:4
msgid "female^Battle Queen"
msgstr "Reina de Batalla"

#. [unit_type], id=Dragana, race=baryag, gender=female
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/baryags/Battle_Queen.cfg:24
msgid ""
"The Battle Queen of the Baryags, Dragana Vasilya, is widely known even "
"outside the Emerald Plains - something which few of her predecessors can "
"boast. And the reasons are many: her fierce beauty, which has attracted the "
"interest of many lords of the Northlands; her outstanding skill with the "
"sword; and her many deeds, the greatest of which are easily the union of the "
"warring Baryag clans and the defeat of the massive orcish horde of Red-Eye "
"Bork, which threated the entire North. But she still strives to achieve her "
"greatest deed: to build a solid and fruitful alliance between the Baryags "
"and neighbouring peoples. For she knows that, in an age where two suns "
"scorch the earth and people grow ambitious beyond measure, those who don't "
"wish to drown in the imminent chaos must unite."
msgstr ""
"La Reina de Batalla de los Baryags, Dragana Vasilya, es ampliamente conocida "
"incluso fuera de las Llanuras Esmeralda —algo de lo que pocos de sus "
"predecesores pueden jactarse. Y las razones son muchas: su feroz belleza, "
"que ha atraído el interés de muchos señores de las Tierras del Norte; su "
"destacada habilidad con la espada; y sus numerosas hazañas, las mayores de "
"las cuales son fácilmente la unión de los clanes baryag en guerra y la "
"derrota de la masiva horda orca de Ojo Rojo Bork, que amenazó a todo el "
"Norte. Pero aún se esfuerza por lograr su mayor hazaña: construir una "
"alianza sólida y fructífera entre los Baryags y los pueblos vecinos. Pues "
"sabe que, en una era en que dos soles abrasan la tierra y las personas "
"crecen ambiciosas sin medida, quienes no deseen ahogarse en el caos "
"inminente deben unirse."

