#. [unit_type], id=Queensguard, race=baryag, gender=female
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/baryags/Queensguard.cfg:20
msgid ""
"Handpicked and trained by Queen Dragana Vasilya herself, these warrior women "
"may not have the brute strength of their male counterparts, but they are "
"clever and fierce fighters, and will disdain even their own life if it means "
"protecting their queen."
msgstr ""
"Seleccionadas y entrenadas personalmente por la Reina Dragana Vasilya, estas "
"mujeres guerreras pueden no tener la fuerza bruta de sus contrapartes "
"masculinas, pero son luchadoras astutas y feroces, y desdeñarán incluso su "
"propia vida si eso significa proteger a su reina."

