#. [unit_type], id=Black Elf Shaman, race=blackelf, gender=female
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/black-elves/Black_Shaman.cfg:5
msgid "female^Black Shaman"
msgstr "Chamán Negro"

#. [unit_type], id=Black Elf Shaman, race=blackelf, gender=female
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/black-elves/Black_Shaman.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Of all classes in elvish society, the one most affected by their migration "
"into the underground was probably that of the shamans. Though their power "
"does not depend on the presence of vegetation, they felt much more at ease "
"amidst leafy forests and green pastures; once in the dark, damp caves, "
"however, they were in as alien a world as they could possibly be, and that "
"ultimately affected even their own connected to the faerie.\n"
"\n"
"Nevertheless, the presence of nature persists even in the rocky underground, "
"and shamans have learned to use its energy to their own use; and, while "
"traditional shamans use the power of the forest to contain their foes, Black "
"Elf shamans use the cold of the caves to freeze to death anyone foolish "
"enough to approach them."
msgstr ""
"De todas las clases en la sociedad élfica, la más afectada por su migración "
"al subsuelo probablemente fue la de los chamanes. Aunque su poder no depende "
"de la presencia de vegetación, se sentían mucho más a gusto entre bosques "
"frondosos y pastos verdes; una vez en las cuevas oscuras y húmedas, sin "
"embargo, estaban en un mundo tan ajeno como podían estar, y eso finalmente "
"afectó incluso su propia conexión con el feérico.\n"
"\n"
"Sin embargo, la presencia de la naturaleza persiste incluso en el subsuelo "
"rocoso, y los chamanes han aprendido a usar su energía para su propio "
"beneficio; y, mientras los chamanes tradicionales usan el poder del bosque "
"para contener a sus enemigos, los chamanes elfos negros usan el frío de las "
"cuevas para congelar hasta la muerte a cualquiera lo suficientemente tonto "
"como para acercarse a ellos."

#. [attack], type=cold, range=ranged
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/black-elves/Black_Shaman.cfg:36
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/black-elves/Black_Sylph.cfg:84
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/black-elves/Caster.cfg:38
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/black-elves/Witch.cfg:40
msgid "underground chill"
msgstr "frío subterráneo"

#. [unit_type], id=Black Elf Sylph, race=blackelf, gender=female
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/black-elves/Black_Sylph.cfg:4
msgid "Black Sylph"
msgstr "Sílfide Negra"

#. [unit_type], id=Black Elf Sylph, race=blackelf, gender=female
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/black-elves/Black_Sylph.cfg:18
msgid ""
"The path of Black-Elf shamans has always been a difficult one: beside never "
"being able to fully connect to their faerie nature, they have to endure the "
"suspicion that most black-elves feel for them. Furthermore, they have to "
"endure the criticism of those who believe that they are 'failed shamans', as "
"they will never achieve their full potential. Finally, there is the fact "
"that they seldom have friends, even amongst themselves. All of this often "
"hinders the shamans' own development, and consequently many of them never go "
"past the level of a witch or a caster.\n"
"\n"
"Nonetheless, there are those who embrace themselves and their power as they "
"are, feeling no shame of anything - be it their aggressiveness, their "
"passion or the dark nature of their spells. Unimpeded by personal scruples, "
"they develop their own power to its peak, assuming the title of 'Sylphs' in "
"defiance to those who consider them as failures. Indeed, the sight of a "
"Black Sylph on a battlefield, keeping her allies alive at the same time she "
"ensorcels and slays her foes with cold blasts and polearms, is enough to "
"make anyone reconsider viewing them as inferior to forest Sylphs."
msgstr ""
"El camino de los chamanes elfos negros siempre ha sido difícil: además de "
"nunca poder conectarse completamente con su naturaleza feérica, tienen que "
"soportar la sospecha que la mayoría de los elfos negros sienten por ellos. "
"Además, deben soportar la crítica de aquellos que creen que son «chamanes "
"fallidos», ya que nunca alcanzarán su pleno potencial. Finalmente, está el "
"hecho de que rara vez tienen amigos, incluso entre ellos mismos. Todo esto a "
"menudo obstaculiza el propio desarrollo de los chamanes, y en consecuencia "
"muchos de ellos nunca pasan del nivel de bruja o lanzadora.\n"
"\n"
"Sin embargo, hay quienes se abrazan a sí mismos y a su poder tal como son, "
"sin sentir vergüenza por nada —sea su agresividad, su pasión o la naturaleza "
"oscura de sus hechizos. Sin impedimentos por escrúpulos personales, "
"desarrollan su propio poder hasta su máximo, asumiendo el título de "
"«Sílfides» en desafío a quienes los consideran fracasos. En efecto, la "
"visión de una Sílfide Negra en un campo de batalla, manteniendo vivos a sus "
"aliados al mismo tiempo que encanta y mata a sus enemigos con ráfagas de "
"frío y armas de asta, es suficiente para hacer que cualquiera reconsidere "
"verlas como inferiores a las Sílfides del bosque."

