#. [unit_type], id=Black Elf Caster, race=blackelf, gender=female
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/black-elves/Caster.cfg:5
msgid "female^Caster"
msgstr "Lanzadora"

#. [unit_type], id=Black Elf Caster, race=blackelf, gender=female
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/black-elves/Caster.cfg:21
msgid ""
"It is well-known amongst black-elves that shamans, with their high "
"sensitivity to the world around them, have never managed to adapt well to "
"the underground world; still, only those who walk this path understand just "
"how far that environment affects them. While forest shamans, if properly "
"evolved, become radiant and kind Shydes, the most powerful and skilled Black-"
"Elf shamans will become darkner and more callous as they try to fathom and "
"embrace that dark and harsh world which their ancestors have chosen as their "
"home. This takes them further away from the faerie world, but it also "
"enables them to unlock new, mysterious powers with which they can drive even "
"the bravest of warriors to madness."
msgstr ""
"Es bien sabido entre los elfos negros que los chamanes, con su alta "
"sensibilidad al mundo que los rodea, nunca han logrado adaptarse bien al "
"mundo subterráneo; aun así, solo quienes recorren este camino entienden cuán "
"lejos afecta ese entorno. Mientras los chamanes del bosque, si evolucionan "
"adecuadamente, se convierten en Shydes radiantes y bondadosas, los chamanes "
"elfos negros más poderosos y hábiles se vuelven más oscuros y fríos a medida "
"que intentan comprender y abrazar ese mundo oscuro y duro que sus ancestros "
"eligieron como hogar. Esto los aleja aún más del mundo feérico, pero también "
"les permite desbloquear nuevos y misteriosos poderes con los que pueden "
"llevar incluso al guerrero más valiente a la locura."

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/black-elves/Caster.cfg:30
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/maatkarians/MaatKarian_Aaneb.cfg:51
