#. [unit_type], id=Black Elf Crossbowman, race=blackelf
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/black-elves/Crossbowman.cfg:5
msgid "Crossbowman"
msgstr "Ballestero"

#. [unit_type], id=Black Elf Crossbowman, race=blackelf
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/black-elves/Crossbowman.cfg:18
msgid ""
"One of the main challenges of the first cave elves concerned the maintenance "
"of their weapons, namely the bow; that was due to the fact that the humidity "
"of the underground easily damaged both the bow and its string, also making "
"way for the proliferation of fungi. Furthermore, the dwellers of the "
"underground, tough and hard-skinned as their were, proved to be very "
"resistant to even the sharpest elvish arrows.\n"
"\n"
"Many elves were against abandoning their most traditional weapon for the "
"'brutish' crossbows, but even they acknowledged the advantages of those new "
"weapons when they first saw a dwarvish lord's armour failing to protect its "
"wearer against a well-shot crossbow bolt."
msgstr ""
"Uno de los principales desafíos de los primeros elfos de cueva concernió el "
"mantenimiento de sus armas, principalmente el arco; esto se debía a que la "
"humedad del subsuelo dañaba fácilmente tanto el arco como su cuerda, además "
"de favorecer la proliferación de hongos. Además, los habitantes del "
"subsuelo, duros y de piel gruesa como eran, demostraron ser muy resistentes "
"incluso a las flechas élficas más afiladas.\n"
"\n"
"Muchos elfos se opusieron a abandonar su arma más tradicional por las "
"«brutales» ballestas, pero incluso ellos reconocieron las ventajas de esas "
"nuevas armas cuando vieron por primera vez la armadura de un señor enano "
"fallar en proteger a su portador contra un virote de ballesta bien disparado."

