#. [unit_type], id=King in the Woods, race=elf
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/irdya-kings/King_In_The_Woods.cfg:4
msgid "King-in-the-Woods"
msgstr "Rey-en-el-Bosque"

#. [unit_type], id=King in the Woods, race=elf
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/irdya-kings/King_In_The_Woods.cfg:18
msgid ""
"In ancient times, little after the Great Awakening of the elves, a lord rose "
"amongst them who had not only great wisdom, but a greater connection to the "
"faerie plane than any of his folk - a connection which gave him access to "
"powers both incredible and dreadful. His descendants, spread throughout "
"elvenkind, inherited these powers to some extent; but only one true heir - "
"and, in every generation, there was only one - would be able to materialize "
"the full power of the faerie plane into the mortal world. This heir will not "
"come from any particular bloodline; he may be born in any elvish family "
"anywhere in the continent, and it's up to the High Lords to locate and find "
"him, and make sure he grows into the wise and powerful ruler he's destined "
"to become. This is how the King-in-the-Woods, the supreme lord of all elves "
"in the world, is chosen."
msgstr ""
"En tiempos antiguos, poco después del Gran Despertar de los elfos, surgió "
"entre ellos un señor que no solo tenía gran sabiduría, sino una conexión aún "
"mayor con el plano feérico que cualquiera de su pueblo —una conexión que le "
"daba acceso a poderes tanto increíbles como temibles. Sus descendientes, "
"dispersos por toda la elkind, heredaron estos poderes en cierta medida; pero "
"solo un verdadero heredero —y en cada generación había solo uno— sería capaz "
"de materializar el poder completo del plano feérico en el mundo mortal. Este "
"heredero no vendrá de ninguna línea de sangre en particular; puede nacer en "
"cualquier familia élfica en cualquier parte del continente, y corresponde a "
"los Altos Señores localizarlo y encontrarlo, y asegurarse de que crezca "
"hasta convertirse en el gobernante sabio y poderoso que está destinado a "
"ser. Así es como se elige al Rey-en-el-Bosque, el señor supremo de todos los "
"elfos del mundo."

#. [attack], type=arcane, range=ranged
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/irdya-kings/King_In_The_Woods.cfg:49
msgid "faerie fire"
msgstr "fuego feérico"

