#. [unit_type], id=Soul_Veela, race=undead
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/souls/Soul.cfg:21
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/souls/Soul_Addraryn.cfg:21
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/souls/Soul_Aegaion.cfg:21
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/souls/Soul_Akhen.cfg:21
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/souls/Soul_Ashura.cfg:21
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/souls/Soul_Assix.cfg:21
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/souls/Soul_Jevyan.cfg:21
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/souls/Soul_Maat.cfg:21
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/souls/Soul_Raihien.cfg:21
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/souls/Soul_Ravanal.cfg:21
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/souls/Soul_Varthan.cfg:21
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/souls/Soul_Veela.cfg:21
msgid ""
"When someone dies, his or her soul returns to the Land of the Dead; once "
"there, it will plunge into the Wailing River and be renewed for its next "
"incarnation. However, for such thing to happen, the soul must be at peace; "
"but in a world of war and conflict, there are many who go to the world of "
"the dead with their souls taken by strong feelings, such as anger or "
"regretfulness. Such souls avoid the Wailing River, and begin to roam the "
"realm of Death in a vain search for a way back to the Living World. Unlike "
"ghosts - which are spirits bound and reshaped by dark magic - these lost "
"souls are made of pure soul essence; albeit not as strong as the "
"Necromancers' creations, they could pose great danger to any living soul "
"that dares to enter their world."
msgstr ""
"Cuando alguien muere, su alma regresa a la Tierra de los Muertos; una vez "
"allí, se sumerge en el Río del Lamento y se renueva para su próxima "
"encarnación. Sin embargo, para que eso ocurra, el alma debe estar en paz; "
"pero en un mundo de guerra y conflicto, hay muchos que van al mundo de los "
"muertos con sus almas tomadas por fuertes sentimientos, como ira o "
"remordimiento. Tales almas evitan el Río del Lamento y comienzan a vagar por "
"el reino de la Muerte en una vana búsqueda de un camino de regreso al Mundo "
"de los Vivos. A diferencia de los fantasmas —que son espíritus atados y "
"remodelados por magia oscura—, estas almas perdidas están hechas de esencia "
"de alma pura; aunque no tan fuertes como las creaciones de los Nigromantes, "
"podrían representar un gran peligro para cualquier alma viva que se atreva a "
"entrar en su mundo."

