#. [unit_type], id=Anuran Rider, race=woodlander
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/woodlanders/Anuran_Rider.cfg:5
msgid "Anuran Rider"
msgstr "Jinete Anuro"

#. [unit_type], id=Anuran Rider, race=woodlander
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/woodlanders/Anuran_Rider.cfg:20
msgid ""
"Once the amphibious creature has grown, the owner is able to mount it. The "
"amphibian or anuran can slap enemies with its tongue, stunning them in the "
"process. The stunning effect of the tongue combined with the elfin's "
"accuracy with javelins, makes these riders a force to be reckoned with."
msgstr ""
"Una vez que la criatura anfibia ha crecido, su dueño puede montarla. El "
"anfibio o anuro puede golpear a los enemigos con su lengua, aturdiéndolos en "
"el proceso. El efecto aturdidor de la lengua combinado con la precisión del "
"elfo con jabalinas hace que estos jinetes sean una fuerza a tener en cuenta."

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/woodlanders/Anuran_Rider.cfg:39
msgid "tongue"
msgstr "lengua"

#. [unit_type], id=Elfin, race=woodlander, gender=male
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/woodlanders/Elfin.cfg:5
msgid "Elfin"
msgstr "Elfin"

#. [unit_type], id=Elfin, race=woodlander, gender=male
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/woodlanders/Elfin.cfg:20
msgid ""
"Elfins are mischievous creatures found only in the deepest forests. They are "
"called such, by travelers, due to the crude resemblance to the elves they "
"exhibit. Nimble and armed with torches, these beings are hard to hit, but "
"can be injured severely due to their lack of armor. Every Elfins also "
"carries a young rodent along with him, until the rodent grows big enough to "
"be mounted."
msgstr ""
"Los elfins son criaturas traviesas que solo se encuentran en los bosques más "
"profundos. Los viajeros los llaman así debido al parecido crudo que exhiben "
"con los elfos. Ágiles y armados con antorchas, estos seres son difíciles de "
"alcanzar, pero pueden ser gravemente heridos debido a su falta de armadura. "
"Cada elfin también lleva consigo un roedor joven hasta que este crece lo "
"suficiente para ser montado."

#. [unit_type], id=Faun Captain, race=woodlander, gender=male
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/woodlanders/Faun_Captain.cfg:5
msgid "Faun Captain"
msgstr "Capitán Fauno"

#. [unit_type], id=Faun Captain, race=woodlander, gender=male
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/woodlanders/Faun_Captain.cfg:28
msgid ""
"Fauns are sometimes chosen to lead their kind to battle. Such fauns forgo "
"their bows, take the sword and shield and can either slash enemies or bash "
"them. The presence of a captain in faun hunting or war parties inspires the "
"younger fauns to fight with more skill and dexterously."
msgstr ""
"Los faunos a veces son elegidos para liderar a los suyos en batalla. Tales "
"faunos renuncian a sus arcos, toman espada y escudo y pueden tanto cortar "
"como golpear a los enemigos. La presencia de un capitán en partidas de caza "
"o guerra faunas inspira a los faunos más jóvenes a luchar con más habilidad "
"y destreza."

#. [attack], type=impact, range=melee
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/woodlanders/Faun_Captain.cfg:109
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/woodlanders/Faun_Lord.cfg:60
msgid "shield"
msgstr "escudazo"

#. [unit_type], id=Faun Lord, race=woodlander, gender=male
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/woodlanders/Faun_Lord.cfg:5
msgid "Faun Lord"
msgstr "Señor Fauno"

#. [unit_type], id=Faun Lord, race=woodlander, gender=male
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/woodlanders/Faun_Lord.cfg:29
msgid ""
"Fauns who have gained the title of 'Lord,' are truly born leaders. Leading "
"armies of forest dwellers, these commanders can give enemies a pain to "
"counteract the mastermind strategy devised. Improving on their sword and "
"shield combination, these warriors can take down most foes with ease."
msgstr ""
"Los faunos que han ganado el título de «Señor» son verdaderos líderes natos. "
"Liderando ejércitos de habitantes del bosque, estos comandantes pueden "
"causar dolor a los enemigos para contrarrestar la estrategia maestra ideada. "
"Mejorando su combinación de espada y escudo, estos guerreros pueden derribar "
"a la mayoría de los enemigos con facilidad."

#. [unit_type], id=Faun Marksman, race=woodlander, gender=male
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/woodlanders/Faun_Marksman.cfg:5
msgid "Faun Marksman"
msgstr "Tirador Fauno"

#. [unit_type], id=Faun Marksman, race=woodlander, gender=male
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/woodlanders/Faun_Marksman.cfg:21
msgid ""
"Fauns, after lots and lots of practice and improve greatly in their bows. "
"Such skill allows them to accurately hit targets far away."
msgstr ""
"Los faunos, tras mucha práctica, mejoran enormemente en sus arcos. Tal "
"habilidad les permite acertar con precisión a objetivos lejanos."

#. [attack], type=pierce, range=melee
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/woodlanders/Faun_Marksman.cfg:68
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/woodlanders/Faun_Sharpshooter.cfg:67
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/woodlanders/Faun_Soldier.cfg:68
msgid "horns"
msgstr "cuernos"

#. [unit_type], id=Faun Sharpshooter, race=woodlander, gender=male
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/woodlanders/Faun_Sharpshooter.cfg:5
msgid "Faun Sharpshooter"
msgstr "Francotirador Fauno"

#. [unit_type], id=Faun Sharpshooter, race=woodlander, gender=male
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/woodlanders/Faun_Sharpshooter.cfg:22
msgid ""
"Fauns have tried to precede the elves in their archery skills, but they have "
"failed to do so. Instead they decide to use more weapons in their arsenal. "
"The result is a master archer with deadly arrows and a few darts containing "
"a mixture of the most venomous toxins the forest has to offer. This arsenal "
"of weapons and the ability of these fauns to move quickly throw the forest, "
"make them skilled assassins. If you ever encounter one of these master "
"killers, then run or prepare to take an arrow throw the heart."
msgstr ""
"Los faunos han intentado superar a los elfos en sus habilidades de arquería, "
"pero han fallado en hacerlo. En cambio decidieron usar más armas en su "
"arsenal. El resultado es un maestro arquero con flechas letales y algunos "
"dardos que contienen una mezcla de las toxinas más venenosas que el bosque "
"tiene para ofrecer. Este arsenal de armas y la capacidad de estos faunos "
"para moverse rápidamente a través del bosque los convierten en asesinos "
"hábiles. Si alguna vez te encuentras con uno de estos maestros asesinos, "
"entonces corre o prepárate para recibir una flecha en el corazón."

#. [attack], type=pierce, range=ranged
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/woodlanders/Faun_Sharpshooter.cfg:103
msgid "blowgun"
msgstr "cerbatana"

#. [unit_type], id=Faun Soldier, race=woodlander, gender=male
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/woodlanders/Faun_Soldier.cfg:5
msgid "Faun Soldier"
msgstr "Soldado Fauno"

#. [unit_type], id=Faun Soldier, race=woodlander, gender=male
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/woodlanders/Faun_Soldier.cfg:21
msgid ""
"Fauns are mythical creatures, only seen by other forest dwellers. Having the "
"legs and horns of a goat, they can ram foes and move at a remarkable pace. "
"They are also very dexterous with their bows."
msgstr ""
"Los faunos son criaturas míticas, solo vistas por otros habitantes del "
"bosque. Teniendo las piernas y cuernos de una cabra, pueden embestir a los "
"enemigos y moverse a un ritmo notable. También son muy diestros con sus "
"arcos."

#. [unit_type], id=Rodent Knight, race=woodlander
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/woodlanders/Rodent_Knight.cfg:5
msgid "Rodent Knight"
msgstr "Caballero Roedor"

#. [unit_type], id=Rodent Knight, race=woodlander
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/woodlanders/Rodent_Knight.cfg:20
msgid ""
"Elfins who have earned the title of 'Knight,' are respected in the elfin "
"society for their courage and valor. They have incredibly fast mounts and "
"can dodge around the battlefield, piercing through flanks of the enemy. The "
"riders themselves have a good aim at throwing spears and finishing off "
"injured enemies."
msgstr ""
"Los elfins que han ganado el título de «Caballero» son respetados en la "
"sociedad elfin por su coraje y valor. Tienen monturas increíblemente rápidas "
"y pueden esquivar por el campo de batalla, atravesando los flancos del "
"enemigo. Los propios jinetes tienen buena puntería al lanzar lanzas y "
"rematar a enemigos heridos."

#. [attack], type=blade, range=melee
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/woodlanders/Rodent_Knight.cfg:43
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/woodlanders/Rodent_Predator.cfg:39
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/woodlanders/Rodent_Rider.cfg:38
msgid "fangs"
msgstr "colmillos"

#. [unit_type], id=Rodent Predator, race=woodlander
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/woodlanders/Rodent_Predator.cfg:5
msgid "Rodent Predator"
msgstr "Depredador Roedor"

#. [unit_type], id=Rodent Predator, race=woodlander
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/woodlanders/Rodent_Predator.cfg:20
msgid ""
"Some elfins undertake the task of riding the 'Shadow Rats'. These are "
"aggressive black rats raised in the wild and cannot be tamed easily. Elfins, "
"who have managed to tame them, ride these beasts with pride and are known to "
"strike in the night."
msgstr ""
"Algunos elfins emprenden la tarea de montar las «Ratas Sombra». Estas son "
"ratas negras agresivas criadas en la naturaleza y no pueden ser domesticadas "
"fácilmente. Los elfins que han logrado domarlas montan estas bestias con "
"orgullo y se les conoce por atacar en la noche."

#. [unit_type], id=Rodent Rider, race=woodlander
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/woodlanders/Rodent_Rider.cfg:5
msgid "Rodent Rider"
msgstr "Jinete Roedor"

#. [unit_type], id=Rodent Rider, race=woodlander
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/woodlanders/Rodent_Rider.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Once the rodent has grown, the elfins mount and ride them. These large rat-"
"like beasts are very fast and quick to dodge enemies, and their riders have "
"an impressive accuracy in throwing spears."
msgstr ""
"Una vez que el roedor ha crecido, los elfins lo montan y cabalgan. Estas "
"grandes bestias parecidas a ratas son muy rápidas y ágiles para esquivar "
"enemigos, y sus jinetes tienen una precisión impresionante al lanzar lanzas."

#. [unit_type], id=Swamp Elfin, race=woodlander, gender=male
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/woodlanders/Swamp_Elfin.cfg:5
msgid "Swamp Elfin"
msgstr "Elfin del Pantano"

#. [unit_type], id=Swamp Elfin, race=woodlander, gender=male
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/units/woodlanders/Swamp_Elfin.cfg:20
msgid ""
"The Swamp Elfins differ in a variety of ways from their dry land counter "
"parts. They are good swimmers and raise amphibious creatures instead of "
"rodents. They prefer to use a spear in melee and have a good aim at throwing "
"javelins as well."
msgstr ""
"Los elfins del pantano difieren de muchas maneras de sus contrapartes de "
"tierra firme. Son buenos nadadores y crían criaturas anfibias en lugar de "
"roedores. Prefieren usar una lanza en cuerpo a cuerpo y también tienen buena "
"puntería al lanzar jabalinas."

#. [regenerate], id=healing
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:14
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:16
msgid "earth and forest recuperation"
msgstr "recuperación de tierra y bosque"

#. [regenerate], id=healing
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:15
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:17
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:19
msgid ""
"This unit will repair its body with the rocks and the plants found on "
"forested, mountainous or hilly terrain, recovering 10 hp in the process."
msgstr ""
"Esta unidad reparará su cuerpo con las rocas y plantas encontradas en "
"terreno boscoso, montañoso o colinoso, recuperando 10 PV en el proceso."

#. [regenerate], id=healing
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:32
msgid "fire renewal"
msgstr "renovación de fuego"

#. [regenerate], id=healing
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:33
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:35
msgid ""
"This unit will burn brighter whenever it is on or floating above lava, thus "
"recovering 10 HP. It will also absorb heat from other warm terrain like sand."
msgstr ""
"Esta unidad arderá más intensamente cuando esté sobre o flotando sobre lava, "
"recuperando así 10 PV. También absorberá calor de otros terrenos cálidos "
"como la arena."

#. [regenerate], id=healing
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:49
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:63
msgid "water regeneration"
msgstr "regeneración acuática"

#. [regenerate], id=healing
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:50
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:52
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:64
msgid ""
"This unit will use nearby water - such as from pure water, swamps and even "
"mud and blood pools to replenish itself. In water and swamps, it will "
"recover 10 hp, whilst in mud and blood pools, it will recover only 4 hp."
msgstr ""
"Esta unidad usará el agua cercana —como de agua pura, pantanos e incluso "
"charcos de lodo y sangre— para reponerse. En agua y pantanos recuperará 10 "
"PV, mientras que en charcos de lodo y sangre solo recuperará 4 PV."

#. [leadership], id=nature_master
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:76
msgid "nature master"
msgstr "maestro de la naturaleza"

#. [leadership], id=nature_master
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:77
msgid "female^nature master"
msgstr "maestra de la naturaleza"

#. [leadership], id=nature_master
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:78
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:90
msgid ""
"This unit's high connection to nature makes elemental and true elemental "
"units stronger."
msgstr ""
"La alta conexión de esta unidad con la naturaleza hace más fuertes a las "
"unidades elementales y elementales verdaderas."

#. [illuminates], id=obscure
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:166
msgid "obscures"
msgstr "oscurece"

#. [illuminates], id=obscure
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:167
msgid "female^obscures"
msgstr "oscurece"

#. [illuminates], id=obscure
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:168
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:172
msgid ""
"This unit darkens the surrounding area, making chaotic units fight better, "
"and lawful units fight worse.\n"
"\n"
"Any units adjacent to this unit will fight as if it were dusk when it is "
"day, and as if it were night when it is dusk."
msgstr ""
"Esta unidad oscurece el área circundante, haciendo que las unidades caóticas "
"luchen mejor y las legales luchen peor.\n"
"\n"
"Cualquier unidad adyacente a esta luchará como si fuera atardecer cuando es "
"de día, y como si fuera noche cuando es atardecer."

#. [leadership], id=terror
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:193
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:226
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:273
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:334
msgid ""
" This unit can frighten enemy units that are next to it, making them fight "
"worse."
msgstr ""
"Esta unidad puede asustar a las unidades enemigas que estén a su lado, "
"haciéndolas luchar peor."

#. [abilities]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:395
msgid "terror"
msgstr "terror"

#. [abilities]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:396
msgid ""
"This unit can frighten enemy units that are next to it, making them fight "
"worse.\n"
"\n"
"Adjacent enemy units of lower level will do less damage in battle. When an "
"enemy unit of the same or lower level is adjacent and engages in combat, its "
"attacks do 15% less damage times the difference in their levels + 15%."
msgstr ""
"Esta unidad puede asustar a las unidades enemigas que estén a su lado, "
"haciendo que luchen peor.\n"
"\n"
"Las unidades enemigas adyacentes de nivel inferior infligirán menos daño en "
"batalla. Cuando una unidad enemiga del mismo nivel o inferior esté adyacente "
"y entre en combate, sus ataques infligen un 15 % menos de daño por cada "
"diferencia de nivel + 15 %."

#. [leadership], id=heroic_terror
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:406
msgid "heroic terror"
msgstr "terror heroico"

#. [leadership], id=heroic_terror
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:407
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:419
msgid ""
"As they remember the legends surrounding this unit's prowess in battle, the "
"enemies fight worse as they're near it.\n"
"\n"
"Adjacent enemy units of levels 0 to 5 will do less damage in battle, though "
"those of higher levels will suffer a lesser decrease in power."
msgstr ""
"Al recordar las leyendas sobre la destreza en batalla de esta unidad, los "
"enemigos luchan peor cuando están cerca de ella.\n"
"\n"
"Las unidades enemigas adyacentes de niveles 0 a 5 harán menos daño en "
"combate, aunque las de niveles superiores sufrirán una disminución menor en "
"su poder."

#. [leadership], id=heroic_spirit
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:501
msgid "heroic spirit"
msgstr "espíritu heroico"

#. [leadership], id=heroic_spirit
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:502
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:514
msgid ""
"As they remember the legends surrounding this unit's prowess in battle, "
"allies feel inspired to give their full in battle.\n"
"\n"
"Adjacent units of the same side, from levels 0 to 5, will do more damage in "
"battle, though those of higher levels will suffer a lesser increase in power."
msgstr ""
"Al recordar las leyendas sobre la destreza en batalla de esta unidad, los "
"aliados se sienten inspirados a darlo todo en combate.\n"
"\n"
"Las unidades aliadas adyacentes de niveles 0 a 5 harán más daño en combate, "
"aunque las de niveles superiores sufrirán un aumento menor en su poder."

#. [heals], id=asphyxiate
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:596
msgid "asphyxiate"
msgstr "asfixiar"

#. [heals], id=asphyxiate
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:597
msgid "female^asphyxiate"
msgstr "asfixiar"

#. [heals], id=asphyxiate
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:598
msgid ""
"The heavy, humid atmosphere surrounding this unit asphyxiates enemy units "
"that are not used to breathing underwater, reducing their hp in 8"
msgstr ""
"La atmósfera pesada y húmeda que rodea a esta unidad asfixia a las unidades "
"enemigas que no están acostumbradas a respirar bajo el agua, reduciendo sus "
"PV en 8"

#. [heals], id=asphyxiate
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:629
msgid ""
"The heavy, humid atmosphere surrounding this unit asphyxiates enemy units "
"that are not used to breathing underwater, reducing their hp in 5."
msgstr ""
"La atmósfera pesada y húmeda que rodea a esta unidad asfixia a las unidades "
"enemigas que no están acostumbradas a respirar bajo el agua, reduciendo sus "
"PV en 5."

#. [heals], id=life_flow
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:638
msgid "life flow"
msgstr "flujo vital"

#. [heals], id=life_flow
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:639
msgid "female^life flow"
msgstr "flujo vital"

#. [heals], id=life_flow
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:640
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:646
msgid ""
"The life energy emanating from this unit is so intense that it heals allied "
"units in 30 hp"
msgstr ""
"La energía vital que emana de esta unidad es tan intensa que sana a las "
"unidades aliadas 30 PV"

#. [heals], id=runa_jeran
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:655
msgid "Runa Jeran"
msgstr "Runa Jeran"

#. [heals], id=runa_jeran
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:656
msgid "female^Runa Jeran"
msgstr "Runa Jeran"

#. [heals], id=runa_jeran
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:657
msgid ""
"Allows the unit to heal adjacent allied units at the beginning of our turn.\n"
"\n"
"A unit cared for by this healer may heal up to 10 HP per turn, or stop "
"poison from taking effect for that turn.\n"
"A poisoned unit cannot be cured of its poison by a healer, and must seek the "
"care of a village or a unit that can cure."
msgstr ""
"Permite a la unidad sanar a las unidades aliadas adyacentes al comienzo de "
"nuestro turno.\n"
"\n"
"Una unidad atendida por este sanador puede sanar hasta 10 PV por turno, o "
"detener el efecto del veneno durante ese turno.\n"
"Una unidad envenenada no puede ser curada de su veneno por un sanador y debe "
"buscar el cuidado de una aldea o de una unidad que pueda curar."

#. [heals], id=runa_jeran
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:666
msgid ""
"A unit cared for by this healer may heal up to 10 HP per turn, or stop "
"poison from taking effect for that turn.\n"
"A poisoned unit cannot be cured of its poison by a healer, and must seek the "
"care of a village or a unit that can cure."
msgstr ""
"Una unidad atendida por este sanador puede sanar hasta 10 PV por turno, o "
"detener el efecto del veneno durante ese turno.\n"
"Una unidad envenenada no puede ser curada de su veneno por un sanador y debe "
"buscar el cuidado de una aldea o de una unidad que pueda curar."

#. [resistance], id=runa_othala
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:677
msgid "Runa Othala"
msgstr "Runa Othala"

#. [resistance], id=runa_othala
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:678
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:701
msgid ""
"Adjacent units of level 5 or below from this side receive a +30% bonus to "
"all resistances (up to a maximum of 70%)."
msgstr ""
"Las unidades adyacentes de nivel 5 o inferior de este bando reciben un bono "
"de +30 % a todas las resistencias (hasta un máximo de 70 %)."

#. [dummy], id=shieldwall
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:708
msgid "shieldwall"
msgstr "muro de escudos"

#. [dummy], id=shieldwall
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:709
msgid "female^shieldwall"
msgstr "muro de escudos"

#. [dummy], id=shieldwall
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:710
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:711
msgid ""
"This unit gains a +10% bonus to defense when another unit with the same "
"ability is adjacent to it. However, this cannot raise the unit's defense "
"above 70%."
msgstr ""
"Esta unidad gana un bono de +10 % a la defensa cuando otra unidad con la "
"misma habilidad está adyacente a ella. Sin embargo, esto no puede elevar la "
"defensa de la unidad por encima del 70 %."

#. [regenerate], id=life_force
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:721
msgid "life force"
msgstr "fuerza vital"

#. [regenerate], id=life_force
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:722
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:725
msgid ""
"This unit draws upon the power of Nature, thus recovering its strength and "
"24 hp. Effects of poisoning are nullified as well."
msgstr ""
"Esta unidad recurre al poder de la Naturaleza, recuperando así su fuerza y "
"24 pv. Los efectos del veneno quedan anulados también."

#. [regenerate], id=soul_regeneration
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:733
msgid "soul regeneration"
msgstr "regeneración de alma"

