#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:889
msgid ""
"The divine powers possessing this unit heals it in 30 hp per turn, and also "
"make it virtually immortal."
msgstr ""
"Los poderes divinos que poseen a esta unidad la sanan 30 PV por turno y "
"también la hacen virtualmente inmortal."

#. [teleport], id=sidhe
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/aotds-abilities.cfg:896
