msgstr "refrescado"

#. [lua]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/dehydration-utils.cfg:231
msgid ""
"dehydrated: This unit is dehydrated. It will lose HP and have its damage "
"reduced by 1 each turn during the day unless prevented by healers or cured "
"by water at an oasis.\n"
"\n"
"Units cannot be killed or deal no damage as a result of dehydration."
msgstr ""
"deshidratado: Esta unidad está deshidratada. Perderá PV y su daño se "
"reducirá en 1 cada turno durante el día a menos que sea prevenido por "
"sanadores o curado con agua en un oasis.\n"
"\n"
"Las unidades no pueden morir ni dejar de hacer daño como resultado de la "
"deshidratación."

#. [unstore_unit]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/dehydration-utils.cfg:540
msgid "scorched"
msgstr "abrasado"

#. [lua]
#: Aria_of_the_Dragon_Slayer/utils/dehydration-utils.cfg:627
msgid ""
"scorched: This unit is affected by Aghayu's supernatural heat. It will lose "
"HP and have its damage reduced by 2 every turn during every time of day "
"unless protected by healers.\n"
"\n"
"Units cannot be killed or deal no damage as a result of dehydration."
msgstr ""
"abrasado: Esta unidad está afectada por el calor sobrenatural de Aghayu. "
"Perderá PV y su daño se reducirá en 2 cada turno durante todo el día a menos "
"que sea protegida por sanadores.\n"
"\n"
"Las unidades no pueden morir ni dejar de hacer daño como resultado de la "
"deshidratación."

